NK063(gu)001:1: // sgyu 'phrul gsang snying gi 'grel pa rgyud don rnam nges zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK063(gu)001:3: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi dka' 'grel rgyud don rnam par nges pa zhes bya ba /
NK063(gu)001:4: rang bzhin mngon byas phyogs dus bde gshegs kun gyi ngo bo nyid //
NK063(gu)001:5: zhi dang khro mdzad mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lor rab snang zhing //
NK063(gu)001:6: dbyings phyug kro ti'i tshogs dang gnyis med ston pa sku lnga'i bdag /
NK063(gu)001:7: 'chad pa'i skyes bu gsang 'dzin bcas la gus par phyag 'tshal lo //
NK063(gu)001:8: thogs med blos gros 'dul ba'i thabs ldan tshig gis sdud pa po //
NK063(gu)001:9: lha dbang klu rgyal gnod sbyin ded dpon mi yi rig 'dzin dang //
NK063(gu)001:10: byin rlabs ltas shar 'khor lo'i sgyur rgyal la sogs rim brgyud pa //
NK063(gu)001:11: bla ma rnams te sprul pa'i rgyal tshab mdzad phyir rab tu mos //
NK063(gu)001:12: rin chen dbyig ltar gdul bya'i dgos pa ma lus kun skong zhing //
NK063(gu)001:13: shin tu rnam grol zab cing rgya che shes bya'i gnas rnams la //
NK063(gu)001:14: mkhas dang don gnyis grub pa mkhyen dang brtse ba'i rang bzhin can //
NK063(gu)001:15: dbang sgyur mi mchog khyed zhabs pad mo bdag gis spyi bos len //
NK063(gu)001:16: skul byed khyed yon mang du bsten thos mthus //
NK063(gu)001:17: yongs su shes bya mtshon byed yi ge rgyud //
NK063(gu)001:18: rtogs daka'i blo can rnams la phan don du //
NK063(gu)001:19: snying po don gyi chos srid 'dir brjod bya /
NK063(gu)001:20: 'dir brjod bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud zab cing gting
NK063(gu)001:21: dpag dka' ba thugs kyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi
NK063(gu)001:22: khyab pa / bsgrub par bya ba'i don gyi bcud
NK063(gu)001:23: bsdus pa'i snying po ste theg pa mchog gi 'bras
NK063(gu)001:24: khyab pa / bu / yang dag pa'i don de
NK063(gu)001:25: kho na nyid du gtan la 'bebs par byed pa
NK063(gu)001:27: chos nyid nges par ston pas drang ba'i don las ches rnams par rgyal ba /
NK063(gu)001:28: 'brel zhing tshang bar ston pa'i rgyud kyi rgyal po 'di rnam par bshad na don bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:29: rgyud kyi don spyi'i rnam par gzhag pa bstan pa'i phyir stong thun du bshad pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:30: rgyud kyi don rab tu dbye ba'i phyir dkyus la sa bcad pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:31: de'i don shin tu nges par bya ba'i phyir tshig gi 'bru gnyer ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:32: de dag la gzhan gyis log par brtags te rtsod pa rnams spang ba dang bzhir 'chad do //
NK063(gu)001:33: de yang dang po ni gzhan du shes la /
NK063(gu)001:34: phyi ma gsum thun mong du ston par byed do //
NK063(gu)001:36: rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:37: mtshan de dang ldan pa'i rgyud kyi don dngos so //
NK063(gu)001:39: dbang po rab la ltos te mtshan tsam gyis rgyud kyi don rtogs pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:42: mtshan bsgyur zhing shan sbyar ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:44: mtshan gyi don la rtsod pa spang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:46: spyir mtshan tsam zhig smos pa'i dgos pa ni dbang
NK063(gu)001:47: po rab kyis rgyud don rtogs pa dang 'bring mthas
NK063(gu)001:48: mtshan gyi don la rmongs pa sel ba yin zhing
NK063(gu)001:49: / klad du smos pas yang rab tshegs chung ba
NK063(gu)001:50: dang glegs bam bshad bde ba'i dgos pa yod la
NK063(gu)001:51: / / bod skad dngos su smos pas bod kyis don go ba'i dgos pa yod cing /
NK063(gu)001:52: rgya skad shugs la sbyar bas samskri ta'i skad la
NK063(gu)001:53: bag chags 'jog pa dang sgra'i bye brag shes pas
NK063(gu)001:55: gnyis pa shan sbyar ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:57: gu h+ya gar+b+ha ta th+aa ya hi na zhes pa de /
NK063(gu)001:58: bod skad du gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:59: zhes bya bar gnas pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:60: gsum pa mtshan gyi don bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:61: phyi shes rab grol ba'i lam gyi dbang du bshad pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:62: nang thabs lam steng sgo'i dbang du bshad pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:63: gsang ba 'og sgo'i dbang du bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:65: gsang ba'i zhes pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:69: dang po ni le'u gnyis pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:70: e ma ho ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK063(gu)001:71: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK063(gu)001:72: ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang //
NK063(gu)001:73: gzhan du min las shin tu gsang //
NK063(gu)001:75: gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid rang byung gi ye
NK063(gu)001:76: shes yon tan thams cad lhun gyis grub pa de
NK063(gu)001:77: rang la yod kyang ngo ma shes pa ni ye
NK063(gu)001:78: nas gsang ba'o // de nyid chos thams cad du
NK063(gu)001:79: snang ba'i dngos po ril mi zad pa rgyan gyi
NK063(gu)001:80: 'khor lo'i rgyud du gnas pa yin yang rang gi
NK063(gu)001:81: btags pas bsgribs pa ni rang bzhin gyi gsang ba
NK063(gu)001:82: nas gsang ba'o // yin cing / rang bzhin gyi
NK063(gu)001:83: rgyud de yang yul sems dang rgyu 'bras dang bden
NK063(gu)001:84: pa la sogs pa las ngo bo nyid kyis grol
NK063(gu)001:85: te rang snang ba'i phyir yul du bya bar ma
NK063(gu)001:86: dmigs pa ni ngo bos gsang ba yin la /
NK063(gu)001:87: bsgrub bya 'bras bu'i rgyud de yang sems las gud
NK063(gu)001:88: na med kyang nyon mongs pa dang shes bya la
NK063(gu)001:89: sogs pa'i sgrib pas bsgribs nas gzhan du 'tshol ba
NK063(gu)001:91: rang la gnas kyang rang gi ngo mi shes pa ni shin tu gsang ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:92: de ltar gsang ba bzhi po de rgyu gcig pa
NK063(gu)001:93: ma gtogs pas ye nas gsang ba la sogs rtogs
NK063(gu)001:94: pa bzhi dang yang sbyar zhing /
NK063(gu)001:95: don dam ma gtogs pas ye nas gsang ba la
NK063(gu)001:96: sogs pa bden pa bzhi dang yang sbyar la 'chad
NK063(gu)001:98: gnyis pa sbas pa'i gsang ba la'ang bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:99: gang sbas na spyod pa'i khyad par lnga gsum dang
NK063(gu)001:100: bya ba med pa'i spyod pa la sogs pa lta
NK063(gu)001:101: spyod 'brel bas spyad par gsungs pa de dag sbas
NK063(gu)001:102: / gang la na sngags kyi man ngag med pa dang sgra bzhin spyod pa rnams la sbas /
NK063(gu)001:103: gang gi phyir na de dag gi yul ma yin pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:104: ji skad du rgyas pa las /
NK063(gu)001:105: kha cig lta ba mnyam gnas kyang //
NK063(gu)001:106: spyod pa dag ni yongs mi mnyam //
NK063(gu)001:107: zhes pas man ngag med pa'i yul min la /
NK063(gu)001:108: kha cig spyod pa rdzogs byed kyang //
NK063(gu)001:109: mnyam pa'i lta ba yongs mi gnas //
NK063(gu)001:111: sgra bzhin spyod pa'i yul min pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:113: gsang phyir brda dag sna tshogs gsungs //
NK063(gu)001:114: zhes brdar sbas pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:115: gsum pa gab pa'i gsang ba la'ang bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:116: gang du na rang bzhin rgyud kyi khong du /
NK063(gu)001:117: gang la na las dang po pa'am 'khrul pa can la /
NK063(gu)001:118: gang gab na brjod bya rang bzhin gyi gsang ba snying po'i don no //
NK063(gu)001:119: de gang gis 'byin na lung tshad ma'i bdag po sangs rgyas kyis so //
NK063(gu)001:120: yang na gang du na yi ge'i rgyud kyi khong du /
NK063(gu)001:121: gang la na ras chod mkhan nam snod ngan pa la /
NK063(gu)001:122: gang na mtshon byed yi ge'i rgyud don gsang ba'i snying po 'adi'o //
NK063(gu)001:123: de gang gis 'byin na man ngag tshad ma'i bdag
NK063(gu)001:124: po rdo rje slob dpon gyis 'byin pa yin te
NK063(gu)001:125: / ji skad du le'u bcu gsum pa las /
NK063(gu)001:126: yi ge sgra btags ming tshogs la //
NK063(gu)001:127: brten pa'i tshig gis rab mtshon te //
NK063(gu)001:128: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK063(gu)001:129: ston pa rdo rje'i thugs la gnas //
NK063(gu)001:131: snying po zhes pa la yang gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:132: rgyu'i don gyi snying po dang /
NK063(gu)001:134: bcud 'dus pa'i don gyi snying po'o //
NK063(gu)001:136: rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa las 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:137: gdul bya las tha dad pa'i don rgyud 'di'i byin
NK063(gu)001:138: gyis brlabs kyis go phye nas bstan pa thams cad
NK063(gu)001:141: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK063(gu)001:142: dam tshig bsgrub dang sgrub pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:143: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK063(gu)001:144: phyogs bcu kun tu rab grags pa //
NK063(gu)001:145: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros te //
NK063(gu)001:148: theg pa'i sgo kun nas bsgrub pa'i mtha' rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:149: gsang ba'i snying po'i 'di'i don mngon du byed pa
NK063(gu)001:151: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK063(gu)001:152: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK063(gu)001:155: dag pa gsum dang rtogs pa bzhi la sogs pa gtan tshigs kyi sgo gang nas gzhal kyang /
NK063(gu)001:156: mthar thug de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul ni rtogs
NK063(gu)001:157: tshogs su btags pa thams cad sku dang ye shes
NK063(gu)001:158: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su gtan la phab pas 'khor
NK063(gu)001:159: ba kar dag pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:161: don bsdus gsung rab bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK063(gu)001:162: de las lhag pa'i don smra ba //
NK063(gu)001:163: de ni rnam dag lam min te //
NK063(gu)001:164: rang blo'i bsams pas 'khrul pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:166: de kho na nyid ces pa la yang gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:169: gzhan ma yin pa'i de kho na nyid do //
NK063(gu)001:171: rtog tshogs ril rang rig las mi gzhan pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:172: snang stong gnyis dang bral ba'i ye shes kyi dkyil
NK063(gu)001:173: 'khor la blos ma bcos par bzhag pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:176: ma bcos lhun mnyam ji bzhin ngang bzhag dang //
NK063(gu)001:179: de nyid ye shes kyi phyag rgya mang por rang
NK063(gu)001:180: byung ba ste de la 'ga' zhig gi 'bras bu'i
NK063(gu)001:181: de kho na nyid du'ang tha snyad 'dogs so //
NK063(gu)001:183: rgyu 'bras lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang du gnas //
NK063(gu)001:186: de dag gi mngon par zhen pa dag las gzhan
NK063(gu)001:187: ma yin pa ste de la kha cig rgyu 'bras
NK063(gu)001:188: gnyis su med pa'i de kho na nyid ces kyang
NK063(gu)001:189: zer ro // de yang 'di nyid kyi dgu pa las /
NK063(gu)001:190: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK063(gu)001:191: gzhan nas yod 'ongs ma yin te //
NK063(gu)001:193: nges pa'o zhes pa la yang gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:198: rgyud kyi gzhi rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po ni chos nyid sgro skur dang bral bar nges la /
NK063(gu)001:199: de nges byed 'dis nges par ston pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:202: sgro dang skur pa zhi ba yi //
NK063(gu)001:203: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK063(gu)001:204: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung //
NK063(gu)001:207: theg pa 'di'i lugs kyi 'bras bu lam du byed pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:209: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK063(gu)001:210: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:213: 'di rang gi ngo bos de bzhin gshegs pa'i dgongs
NK063(gu)001:214: pa nges don mngon du phyung nas ston pa yin
NK063(gu)001:216: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus la //
NK063(gu)001:217: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK063(gu)001:219: gnyis pa gdams ngag tu thabs lam rim gyis pa
NK063(gu)001:220: dang sbyar nas steng sgo'i dbang du bshad pa ni
NK063(gu)001:221: / mtshan gyi don bzhi po dag re re la
NK063(gu)001:222: yang chos gsum gsum du ston pa'i ming 'dogs snga
NK063(gu)001:224: de yang gsang ba'i zhes pa la gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:225: dang po rang bzhin gyi gsang ba la yang bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:226: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo'i rtsa 'dab brgyad la /
NK063(gu)001:227: gsum chos nyid kyi rtsa dbyibs zlum po //
NK063(gu)001:228: shes pa las kun gzhi'i rnam shes /
NK063(gu)001:229: 'khor ba'i sa bon las su dang tri /
NK063(gu)001:230: ye shes kyi snying po las +amo ser po gcig gnas so //
NK063(gu)001:231: de bzhin du ye shes kyi rtsa gru bzhi /
NK063(gu)001:233: sa bon las a dang n+ri /
NK063(gu)001:234: snying po las h+aum mthing kha gcig gnas so //
NK063(gu)001:235: gsum rang rgyud kyi rtsa zla gam /
NK063(gu)001:237: sa bon las pre dang duh snying po las +aam dmar po gcig gnas so //
NK063(gu)001:238: gcig yon tan gyi rtsa gru gsum /
NK063(gu)001:240: kha dog dmar nag lkog shal ltar shes pa gsum
NK063(gu)001:241: la snyoms par 'gebs pa ste blo rmugs par byed
NK063(gu)001:242: pa'i snod du bshad pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:244: dmar nag gdong la lkog shal dbyibs //
NK063(gu)001:245: de ni blo rmugs snod yin te //
NK063(gu)001:246: shes pa gsum la snyoms par 'gebs //
NK063(gu)001:247: drag po'i nyid du bshad pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:249: de rnams kyi dbus na rtsa'i dwangs ma dar dkar
NK063(gu)001:250: gyi skud pa 'dra ba'am rta rnga bcur gshags pa'i
NK063(gu)001:252: de'i nang na khrag gi dwangs ma mtshal lcog la ma bcag pa'i khu ba 'dra ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:253: de la drod kyi dwangs ma me long nyi ma la bzhag pa'i ngad tsam dang /
NK063(gu)001:254: de la dbugs kyi dwangs ma gser sa 'og nas byung ba'i rlangs tsam dang /
NK063(gu)001:255: 'di la 'od kyi dwangs ma kha dog sna tshogs pa zhig gnas te /
NK063(gu)001:256: de'i dkyil na ye shes kyi snying po kun rdzob
NK063(gu)001:257: byang chub sems kyi thig le gnas kyang de nyid
NK063(gu)001:258: ngo ma shes pa ni ye nas gsang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:259: de nyid yul lam rang bzhin sku dang ye shes
NK063(gu)001:260: kyi dkyil 'khor du snang ba yang rtog pas bsgribs
NK063(gu)001:261: nas ngo ma shes pa ni rang bzhin gyi gsang
NK063(gu)001:262: ba yin no // rtsa dang thig le'i bde ba
NK063(gu)001:263: de ngo bo nyid kyis bstan dkar bas ngo bo'i
NK063(gu)001:265: de nyid thabs kyi bzhu btul gyis snang ba las
NK063(gu)001:266: gzhan du btsal kyang mi rnyed pa ni shin tu
NK063(gu)001:268: ji skad du gsang thig las /
NK063(gu)001:269: gang la yod pa gnas pa brgyad du shes //
NK063(gu)001:270: gang gis ci 'dra de nyid bsres pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:271: rnam bzhi bye brag drug las brgyad dkyil na //
NK063(gu)001:272: don dam snying po de la zhes bshad pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:273: gnyis pa sbas pa'i gsang ba la yang bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:274: gang sbas na 'khor lo bzhi po bsgom pa'i thabs sbas la /
NK063(gu)001:275: gang la na mu stegs dang skye bo la sogs phyi rgyud man chad la sbas shing /
NK063(gu)001:276: tshul ji ltar na bsgom pa'i thabs kyis khyad par du 'gyur zhing rag las pa'i tshul du'o //
NK063(gu)001:277: gang gi phyir na snod min gyis skur pas de dag gi don du mi 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:278: tha ma gab pa'i gsang ba la yang bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:279: gang gab na lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo na
NK063(gu)001:280: kun gzhi kun tu bzang mo'i thig le gnas pa
NK063(gu)001:281: dang / gong gi snying ga'i thig le kha sbyor du bsgom zhing /
NK063(gu)001:282: mgrin pa longs spyod dang klad pa bde chen gyi
NK063(gu)001:283: thig le gnyis kha sbyor du bsgom pas bde ba'i
NK063(gu)001:284: ye shes skye ba'i thab de gab bo //
NK063(gu)001:285: gang du na rang lus thabs ldan gyi 'khor lo bzhi'i thig le la gab ste /
NK063(gu)001:286: de yang kun gzhi kun tu bzang mo'i thig le
NK063(gu)001:287: ni lte ba'i rtsa 'dab drug rtsa bzhi'i dbus na
NK063(gu)001:289: bcu drug bzhi yi dkyil na bzhugs //
NK063(gu)001:291: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi thig le ni rtsa 'dab bcu drug gi dkyil na gnas te /
NK063(gu)001:292: lnga gnyis drug gi dkyil 'khor na //
NK063(gu)001:294: klad pa bde chen gyi thig le ni rtsa 'dab so gnyis pa'i dbus na gnas te /
NK063(gu)001:295: bcu gsum gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor na //
NK063(gu)001:296: de yi thig le mnyam pa'i dbyings /
NK063(gu)001:298: gang la na lam 'di kun gyi yul du ma
NK063(gu)001:299: gyur pas 'di bsgom pa'i man ngag med pa la
NK063(gu)001:300: gab bo // de gang gis 'byin na thabs kyis
NK063(gu)001:301: nyams su blangs pas bde ba'i rim pa rgyud la
NK063(gu)001:303: snying po zhes pa la yang gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:304: rgyu'i don gyi snying po ni gong gi steng sgo'i
NK063(gu)001:305: dwangs ma lnga'i bde ba de nyid ye shes 'byung
NK063(gu)001:306: ba'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:307: 'bras bu'i don gyi ni de nyid bsgoms pa'i mtha' ye shes 'di mngon du byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:308: bcud 'dus pa ni steng sgo bsgom pa'i thabs bzhi
NK063(gu)001:309: las gang nas bsgoms kyang rtog tshogs kyi rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:310: sku dang ye shes su sangs rgyas pas 'khor ba
NK063(gu)001:312: de kho na nyid ces pa la yang gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:313: ma bcos pa'i ni rtsa'i thig le bde ba dang
NK063(gu)001:314: bcas par ye nas ma bcos par gnas pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:315: de la blos ma bcos par bsgom pa de yin
NK063(gu)001:316: la / ma nor ba ni de nyid ye shes su gsal ba de yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:317: gzhan ma yin pa ni de dag nyams su blangs
NK063(gu)001:318: pa'i tshe bsgoms pa'i ro la zhen pa dag gi
NK063(gu)001:319: skabs las gzhan ma yin pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:320: nges pa'o zhes pa la yang gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:321: de dag rang bzhin gyis rang la gnas pas gzhir nges shing /
NK063(gu)001:322: steng sgo sgom pa pos lam du byed pas lam du nges la /
NK063(gu)001:323: de goms pa mthar phyin pa ni 'bras bu yin pas 'bras bur nges pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:324: gsum pa thabs lam cig car ba dang sbyar te 'og sgo'i dbang du bshad pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:325: gsang ba'i zhes pa la gsum gyi /
NK063(gu)001:326: dang po rang bzhin gyi gsang ba la yang bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:327: dang po ni yab yum gyi thig le bde ba'i
NK063(gu)001:328: ro dang bcas pa rang la yod kyang ngo ma
NK063(gu)001:329: shes pa ni ye nas gsang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:330: de nyid yab kyi rdo rje ni sku /
NK063(gu)001:332: gsang ba'i rnam shes thugs su gnas kyang /
NK063(gu)001:333: rtog pas bsgribs nas ngo ma shes pa ni rang bzhin gyi gsang ba yin la /
NK063(gu)001:334: de tshig gis mtshon bya ma yin pas ngo bos
NK063(gu)001:335: bstan dka' ba'i phyir ngo bos gsang ba yin zhing
NK063(gu)001:336: / de nyid 'bras bu yin kyang gzhan du 'tshol
NK063(gu)001:337: btsal kyang gzhan nas mi rnyed pa ni shin tu
NK063(gu)001:339: gnyis pa sbas pa'i gsang ba la yang bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:340: gang sbas na yab yum sbyor ba'i thabs so //
NK063(gu)001:341: gang la na rgas pa zong zad dang /
NK063(gu)001:343: ma ning bde bas dben pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:344: dge slong ser snas bcings pa ste yul bzhi la'o //
NK063(gu)001:345: gang gi phyir na thabs kyis khyad par du byas
NK063(gu)001:346: pa'i lam 'di de dag gi yul ma yin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:347: phyir ro // gang ltar na myong ba'i ye shes
NK063(gu)001:348: de ngos ma zin pa'i tshul gyis sbas pa yin
NK063(gu)001:349: phyir ro // no // gsum pa gab pa'i gsang ba la yang bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:351: gsang ba'i rnam shes rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes de'o //
NK063(gu)001:353: gsang ba'i yul dang dbang po'i gnas su'o //
NK063(gu)001:354: gang gi phyir na thabs kyi man ngag rag las par bya ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:355: de gang gis 'byin na sbyor ba'i thabs kyis dngos
NK063(gu)001:356: po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes su 'byin pa'o
NK063(gu)001:357: // snying po zhes pa la yang gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:358: rgyu'i don gyi ni yab yum gyi thig le la
NK063(gu)001:359: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes 'byung ba'i
NK063(gu)001:360: phyir ro // 'bras bu'i don gyi ni /
NK063(gu)001:361: de yang 'khor lo bsgyur ba drug la sogs byed pa sdom pa'i thabs las byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:362: bcud 'dus pa'i don gyi ni thig le de nyid
NK063(gu)001:363: ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su gsal ba'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:364: ro // de kho na nyid ces pa la yang gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:365: thig le bde ba'i ro dang ldan par rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:366: gyis gnas pa ni ma bcos pa'am rgyu'i de kho
NK063(gu)001:368: thabs kyis thig le mngon du gsal ba na ye
NK063(gu)001:369: shes mngon du gsal ba ni ma nor ba'i de
NK063(gu)001:371: de dag gi mngon par zhen pa las lhag pa'i
NK063(gu)001:372: ye shes gzhan med pa ni gzhan ma yin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:374: nges pa'o zhes pa la yang gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:375: gzhir nges pa ni ye shes kyi gzhi bde ba'i
NK063(gu)001:376: ro yin zhing de thig le la brten pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:377: ro // lam du nges pa ni de gang zag
NK063(gu)001:378: skal ba can gyis nyams su blang bya yin la
NK063(gu)001:379: lam de bskyed pa'i ye shes ni don dam yin
NK063(gu)001:380: pa'i phyir sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa ni 'bras bur
NK063(gu)001:382: rtsod pa spang ba la yang bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:383: rgya skad med pa la brtags te dang /
NK063(gu)001:384: mtshan rgyud don yin min brtag te dang /
NK063(gu)001:385: mtshan gsum la brtags te dang /
NK063(gu)001:386: dbang po rab kyis mtshan la brten nas rgyud don rtogs tshul la brtags te rtsod pa spang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:390: dang po ni kha cig gsang ba'i snying po 'di chos can /
NK063(gu)001:391: rgya gar nas bsgyur ba ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:393: bod du brtsams pa'i bstan bcos bzhin zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:397: dang po ni kha cig bod skad dngos su smos pas rgya skad shugs la grub pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:398: dper na yul sngon por nges pa na shes pa
NK063(gu)001:399: sngon 'dzin du shugs la nges pa bzhin no zhes
NK063(gu)001:400: gsung pa ni ma yin par sems te /
NK063(gu)001:401: de nges kyang rgyud rgya gar nas bsgyur bar mi 'grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:402: gal te 'grub na bod du brtsams pa'i bstan bcos ril po chos can /
NK063(gu)001:403: rgya gar nas bsgyur bar 'gyur te //
NK063(gu)001:404: de dag gi sgra rgya skad du shugs la sbyar du rung ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:405: rtags de tshad mas 'grub cing khyab pa khas blangs /
NK063(gu)001:407: gnyis pa la yang gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:408: thal 'gyur gyis sgrub byed dgag pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:409: rang rgyud kyi rtags kyis rgya gar nas bsgyur bar bsgrub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:410: dang po ni 'di'i klad du rgya skad med kyang
NK063(gu)001:411: rgya gar nas bsgyur bar ci 'gal te khyab pa
NK063(gu)001:412: med do // khong gis smras pa /
NK063(gu)001:413: gang rgya skad med pa la rgya gar nas bsgyur ba ma yin pas khyab ste /
NK063(gu)001:414: bod kyi bstan bcos bzhin zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:415: de ltar na bde mchog rtsa ba'i rgyud dang /
NK063(gu)001:416: mya ngan las 'das pa'i mdo dang /
NK063(gu)001:417: dga' bo mngal du 'jug pa'i mdo sde la sogs
NK063(gu)001:418: pa rnams kyang rgya gar nas bsgyur ba ma yin
NK063(gu)001:419: par 'gyur te / rgya skad med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:420: rtags de dag gi gzhung gis grub cing khyab pa med na dam bca' nyams la /
NK063(gu)001:422: des na rgya skad med pa la rgya gar nas bsgyur ba mi khegs shing /
NK063(gu)001:423: de yod pa la rgya gar nas bsgyur ba'i khyab pa'ang med de /
NK063(gu)001:424: bod du brtsams pa la'ang rgya skad yod par dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:425: gnyis pa sgrub byed ni rgyud chen po 'di chos can /
NK063(gu)001:426: rgya gar nas bsgyur ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:427: 'di'i le'u bdun pa dang bcu drug pa'i gzhung rnams samskri ta'i skad du yod pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:428: yongs su grags pa'am rgya gar gyi pan+di ta rnams kyis yang dang yang du bkral ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:429: rtags de gzhung tshad mas grub cing /
NK063(gu)001:430: gzhung samskri ta'i skad du yod cing rgya gar du
NK063(gu)001:431: bkral ba la rgya gar nas byung ba'i khyab pa'ang
NK063(gu)001:432: tshad mas grub pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:433: rtsod pa gnyis pa ni kha cig mtshan 'di rgyud don yin nam ma yin zhes 'adri'o //
NK063(gu)001:434: phyi ma ltar na dbang po rab kyis mtshan la brten nas rgyud don mi rtogs par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:435: rgyud don min pa'i phyir te rtogs pa la yin pa zhig dgos pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:436: dang po ltar na gong ma slang bar rgyud don
NK063(gu)001:437: byung bas gnyis pa'i gleng slang ba mi dgos par
NK063(gu)001:438: 'gyur ro // gal te dgos pa yod na rgyud
NK063(gu)001:439: kyi rnam gzhag 'chol zhing go rim 'khrugs pa yin
NK063(gu)001:440: 'gyur ro // no zhe na / kha cig rgya
NK063(gu)001:441: dpe la le mtshams dang mjug na yod pa'i mtshan
NK063(gu)001:442: lo ts+aa bas klad du bkod pa yin par rgyud
NK063(gu)001:443: don min pa de'i phyir gleng slang ba yang mi
NK063(gu)001:444: dgos zhes zer ba ni ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:445: ji skad du khog gzhung las /
NK063(gu)001:446: rab la mtshan bstan zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:448: de la rab kyi don du rgyud kyi mtshan bshad
NK063(gu)001:449: pa yang 'dir gsum ste zhes pa dang 'gal bar
NK063(gu)001:451: des na mtshan rgyud don yin pas nyes pa dang po med la /
NK063(gu)001:452: gleng slang bas le'u gnyis pa don yod cing /
NK063(gu)001:453: go rim ni mtshon byed yi ge'i rgyud kyi dbang yin par sems te /
NK063(gu)001:454: mtshon bya la mtshan gyi sngon du gling slang ba
NK063(gu)001:455: lta zhog gleng gzhi yang grub pa med pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:456: ro // 'di bla ma'i gsung gis klad du bkod pa'i mtshan 'di rgyud don min la /
NK063(gu)001:457: don la gnas pa'i mtshan gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum
NK063(gu)001:458: du bkral ba ni rgyud don yin zhes gsung ba
NK063(gu)001:460: rgyud don yin min gnyis po 'gal ba'i chos ldan
NK063(gu)001:461: yin pa'i phyir sgra dang don la 'grel ba med
NK063(gu)001:462: par 'gyur ro // rtsod pa gsum pa ni rgyud
NK063(gu)001:463: 'di la mtshan gsum yod pa la rgyud lung gi
NK063(gu)001:465: man ngag kho na'i mtshan nas smos pa'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:468: rgyud kyi man ngag gsum du nges la /
NK063(gu)001:469: khyad par du sems dang ye shes rang snang du
NK063(gu)001:470: bstan pa 'di ni zab don gtso che bas rgyud
NK063(gu)001:471: kyi man ngag yin pa'i phyir de'i mtshan nas smos
NK063(gu)001:472: pa yin no // rtsod pa tha ma ni dbang
NK063(gu)001:473: po rab la rgyud kyi mtshan tsam bstan pas rgyud
NK063(gu)001:475: mtshan der rgyud don ma 'dus kyang rtogs pa yin nam 'dus nas rtogs pa yin /
NK063(gu)001:476: dang po ltar na ha cang thal te de tshod
NK063(gu)001:477: du mig shes kyi sgra thos pa cis 'gog ce
NK063(gu)001:479: sgra thos pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:480: sgra mig gis yul ma yin pa'i phyir zhes smras pas /
NK063(gu)001:481: kho na re rab kyis mtshan la brten nas rgyud don rtogs pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:482: mtshan du rgyud don ma 'dus pa'i phyir zhes zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:483: des na mtshan du rgyud don 'dus nas rtogs pa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:484: 'dus lugs ji ltar zhe na gsung sgros kyis brda 'phrad tha snyad 'dus ma yin zhes /
NK063(gu)001:485: rgyud dbu zhabs nas kyang brjod bya gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las lhag pa mi ston la /
NK063(gu)001:486: 'dir mtshan du yang de gsum tshang bar ston pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:487: 'di ltar mtshan dang po gsang ba la yang gsum
NK063(gu)001:488: yod pa'i rang bzhin gyi gsang ba 'bras bu gtso
NK063(gu)001:489: che zhing / sbas pa bzhi yin la /
NK063(gu)001:490: gab pa la gnyis yod pa'i rang bzhin gyi rgyud du gab pa gzhi yin la /
NK063(gu)001:491: yi ge'i rgyud du gab pa lam yin no //
NK063(gu)001:492: snying po la yang gsum yod pa'i rgyu'i snying po gzhi /
NK063(gu)001:495: de kho na nyid la yang gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:499: de bzhin du nges pa la yang gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:503: zhes gsung ba yang cung zad gnod pa dang bcas pa zhig ste /
NK063(gu)001:504: de ji ltar na brda gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du yang ma 'phrad par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:505: tha snyad tsam ma 'dus pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:506: des na 'di rgyal ba dang rig 'dzin gyis rtogs tshul la ltos pa yin na sla yi /
NK063(gu)001:507: gang zag la de lta bu'i rtogs tshul med cing /
NK063(gu)001:509: tha snyad dag la ma brten par //
NK063(gu)001:510: dam pa'i don nyid rtogs mi 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:512: gzhan yang mtshan tsam dang gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum
NK063(gu)001:513: yang tha snyad kyi bdag nyid du gnas pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:515: 'o na ji ltar zhe na mtshan tsam bstan pas
NK063(gu)001:516: rgyud don rtogs pa 'di ni phal cher sngon byung
NK063(gu)001:517: gi 'khor gyis rtogs tshul yin par sems te /
NK063(gu)001:518: de yang 'chad pa'i skyes bus rgyud kyi don thugs
NK063(gu)001:519: su chud nas rang gi 'khor la ston pa'i tshe
NK063(gu)001:520: de'i mtshan gsang ba'i snying po zhes bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:521: don mthong ba la brten nas mtshan du btags pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:522: sngon byung gi 'khor la ltos nas mtshan du tshig
NK063(gu)001:523: don ma lus pa 'dus shing skad cig tsam ma
NK063(gu)001:525: ji skad du rgya mtsho las /
NK063(gu)001:526: sgrib pa mtha' spong gdul bya la //
NK063(gu)001:527: skad cig tsam gyis snang bar mdzad //
NK063(gu)001:529: rjes 'jug tu mtshan thos pa la brten nas don go ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:530: mtshan der gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du brda 'phrad pa tsam du go ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:531: ming don 'brel ba nges pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:532: des na 'di ni don rang gi ngo bo la mtshan du btags pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:533: don gnyis pa mtshan de dang ldan pa'i rgyud kyi don dngos la gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:534: klad kyi don phyag btsal ba ni ston pa la dbang mi za ba'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:535: de yang bcom zhes pa bdud bzhi bcom pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:536: bdud tsam gyi go ba ni gang bar du gcod pa zhig yin no //
NK063(gu)001:537: de la bzhi nyon mongs pa rang rgyud du 'dzin pa nyon mongs pa'i bdud dang /
NK063(gu)001:538: phung po la bdag tu 'dzin pa phung po'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:539: skye 'chi rang gar 'dzin pa 'chi bdag gi dang /
NK063(gu)001:540: rtog tshogs tha mal du 'dzin pa lha'i bu bdud do //
NK063(gu)001:541: de dag la ston pa sku lnga'i bdag nyid kyis
NK063(gu)001:542: nyon mongs ye shes su dag cing phung po lnga
NK063(gu)001:543: rigs lngar sangs rgyas la thugs 'chi med rdo rjer
NK063(gu)001:544: rtogs nas rtog tshogs su btags pa thams cad sku
NK063(gu)001:545: dang ye shes su gsal bas bdud bzhi bcom pa
NK063(gu)001:546: yin te / ji skad du rgyas pa las /
NK063(gu)001:547: nyon mongs pa nyid rnam par dag /
NK063(gu)001:548: phung po lnga nyid mngon sangs rgyas //
NK063(gu)001:549: bdag nyid lha yin dkyil 'khor te //
NK063(gu)001:550: skye shi med par g.yung drung gnas //
NK063(gu)001:552: ru sangs rgyas gsang ba'i gzhung las kyang /
NK063(gu)001:553: bdud bzhi la sogs rig pa'i gdeng gis dag /
NK063(gu)001:555: ldan zhes pa ni 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan thams cad lhun gyis grub pa'i don yin te /
NK063(gu)001:557: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK063(gu)001:558: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK063(gu)001:561: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub //
NK063(gu)001:564: sku lnga la sogs yon tan lhun grub kyang //
NK063(gu)001:566: yon tan de dag kyang rigs bsdu na drug ste /
NK063(gu)001:567: ji skad du rgyud gzhan las /
NK063(gu)001:568: dpal dang grags dang ye shes dang //
NK063(gu)001:569: dbang phyug dang ni gzugs bzang dang //
NK063(gu)001:570: brtson 'grus phun sum tshogs ldan pa //
NK063(gu)001:571: drug po de la ldan zhes brjod //
NK063(gu)001:573: gzhung 'di'i dgongs pa ma yin kyang 'di ltar gsungs
NK063(gu)001:574: shing 'chad par 'gyur bas de'i dbang du lam pha
NK063(gu)001:575: rol tu phyin pa drug gi 'bras bu ye shes
NK063(gu)001:576: lngar snang ba'am / yang na chos nyid mngon du
NK063(gu)001:577: byas pa'i chos sku ni rtogs pa bdag gi dang
NK063(gu)001:578: lngar snang ba'am / / gzhan snang la rtog med
NK063(gu)001:579: du gzugs sku gnyis kyi yon tan du mi 'gag
NK063(gu)001:580: pa thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal lo //
NK063(gu)001:581: de lta bu'i ston pa phun sum tshogs pa'i bdag
NK063(gu)001:582: nyid des zhing khams kun tu khyab pa ni grags
NK063(gu)001:583: pa'o // dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK063(gu)001:584: cad kyi rang gi mtshan nyid mi mkhyen pa dang
NK063(gu)001:585: mi gzigs pa dang mi 'grel ba gang yang med
NK063(gu)001:587: des chos thams cad la dbang sgyur bas gzhan du rag ma lus pa ni dbang phyug go //
NK063(gu)001:588: mtshan dpes spras pa'i phyir kun las khyad par 'phags
NK063(gu)001:589: te gdul byas lta bas chog mi za ba ni
NK063(gu)001:590: gzugs bzang ba'o // dgongs pa g.yel ba mi mnga'
NK063(gu)001:591: bas dus la bab pa'i don phra ba yang mi
NK063(gu)001:594: 'di rgya gar gyi sgra la med pa'i phyir mi 'chad zer yang /
NK063(gu)001:596: bcom zhes pa dngos med stong pa'i mtha' dang /
NK063(gu)001:597: ldan zhes pa dngos po snang ba'i mthar thug ste mtha' gnyis las 'das pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:599: de phyir dngos dang dngos med par //
NK063(gu)001:600: 'jig pas dmigs med shes par gyis //
NK063(gu)001:603: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK063(gu)001:606: rang gi ngo bo 'di zhes bstan du med //
NK063(gu)001:608: rgya gar na yang 'di 'chad par slob dpon gyi gzhung 'dis mngon pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:609: dpal zhes pa'i don la gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:610: gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dpal ni bde
NK063(gu)001:611: bar gshegs pa'i snying po khyab byed du yod pas
NK063(gu)001:612: gang gis de brtags na rtogs su rung la bsgrub
NK063(gu)001:613: na 'grub tu rung ba de yin te /
NK063(gu)001:615: e ma bde gshegs snying po las //
NK063(gu)001:618: snying po rang bzhin mtshungs pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:620: thugs rig pa rang snang gi dpal ni de mngon du byas pa'i ye shes yin te /
NK063(gu)001:621: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyod yul lo //
NK063(gu)001:623: de yis mi mkhyen gang yang med //
NK063(gu)001:625: thugs rje chen po gzhan la snang ba'i dpal ni /
NK063(gu)001:626: mdzad pa'i phrin las kyis gdul bya 'dren pa'i thabs
NK063(gu)001:627: mnga' ba yang rtsol rtog dang bral bar snang ba
NK063(gu)001:629: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK063(gu)001:630: phyogs bcu 'jig rten rdul bsnyed du //
NK063(gu)001:631: 'gro ba'i phrin las bsam mi khyab //
NK063(gu)001:634: rang bzhin mngon byas ma lus re ba skong //
NK063(gu)001:636: kun tu zhes pa shes bya'i dkyil 'khor na lhag ma lus pa'i bdag nyid yin te /
NK063(gu)001:637: ji skad du gnyis pa las /
NK063(gu)001:638: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK063(gu)001:640: bzang po zhes pa ni de'i rang bzhin phyin ci
NK063(gu)001:641: ma log par mngon du byas pas spyod yul dag
NK063(gu)001:643: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK063(gu)001:645: la zhes pa rnam dbye gnyis pa'i sgras phyag btsal ba'i yul mtshon pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:646: gang zhe na ston pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK063(gu)001:647: phyag 'tshal lo zhes pa rang gi ngo bo ste /
NK063(gu)001:648: gang gis na sdud pa po gsang bdag gis so //
NK063(gu)001:649: ji ltar na bdag don du rang bzhin gyi rgyud
NK063(gu)001:650: khong du chud pa'i tshe ston pa'i thugs dang tha
NK063(gu)001:651: dad med pas gnyis med rtogs pa'i phyag yin la
NK063(gu)001:652: / gzhan don du yi ge rgyud du 'chad pa'i
NK063(gu)001:653: tshe khyad par gyi ston pa la dbang mi za
NK063(gu)001:654: ba'i phyir mos shing 'dud pa'i phyag yin te /
NK063(gu)001:655: ji skad du spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:656: 'di tshig tu gnyer ba'i tshe rang gi ston pa la mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:658: 'dir kha cig phyag gi dgos don bsdus don la
NK063(gu)001:659: sogs su ming 'dogs pa ni rig pa ma yin
NK063(gu)001:660: te / de dag bstan bcos 'chad pa'i man ngag tu gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:661: gnyis pa bka' bde blag tu rtogs par bya ba'i phyir gzhungs gi don gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:662: gzhung tshogs le'u nyer gnyis kyang dbang po 'bring gi don du chos lngar sdud de /
NK063(gu)001:663: ji skad du spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:664: spros pa la dga' ba dbang po 'bring gi don
NK063(gu)001:665: du rgyud kyi don rnam par phye bas lnga ste
NK063(gu)001:666: zhes pas le'u dang po dang gsum pa'i stod nas
NK063(gu)001:667: rgyud dam bstan pa 'byung ba'i rgyu gleng gzhi phun
NK063(gu)001:669: gnyis pa rkyen gleng slang ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:670: gsum pa'i smad nas nyer gcig pa yan chad 'bras bu rgyud don dang /
NK063(gu)001:671: de dag la khyab byed du rgyud kyi dgos 'brel dang /
NK063(gu)001:672: le'u tha mas 'khor la rgyud gdams shing bstan pa gtad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:674: thun mong ma yin pa'i sgo nas gleng gzhi mdor bstan pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:675: gleng gzhi'i don bshad pa dngos dang /
NK063(gu)001:676: de la rtsod pa spang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:677: dang po ni bshad thabs kyi yan lag las kyang
NK063(gu)001:678: rgyud mda' ltar rtse mo nas bzung ste bshad pa
NK063(gu)001:679: zhes bya ste bshad thabs gzhan yang rgyas par 'chad
NK063(gu)001:682: phyi shes rab grol ba'i lam gyi dbang du dang /
NK063(gu)001:683: nang thabs lam steng sgo'i dbang du dang /
NK063(gu)001:684: gsang ba 'og sgo'i dbang du bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:685: dang po ni sku lnga'i gleng gzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:686: 'di zhes pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:687: 'og gi sku lnga'i gnas rim pa ltar don gyi 'og min dang /
NK063(gu)001:689: rig pa snang stong gnyis med dang /
NK063(gu)001:690: dbang phyug chen po'i 'og min dang /
NK063(gu)001:691: stong gsum mam rdo rje gdan no //
NK063(gu)001:692: skad ces pa ston pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:693: chos kyi sku dang mngon par byang chub pa'i sku
NK063(gu)001:694: dang dbyer med rdo rje'i sku dang longs spyod rdzogs
NK063(gu)001:695: pa'i sku dang sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK063(gu)001:697: ye shes rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i
NK063(gu)001:698: tshogs dang dbyer med rdo rje'i tshogs dang smin pa
NK063(gu)001:699: rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang lha mi la sogs pa sems
NK063(gu)001:700: can las dag pa'i tshogs so //
NK063(gu)001:701: pa'i zhes pa bstan pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:702: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying por gcig cing /
NK063(gu)001:704: brjod med kyis 'khor la go brda' sprod pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:705: byin gyis brlabs kyis 'khor lo bskor ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:706: dbyer med kyi sgo nas bka' stsal pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:707: brda' ma dgongs pas bstan pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:708: drang don du tshig tu gsungs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:709: bstan pa de dag gi sdud pa po ni dus
NK063(gu)001:710: gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs kyi gsang
NK063(gu)001:711: ba'i mdzod 'dzin pa gsang bdag tu gcig pa yin
NK063(gu)001:713: 'khor gyi nang nas skal mchog ldan //
NK063(gu)001:714: 'dul ba'i dus bab gsang ba'i bdag /
NK063(gu)001:715: lag na rdo rjes bsdu ba mdzad //
NK063(gu)001:718: rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK063(gu)001:720: dus na zhes pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:721: brjod du med pa'i dus dang /
NK063(gu)001:722: byin gyis brlabs kyis 'khor lo bskor ba'i dus dang /
NK063(gu)001:723: dbyer med du bka' stsal ba'i dus dang /
NK063(gu)001:724: brda yis bstan pa'i dus dang /
NK063(gu)001:725: shin tu dkon pa'am sgron ma yongs su bkod pa'i dus so //
NK063(gu)001:726: gnyis pa steng sgo'i dbang du bshad pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:727: 'di zhes pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:730: 'od bzhi e sogs dbyibs su gnas //
NK063(gu)001:732: tsakra ni 'khor lo ste snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo'i rtsa 'dab bzhi ni /
NK063(gu)001:733: mdun na ye shes kyi rtsa gru bzhi ser po /
NK063(gu)001:734: g.yas na chos nyid kyi rtsa zlum po dkar po /
NK063(gu)001:735: rgyab rang rgyud kyi rtsa gru gsum dmar nag /
NK063(gu)001:736: g.yon yon tan gyi rtsa zla gam dmar po la
NK063(gu)001:737: sogs pa las bzhi'i dbyibs dang kha dog tu gnas
NK063(gu)001:739: skad ces pa ni ston pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:741: mi shigs thig le bam dbyibs can //
NK063(gu)001:742: rang la bde ba gsal byed dag /
NK063(gu)001:744: de dag gi dbus na srog mi shigs pa'i thig le dwangs ma lnga ste /
NK063(gu)001:745: 'di ltar rtsa dang khrag dang drod dang dbugs dang
NK063(gu)001:746: 'od kyi dwangs ma rnams ni rim pa ltar dar
NK063(gu)001:747: dkar gyi skud pa lta bu dang /
NK063(gu)001:748: mtshal lcog la ma bcag pa'i khu ba 'dra ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:749: me long nyi ma la bzhag pa'i ngad tsam dang /
NK063(gu)001:750: gser sa 'og nas byung ba'i rlangs tsam dang /
NK063(gu)001:751: 'od kha dog sna tshogs pa rnams 'dus pa'i ngo
NK063(gu)001:752: bo yi ge bam gyi dbyibs can ni ston pa
NK063(gu)001:753: yin te / ci'i phyir na snum sdong phun sum
NK063(gu)001:754: tshogs pa'i mar me gsal byed gzhan la mi ltos
NK063(gu)001:755: pa ltar de nyid kyis bde ba de nyid la
NK063(gu)001:759: ma nu yid sogs rnam shes bzhi //
NK063(gu)001:760: ye shes myong bas bsdus bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:762: ma nu ni yid ces bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:763: de ye shes kyi rtsa la gnas shing sogs pa'i sgras gzhan bsdus te /
NK063(gu)001:764: chos nyid kyi rtsa la kun gzhi /
NK063(gu)001:765: yon tan gyi rtsa la nyon yid /
NK063(gu)001:766: rang rgyud kyi rtsa la sgo lnga'i rnam shes gnas
NK063(gu)001:767: te rnam shes de dag gi rtog pa dag nas
NK063(gu)001:768: mi rtog par skyes pa la bshad ces bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:769: pa'i zhes pa ni bstan pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:771: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes pa //
NK063(gu)001:772: pa ra m+aar+tha don zab mo //
NK063(gu)001:774: nam mkha' gzugs med kyang de'i dus su rnam par
NK063(gu)001:775: mi rtog pa'i ye shes skyes pa la de skad
NK063(gu)001:776: ces bya'o // de nyid kho na pa ra ma ta ste don zab mo yin no //
NK063(gu)001:777: dus na zhes pa dus dngos te /
NK063(gu)001:779: bde ba'i dus nyid snga phyi bral //
NK063(gu)001:780: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK063(gu)001:782: steng sgo'i bde ba skyes pa tshe snga phyir 'dzin pa'i rtog pa dang bral te /
NK063(gu)001:783: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid du bzhugs pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:784: gsum pa 'og sgo'i dbang du bshad pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:787: 'di zhes nye bar mtshon pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:788: e sogs rnam bzhi'i dbyibs can gnas //
NK063(gu)001:790: yum gyi mkha' phyi khyams gru bzhi bar khyams gru
NK063(gu)001:791: gsum skye gnas zla gam sna tshogs mdud pa zlum
NK063(gu)001:792: po rnams ni las bzhi'i dbyibs su gnas pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:793: ro // skad ces pa ston pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:795: skad ces gsal byed las ming can //
NK063(gu)001:796: bam yig theg ler bcas ston pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:798: yab kyi rdo rje bum par thig le thabs kyis
NK063(gu)001:799: bzung ba'i tshe yab yum gnyis ka'i rgyud la bde
NK063(gu)001:800: ba gsal bar byed pa'i bdag nyid du bzhugs pa
NK063(gu)001:801: ni ston pa'o // bshad ces pa 'khor te /
NK063(gu)001:803: ma da ma nu sdom byed yid //
NK063(gu)001:804: lus can rnam shes de dag la //
NK063(gu)001:805: gsal bar go bas bshad par 'dod //
NK063(gu)001:807: ma ma nu na yid ces bya ste de la
NK063(gu)001:808: sogs pa gsang ba'ii rnam shes ni bde ba nyams
NK063(gu)001:810: ma ma ta na sdom byed de /
NK063(gu)001:811: nyams su myong ba'i chos thams cad bde bar bsdus
NK063(gu)001:812: nas zhor la ston par byed pa'i phyir sdud pa
NK063(gu)001:814: pa'i zhes pa bstan pa yang de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:815: pa sgra don dam nges pa'i rgyud /
NK063(gu)001:816: ya na theg chen 'di nyid do //
NK063(gu)001:818: bde ba de nyid la pa ra ma ta bo
NK063(gu)001:819: d+hi tsit+ta zhes pa na don dam byang chub kyi
NK063(gu)001:820: sems zhes bya ste nges don du bstan pa'i rgyud
NK063(gu)001:821: 'di yin la / ma h+aa ya na ni theg
NK063(gu)001:822: pa chen po ste bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa
NK063(gu)001:823: 'di yin la / 'di nyid do // dus na zhes pa yang /
NK063(gu)001:825: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab dus //
NK063(gu)001:826: n+aa ma de ming zhes bya ba //
NK063(gu)001:828: de'i dus su 'dzin pa'i rtog pa dang bral ba
NK063(gu)001:829: ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus zhes bya ste
NK063(gu)001:830: n+aa ma na dus de la bab pa'i ming can
NK063(gu)001:832: gnyis pa rtsod pa spang ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:833: spyir gsang sngags la bshad tshul nyes pa'i skyon brgyad las /
NK063(gu)001:834: 'dir rtog ge bas btags pa'i the tshom gyi gegs
NK063(gu)001:835: sel mi shes na mdzangs pa lce rdum du 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:836: bas de spang pa la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:839: dang po ni kha cig na re /
NK063(gu)001:840: 'di gleng gzhi log pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:841: mdo rgyud gzhan thams cad na 'di skad bdag gis
NK063(gu)001:842: thos pa'i dus gcig na zhes bya bar byung ba'i
NK063(gu)001:843: phyir zhe na / gnyis pa lan la'ang gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:846: thos pa 'khor gyi ngos nas smos shing bshad pa
NK063(gu)001:847: ston pa'i ngos nas smos pa yin no zhes zer
NK063(gu)001:848: ba ni / 'thad pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:849: gsang bdag gsang sngags thams cad kyi sdud pa por mtshungs pa la /
NK063(gu)001:850: rgyud 'dir ston pa'i ngos nas smos la gsang ba
NK063(gu)001:851: 'dus pa la sogs pa gzhan du 'khor gyi ngos
NK063(gu)001:852: nas smoos pa la rgyu mtshan ci yang med pa'i
NK063(gu)001:853: phyir ro // yang kha cig ni sprul sku'i gleng
NK063(gu)001:854: gzhi'i tshig gi rgyan 'god pa'i tshe 'di skad thos
NK063(gu)001:856: thun mong gi 'khor la tshig tu gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:857: longs sku'i gleng gzhi'i tshig gi rgyan 'god pa'i tshe 'di skad bshad par 'ong ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:858: thun mong ma yin pa'i 'khor la brda dang dgongs pas gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:859: zhes zer ba yang ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:860: gsang ba 'dus pa la sogs gzhan du yang tha
NK063(gu)001:861: dad par 'ong bar 'gyur te longs sku'i bstan par
NK063(gu)001:863: yang kha cig ni slar thos pa la skyon yod de /
NK063(gu)001:864: ston 'khor khyad par yod pa'i tshig yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:865: thos kyang ma rtogs pa dang log par rtogs pa dang the tshom za ba rnams srid la /
NK063(gu)001:866: 'dir 'khor dbang thob pas ston 'khor dgongs pa khyad
NK063(gu)001:867: par med pas de nyid la de nyid bshad pa'i
NK063(gu)001:868: phyir nyes pa de rnams las grol zhes zer ba
NK063(gu)001:869: yang / ston 'khor dgongs pa khyad par med pa'i phyir bshad mi dgos par 'gyur ro //
NK063(gu)001:870: yang kha cig ni thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i khyad par yin te /
NK063(gu)001:872: thos zhes pa sdud pa po rang gi blo'i snang
NK063(gu)001:873: ba 'dzin par byed pa dang ston pas ji ltar
NK063(gu)001:874: gsungs pa bzhin khas len mi nus pas ston pa
NK063(gu)001:875: dang sdud pa po'i khyad par mtshon pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:876: thos pa'i yon tan bdun dang ldan te /
NK063(gu)001:878: 'di skad thos zhes bka' sgro skur dang bral bar dang /
NK063(gu)001:879: bdag gis thos zhes pa sdud pa po ston pa ma yin par dang /
NK063(gu)001:880: gzhan las ma brgyud pas sdud pa po tshad mar dang /
NK063(gu)001:881: dus gcig na 'di thos kyi dus thams cad du
NK063(gu)001:882: ma thos pas bka' grags pa 'byung dka' ba dang
NK063(gu)001:883: / dus gcig na 'di thos shing dus gzhan du
NK063(gu)001:884: gzhan yang thos zhes pa thos pa rgya che bar
NK063(gu)001:885: / dang / de yang ma yengs pa'i dus na thos zhes pas dgongs pa dang ldan par dang /
NK063(gu)001:886: thos pa'i don khong du chud pas sdud pa po
NK063(gu)001:887: shes rab che ba rnams su mtshon pa yin la
NK063(gu)001:888: / 'di skad bshad ces pa ni yang dag par
NK063(gu)001:889: sdud pa pos ston pa'i dgongs pa dang gnyis su
NK063(gu)001:890: med par khas blangs nas der smos pa yin te
NK063(gu)001:891: / / de'i yon tan nam che ba gsum dang ldan te /
NK063(gu)001:893: 'di skad ces pas bka' 'di dgongs pa'i zhe phugs yin pas bstan pa'i che ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:894: bshad ces pa sdud pa po nyid thams cad mkhyen
NK063(gu)001:895: par khas blangs pas sdud pa po'i che ba dang
NK063(gu)001:896: / dus na zhes pas dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid yin pas dus kyi che ba dang ldan te /
NK063(gu)001:897: ji skad du mdo chen po'i le'u tha ma las /
NK063(gu)001:898: de bzhin nyid kyi don bstan du //
NK063(gu)001:899: de bzhin nyid du kun gcig pas //
NK063(gu)001:900: gang gis gang la gang zhig bstan //
NK063(gu)001:901: nyid la nyid gleng kho nar zad //
NK063(gu)001:904: chos chen 'chad pa nga nyid de //
NK063(gu)001:905: tshogs kyi nang du nyan pa'ang nga //
NK063(gu)001:907: zhes zer ba yang blo rtse gong ma dag dang mtshungs shing /
NK063(gu)001:908: gzhan yang sdud pa po thams cad mkhyen par khas len mi len dang /
NK063(gu)001:909: ston pa'i dgongs pa dang khyad par yod med gnyis
NK063(gu)001:910: kyi phyiir gsang bdag tu gcig pa ma yin par
NK063(gu)001:911: 'gyur ro // 'o na ji ltar zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:912: gnyis pa rang lan gdab pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:913: lha rje chen po'i gsung gis rjes su 'brangs te
NK063(gu)001:914: mdo rgyud thams cad na gleng gzhi 'di skad bdag
NK063(gu)001:915: gis thos pa kho nar yod par ma grub ste
NK063(gu)001:916: / thams cad khyod kyis ma mthong ba'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:917: ma mo mkha' 'gros dbang byas shing mi la nyan bshad med pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:918: gzhan yang bod du ma 'gyur ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:919: 'gyur yang thams cad khyod kyis ma thos shing ma mthong ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:920: des na tha snyad du rtags ma grub pas lan thebs pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:921: rnal don la chab bar pa ltar thos pa 'khor
NK063(gu)001:922: dang bshad pa ston pa'i ngos nas smos pa bde
NK063(gu)001:923: bar sems so // gzhan yang slob dpon jo mdo na re /
NK063(gu)001:924: 'di ni lo ts+aa ba'i 'gyur gyi rigs yin te /
NK063(gu)001:925: de gnyis car la rgya skad e bam ma yar mthun pa'i phyir ro zhes gsungs so //
NK063(gu)001:926: gnyis pa gleng gzhi rgyas par bstan pa la gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:927: dang po ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:928: bi ma las ston pa'i rang bzhin bzhi ldan du 'dod la /
NK063(gu)001:929: sgeg pas rang bzhin bdun ldan du bzhed de /
NK063(gu)001:930: dang po ni de bzhin gshegs pa zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:931: bcom ldan 'das zhes pa'i bar byang chub chen po'i rang bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:932: longs spyod chen po zhes pa ni chos rnams rol pa'i longs spyod do //
NK063(gu)001:934: rdo rje'i bdag nyid ces pa'i bar phyogs dus bde gshegs bdag po'o //
NK063(gu)001:935: ma lus mi lus zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:936: rang bzhin te zhes pa'i bar chos so cog dang dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:937: gnyis pa ltar rang bzhin bdun ldan ni /
NK063(gu)001:938: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes pa gzhi ji bzhin nyid du mthar son pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:939: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i zhes pa yon tan btsal ba med par lhun gyis grub pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:940: sangs rgyas zhes pa sgrib pa dang bral ba'i ye shes mtha' dbus med par brdal ba'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:941: bcom ldan 'das zhes pa bdud bzhi 'bras bur mnga'
NK063(gu)001:942: mdzad kyang rang gi ngo bo 'di zhes bstan du
NK063(gu)001:943: med pa'i dang / longs spyod chen po zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:944: thams cad kyis ro myong yang bltar la 'dzin pa
NK063(gu)001:945: med pa'i dang / med pa'i dang / phyogs bcu zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:946: rdo rje bdag nyid ces pa'i bar bdag nyid chen po dbyer med pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:947: ma lus mi lus zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:948: rang bzhin te zhes pa'i bar ni dus gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:949: de gnyis car gyi 'bru mthun te gzhung ltar ro //
NK063(gu)001:950: 'dir kha cig ni phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin
NK063(gu)001:951: gshegs pa zhes pa'i skabs su gzhi dang lam gyi
NK063(gu)001:952: nyes pa gnyis zad pas rgyu spyad zin cing 'bras
NK063(gu)001:953: bu zhing tha dad du dar lo bskor bas 'das
NK063(gu)001:955: nyes pa gnyis zad pas rgyu'i bya ba byas zin
NK063(gu)001:956: pas 'bras bu dar lo bskoor bzhin pa da ltar
NK063(gu)001:958: gzhi'i nyes pa nyon sgrib zad cing 'bras bu'i shes
NK063(gu)001:959: sgrib zad pa'i rgyu rkyen tshogs pas 'bras bu 'byin
NK063(gu)001:960: pa la ma rag pa ni ma 'ongs pa'i de
NK063(gu)001:961: pa ste de ni sems dpa' lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:962: nyes pa gnyis zad par byed pa'i rgyu rang rig dang rkyen lam gnyis rang chas su yod kyang /
NK063(gu)001:963: bdag rkyen du dang gdams ngag tshogs pa la rag
NK063(gu)001:964: las pa ni ma 'ongs pa'i de pa ste gdul
NK063(gu)001:965: bya thams cad do zhes zer ba ni spyir dus
NK063(gu)001:966: bzhi'i de pa'i rnam gzhag de ltar yin par srid
NK063(gu)001:967: kyang 'dir de 'thad pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:969: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid ces pas /
NK063(gu)001:970: 'di dbyer med kyi ston pa yin la de dag
NK063(gu)001:971: gi rgyud tha dad yin pa'i phyir snyam du sems
NK063(gu)001:972: so // gnyis pa ston pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK063(gu)001:973: skabs 'dir yang rat+na bstar 'chol gyi bshad pa'i skyon
NK063(gu)001:974: spangs te rgyud 'khrugs pa'i bdag nyid sdebs la gzhung
NK063(gu)001:976: 'di la ngag don gyi tshoms ni sku gsum gyi
NK063(gu)001:977: bdag nyid thabs shes rab gnyis su med cing ye
NK063(gu)001:979: rnam par thar pa gsum chub pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:980: de yang dang po ni sku gsum las chos sku'i
NK063(gu)001:981: bdag nyid yin pa ni sku zhes pa 'bras bu
NK063(gu)001:982: che ba'i yon tan ma lus pa'i rten byed pa
NK063(gu)001:983: ste / de ni chos sku yin la de la
NK063(gu)001:984: mdun rgyab kyi ris med cing sku thams cad kyi
NK063(gu)001:986: chos skus khyab pa gcig pa'i phyir zhes pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:987: de ltar ris med par gnas pa nyid kyi phyir
NK063(gu)001:988: gdul bya gnas pa'i phyogs mtshams thams cad du zhal
NK063(gu)001:991: kun tu bzang po'i zhal ni phyogs bcur gsal //
NK063(gu)001:992: kun gzigs kun bzang sku la mdun rgyab med //
NK063(gu)001:993: phyogs bcu gang bar spyan gyis rnam par gzigs //
NK063(gu)001:995: mdor na gdul bya shar phyogs pa'i ngo na shar kho nar gzigs par snang ba ltar /
NK063(gu)001:996: phyogs thams cad du gsal zhing gzugs sku gnyis kyi yon tan du mi 'gag pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:997: de'i phyir longs sku'i bdag nyid yin pa ni mtshan
NK063(gu)001:998: dang dpe byad du zhes pa longs sku'i sku mtshan
NK063(gu)001:1002: thun mong ma yin pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:1003: gsang ba'i mtshan dang dpe byad do //
NK063(gu)001:1004: de yang de dag gi mtshan gyi rnam grangs ni
NK063(gu)001:1005: sum cu rtsa gnyis dang dpe byad ni brgyad cu
NK063(gu)001:1007: mtshan ni sum cu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK063(gu)001:1008: dpe byad brgyad cu'i bdag nyid 'di //
NK063(gu)001:1010: de yang thun mong gi mtshan ni /
NK063(gu)001:1011: phyag zhabs 'khor lo'i mtshan dang rus sbal zhabs /
NK063(gu)001:1012: phyag dang zhabs sor d+r+wa bas 'brel ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:1014: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu ni /
NK063(gu)001:1015: thub pa'i sen mo zangs mdog dang //
NK063(gu)001:1016: mdog snum mtho dang sor mo rnams //
NK063(gu)001:1017: zlum rgyas byin rgyas phra ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:1019: de dag ni thun mong gi mtshan dpe yin te /
NK063(gu)001:1020: sprul pa'i sku la'ang yod cing 'khor lo sgyur ba'i
NK063(gu)001:1021: rgyal po sogs la yang phyogs mthun yod par srid
NK063(gu)001:1022: pa'i phyir snyam du sems so //
NK063(gu)001:1023: thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan dpe yang sems dpa'
NK063(gu)001:1024: bcu drug dang sems ma bcu drug gi 'khor dang
NK063(gu)001:1025: ldan pa mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis yin la /
NK063(gu)001:1026: sems dpa' rnams re re la yang dbu rgyan lnga lngar ldan pa ni dpe byad brgyad cu ste /
NK063(gu)001:1027: ji skad du mdo chen po las /
NK063(gu)001:1028: mtshan gyi me tog gis mdzes shing dpe byad kyi
NK063(gu)001:1029: 'bras bu spras pa'i phyir sras kyi tshogs kyis kun
NK063(gu)001:1030: nas bskor ba'o zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1031: 'o na sems ma la dbu rgyan med dam zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1033: mtshan dpe'i rtsis las 'das pa'i khongs su bgrangs pa'am /
NK063(gu)001:1034: yang na thabs kyi zhags pa las yum dbyings kyi
NK063(gu)001:1035: cha yin pa'i phyir mi bgrang zhes dpe byad du
NK063(gu)001:1036: mi bgrang bar bshad pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1037: 'di dag longs sku kho na la yod pa'i phyir thun min no //
NK063(gu)001:1038: gsang ba'i mtshan dpe ni ston pa yab yum gyi mkha' gsang la brtsi ste /
NK063(gu)001:1039: yab yum gnyis la dga' ba bcu drug bcu drug ni mtshan so gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:1040: yab kyi dga' ba rnams re re yang ye shes
NK063(gu)001:1041: lnga lnga dang ldan pa ni dpe byad brgyad cu'o
NK063(gu)001:1042: // 'o na yum gyi dga' ba de dag ye shes lnga lnga dang mi ldan nam zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1044: gong ma dang mtshungs par bsnyad do //
NK063(gu)001:1045: ldan zhes pa mtshan dpe de dag gis sku la
NK063(gu)001:1046: ji ltar spras na thun mong gi sku lder bzo
NK063(gu)001:1047: lta bu la mtshan dpe'i ri mo bris pa lta
NK063(gu)001:1048: bu'o // thun min gyi ni lus sor gdub kyi mdzes pa de phra mig gis mdzes pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:1049: rtsa ba'i lha mtshan gyis mdzes shing mtshan gyi lha dpe byad kyi lhas mdzes pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:1050: yang na 'jig rten na gtso 'khor ltar ston pa
NK063(gu)001:1051: sems dpa' dang sems ma'i tshogs kyi bskor ba ni
NK063(gu)001:1052: gcig gis gcig mdzes pa bskyed pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:1053: gsum char yongs su rdzogs pas ni //
NK063(gu)001:1054: dper na me long chung ngur yang gnam sa ri brag chen po'i gzugs brnyan shong ba ltar /
NK063(gu)001:1055: sku gcig la'ang mtshan dpe'i bkod pa du ma gsal ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:1057: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK063(gu)001:1058: stangs dpyal gnyis kyi phyag rgya dang //
NK063(gu)001:1059: ri rib til 'bru'i tshul bzhin du //
NK063(gu)001:1060: dpe byad mtshan gyis spras pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:1063: mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs //
NK063(gu)001:1065: sprul pa sku'i bdag nyid yin pa ni bsam gyi
NK063(gu)001:1066: mi khyab pa thams cad du sku gsung thugs sna
NK063(gu)001:1067: tshogs pa kun tu snang ba zhes pa /
NK063(gu)001:1068: zhi khro la sogs sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1069: chos kyi sgo brgyad khri la sogs gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1070: mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang mngon shes la sogs thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:1071: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:1072: thabs dang shes rab kyi zhabs gnyis zhes pa zhabs
NK063(gu)001:1073: g.yas kyis thabs dang g.yon pas shes rab mtshon pa'o
NK063(gu)001:1074: // yang na thabs dang zhes pas yab dang shes rab ces pas yum mtshon pa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:1075: mnyam pa'i zhes pas yab dang /
NK063(gu)001:1076: brtul zhugs kyi zhes pas yum gyi skyil krung ste
NK063(gu)001:1077: gnyis char rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa
NK063(gu)001:1079: 'dir kha cig sku gsung thugs sna tshogs pa zhes
NK063(gu)001:1080: pa dang thabs dang shes rab kyi zhabs gnyis zhes
NK063(gu)001:1081: pa 'gal te / sku sna tshogs pa la zhabs gnyis las med pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1083: sna tshogs pa'i sku de dag re re yang zhabs gnyis gnyis dang ldan pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:1084: de ltar dbu gsum dang phyag drug kyang shes par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:1085: ye shes drug dang ldan pa ni don ye shes
NK063(gu)001:1086: lnga rang byung gi ye shes dang drug gi mtshon
NK063(gu)001:1088: de yang ye shes rang la gnas par phyag gis
NK063(gu)001:1089: mtshon cing nges don mdzad par phyag mtshan gyis mtshon
NK063(gu)001:1090: pa ste / 'di ltar ye shes rin po che'i phyag rgya 'bar ba can zhes pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:1091: rgyas pa'i nyer gnyis pa las /
NK063(gu)001:1092: rdo rje 'khor lo ral gri dang //
NK063(gu)001:1095: de dag 'od 'bar ba dang bcas pa 'dzin pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:1096: rnam par thar pa gsum chub pa ni sku gsung
NK063(gu)001:1097: thugs zhes pa de dag gi rnam par thar pa
NK063(gu)001:1099: de ya nga mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:1100: de'i rtags su dbu gsum dang ldan pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:1102: sku rdzogs pa stong pa nyid mtshon pa'i phyir g.yas dkar ba /
NK063(gu)001:1103: gsung rdzogs pa smon pa med pa mtshon pa'i phyir g.yon dmar ba /
NK063(gu)001:1104: thugs rdzogs pa mtshan ma med pa mtshon pa'i phyir dbus mthing ga'o //
NK063(gu)001:1105: don gnyis pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:1106: 'og min gyi gnas zhes pa de la gsum mam lnga ste /
NK063(gu)001:1111: dbang phyug chen po'i 'og min no //
NK063(gu)001:1112: de las dang po ni 'jig rten gyi gnas gzhan
NK063(gu)001:1113: bgrangs pa'i sa gtsang ma ris kyi lha lnga'i dang
NK063(gu)001:1115: de la der grags pas na grags pa'i 'og min zhes kyang bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:1116: gnyis pa ni gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i ye shes
NK063(gu)001:1117: gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid de ni rgyal ba
NK063(gu)001:1118: ma lus pa'i rten yin pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:1120: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes ni //
NK063(gu)001:1121: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi gnas //
NK063(gu)001:1124: de mngon du byas pa'i rig pa la gzhal yas su snang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:1125: yang na 'og min chen po na yod pa ltar
NK063(gu)001:1126: lam pa'i blos btags te lhag pa ting dkyil du
NK063(gu)001:1128: de la btags pa'i 'og min zhes kyang zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:1130: yum gyi mkha' e wam ma yas mtshon pa'i gnas de yin te /
NK063(gu)001:1131: der gsang ba'i 'dod yon rdzogs shing lhan skyes kyi
NK063(gu)001:1132: ye shes bsten pa'i gzhi yin la tha mal las
NK063(gu)001:1133: khyad par du byas pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:1134: ji skad du rgyas pa las /
NK063(gu)001:1135: nub phyogs 'og min gnas mchog tu //
NK063(gu)001:1136: ma chags pad+ma'i gdan bting ba //
NK063(gu)001:1137: dus gsum rgyal ba bzhug pa'i gnas //
NK063(gu)001:1140: 'di zhes nye bar mtshon pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:1141: e sogs rnam bzhi'i dbyibs can gnas //
NK063(gu)001:1143: e wam ma ya mkha' ldan gnas //
NK063(gu)001:1146: de la nye bar mtshon pa ni gnas te khyams
NK063(gu)001:1147: dang sgo dang bya'i gdong dang za ma tog rnams
NK063(gu)001:1148: drag rgyas zhi dbang du gnas pa ni sangs rgyas
NK063(gu)001:1149: ril gyi bzhugs gnas su gsungs so //
NK063(gu)001:1151: zab mo'i rgyud gzhan las kyang /
NK063(gu)001:1152: btsun mo'i b+ha ga rnams la bzhugs so //
NK063(gu)001:1154: tha ma ni 'dir 'chad pa'i gnas kyi ngo bo'i
NK063(gu)001:1155: chos gazhi'am rgyu la sogs pa nas gdan khri'i bar
NK063(gu)001:1157: de ni gnas kyi che ba yon tan thams cad
NK063(gu)001:1158: kyi blar gyur pa'i phyir 'og min chen po zhes
NK063(gu)001:1159: bya'o // de yang gong gi rnam grangs lnga las bar ma gsum gyi bdag nyid du gyur cing /
NK063(gu)001:1160: dang po las yon tan nyis 'gyur gyis dpags te /
NK063(gu)001:1161: ji skad du rgya mtsho las /
NK063(gu)001:1163: nyis 'gyur shin tu dpags pa'i gnas //
NK063(gu)001:1164: ngo bo mtha' dbus med pa yi //
NK063(gu)001:1165: yon tan lnga yi bdag nyid de //
NK063(gu)001:1166: ma spangs rgyan sogs gzhal yas khang //
NK063(gu)001:1167: gru bzhi spyi bo 'khyil nang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:1170: gtsang ma'i rigs dag rnam spangs pa //
NK063(gu)001:1171: 'og min chen po'i gnas mchog na //
NK063(gu)001:1172: zhes gsungs pa ltar yin no //
NK063(gu)001:1173: de'i rang bzhin ni chos nyid yin la de mtha'
NK063(gu)001:1174: dang bral ba'i phyir dbus su 'dzin pa'ang med pa
NK063(gu)001:1175: na de la chos kyi dbyings kyis mngon par mtho
NK063(gu)001:1178: de'i phyir dbyings de gnas de'i gzhi yin la /
NK063(gu)001:1179: de nyid ye shes chen po'i tshad gdul bya'i blos gzung du med pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:1180: ye shes kyi zhes pa ye shes las grub pa
NK063(gu)001:1181: gzhal yas kyi gzhi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba
NK063(gu)001:1182: dang bcas par gsal ba ni ye shes yin la
NK063(gu)001:1183: / rgyu ni ye shes rin po che zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:1184: ye shes la rin po cher 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan
NK063(gu)001:1185: / ni / ye shes nyid dbyibs dang kha dog tu snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:1186: snang ba des gdul bya'i re ba skong ba'i phyir rin po che zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:1188: sangs rgyas rnams kyi ye shes rgya mtsho chen po'i
NK063(gu)001:1189: nang na ye shes kyi rin po che chen po
NK063(gu)001:1190: bsod nams dang ye shes dang yon tan phun sum
NK063(gu)001:1193: rgya khyon ni rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad
NK063(gu)001:1194: pa zhes pa gong nas mtha' dang dbus med pa
NK063(gu)001:1195: na zhes mtha' dbus dang bral ba'i phyir rgya ma
NK063(gu)001:1196: chad pa ste shes bya'i khyab byed du gnas pa
NK063(gu)001:1197: yin no // dbyibs ni 'bru bsgyur te /
NK063(gu)001:1198: gru bzhi gyur pa ni ye shes la 'bras bu
NK063(gu)001:1199: che ba'i yon tan dpag tu med pa rgyas pa'i
NK063(gu)001:1200: phyir ro // 'dir rgya ma chad pa dang dbyibs gru bzhir gyur pa 'gal lo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1201: 'dir yang shes rab long ba'i bshad pa'i skyon spangs
NK063(gu)001:1202: te mi mthun pa'i tshig don sdeb pa ni snang
NK063(gu)001:1203: ba gnyis kyi phyir mi 'gal te /
NK063(gu)001:1204: rgya ni de pa'i snang yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:1205: dbyibs ni gdul bya'i snang ba'i ngos nas yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1206: yang na gdul bya'i snang ba rang gi ngos nas
NK063(gu)001:1207: kyang pany+tsa re kh+aa'i rgya ma chad cing de nyid
NK063(gu)001:1208: da byibs gru bzhir gyur pa yang 'gal ba med
NK063(gu)001:1209: do // rtse mo ni tha dad med pa'i dgongs
NK063(gu)001:1210: pa mthar thug pa med pa mnga' ba'i rtags su
NK063(gu)001:1211: gzhal yas khang gi rtse mo tog stong 'bar ba
NK063(gu)001:1213: rgyan ni rnam grangs bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:1214: ye shes rang snang rgyu'i rgyan ni /
NK063(gu)001:1215: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1216: phreng ba la sogs kyi rgyan ni /
NK063(gu)001:1217: ye shes rin po che sna tshogs kyi phreng ba zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1218: bkra shis 'dod yon gyi rgyan ni /
NK063(gu)001:1219: gzugs sna tshogs dang zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1220: mdzes pa rta babs kyi rgyan ni 'og tu 'chad de /
NK063(gu)001:1222: 'dir yang kha cig 'dod yon 'di dag 'di nas phyogs bcu dang /
NK063(gu)001:1224: sna tshogs mchod byed rol mo yis //
NK063(gu)001:1225: bar snang khams su sprin phung bzhin //
NK063(gu)001:1227: bar snang du 'khrigs par bshad pa gnyis 'gal zhes zer ba ni ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:1228: phyogs bcu dang bar snang gnyis mun snang ltar phan tshun spangs pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1229: tsha grang ltar lhan cig mi gnas pa'i 'gal ba gang yang ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1230: 'on kyang rgyud dang sgrub thabs cung zad mi mthun
NK063(gu)001:1231: pa ni snang ba gnyis kyi phyir te phyogs bcur
NK063(gu)001:1233: bar snang du 'khrigs pa gdul bya'i snang ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:1235: theg pa dang sa lam gzhan las 'di khyad par
NK063(gu)001:1236: du gyur pa'i gzhal yas khang gi sgo nas pho
NK063(gu)001:1237: brang lte ba'i bar rdo rje 'greng bu re res
NK063(gu)001:1238: spags pa dang / 'di nyid kyi dgongs pa'i don
NK063(gu)001:1239: la mthar thug pa med pa'i phyir gzhal yas khang
NK063(gu)001:1240: gi rtse mo mtho dman gyi tshad dpag tu med
NK063(gu)001:1241: pa ste de pa'i dbu'i gtsug tor lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:1242: 'o na gong gi rtse mo'i don dang zlos so zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1243: gong ma rtse mo'i rnam pa yin cing 'di tshad yin no //
NK063(gu)001:1244: glo 'bur ni lhag pa'i zhes pa ma dgongs nas dang /
NK063(gu)001:1246: 'dir phyi ma ste de la don dang rtags gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:1247: don ni ye shes re re yang lnga lngas khyad
NK063(gu)001:1248: par du byas pas gdul bya'i 'dod pa skong ba'i
NK063(gu)001:1250: rtags ni gzhal yas khang gi phyogs bzhir lha mi
NK063(gu)001:1251: bzhugs pa'i khang pa bzhi glo 'bur gyi tshul gyis
NK063(gu)001:1252: mdzad pa ste / de yang mkhar thabs la sogs
NK063(gu)001:1253: dbyibs dang dkar ser la sogs kha dog gi khyad
NK063(gu)001:1255: sgo ni 'di'i lam gyi ting nge 'dzin bzhi ni rnam par thar pa bzhi'o //
NK063(gu)001:1256: de nas 'jug pa'i phyir gzhal yas khang gi phyogs
NK063(gu)001:1257: bzhir sgo bzhir 'byung ste sgo khyud ces pa ngos
NK063(gu)001:1258: dang 'gram pa dang ya phubs la sogs so //
NK063(gu)001:1259: can zhes pa de rnams rgyan gyi bye brag sna tshogs dang ldan pa'i sgra yin te /
NK063(gu)001:1260: ji skad du rngam glog las /
NK063(gu)001:1261: gzhal yas de yi sgo bzhi na //
NK063(gu)001:1262: glang seng rnams kyis mdzes par byas //
NK063(gu)001:1265: ye nas mnyam nyid mi g.yo'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:1266: ta la'i ljon shing rang bzhin gnas //
NK063(gu)001:1268: rta babs ni rnam par thar pa brgyad ces pas /
NK063(gu)001:1269: de ni pi na tar las /
NK063(gu)001:1270: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub dang //
NK063(gu)001:1271: bya ba'i rgyud dang gnyis ka'i rgyud //
NK063(gu)001:1272: rnal 'byor bskyed dang rdzogs pa'i tshul //
NK063(gu)001:1273: rnam thar brgyad kyi rta babs ldan //
NK063(gu)001:1276: theg pa brgyad la sbyangs pa las snang ba'i phyir nye bar mtshon pa zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:1277: de dag gi mtshon byed du rgyan gyi rta babs brgyad du byung ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:1278: ldan pa zhes pa de yang rgyan dang ldan pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:1279: ta la'i ljon shing dang gser gyi tsong tsong gis
NK063(gu)001:1280: sbrel ba rat+na'i phra mig gis spras pa la sogs
NK063(gu)001:1281: pa ste / stod na pad+ma'i khong gseng la rat+na'i zar tshags dang /
NK063(gu)001:1282: shar bu dang phreng ba dang sgrom dang g.yas g.yon na khyung mgos brgyan pa'am /
NK063(gu)001:1283: yang na chos kyi ri dwags kyis chos kyi 'khor
NK063(gu)001:1284: lo bskor ba'i tshul dang 'khor lo rim pa bcu
NK063(gu)001:1285: gsum gyi steng na rat+na'i gdugs kyis mdzes shing tog
NK063(gu)001:1286: dang ldan pa'o // de yang ji skad du rgyas pa las /
NK063(gu)001:1287: zhabs dang ma chags za ra tshags //
NK063(gu)001:1289: sna tshogs khyung mgos rim par 'khrigs //
NK063(gu)001:1291: rta babs rnams kyi rtse mo la //
NK063(gu)001:1292: gser gyi dril bu 'bar ba dag /
NK063(gu)001:1293: dkon cog gsum gyi sgra yang sgrogs //
NK063(gu)001:1296: dbyer med mngon du byas pas phyi sems can gyi
NK063(gu)001:1297: rtog pa dang nang rgyal ba'i thugs gnyis tha dad
NK063(gu)001:1298: du 'dzin pa med pas shes bya'i dkyil 'khor kun
NK063(gu)001:1299: tu yang ye shes su gsal ba las gzhan ma
NK063(gu)001:1300: dmigs pa'i phyir nang du gyur pa zhes bya ste
NK063(gu)001:1302: phyi nang gnyis ka phyi nyid nang //
NK063(gu)001:1304: de mtshon pa la gdul bya'i don gzhal yas kyi
NK063(gu)001:1305: phyi nang thams cad mi sgrib par gsal ba yin
NK063(gu)001:1306: no // gdan khri la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:1307: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:1308: sa'i khyad par bgrod pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:1309: yon tan gyi che ba bcom pa'i gdan no //
NK063(gu)001:1311: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo gsal
NK063(gu)001:1312: ba la zhes pa'i 'bru gnas kyi rang bzhin gyi
NK063(gu)001:1314: 'dir gdan gyi dbang du cung zad sbyar na 'bras
NK063(gu)001:1315: bu chos kyi 'khor lo rgyun mi 'chad pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:1316: gzhal yas khang gi gzhi 'khor lo chen po gcig
NK063(gu)001:1318: de nyid gdul bya'i blos tshad gzung du med cing
NK063(gu)001:1319: ye shes las grub pa'i phyir 'od zer kha dog
NK063(gu)001:1320: lngar gsal ba la 'od kyi phreng ba phyi nang
NK063(gu)001:1323: de pa rnams la thugs mi 'jigs pa bzhi lhun
NK063(gu)001:1324: gyi grub pa'i rtags su dbus su seng ge brgyad
NK063(gu)001:1325: rat+na'i khri rkang gi bar du phyogs rer yang gnyis
NK063(gu)001:1326: gnyis gshibs nas kha phyir bltas pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1327: sku stobs bcu dang ldan pa'i rtags su shar du glang po che brgyad dang /
NK063(gu)001:1328: yon tan rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su lhor rta brgyad dang /
NK063(gu)001:1329: gsung dbang bcu dang ldan pa'i rtags su nub tu rma bya brgyad dang /
NK063(gu)001:1330: phrin las bzhis 'gro ba thogs pa med par sgrol
NK063(gu)001:1331: ba'i rtags su byang du nam mkha' lding brgyad do
NK063(gu)001:1332: // de dag pin tar las kyang /
NK063(gu)001:1333: thugs ni mi 'jigs bzhi yis bdud bzhi 'joms //
NK063(gu)001:1334: de grub rtags su seng ge'i khri la bzhugs //
NK063(gu)001:1335: sku ni stobs bcus mi dge bcu rnams 'dul //
NK063(gu)001:1336: de grub rtags su glang po'i khri la bzhugs //
NK063(gu)001:1337: yon tan rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis chags med sgrol //
NK063(gu)001:1338: de grub rtags su rta mchog khri la bzhugs //
NK063(gu)001:1339: gsung ni dbang bcu mthar phyin rgyal po'i tshul //
NK063(gu)001:1340: de grub rtags su rma bya'i khri la bzhugs //
NK063(gu)001:1341: las ni phrin las rnam bzhis skye bzhi sgrol //
NK063(gu)001:1342: de grub rtags su mkha' lding khri la bzhugs //
NK063(gu)001:1344: 'o na mi 'jigs pa bzhi mi bskyod pa kho
NK063(gu)001:1345: na la grub kyi rgyal ba gzhan la ma grub
NK063(gu)001:1346: bam zhe na / ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:1347: thams cad la thams cad grub cing 'dir so sor
NK063(gu)001:1348: sbyar ba ni chos mthun pa brtsis pa yin no
NK063(gu)001:1349: // gal te seng ge la sogs pa 'di rnams
NK063(gu)001:1350: thugs ye shes rang snang gi gdan yin nam 'on
NK063(gu)001:1351: te smon lam gus pa'i gdan yin /
NK063(gu)001:1352: dang po ltar na lung rig gnyis kyis gnod de /
NK063(gu)001:1354: byang chub sems dpa' smon lam dbang //
NK063(gu)001:1355: thos pa rgya mtsho bsags pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:1356: lus ni seng ge gdan du sprul //
NK063(gu)001:1359: byang chub sems dpa' gcig gcig kyang brgyad brgyad ces pa dang 'gal lo //
NK063(gu)001:1360: rig pa'i gnod byed kyang 'dul byed sprul pa ba de don med du 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:1361: gdul bya med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1362: gnyis pa ltar na spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:1363: 'bras bu chos bzhi dang bcu gnyis gnyis dang /
NK063(gu)001:1364: thams cad mkhyen pa nyid rdzogs pas zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1365: gzhan yang gong ltar pin tar dang yang 'gal lo //
NK063(gu)001:1367: 'dul byed med pa'i gdul bya mi srid do zhes zer te /
NK063(gu)001:1370: ye shes rang snang dang smon lam gus pa gnyis car yin no //
NK063(gu)001:1371: de la kha cig do mi 'thad de /
NK063(gu)001:1372: de gnyis tha dad cing khyad par yang yod pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1373: spyir rgyud tha dad la bltas nas khyad par yod kyang /
NK063(gu)001:1374: skabs 'dir de gnyis rgyud tha dad par ma grub
NK063(gu)001:1375: pas seng ge la sogs gzhi gcig gi steng du
NK063(gu)001:1376: ye shes rang snang dang smon lam gus pa gnyis
NK063(gu)001:1378: dper na dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi chibs pa de
NK063(gu)001:1379: slob mas dad pas phul ba dang de nyid dge
NK063(gu)001:1380: bshes kyi bsod nams las grub pa gnyis rta gcig
NK063(gu)001:1381: gi steng du mtshungs pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:1382: rgyal ba rnams la mi 'jigs pa bzhi la sogs
NK063(gu)001:1383: pa lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su seng ge la
NK063(gu)001:1384: sogs pa'i gdan du snang la /
NK063(gu)001:1385: sa la gnas pa'i sems dpa' yang lus sgrib kyi
NK063(gu)001:1386: cha dang bcas pa rnams seng ge la sogs par
NK063(gu)001:1387: sprul nas dbu'i gtsug tor gyi zhabs kyi gdan khri
NK063(gu)001:1388: bteg pas nyon sgrib sbyong zhing /
NK063(gu)001:1389: rna bas chos nyan pas shes sgrib sbyong ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:1391: tha ni 'bru bsgyur te dang la rin po che'i zhes pa /
NK063(gu)001:1392: rat+na'i khri rkang gis bteg pa'i gdung gi logs la
NK063(gu)001:1393: spar khab bdun bdun yod pa ni 'bras bu'i chos
NK063(gu)001:1394: dkor bdun lhun gyis grub par mtshon pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:1395: de'i dbus na mtha'i skyon gyis gos pa med pa'i
NK063(gu)001:1396: rtags su pad+ma'i sdong po rgyas pa na yal ga
NK063(gu)001:1397: las me tog kha mar log pas rat+na'i gdung dang
NK063(gu)001:1398: sems can gyi sgal pa g.yogs shing yar la log
NK063(gu)001:1399: pas nyi zla'i gdong g.yogs pa yin zhes gsung ngo
NK063(gu)001:1400: // rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK063(gu)001:1401: par dag cing 'od gsal ba mtshon pa'i phyir ram
NK063(gu)001:1402: thabs shes rab gnyis mtshon pa la nyi zla'i dkyil
NK063(gu)001:1403: // 'khor ro // 'og nas gdan zhes pa de dag gi brtseg lugs ni /
NK063(gu)001:1405: theg le chen po dang sa bon ni thams cad
NK063(gu)001:1406: kyi byed pa po'i phyir bdag po dang rdo rje
NK063(gu)001:1407: ste dbus na zla ba blar gnas so zhes so
NK063(gu)001:1408: // de la kha cig phyi grol lam ltar du
NK063(gu)001:1409: don dam rgyu dang kun rdzob 'bras bu la dgongs
NK063(gu)001:1410: // shing / nang steng sgo ltar du snying tshil
NK063(gu)001:1411: dkar po steng dang snying sha dmar po 'og na
NK063(gu)001:1413: gsang ba 'og sgo ltar du yab kyi thig le
NK063(gu)001:1414: dkar po steng nas 'bab cing yum gyi thig le
NK063(gu)001:1415: dmar po 'og nas 'byung ba la dgongs zhes zer
NK063(gu)001:1416: ro // kha cig ni chos mthun yin te kun
NK063(gu)001:1417: tu bzang po rgyud kyi byed pa po yin zhing
NK063(gu)001:1418: rdo rje sems dpa' dkyil 'khor gyi byed pa po
NK063(gu)001:1419: ro // yin la / thig le chen po 'das pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1420: sa bon ni 'khor ba'i byed pa po yin pa'i phyir zla dkyil steng du byung zer te /
NK063(gu)001:1422: gtso bo ni shes rab la spyod pa'i phyir dang
NK063(gu)001:1423: nang gi chu skyes nyi ma'i lte ba la zla
NK063(gu)001:1424: ba brten pa'i phyir ri bong can steng na gnas
NK063(gu)001:1426: gzhan yang zla ba slar gnas pa ni thabs mtshon
NK063(gu)001:1427: pa'i phyir ro zhes gsungs pas shes so gsung ngo
NK063(gu)001:1428: // la zhes pa gnas gzhi'i sgras bstan de dag la gong gi ston pa'i bdag nyid /
NK063(gu)001:1429: 'og nas 'byung ba 'chad pa'i skyes bu rnams bzhugs par mtshon pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:1430: gsum pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa la rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:1431: gnyis med kyi 'khor ni bcom ldan 'das zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:1432: la sogs te / de yang bcom ldan 'das dang de bzhin gshegs pa gnyis sngar bshad zin te /
NK063(gu)001:1433: ston pa'i bdag nyid dang mtshan thun mong ba yin pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:1434: de ltar yang spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:1435: mtshan mthun pa ni sngar thal te zhes pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1436: 'dir kha cig rigs lnga la sogs pa'i 'khor 'di
NK063(gu)001:1437: rnams la sangs rgyas kyi mtshan nas mi smos par
NK063(gu)001:1438: rtog pa'i ming nas smos pa'i 'bad pa ji ltar
NK063(gu)001:1439: yin zhe na / bla ma'i gsung sgros kyi rgyu mtshan gnyis kyis grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:1440: 'og sgo'i gleng gzhi'i skabs su rtog pa rnams 'khor yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:1441: rtog pa'i rang bzhin sangs rgyas yin pa'i phyir zhes gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:1442: de ltar yin par ma grub ce na /
NK063(gu)001:1444: ji skad du thal rgyud las /
NK063(gu)001:1445: ma da ma nu sdom byed yid //
NK063(gu)001:1446: lus can rnam shes de dag la //
NK063(gu)001:1447: gsal bar go bas zhes pas 'og sgo'i skabs su 'khor yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:1449: phung po lnga nyid mngon sangs rgyas //
NK063(gu)001:1450: zhes pas rtog pa'i rang bzhin sangs rgyas yin par gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1451: slob dpon sgeg pas kyang 'di bzhed de /
NK063(gu)001:1453: de dag kar dag par thugs su chud pa las
NK063(gu)001:1454: rdo rje 'dzin pa la sogs par snang ba'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:1455: ro zhes gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:1456: de yang rnam par shes pa'i zhes pa chos rig cing gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:1457: rgyal po zhes pa lnga char rang bzhin rtog pa
NK063(gu)001:1458: las khyad par rgyal ba'i skur dbang sgyur bas sam
NK063(gu)001:1459: / yang na zag pa med pa'i longs spyod la mnga' brnyes pas so //
NK063(gu)001:1460: de bzhin du gzugs kyi zhes pa gzhig cing gzhom du rung ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:1461: tshor ba'i zhes pa nyams su myong ba'i rang bzhin can dang /
NK063(gu)001:1462: 'du shes kyi zhes pa yul la mtshan mar 'dzin pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1463: 'du byed kyi zhes pa rgyu rkyen las skyes pa'i
NK063(gu)001:1464: sems mngon par 'du byed pa rnams rdo rje mi
NK063(gu)001:1465: bskyod pa la sogs pa 'chad pa'i skyes bu lnga'i
NK063(gu)001:1466: bdag nyid do // yang 'di bsam par bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:1467: gong ltar spyir rtog pa smos pa'i dgos pa grub
NK063(gu)001:1468: kyang bye brag tu rnam shes mi bskyod pa kho
NK063(gu)001:1469: nar sbyor ba la rgyu mtshan med de /
NK063(gu)001:1470: de tshod du rnam shes rnam snang yin pa cis 'gog ce na /
NK063(gu)001:1473: rnam shes dag pa thugs yin la de rdo rje'i rigs mi bskyod pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:1474: dper na rgyal po'i bu yin pa la rgyal rigs zer ba bzhin no zhes smras pa la /
NK063(gu)001:1475: mi bskyod pa thugs kyi rigs yin par ma grub bo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1477: ji skad du glang po rab 'bog las /
NK063(gu)001:1478: don dam par sems can gyi rnam par shes pa
NK063(gu)001:1479: gnas su dag pa de pa'i thugs kyi bdag nyid
NK063(gu)001:1480: ces pa nas / bcom ldan 'das rdo rje mi bskyod pa zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1482: rnam shes mi bskyod rang bzhin te //
NK063(gu)001:1484: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i gzhung las /
NK063(gu)001:1485: rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK063(gu)001:1487: mi bskyod yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK063(gu)001:1489: de dag gi yum ni btsun mo zhes pa la
NK063(gu)001:1490: spyir d+hoo sid kyi sgra las drangs na bskyed pa
NK063(gu)001:1492: 'dir de gnyis ka'i chos dang ldan te /
NK063(gu)001:1493: rtogs pa'i skabs su sra ba la sogs pa'i phung po lnga skyed cing /
NK063(gu)001:1494: de dag gnas 'gyur gyi skabs su 'byung ba lnga
NK063(gu)001:1495: dag pa'i yum lnga ni phung po lnga dag pa
NK063(gu)001:1496: rigs lnga'i spyad par bya ba'i yul yin pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:1497: ro // dam pa zhes pa la kha cig sems
NK063(gu)001:1498: dpa'i yum las khyad par du gyur pas dam pa
NK063(gu)001:1499: zer ba ni mi 'thad par sems te /
NK063(gu)001:1500: 'dir rgyud gcig gis bsdus pa'i rtog pa dang sbyar ba'i phyir de ltar ma yin par 'gyur ro //
NK063(gu)001:1501: des na rang bzhin rtog pa las rgyal ba'i skur mngon du byas pas so //
NK063(gu)001:1502: snang ba'i zhes pa la sogs gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:1503: dbyings dang zhes pa lnga char sras kyi dkyil 'khor
NK063(gu)001:1504: bskyed pa'am yon tan dang bde ba'i 'byung khungs su
NK063(gu)001:1505: gyur pas na'o // btsun mo zhes pa bshad zin la /
NK063(gu)001:1506: tshogs zhes pa mang po'i sgra ste /
NK063(gu)001:1507: 'dil kha cig spyir thabs dang shes rab dbyer med
NK063(gu)001:1508: kyi rgyud gsum las 'di yum shas che ba'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:1509: shes rab kyi rgyud du ngos gzung zhes zer ba
NK063(gu)001:1511: yab yum grangs mnyam du yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1512: des na shes rab yum gyi tshogs dang thabs yab
NK063(gu)001:1513: rnams gnyis su med par sbyar bas lhan cig skyes
NK063(gu)001:1514: pa'i sku bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin no //
