NK063(gu)001:1515: rgyas sras sems dpa' ni byang zhes pa mig shes la sogs pa rtog pa rnams so //
NK063(gu)001:1516: chub ces pa sa snying la sogs sems dpar grub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:1517: chen po zhes pa rgyud mas sbyangs kyi sems dpa' las khyad par du gyur bas so //
NK063(gu)001:1518: rdo rjee zhes pa la kha cig 'grel ba ltar
NK063(gu)001:1519: lta ba'i sgrib pa 'joms pa la 'dod pa ni
NK063(gu)001:1521: sgrib pa de med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1522: de med par ma grub ce na /
NK063(gu)001:1524: 'di rnams thugs yas sprul du bsgrub pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1525: des na spyir rdo rjer brjod pa'i rgyu mtshan lnga
NK063(gu)001:1526: las 'di mig shes dang sa snying gnyis rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:1527: dbyer med yin pa'i phyir der brjod do snyam du
NK063(gu)001:1528: sems so // mthong ba la sogs gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:1529: de dag gi yum ni btsun mo zhes pa gong
NK063(gu)001:1530: ltar rtog pa'i dus su gzugs la sogs pa yul
NK063(gu)001:1531: bzhis mig shes la sogs rnam shes bzhi bskyed la
NK063(gu)001:1532: / gnas 'gyur gyi skabs su la s+ya la sogs
NK063(gu)001:1533: sems ma 'di rnams sa snying la sogs thugs kyi
NK063(gu)001:1534: sems dpa'i yum yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1535: mthong bar bya ba la sogs gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:1536: de la kha cig yul dang yul can 'khrul te /
NK063(gu)001:1537: rna ba'i yul sgra gi rtir 'thad cing sna'i yul dri m+aa ler 'thad do zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1538: 'grel chen gyis yul dang yul can du bya ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:1539: rigs kyi dbang du byas pa la gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:1541: de ltar phyi'i sems dpa'i yab yum rnams gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:1542: 'jigs byed chen po'i 'khor ni 'joms pa zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:1543: khro bo rnams kyi mdzad pas gdul bya gdug pa
NK063(gu)001:1545: chen po zhes pa gnod sbyin dang srin po la sogs pa las khyad par du gyur pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:1547: de dag gis gsod cing 'joms pa ni rang la
NK063(gu)001:1548: sdig pas gos shing gzhal la sdug bsngal bskyed pas
NK063(gu)001:1549: 'joms pa yin kyang chen po ma yin la /
NK063(gu)001:1550: khro bo rnams kyi mdzad pas ni de gnyis dang
NK063(gu)001:1551: bral ba'i phyir sgra don dang ldan pa yin no
NK063(gu)001:1552: // rdo rje ni gong ltar reg sogs lus kyi
NK063(gu)001:1553: chos bzhi dang gshed po la sogs khro bo bzhi
NK063(gu)001:1554: rang bzhin dbyer med yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1555: reg pa dang zhes pa la sogs pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:1557: lus kyi reg pa la sogs ni gsang ba'i rnam
NK063(gu)001:1558: shes te gzhan yang dor ba ma yin no zhes
NK063(gu)001:1559: pas phyi nang gnyis su gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:1561: gtso bo dang 'khor du bcas pa de dag kun
NK063(gu)001:1562: kyang zhes sku mdog 'di rnams gang la yod pa'i
NK063(gu)001:1565: rang bzhin gyi sku mdog go //
NK063(gu)001:1566: dang po ni stong pa nyid kyi ye shes la
NK063(gu)001:1567: 'gyur ba med pa'i phyir mi bskyod pa la sogs
NK063(gu)001:1568: rdo rje'i rigs thams cad mthing kha dang /
NK063(gu)001:1569: me long lta bu'i ye shes la nyes pa'i skyon
NK063(gu)001:1570: gyis ma gos pa'i phyir rnam snang la sogs de
NK063(gu)001:1572: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes la che ba'i yon
NK063(gu)001:1573: tan rgyas pa'i phyir rin 'byung la sogs rat+na'i rigs
NK063(gu)001:1574: ser po dang / so sor rtog pa'i ye shes
NK063(gu)001:1575: kyis gdul bya la chags pa'i phyir mtha' yas la
NK063(gu)001:1576: sogs pad+ma'i rigs le brgan dang /
NK063(gu)001:1577: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyis las sna tshogs
NK063(gu)001:1578: grub pa'i phyir don grub la sogs las kyi rigs
NK063(gu)001:1580: 'tsher ba zhes pa ni gnyis pa rang bzhin gyi sku mdog ste /
NK063(gu)001:1581: thugs la ma rig pa med pa'i rtags su dung
NK063(gu)001:1582: dang nyi ma dang zla ba dang ku mu ta
NK063(gu)001:1583: dang gser sbyangs dang dngul dang shel gyi kha dog
NK063(gu)001:1584: lta bu ste / gsal zhing dag pa dang ma
NK063(gu)001:1585: ni sku mdog thams cad la khyab byed du yod
NK063(gu)001:1586: lta bu ste / pa yin no // tshad ni /
NK063(gu)001:1587: chos kyi dbyings zhes pa la sogs khyab pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:1588: de lta bu tshogs zhes pa la sogs mang ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:1589: gnyis su med par bzhugs so zhes pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:1592: thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1594: gnas kyi phyir bzhag pa'o zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:1595: mtshungs pa bzhi'i phyir ston 'khor dgongs pa tha dad pa med par bzhugs pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:1596: da ni 'di dpyad par bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:1597: le'u dang po'i 'khor 'di rnams rgyud mas sbyangs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:1598: 'khor yin nam 'on te thugs las sprul pa yin
NK063(gu)001:1599: nam / 'on te de gnyis ka zhes gsum du brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:1600: dang po ltar na skyon gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:1601: 'di nyid kyi rtsa bshad dang 'gal ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:1602: man ngag dang 'gal ba dang rig pa'i gnod byed dang gsum mo //
NK063(gu)001:1603: de dag rim par brjod na dang po ni /
NK063(gu)001:1605: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1607: sems dpa' che dang 'joms pa che //
NK063(gu)001:1608: de bzhin thugs kyi khyad par las //
NK063(gu)001:1609: zhes skyes bu rnams ston pa nyid dang khyad par
NK063(gu)001:1610: med cing sems dpa' dang sgo ba yang nyid kyi
NK063(gu)001:1611: thugs kyi khyad par las snang bar bshad pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:1612: ro // gnyis pa ni spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:1613: mtshan thun mong pa gnyis nas sngar thal te zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1615: mtshungs pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:1616: lngas kyang bstan pa gsung mi 'gal //
NK063(gu)001:1617: zhes ston pa nyid dang khyad par med cing rgyud
NK063(gu)001:1618: kyi byed pa po skyes bu lnga yin par bshad
NK063(gu)001:1619: pa'i phyir ro // tha ma ni 'khor 'di rnams
NK063(gu)001:1620: rgyud mas sbyangs yin na gang zag gcig gam tha
NK063(gu)001:1622: dang po ltar na gtso 'khor dang sangs rgyas ma
NK063(gu)001:1623: rgyas gcig pa la 'gal ba'i chos ldan yin la
NK063(gu)001:1624: / gnyis pa ltar na 'di nas gcig go rtog pa las ma smos pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1625: gnyis pa thugs yas sprul yin na yang skyon gsum gong ltar rim par brjod de /
NK063(gu)001:1626: rtsa rgyud 'di'i le'u gnyis pa las /
NK063(gu)001:1627: thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyi mkhyen to zhes /
NK063(gu)001:1628: dbang ma thob bar du ston pa'i dgongs pa ji
NK063(gu)001:1629: lta bar 'khor gyis nyams su ma myong bar bshad
NK063(gu)001:1630: pa dang / yang bshad rgyud las /
NK063(gu)001:1631: rang snang rgyal ba'i sems sogs pa //
NK063(gu)001:1632: dang po'i sangs rgyas sar rgyal ba //
NK063(gu)001:1633: zhes sems dpa' la sogs sa la sbyangs pas rgyal bar gyur par mngon pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1636: gdul byas las mthar thug pa ni sangs rgyas kyi
NK063(gu)001:1637: zhing du 'gyur te zhes mthar lam bar bshad pa'i
NK063(gu)001:1638: phyir ro // tha ma ni gdul byed sprul pa ba de dgos pa med par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:1639: gdul bya rang rgyud pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1640: rtags de ma grub bo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1641: sngar dang brtag pa mtshungs te rang rgyud pa tha dad yod dam gcig yod /
NK063(gu)001:1642: dang po ltar na gcig gi rtog pa las ma smos shing /
NK063(gu)001:1643: gnyis pa ltar na lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las
NK063(gu)001:1644: mi mnga' bar 'gyur te sprul pa du mas gdul
NK063(gu)001:1645: bya gcig gi don byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1646: 'o na gsum pa sbyangs sprul gnyis ka yin pa
NK063(gu)001:1647: la gang gis gnod ce na gong ltar skyon gsum
NK063(gu)001:1648: ste / lung ni rgya mtsho las /
NK063(gu)001:1649: don bsdus gsung rab bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK063(gu)001:1650: de las lhag pa'i don smra ba //
NK063(gu)001:1651: zhes nges don sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su
NK063(gu)001:1652: sangs rgyas par bshad pas de mi tshang par 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:1654: man ngag ni spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:1655: rigs lnga dang sems dpa'i skabs su rtog pa smos pa'i rjes su mthun zhes pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:1656: yang de dag kar dag pa thugs su chud pas
NK063(gu)001:1657: rdo rje 'dzin pa la sogs par rang snang ba'i
NK063(gu)001:1658: phyir zhes bshad pa dang 'gal zhing /
NK063(gu)001:1659: rig pa ni kar dag kyang sangs rgyas min na
NK063(gu)001:1660: rigs lnga nyid kyang sangs rgyas min par 'gyur zhing
NK063(gu)001:1661: / byang chub sems dpa' zer bas rgyud mas sbyangs
NK063(gu)001:1662: yin na ma h+aa'i mthar thug yi ge 'khor lo
NK063(gu)001:1663: tshogs chen gyi byang chub sems dpa' yang rgyud mas
NK063(gu)001:1664: sbyangs su 'gyur ro zhes 'gegs par snang ngo //
NK063(gu)001:1665: dgag pa 'di rnams ma nges par sems te /
NK063(gu)001:1667: dang po lung gi dgongs pa gzhan yin te /
NK063(gu)001:1668: nges don bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su bshad cing de ma tshang yang 'dir mi gnod de /
NK063(gu)001:1669: 'di ni 'khor gyi rnam grangs so bzhi las ma gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1670: man ngag gi dgongs pa yang rtog pa smos shing
NK063(gu)001:1671: kar dag pa nyid kyi phyir rgyud sbyangs su bsgrub
NK063(gu)001:1672: tu rung ngo // rig pa dang po la thal 'gyur gyi gnas med de /
NK063(gu)001:1673: rtog pa dag kyang sangs rgyas min par sus khas blangs /
NK063(gu)001:1674: rig pa gnyis pa yang ma h+aa'i yig log la
NK063(gu)001:1675: rgyud sbyangs khegs par rgyud 'grel gang nas kyang ma
NK063(gu)001:1676: bshad do // gzhan yang sprul pa ba dang rtog
NK063(gu)001:1677: pa gnyis lhan cig mi gnas pa yin par sems
NK063(gu)001:1678: bshad do // te / gang sprul pa ba yin
NK063(gu)001:1679: pa la dag bya rtog pa med pa'i phyir ro
NK063(gu)001:1680: bshad do // te / // 'o na 'dir rtog pa smos pa dang 'gal zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1681: ci sprul pa la de dag yod nas smos pa
NK063(gu)001:1682: ma yin kyang gdul bya la yod pas de dag
NK063(gu)001:1683: tshul gyi mtshon byed du smos pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:1684: dper na mi blun po la ba glang du btags
NK063(gu)001:1685: pa de nog shal la sogs ldan nas btags pa
NK063(gu)001:1686: min gyi blun pa'i go byed du btags pa bzhin
NK063(gu)001:1687: no // des na spyir lhan cig pa'i 'khor 'di'i
NK063(gu)001:1688: skabs su sbyangs sprul gang yin zhes dpyad pa la
NK063(gu)001:1689: dgos pa yod par ma mthong ste /
NK063(gu)001:1690: rtog pa khyad par can mi skyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1691: gal te dgos pa yod na ston pa yang sbyangs
NK063(gu)001:1692: sprul gang yin zhes pa dang mtshungs par sems so
NK063(gu)001:1693: // ji srid dpyod na gnyis char yin pa bde bar seems te /
NK063(gu)001:1694: ji skad du spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:1695: mtshan thun mong ba gnyis ni lngar thal te zhes pas rigs lnga sprul par gsal zhing /
NK063(gu)001:1696: gdul bya las mthar thug pa ni zhes pas sems
NK063(gu)001:1697: dpa' rnams sbyangs pa ba yin par slob dpon sgeg
NK063(gu)001:1698: pa yang bzhed pa yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:1699: mang ba'i tshad kyi skabs su 'khor cha gnyis su
NK063(gu)001:1700: mngon pa yang 'di'i shes byed du 'gyur ba'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:1701: ro // mkhas pa kha cig kyang de ltar 'dod de /
NK063(gu)001:1702: de'i rgyu mtshan yang 'di nyid nas 'chad pa'i skyes bu la bcom ldan 'das zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1703: sems dpa' la byang chub chen po zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro zhes 'dod do //
NK063(gu)001:1704: 'dir bla ma gong ma rnams kyis rtog pa dang
NK063(gu)001:1705: sbyar ba'i 'khor 'di rnams thugs yas sprul du bzhed
NK063(gu)001:1706: do // 'o na gdul bya med pa'i sprul pa don med cing /
NK063(gu)001:1707: le'u gnyis pa las ston pa'i dgongs pa da gzod dbang thob nas myong bar bshad pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1709: de bzhin thugs kyi khyad par las //
NK063(gu)001:1710: rang snang rgyal ba'i sems sogs dang //
NK063(gu)001:1711: zhes pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1712: de dag de dang cha 'dra ba'i mthar lam pa
NK063(gu)001:1713: dang thun mong gi lam mthar phyin pa'i rgyal ba
NK063(gu)001:1714: brjod kyis mi lang ba rnams yod pa la dgongs
NK063(gu)001:1715: pa yin te / de ltar 'khor cha gnyis yod par yang 'di nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:1716: de lta bu'i tshogs brjod kyis mi long ba dang gnyis su med pa bzhugs so zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1718: dang po sangs rgyas sar rgyal ba //
NK063(gu)001:1719: sems dpa' che dang 'joms pa che //
NK063(gu)001:1720: brjod kyis mi lang tshad med dang //
NK063(gu)001:1721: rnam gnyis tshul du bzhugs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:1723: 'o na cha gnyis dang 'dir gang zag gcig gi
NK063(gu)001:1724: rtog pa las ma smos pa gnyis 'gal lo zhe
NK063(gu)001:1725: na / spyir cha gnyis yod pa las 'dir thugs ye shes rang snang gi dbang yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:1726: gdul bya'i rtog pa spyod tshul kyang sprul pa re
NK063(gu)001:1727: res rtog pa re re dag pa ma yin te
NK063(gu)001:1728: / sprul pa gcig gcig gis kyang rtog pa mtha'
NK063(gu)001:1729: dag dag pa yin pas des na ye shes rang
NK063(gu)001:1730: snang du bzhed pa'i phyir de'i rjes su 'brang ba
NK063(gu)001:1731: / yin no // gsum pa gleng gzhi bsdu ba la gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:1732: dang po ni ston pas gsungs pa de sdud pa
NK063(gu)001:1733: pos lo rgyus su brjod pa'i phyir mtshams sbyor sdud
NK063(gu)001:1737: gcus dang dkrugs dang gab pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:1738: rgyal ba nyid kyi lung yin te //
NK063(gu)001:1739: rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK063(gu)001:1741: gnyis pa bsdus pa dngos ni /
NK063(gu)001:1743: rgyud 'di rtsa ba'i rgyud yin la /
NK063(gu)001:1744: 'di'i yang rtsa ba ni bsdus pa 'di yin te /
NK063(gu)001:1745: ci'i phyir na rgyud 'di'i brjod bya snang ba gzhi yin la de 'dir bsdus pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:1746: gang zhe na de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid ces pa rang bzhin gyi snang ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:1747: de gzhi'i rgyud kyi mdor bstan nam rtsa ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:1748: rgyud kyi dbu zhabs brjod bya de dang de ston pa thams cad de las 'phros pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:1749: dbang sgyur zhes pa dang rang snang ba nyid ting
NK063(gu)001:1750: 'dzin gzugs brnyan sgyu ma rnam dag gsal ba ni
NK063(gu)001:1751: zhes pa gdul bya'i snang ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:1752: de lam gyi rgyud kyi rtsa ba'am mdor bstan yin
NK063(gu)001:1753: pa'i phyir rgyud dbu zhabs kyi brjod bya de dang
NK063(gu)001:1754: de ston pa thams cad de las 'phros pa yin
NK063(gu)001:1755: no // ye shes dkyil 'khor zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1756: sku gsung zhes pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo zhes pa rnams de pa'i snang ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:1757: de 'bras bu'i rgyud kyi rtsa ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:1758: rgyud dbu zhabs kyi brjod bya de dang de ston pa thams cad de las 'phros pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:1759: de ltar yin par yang rgya mdud 'grel las /
NK063(gu)001:1760: da ni rgyud phun sum tshogs pa bshad par bya ste zhes pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:1762: phyung ngo zhes pa'i bar rgyal tshab lngas gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1763: gsungs pa'i dngos gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1765: rdo rje mchog gi gnas nyid do zhes pa'i bar
NK063(gu)001:1766: gyi bsdus pa 'di rgyud don mdor bstan du bzhed
NK063(gu)001:1767: cing / le'u gsum pa man chad rgyud rgyas par bshad pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:1768: pin tar las kyang ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:1769: rgyud 'di nyid kyi mtshan gzhi'i don //
NK063(gu)001:1771: sku gsung yon tan phrin las thugs //
NK063(gu)001:1772: rdo rje las ni nges par byung /
NK063(gu)001:1774: rgyud mdor bstan du bshad pa'i phyir zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:1775: yang kha cig gis ni pin tar gyi le'u gnyis pa 'grel pa'i skabs na /
NK063(gu)001:1777: de nas ston pa rgyal mchog gis //
NK063(gu)001:1778: de la mdo yi don gleng ba //
NK063(gu)001:1779: de nyid don ni bsdu 'dod nas //
NK063(gu)001:1780: zhes pa'i phyir gleng gzhi bsdus pa yin zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:1781: 'dir gsung sgros kyis theg pa bsdu ba /
NK063(gu)001:1783: gleng gzhi bsdu ba zhes gsum du bzhed do //
NK063(gu)001:1784: de yang e zhes pa theg pa dgu'i don dang /
NK063(gu)001:1785: e ma zhes pa dkyil 'khor bdun nam bcu gnyis kyi don dang /
NK063(gu)001:1786: e ma ho zhes pa gleng gzhi rgyas pa rnams la ngam pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:1787: de yang dang po theg pa dgu dang sbyar na /
NK063(gu)001:1788: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid ces pa chos thams
NK063(gu)001:1789: cad ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings su
NK063(gu)001:1790: ston pa a ti yo ga'o //
NK063(gu)001:1791: dbang bsgyur zhes pa thams cad sku dang ye shes su dbang sgyur ba ma h+aa yo ga'o //
NK063(gu)001:1792: ye shes dkyil 'khor zhes pa chos thams cad dbyings
NK063(gu)001:1793: dang ye shes gnyis su med par ston pa a
NK063(gu)001:1794: nu'o // thugs rje'i ngang zhes pa theg pa dgu'i
NK063(gu)001:1795: nang nas blo chung ba rgyal ba'i thugs rje skye
NK063(gu)001:1797: rang snang ba nyid ces pa don dam mtshan ma
NK063(gu)001:1798: med pa'i byin rlabs kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi
NK063(gu)001:1799: lhar rang snang ba yo ga'o //
NK063(gu)001:1800: ting 'dzin zhes pa de kho na nyid bzhi dang
NK063(gu)001:1801: ldan pa'i lung gis 'bras bu bsgrub pa u pa
NK063(gu)001:1802: ya'o // gzugs brnyan zhes pa don dam dag pa
NK063(gu)001:1803: chos nyid kyi gzugs brnyan kun rdzob rigs gsum du
NK063(gu)001:1805: sgyu ma zhes pa phyi nang gi rten 'brel bcu
NK063(gu)001:1806: gnyis sgyu ma tsam du rtogs pa rang rgyal lo
NK063(gu)001:1807: // rnam dag ces pa spros pa'i mtha' rnam par dag pa dbu ma'o //
NK063(gu)001:1808: gsal ba ni zhes pa sems rang rig tu gsal ba sems tsam mo //
NK063(gu)001:1809: sku gsung thugs zhes pa la sogs pa theg pa de dag gi 'bras bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:1810: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor bsdu ba ni gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:1811: pin tar ltar dkyil 'khor bcu gnyis dang sbyar ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:1812: spar khab ltar dkyil 'khor bdun dang sbyar ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:1813: dang po ni de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid ces pa de bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK063(gu)001:1814: dbang sgyur ye shes dkyil 'khor zhes pa dang dbang sgyur thabs kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:1815: thugs rje zhes pa rang byung thugs rje'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:1816: ngang zhes pa thugs rje'i 'dul ba'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:1817: rang snang ba nyid ting nge 'dzin gyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:1818: gzugs brnyan zhes gzugs brnyan gyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:1819: rnam dag gsal ba zhes lhag pa ting nge'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:1820: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zhes lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:1821: sel med pa'i zhes byang chub sems kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:1822: yon tan yid bzhin rin po che zhes lhag pa byang chub sems kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:1823: rgyan gyi 'khor lo zhes mchog gi dang /
NK063(gu)001:1824: rdo rje mchog gi gnas nyid do zhes lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)001:1825: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor bdun dang sbyar ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:1826: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid ces pa rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)001:1827: dbang sgyur ye shes dkyil 'khor zhes pa rig pa
NK063(gu)001:1828: la rang dbang sgyur cing ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor
NK063(gu)001:1829: gzhan don du ngang ngam shugs kyis 'byung ba rang
NK063(gu)001:1830: bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)001:1831: de gnyis char la rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor zhes gcig tu bgrang ngo //
NK063(gu)001:1832: rang snang ba nyid ting 'dzin zhes pa sems nyid
NK063(gu)001:1833: lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal bar bsgom pa lhag pa
NK063(gu)001:1835: gzugs brnyan zhes pa de'i dkyil 'khor dngos so //
NK063(gu)001:1836: sgyu ma zhes pa snang la yang dag tu ma grub pa lhag pa gzugs brnyan no //
NK063(gu)001:1837: rnam dag gsal ba zhes pa gzugs 'dzin gyi rtog
NK063(gu)001:1838: pa dag nas mi rtog par gsal ba ting nge
NK063(gu)001:1840: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zhes pa rigs
NK063(gu)001:1841: lnga gtso 'khor dang bcas pa tshom bu tshogs kyi
NK063(gu)001:1842: dkyil 'khor ro // sel med pa zhes pa rtsa
NK063(gu)001:1843: dang thig le'i bde ba la rnam rtog gi sel
NK063(gu)001:1844: med pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)001:1845: yang sku gsung thugs yan chad ni dkyil 'khor bdun gyis bsgrubs pa'i yon tan nam 'bras bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:1846: de dag ni snga ma rnams kyis bshad pa'i srol ma dor ba tsam mo //
NK063(gu)001:1847: 'di dag gi dbang du rgyud don mdor bstan du'ang
NK063(gu)001:1848: 'ong bar sems te dkyil 'khor bdun ni rgyud don
NK063(gu)001:1849: dngos yin zhing theg pa yang rgyud don dang ngo
NK063(gu)001:1851: bye brag theg pa 'di dang ngo bo gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:1852: bshad pa'i mthil ni gleng gzhi bsdu ba la bzhed de /
NK063(gu)001:1853: de'i dbang du don gsum yin no //
NK063(gu)001:1855: bsdu rgyu ni sngar bshad pa'i gleng gzhi rgyas pa rnams so //
NK063(gu)001:1856: sdud tshul ni don gsum du bcings te gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1857: rgya dang bral ba gnas kyi don bsdu ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:1858: rgyud kyi byed po ston pa'i don bsdu ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:1859: ye shes rang snang 'khor gyi don bsdu ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:1861: gnas kyi rang bzhin bsdu ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:1862: bye brag gdan gyi don bsdu ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:1865: de gdul bya la gzhal yas su snang tshul dang /
NK063(gu)001:1867: dang po ni bsdus pa de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid ces par /
NK063(gu)001:1868: 'og min gyi gnas zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:1869: gsal ba la zhes pa'i bar rang bzhin dang /
NK063(gu)001:1870: yang rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa zhes rgya khyon dang /
NK063(gu)001:1871: yang phyi dang nang med pa kun tu yang nang
NK063(gu)001:1872: du gyur pa zhes pas mtshan nyid rnams bsdu ba'o
NK063(gu)001:1873: // tshul ni lhun gyis grub pa'i de bzhin nyid
NK063(gu)001:1874: dang mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su chos thams cad
NK063(gu)001:1875: dbyer med du gnas pa rang bzhin yin no zhes
NK063(gu)001:1876: // so // gnyis pa ni tshig bsgyur te 'og
NK063(gu)001:1877: nas rang snang ba nyid ces par ye shes rin
NK063(gu)001:1878: po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang zhes pas rgyu
NK063(gu)001:1879: // so // dang / yon tan dpag tu med
NK063(gu)001:1880: pa rgyas pa'i phyir gru bzhir gyur pa zhes pas
NK063(gu)001:1881: // so // dang / dbyibs dang / lhag pa'i
NK063(gu)001:1882: ye shes glo 'bur gyis mdzes zhes glo 'bur dang
NK063(gu)001:1883: // so // dang / dbyibs dang / / rtse mo zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:1885: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:1886: klubs pa zhes pa'i bar gyis rgyan rnams sdud do //
NK063(gu)001:1887: tshul ni rang snang ba'i ye shes las gdul bya'i
NK063(gu)001:1888: snang ba la dbyibs legs shing kha dog gsal la
NK063(gu)001:1889: rgyan gyis mdzes par rnam par 'phrul pa ste de
NK063(gu)001:1890: nyid 'og gzhi mi 'gyur zhing rtse mo mi nub
NK063(gu)001:1891: par snang ba yin no zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:1893: ting 'dzin zhes pas rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhi
NK063(gu)001:1894: nas 'jug pa'i sgo khyud can zhes pas sgo'i don
NK063(gu)001:1895: sdud do // tshul ni stong ba nyid la sogs
NK063(gu)001:1896: pa ting nge 'dzin bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug par bya
NK063(gu)001:1897: ba ni khyad par yin no zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:1898: gzugs brnyan zhes par rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi
NK063(gu)001:1899: rta babs dang ldan pa zhes rta babs sdud la
NK063(gu)001:1900: / tshul ni thun mong gi lam theg pa brgyad
NK063(gu)001:1901: kyi mtshon byed du rta babs su snang ngo zhes
NK063(gu)001:1902: / so // gnyis pa bye brag tu gdan gyi don ni /
NK063(gu)001:1903: sgyu ma zhes par mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i zhes
NK063(gu)001:1904: pa nas nam mkha' lding gi khri dang zhes pa'i
NK063(gu)001:1905: bar sdud do // tshul ni stobs dang mi 'jigs
NK063(gu)001:1906: pa la sogs pa'i mtshon byed du rig pa'i ye
NK063(gu)001:1907: shes nyid sgyu ma ltar seng ge la sogs par
NK063(gu)001:1908: snang ba yin no zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1909: rnam dag ces pa ra gos pa med pa pad+ma zhes sdud de /
NK063(gu)001:1910: pad+ma ni mtha'i nyes pas ma gos pa mtshon pa yin no zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:1911: gsal ba zhes par rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor zhes pa sdud de /
NK063(gu)001:1912: de ni thabs dang shes rab mtshon pa la nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:1914: don gnyis pa ston pa'i don ni /
NK063(gu)001:1915: gong nas dbang sgyur zhes par /
NK063(gu)001:1916: sku mdun dang zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:1917: dbu gsum dang ldan pa zhes pa'i bar sdud cing /
NK063(gu)001:1918: tshul ni ye shes la mnga' mdzad pas dngos po
NK063(gu)001:1919: gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad la 'dod rgur
NK063(gu)001:1920: dbang sgyur ba ni rgyud kyi byed po ste de
NK063(gu)001:1921: ni ston pa'i bdag nyid do zhes sdud la /
NK063(gu)001:1922: ye shes dkyil 'khor thugs rje'i ngang //
NK063(gu)001:1924: de pa zhes pa nas rang bzhin te zhes pa'i bar sdud do //
NK063(gu)001:1925: tshul ni ston pa de'i mtshan nyid ni de bzhin
NK063(gu)001:1926: nyid mngon du byas pas rang bzhin bdun dang ldan
NK063(gu)001:1927: pa ste sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa yin no
NK063(gu)001:1928: zhes sdud do // don gsum pa 'khor gyi don bsdu ba la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:1930: zhor la de'i tshad kyi don bsdu ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:1932: rang bzhin gnyis med kyi 'khor gyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:1933: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor gyi dang //
NK063(gu)001:1934: de dag gi sku mdog gi don bsdu ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:1935: dang po ni 'og nas sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK063(gu)001:1936: phrin las zhes par bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs
NK063(gu)001:1938: 'du byed kyi rgyal po dang zhes pa'i bar dang /
NK063(gu)001:1939: yang btsun mo dam pa zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:1940: gnyis su med par zhes pa'i bar sdud do //
NK063(gu)001:1941: tshul ni ston pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga las /
NK063(gu)001:1942: rnam shes la sogs phung po lnga dang nam mkha'
NK063(gu)001:1943: la sogs 'byung ba lnga dag pa thugs kyi rigs
NK063(gu)001:1944: mi bskyod pa yab yum la sogs 'chad pa'i skyes
NK063(gu)001:1945: bu rigs lnga yab yum du snang ba yin no
NK063(gu)001:1946: zhes so // gnyis pa ni yang 'og nas mi zad par ldan rgyan gyi 'khor lo zhes par /
NK063(gu)001:1947: de nas byang chub chen po zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:1948: mtshan mar ma yin pa la sogs pa zhes pa'i
NK063(gu)001:1949: bar gyis rgyal sras sems dpa' dang 'jigs byed chen
NK063(gu)001:1951: tshul ni khams dang skye mched la sogs dag pa'i
NK063(gu)001:1952: tshul sems dpa' dang sgo ba yab yum la sogs
NK063(gu)001:1953: par thugs kyi khyad par las snang ba yin no
NK063(gu)001:1954: zhes so // gsum pa ni de'i gong nas yon tan yid bzhin rin po che zhes par /
NK063(gu)001:1955: de dag kun kyang zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:1956: 'tsher ba zhes pa'i bar sdud de /
NK063(gu)001:1957: tshul ni 'khor de dag gi rang bzhin dang rigs
NK063(gu)001:1958: kyi sku mdog tu snang bas gdul bya'i 'dod pa
NK063(gu)001:1959: grub pa ni thabs ma 'dres par gsal ba mtshon
NK063(gu)001:1961: gnyis pa tshad ni de'i gong na sel med pa zhes par /
NK063(gu)001:1962: chos kyi dbyings zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:1963: khyad par bzhugs so zhes pa'i bar khyab pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:1964: de lta bu'i tshogs zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:1965: bzhugs so zhes pa'i bar gyis mang ba'i tshad gnyis sdud do //
NK063(gu)001:1966: tshul ni sna tshogs su snang ba la sku dang
NK063(gu)001:1967: ye shes kyis khyab pas sel med cing de chos
NK063(gu)001:1968: kyi dbyings dang dbyer med pa ni khyab pa'i tshad
NK063(gu)001:1969: yin la / ye shes kyi bye brag brjod kyis
NK063(gu)001:1970: mi lang ba ni mang ba'i tshad yin no zhes
NK063(gu)001:1971: yin la / sdud do // nges tshig ni 'og
NK063(gu)001:1972: nas rdo rje mchog gi gnas nyid do zhes pas
NK063(gu)001:1973: yin la / sdud do // / rdo rje ni
NK063(gu)001:1974: gnyis med de mchog ni rgyud 'byung ba khyad par
NK063(gu)001:1975: yin la / sdud do // / can no //
NK063(gu)001:1976: gnas nyid do zhes pas phun sum tshogs pa lnga
NK063(gu)001:1977: po ni rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu'am gnas yin zhes pa'i
NK063(gu)001:1978: yin la / sdud do // / can no //
NK063(gu)001:1979: tha tshig go // 'o na 'dir yum kun mo
NK063(gu)001:1980: dang thub pa ma tshogs so zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1981: gleng gzhi 'di rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu yin pas yum 'dir mi dgos pa'i phyir ma byung la /
NK063(gu)001:1982: le'u gnyis par rkyen dbang bskur ba'i skabs su yum dgos pas der byung ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:1983: 'khor thub pa yang 'gro ba ma nges pa 'dul
NK063(gu)001:1984: ba'i 'khor yin pas 'dir de med pa'i phyir ma
NK063(gu)001:1985: byung la / le'u gsum par 'khor 'gro ba phal
NK063(gu)001:1986: pa yod pas de 'dul ba'i phyir der byung ba
NK063(gu)001:1987: byung la / yin no // 'o na gleng gzhi
NK063(gu)001:1988: 'di rgyu yin pas 'dir ma byung na 'og tu
NK063(gu)001:1990: rgyu la khegs na 'bras bu la'ang khegs pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:1991: rtags ma grub ste 'dir rgyu sa bon tsam yod pas 'og tu 'byung ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:1993: shes rab kyi zhabs zhes pa yum gyi sa bon la /
NK063(gu)001:1994: sku gsung thugs sna tshogs pa kun tu snang ba zhes pa thub pa'i sa bon yin no //
NK063(gu)001:1995: rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o zhes pa /
NK063(gu)001:1996: gong du bshad pa'i mngon rtogs ltar bsdus pa 'di gsang bdag gis bsdus pa'i don no //
NK063(gu)001:1997: yang 'di bsam par bya ste bsdus pa 'di rgyud don yin nam min /
NK063(gu)001:1998: yin na ston pas gsungs sam ma gsungs /
NK063(gu)001:2001: dang po ltar na gleng ma slang bar gsal la /
NK063(gu)001:2002: gnyis pa ltar na le'u gnyis pa dgos pa med par 'gyur ro //
NK063(gu)001:2003: gal te ston pas ma gsungs na gang gis gsungs /
NK063(gu)001:2005: ston pas gsung pa zhig gam ma gsungs pa zhig gsungs /
NK063(gu)001:2006: dang po ltar na gleng slang ma slang gi brtag pa sngar dang 'dra la /
NK063(gu)001:2007: ston pas ma gsungs pa cig sdud pa pos gsungs na /
NK063(gu)001:2008: ston pa don med du 'gyur te //
NK063(gu)001:2009: rgyud don sdud pa pos gsungs pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2013: de la gzhan gyi rtsod pa spang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:2016: bsdus pa 'di rgyud don min te /
NK063(gu)001:2017: lo rgyus bsdus pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:2018: sdud pa pos gsungs kyang rgyud bshad par mi 'gro
NK063(gu)001:2019: bas gleng slang ba yang mi dgos zer ba ni
NK063(gu)001:2020: / rgyud kyi don la rmongs pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:2021: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rdo rje las phyung ngo zhes pa'i phyir rgyud don yin la /
NK063(gu)001:2022: sus gsungs she na ston pas so //
NK063(gu)001:2023: 'o na gleng ma slang ngo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2024: kha cig na re rtags ma grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:2025: thun mong ma yin pa'i 'khor la gzhan gyi yi
NK063(gu)001:2026: tshod ma yin par gleng slang nas gsungs pa yin
NK063(gu)001:2027: zer ro // 'o na le'u gnyis pa mi dgos par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2028: gleng slang zhing rgyud don yang gsungs pa'i phyir zhes brjod pas /
NK063(gu)001:2030: thun mong gi 'khor lha mi la sogs pa gnyis
NK063(gu)001:2031: par gleng slang nas gsungs pa yin no zer ba
NK063(gu)001:2032: yang shin tu 'khrul pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:2033: lha mi la sogs thun mong gi 'khor de rnams ston pa dngos kyi 'khor ma yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:2034: gnyis pa'i rkyen gsang dbang ni thun min lhan cig pa'i 'khor kho na la bskur ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2035: gnyis pa ni rje thag pa na re /
NK063(gu)001:2036: 'og min du gleng gzhi tshogs shing gleng slang nas
NK063(gu)001:2037: rgyud don rgyas pa de sdud pa pos don 'og
NK063(gu)001:2038: min du ston pa nyid la thos pas ston pa
NK063(gu)001:2039: mi dgos pa'i skyon med la /
NK063(gu)001:2040: thos pa de ma la ya'i rtser lo rgyus kyi
NK063(gu)001:2041: tshul du tshig tu bsdus te dam pa'i rigs can
NK063(gu)001:2042: lnga la sdud pa pos gsungs pa'i phyir gleng slang
NK063(gu)001:2043: ba yang mi dgos pa yin no gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:2045: bsdus pa 'di yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos
NK063(gu)001:2046: po rgyud don yin na ma min na ma yin
NK063(gu)001:2047: / de la rgyu mtshan gnyis yod de /
NK063(gu)001:2048: gleng gzhi bsdus pas rgyud don du mi 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:2049: rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o zhes tshig sdud pa pos gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2050: mtshon byed yi ge rgyud kyi rgyud don yin nam ma yin na yin te /
NK063(gu)001:2051: 'og min du gleng gzhi tshogs gleng slang nas rgyud
NK063(gu)001:2052: don gsungs pa de gsang bdag gis bsdus pa la
NK063(gu)001:2054: gsum pa rtsod pa spang ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:2057: dang po ni de ltar na mtshon byed yi ge'i rgyud dang /
NK063(gu)001:2058: mtshon bya yongs su shes par bya ba gnyis chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2060: rgyud don yin min gnyis po 'gal ba'i chos ldan yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:2063: ci de gnyis 'grel pa dngos po ba med pa'i thal zhes sam /
NK063(gu)001:2065: dang po ltar na 'dod pa yin te tshig dang don la 'grel pa dngos por med do //
NK063(gu)001:2066: gal te yod na ngag tu me zhes brjod pa'i tshe kha 'tshig par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2067: 'brel pa dngos por yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2068: gnyis pa ltar na khyab pa med de /
NK063(gu)001:2069: 'gal ba la 'brel tsam mi khegs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2071: gang 'gal ba yin pa la 'brel ba med pas khyab mun snang bzhin no zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2072: rgyu mtshan mtshungs pa'i 'go snyoms shig bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:2073: tsha reg grang reg gi me chu gnyis chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2074: rgyu 'bras kyi 'brel tsam med par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2075: lhan cig mi gnas pa'i 'gal ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:2076: rtags tshad mas grub cing khyab pa med na /
NK063(gu)001:2077: 'gal ba la 'brel med kyis khyab pa nyams la /
NK063(gu)001:2078: thal 'gyur 'dod na de gnyis rgyu 'bras su 'grel par bsal te /
NK063(gu)001:2079: me bud shing las byung zhing de chu las skyes pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2080: des na le'u bsdus pa 'di gong ltar rgya mdud
NK063(gu)001:2081: 'grel la sogs kyi rtsa bar bzhed pa ltar na
NK063(gu)001:2082: rang bzhin gyi rgyud don yang yin la /
NK063(gu)001:2083: spar khab ltar gleng gzhi bsdus par bzhed pa ltar
NK063(gu)001:2084: na mtshon byed kyi rgyud don du 'gyur bas rgyud
NK063(gu)001:2085: don yin min 'gal bar ma grub cing 'brel ba
NK063(gu)001:2087: de byung shes bya shes byed kyi 'brel ba yod pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:2088: rgyud don rnam par nges pa las le'u dang po'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2090: // le'u gnyis pa ni don gnyis pa rgyud kyi gleng slang ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:2092: thun min gyi gleng slang ni sngon byung gi zab mo'i dbang yin la /
NK063(gu)001:2096: shin tu bstan pa'i dbang ngo //
NK063(gu)001:2098: 'jug par gyur to zhes yab yum snyoms 'jug las byung ba'i nyi zlas rgyu byas shing /
NK063(gu)001:2099: e ma ho zhes pa la sogs gzhung brtags te
NK063(gu)001:2100: yab kyi nyams su bstar ba'i don brjod pas rkyen
NK063(gu)001:2101: byas nas / rgyu rkyen de'i 'bras bu 'khor gyis
NK063(gu)001:2102: kun rdzob kyi bden pa rtog tshogs su btags pa
NK063(gu)001:2103: thams cad sku dang ye shes su sangs rgyas par
NK063(gu)001:2104: byas nas / rtogs pa dang / yang rgyu gong
NK063(gu)001:2105: ma dang rkyen kye ma zhes pa la sogs gzhung
NK063(gu)001:2106: byas nas / rtogs pa dang / brtag ste /
NK063(gu)001:2107: 'bras bu rtog pa sku dang ye shes su gsang
NK063(gu)001:2108: ba nyid don dam pa'i bden pa rang bzhin chos
NK063(gu)001:2110: de'i phyir yab yum gnyis nyams su bstar ba dus gcig pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:2111: ji skad du spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:2112: thig le gnyis su med pa ste dgongs pa yang bsdu'o //
NK063(gu)001:2113: yab yum gyi las dang nyams su myong ba dang
NK063(gu)001:2114: tshig 'di dag yi ge snga phyi yin gyi dus
NK063(gu)001:2117: des na sngon du zhugs pa gnyis bshad cing bstar
NK063(gu)001:2118: ba gnyis phyi la bshad na bde bar sems so
NK063(gu)001:2119: // 'dir kha cig lhan cig pa la dbang mi
NK063(gu)001:2120: dgos kyang go phye ba'i ched du bskur ba yin
NK063(gu)001:2121: // zhes zer ro // de ltar ma yiin par gsang dbang gi nges tshig gis shes te /
NK063(gu)001:2122: de ni zhes brjod pas thams cad ye nas sangs
NK063(gu)001:2123: rgyas par de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis mkhyen to
NK063(gu)001:2125: des na gsang dbang ni nyi zla'i rdzas kyi khyad
NK063(gu)001:2126: par du byas te rtog med kyi ye shes shar
NK063(gu)001:2127: kyang ston pa'i dgongs pa dbyer med kyi ye shes
NK063(gu)001:2128: da dung ma myong ba'i phyir gsang dbang zhes bya'o
NK063(gu)001:2129: // de la kha cig shes rab ye shes kyi dbang yang der thal /
NK063(gu)001:2130: gnyis med kyi ye shes 'dir yang gsang ba'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2131: spyir mtshan nyid du gzhag pa la khyab ches pa
NK063(gu)001:2132: chung ba mtshan gzhi la mi srid pa rnams skyon
NK063(gu)001:2133: yin gyi / 'dir nges tshig la de dag skyon ma yin no //
NK063(gu)001:2134: gal te mi shes pa'i dam tshig gis skyon du brjod na khyab pa med de /
NK063(gu)001:2135: shes rab ye shes ni nyi zla'i rdzas kyis khyad
NK063(gu)001:2136: par du byas pa ma yin pa'i phyir tshogs pa
NK063(gu)001:2137: rgyu mtshan la ya gyal ba'i skyon gyis mi gnod
NK063(gu)001:2138: pa yin no // yang 'dir kha cig ston pa
NK063(gu)001:2139: yab yum gyis gsang dbang bskur ba 'di mi 'thad
NK063(gu)001:2140: pa yin no // de / khyad par gyi byed chos dbang rdzas med pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2141: de med par ma grub ces smras pas /
NK063(gu)001:2142: kho na re dbang rdzas med de /
NK063(gu)001:2143: ston pa yab yum rdos pa'i lus su med pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:2144: de la brten pa'i nyi zla yang med de /
NK063(gu)001:2145: gyang med na de la brten pa'i ri mo med pa bzhin no zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2147: rdos pa'i de dang de med kyang ston pa yab
NK063(gu)001:2148: yum ye shes sgyu ma'i skur bzhugs pas de la
NK063(gu)001:2149: brten pa'i nyi zlas dbang bskur ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:2150: ji skad du dbang nges 'byed las /
NK063(gu)001:2151: gnas brten rtsa dang thig le las //
NK063(gu)001:2152: ye shes sgyu ma'i gzugs su 'char //
NK063(gu)001:2154: gnyis pa shes rab ye shes dang gsum pa bde ba chen po gnyis thun mong du bstan pa'am /
NK063(gu)001:2155: yang na sems bskyed pa'i rgyu gsang dbang bstan nas /
NK063(gu)001:2156: dbang gnyis kyi las sems bskyed pa dngos ston te /
NK063(gu)001:2157: ji skad du spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:2158: sems lnga'i gleng slang ba'i las kyis zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2159: de la gsum las lo rgyus su brjod pa ni sdud pa po'i mtshams sbyar ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:2160: sems bskyed pa'am dbang bskur ba dngos la 'grel pa mkhan po tha dad pas dgongs pa gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:2161: spyan 'grel ltar rang bzhin gzhi'i sems bskyed dang /
NK063(gu)001:2162: spar khab ltar bgrod pa lam gyi sems bskyed dang /
NK063(gu)001:2163: rgya che 'grel ltar mthar phyin 'bras bu'i sems bskyed do //
NK063(gu)001:2165: gzhi don gyi kun gzhi stong pa nyid kyi ye shes su dang /
NK063(gu)001:2166: kun gzhi me long lta bu'i ye shes su dang /
NK063(gu)001:2167: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes su dang /
NK063(gu)001:2168: yid kyi rnam shes so sor rtog pa'i ye shes su dang /
NK063(gu)001:2169: sgo lnga bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su sems bskyed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2171: e ma ho zhes gzhi don gyi kun gzhi stong
NK063(gu)001:2172: pa nyid kyi ye shes yin pa'i don gzhi la
NK063(gu)001:2173: ngam / ngo mtshar zhes pa de ltar rtogs nas de'i don nyams su len pa'i lam la ngam /
NK063(gu)001:2174: rmad kyi chos zhes pa de mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu la ngam pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2175: de ltar gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du sbyar ba 'di 'og ma bzhi la'ang shes par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:2176: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK063(gu)001:2177: zhes pa ni ye shes kun tu brdal bas 'ching
NK063(gu)001:2178: ba dang bral zhing 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan
NK063(gu)001:2179: lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyal ba rnams kyi dgongs pa
NK063(gu)001:2180: 'di phal gyi yul ma yin pas te 'og ma
NK063(gu)001:2181: bzhi yang 'adi'o // skye ba med las zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:2182: gzhi sems nyid gnyis med du gtan la 'bebs pa
NK063(gu)001:2183: la rim gyis pa'i blo la ltos te dang po
NK063(gu)001:2184: chos thams cad rang bzhin skye med du gtan la
NK063(gu)001:2186: sgrub byed rtags kyi mtshan gzhi'i ngo bo dang /
NK063(gu)001:2187: rtags de'i mtshan nyid phyogs chos khyab pa bsgrub pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:2188: mtshon bya rtags kyi rigs gang yin nges par bya ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:2189: dang po ni sems nyid chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2190: skye ba med pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:2193: rgyu rkyen gzhan las mi skyes pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:2194: byed pa po gzhan gyis ma byas pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:2195: rgyu rkyen med par dus glo bur du 'byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:2196: skyes pa'i dngos po 'di 'dra btsal na mi rnyed pa'i phyir dper na nam mkha' bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:2197: gnyis pa ni rang bzhin gyi sde pa dag rtags de dag ma grub bo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2198: de dag gi tshul bsgrub pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:2199: de yang phyi rol grangs can pa na re /
NK063(gu)001:2200: dngos po thams cad rgyu rkyen las skyes pa'i phyir tshul dang po ma grub bo zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:2201: 'o na dngos po de rang las skyes sam /
NK063(gu)001:2205: dang po ltar na skyes byed rgyu grub dus su
NK063(gu)001:2206: bskyed bya 'bras bu grub pa cig skye'am ma grub
NK063(gu)001:2207: pa cig skye / dang po ltar na myu gu lta bu'i dngos po chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2209: sa bon la grub zin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2210: rtags de ma grub na rgyu grub dus su 'bras bu grub pa nyams la /
NK063(gu)001:2211: gal te grub zin yang skye ba ci 'gal zhe
NK063(gu)001:2212: na ha cang thal te rgyu nyid rgyu nyid du
NK063(gu)001:2214: dang po'i thal ba 'dod na rang las rang skye ba nyams so //
NK063(gu)001:2215: gnyis pa ma grub pa cig skye na /
NK063(gu)001:2217: sa bon gyi bdag nyid ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2218: ma grub pa dang skye ba 'gal ba'i chos ldan yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:2219: de tshad mas grub cing ma grub pa la sa bon min pas khyab la /
NK063(gu)001:2220: 'dod na rang las skye zhes rgyu 'bras bdag gcig tu 'dod pa nyams so //
NK063(gu)001:2221: gzhan yang myu gu chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2222: blo rdzas gcig la snang mi snang cha gnyis med par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2223: rgyu 'bras rdzas gcig yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2224: gnyis pa gzhan las skye'o zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2226: me dang sol ba las skye bar 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2227: myu gu de me sol la ltos nas gzhan yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2228: kho na re khyab pa med de /
NK063(gu)001:2229: rgyu 'bras su 'gyur ba'i gzhan las gzhan skye ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:2230: sa bon las myu gu skye bar snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:2231: de de las skye ba'i nus pa yod pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:2232: de las de skye ba chos nyid yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2233: rgyu 'bras su mi 'gyur ba'i gzhan las gzhan mi skye ste /
NK063(gu)001:2234: me sol las myu gu skye bar sus kyang ma mthong zhing /
NK063(gu)001:2235: de la de skyed pa'i nus pa med la /
NK063(gu)001:2236: rgyu 'bras 'chol bar mi 'gyur ba chos nyid yin pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2237: 'o na me sol las myu gu skye ba lta
NK063(gu)001:2238: bu ma mthong bas 'bras bu skye ba khegs na
NK063(gu)001:2240: phyi ma'i bde sdug tu smin pa med par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2241: de ma mthong ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2242: de la khyab pa med na 'dir me dang myu gu la yang mtshungs so //
NK063(gu)001:2243: yang sa myug lta bu de las de skye bar snang bas 'bras bu skye bar grub na /
NK063(gu)001:2244: rmi lam gyi sa myug chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2245: de las de skye bar grub par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2246: rmi lam du de las de skyes par snang ba'i phyir zhes brjod pas /
NK063(gu)001:2247: kho na re khyab pa med de rmi lam du
NK063(gu)001:2248: de las de skye bar snang yang 'khrul pa yin
NK063(gu)001:2250: sad pa'i shes yul na de las de skye bar
NK063(gu)001:2251: snang ba ni ma 'khrul bas bden pa yin no
NK063(gu)001:2252: zhe na / blo 'khrul ma 'khrul dang yul bden
NK063(gu)001:2253: rdzun gyi khyad par de lta bu chos thams cad
NK063(gu)001:2254: kyi rang bzhin skye med du rtogs pa la ltos
NK063(gu)001:2256: rgyu 'bras su snang tsam rmi lam na yang yod
NK063(gu)001:2257: cing de bden par gnyid sad pa'i shes yul na
NK063(gu)001:2259: yang rtags rmi lam du sa bon las myu gu skye bar snang ba de ma grub ce na /
NK063(gu)001:2260: sad shes kyi sa myug la yang mtshungs so //
NK063(gu)001:2261: gal te rmi lam gyi shes yul chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2263: sad pa'i shes yul na med pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2265: da ltar gyi rgyu 'bras chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2267: brtags na mi rnyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2268: gsum pa gnyis ka las skye ba ni rgyu 'bras
NK063(gu)001:2269: rdzas gcig pa dang de rdzas gzhan gnyis ka las
NK063(gu)001:2270: skye ba ste / de ni bye brag tu rang gzhan gnyis las skye ba khegs pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:2271: spyir gnyis ka las skye ba khegs pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:2272: dper na bye ma re re la mar 'byin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:2273: nus pa med na bye ma tshogs pa'i phung po
NK063(gu)001:2274: la yang nus pa de med pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:2275: bzhi pa rgyu med pas skye bo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2277: yul dus rang bzhin gyi rgyu gsum la ltos mi dgos par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2278: rgyu med yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2279: rtags de khas blangs la khyab pa med na rgyu med las skye ba nyams shing /
NK063(gu)001:2281: rgyu de gsum la ltos par bsal te /
NK063(gu)001:2282: yul gangs rtse na med cing zhing steng na yod la /
NK063(gu)001:2283: rang bzhin me sol las mi skye ste /
NK063(gu)001:2284: nas lta bu la skye zhing /
NK063(gu)001:2285: dus dgun med cing dbyar gyi dus su yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2286: des na rang gzhan dang gnyis ka dang rgyu med
NK063(gu)001:2287: las skye ba bzhi khegs pa na phyogs chos dang
NK063(gu)001:2288: po rgyu rkyen gzhan las ma skyes par grub pa
NK063(gu)001:2289: yin no // rtags gnyis pa ni dbang phyug pa
NK063(gu)001:2290: kha cig chos thams cad dbang phyug la sogs byed
NK063(gu)001:2291: pa po zhig gis byas pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:2292: tshul gnyis pa byed pa po gzhan gyis ma byas par ma grub ce na /
NK063(gu)001:2293: 'o na gzhan byed pa po de rtag pa zhig gam mi rtag pa zhig gis byas /
NK063(gu)001:2294: dang po ltar na dbang phyug chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2295: don byed mi nus par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2296: rtag pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2298: khyab pa med na rtag pa nyams so //
NK063(gu)001:2300: byed pa po ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2301: don byed mi nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2303: don byed mi nus kyang byed pa po yin par ci 'gal zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2304: gang don byed mi nus pa la byed po min pas khyab /
NK063(gu)001:2305: dper na ri bong gi rwa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:2306: gal te mi rtag pa zhig gis byas so zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2307: de ni dus gsum gyis bsdus pa yin pas 'das
NK063(gu)001:2308: pa dang ma 'ongs pa dngos med yin pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:2310: ji srid de byed pa por 'gyur na ri bong
NK063(gu)001:2311: gi rwa las kyang 'bras bu skye ba cis 'gog
NK063(gu)001:2313: da ltar ba yang snga phyir dpyad na rnyed pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:2314: ji skad du gzhung gzhan las /
NK063(gu)001:2315: ji ltar skad cig mtha' yas ltar //
NK063(gu)001:2316: thog ma dbus kyang brtag par gyis //
NK063(gu)001:2317: skad cig gsum gyi bdag nyid phyir //
NK063(gu)001:2318: 'jig rten skad cig la mi gnas //
NK063(gu)001:2320: de ltar byed pa po khegs pa'i phyir phyogs chos gnyis pa grub pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:2321: gtan tshigs gsum pa ni rang sde sems tsam pa
NK063(gu)001:2322: dag 'di ltar dngos po thams cad sngar med gsar
NK063(gu)001:2323: du skyes pa'i phyir tshul gsum pa ma grub bo
NK063(gu)001:2324: zhe na / sa bon chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2326: rgyu sa bon gyi dus na 'bras bu med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2327: de med par ma grub na 'bras bu thams cad sngar med gsar du skyed pa nyams la /
NK063(gu)001:2328: gal te sa bon kyi dus na med kyang gsar du skye ba ci 'gal zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2329: mo gsham la bu skye ba cis 'gog /
NK063(gu)001:2330: kho na re mo gsham dang bu skye ba 'gal lo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2332: sa bon la myu gu med par de skye bar 'gal ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:2333: gzhan yang sa bon chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2334: da las ri bong rwa yang skye bar 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2335: rgyu sa bon gyi dus na myu gu dang ri
NK063(gu)001:2336: bong gi rwa gnyis char med mnyam yin pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:2337: ro // gal te khyab pa med de sa bon
NK063(gu)001:2338: las ri bong gi rwa skyes par ma mthong bas
NK063(gu)001:2340: myu gu skye bar dmigs pa'i phyir de gnyis rgyu 'bras yin no zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2341: gong ltar tshe 'di'i dge sdig phyi ma'i rgyu 'bras su mi 'gyur zhing /
NK063(gu)001:2342: rmi lam gyi sa myug kyang rgyu 'bras dngos por 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2343: ma mthong ba dang mthong ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2344: des na 'bras bu dmigs pa la rgyu sngon song
NK063(gu)001:2345: gi khyab pa'i phyir phyogs chos gsum pa grub pa
NK063(gu)001:2346: yin no // rtags bzhi pa ni gzhan sde rtag
NK063(gu)001:2347: pa ba na re dngos po rdzas su grub cing
NK063(gu)001:2348: de skad cig gnyis pa phan chad du mi 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:2349: zhing rtag pa gcig pu yin pa'i phyir tshul tha
NK063(gu)001:2350: ma'ang ma grub bo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2352: don byed mi nus par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2353: rtag pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2355: rtag kyang don byed nus par ci 'gal zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2356: gang rtag pa la don byed mi nus pas khyab ste /
NK063(gu)001:2358: des na don ni 'bras bu yin la byed pa
NK063(gu)001:2359: ni de rim par bskyed pa ste dus snga phyi
NK063(gu)001:2360: bzhin no // de rtag pa la khegs pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:2361: rtag pa dang don byed nus pa 'gal ba yin
NK063(gu)001:2362: bzhin no // te / ji skad du gzhung gzhan las /
NK063(gu)001:2363: rim dang rim med 'gal ba'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:2364: rtag pas don byed nus ma yin //
NK063(gu)001:2366: de las ldog ste don byed pa la mi rtag pas khyab par yang de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:2367: dngos rnams gzhan du 'gyur ba la //
NK063(gu)001:2368: mkhas pa rnams ni mi rtag brjod //
NK063(gu)001:2369: ces ldog khyab kyang grub par bshad pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:2370: gzhan yang rtag pa chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2372: bden pa'i gcig dang du ma dang bral ba'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:2373: zhes pa'i rtags kyis dpyad na rtag dngos shes bya
NK063(gu)001:2374: na btsal yang mi rnyed pas phyogs chos tha ma'ang
NK063(gu)001:2376: de ltar phyogs chos bzhi grub pa na de la skye ba med pas khyab bo //
NK063(gu)001:2377: don gsum pa gtan tshigs kyis rig pa nges pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:2378: bsgrub bya skye ba med pa ni don yin la
NK063(gu)001:2379: de gtan tshigs bzhis grub pa'i phyir don grub rang
NK063(gu)001:2380: bzhin gyi gtan tshigs yin no //
NK063(gu)001:2381: thams cad skyes zhes pa de ltar ma rtogs te
NK063(gu)001:2382: 'khrul ngo na sngo 'dzin sngon po las skyes pa
NK063(gu)001:2383: ltar rtog bcas kyi sems rgyu rkyen las skyes pa
NK063(gu)001:2384: ste / des med pa phyogs gcig gi mtha' sel ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:2385: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med ces pas sna
NK063(gu)001:2386: tshogs rgyu rkyen las skyes pa nyid kyi phyir chos
NK063(gu)001:2387: thams cad rang gi ngo bos stongs ni stong pa
NK063(gu)001:2390: e ma ho zhes pa kun gzhi me long lta
NK063(gu)001:2391: bu'i ye shes yin pa la sogs gong ltar ro
NK063(gu)001:2392: // 'gag pa med ces pa sems kyi snang ba mi 'gag par bsgrub pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:2393: de'i sgrub byed kyang rje thag pa ni sngar gyi
NK063(gu)001:2394: skye med sgrub byed kyi rig pa de nyid 'gag
NK063(gu)001:2395: med kyi sgrub byed du rung ste /
NK063(gu)001:2396: dgag pa bkag pa bsgrub pa yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:2397: don la snang stong dbyer med yin pa'i phyir ro zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:2398: de la kha cig de ltar mi rung ste //
NK063(gu)001:2399: rim gyis pa la ltos te bden pa gsum rim
NK063(gu)001:2400: par rgyud la skye ba'i phyir ro zhes gsung ba
NK063(gu)001:2402: de tshod du shes bya la bden dngos grub par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2403: cis na phyi rol pa'am nyan rang gis de 'dod pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2404: rtags de dag gi gzhung nas de 'dod pas grub bo //
NK063(gu)001:2405: de dag gis bden dngos 'dod kyang shes bya la de ma grub na ci 'gal zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2406: 'dir yang de dang mtshungs te rim gyis pa la bden pa gsum rim par skye dgos kyang /
NK063(gu)001:2407: yin lugs la snang stong dbyer med yin na ci 'gal te khyab pa med do //
NK063(gu)001:2408: yang 'ga' zhig 'gag med du sgrub byed gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:2409: 'khrul pa'i snang tsam gcig dmigs pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:2410: snang ba mi khegs pa' phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:2411: snang ba med na skyon du 'gyur ba'i phyir snang ba yod pa yin no zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:2413: sems nyid 'gag med du sgrub byed kyi rtags dgod pa /
NK063(gu)001:2415: de'i rigs nges par bya ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:2416: dang po ni sems nyid chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2417: snang ba 'gag pa med pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:2418: snang ba med na stong pa rang du shes byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:2419: gshis la snang ba ma grub na da ltar gyi 'khrul snang 'di rang mi 'byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:2420: snang ba med na snang stong dbyer med mi 'grub pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:2421: bden pas stong pa'i snang tsam gang gis kyang dgag
NK063(gu)001:2422: par mi nus pa'i phyir zhes 'di yang rgyu mtshan
NK063(gu)001:2423: bzhis bsgrub bo // gnyis pa ni gzhan sde chad
NK063(gu)001:2424: par smra ba'am rang sde dbu ma rgyun chad pa
NK063(gu)001:2425: kha cig rtags de dag ma grub ste snang ba
NK063(gu)001:2426: bden pa lta zhog snang tsam du yang grub pa
NK063(gu)001:2428: dang po'i tshul bsgrub pa ni 'o na shes bya
NK063(gu)001:2429: snang tsam du yang med de stong par gang gis
NK063(gu)001:2430: shes / snang ba ma yin pa zhig gis shes so zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2432: dang po ltar na shes bya stong par mi bden par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2433: shes byed 'khrul pas shes pa'i yul yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:2434: rtags de khas blangs shing khyab pa med na /
NK063(gu)001:2435: gang shes byed 'khrul pas shes pa'i shes bya de ltar min pas khyab ste /
NK063(gu)001:2436: mig shes 'khrul pas shes pa'i dung gi rang bzhin ser po min pa bzhin /
NK063(gu)001:2437: 'dod na stong pa phyogs gcig tu bden par 'dod pa nyams so //
NK063(gu)001:2438: yang phyogs gnyis pa ltar na shes bya stong pa
NK063(gu)001:2439: shes pa'i shes byed ma 'khrul pa de kho na
NK063(gu)001:2440: la kho bo cag snang ba zer ba yin te
NK063(gu)001:2441: ba glang zhes pa nog po shal can la zer
NK063(gu)001:2442: ba bzhin no // tshul gnyis pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:2443: da ltar gyi 'khrul pa 'di chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2445: de'i gzhi snang ba med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2446: de ma grub na snang ba yod par 'gyur ro //
NK063(gu)001:2447: khyab pa med na snang ba khegs pa la 'khrul pa khegs pas khyab ste /
NK063(gu)001:2448: dung khegs na de ser po 'dzin pa khegs pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:2449: thal 'gyur 'dod na 'khrul pa dmigs pas bsal lo //
NK063(gu)001:2452: dbyer med ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2453: ya gyal snang ba med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2454: rtags khas blangs la khyab pa ni ya gyal khegs
NK063(gu)001:2455: pa la tshogs pa khegs pas khyab ste thal mo
NK063(gu)001:2456: ya gyal med na thal mo'i sgra med pa bzhin
NK063(gu)001:2458: gang gis stong dang rten 'byung dag dbu ma'i don du don gcig pa //
NK063(gu)001:2461: snang dang mi snang gnyis ka med //
NK063(gu)001:2462: yod dang med pa'ang dbyer med do //
NK063(gu)001:2463: zhes pa la sogs dbyer med kyi lung zab cing rgya che bar bshad pas bsal lo //
NK063(gu)001:2464: des na sems nyid chos can /
NK063(gu)001:2465: snang stong dbyer med yin te /
NK063(gu)001:2466: stong pa la snang ba ngo bo nyid du grub
NK063(gu)001:2467: pa'i phyir dper na rin po che la dgos 'dod
NK063(gu)001:2468: grub pa bzhin zhes pa'i rtags kyis dbyer med du
NK063(gu)001:2469: bsgrub par nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2470: tshul tha ma ni dbu ma pa kha cig snang ba dgag par nus te /
NK063(gu)001:2471: gcig dang du bral la sogs pa'i rtags kyis khegs pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2472: de ni bden pa'i 'gog byed yin gyi snang ba tsam gyi 'gog byed ma yin no //
NK063(gu)001:2473: gal te snang tsam gyi 'gog byed yin na rtags de chos ca na /
NK063(gu)001:2474: yang dag ma yin par thal /
NK063(gu)001:2475: ldog pa'i tshul med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2476: rtags ma grub na gcig dang du ma'i dngos por bden pa srid par 'gyur la /
NK063(gu)001:2477: ldog khyab med pa la yang dag ma yin pas khyab ste ma nges pa'i ltar snang bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:2479: rtags de snang ba 'gog byed du mi rung ste /
NK063(gu)001:2480: yang dag ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2481: gzhan yang 'khrul ngo na snang ba grub pas rang
NK063(gu)001:2482: bzhin shes pa'i ngo na yang de grub pa yin
NK063(gu)001:2483: te / de gnyis kyi khyad par snang ba chos nyid du rtogs ma rtogs las med pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:2484: gzhi snang ba med na de chos nyid du rtogs bya med de /
NK063(gu)001:2485: dper na sbrul shes bya la med na thag pa
NK063(gu)001:2486: la der 'dzin shes bya la med pa bzhin no
NK063(gu)001:2487: // des na grub mtha' 'di 'dzin pas stong nyid
NK063(gu)001:2488: rig pas grub tshod du snang ba yang rig pas
NK063(gu)001:2490: don la snang stong dbyer med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2491: gsum pa ni 'khrul pa dmigs shing de stong par
NK063(gu)001:2492: shes pa la sogs snang tsam las byung bas 'bras
NK063(gu)001:2494: yang na dbyer med kyi rang bzhin yin pa ni rang bzhin gyi'o //
NK063(gu)001:2495: yang 'di bsam par bya ste sems nyid gcig gi
NK063(gu)001:2496: steng du sngar skye med du bsgrubs pa dang 'dir
NK063(gu)001:2497: 'gag med du bsgrub pa gnyis 'gal lo zhe na
NK063(gu)001:2498: / de ni de gnyis ngo bo tha dad du bsgrub pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:2499: rgyu shes pa'i skabs su rim gyis pas dbyer med
NK063(gu)001:2500: du ma rtogs pa'i phyir ldog pa tha dad du
NK063(gu)001:2501: bsgrubs shing gtan la phab pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:2502: thams cad 'gag ces pa 'khrul ngo na rtog bcas
NK063(gu)001:2503: kyi sems skyes pa'i dus las skad cig gnyis par
NK063(gu)001:2505: rig ngo na de nyid la bden par 'dzin pa
NK063(gu)001:2506: gong gi skye med sgrub byed kyi rtags kyi khegs
NK063(gu)001:2509: ces pa shes bya la grub tshul nas 'gag med
NK063(gu)001:2510: gsal ba nyid 'gag pa stong nyid dang dbyer med
NK063(gu)001:2511: pas rtog pa med pa ste de ni me long
NK063(gu)001:2513: don gsum pa ni e ma ho zhes pa nyon yid mnyam pa nyid do //
NK063(gu)001:2514: gnas pa med las zhes pa gong gi skye med
NK063(gu)001:2515: sgrub byed dang 'gag med sgrub byed kyi rtags de
NK063(gu)001:2516: dag chos can / gcig gi steng na tha dad
NK063(gu)001:2517: med pa'i phyir phyogs gcig tu gnas pa med pa'o
NK063(gu)001:2518: dag chos can / // thams cad gnas zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:2519: de nyid ma rtogs te 'khrul pa'i gzhan sde stong
NK063(gu)001:2521: rang sde nyan rang gis chos bdag dang /
NK063(gu)001:2522: sems tsam pa'i rang rig la sogs dngos por smra ba rnams dang /
NK063(gu)001:2523: yang gzhan sde chad pa bas med pa phyogs gcig dang /
NK063(gu)001:2524: rang sde dbu ma pas stong nyid du smra ba
NK063(gu)001:2525: rnams rtog bcas kyi sems de dag la tha dad
NK063(gu)001:2526: du gnas pa'o // gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK063(gu)001:2527: ces pa de dag dngos po'i gnas lugs la tha
NK063(gu)001:2528: dad dang phyogs ris med pa mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK063(gu)001:2529: ye shes so // don bzhi pa ni e ma ho zhes pa yid shes so sor rtog pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2530: dmigs pa med las zhes pa dbyer med dam mtha'
NK063(gu)001:2531: bral gyi chos nyid de yul gud du dmigs su
NK063(gu)001:2532: med pa'o // thams cad dmigs zhes pas 'khrul pa'i
NK063(gu)001:2533: ngo na 'dzin pa'i sems kyis gzung bya'i yul la
NK063(gu)001:2535: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK063(gu)001:2536: ces pa yang dag par na yul dang yul can
NK063(gu)001:2537: dbyer du rtogs pa na gzugs nas rnam pa thams
NK063(gu)001:2538: cad mkhyen pa'i bar chos thams cad rang rang gi
NK063(gu)001:2539: mtshan nyid phyin ci ma log par rtogs pa so
NK063(gu)001:2540: sor rtog pa'i ye shes so //
NK063(gu)001:2541: don lnga pa ni e ma ho zhes pa sgo lnga bya ba grub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2542: 'gro 'ong med las zhes pa sems kyi rang bzhin mtha' gang du'ang g.yo ba med pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2543: 'gro dang 'ong zhes pa de nyid rtogs pa dang
NK063(gu)001:2544: ma rtogs pas 'khor 'das kyi rang bzhin cir yang
NK063(gu)001:2546: ces pa de dag sems nyid la rtsol ba med
NK063(gu)001:2547: par lhun gyis grub pa ni bya ba grub pa'i
NK063(gu)001:2548: ye shes so // gnyis pa bgrod pa lam gyi sems bskyed la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:2549: grol lam cig car ba'i dbang du dang /
NK063(gu)001:2557: dang po ni e ma ho zhes pa 'og gi gzhung don skye ba med pa la ngam zhing /
NK063(gu)001:2558: ngo mtshar zhes pa thams cad skyes pa la ngam la /
NK063(gu)001:2559: rmad kyi chos zhes pa skyes pa nyid na skye
NK063(gu)001:2560: ba med pa la ngam pa ste 'og ma bzhi
NK063(gu)001:2562: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK063(gu)001:2563: zhes pa lnga car bden pa dbyer med kyi don
NK063(gu)001:2564: 'di yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK063(gu)001:2565: thugs kyi dgongs pa yin la de rtogs par dka'
NK063(gu)001:2567: skye ba med las zhes pa sems nyid stong par
NK063(gu)001:2568: skye ba med pa las dkor bdun gyi snang ba
NK063(gu)001:2569: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2570: thams cad skyes zhes pa kun rdzob rig pa sgyu
NK063(gu)001:2571: ma tsam du skye ba'i cho 'phrul du ma 'gags
NK063(gu)001:2572: pa'o // skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK063(gu)001:2573: ces pa bden pa gnyis ldog pa dang mtshon tshul tha dad kyang ngo bo dbyer med pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:2574: lam pa'i blo la dang por dbyer med 'go g.yo ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:2575: de bzhin du 'gag pa med ces don dam pa
NK063(gu)001:2576: thams cad 'gag ces pa kun rdzob tu skye 'gag
NK063(gu)001:2577: ltar snang ba'o // 'gag pa nyid na 'gag pa med //
NK063(gu)001:2578: ces pa dbyer med kyi don la 'jug pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2579: gnas pa med las zhes pa don dam la /
NK063(gu)001:2580: thams cad gnas zhes pa kun rdzob bo //
NK063(gu)001:2581: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK063(gu)001:2582: ces pa dbyer med kyi don la gnas pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2583: dmigs pa med las zhes pa don dam la /
NK063(gu)001:2584: thams cad dmigs zhes pa kun rdzob bo //
NK063(gu)001:2585: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK063(gu)001:2586: ces pa dbyer med la smon pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:2587: de ni dkyus kyi go rim yin la rgyud la
NK063(gu)001:2588: skye rim gyi dbang du g.yo ba'i rjes su 'ong
NK063(gu)001:2589: ngo // 'gro 'ong med las zhes pa don dam la /
NK063(gu)001:2590: 'gro dang 'ong zhes pa kun rdzob bo //
NK063(gu)001:2592: ces pa dbyer med kyi don mthar phyin pa ste mthar phyin pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK063(gu)001:2593: don gnyis pa 'og sgo'i dbang du bshad pa la
NK063(gu)001:2594: yang thabs lam gyi sems lnga ste dbang phyi ma
NK063(gu)001:2595: gnyis 'dir bskur bar shes par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:2597: e ma ho zhes pa 'dod chags chen po'i spyod pas 'khor bar mi 'ching ba la ngam pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2598: ngo mtshar des slar 'bras bu myur ba la /
NK063(gu)001:2599: rmad kyi chos zhes pa thabs de ka gzhan las
NK063(gu)001:2600: khyad par 'phags pa 'di'i dgongs pa yin pas ngam
NK063(gu)001:2601: pa ste 'og ma rnams kyang de ltar ro //
NK063(gu)001:2602: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK063(gu)001:2603: zhes pa lnga char yang dag par rdzogs pa'i rgyal
NK063(gu)001:2604: ba kun gyi dgongs pa nyon mongs pa la spyad
NK063(gu)001:2605: par 'bras bu grub pa 'di khe nyen dang bcas
NK063(gu)001:2606: pas gsang ba'o // skye ba med las zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:2607: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa rten med kyi ye
NK063(gu)001:2608: shes rgyu rkyen las skye ba med pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2609: thams cad skyes zhes pa de lam pa'i thabs kyis
NK063(gu)001:2610: nyams su blangs tshe rten can gyi dga' ba bcu
NK063(gu)001:2612: skye ba nyid na skye ba med //
NK063(gu)001:2613: ces pa thig le'i bde ba rim par skyes pa'i
NK063(gu)001:2614: dus nyid na rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye
NK063(gu)001:2615: shes la skye ba med pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:2616: de ni lam pa'i ngo na thig le 'go ldang
NK063(gu)001:2617: tsa na bde ba dus mnyam du 'go g.yo bas
NK063(gu)001:2619: 'gag pa med las zhes pa rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i bde ba la'o //
NK063(gu)001:2620: thams cad 'gag ces pa lam pas nyams su blangs
NK063(gu)001:2621: pa'i tshe phyi ma'i bde ba skyes tsam na snga
NK063(gu)001:2624: ces pa rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la 'gag pa med pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:2625: de ni snga ma'i bde ba zhig nas phyi ma'i
NK063(gu)001:2626: bde ba la 'jug pas 'jig 'jug byang sems so
NK063(gu)001:2627: // gnas pa med las zhes pa rang bzhin gyi bde ba la rten med pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2628: thams cad gnas zhes pa rten can gyi bde ba rang sa na gnas pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2629: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK063(gu)001:2630: ces pa rang bzhin gyi bde ba la gnas bca' ba dang bral ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:2631: de ni dga' ba bcu drug rang sa'i bde ba
NK063(gu)001:2632: skyes la ma 'gags par gnas pa ni gnas pa
NK063(gu)001:2633: byang sems so // dmigs pa med las zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:2634: rang bzhin gyi ye shes la yul gud du dmigs
NK063(gu)001:2635: byang sems so // su med do // thams cad
NK063(gu)001:2636: dmigs zhes pa dga' ba bcu drug rang sa'i bde
NK063(gu)001:2637: ba bas phyi ma'i bde ba la mos pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2638: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK063(gu)001:2639: ces pa rang bzhin gyi ye shes de yul gud du dmigs su med pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:2640: de ni bde ba phyi ma la smon pas smon pa byang sems so //
NK063(gu)001:2641: 'gro 'ong med las zhes pas rang bzhin gyi ye
NK063(gu)001:2642: shes ni rtsa gnas nas lugs su 'gro ba dang
NK063(gu)001:2643: slar log nas 'ong ba gnyis ma grub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2644: 'gro dang zhes pas thig le dbab pa'i thabs kyis
NK063(gu)001:2645: phab ste rdor pad kyi rtser dga' ba bcu drug
NK063(gu)001:2647: dus der thig le gnyis 'phrad nas bzung thabs kyis
NK063(gu)001:2648: bzung ste ma shor ba ni shes rab ye shes
NK063(gu)001:2649: kyi dbang thob pa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:2650: des shes sgrib dag nas don dam 'od gsal gyi ye shes skyes pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2651: 'ong zhes pas thig le slar ldog pa'i thabs kyi
NK063(gu)001:2652: pad+ma dang rdo rje'i rtse nas ldog ste lte ba
NK063(gu)001:2653: sprul pa'i 'khor lo na yar song bas thig le
NK063(gu)001:2654: gzhi mdo la slebs tsa na sngon gyi gnas rjes
NK063(gu)001:2655: su dran pa'i shes pa zhes bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:2656: rtog tshogs thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK063(gu)001:2657: 'khor du sangs rgyas pa ni bde ba chen po'i
NK063(gu)001:2658: dbang thob pa ste kun rdzob dang dbyer med kyi
NK063(gu)001:2661: ces pas lam pa la de ltar snang yang rang
NK063(gu)001:2662: bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la 'gro 'ong
NK063(gu)001:2663: gnyis med de / de ni byang chub sems dbab bzung gis lugs su 'gro ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:2664: ldog dgram gyi slar 'ong ba ste 'gro 'ong byang sems so //
NK063(gu)001:2665: 'dir kha cig zab mo'i dbang gsum po 'di rkyen
NK063(gu)001:2666: gleng slang ba yin nam bstan pa rgyud don yin
NK063(gu)001:2667: / dang po ltar na lhan cig pa'i 'khor gyis dbang thob pas rgyud go bar mi 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2668: rgyud ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2669: gnyis pa ltar na le'u'i mtshan dang yang 'gal zhing
NK063(gu)001:2670: bstan pa 'byung ba'i rkyen ma yin par 'gyur ro
NK063(gu)001:2671: zhe na / lhan cig pa'i 'khor la bltas nas
NK063(gu)001:2672: gsang dbang rkyen yin cing dbang phyi ma gnyis rgyud
NK063(gu)001:2673: don yin pas nyes pa dang po med de /
NK063(gu)001:2674: ji skad du spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:2675: rgyud kyi rkyen gnyis las thun mong ma yin par gleng slang ba gsang ba'i dbang bstan pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:2678: ston pa yab yum gyis gleng slang ba ni dbang
NK063(gu)001:2679: bskur zhing rgyud bshad pa'i phyir zhes gsungs pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:2680: ro // go phye ba'i 'khor la bltas nas dbang
NK063(gu)001:2681: gsum ka rkyen yin pas nyes pa gnyis pa yang
NK063(gu)001:2682: ro // med de / ji skad du de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:2683: 'khor gyis rtogs nas gleng slang ba ni go phye
NK063(gu)001:2684: ba rnams kyi ched du zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro
NK063(gu)001:2685: // des na bltas pa gnyis la ltos nas dbang
NK063(gu)001:2686: gsum po rgyud 'byung ba'i rkyen dang rgyud don gnyis
NK063(gu)001:2688: gleng slang ba dbang thob pa rgyud go ba gsum
NK063(gu)001:2689: ngo bo gcig pa'i phyir lhan cig pa'i 'khor la
NK063(gu)001:2690: bltas te rgyud tshar gcig rdzogs pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:2691: de'i phyir lhan cig pa rnams rang don du sku lnga'i bdag nyid du sangs rgyas pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:2692: gsum pa mthar phyin 'bras bu'i sems bskyed pa ste gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2693: e ma ho zhes pas lnga char snyoms par zhugs shing gleng slang ba la ngam zhing /
NK063(gu)001:2694: ngo mtshar zhes pa yang dbang skur zhing rgyud bshad pa la ngam la /
NK063(gu)001:2695: rmad kyi chos zhes pas sgrib pa dag cing sangs rgyas pa la ngam pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2696: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK063(gu)001:2697: zhes pa ni lnga char rang don du mngon par
NK063(gu)001:2698: rdzogs par sangs rgyas pas ston pa'i dgongs pa dang
NK063(gu)001:2699: tha dad med pa de go phye ba'i 'khor gyis
NK063(gu)001:2700: spyod yul du ma gyur pas gsang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:2701: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK063(gu)001:2702: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK063(gu)001:2703: ces pa rkang pa gnyis ni skye ma skyes dbyer med chos kyi skur dang /
NK063(gu)001:2704: 'gag pa med las zhes pa gnyis ni 'gag mi 'gag gnyis med longs skur dang /
NK063(gu)001:2705: gnas pa med las zhes pa gnyis ni gnas mi gnas dbyer med rdo rje'i sku dang /
NK063(gu)001:2706: dmigs pa med las zhes pa gnyis ni dmigs mi
NK063(gu)001:2707: dmigs gnyis med mngon par byang chub pa'i skur dang
NK063(gu)001:2708: / 'gro 'ong med las zhes pa gnyis ni 'gro 'ong gnyis med sprul pa'i skur sems bskyed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2709: gnyis pa thun mong du gleng slang ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:2710: de ltar rang don du ston pa dang dgongs pa
NK063(gu)001:2711: tha dad med pa'i phyir rgyud zhu mi dgos kyang
NK063(gu)001:2712: gzhan don du go phye ba'i 'khor gyi ched du
NK063(gu)001:2715: 'khor gyis rtogs nas gleng slang ba ni go phye ba rnams kyi ched do //
NK063(gu)001:2717: zhus pa dngos gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2718: e ma ho ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK063(gu)001:2719: zhes pa rkang pa bzhi gzhung brtag la /
NK063(gu)001:2720: 'di'i don la 'grel pa'i dgongs pas ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:2721: lam gyi rgyud dang theg pa thun mong ba rnams
NK063(gu)001:2722: bshad du gsol zhes pas zur gnyis su shes par
NK063(gu)001:2723: bya ste 'di nyid go ba'i skal ba can rnams
NK063(gu)001:2724: la khyad par gyi lam 'di nyid bshad du gsol
NK063(gu)001:2725: zhes pa dang / skal pa de dang mi ldan
NK063(gu)001:2726: pa rnams la thun mong gi lam dang theg pa
NK063(gu)001:2727: rnams bshad du gsol zhes zhus par spar khab kyis
NK063(gu)001:2728: zhes pa dang / bsal lo // ston pas gnang
NK063(gu)001:2729: ba ni phal cher gzhung brtags te mthar spro ba
NK063(gu)001:2730: sna tshogs mdzad ces pa la 'grel pa nas gsang
NK063(gu)001:2731: ba'i snying po 'di nyid bshad par dgyes pa'i tshul
NK063(gu)001:2732: drug mdzad pa dang zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:2733: tshul drug po gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2739: sprul pa spro ba'am 'od zer 'gyed pa dang drug go //
NK063(gu)001:2740: de la snga rabs pa kha cig 'grel pa mkhan
NK063(gu)001:2741: po ni pho kham chung zhing 'du shes 'khums pa
NK063(gu)001:2742: yin te / gzhung nyid nas sna tshogs mdzad ces gsungs pa'i phyir zer ba la /
NK063(gu)001:2743: bla ma ni gong gi drug po yang sna tshogs pa yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:2744: de'i bye brag sprul pa'am 'od zer ni ba spu'i
NK063(gu)001:2745: bu ga re re nas kyang bye ba phrag drug
NK063(gu)001:2746: cu drug cu 'gyed pa'i phyir da ltar mi 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:2747: gsung ngo // yang thun mong gi gleng slang ba
NK063(gu)001:2748: 'dir bka' stsal pa dang gsol pa zhes mi 'dug
NK063(gu)001:2749: gsung ngo // pas / 'khor gyis zhus shing ston pas gnang bar mi 'thad do zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2750: rdo rje'i tshig 'dir zhus pa dang lan dngos su mi gsal yang don gyis zhus lan yin te /
NK063(gu)001:2751: ston 'khor dgongs pa tha dad med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2752: 'o na zhu mi dgos par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:2753: tha dad med pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2754: rang don du 'dod cing gzhan don du khyab pa med do //
NK063(gu)001:2756: thun mong ma yin nges pa'i rgyud //
NK063(gu)001:2757: dris lan mi mngon don gyis bsdus //
NK063(gu)001:2759: yang mtshan ni samskrita'i sgra pa ta la zhes pa las drangs na le'u zhes bya la /
NK063(gu)001:2760: le'u'i mtshan gyis gzhung 'gebs pa'am skyob pa yin pa
NK063(gu)001:2761: la 'dir mtshan gyis gzhung ma khebs so zhe na
NK063(gu)001:2762: / de ni 'di ltar don dam par zhes par gsang dbang 'dus te /
NK063(gu)001:2763: de ni gnyis med kyi ye shes nyams su myong
NK063(gu)001:2764: byed yin la gnyis med kyi ye shes ni don
NK063(gu)001:2766: kun rdzob kyi ye shes zhes par ye shes rang gnas 'dus te /
NK063(gu)001:2767: de ni myong ba'i ye shes rgyud la gsal byed
NK063(gu)001:2768: yin la gsal ba ni kun rdzob yin pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:2769: ro // bde ba chen po ma 'dus so zhe
NK063(gu)001:2770: na gong ma gnyis kyis shugs la 'dus pa yin
NK063(gu)001:2771: ro // te / gong ma rgyud la brtan pa ni bde ba chen po yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2772: 'o na thun min gyi gleng slang de dag tu 'dus kyang /
NK063(gu)001:2773: thun mong gi gleng slang ma 'dus so zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2775: lhan cig pa rnams chos zhu mi dgos kyang dgongs
NK063(gu)001:2776: pa tha dad med pa rgyu mtshan du byas nas
NK063(gu)001:2777: de ma rtogs pa'i don du thugs rje zhu ba'i
NK063(gu)001:2778: phyir / thun mong gi gleng slang de thun min
NK063(gu)001:2779: gyi yon tan nam 'bras bu yin pas thun min
NK063(gu)001:2781: yang kha cig ni gsang dbang ni sems bskyed pa'i
NK063(gu)001:2782: rgyu yin zhing thun mong gi gleng slang de'i 'bras
NK063(gu)001:2783: bu yin pas rgyu ming 'bras la btags pa dang
NK063(gu)001:2784: / yang de las ldog ste thun mong gi gleng
NK063(gu)001:2785: slang 'bras bu'i ming gis rgyu sems bskyed pa la
NK063(gu)001:2786: btags pas 'bras ming rgyu la btags pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:2787: thun mong thun min du 'du la de mtshan du
NK063(gu)001:2788: 'dus par sngar 'bru bshad pas shes so gsung ngo
NK063(gu)001:2789: // yang na gsang dbang ni sems bskyed pa'i rgyu yin /
NK063(gu)001:2790: dbang gnyis kyi las sems bskyed pa dngos yin /
NK063(gu)001:2791: go phye ba'i ched du rgyud zhu ba thun mong
NK063(gu)001:2792: gi gleng slang ni de dag gi 'bras bu yin
NK063(gu)001:2793: pa'i phyir mtshan du thams cad 'dus par sems te
NK063(gu)001:2795: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u gnyis pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2797: // le'u gsum pa'i 'grel pa ni de nas zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:2798: la kha cig le'u gnyis par gleng slang ba bstan
NK063(gu)001:2799: nas gsum pa 'dir gleng gzhi ston zhes pa ni
NK063(gu)001:2801: ji skad du spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:2802: rgyud dum bur gyur kyang rim pa ma nor ba'i phyir nas zhes bya'o zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:2803: gsum pa'i gleng gzhi 'di rgyud 'byung ba khyad par
NK063(gu)001:2804: can gyi gleng gzhi ma yin pa'i phyir gnyis par
NK063(gu)001:2805: gleng slang nas 'di'i smad nas rgyud 'byung ba ni
NK063(gu)001:2807: 'o na gsum pa'i stod 'dir bstan pa 'byung ba
NK063(gu)001:2808: spyi'i gleng gzhi zhes bya ba thub pas thun mong
NK063(gu)001:2809: gi theg pa gsungs pa 'di mi 'thad de /
NK063(gu)001:2810: le'u gnyis par lhan cig pas e ma ho zhes
NK063(gu)001:2811: gsang ba bzhis bsgribs pa'i ched du rgyud bshad par
NK063(gu)001:2812: zhus shing / ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK063(gu)001:2813: bstan phyin zhes ston pas rgyud 'di nyid gsung bar zhal gyis bzhes pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:2814: gnyis par zhus pa'i don la 'grel pa mkhan pos zur gnyis su bkral te /
NK063(gu)001:2815: rgyud 'di nyid chig chod du go ba'i skal ba
NK063(gu)001:2816: dang mi ldan pa rnams la lam stegs kyi theg
NK063(gu)001:2817: pa gsung bar zhus pa'i lan du gsungs pa yin
NK063(gu)001:2819: ji skad du theg pa thun mong ba rnams bshad du gsol zhes pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:2820: des na thun mong gi theg pa gsung ba po
NK063(gu)001:2821: thub pa yin la de ston pa nyid las sprul
NK063(gu)001:2822: pa'i phyir gleng gzhi'i rgyu yin te /
NK063(gu)001:2823: de ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las zhes pa la sogs gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:2824: gleng gzhi spyir bstan pa ni 'thon nas kyang zhes pa la sogs la ngag don bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:2825: don bya ba'i zhing stong gsum dang /
NK063(gu)001:2826: don mdzad pa po thub pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:2827: don mdzad tshul 'dul pa bzhi dang /
NK063(gu)001:2828: don mdzad pa'i yul 'gro ba lnga'o //
NK063(gu)001:2829: dang po ni stong gsum gyi stong chen po zhes pa ni gzhung gzhan las ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:2830: gling bzhi pa dang ri rab dang //
NK063(gu)001:2831: nyi zla dang ni 'dod lha dang //
NK063(gu)001:2832: tshangs pa'i 'jig rten stong la ni //
NK063(gu)001:2833: stong ni spyi phud yin par 'dod //
NK063(gu)001:2834: de stong la ni stong gnyis pa //
NK063(gu)001:2835: bar ma'i 'jig rten khams yin no //
NK063(gu)001:2836: de stong la ni stong gsum pa //
NK063(gu)001:2837: zhes bshad pa de lta bu re re ni sprul
NK063(gu)001:2838: pa'i sku thub pa gcig gcig gi zhing yin no
NK063(gu)001:2839: // 'o na gong du 'jig rten drug gi phyogs
NK063(gu)001:2840: bcu mtha' yas mu med pa'i zhes pa dang 'gal
NK063(gu)001:2842: de ni lhun grub longs sku'i zhing yin la de sprul sku'i zhing gi gzhir mtshon pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:2843: gnyis pa ni thub pa zhes pa ni sku thub ste stag dang spre'u ltar mi mdzad /
NK063(gu)001:2844: gsung thub ste ca co mi mnga' /
NK063(gu)001:2845: thugs thub ste mnyam par ma bzhag pa mi mnga' ba'o zhes pa'am /
NK063(gu)001:2846: yang na mdo chen po nas ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:2847: rdo rje sems dpa' sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab
NK063(gu)001:2848: pas 'khor ba'i dpung gtan bcom pa'i phyir thub pa
NK063(gu)001:2849: zhes bya'o zhes gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK063(gu)001:2850: de lta bu thub pa chen po bcom ldan 'das re res so //
NK063(gu)001:2851: gsum pa ni skus 'dul pa la sogs pa mdzad pa bzhis don mdzad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:2852: bzhi pa ni 'gro ba lnga'i zhes pa ni spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:2853: lnga ni bsdus pa ste drug kho na'o zhes pas
NK063(gu)001:2854: lha min stod ris lha la smad ris mir sdud
NK063(gu)001:2855: pa'am / yang na lha'i rigs ngan shos su bsdus
NK063(gu)001:2856: pa de dag gi don mdzad de gang zhe na
NK063(gu)001:2857: pa'am / / gnyis pa bye brag tu mdzad pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:2858: dang po sku'i mdzad pa ni 'dir gsungs pa'i brgyad
NK063(gu)001:2859: po 'di dag mdo sde dang mthun par bcu gnyis
NK063(gu)001:2860: su gsungs te / de yang gzhung gzhan las ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:2861: thugs rje chen por 'jig rten mkhyen //
NK063(gu)001:2862: 'jig rten kun la gzigs nas ni //
NK063(gu)001:2863: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos par //
NK063(gu)001:2864: sprul pa'i rang bzhin sna tshogs kyis //
NK063(gu)001:2865: skye ba mngon par skye ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:2866: dga' ldan gnas nas 'pho ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:2867: lhums su zhugs dang bltams pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:2868: khab dang rgyal srid bzhes pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:2869: btsun mo'i 'khor gyis rol pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:2870: nges 'byung dka' ba spyad pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:2871: bdud sde 'joms dang rdzogs par ni //
NK063(gu)001:2872: byang chub chos kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK063(gu)001:2873: mya ngan 'das par gshegs mdzad rnams //
NK063(gu)001:2874: yongs su ma dag zhing rnams su //
NK063(gu)001:2875: srid pa ji srid gnas par ston /
NK063(gu)001:2877: dga' ldan gyi gnas su lha'i bu dam pa tog dkar pos skye ba zhes pa na /
NK063(gu)001:2878: rol mo dang sil snyan dag las ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:2879: dpal ldan khyod kyi bsod nams dpal gyis ni //
NK063(gu)001:2880: dga' ldan pho brang shin tu mdzes mod kyi //
NK063(gu)001:2881: 'on kyang thugs rje'i dpal dang ldan pas na //
NK063(gu)001:2882: 'dzam bu'i rgyal mtshan du ni char pa phob //
NK063(gu)001:2884: byang chub sems dpa' des gzigs pa rnam pa bzhi'am lnga la gzigs te /
NK063(gu)001:2885: de yang dus yar 'phel gyi dus su mi 'byon
NK063(gu)001:2886: zhing mar 'grib sdug bsngal bzhis gdungs pa'i dus su'o
NK063(gu)001:2887: // gling ni mun pa'i gling du gyur pa gsum du ma yin te 'dzam bu'i gling du'o //
NK063(gu)001:2888: yul yang mtha' 'khob dang dbang po rtul bas legs
NK063(gu)001:2889: spyad dang nyes spyad mi phyed par mi 'byon te
NK063(gu)001:2890: yul dbus su'o // rigs ni gdol pa la sogs
NK063(gu)001:2891: srid pa tha ma pa'i rgyal sras la 'os pa
NK063(gu)001:2892: yul dbus su'o // ma yin te / 'jig rten
NK063(gu)001:2893: na bkur ba'i gnas yon tan drug cu rtsa bzhi
