NK063(gu)001:2894: dang ldan pa'i phyir rgyal po'am bram ze'i rigs te
NK063(gu)001:2895: yul dbus su'o // ma yin te / / 'dir
NK063(gu)001:2896: sh+aakya'i rigs zas gtsang yang chos de dag dang ldan
NK063(gu)001:2897: zhing 'jig rten na ma smad pa yin pas de
NK063(gu)001:2898: yul dbus su'o // ma yin te / / dang
NK063(gu)001:2899: / bud med kyang g.yo sgyu dang bcas pa'i mngal
NK063(gu)001:2900: du mi 'jug ste skyon brgyad dang bral zhing yon
NK063(gu)001:2901: tan sum cu rtsa gnyis dang ldan pa'i lha mo
NK063(gu)001:2902: yul dbus su'o // ma yin te / / dang
NK063(gu)001:2903: / sgyu ma'o // de nas byang chub sems dpa'
NK063(gu)001:2904: byams pa la khyod lha rnams la chos ston par
NK063(gu)001:2906: rang gi mgo las thod dang cod pan phog nas
NK063(gu)001:2907: byams pa'i mgo la bzhag ste khyod 'di'i 'og nas
NK063(gu)001:2908: mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur ro zhes
NK063(gu)001:2909: lung bstan nas rgyal tshab tu dbang bskur ro //
NK063(gu)001:2910: de nas byang chub sems dpa'i bram ze rigs byed
NK063(gu)001:2911: kyi bstan bcos las byung ba ltar glang po che'i
NK063(gu)001:2912: gzugs kyis 'dzam bu'i gling du gshegs par bzhed pa
NK063(gu)001:2913: na zas gtsang gi pho brang du ltas chen po
NK063(gu)001:2914: brgyad byung zhing / yum yang sngar bas mdzad pa
NK063(gu)001:2915: dang ldan zhing sems bde bar gyur nas rgyal po'i
NK063(gu)001:2916: drung du phyin te tshigs su 'acada pa du ma
NK063(gu)001:2917: smras nas lhan cig tu 'dug pa ni mdzad pa
NK063(gu)001:2918: brgyad byung zhing / dang po'o // de nas dpyid
NK063(gu)001:2919: zla tha chung skar ma sa ga la babs pa
NK063(gu)001:2920: na zla ba nya'i mtshan mo yum gso sbyong la
NK063(gu)001:2921: brgyad byung zhing / dang po'o // gnas pa'i tshe
NK063(gu)001:2922: / dran bzhin shes bzhin du glang po che thal
NK063(gu)001:2923: dkar mche ba drug dang ldan par sprul nas yum
NK063(gu)001:2924: gyi glo g.yas na zhugs shing zhugs nas kyang g.yas
NK063(gu)001:2926: de'i tshe yum la rmi lam yang de lta bu rmis pa rgyal po la smras pa /
NK063(gu)001:2927: glang po kha ba dngul mdog mche ba drug /
NK063(gu)001:2928: rkang lag rab mdzes mgo bo dmar sdug pa //
NK063(gu)001:2929: 'gro bzang lus tshigs rdo rje bzhin brtan pa //
NK063(gu)001:2930: glang po mchog gcig khong du song snyam byed //
NK063(gu)001:2932: bram ze rmi lam mkhan la dris pas des smras pa /
NK063(gu)001:2933: khyod la sras mnga' yon tan gyis ni brgyan pa skye bar 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:2934: gal te 'dod pa dag dang rgyal po'i pho brang spangs gyur te //
NK063(gu)001:2935: 'jig rten thugs brtse chags med rab tu byung gyur na /
NK063(gu)001:2936: de ni 'jig rten gsum na sbyin gnas sangs rgyas 'gyur ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:2937: bdud rtsi mchog gi ro yis 'jig rten thams cad tshim mdzad 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:2938: zhes lung bstan pas rgyal po dgyes te bram ze tshim par byas nas bakye'o //
NK063(gu)001:2939: de nas bltams pa dang zhes pa zla ba dgu
NK063(gu)001:2940: 'das pa na skyed mos tshal du me tog kha
NK063(gu)001:2941: 'bus pa la sogs pa bltas bzang po rnams ni
NK063(gu)001:2942: lha mos btsa' ba'i dus la bab par shes nas
NK063(gu)001:2943: / lha mo rgyan du mas brgyan cing 'khor du
NK063(gu)001:2944: mas bskor te shing rta'i steng du 'dug nas lum
NK063(gu)001:2945: bi'i tshal du song ste shing rta las babs nas
NK063(gu)001:2946: glag sha'i yal ga la phyag g.yas pa 'jus te
NK063(gu)001:2947: / / mngal gyi dri mas ma gos par dran
NK063(gu)001:2948: bzhin du g.yas kyi rtsib ma'i go bar nas byon
NK063(gu)001:2949: / / no // tshangs pa dang brgya byin gyis ka shi ka'i gos kyis blangs /
NK063(gu)001:2950: klu'i rgyal po dga' bo la sogs pas lus phyed phyung nas khrus gsol /
NK063(gu)001:2951: lha'i dbang pos me tog sil mas gtor ba dang
NK063(gu)001:2952: dngul gyi rnga yab dang rin po che'i gdugs su
NK063(gu)001:2953: gyur to // de'i tshe ri bo gangs ldan na
NK063(gu)001:2954: gnas pa'i drang srong mdog nag dang rang gi gnag
NK063(gu)001:2955: bram ze me bzhin gnyis rang rang gi rdzu 'phrul
NK063(gu)001:2956: gyis 'ongs pa la mtshan bstan pas brgyal bar gyur
NK063(gu)001:2957: gyur to // to // de las sangs te dris pas /
NK063(gu)001:2958: khye'u 'di la bkra mi shis pa'i mtshan ni med mod kyi /
NK063(gu)001:2959: 'di sangs rgyas pa na bdag cag rgas par gyur
NK063(gu)001:2960: pas tshe'i dus byed par 'gyur te bdag nyid la
NK063(gu)001:2961: brgyal bar zad do zhes smras pa /
NK063(gu)001:2962: btsas gyur gzhon nu 'di yan mtshan ltas ni //
NK063(gu)001:2963: sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan gyis brgyan pa mthong //
NK063(gu)001:2964: 'di ni gnyis su 'gyur te gzhan du min //
NK063(gu)001:2965: khyim na gnas na 'khor lo sgyur rgyal lam //
NK063(gu)001:2966: khyim nas khyim med rab tu byung gyur na //
NK063(gu)001:2967: 'dren pa gzhan gyi dring la mi 'jog par //
NK063(gu)001:2968: 'jig rten 'dir ni mngon rdzogs sangs rgyas 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:2969: gsang ba'i gnas mchog nges par nub gyur cing //
NK063(gu)001:2970: spyi gtsug 'gro ba kun gyis mi mthong ba'i //
NK063(gu)001:2971: mtshan mchog gnyis ldan gzhon nu dam pa 'di /
NK063(gu)001:2972: khab tu bzhugs mi 'gyur zhes lung yang bstan //
NK063(gu)001:2973: zhes mtshan dam par bsgrags so //
NK063(gu)001:2974: de nas byang chub sems dpa' sus kyang ma brten
NK063(gu)001:2975: par drang por bzhengs te phyogs bzhir gom pa bdun
NK063(gu)001:2976: bdun bor pas pad+ma'i phreng ba bdun du gyur to
NK063(gu)001:2977: // de nas skyes bu chen po'i lta stangs kyis
NK063(gu)001:2978: seng ge ltar zhum pa med par gnas nas bdag
NK063(gu)001:2980: lha dang mi'i sbyin gnas su bya'o la sogs pa seng ge'i sgra bsgrags so //
NK063(gu)001:2981: de'i tshe yab rgyal pos 'di btsas ma thag tu
NK063(gu)001:2982: bdag gi bsam pa dang don thams cad grub pas
NK063(gu)001:2983: mtshan yang der gdags par rigs so zhes der btags
NK063(gu)001:2984: so // gzhan yang de'i tshe ya rabs kyi rigs lnga brgya dang /
NK063(gu)001:2989: glang po che'i phrug gu lnga brgya btsas shing 'brangs
NK063(gu)001:2990: pa rnams kyang rgyal pos gzhon nu la rtsed mo'i
NK063(gu)001:2991: phyir byin no // gliing gi dbus su byang chub
NK063(gu)001:2992: kyi shing skyes skyed tshal lnga brgya dang gter kha
NK063(gu)001:2993: lnga brgya yang byung phyogs bzhir rgyal phran bzhi yang
NK063(gu)001:2994: btsas te rgyal po'i khab tu rgyal po pad chen
NK063(gu)001:2995: gyi gzugs can snying po dang /
NK063(gu)001:2996: mnyan yod du rgyal po tshangs byin gyi bu gsal rgyal dang /
NK063(gu)001:2997: 'phags rgyal du rgyal po mu khyud mtha' yas kyi bu rab snang dang /
NK063(gu)001:2998: koo sham+b+hira rgyal po dmag brgya pa'i bu shar ba rnams btsas par gyur /
NK063(gu)001:2999: de ltar yum gyis bskyed pa'i bya ba rdzogs zin cing /
NK063(gu)001:3000: skye bo phal pa skyed pa'i mar mi rigs pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:3001: khyim nas byung ba yum gyis mi bzod pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:3002: yum gyi phyag mang mi bzhed pa'i phyir 'khrungs nas
NK063(gu)001:3003: zhag bdun yum gyi sku tshe lus par 'gyur ba'i
NK063(gu)001:3004: dus lhums su 'jug par mdzad pa'i phyir de nas
NK063(gu)001:3005: dgu bdun na yum sgyu ma chen mo 'das nas
NK063(gu)001:3006: ring bo ma lon par rin po che sna tshogs
NK063(gu)001:3007: bkod pa zhes bya ba nyid kyi khang bzang der
NK063(gu)001:3009: sru skye rgu'i bdag mo la gtad cing ma ma sum cu rtsa gnyis bsgo ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:3010: gtsang ma'i rigs kyi lha rnams kyis kyang bkur sti byas so //
NK063(gu)001:3011: de nas cung zad brtas pa dang sh+aakya'i khye'u stong
NK063(gu)001:3012: phrag bcu dang lhan cig tu byis pa'i slob dpon
NK063(gu)001:3014: tshangs pa dang kha ro skyong dang pad+ma'i yi ge
NK063(gu)001:3015: la sogs pa gzhan gyis mi shes pa drug cu
NK063(gu)001:3017: de nas bram zes lung bstan pa sh+aakya rnams kyis
NK063(gu)001:3018: thos nas rgyal po la khab bzhes par zhus pa
NK063(gu)001:3019: dang / rgyal pos khab tu 'os pa rgyal bu nyid la dris pas rgyal bus smras pa /
NK063(gu)001:3020: gang zhig bdag gi sems ni mngon par dga' byed cing //
NK063(gu)001:3021: bag yod gzugs dang na tshod rus rigs dag pa 'os //
NK063(gu)001:3022: yon tan de ni tshigs su bcad de yi ger bris //
NK063(gu)001:3023: 'di 'dra'i bu mo mchis na bdag la stsol zhes spring ngo //
NK063(gu)001:3024: de 'dra'i bu mo sh+aakya lag na be con las rnyed nas de slong du phyin pas /
NK063(gu)001:3025: lag na be con gyiis smras pa /
NK063(gu)001:3026: zas gtsang gi bu pho brang na skyid bder gnas pa la bdag gi bu mo mi sbyin te /
NK063(gu)001:3027: sgyu rtsal gyi spyod pa ral gri'i thabs dang //
NK063(gu)001:3028: 'phong dang stobs dang rtsis la sogs pa su rgyal ba des 'di khyer cig ces dam bcas so //
NK063(gu)001:3029: de nas zhag bdun na sh+aakya gzhon nu lnga brgya tsam tshogs te /
NK063(gu)001:3030: sa 'tsho ma rgyal ba'i ru mtshon du bzhag pas /
NK063(gu)001:3031: thog mar lhas byin gyis lag pa g.yon pas glang
NK063(gu)001:3032: po che'i sna nas bzung nas g.yas pa'i thal mos
NK063(gu)001:3033: bsad pa dang / de mdzes dga' bos gud du bor ro //
NK063(gu)001:3034: byang chub sems dpas shing rta la 'dug bzhin du
NK063(gu)001:3035: rkang pa ya gcig sa la brkyangs te mthe bos
NK063(gu)001:3036: glang po che'i mjug ma nas bzung ste 'phangs pas
NK063(gu)001:3037: / ra ba dang 'obs bdun bdun las 'das te rgyang grags gcig tu dor ba na /
NK063(gu)001:3038: sa de gshong chen po zhig tu gyur te deng
NK063(gu)001:3039: sang gi bar du yang glang po che'i gshong zhes
NK063(gu)001:3040: grags so // lha yis tshigs su bcad de smras pa /
NK063(gu)001:3041: glang po'i dbang po rdo rje bzhin bzhud pa //
NK063(gu)001:3042: zhabs kyi mthe bos glang po'i dbang po blangs //
NK063(gu)001:3043: ra ba bdun dang 'obs bdun yongs 'das nas //
NK063(gu)001:3044: grong khyer 'di yi phyi rol rgyang ring 'phangs //
NK063(gu)001:3046: de bzhin du 'phong 'gran pa yang 'ben ni lcags
NK063(gu)001:3047: kyi pha gu dang sla nga dang ta la'i sdong
NK063(gu)001:3048: po rnams re re zhing bdun bdun te nyer gcig
NK063(gu)001:3049: la / lhas byin la sogs pas 'ga' zhig las phig par ma gyur to //
NK063(gu)001:3050: byang chub sems dpas mes seng ge 'gram gyi lcags
NK063(gu)001:3051: mda' dang lcags gzhu blangs te 'phangs pas thams cad
NK063(gu)001:3052: las pha rol tu gyur to //
NK063(gu)001:3053: mda' de nub pa'i khung de nas khron pa lta bu'i chu zhig byung ste /
NK063(gu)001:3054: ding sang gi bar du yang mda' chu khron pa skyes zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:3055: de bzhin du rtsis dang yi ge la sogs sgyu
NK063(gu)001:3056: rtsal gyi spyod pa drug cu rtsa bzhi po rnams
NK063(gu)001:3057: gang yang thub par ma gyur pas sa 'tsho ma
NK063(gu)001:3058: byang chub sems dpa' la phul te /
NK063(gu)001:3059: sa 'tsho ma la sogs pa bu mo lnga brgya
NK063(gu)001:3060: dang yang spyod tshul las ma g.yos par gnas so
NK063(gu)001:3061: // de nas sras sgra can 'dzin bltams shing rgyal
NK063(gu)001:3062: po'i thugs la nye bar gnas pa yan chad lnga
NK063(gu)001:3064: de nas rab tu byung ba dang zhes pa byang chub sems dpa'i thugs rnam par dag pa las /
NK063(gu)001:3065: 'dam dang ljan ljin khrod na pad+ma rnam par rgyas //
NK063(gu)001:3066: mi rnams dga' ba'i nang nas rgyal po 'byor pa thob //
NK063(gu)001:3067: sngon chad rgyal ba rnams kyang btsun mo yi //
NK063(gu)001:3068: nang nas mngon par byung nas zhi ba thob pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:3069: snyam du sems na phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi byin
NK063(gu)001:3070: gyis brlabs kyis rol mo dang sil snyan dag las
NK063(gu)001:3072: sdug bsngal brgyal bar sems can mthong nas ni //
NK063(gu)001:3073: 'gro ba'i mgon dang skyabs dang gnas gyur cing //
NK063(gu)001:3074: phan yon mchog dang dpung gnyen gyur cig ces //
NK063(gu)001:3075: khyod kyis sngon ni smon lam de skad btab //
NK063(gu)001:3076: 'gro phan bya phyir smon lam dran par byos //
NK063(gu)001:3077: zhes bskul ba dang byang chub sems dpa' shing rta
NK063(gu)001:3078: la zhon nas grong khyer gyi phyogs kyi sgo bzhir
NK063(gu)001:3079: byon pas shar la sogs par lha'i bu rnams kyis
NK063(gu)001:3080: rgas pa dang na ba dang shi ba rnams bstan
NK063(gu)001:3081: pas / mkhyen bzhin du 'di dag ci yin zhes 'dun pa la dris pa /
NK063(gu)001:3082: 'di yi chos 'di rigs chos yin nam 'on tang ni //
NK063(gu)001:3083: 'gro ba 'di kun la'ang de srid de smros shog /
NK063(gu)001:3084: tshig 'di ma thogs ji bzhin myur du smros shig dang //
NK063(gu)001:3085: thos nas de bzhin don la 'di ni tshul bzhin bsam //
NK063(gu)001:3086: zhes dris pa dang kha lo sgyur bas smras pa /
NK063(gu)001:3087: lha 'di rigs chos ma lags yul 'khor chos ma lags //
NK063(gu)001:3088: skye bo kun gyi dar la bab pa'ang rgas pas 'joms //
NK063(gu)001:3089: khyod kyi yab dang yum dang nye du gnyen tshogs kyang //
NK063(gu)001:3090: rga las ma thar grol pa'i thabs ni gzhan ma mchis //
NK063(gu)001:3092: yang rgyal bus smras pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:3093: kha lo sgyur ba byis pa skye bo mi mkhas pa //
NK063(gu)001:3094: blo dman gzhon pas rgyags shing rmongs pas rga ma mthong //
NK063(gu)001:3095: nga ni slar 'gro nga yi shing rta myur du sgyur //
NK063(gu)001:3096: gang yang rga la gnas ni rtse dgas ci zhig bya //
NK063(gu)001:3100: nub tu shi ba la sogs sngar bzhin du dris shing lan btab nas /
NK063(gu)001:3101: byang gi sgor byang chub sems dpa' nyid kyi mthus
NK063(gu)001:3102: dge slong gi 'byor ba dang ldan pa zhig sprul
NK063(gu)001:3103: te su yin dris pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:3104: lha 'di ni dge slong zhes bya ste sngar gyi
NK063(gu)001:3105: sdug bsngal de dag las thar pa'i lam la zhugs
NK063(gu)001:3106: pa yin no zhes smras pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:3107: 'dun pa thabs de la bdag kyang 'jug par byed do zhes gsungs pa yab kyis gsan nas /
NK063(gu)001:3108: bsrung ba'i phyir 'obs dang sgo gtan dang srung ma yang mang du bsgo bar gyur to /
NK063(gu)001:3109: de nas byang chub sems dpa' pha mas ma gnang
NK063(gu)001:3110: bar rab tu 'byung bar mi rigs par mthong nas
NK063(gu)001:3111: yab kyi drung du song ste 'di skad ces gsol
NK063(gu)001:3112: to // lha cig bdag ni mngon par 'byung ba'i dus bab rigs //
NK063(gu)001:3113: gegs kyang ma mdzad dgyes pa'ang ma mdzad cig /
NK063(gu)001:3114: rgyal po gnyen bcas yul 'khor bcas te glod par mdzod //
NK063(gu)001:3115: ces zhus pas rgyal pos sh+aakya'i rigs rnams sbran te
NK063(gu)001:3116: bsrung ba'i phyir sgo 'phar chen po sgra dpag tshad
NK063(gu)001:3117: phyed du grags pa mi lnga brgya lnga brgyas 'byed
NK063(gu)001:3118: cing gcod pa byas sgo re rer yang sngar bas
NK063(gu)001:3119: lhag pa'i srung ma lnga brgya lnga brgya bkod do
NK063(gu)001:3120: // de nas lhas bskul te 'dun pas byang chub sems dpa' la rta phul ba blangs te /
NK063(gu)001:3121: 'jig rten skyong ba bzhi'i phyag pad+ma dang 'dra bas
NK063(gu)001:3122: rta'i rmig pa nas bteg cing brgya byin dang tshangs
NK063(gu)001:3124: lha klu dri za la sogs pas rol mo dang
NK063(gu)001:3125: mchod pa sna tshogs dang bcas te pho brang gi
NK063(gu)001:3126: mthong sa na yar byon pas /
NK063(gu)001:3127: sh+aakya'i yul dang ne'u ta'i yul dang gyad yul las
NK063(gu)001:3128: 'das te e na'i yul gyi grong rdal rjes su
NK063(gu)001:3129: spags pa nas / dpag tshad drug phyin pa na
NK063(gu)001:3130: nam langs par gyur pa dang rta las babs nas
NK063(gu)001:3131: lha la sogs pa'i 'khor rnams slar bkye ste 'dun
NK063(gu)001:3132: pa la rgyan dang rta byin nas btang ngo //
NK063(gu)001:3133: der mchod rten brtsigs pa ni 'dun pa slar log gi mchod rten zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:3134: de nas mchod rten rnam dag gi rtsar nyid kyi
NK063(gu)001:3135: gtsug phud nyid kyis bregs te nam mkha' la dor
NK063(gu)001:3136: ba lhas blangs te sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gnas
NK063(gu)001:3137: su mchod rten bzhengs pa ni gtsug phud kyi mchod
NK063(gu)001:3138: rten zhes bya'o // rngon pa las rab tu byung
NK063(gu)001:3139: ba dang tshul mthun par gos ngur smrig blangs pa
NK063(gu)001:3141: der mchod rten brtsigs pa la ngur smrig blangs pa'i mchod rten zhes grags so //
NK063(gu)001:3142: de nas sru skye rgu'i mos rgyan mthong ba de
NK063(gu)001:3143: srid du bdag gi snying la mya ngan du 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:3144: gyi rnyam nas rgyan de dag rdzing bur bor ba
NK063(gu)001:3145: la rgyan gyi rdzing bu zhes grags so //
NK063(gu)001:3146: de nas sa 'tsho mas rta la 'jus shing ngus te smras pa /
NK063(gu)001:3147: kye hud basngagasa ldan legs skyes nga'i khyim thab grogs po yin te khyod kyis gzhan du khrid //
NK063(gu)001:3148: 'dun pa rgyal ba kun gyis pha dang ma dag mchod pa'i 'os zhes rtag tu basngagasa mdzad na //
NK063(gu)001:3149: de dag rnams kyang spangs te byung na bud med 'dod pa'i dga' bas 'di lta rmos ci dgos //
NK063(gu)001:3150: kyi hud sdug pa rnams dang bral ba gar las 'da' ba'i rang bzhin dran te rtag ma yin //
NK063(gu)001:3152: de nas dka' thub mdzad pa dang zhes pa ni
NK063(gu)001:3153: 'dzam bu'i gling snyigs ma lnga shas che zhing phyi
NK063(gu)001:3154: rol pa'i lta ba dang dka' thub dang dka' spyad
NK063(gu)001:3155: la mos pa rnams las ldog pa'i don du chu
NK063(gu)001:3156: bo nee rany+dza na'i 'gram du dka' thub lo drug
NK063(gu)001:3157: tu mdzad pas lus chung zhing rid par gyur pa
NK063(gu)001:3158: la lhas tshig su bcad de smras pa /
NK063(gu)001:3159: mi yi dbang po sh+aakya'i sras 'di ni //
NK063(gu)001:3160: brnag pa ma rdzogs don yang ma mdzad cing //
NK063(gu)001:3161: 'jig rten gsum po sdug bsngal mgon med par //
NK063(gu)001:3162: mdzad nas mgon 'di 'grongs par mi 'gyur drang //
NK063(gu)001:3164: grong pa'i bu mo stobs ldan ma la sogs pas
NK063(gu)001:3165: tshod ma phul ba la longs spyod pas stobs dang
NK063(gu)001:3166: mdog phun sum tshogs pas dge sbyong mdzes pa zhes
NK063(gu)001:3167: grags so // de la lnga sde bzang po ma dad nas ba ra n+aa sir gshegs so //
NK063(gu)001:3168: de nas bu mo legs skyes ma'i smon lam mdzad pa de la bskul bas /
NK063(gu)001:3169: ba stong gi 'o ma nying khur byas te 'bras
NK063(gu)001:3170: gsar pa dang lhan cig tu btsos pa'i tshe dpal
NK063(gu)001:3171: gyi be'u la sogs pa bkra shis pa'i mtshan ma
NK063(gu)001:3173: de phul ba blangs nas sngar gyi chu 'gram du khyer te /
NK063(gu)001:3174: longs spyad cing lhung bzed kyang chur dor ro //
NK063(gu)001:3175: de nas spre'usa sbrang rtsi phul bas sku gser gyi mdog can du gyur to //
NK063(gu)001:3176: de nas byang chub snying por gshegs te sngon gyi
NK063(gu)001:3177: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyang r+ts+wa'i gdan bting ba
NK063(gu)001:3178: la bzhugs par mkhyen nas r+ts+wa mchog mya ngan med
NK063(gu)001:3179: pa ni rma bya'i mgrin pa ltar 'jam zhing reg
NK063(gu)001:3180: na bde ba la bzhugs par bzhed pa la lha
NK063(gu)001:3181: yis mthun gyur brjod pa'i tshe /
NK063(gu)001:3182: bkra shis rtsa dag bdag la myur du byin //
NK063(gu)001:3183: de ring nga la r+ts+wa ni don chen 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:3184: dpung dang bcas pa'i bdud ni bcom nas ni //
NK063(gu)001:3185: byang chub dam pa zhi ba reg par bya //
NK063(gu)001:3186: zhes blangs te r+ts+wa'i rtse mo nang du bstan ma
NK063(gu)001:3187: 'khrugs par bting nas zhal shar du bltas te skyil
NK063(gu)001:3188: mo krung bcas sku drang por bsrangs dran pa mngon
NK063(gu)001:3190: stan 'di la ni bdag gi lus 'di bskams kyang rung //
NK063(gu)001:3191: pags pa sha dang rus pa'i tshogs rnams zhig kyang rung //
NK063(gu)001:3192: bskal mang rnyed daka'i byang chub ma thob par //
NK063(gu)001:3193: stan 'di las ni lus bskyod mi bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:3194: zhes dam bcas nas byang chub snying po las mi g.yo bar bzhugs so //
NK063(gu)001:3195: de nas tshig bsgyur te bdud btul ba dang zhes
NK063(gu)001:3196: pa ni de ltar bzhugs nas gdul bya rnams byang
NK063(gu)001:3197: chub mchog tu sems bskyed du gzhug snyam du dgongs
NK063(gu)001:3198: te / nam gyi srod la smin mtshams kyi 'od
NK063(gu)001:3199: zer las bdud thams cad spa bkong zhing mog mog
NK063(gu)001:3200: por byas te gnas thams cad mun pas khyab pa
NK063(gu)001:3201: te / dang / bdud sde dang bcas pa rab
NK063(gu)001:3202: tu 'khrugs te rang gi mngon shes kyis bltas pas
NK063(gu)001:3203: te / dang / / byang chub sems dpa'i ting
NK063(gu)001:3204: nge 'dzin dang lhag par sems bskyed pa la bar
NK063(gu)001:3205: du ma bcad na bdud kyi rigs brlag par shes
NK063(gu)001:3206: nas phrag dog gi mun pas g.yogs te /
NK063(gu)001:3207: rang rang gi 'khor yan lag bzhi pa'i dpung gi
NK063(gu)001:3208: tshogs 'jigs su rung ba rnams ni 'di lta ste
NK063(gu)001:3209: / kha bzhin dmar la lus ni ser ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:3210: kha bzhin ser la lus ni gnag pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:3211: mgo gcig mgo gnyis mgo gsum ldan pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:3212: mgo stong ldan pa'i bar du rab tu mang //
NK063(gu)001:3213: zhes sgyu ma ltar shes pa'i blo dang mi ldan
NK063(gu)001:3214: pas bltas na snying 'gas par 'gyur ba dag gis
NK063(gu)001:3216: sh+aakya'i sras pos rten cing 'brel pa'i chos //
NK063(gu)001:3217: dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid du rtogs //
NK063(gu)001:3218: nam mkha' lta bu'i sems dang rab ldan pas //
NK063(gu)001:3219: g.yo can dpung bcas tshogs kyis bardzi ba med //
NK063(gu)001:3220: ces pa ltar cung zad kyang bskyod par ma nus
NK063(gu)001:3221: te mtshon cha'i char rnams me tog gi bla bre
NK063(gu)001:3223: de nas gong na sangs rgyas pa dang zhes pa de ltar srod la bdud btul nas /
NK063(gu)001:3224: nam gyi cha stod la bsam gtan bzhi mngon du
NK063(gu)001:3225: mdzad de lha'i mig gis sems can gyi 'chi 'pho
NK063(gu)001:3227: nam gyi gung la sngon gyi gnas mkhyen /
NK063(gu)001:3228: tho rangs rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba mtha' dag thugs su chud de /
NK063(gu)001:3229: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin nas zag pa
NK063(gu)001:3230: med pa'i mngon par shes pa mngon du byas pas
NK063(gu)001:3231: rang dang gzhan gyi don grub ste mngon par rdzogs
NK063(gu)001:3233: de nas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang zhes
NK063(gu)001:3234: pa mdzad pa gzhan rnams ni gdul bya 'dun par
NK063(gu)001:3235: byed pa'i yan lag tsam yin gyi chos kyi 'khor
NK063(gu)001:3236: los ni gdul bya dngos su grol bar byed pa
NK063(gu)001:3237: yin no // de yang sangs rgyas ma thag tu
NK063(gu)001:3238: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis phyag brkyangs
NK063(gu)001:3240: bdag cag ji ltar byang chub thob ltar khyed sangs rgyas //
NK063(gu)001:3241: dper na mar dang mar gyi nying khu mtshungs 'dra zhing //
NK063(gu)001:3244: bsod nams rnam smin bde ster sdug bsngal thams cad sel //
NK063(gu)001:3245: bsod nams ldan pa'i mis kyang bsams pa rnams kyang 'grub //
NK063(gu)001:3246: bdud bcom nas ni byang chub myur du reg par gyur //
NK063(gu)001:3247: mya ngan las 'das zhi ba bsil ba'i dngos po thob //
NK063(gu)001:3248: ces gsungs te skyil mo krung ma bshig par byang
NK063(gu)001:3249: chub kyi shing la gzigs te zhag bdun gnas so
NK063(gu)001:3250: // bdun phrag gnyis pa la stong gsum rgyang ring por sku bcags so //
NK063(gu)001:3251: gsum pa la byang chub kyi shing la brten te bzhugs so //
NK063(gu)001:3252: bzhi pa la 'dzam bu'i gling ther med du bcags so //
NK063(gu)001:3253: lnga pa la klu'i rgyal po btang gzung gi gnas su bzhugs so //
NK063(gu)001:3254: drug pa la shing nya gro d+ha skyong gi drung du gshegs shing bzhugs so //
NK063(gu)001:3255: bdun pa sgrol rgyu'i tshal du bzhugs pa'i tshe //
NK063(gu)001:3256: tshong pa ga gon dang bzang pos rnyed pa chen
NK063(gu)001:3257: po rnyed nas tshong pa phal mo che rnams dang
NK063(gu)001:3258: lhan cig tu lho nas byang du chas pa'i shul
NK063(gu)001:3259: lam / glang bu legs skyes dang grags pa gnyis
NK063(gu)001:3260: kyis sangs rgyas bzhugs pa'i phyogs su shing rta drangs
NK063(gu)001:3261: lam / pa dang / de bzhin gshegs pa bzhugs
NK063(gu)001:3262: pa mthong nas dad pa skyes te sbrang rtsi dang
NK063(gu)001:3263: bu ram phul ba rnams 'jig rten skyong bas phul
NK063(gu)001:3264: ba'i lhung bzed du bzhes nas /
NK063(gu)001:3266: lha yis bkra shis don grub cing //
NK063(gu)001:3267: phyogs rnams bkra shis byed pa des //
NK063(gu)001:3269: thams cad myur du mthun par shog /
NK063(gu)001:3270: ces pa la sogs mdo la snga ba shis pa
NK063(gu)001:3271: brjod pa gsungs pa ni bkra shis dam pa'i chos
NK063(gu)001:3272: 'byung ba'i lnga ltas yin no zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:3273: de nas dam pa'i chos btsun par bya ba'i phyir glag sha la gzigs te /
NK063(gu)001:3274: zab zhi spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK063(gu)001:3275: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos shig kho bos rnyed //
NK063(gu)001:3276: su la bstan kyang go bar mi nus pas //
NK063(gu)001:3277: mi smra nags 'dab dag tu gnas par bya'o snyam //
NK063(gu)001:3278: zhes smin mtshams nas 'od byung bas de'i dgongs pa
NK063(gu)001:3279: tshangs pa gtsug phud 'dzin gyis rig nas tshangs ris
NK063(gu)001:3280: kyi lha'i bu rnams sbran te tshangs pa 'bum phrag
NK063(gu)001:3281: drug cu rtsa brgyad kyis bskor te 'dren pa'i spyan
NK063(gu)001:3282: sngar 'ongs nas phyag btsal te gser gyi 'khor lo
NK063(gu)001:3283: rtsibs stong ldan pa phul nas /
NK063(gu)001:3284: ye shes chen po mchog gi dkyil 'khor bsgrubs nas ni //
NK063(gu)001:3285: phyogs bcu dag tu 'od zer rnam par bkye mdzad de //
NK063(gu)001:3286: ye shes zer gyis blo yi pad+ma kha 'byed pa //
NK063(gu)001:3287: smra ba'i nyi ma 'di ring ci slad btang snyoms mdzad //
NK063(gu)001:3288: chos kyi rnga bo che ni brdung du gsol //
NK063(gu)001:3289: dam pa chos kyi dung ni 'bud du gsol //
NK063(gu)001:3290: chos kyi mchod sdong chen po bsgreng du gsol //
NK063(gu)001:3291: zhes gsol ba btab pas cang mi gsung bas gnang
NK063(gu)001:3292: bar rig nas lha'i tsan+dana gyi phye ma dag gis
NK063(gu)001:3293: gtor nas rang gi gnas su dong ngo //
NK063(gu)001:3294: yang brgya byin la sogs 'dod pa dang gzugs kyi lha du mas /
NK063(gu)001:3295: zla ba nya ba gza' las thar pa ltar //
NK063(gu)001:3296: khyod kyi thugs ni rnam par grol ba lags //
NK063(gu)001:3297: g.yul las rnam par rgyal ba bzhengs su gsol //
NK063(gu)001:3298: 'jig rten mun par shes rab 'od dbyung gsol //
NK063(gu)001:3299: zhes gsol ba btab kyang ma gnang ste /
NK063(gu)001:3301: tshangs pa nga yi tha ba kun //
NK063(gu)001:3302: skyon rnams bcom nas rtogs gyur ba //
NK063(gu)001:3303: srid dang chags pas bcings pa yi //
NK063(gu)001:3306: de nas tshangs pas ma ga d+har log pa'i lta ba rgyas par rig nas /
NK063(gu)001:3307: ma ga d+ha 'dir sngon chad chos byung ba /
NK063(gu)001:3308: ma dag dri ma'i rjes su 'brangs par rtogs //
NK063(gu)001:3309: bdud rtsi'i sgo mo dbye bar mdzod cig chos //
NK063(gu)001:3310: rdul bral dri ma med pa bstan du gsol //
NK063(gu)001:3311: zhes pa la sogs kyis zhus pas 'jig rten la
NK063(gu)001:3312: gzigs te snod du gyur cing dus la bab par
NK063(gu)001:3313: mkhyen nas / tshangs pa ma ga d+ha yi sems can gang //
NK063(gu)001:3314: rna bar ldan zhing dad dang ldan gyur par //
NK063(gu)001:3315: mi tsher rtag tu dam pa'i chos mnyan tam //
NK063(gu)001:3316: de dag la ni bdud rtsi sgo dabye'o //
NK063(gu)001:3317: zhes gnang bas tshangs pa dga' mgu yi rangs so //
NK063(gu)001:3318: de nas chos su la bstan snyam du dgongs pas /
NK063(gu)001:3319: rangs byed kyi bu lhag spyod dang sgyu rtsal shes
NK063(gu)001:3320: kyi bu ring 'phur gnyis snod du gyur pa yin
NK063(gu)001:3321: mod kyang de gnyis shi nas zhag bdun dang gsum
NK063(gu)001:3322: lon par mkhyen / de'i 'og tu lnga sde bzang
NK063(gu)001:3323: po snod du gyur pa ni da lta yul ba
NK063(gu)001:3324: r+aa na si na 'khod par gzigs nas /
NK063(gu)001:3327: grong khyer dpal ldan der song nas //
NK063(gu)001:3328: long ba lta bu'i 'jig rten la //
NK063(gu)001:3331: byang chub shing gi lha mos de ni skye bo
NK063(gu)001:3332: chung ste grong khyer chen po gzhan du chos kyi
NK063(gu)001:3335: de skad ma zer cig ngas der mchod sbyin chen po stong phrag drug cu byas so gsungs so //
NK063(gu)001:3336: de nas ba ra n+aa sir byon pa'i tshe lnga sde bzang pos bca' ba byas pas /
NK063(gu)001:3337: de pa'i gzi brjid ma bzod de dam bca' nang
NK063(gu)001:3338: zhig nas ldang ba dang bsu ba dang mchod pa'i
NK063(gu)001:3339: sgo nas dga' bar gyur pa'i gtam du ma yang
NK063(gu)001:3341: de nas sa phyogs der rin po che'i khri stong phrag gcig rang byung ba las /
NK063(gu)001:3342: de pa snga ma rnams la gus par bya ba'i
NK063(gu)001:3343: phyir khri dang po gsum la bskor ba mdzad de
NK063(gu)001:3344: / bzhi pa la bag tsha ba med par bzhugs pas gzhan rnams nub par gyur to //
NK063(gu)001:3345: de nas de bas tshangs pa'i gsung gis chos kyi dung phyung nas /
NK063(gu)001:3346: rnam par dag cing grol bar byed pa'i thabs dpag tu med pa cig gsungs so //
NK063(gu)001:3347: de dag kyang theg pa che chung gi mdo ma
NK063(gu)001:3348: lus pa rnams sde snod gsum du bsdus pa yang
NK063(gu)001:3349: nye bar spyod pa dang kun nas dkris pa dang
NK063(gu)001:3350: bag la nyal rnams kyi gnyen por bslab pa gsum
NK063(gu)001:3351: gyi rjod byed du gsungs pa ste bka' dang po
NK063(gu)001:3353: bar pa bya rgod phung po dang rgyal po'i khab la sogs pa mtshan nyid med pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:3354: tha ma dur khrod bsil ba'i tshal dang grong khyer
NK063(gu)001:3355: r+ts+wa mchog la sogs par theg pa sna tshogs sam
NK063(gu)001:3356: don dam rnam par nges pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK063(gu)001:3357: bskor ba'o // de nas cho 'phrul chen po bstan
NK063(gu)001:3358: pa dang zhes pa ni ljags las mchil ma'i thal
NK063(gu)001:3359: ba zhig gis mu stegs kyi ston pa sum brgya
NK063(gu)001:3360: drug cu chus khyer bar mdzad pa la sogs cho
NK063(gu)001:3362: de nas 'gro ba rnams rtag pa la mngon par
NK063(gu)001:3363: zhen pa bzlog pa'i ched du mya ngan 'das pa
NK063(gu)001:3364: zhes pa lo brgyad cu la 'da' bar dgongs pa
NK063(gu)001:3365: las / bram ze su ka tos ut+pala gtor nas
NK063(gu)001:3366: mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol ba btab pas
NK063(gu)001:3367: las / / lo gnyis bzhugs te skal pa dang ldan pa btul zhing /
NK063(gu)001:3368: skal med mi 'dul ba dang le lo can brtson 'grus la bskul te skyo ba bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:3369: r+ts+wa mchog gi grong gyad stobs po che 'byung ba'i
NK063(gu)001:3370: gnas shing s+aa la zung cig gi dbus chu bo
NK063(gu)001:3371: ba ti ha ri'i 'gram du shing zad pa'i me
NK063(gu)001:3372: ltar dgongs pa yongs su mya ngan las 'da' ba'i
NK063(gu)001:3373: tshul bstan to // de yang nyan thos pas 'dod
NK063(gu)001:3374: pa ltar bstan nas rgyun chad pa mi mnga' ste
NK063(gu)001:3375: tshul bstan to // / ji skad du 'di nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:3376: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'da' //
NK063(gu)001:3377: chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur te //
NK063(gu)001:3378: ma rig smin mdzad 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:3379: byung nas mya ngan 'da' bar ston //
NK063(gu)001:3381: la sogs pa zhes sku gdung ring bsrel bgos pa
NK063(gu)001:3382: la sogs 'di'i brgyad du bcu gnyis su gsungs pa
NK063(gu)001:3383: rnams bsdus pa'i sgra yin no //
NK063(gu)001:3384: de rnams ni drang ba'i don yin te /
NK063(gu)001:3385: nges don du ston pa kun tu bzang po nyid
NK063(gu)001:3386: las ma g.yos par gdul bya dang grangs mnyam par
NK063(gu)001:3387: rgyud drug gi 'dul byed du thub pa drug tu
NK063(gu)001:3388: sprul zhing / khyad par mi'i gnas kyi zhing 'dir
NK063(gu)001:3389: thub pa'i dbang po 'dir bstan nas don mdzad pa
NK063(gu)001:3390: sprul zhing / yin no // yang sku'i mdzad pa'i
NK063(gu)001:3391: skabs 'dir chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang zhes
NK063(gu)001:3392: pa ni sku'i mdzad par mi rung ste /
NK063(gu)001:3393: gsung gi mdzad pa yin pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:3395: sgra don gyi gtso bo las thob pa dmag dpon lta bu dang /
NK063(gu)001:3396: gzhi po las thob pa lha khang bzhengs pa'i gnas brtan lta bu dang /
NK063(gu)001:3397: phal che ba las thob pa skyes pa stong gi
NK063(gu)001:3398: gseb na bud med gcig gnyis yod pa lta bu
NK063(gu)001:3399: las / de dag gsum ka dang ldan te rim
NK063(gu)001:3400: pa ltar mdzad pa rnams kyi gtso bo yang sku'i
NK063(gu)001:3402: brten pa gsung gi gzhi yang rten sku yin pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:3403: rnam grangs brgyad dam bcu gnyis las phal yang sku'i
NK063(gu)001:3404: che ste gsung gi gcig las med pa'i phyir sku'i
NK063(gu)001:3405: khongs su bsdus pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:3406: yang 'dir kha cig le'u'i slad nas sku gsung thugs
NK063(gu)001:3407: rdo rje las 'thon to zhes ston pa las sprul
NK063(gu)001:3408: pa dang / bltams pa dang zhes dga' ldan nas
NK063(gu)001:3409: babs shing lha mdzes la bltams par gsungs pa gnyis
NK063(gu)001:3411: gong ma ni nges don gyi dbang yin la phyi
NK063(gu)001:3412: ma ni gdul bya'i ngo la drang don gyi dbang
NK063(gu)001:3413: yin no // yang na nges don gyi dbang du
NK063(gu)001:3414: yang ston pa'i sprul pa lha mdzes la bltams pa
NK063(gu)001:3416: thugs kyi mdzad pa ni dus bzhi zhes pa /
NK063(gu)001:3417: de ni 'das pa rgyu 'bras gnyis ka spyad zin pa /
NK063(gu)001:3418: da ltar ba rgyu spyad cing 'bras bu ma spyad pa /
NK063(gu)001:3419: ma 'ongs pa rgyu 'bras tshogs pa ma spyad pa /
NK063(gu)001:3420: 'byung bar ma nges pa rgyu 'bras yod la ma 'tshogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:3421: kun tu mkhyen pa dang zhes pa dus de dag re mos mkhyen nam mnyam pa'am gcig tu mkhyen /
NK063(gu)001:3422: dang po ltar na de sangs rgyas kyi mngon shes ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:3423: de ltar sems can gyi rtog pa la'ang snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:3424: gnyis pa ltar na dus bzhi ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:3425: gcig pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:3426: bzhir snang ba ni 'khrul pa'i blo yin la /
NK063(gu)001:3427: 'khrul pa de dag la mnyam pa'am gcig tu mkhyen pas skyon gnyis ka las grol lo //
NK063(gu)001:3428: yang 'dir kha cig 'dir dus log pa'i skyon yod de /
NK063(gu)001:3429: chos gzhan nas gsum du bshad pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:3430: de gang zhes dri bar bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:3431: kho na re 'das ma 'ongs da ltar gsum yin zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:3432: de'i steng du 'byung bar ma nges pa dang bzhi yin no //
NK063(gu)001:3433: de bsnan pas bzhir 'gyur gyi nges par gsum yin no zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:3434: de tshod du nges par gnyis yod pa gang gis 'gog byas pas /
NK063(gu)001:3435: de gang yin zhes 'dri na da ltar dang da ltar ma yin pa gnyis yin no //
NK063(gu)001:3436: de la khong gis smras pa da ltar ma yin
NK063(gu)001:3437: pa la bye bas 'das ma 'ongs gnyis da ltar
NK063(gu)001:3438: dang gsum du nges so zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:3439: mtshungs te da ltar ma yin pa la ma nges
NK063(gu)001:3440: pa dang gsum da ltar dang bzhir nges pa yin
NK063(gu)001:3441: no // gzhan yang spyir dus nges ma nges gnyis su tshad mas grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:3442: nges pa la gsum du tshad mas grub pa'i phyir nges par yang sems so //
NK063(gu)001:3443: 'dir gsung sgros kyis blo dus las 'khrul pa chos
NK063(gu)001:3444: nyid dus las 'das pa rang byung ye shes dus
NK063(gu)001:3445: la dbang sgyur ba ste dus tha dad du 'dzin
NK063(gu)001:3447: 'khrul pa de dag pa'i rgyal ba la dus tha dad mi mnga' ste /
NK063(gu)001:3448: ji skad du rgyas pa las /
NK063(gu)001:3450: ye shes rtogs pa'i khyad par las //
NK063(gu)001:3451: dus bzhi snga phyi med pa yi //
NK063(gu)001:3452: mnyam pa nyid du lhan ner sbyor //
NK063(gu)001:3454: des na rgyal ba ni chos nyid mngon byas yin la /
NK063(gu)001:3455: chos nyid ni dus las 'das pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:3456: chos nyid rtogs pas dus la dbang sgyur ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:3457: de'i phyir ma 'khrul pa'i nga na dus tha dad
NK063(gu)001:3458: med cing 'khrul ngo na gsum du'ang ma nges te
NK063(gu)001:3459: / gzhi mi khegs shing gnyis su'ang 'dus pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:3460: de ltar dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pas sngon dang
NK063(gu)001:3461: phyi ma'i gnas mkhyen pa la sogs mngon shes drug
NK063(gu)001:3462: tu rtsi zhing gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:3463: yang 'dir rdzu 'phrul gyi cho gas kun tu don
NK063(gu)001:3464: spyod pa dang zhes pa stod nas me 'bar ba
NK063(gu)001:3465: dang smad nas chu 'brub pa la sogs pa rnams
NK063(gu)001:3466: lus kyi rdzu 'phrul yin pa'i phyir thugs kyi mdzad
NK063(gu)001:3469: rdzu 'phrul gang gis 'dul ba'i bya ba shes pa ni mngon shes yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:3470: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdzad pa ni kun tu
NK063(gu)001:3471: sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang zhes pa la
NK063(gu)001:3472: 'grel pa'i dgongs pas stag dang spre'u la sogs pa
NK063(gu)001:3473: 'gro ba tha dad kyi gzugs su snang ba ste
NK063(gu)001:3477: de la sogs te bsam mi khyab //
NK063(gu)001:3478: ri dang skye bo thams cad do //
NK063(gu)001:3480: yang na mdo sde 'ga' zhig nas grangs dang tshad bsam gyis mi khyab pa gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:3481: dang po ni sgyu ma mkhan bzang pos sgyu ma'i
NK063(gu)001:3482: khang pa dang longs spyod mang po bshams nas de
NK063(gu)001:3483: pa spyan drangs pas de dag re re na yang
NK063(gu)001:3484: bzhugs shing longs spyod par snang la /
NK063(gu)001:3485: rdo rje gdan na ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs shing
NK063(gu)001:3486: bya rgod phung po'i ri la chos gsung ba rnams
NK063(gu)001:3487: dus gcig la snang ba lta bu dang /
NK063(gu)001:3488: gnyis pa ni mo gal gyi bu'am shugs 'chang gis
NK063(gu)001:3489: steng gi phyogs kyi zhing khams mang po brgal ba'i
NK063(gu)001:3490: pha rol na yang de pa'i dbu'i gtsug tor blta
NK063(gu)001:3491: bar mi mngon pa lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:3492: yang sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'di 'grel pa
NK063(gu)001:3493: ltar na le'u'i klad du thub pa'i nges tshig sku
NK063(gu)001:3494: thub ste stag dang spre'u ltar mi mdzad ces pa
NK063(gu)001:3496: lan ni don du 'gyur ba bzhi dang mi ldan na thub pa'i nges tshig nyams shing /
NK063(gu)001:3497: de dang ldan na sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa ltar yang yin no //
NK063(gu)001:3498: yang kha cig ni sna tshogs gdul bya'i snang ba yin la /
NK063(gu)001:3499: thub pa'i nges tshig de pa'i snang ba yin no zhes gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:3500: 'di ni 'grel pa'i ngag gong 'og 'gal ba ltar
NK063(gu)001:3501: snang ba ste de'i lan gong ma dag gis thebs
NK063(gu)001:3502: shing / gzhung la thub pa'i nges tshig mdo chen
NK063(gu)001:3503: po ltar dang sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa mdo
NK063(gu)001:3504: sde ltar na 'gal ba med par sems so //
NK063(gu)001:3506: gsung gi mdzad pa ni chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang zhes pa'am /
NK063(gu)001:3507: gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa de dag thams cad
NK063(gu)001:3508: kyang 'og tu ston pa 'di lta ste zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:3509: la / spyir theg pa'i don la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:3510: nang pa'i theg pa tsam du mtshon pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK063(gu)001:3511: de'i rab tu dbye ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:3512: phye ba theg pa so so'i don bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:3513: dang po ni gang rnam grol gyi lam 'bras bu dang bcas pa cig yin no //
NK063(gu)001:3514: gnyis pa dbye ba la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:3515: mtshon bya sgra bshad pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:3517: dang po ni samskri ta'i sgra las ya na zhes pa las drangs na theg pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:3518: de ni rang gi blo dang 'tshams par snang ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:3519: ji skad du rgyas pa las /
NK063(gu)001:3520: bla med theg pa bsam yas gsungs pa yang //
NK063(gu)001:3521: so so rang gi blo la snang bar zad //
NK063(gu)001:3523: yang na 'dis 'di 'dir bgrod pa'i don gyis na theg pa ste rim pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:3524: dang po ni bzhon pa bzang po rta dang glang
NK063(gu)001:3525: po lta bu theg pa rang rang gi bstan pa'i
NK063(gu)001:3526: gzhung tshogs so // gnyis pa ni de dag la
NK063(gu)001:3527: zhon pa'i mi lta bu theg pa nyams su len
NK063(gu)001:3528: pa po rten gyi gang zag go //
NK063(gu)001:3529: gsum pa ni gang du 'gro bya'i gnas lta bu
NK063(gu)001:3530: theg pa rang rang gi 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:3531: phyir na theg pa zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:3532: gnyis pa dbye ba dang po ni spyir bka' rgyud
NK063(gu)001:3533: so so'i gzhung gis 'dod pa tha dad pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:3534: theg pa'i rnam grangs ma nges par 'dod do //
NK063(gu)001:3535: bye brag tu rgyud 'di'i dbang du sngar gsungs pa 'di yin no //
NK063(gu)001:3536: gsum pa dbye ba so so'i don ni gdul bya
NK063(gu)001:3537: tha dad pa'i rgyud 'dul ba'i dbang gis theg pa'i
NK063(gu)001:3538: bye brag so sor bstan te gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:3539: dang po lha dang mi'i zhes pa ni bsod nams
NK063(gu)001:3540: kyi bye brag las thar pa'i rten du gyur pa'o
NK063(gu)001:3541: // theg pa zhes pa la rgyu mtshan bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:3542: dge sdig gi rgyu 'bras phyin ci ma log par
NK063(gu)001:3543: rtogs nas zhi rags sam mi g.yo ba bsgom zhing
NK063(gu)001:3544: dge sdig 'dor len du spyad pas ngan song las
NK063(gu)001:3545: thar te / lha mi'i mngon par mtho ba'i go 'phang thob pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:3546: nyan thos kyi zhes pa rang gi lam du zhugs
NK063(gu)001:3547: nas 'bras bu ma thob kyi bar rkyen slob dpon
NK063(gu)001:3548: la phal cher nyan zhing thos dgos pas na'o //
NK063(gu)001:3549: theg pa ni sngar ltar bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:3550: gang zag gi bdag med rtogs nas 'gog pa'i ting
NK063(gu)001:3551: nge 'dzin bsgom zhing rang don gtso bor spyad pas
NK063(gu)001:3552: 'bras bu dgra bcom pa 'thob pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:3553: rang byang chub kyi zhes pa sbyor lam gyi bzod
NK063(gu)001:3554: pa 'bring po nas rang gi 'bras bu thob thob
NK063(gu)001:3555: tu rkyen slob dpon la mi ltos par rang gi
NK063(gu)001:3556: shes rab kyis 'bras bu thob pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:3557: theg pa zhes pa yang gang zag dang chos kyi
NK063(gu)001:3558: phyogs gcig la rang bzhin med par rtogs nas rten
NK063(gu)001:3559: 'brel lugs ldog bsgom zhing rang don gtso bor spyod
NK063(gu)001:3560: de / lus kyi rdzu 'phrul gyis gzhan don shas
NK063(gu)001:3561: 'ga' nus shing yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi sa
NK063(gu)001:3563: byang chub sems dpa'i zhes pa shes rab chen pos
NK063(gu)001:3564: byang chub cing snying rje chen pos sems can la
NK063(gu)001:3565: sems dapa'o // theg pa zhes pa yang bdag med
NK063(gu)001:3566: gnyis rtogs nas sa bcu'i ting nge 'dzin rim par
NK063(gu)001:3567: bsgom zhing pha rol tu phyin pa bcus don gnyis
NK063(gu)001:3568: rgya chen po spyad pas kun tu 'od kyi sa
NK063(gu)001:3570: de dag de ltar rang rang gi blo dang 'tshams pa'i phyir theg pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:3571: bla na med pa'i zhes pa kri ya nas a
NK063(gu)001:3572: ti'i bar gsang sngags kyi bstan pa mtha' dag gi
NK063(gu)001:3573: don yin te / 'og ma dag gis blar gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:3574: theg pa zhes rgyu mtshan bzhi po dag kyang gong ma las khyad par du gyur pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:3575: 'di ltar lta bas chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:3577: gnyis bral mnyam dang mi mnyam de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings //
NK063(gu)001:3580: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba yi //
NK063(gu)001:3582: de'i don yul med du bsgom pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:3584: ma bcos de bzhin ngang bzhag dang //
NK063(gu)001:3587: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK063(gu)001:3589: de'i ngang la blang dor dang bral bar spyod pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:3591: spyod pa ci la'ang thogs med spyod //
NK063(gu)001:3593: de dag gis 'bras bu sku lnga mngon du 'gyur pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:3595: de tshe sku lnga lhun gyis grub //
NK063(gu)001:3597: des na gong gi nges 'byung gi theg pa rnams
NK063(gu)001:3598: las khyad par du gyur pa'i phyir bla na med
NK063(gu)001:3599: pa'o // gal te sngar gyi grub mtha' 'dzin pa
NK063(gu)001:3600: dag khyad par de dag yod par ma grub ce
NK063(gu)001:3601: pa'o // na / 'dir mdo sngags kyi khyad par gzhag par bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:3602: de la kha cig ni sgra don gyi khyad par yod de /
NK063(gu)001:3603: rgyu mtshan nyid zer bas sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi rgyur 'dod cing /
NK063(gu)001:3604: 'bras bu gsang sngags zer bas sems nyid ye nas
NK063(gu)001:3605: 'bras bur gnas par 'dod pa'i phyir ro zhes zer
NK063(gu)001:3606: ro // yang kha cig ni don dam la dngos stong du 'dzin mi 'dzin dang /
NK063(gu)001:3607: kun rdzob la 'khrul par 'dzin mi 'dzin dang /
NK063(gu)001:3608: bden pa dbyer med khas len nus mi nus kyi khyad par yod zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:3609: yang kha cig ni shes rab la khyad par med
NK063(gu)001:3610: cing thabs kyi khyad par gang zhig gis phye ba
NK063(gu)001:3611: yin te pha wang nam 'phang gcod pa lta bu
NK063(gu)001:3612: zer ro // kha cig lta ba gtan la 'bebs
NK063(gu)001:3613: tshul la brtags na go myur bul gyi khyad par
NK063(gu)001:3614: zer ro // yod de / 'di ni chos nyid
NK063(gu)001:3615: rang gi mtshan nyid mngon sum du gtan la 'bebs
NK063(gu)001:3616: zer ro // yod de / pas myur la /
NK063(gu)001:3617: cig shos ni rjes dpag gis gtan la 'bebs pas
NK063(gu)001:3618: rang mtshan mi mthong ba'i phyir bul lo //
NK063(gu)001:3619: gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha' la brtags na mtha' skyon che chung yod de /
NK063(gu)001:3620: cig shos ni kun rdzob snang ba las grol kyang don dam stong par zhen pas skyon che la /
NK063(gu)001:3621: 'di ni de la ma zhen pas skyon dang bral ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:3622: lam nyams su len tshul la brtags na lam nye ring gi khyad par yod de /
NK063(gu)001:3623: 'dir tshe gcig gam rtogs grol dus mnyam pa'ang 'dod pas nye la /
NK063(gu)001:3624: cig shos bskal par sbyong dgos pa'i phyir ring ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:3625: nyams su blangs pa'i 'bras bu la brtags na gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi khyad par yod de //
NK063(gu)001:3626: ji skad du dbyig sgron las /
NK063(gu)001:3627: khyod kyi bcu gcig kun tu 'od //
NK063(gu)001:3628: thabs chen theg pa'i bsti gnas sa //
NK063(gu)001:3631: pad+ma can du gyur pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:3634: de dag ston pa'i gzhung la brtags na gsal bar ston mi ston gyi khyad par yod de /
NK063(gu)001:3635: 'di'i gzhung rnams nas 'og ma ba'i lta spyod 'bras bu la sogs ji lta bar ston la /
NK063(gu)001:3636: 'og ma'i gzhung nas 'di'i de dag ming tsam yang brjod par mi nus pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:3637: de ltar khyad par lngar bzhed do //
NK063(gu)001:3638: de ltar yin kyang de dag ni cung zad zhe 'dod kyi dbang gis bkod pa'ang srid la /
NK063(gu)001:3639: gzhung rnams nas khyad par du ma gsungs te /
NK063(gu)001:3641: don gcig na yang ma rmongs dang //
NK063(gu)001:3642: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:3643: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas pas //
NK063(gu)001:3644: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK063(gu)001:3647: dkar po'i mthar thug bsod nams kyis //
NK063(gu)001:3648: gsang nyid skad cig 'bum char min //
NK063(gu)001:3651: yan lag lta bu'i dbu ma nyams kyang 'tsho //
NK063(gu)001:3652: snying dang 'dra ba'i gsang nyid med na brlag /
NK063(gu)001:3653: ces pa la sogs pa du ma gsungs shing //
NK063(gu)001:3655: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK063(gu)001:3656: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK063(gu)001:3657: zhes pa la sogs bka' rgyud dang gzhung rnams nas
NK063(gu)001:3658: khyad par gsungs pa rnams ni yang dag pa'i sgrub
NK063(gu)001:3660: de yang khyad par de dag gi dpe'i stong thun
NK063(gu)001:3661: chen po bzhi las 'dir dug sdong dang sbyar te
NK063(gu)001:3662: / dper na khyim bdag cig gis bza' shing sna
NK063(gu)001:3663: tshogs bskyed pa'i ra bar dug gi rtsa ba cig
NK063(gu)001:3664: 'phel bas khyim bdag gi bu shi na /
NK063(gu)001:3665: de'i 'khor rnams dug gi spong lugs la blo che chung du ma byung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:3666: de yang bza' shing gi ra ba dang 'dra bar
NK063(gu)001:3667: kun gzhi rnam shes dge sdig gi bag chags sna
NK063(gu)001:3669: dug gi rtsa ba ltar ma rig pa las nyon mongs pa 'phel ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:3670: khyim bdag shi ba ltar sems nyid 'khor ba'i 'dam du bying ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:3671: 'khor rnams dug gi spong lugs du ma byung ba
NK063(gu)001:3672: ltar 'khor ba spong lugs la blo che chung gis
NK063(gu)001:3673: theg pa mtho dman du ma'o //
NK063(gu)001:3674: de'i tshe 'khor 'ga' zhig ni sngar yang nyes pa
NK063(gu)001:3675: de lta bu byung zhing da gzod kyang 'byung srid
NK063(gu)001:3676: pas dug 'dis 'dom dgu'i bar rtsad nas spong dgos
NK063(gu)001:3677: zer ba ltar / nyan rang gi nyon mongs pa
NK063(gu)001:3678: la dgra dang tsher ma ltar spong ba ni gzhi
NK063(gu)001:3680: 'ga' zhig ni dug de ther slang la sogs par
NK063(gu)001:3681: mes bsregs shing sbyangs na chus med du 'gyur zer
NK063(gu)001:3682: ba ltar / byang chub sems dpas sa dang lam
NK063(gu)001:3683: du gnyen po ye shes kyis sbyong bar 'dod pa
NK063(gu)001:3685: 'ga' zhig bram ze la sogs kyi sngags kyi btab
NK063(gu)001:3686: nas slar sman du yang 'gyur zer ba ltar sngags
NK063(gu)001:3687: phyi rgyud pas cho ga yan lag gis snod gzhal
NK063(gu)001:3688: yas khang dang bcud lhar bsgyur pa ni bsgyur ba'i
NK063(gu)001:3689: lam pa'o // de'i tshe rma byas dug mthong ma
NK063(gu)001:3690: thag tu zas su ngo shes shing longs spyad pas
NK063(gu)001:3691: kho'i skad snyan pa dang mdongs legs pa la sogs
NK063(gu)001:3692: yon tan de las byung ba ltar /
NK063(gu)001:3693: nang rgyud bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyis nyon mongs pa chos
NK063(gu)001:3694: nyid du rtogs shing thabs kyi zin par spyad pas
NK063(gu)001:3695: slar 'bras bu myur ba ni dbang du byed pa'i
NK063(gu)001:3696: lam pa'o // de'i dus kyi sa gzhi de la dug skyes pas mi dga' ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:3697: spangs pas dga' ba'i rnam rtog dang bral ba ltar /
NK063(gu)001:3698: a ti bla na med pa'i theg pa ni chos
NK063(gu)001:3699: thams cad skye 'gag dbyer med kyi ngang du mnyam
NK063(gu)001:3700: pa rtogs pas spang bya dang gnyen po gnyis dang
NK063(gu)001:3701: bral ba ni dgag sgrub med pa'i lam pa zhes
NK063(gu)001:3702: bya'o // de ltar 'dir theg pa kun gyi sa
NK063(gu)001:3703: bon yod kyang ha cang rgyas par bshad na skabs
NK063(gu)001:3704: don las 'chol ba dang dus ring du mi thon
NK063(gu)001:3705: pas 'gyangs par 'gyur ba'i phyir mdor bsdus pa yin
NK063(gu)001:3706: bya'o // no // nyon mongs pa la dgongs te dbye ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:3707: gdul bya sems can rnams ma rig pa'i dbang gis
NK063(gu)001:3708: rang rang gi rnam par rtog pa dang nyon mongs
NK063(gu)001:3709: pa bsam gyis mi khyab kyang cung zad rigs bsdu
NK063(gu)001:3710: na stog phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:3711: dug gsum dang de gsum cha mnyam pa las gyur
NK063(gu)001:3712: pa'am nga rgyal phrag dog gnyis gcig tu bsdu ste
NK063(gu)001:3713: / de ltar rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa bzhi po
NK063(gu)001:3714: dag re re las kyang nyi khri chig stong re
NK063(gu)001:3715: rer gyur pas stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK063(gu)001:3716: de'i gnyen por chos kyi sgo yang de snyed du
NK063(gu)001:3717: sde snod gsum la nyi khri chig stong re re
NK063(gu)001:3718: dang / sngags kyi bstan pa thams cad gcig tu bsdus pa las nyi khri chig stong gcig ste /
NK063(gu)001:3719: de ltar stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK063(gu)001:3720: de dag 'das pa'i dus su'ang gsungs shing da ltar yang gsung la /
NK063(gu)001:3721: ma 'ongs pa'i dus su'ang gsung bar 'gyur zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:3722: 'dir gsang sngags kyi bstan pa thams cad 'ga' zhig sems kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:3723: 'ga' zhig shes rab kyi bslab pa ston pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:3724: gong gi sde snod gsum las mdo sde dang mngon
NK063(gu)001:3725: pa gnyis su 'du zer ba ni ma yin par
NK063(gu)001:3727: thub pa chen pos chos phung po //
NK063(gu)001:3728: brgyad khri dang ni bzhi stong gsungs //
NK063(gu)001:3731: brgyad khri bzhi stong bstan pa yang //
NK063(gu)001:3733: gong gi chos stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi zhes
NK063(gu)001:3734: pas chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong du
NK063(gu)001:3735: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gnyis ka nas gsungs la
NK063(gu)001:3737: sngags las gzhan pa'i sde snod bzhi pa shes bya la khegs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:3738: gzhan yang sngags la tshul khrims kyi bslab pa mi khegs te /
NK063(gu)001:3739: dam tshig yin pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:3742: bla med mchog gi dam tshig tu //
NK063(gu)001:3743: 'dul ba'i dbang gis tshul khrims dang //
NK063(gu)001:3744: ji snyed sdom pa bsam yas pa //
NK063(gu)001:3745: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /
NK063(gu)001:3747: des na bslab pa gsum ni rjod byed sde snod thams cad kyi khyab byed yin par sems so //
NK063(gu)001:3748: gnyen po la dgongs te bsdu ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:3749: de ltar chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong
NK063(gu)001:3750: gsungs pa de dag thams cad kyang dbang po'i bye
NK063(gu)001:3752: dang po lha mi ni tshig bsgyur te 'og nas /
NK063(gu)001:3753: dge sdig gi las tha dad pa dang mi g.yo ba'i las dang gsum gyi rang bzhin /
NK063(gu)001:3754: yang 'bru bsgyur la chud mi za ba'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:3755: gong nas 'bras bu mtho riss ma bde ba dang
NK063(gu)001:3756: ngan song ngam sdug bsngal dang khams gong ma'i btang
NK063(gu)001:3757: snyoms rnams su smin par rtogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:3758: nyan thos ni tshig gong na /
NK063(gu)001:3759: gang zag gi bdag med rtogs nas chos kyi bdag
NK063(gu)001:3760: phyi gzung ba'i yul rags pa la rang bzhin med
NK063(gu)001:3761: par rtogs shing / phra ba nyi zer gyi rdul
NK063(gu)001:3762: 'bring po la zhe dgur bgos pa'i cha gcig lta
NK063(gu)001:3763: bu rdul phran cha med don dam gyi dngos por
NK063(gu)001:3764: par rtogs shing / 'dod pa dang / nang 'dzin
NK063(gu)001:3765: pa'i shes pa la 'das ma 'ongs kyi rgyun rang
NK063(gu)001:3767: skad cig ces bya ba se gol gcig gtogs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:3768: sbyor ba skor gcig la cha brgya drug cu skye
NK063(gu)001:3769: 'gag gnas gsum phyed pa'i cha gcig lta bu don
NK063(gu)001:3771: rang rgyal ni bstan pa'i gzhung nyan thos la sogs pa med de /
NK063(gu)001:3772: rigs kyis phye ba tsam yin no //
NK063(gu)001:3773: 'on kyang lta ba'i khyad par ni gang zag gi
NK063(gu)001:3774: bdag med nyan thos dang 'dra ba'i steng du chos
NK063(gu)001:3775: bdag gzung yul rdul phran la rang bzhin med par
NK063(gu)001:3776: rtogs nas 'dzin shes skad cig bden dngos su 'dod
NK063(gu)001:3777: la / phyi zhes pa de'i rten cing 'brel bar
NK063(gu)001:3778: 'byung ba ni rgyu dang 'brel ba'i chos sa bon
NK063(gu)001:3780: de dag kyang 'byung ba lnga dang dus kyis 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:3781: ba la sogs rkyen gyis bsdus pa'i chos drug ste
NK063(gu)001:3782: bcu gnyis po sgyu ma ltar shes shing /
NK063(gu)001:3783: nang zhes pa de'i rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba
NK063(gu)001:3784: ni ma rig pa la las 'du byed de las
NK063(gu)001:3785: rnam shes ming dang gzugs skye mched drug reg pa
NK063(gu)001:3786: tshor ba sred pa len pa srid pa skye ba
NK063(gu)001:3787: rga shi la sogs pa gcig la gcig brten nas
NK063(gu)001:3788: byung ste lugs 'byung 'khor ba'i chos de dag mig
NK063(gu)001:3790: de ltar yang rgyas pa las /
NK063(gu)001:3791: phyi nang rten 'brel sgyu ma mig g.yor tshul shes shing //
NK063(gu)001:3793: byang chub sems dpas ni rang rgyal gyis 'dod pa'i
NK063(gu)001:3794: 'dzin pa'i shes pa skad cig ma de chos can
NK063(gu)001:3796: gzung yul med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:3797: rtags kho rang gi khas kyang len cing tshad mas kyang grub bo //
NK063(gu)001:3798: khyab pa ni gzung don med na 'dzin shes med
NK063(gu)001:3799: de sngon po med na sngo 'dzin med pa bzhin
NK063(gu)001:3801: gzung ba med na der 'dzin med //
NK063(gu)001:3803: 'dzin shes ma grub par shes pas bdag med gnyis ka rtogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:3804: dkar dmar la sogs phyi rol gyi snang tsam 'di
NK063(gu)001:3805: dag rtog med snang yul la 'khrul pa'i shes pa
NK063(gu)001:3806: yin pa'i phyir / de la kun rdzob ces tha
NK063(gu)001:3807: snyad 'dogs pa ste zla ba gnyis 'dzin gyi shes
NK063(gu)001:3808: yin pa'i phyir / pa bzhin no // de ltar
NK063(gu)001:3809: nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi po de dag lta
NK063(gu)001:3810: ba'i dbang du bsdus pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:3811: 'bras bu'i theg pa gcig tu bstan pa ni spyod pa'i dbang du ston te /
NK063(gu)001:3812: gang zhe na las dang zhes pa kri ya ste /
NK063(gu)001:3814: khrus dang gtsang sbra gtsor byed cing //
NK063(gu)001:3815: sdom dang tshul khrims dag la brtson //
NK063(gu)001:3816: yang lag tshang dang bzhugs gsol dang //
NK063(gu)001:3817: bzlas pa zur phyin las su byed //
NK063(gu)001:3818: de phyir kri ya las zhes bya //
NK063(gu)001:3820: de 'og gi mi gos zhes pa dang sbyor te /
NK063(gu)001:3821: de dag gis 'khor ba'i las dang bag chags kyis mi gos pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:3822: las kyi 'bras bu zhes pa yo ga ste /
NK063(gu)001:3824: yan lag dgu ste gnyis med sbyor //
NK063(gu)001:3825: mtshan ma'i las la brten can nas //
NK063(gu)001:3826: mtshan ma med pa'i 'bras bu bsgrub //
NK063(gu)001:3827: de phyir yo ga las kyi 'bras //
NK063(gu)001:3829: de 'og gi gos par mi 'gyur zhes pa dang
NK063(gu)001:3830: sbyar bas las kyi 'bras bu la mtshan mar 'dzin
NK063(gu)001:3832: bsgrub bya mtshan med gos su med pa grub pa'i phyir ro zhes pa'i don yin no //
NK063(gu)001:3834: bltas sa nges 'byung gi theg pa la ltos nas
NK063(gu)001:3835: mthar thug go zhes bya ste gnas skabs kyi chos
NK063(gu)001:3837: 'dir kha cig ston pa'i mthar thug go //
NK063(gu)001:3839: gong gi bla na med pa zhes pa gnyis bstan
NK063(gu)001:3840: pa gsang ba'i snying po 'di yin nam ma yin
NK063(gu)001:3841: / yin na 'og nas rgyud don gsung mi dgos la /
NK063(gu)001:3842: min na mthar thug dang bla na med par bshad pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:3843: ma yin pas nyes pa dang po med la /
NK063(gu)001:3844: mthar thug kyang 'das ma thag de nyid 'bru bsnan
NK063(gu)001:3845: pa'i skabs su bshad zin te bltas pa'i mthar thug
NK063(gu)001:3846: 'dod rgyal du smras pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:3847: bla na med pa zhes pa yang gsang sngags mtha' dag la dgongs pa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:3848: de'i bye brag gi ming gis spyi la btags nas
NK063(gu)001:3849: bla na med pa zhes bya ba'i rgyu mtshan yang
NK063(gu)001:3851: yang spyir thub pa'i mdzad pa 'di rnams la /
NK063(gu)001:3853: drang ba pa dag dga' ldan gyi gnas nas babs zer ba ni bden mod kyi /
NK063(gu)001:3855: mdzad pa 'di dag drang don rgyu'i theg pa bas
NK063(gu)001:3856: dam pa tog dkar po dga' ldan nas 'phos pa
NK063(gu)001:3858: dga' ldan gnas nas 'pho ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:3859: lhums su zhugs dang bltams pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:3861: mdzad pa rnams mthar phyin pas srid pa tha ma
NK063(gu)001:3862: pa'i byang chub sems dpa' ste rgyud mas sbyangs su
NK063(gu)001:3863: 'dod la / nges don gsang sngags 'di'i dgongs pas
NK063(gu)001:3864: ston pa nyid las ma g.yos par gdul bya'i ngo
NK063(gu)001:3865: la thub pa drug tu shar te /
NK063(gu)001:3866: khyad par mi'i gnas su sh+aakya thub par sprul nas
NK063(gu)001:3867: mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyis don mdzad par snang ba
NK063(gu)001:3868: yin te / ji skad du le'u'i klad nas /
NK063(gu)001:3869: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:3870: rdo rje las 'thon to zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:3871: 'o na de ltar ston pa las sprul pa'i thub pas gsang sngags gsungs te /
NK063(gu)001:3873: bla na med pa'i theg pa /
NK063(gu)001:3875: mdo chen po nas thub pa 'das nas lo nyer brgyad kyi dus su 'byung bar bshad de /
NK063(gu)001:3877: nga ni 'di na mi snang nas //
NK063(gu)001:3878: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK063(gu)001:3879: zhes gsungs pa gnyis mi 'gal lam zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:3880: 'di gzhung so so'i dgongs pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:3881: bka' gzhan nas phyis 'byung bar bshad pa ni sprul
NK063(gu)001:3882: pa nyid bzhugs pa'i tshe thun mong gi 'khor 'dus
NK063(gu)001:3883: pa phal mo che rnams la rgyu'i theg pa las
NK063(gu)001:3884: sngags ma gsungs shing gsang sngags ni phyis gsang bdag
NK063(gu)001:3885: gis ston par lung bstan pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:3886: 'di nas bla na med pa zhes gsungs pa ni
NK063(gu)001:3887: khyad par gyi 'khor rig 'dzin nam sa non pa
NK063(gu)001:3888: rnams la gzhan gyi mi tshod ma yin par gsungs
NK063(gu)001:3890: yang na 'dir sngags gsungs pa ni gsang sngags tsam du gyur pa phyi rgyud yin la /
NK063(gu)001:3891: gzhan nas phyis 'byung bar gsungs pa na khyad par can nang gi rgyud rnams yin par sems so //
NK063(gu)001:3892: 'o na 'dir thun mong ma yin pa theg pa
NK063(gu)001:3893: 'byung dgos pa'i skabs su thub pas lam stegs kyi
NK063(gu)001:3894: theg pa gsung pa 'di skabs 'chol bar mi 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:3895: ram zhe na / ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:3896: rgyud 'di'i byin gyis rlabs las de dag byung ba'i
NK063(gu)001:3897: phyir rgyud dang ston pa'i che bar 'gyur ba'i dgos
NK063(gu)001:3899: yang 'dir chig chod du 'jug mi nus pa'i ched
NK063(gu)001:3900: du lam stegs kyi theg pa la blo sbyangs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:3902: ji skad du tha ma las /
NK063(gu)001:3903: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK063(gu)001:3904: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK063(gu)001:3905: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir skabs 'chol bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK063(gu)001:3906: gsum pa 'bras bu rgyud don dngos ni gsum pa'i
NK063(gu)001:3907: smad 'di nas nyer gcig pa yan chad du le'u
NK063(gu)001:3908: phyed dang bcu dgus ston no //
NK063(gu)001:3909: de yang lo rgyus su brjod pa ni de nas zhes mtshams sbyor sdud pa po'i tshig ste /
NK063(gu)001:3910: de pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid kyis lam gyi
NK063(gu)001:3911: rgyud don 'di nyid go phye ba'i 'khor gyi ched
NK063(gu)001:3912: du brjod pa 'og nas 'byung ba 'di brjod do
NK063(gu)001:3915: zur gnyis kyi dang po lam dang zhes pa 'di
NK063(gu)001:3916: nyid go ba'i skal ba can rnams la 'di nyid
NK063(gu)001:3917: lam gyi rgyud du bshad du gsol zhes pa'i lan
NK063(gu)001:3918: du / gnyis pa rgyud dngos gsungs pa las /
NK063(gu)001:3919: dang po rgyu shes pa lta ba'i don gtan la dbab par bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:3920: de las kyang 'khor ba'i chos gtan la dbab pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:3921: gang gzhal bya chos can dang /
NK063(gu)001:3922: gang gis 'jal byed gtan tshigs dang /
NK063(gu)001:3923: ji ltar gzhal zhing gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha'o //
NK063(gu)001:3925: ji snyed ces pa la sogs rkang pa bzhis 'khor
NK063(gu)001:3926: ba'i rgyu dang ngo bo dang tshul dang nyes pa
NK063(gu)001:3928: 'di'i don nges par bya ba la spyir gzhal bya'i don gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:3929: le'u bcu gcig par 'chad pa ltar rigs gsum las 'dir gzhung don gtan la 'bebs pa'i dus su /
NK063(gu)001:3930: ji snyed ces dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:3932: brtags pa'i spyod yul gnyis la gzhal //
NK063(gu)001:3934: de yang de gnyis kyi rang mtshan gzhal bya ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:3935: 'das pa'i rang mtshan spyod yul du ma gyur /
NK063(gu)001:3936: 'khor ba'i rang mtshan 'khrul pa ni brdzun pa'i phyir gzhal byar mi rung la /
NK063(gu)001:3937: de gnyis kyi zhen snang gzhal bya yin te /
NK063(gu)001:3941: de yang zhen snang gnyis re re gzhal bya ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:3942: dper na snang cha nas thag pa yin yang zhen cha nas sbrul du zhen pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:3943: snang cha nas 'das pa yin kyang zhen cha nas
NK063(gu)001:3944: 'khor bar zhen pa'i de gnyis kyi tshogs pa de
NK063(gu)001:3947: de bas yul sems ma 'dres phyir //
NK063(gu)001:3948: zhes snang 'jal la skyon pa med //
NK063(gu)001:3950: de ltar 'dod pa la kha cig na re /
NK063(gu)001:3952: gtan tshigs kyis gzhal mi dgos par thal /
NK063(gu)001:3953: de grub zin pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:3955: zhen snang grub kyang de chos nyid du ma nges
NK063(gu)001:3956: pas gtan tshigs kyis nges par bsgrub pa yin no
NK063(gu)001:3957: // 'o na zhen snang gtan la phab pas chos nyid gtan la mi phebs te /
NK063(gu)001:3958: tha dad pa'i phyir rta gtan la phab kyang glang po'i chos nyid mi rtogs pa bzhin zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:3959: rta glang lta bu tha dad 'brel ba med par ma grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:3960: zhen snang dang chos nyid chos can dang chos nyid yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:3961: chos can zhen snang gtan la phab pas chos nyid de bzhin nyid nges par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:3962: dper na chos can dung la dpyad pas chos nyid dkar po rtogs pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:3963: 'o na zhen snang bsam gyis mi khyab pas gtan
NK063(gu)001:3964: la phab kyis mi lang bar 'gyur ro zhe na
NK063(gu)001:3965: / de dag re re zhing gtan la dbab mi dgos te /
NK063(gu)001:3966: zhen snang gcig chos nyid du gtan la phab pas kun gtan la phebs par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:3967: dper na mar me gcig 'od skyed par grub na
NK063(gu)001:3968: yul dus rang bzhin tha dad kyi mar me yang
NK063(gu)001:3969: 'od skyed par grub pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:3970: gnyis pa gtan tshigs thun mong dang thun min gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:3971: dang po ni bden pa'i gtan tshigs te /
NK063(gu)001:3972: de yang yang dag ces pa don dam dang /
NK063(gu)001:3973: sgyu ma zhes pa kun rdzob bo //
NK063(gu)001:3974: tshul gnyis su zhes pa rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg
NK063(gu)001:3975: pa bas chos thams cad bden pa gnyis su smra
NK063(gu)001:3976: ste / snang ba mtshan gzhi kun rdzob bden pa'i tha snyad du mtshan no //
NK063(gu)001:3977: rig pas dpyad mi bzod 'dzin pa mtshan nyid du bkod pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:3978: yang snang dus nyid na snang med mtshan gzhi don dam bden pa'i tha snyad du mtshan no //
NK063(gu)001:3979: rig pas dpyad bzod 'dzin pa mtshan nyid du bkod pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:3980: de ltar chos thams cad bden pa gnyis su smra ste /
NK063(gu)001:3982: sangs rgyas rnams kyis chos bstan pa //
NK063(gu)001:3983: bden pa gnyis la yang dag brten //
NK063(gu)001:3984: 'jig rten kun rdzob bden pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:3985: dam pa'i don gyi bden pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:3986: zhes de ltar 'dod pa dang tshul mthun par 'dir yang gnyis su smra ste /
NK063(gu)001:3987: ma rig pas bdag tu 'dzin pa'i shes pa dang
NK063(gu)001:3988: phung po la bdag gi bar rtog pa dang 'byung
NK063(gu)001:3989: ba la gzhan du btags te yul du 'dzin pa
NK063(gu)001:3990: rnams chos can / de ltar grub pa med de /
NK063(gu)001:3991: bden pa gnyis su rnam par dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:3992: de'i tshul bsgrub pa ni kun rdzob kyi dbang du bdag ces rnam shes te /
NK063(gu)001:3993: de ye shes su rtog pa ye shes sgyu ma yin la /
NK063(gu)001:3994: gzhan cis 'byung ba ste de yum lngar rtogs pa dngos po sgyu ma yin cing /
NK063(gu)001:3995: bdag gi zhes pa phung po ste de rigs lngar
NK063(gu)001:3996: rtogs pa phyag rgya sgyu ma zhes bya ba yin
NK063(gu)001:3997: no // yang don dam gyi dbang du bdag ces rnam shes te /
NK063(gu)001:3998: de ye shes su rtogs pa ye shes don dam /
NK063(gu)001:3999: gzhan zhes 'byung ba lnga yum gyi rang bzhin don dam yin cing /
NK063(gu)001:4000: bdag gi zhes phung po lnga rigs lngar rtogs pa 'bras bu don dam yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4001: de la kha cig de ltar yin par ma grub ce na /
NK063(gu)001:4002: de dag tu lung gis grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:4004: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK063(gu)001:4005: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK063(gu)001:4006: zhes phung po rigs lngar bshad pas grub cing /
NK063(gu)001:4008: sa chu spyan dang m+aa ma k+ai //
NK063(gu)001:4009: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste //
NK063(gu)001:4010: nam mkha'i dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK063(gu)001:4011: zhes pas 'byung ba yum gyi rang bzhin du grub la /
NK063(gu)001:4014: zhes pas rnam shes yongs su bshad pas grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4015: de ltar bden pa gnyis kyang tha dad du rtogs
NK063(gu)001:4016: pa rnam par dag ste chos kyi dbyings de bzhin
NK063(gu)001:4017: nyid du tshul gcig par go ba ni bden pa'i
NK063(gu)001:4018: rtags kyi bsgrub bya yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4019: gnyis pa thun min la rtogs pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:4021: dang po la rgyu gcig pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:4022: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan rnams ni //
NK063(gu)001:4023: zhes log rtog bdag gzhan gsum po mtshan du sngar dang 'dra'o //
NK063(gu)001:4024: de ltar snang ba ni log par rtog pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4025: 'khrul pa'i ngo bo nyid du snang ba las /
NK063(gu)001:4026: de rang bzhin shes pa'i ngo na phra zhing phra
NK063(gu)001:4027: ste rdul phran tsam dang zab pa skad cig tsam
NK063(gu)001:4028: du'ang yod pa ma yin pa'i phyir dper na nam
NK063(gu)001:4030: 'o na gzugs sgra la sogs pa'i snang dpyod chen po rgyun chad du thal /
NK063(gu)001:4031: de dag phra ste rdul zab ste skad cig tsam
NK063(gu)001:4032: yang ma grub pa'i phyir na nam mkha'i pad+mo bzhin
NK063(gu)001:4033: no zhe na / rang bzhin shes pa'i ngo na
NK063(gu)001:4034: med kyang 'khrul ngo na snang ba mi 'gal te
NK063(gu)001:4035: no zhe na / / log rtog gi rgyun snga
NK063(gu)001:4036: ma nyid kyis rgyun gyis spyod pa ni de ma
NK063(gu)001:4037: yin la der 'dzin pa'i phyir rab rib can la
NK063(gu)001:4038: snang ba'i skra bshad bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:4039: des na 'khrul ngo la snang ba nyid yang dag
NK063(gu)001:4040: par ma grub pa'i phyir chos kyi dbyings las gzhan
NK063(gu)001:4041: du g.yo ba ci yang med par rtogs pa ni
NK063(gu)001:4042: rgyu gcig pa'i rtags kyi bsgrub bya yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4043: 'o na sngar gyi log rtog nyid chos can /
NK063(gu)001:4045: tha snyad pa'i shes ngo na snang spyod tshad mas dmigs pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:4046: blo de yang 'di'i ji bzhin pa rtogs pa la ltos nas log rtog yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4047: de'i rgyu ma rig pa dang 'bras bu snang zhen gyi rgyun nyid dmigs kyang /
NK063(gu)001:4048: de bden par grub pa med na ci 'gal te /
NK063(gu)001:4049: rgyun 'di nyid la brten pa'i gzhi dang bskyed pa'i rtsa ba med de /
NK063(gu)001:4050: chos kyi dbyings ma bcos pa zab mo don gyi skad cig mar rgyu gcig par rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:4051: dper na rab rib can la snang ba'i skra shad
NK063(gu)001:4052: de mig dwang ba'i yul na ma grub pa bzhin
NK063(gu)001:4053: no // yig 'bru'i tshul ni bdag po'i rkyen rtog
NK063(gu)001:4054: snga mas ma rig pa rnam par dag pa'i don
NK063(gu)001:4055: skye med chos kyi dbyings de nyid rtogs pa'i tshul
NK063(gu)001:4057: nyid la zhes pa rtogs bya chos kyi dbyings de bzhin nyid la'o //
NK063(gu)001:4058: dbang sgyur zhes pa de la rtogs byed blo yis dbang sgyur ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:4059: ji ltar sgyur na rgyu shes pa zag bcas kyi
NK063(gu)001:4060: skabs su sgra dang tshig la brten nas dang po
NK063(gu)001:4062: de'i rjes su blos brtags pa 'gal 'brel gyi rnam
NK063(gu)001:4063: dpyod kyis yang dag pa'i don nges pa la yig
NK063(gu)001:4064: 'bru'i tshul gyis rtogs pa zhes 'dod de /
NK063(gu)001:4065: ji skad du bcu gsum pa las /
NK063(gu)001:4066: yi ge sgra btags ming tshogs la //
NK063(gu)001:4067: brten pa'i tshig gis rab mtshon te //
NK063(gu)001:4068: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK063(gu)001:4070: de la yang dag pa'i don mngon du byed pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4071: chos nyid la de rtogs kyi blo nyid kyis spyod pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:4072: ji skad du 'di nyid kyi bzhi pa las /
NK063(gu)001:4073: dbyings la dbyings kyis bris pas na //
NK063(gu)001:4074: yi ge zhes ni de phyir brjod //
NK063(gu)001:4076: gzhung 'dir de ltar rtogs pa gong ma gnyis las
NK063(gu)001:4077: mi gsal kyang shugs la ngag don gyis bzhi char
NK063(gu)001:4079: byin gyis brlabs ni gong gi yig 'bru'i tshul las
NK063(gu)001:4080: rgyu gcig pa chos kyi dbyings su rtogs pa byung
NK063(gu)001:4081: zhing / de ltar snang ldog yig 'bru'i tshul dang /
NK063(gu)001:4082: stong ldog rgyu gcig pa gnyis dngos su rtogs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:4083: byin rlabs las dbyer med du rtogs pa shugs la
NK063(gu)001:4084: byung ba'i phyir byin gyis brlabs kyis rtogs pa zhes
NK063(gu)001:4085: bya'o // mngon sum pa ni thams cad kyi rang bzhin mtshan nyid yin pa la /
NK063(gu)001:4086: de rtogs kyi blo rang rig mngon sum gyis rtogs
NK063(gu)001:4087: pas mtshan nyid kyi don la dbang sgyur ba ni
NK063(gu)001:4088: rtags kyi rjes su dpag nas bsgrub bya rtogs pa
NK063(gu)001:4089: lta bu ma yin pa'i phyir mngon sum pa'i rtogs
NK063(gu)001:4090: pa zhes bya'o // dag pa'i gtan tshigs ni gzhal
NK063(gu)001:4091: bya gong dang 'dra ste bdag phung po dang gzhan
NK063(gu)001:4092: 'byung ba dang rtog pa'i rgyun rnam shes rnams chos
NK063(gu)001:4093: pa zhes bya'o // can / de dag rigs kyi
NK063(gu)001:4094: yab lnga dang yum lnga dang ye shes lngar rnam
NK063(gu)001:4096: de ltar brtags na de dag tu snang ba'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:4097: dper na zad par gyi skye mched goms pa lta
NK063(gu)001:4099: me yi skye mched der bsgoms na //
NK063(gu)001:4100: me de nyid du snang bar 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:4102: rtags 'di ni 'di'i lam grol lam bskyed rim gyi sgrub byed du yang 'gyur zhing /
NK063(gu)001:4103: phung po la sogs rigs kyi yab lnga la sogs
NK063(gu)001:4104: su btags shing bsgoms pas de dag tu dag pa
NK063(gu)001:4105: ni dag pa'i gtan tshigs kyi bsgrub bya yin no
NK063(gu)001:4106: // yang gtan tshigs 'di dag gi skabs su kha cig /
NK063(gu)001:4107: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan med de //
NK063(gu)001:4109: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan rnams ni //
NK063(gu)001:4111: bdag dang gzhan dang rtog pa'i rgyun //
NK063(gu)001:4112: zhes pa gzhal bya de rnams gsum du zlos so zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:4114: dang po ni bden pa'i rtags kyi gzhal byar smos shing /
NK063(gu)001:4115: gnyis pa ni rtogs pa'i gzhal bya smos la /
NK063(gu)001:4116: tha ma ni dag pa'i gzhal byar smos pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4117: 'o na gzhal bya de dag gi 'jal byed gtan
NK063(gu)001:4118: tshigs gsum du mtshon pa la dgos pa zhig yod
NK063(gu)001:4119: dam med / med na zlos par 'gyur la /
NK063(gu)001:4120: yod na gang yin zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:4121: dgos pa yod pas zlos par mi 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:4122: 'jal byed gtan tshigs la 'di'i lugs kyis thun mong dang thun min gnyis su nges pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4123: de yang dang po ni bden pa'i gtan tshigs te sgra mthun don spags yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:4124: phyi ma ni rtogs pa dang dag pa'i gtan tshigs te /
NK063(gu)001:4125: tshad ma bka' gzhung yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4126: 'o na thun min gyi dag rtogs gnyis po zlos so zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:4128: rtogs pas ni gzhal bya bdag gzhan gsum po log
NK063(gu)001:4129: rtog tsam du yang ma grub par gtan la 'bebs
NK063(gu)001:4130: shing / dag pas ni de gsum ye shes kyi
NK063(gu)001:4131: dkyil 'khor du rnam par dag par gtan la 'bebs
NK063(gu)001:4132: pa'i phyir gtan tshigs gnyis zlos pa ma yin no
NK063(gu)001:4133: shing / // yang 'dir 'di ltar bsam par bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:4134: gzhal bya sngar gyi zhen dang /
NK063(gu)001:4135: 'jal byed gtan tshigs 'di dag 'jal ba po'i blo
NK063(gu)001:4136: la ltos te gcig pa yin nam tha dad pa
NK063(gu)001:4137: yin / dang po ltar na gzhal bya 'jal byed du mi rung zhing /
NK063(gu)001:4138: gnyis pa ltar na shes rgyud gnyis 'chang du 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:4139: gzhal bya 'jal byed blo rdzas su gcig pas shes rgyud gnyis 'chang du mi 'gyur zhing /
NK063(gu)001:4140: rdzas rgyun snga ma la phyi mas 'jal bas skyon dang po yang med do //
NK063(gu)001:4141: gsum pa de ltar gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha' ni /
NK063(gu)001:4142: gzhung 'og na gzhal bya log rtog gsum po de dag gi rang bzhin ni /
NK063(gu)001:4143: ma rtogs te 'khor bar snang zhing zhen pa'i dus
NK063(gu)001:4144: na de'i rang bzhin chos nyid yin pa las nyams
NK063(gu)001:4145: pa med de / gong gi gtan tshigs dag gis
NK063(gu)001:4146: gzhal bas de ltar gtan la phebs pa'i dus na
NK063(gu)001:4147: chos nyid de las gzhan du 'dzin pa'i 'khrul pa
NK063(gu)001:4149: dper na rgyal bu rkang 'khyams blon po thabs la mkhas pas rgyal sar phyung ba bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:4151: de ltar ston pa'i grub mtha' ni gud na med
NK063(gu)001:4152: pa 'bras bu rdo rje'i theg pa gzhan las mchog
NK063(gu)001:4153: tu gyur pa 'di ma yin pa gzhan gang gis
NK063(gu)001:4154: kyang smra bar nus pa ma yin no zhes pa'i
NK063(gu)001:4155: don yin no // mya ngan las 'das pa la
NK063(gu)001:4156: theg pa'i khyad par ni gzhung brtag cing de rgyas
NK063(gu)001:4157: par gong gi mdzad pa'i skabs su bstan to //
NK063(gu)001:4158: rang bzhin gyi snang ba ni shes bya'i gnas lugs yang dag pa'i don te /
NK063(gu)001:4159: shes byed de nyid rtogs par nus pas te /
NK063(gu)001:4160: gang zhe na so sor rtog pa'i shes rab de
NK063(gu)001:4161: kho na nyid la dpyod pa'i blos rab tu brtags
NK063(gu)001:4162: na chos thams cad rang bzhin cir yang grub pa
NK063(gu)001:4163: med pa'i phyir / de las sgyu ma ltar rol pa cir yang snang la /
NK063(gu)001:4164: yang cir yang snang ba'i phyir rang bzhin cir yang grub pa med do //
NK063(gu)001:4165: de gnyis gcig gi rgyu mtshan gcig yin te gnyis su med pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:4166: sangs rgyas dang chos la 'byung 'jig med pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:4167: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku yang yang dag par na mya ngan las yongs su mi 'da' ste /
NK063(gu)001:4168: ji skad du 'das pa'i mdo las kyang /
NK063(gu)001:4170: dper na 'dzam bu'i gling du nyi ma nub pa
NK063(gu)001:4171: ni ri bos bsgribs nas sems can gyis mi mthong
NK063(gu)001:4172: ba ste / nyi ma'i rang bzhin yang dag par nub pa med do //
NK063(gu)001:4173: sems can gyis ma mthong ba'i phyir nub pa'i 'du shes bskyed do //
NK063(gu)001:4174: de bzhin du nyan thos kyi nye gnas rnams kyang
NK063(gu)001:4175: nyon mongs pa'i ri bos bsgribs pas nga'i sku mi
NK063(gu)001:4176: mthong ste / de ltar ma mthong ba'i phyir de
NK063(gu)001:4177: pa mya ngan 'das song ba'i 'du shes bskyed do
NK063(gu)001:4178: mthong ste / // nga ni yang dag par ma 'das so zhes gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:4180: rgyud kyi che ba ni 'di brjod bya bslab pa
NK063(gu)001:4181: gsum ston pa'i rjod byed sde snod gsum gyi 'byung
NK063(gu)001:4182: gnas yin te / de'i nges pa sgrub byed ni
NK063(gu)001:4183: 'dul ba zhes pa lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab
NK063(gu)001:4186: ltung dang 'byung dang ldang ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:4187: nges par 'byung dang gang zag dang //
NK063(gu)001:4188: bcas pa dang ni rab dbye dang //
NK063(gu)001:4189: rnam par nges phyir 'dul ba nyid //
NK063(gu)001:4191: mdo sde zhes pa lhag pa sems kyi bslab pa ston pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:4192: gnas rnams dang ni mtshan nyid dang //
NK063(gu)001:4193: chos don smos phyir mdo yi don //
NK063(gu)001:4195: chos mngon dang zhes pa shes rab kyi bslab pa ston pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:4196: mngon du phyir dang yang yang dang //
NK063(gu)001:4197: zil gnon rtogs pa mngon pa'i chos //
NK063(gu)001:4199: de ltar rgyu'i theg pa sde snod gsum dang /
NK063(gu)001:4201: dam tshig bsgrub dang grub pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:4202: zhes phyi rgyud sde gsum dang /
NK063(gu)001:4203: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK063(gu)001:4204: ces pa nang rgyud bskyed rdzogs gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:4205: de ltar lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten gyi phyogs
NK063(gu)001:4206: bcu dang dus bzhi rnams su rab tu grags pa'i
NK063(gu)001:4208: gsang ba'i snying po 'di'i byin rlabs las 'phros pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4209: de'i phyir 'di bstan pa'i 'byung gnas yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4211: yang kha cig le'u 'di'i stod nas lha dang mi'i theg pa dang zhes pa la sogs dang /
NK063(gu)001:4212: yang nyon mongs pa stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'i gnyen por zhes pa la sogs dang /
NK063(gu)001:4213: yang gzung ba dang 'dzin pa zhes pa la sogs gsum dang /
NK063(gu)001:4215: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK063(gu)001:4217: yang 'dul ba mdo sde zhes pa la sogs gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:4218: theg pa'i rnam grangs lan lngar byung bas zlos so zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:4220: stod nas gsum gyi dang po lam pa rim gyis
NK063(gu)001:4221: pa rnams lam stegs kyi theg pa thun mong gi
NK063(gu)001:4222: lam la 'jug pa'i don du gsungs te /
NK063(gu)001:4223: zhugs pa'i dgos ched kyang nges 'byung gi theg chung gsum gyis nyon mongs pa spong ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:4224: byang chub sems dpas sbyong zhing /
NK063(gu)001:4226: nang pa gnyis kyis dbang du byed cing /
NK063(gu)001:4227: a tis rang grol chen por ston pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:4228: de yang dang pos de dag mdor bstan cing /
NK063(gu)001:4229: phyi ma gnyis kyis rgyas par ston pas stod kyi gsum po ma zlos shing /
NK063(gu)001:4230: smad nas gnyis gsungs pa'i dang pos gong gi nges
NK063(gu)001:4231: 'byung gi theg pa las khyad par du mtshon pa'i
NK063(gu)001:4232: phyir yin la / gnyis pa ni 'di bstan pa
NK063(gu)001:4233: thams cad kyi gzhir mtshon pas 'di rtogs na bstan
NK063(gu)001:4234: pa thams cad gtan la phebs par 'gyur ba'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:4235: rgyud kyi che bar gsungs pas smad kyi gnyis kyang
NK063(gu)001:4236: phyir yin la / mi zlos so // yang na
NK063(gu)001:4237: lan lngar gsungs pa'i dang pos gsung gi mdzad pa
NK063(gu)001:4238: theg pa thams cad kyi mdor bstan yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4239: gnyis pa ni nyon mongs pa la dgongs nas dbye ba yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:4240: gsum pa gnyen po la dgongs nas bsdu ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4241: bzhi pa theg pa'i khyad par yin cing /
NK063(gu)001:4242: lnga pa ni rgyud kyi che ba yin pa'i phyir mi zlos par sems so //
NK063(gu)001:4243: gnyis pa gzhung bsdu ba la bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:4244: dang po ni sdud pa pos mtshams sbyar ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:4245: gnyis pa bsdu ba dngos ni brjod bya snang ba
NK063(gu)001:4246: bzhi po rjod byed rtags sbyor ba don gsum du
NK063(gu)001:4248: ji snyed 'khrul pa'i snang ba chos can gyi don du dang /
NK063(gu)001:4249: ji lta ba rang bzhin gyi snang ba gzhal bya'i don du dang /
NK063(gu)001:4250: de shes pa'i shes byed lam gyi snang ba gtan tshigs kyi don du dang /
NK063(gu)001:4251: bsgrub bya de pa'i snang ba grub mtha'i don du bsdu ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:4252: de yang a ho zhes pa ni 'khor 'das kyi
NK063(gu)001:4253: dngos po gnyis med du gtan la phab pa la
NK063(gu)001:4255: de las don dang po ni /
NK063(gu)001:4256: srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs bdag tu rtog las 'phros //
NK063(gu)001:4258: ma rig rtog pa'i gzung 'dzin gyis //
NK063(gu)001:4261: srid pa ni 'khor ba'i rang bzhin nyer dmigs dang bcas pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:4262: de'i rtsa ba ni bdag tu rtog pa kho na yin zhing /
