NK063(gu)001:4263: de las 'phros pa'i las dang nyon mongs pa la
NK063(gu)001:4264: sogs sdug bsngal sna tshogs bskyed pa ni 'khor ba'i
NK063(gu)001:4265: rgyu yin no // rgyud drug skye 'gag lus longs spyod dang //
NK063(gu)001:4269: de ni rgyud drug sems can gyi gnas na skye
NK063(gu)001:4270: ba dang 'gag pa ni 'chi ba la sogs 'jig
NK063(gu)001:4271: pa rnams dang / gzhan yang lus kyi na tsha dang /
NK063(gu)001:4272: longs spyod la'ang med pa btsal gyis mi rnyed pa
NK063(gu)001:4273: la sogs sdug bsngal brgyad dang bcas pa ni 'khor
NK063(gu)001:4274: ba'i ngo bo yin no zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:4275: gnas dang sdug bsngal zhes par /
NK063(gu)001:4276: mi mthun bde sdug myong bar 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:4278: de ni ris su bcad pas rigs drug so so'i
NK063(gu)001:4279: gnas dang skye rga na 'chi la sogs sdug bsngal
NK063(gu)001:4280: sna tshogs nyams su myong ba ni nyes pa yin
NK063(gu)001:4281: no zhes so // 'khrul 'khor la sogs pa //
NK063(gu)001:4285: de'i phyir rang gi chos nyid ma rig ste 'khrul
NK063(gu)001:4286: pa'i dbang gis phyi nang gi rten 'brel bcu gnyis
NK063(gu)001:4287: su rigs drug gi gnas gcig nas gcig tu bskyar
NK063(gu)001:4288: zhing 'khor ba ni tshul yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4289: de la sogs pa gzhan yang nyes pa ji snyed
NK063(gu)001:4290: pa rnams te de dag chos can gyi don no
NK063(gu)001:4291: // don gnyis pa log rtog nyid las zhes par /
NK063(gu)001:4292: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan rnams ni //
NK063(gu)001:4293: log par rtog pa zhes pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:4295: log rtog nyid la nyid spyod de //
NK063(gu)001:4298: log rtog rgyu 'bras rgyun nyid kyang //
NK063(gu)001:4301: bdag dang gzhan dang rtog pa'i rgyun //
NK063(gu)001:4303: de ni de bzhin nyid las gzhan log rtog bdag
NK063(gu)001:4304: gzhan gsum du 'dzin pa ni chos nyid ma rig
NK063(gu)001:4305: pa las byung ba'i phyir 'khrul pa yin no zhes
NK063(gu)001:4306: so // gzhan du ci yang med //
NK063(gu)001:4309: phra zhing zab pa'ang yod ma yin //
NK063(gu)001:4312: gzhan du g.yo ba ci yang med //
NK063(gu)001:4314: gzhi rtsa med dbyings skad cig ma //
NK063(gu)001:4315: rnam par dag pa'i dbyings nyid tshul //
NK063(gu)001:4317: de ni gong ltar 'khrul pa'i dus nyid na chos
NK063(gu)001:4318: nyid las gzhan du gyur cing de las g.yos pa
NK063(gu)001:4320: 'khrul pa dang mtshan nyid dus snga phyi med cing /
NK063(gu)001:4321: rang bzhin bzang ngan med la /
NK063(gu)001:4322: 'dug sa tha dad med pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:4323: ngo bo gcig tu gnas pa ni gzhal bya yin no zhes pa'i don no //
NK063(gu)001:4324: de gnyis char gyis gzhal bya chos can zhes sbyor ba'i don dang po yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4325: don gsum pa ni stong nyid ces par /
NK063(gu)001:4326: yang dag sgyu ma'i zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:4328: zhes pa'i bar rkang pa gsum mo //
NK063(gu)001:4329: de ni gong gi gzhal bya de thun mong bden
NK063(gu)001:4330: pa'i gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab na yod med
NK063(gu)001:4331: la sogs mtha' thams cad kyis stong pa'i stong nyid
NK063(gu)001:4332: du gnas pa yin no zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:4334: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK063(gu)001:4335: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK063(gu)001:4337: de ni gang zag dang chos kyi bdag tu rtogs pa lha mi dang nyan rang yin la /
NK063(gu)001:4338: de med par rtogs pa ni byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:4339: de ltar nges 'byung bzhi las khyad par du gyur
NK063(gu)001:4340: pa bla na med pa'i theg pa 'di yin no
NK063(gu)001:4341: zhes so // ye mkhyen rang rig thugs //
NK063(gu)001:4343: yang dag rtog pas rab brtags na //
NK063(gu)001:4344: rang bzhin med las cir yang 'grub //
NK063(gu)001:4346: de ni de ltar rdo rje'i theg pa 'dis 'bru bsgyur te 'og nas /
NK063(gu)001:4347: rang gi rang bzhin rig pa'i tshul gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:4348: ye nas yin pa'i don phyin ci ma log par
NK063(gu)001:4349: mkhyen pa ni rgyal ba'i thugs gnyis med kyi ye
NK063(gu)001:4351: de ni lam gtan tshigs kyis nges pa las byung ba yin no zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:4352: don tha ma la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:4353: bsgrub bya gzhan du 'dzin pa dag pa grub mtha'i ngo bo dngos dang /
NK063(gu)001:4354: de ltar grub pa'i 'bras bu don mdzad tshul lo //
NK063(gu)001:4355: dang po ni dmigs bya dmigs byed med par dran dbang sgyur //
NK063(gu)001:4358: gzhan na med de de nyid de ltar yin //
NK063(gu)001:4360: nyid la dbang sgyur nyid spyod phyir //
NK063(gu)001:4363: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med //
NK063(gu)001:4367: de nas dmigs par bya ba'i yul chos kyi dbyings
NK063(gu)001:4368: de dmigs byed gong gi gtan tshigs rnams kyis gtan
NK063(gu)001:4369: la phab pa de las gzhan na bsgrub bya med
NK063(gu)001:4370: par rtogs nas / de'i don ma brjed par dran
NK063(gu)001:4371: pa'i rjes su gnas pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis ji
NK063(gu)001:4372: ltar 'dod rgur dbang sgyur ba ni de pa'i snang
NK063(gu)001:4373: ba ste de ni bsgrub bya dngos so //
NK063(gu)001:4374: de'i phyir rang gi chos nyid las gzhan na bsgrub bya 'bras bu med de /
NK063(gu)001:4375: rang gi sems kyi rang bzhin de nyid ji ltar
NK063(gu)001:4376: gtan la phab pa de ltar 'bras bu rang snang
NK063(gu)001:4377: ba yin no // zhes pa ni grub mtha' dngos so //
NK063(gu)001:4378: gnyis pa ni ngo mtshar sku zhes par /
NK063(gu)001:4379: le'u'i klad nas de nas zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:4381: yang bltams pa dang zhes pa nas ston pa'i thub pa zhes pa'i bar dang /
NK063(gu)001:4383: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'da' //
NK063(gu)001:4384: zhes pa la sogs sh+lo ka gcig ste sku'i mdzad pa rnams so //
NK063(gu)001:4385: de ni gong ltar sems nyid rtogs pas chos thams
NK063(gu)001:4386: cad la dbang sgyur bas 'bras bu mngon du byas
NK063(gu)001:4387: pa ni ngo mtshar zhing de'i bye brag sku'i mdzad
NK063(gu)001:4388: pa ni brgyad dam bcu gnyis la sogs pas don
NK063(gu)001:4391: thams cad kyang 'di lta ste zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:4392: ston pa'i mthar thug go zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK063(gu)001:4393: de ni gsung gi mdzad pa chos kyi sgo brgyad khri bzhi stong logs su snang ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4396: dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:4397: mngon par shes pa chen po drug dang zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK063(gu)001:4398: de ni che ba'i yon tan rnams lhun gyis grub
NK063(gu)001:4399: cing mkhyen pa'i ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK063(gu)001:4400: dang ldan pa yin no zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:4402: stod nas las kyi dbang gis s+n+rel gzhi zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:4403: stong chen po re rer zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK063(gu)001:4404: de ni sprul sku'i zhing stong gsum la sogs ni
NK063(gu)001:4405: don mdzad pa'i yul lam zhing khams yin no zhes
NK063(gu)001:4407: kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:4408: phyogs bcur snang bar gyur to zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK063(gu)001:4409: de ni de ltar sku gsung thugs kyi mdzad pa
NK063(gu)001:4410: sna tshogs pa ni phrin las kyi khyad par ro
NK063(gu)001:4411: zhes bdag don grub pa dang gzhan don mdzad pa
NK063(gu)001:4412: ni bsgrub bya grub pa'i mtha'o //
NK063(gu)001:4413: gsang sngags mtshon pa dang bsdus pa'i yon tan gzhung brtag /
NK063(gu)001:4414: rgyud don rnam par nges pa las le'u gsum pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:4416: // le'u bzhi pa'i dang po yi ge 'byung ba'i tshul lam ni /
NK063(gu)001:4417: sgra'i bstan bcos las ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:4418: khog pa mgrin pa rkan dang lce //
NK063(gu)001:4419: sna dang spyi bo so dang mchu //
NK063(gu)001:4420: zhes bshad pa ltar dang po a ni lus spyi'i khong nas byung ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4422: a ni yig 'bru kun gyi mchog /
NK063(gu)001:4423: don chen yi ge dam pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:4424: khong nas 'byung ba skye ba med //
NK063(gu)001:4426: mdo chen po'i so bzhi pa las /
NK063(gu)001:4427: a ni rang bzhin yi ge ste //
NK063(gu)001:4428: khong nas kun khyab nam mkha' 'dra //
NK063(gu)001:4430: rdo rje bkod pa'i le'u gnyis pa las /
NK063(gu)001:4431: thugs kyi klong nas a byung ba //
NK063(gu)001:4433: yi ge gzhan rnams ni mdo chen po las /
NK063(gu)001:4434: dang po mgur gyi gzugs brnyan te //
NK063(gu)001:4435: gnyis pa ljags kyi gzugs brnyan yin //
NK063(gu)001:4436: gsum pa rtse mo las byung ba //
NK063(gu)001:4437: bzhi pa 'byung ba sgros las shar //
NK063(gu)001:4438: lnga pa gsung gi rgyun lam yin //
NK063(gu)001:4439: zhes pas sde tshan lngar gsungs so //
NK063(gu)001:4440: de dag rgyas par rdo rje bkod pa las /
NK063(gu)001:4441: dang po ka la sogs pa lnga //
NK063(gu)001:4442: mgur gyi gsang ba'i rang bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:4443: gnyis pa tsa la sogs pa lnga //
NK063(gu)001:4444: zla gam ljags kyi rang bzhin yin //
NK063(gu)001:4445: gsum pa ta la sogs pa bcu //
NK063(gu)001:4446: ljags kyi rtse mo'i rang bzhin yin //
NK063(gu)001:4447: bzhi pa pa la sogs pa lnga //
NK063(gu)001:4448: zhal gyi sgros las byung bar bshad //
NK063(gu)001:4449: lnga pa ya la sogs pa yi //
NK063(gu)001:4450: bcu tshan gnyis kyi yi ge dag /
NK063(gu)001:4451: sku las 'phros par rab tu bshad //
NK063(gu)001:4452: skyes bu chen po'i byin pa las //
NK063(gu)001:4453: 'khor ba gnon pa'i yi ge ya //
NK063(gu)001:4454: skyes bu chen po'i dgu skabs las //
NK063(gu)001:4455: gti mug sel ba'i yi ge wa //
NK063(gu)001:4456: skyes bu chen po'i sta zur las //
NK063(gu)001:4457: 'dod chags sreg pa'i yi ge ra //
NK063(gu)001:4458: skyes bu chen po'i dpung pa las //
NK063(gu)001:4459: rtogs pa 'joms pa'i yi ge la //
NK063(gu)001:4461: cho 'phrul bstan pa'i yi ge sha /
NK063(gu)001:4462: thugs kar 'khyil ba'i dpal be'u las //
NK063(gu)001:4463: mtshan ma dag pa'i yi ge sha //
NK063(gu)001:4464: sku yi khru tshad lte ba las //
NK063(gu)001:4467: sgrib pa sel ba'i yi ge ha //
NK063(gu)001:4468: gsang ba mkha' yi 'od zer las //
NK063(gu)001:4470: skyes bu chen po'i spyan gnyis las //
NK063(gu)001:4471: rang bzhin yi ge i gnyis shar //
NK063(gu)001:4472: skyes bu chen po'i snyan gnyis las //
NK063(gu)001:4473: rang bzhin yi ge u gnyis shar //
NK063(gu)001:4474: skyes bu chen po'i shangs gnyis las //
NK063(gu)001:4475: rang bzhin yi ge e gnyis shar //
NK063(gu)001:4476: skyes bu chen po'i tshems gnyis las //
NK063(gu)001:4477: rang bzhin yi ge o gnyis shar //
NK063(gu)001:4478: skyes bu chen po'i spyi gtsug las //
NK063(gu)001:4482: bcu tshan gnyis kyi yi ge dag /
NK063(gu)001:4483: ces pa ni spar khab nas yi ge bcu bdun
NK063(gu)001:4484: gyi steng du khyab byed kyi yi ge gsum bsnan
NK063(gu)001:4486: yi ge phyung ba'i mthu ni 'di dag phyung bas
NK063(gu)001:4487: zhes pa nas rnam pa drug tu g.yos so zhes
NK063(gu)001:4488: pa ni spyir sa g.yo ba la de bzhin gshegs
NK063(gu)001:4490: byang chub sems dpa'i mthu las dang /
NK063(gu)001:4491: gnod sbyin la sogs kyi gdug pas dang /
NK063(gu)001:4492: nya mo'i 'dres kyis g.yos ba las /
NK063(gu)001:4494: yi ge la sems sbyang ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:4495: rgyud 'brel ba bzhi ldan du byas nas mngon rtogs
NK063(gu)001:4496: las sdeb kyi dbang du rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin yin
NK063(gu)001:4497: no // lam gyi rim pa'i dbang du le'u gsum
NK063(gu)001:4498: par rgyu shes pa lta ba'i don gtan tshigs kyi
NK063(gu)001:4500: rkyen 'jug pa lam gyi rnal 'byor lnga las /
NK063(gu)001:4501: stong nyid le'u lnga pa ltar bsgoms nas /
NK063(gu)001:4502: phyag rgya gcig pa la phra rags gnyis las phra
NK063(gu)001:4503: mo yig 'bru la sems sbyangs ba ni 'di yin
NK063(gu)001:4505: thos bsam gyi shes rab la brten nas rgyud don shes byar gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:4506: sgom pa'i shes rab kyis rgyud don nyams su blang byar bstan pa gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:4507: dang po ni yi ge'i don bden pa bzhir shes
NK063(gu)001:4508: pa'i sgo nas chos thams cad ming tsam du rtogs
NK063(gu)001:4509: pa de yin te 'og tu 'chad do //
NK063(gu)001:4510: gnyis pa le'u 'di dang lnga pa'i don sdeb nas yi ge'i sgo nas sgyu 'phrul bsgrub pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:4512: ting nge 'dzin sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa ni chos bdun te lag le na ltar ro //
NK063(gu)001:4513: gnyis pa byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa ni
NK063(gu)001:4514: le'u gnyis pa ltar rang bzhin gzhi'i sems bskyed pa'o
NK063(gu)001:4515: // ting nge 'dzin rim pa dngos ni le'u lnga
NK063(gu)001:4516: pa ltar de bzhin nyid dang kun snang bsgoms nas
NK063(gu)001:4517: // / de brtan pa dang rgyu ting yi ge
NK063(gu)001:4518: la sems sbyangs pa yin la de la ngag don
NK063(gu)001:4519: // / lnga ste / rnam pa bsgom zhing spro bsdu bya ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:4520: skyon bcos pas nyams ji ltar gsal ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:4521: yi ge'i sems mngon par 'grub pa'i tshad dang /
NK063(gu)001:4522: yi ge snang byed mthar phyin nas tshogs bsgrub pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:4523: de bsgrubs pas 'bras bu grub pa'i tshul lo //
NK063(gu)001:4524: dang po ni a zhes pa snang stong dbyer med kyi sems nyid a'i rnam par gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:4525: de chos ji lta bu dang ldan na rab tu
NK063(gu)001:4526: brtan gyur zhes pa mi g.yo ba mi 'gyur ba
NK063(gu)001:4527: mngon par mi 'gyur ba cir yang bsgyur du rung
NK063(gu)001:4528: ba'i rang bzhin te brtan pa'i chos bzhi dang /
NK063(gu)001:4530: zhes pa kha dog yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4531: de yang gsal le ba sang nge ba lhag ge ba lhang nge ba ste gsal ba'i bzhi'o //
NK063(gu)001:4533: gsal ba ni byang chub kyi sems kyi phyir zhes
NK063(gu)001:4534: pas de la dri mas ma gos par mtshon pa'o
NK063(gu)001:4535: // rnam pa de'ang blo che chung gi dbang gis
NK063(gu)001:4536: cig car bsgom pa dang thun du bcad cing rim
NK063(gu)001:4538: de gang yin yang rung ste /
NK063(gu)001:4539: de ltar gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad dang ldan pa
NK063(gu)001:4540: la blo brtan pa dang spro bsdu bya ba ni
NK063(gu)001:4541: / spyod yul gyi zhen pa sbyang ba'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:4542: shin tu phra ba'i a rnams spro //
NK063(gu)001:4543: zhes pa de las a phra mo grangs med pa phyogs bcur spros pas /
NK063(gu)001:4544: phyogs bcu thams cad a yis gang zhing 'bru bsgyur te gsal bar gyur nas /
NK063(gu)001:4545: de dag bsdus kyang phyogs bcu'i a 'grib pa med la /
NK063(gu)001:4546: dang po spros pa'i tshe na phyogs bcu'i a ma
NK063(gu)001:4547: 'phel zhing gzhi'i a 'grib pa med de gnyis su
NK063(gu)001:4549: 'o na spros shing bsdus pa dang 'gal te /
NK063(gu)001:4550: spros pas 'phel la bsdus pa nyid kyis 'grib pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:4552: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyi ro //
NK063(gu)001:4553: de'i don ni spros pa'i tshe gzhi ma'i a ma
NK063(gu)001:4554: nyams shing phyogs bcu'i ar snang ba'i go mi 'gog
NK063(gu)001:4556: bsdus pa'i tshe phyogs bcu a yis gang ba rnams
NK063(gu)001:4557: a nyid du gcig cing de las ma g.yos par
NK063(gu)001:4559: dper na me long nang du gzugs mang bas de mi 'phel zhing /
NK063(gu)001:4560: de nyung bas de mi 'grib pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:4561: yang na lam pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi don yang 'phel 'grib med de /
NK063(gu)001:4562: grwa pa mang nyung dang gzugs che chung thams cad sems kyi ngo bor gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4563: yang na don la dgongs par yang sems te /
NK063(gu)001:4564: 'di ltar a ni mtshan nyid skye med mtshon byed kyi yi ge yin la /
NK063(gu)001:4565: mtshan nyid ni shes bya'i khyab byed du yod pa'i phyir spros zhes bya la /
NK063(gu)001:4566: shes bya thams cad kyang mtshan nyid las tha mi dad de /
NK063(gu)001:4567: de'i ngo bor gcig pa'i phyir bsdus pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:4568: des na mtshan nyid skye med la spros pas 'phel
NK063(gu)001:4569: ba dang bsdus pas 'grib pa gnyis dang bral ba'i
NK063(gu)001:4570: phyir ro // gnyis pa ni de ltar bsgoms pas thun mong gi skyon brjed pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:4573: khyad par gyi skyon ni lam rim las /
NK063(gu)001:4574: yi ge nas bzung rdzogs bar du //
NK063(gu)001:4575: khyad par rab rib mag mog grib //
NK063(gu)001:4576: gang tshad dmigs la tshad dang tshul //
NK063(gu)001:4577: grangs dang cha lugs mdog dbyibs dang /
NK063(gu)001:4578: kha dog 'ba' zhig rim par nus //
NK063(gu)001:4580: tshad 'gyur ba ni che ba las chung bar dang /
NK063(gu)001:4581: tshul ni skye ba las 'grib pa'i tshul dang /
NK063(gu)001:4582: grangs ni mang po las nyung ngu dang /
NK063(gu)001:4583: cha lugs ni sku'i skabs las 'dir mi 'byung ste zhi ba las khro bor dang /
NK063(gu)001:4584: dbyibs ka las kha lta bur dang /
NK063(gu)001:4585: mdog ni dkar po las sngon po la sogs dang /
NK063(gu)001:4586: kha dog 'ba' zhig las mi snang ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:4587: rim par nub pa ni stod gsal tshe smad mi gsal ba la sogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:4589: rim par nub na rangs pa ni mi gsal yang gang gsal la gtad /
NK063(gu)001:4590: kha dog 'ba' zhig dbyibs dang bsre /
NK063(gu)001:4591: gzhan drug po la gang bsgom bya de che zhing brtan par ro //
NK063(gu)001:4592: de ltar skyon bcos pas nyams ni lngar gsal te /
NK063(gu)001:4593: bsgom bya a lta bu de yang smig rgyu ltar gya gyu'i rnam par gsal ba g.yo ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:4594: du ba ltar res 'ga' gsal zhing res 'ga' mi gsal ba ni thob pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:4595: me khyer ltar gang sgom gcig pu kho nar gsal ba ni goms pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:4596: mar me gzhan sel nus pa ltar spros shing bsdus kyang mi 'gag pa ni brtan pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:4597: nyi ma ltar bskyed du byar med pa ni mthar phyin pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:4598: brtan pa'i tshad bzhi ni de'i tshe ldan pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4599: de yang gong ltar spros kyang dngos gzhi mi 'gag
NK063(gu)001:4600: pa'i phyir ci yang bsgyur du btub pa ste rab
NK063(gu)001:4602: gsum pa tshad ni de las zhes +aa li dbyangs
NK063(gu)001:4603: dang k+aa li sgra'i yi ge rnams 'dus pa ming
NK063(gu)001:4604: gi tshogs so // yi ge de dag kyang kha
NK063(gu)001:4605: dog gsal zhing 'od 'bar ba dang bcas pa'i yi
NK063(gu)001:4606: ge kun la'ang spro zhing bsdu ba gong du a
NK063(gu)001:4607: la ji ltar byas pa de bzhin du bya ba
NK063(gu)001:4608: gi tshogs so // yin no // de ltar re
NK063(gu)001:4609: re zhing sems sbyangs pas brtan pa thob pa ni
NK063(gu)001:4610: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po rig pa gcig
NK063(gu)001:4611: la gsal ba'i dus na yi ge mngon par grub
NK063(gu)001:4612: gi tshogs so // yin no // pa yin no
NK063(gu)001:4613: // bzhi pa tshogs sgrub pa ni dgu pa ltar
NK063(gu)001:4614: yi ge lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs
NK063(gu)001:4615: gi tshogs so // yin no // pa yin no
NK063(gu)001:4616: // nas / 'jug spyod bco lnga dang ldan pa'i
NK063(gu)001:4617: sgo nas bsgrub pa ni le'u bcu gcig pa ltar
NK063(gu)001:4618: gi tshogs so // yin no // pa yin no
NK063(gu)001:4619: // nas / ro // tha ma 'bras bu ni
NK063(gu)001:4620: 'di ni zhes gong ma la snyeg pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:4621: yi ge'i sgo nas mtshon bya bsgrub pa 'di ye shes kyi rgyu yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4622: rdo rje zhes pa sems dang yi ge rang bzhin tha dad med pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:4623: dngos grub kyi zhes pa lnga pa ltar bsgrub bya thun mong dang mchog gnyis 'grub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:4624: brtan 'byung zhes pa gong gi bsgrub bya thob pa las mi nyams pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4625: de'i thob tshul yang gnas skabs su rig 'dzin las
NK063(gu)001:4626: brgyud nas mthar thug tu sku lnga la sbyor ba'i
NK063(gu)001:4627: phyir ye shes thob pa'i rgyu yi ge'i snang byed
NK063(gu)001:4628: la goms pa de yin no zhes pa'i don no
NK063(gu)001:4629: // de yang sa myug ltar bskyed bya skyed byed dang /
NK063(gu)001:4630: me long dang byad ltar rnam pa gzhag 'jog ni min te /
NK063(gu)001:4631: byas pa dang mi rtag pa ltar ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu 'bras yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4632: de ltar yi ge'i sgo nas bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bur
NK063(gu)001:4633: bstan pa'i phyir sems nyid yi ger sangs rgyas par
NK063(gu)001:4634: ston pa ni gong gi rgyud don shes byar gtan
NK063(gu)001:4636: de las dang po bden pa dbyer med pa'i rang
NK063(gu)001:4637: bzhin chos skur sangs rgyas pa ste a ni yod
NK063(gu)001:4638: med la sogs mtha' thams cad kyis stong pa don
NK063(gu)001:4640: de dag gis mi stong pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:4641: de gnyis kyang ngo bo gcig gi steng na tha
NK063(gu)001:4642: dad med pa ni dbu ma ste bden pa dbyer
NK063(gu)001:4643: med dang / dbyer med kyang ltos sa gong ma
NK063(gu)001:4644: gnyis la ltos pa tsam ste dbyer med nyid ma
NK063(gu)001:4645: grub pa'i phyir dbu ma'ang dmigs su yod ma yin
NK063(gu)001:4646: med dang / no // des na spyod yul dang
NK063(gu)001:4647: bral ba ste dper na chu phar 'gram med na
NK063(gu)001:4649: de ltar bden pa bzhir kun khyab gsum gyi bsgrub par bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:4651: lung dang rig pa man ngag gi //
NK063(gu)001:4652: tshad ma dag gis gang gzhal ba //
NK063(gu)001:4653: shes bya khong du chud par 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:4655: de yang bden pa dang po bsgrub pa ni sems
NK063(gu)001:4656: dang sems snang ba 'di dag gi rang bzhin chos
NK063(gu)001:4657: can / don dam gyi bden pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4658: yin lugs nas mtha' dang bral ba yin pa'i phyir nam mkha' bzhin zhes pa'i rtags kyis bsgrub bo //
NK063(gu)001:4659: de ltar yin par yang 'di'i dgu pa las /
NK063(gu)001:4660: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK063(gu)001:4663: don dam skye ba med par mnyam pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:4665: man ngag ni lam rim las /
NK063(gu)001:4666: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med par //
NK063(gu)001:4667: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK063(gu)001:4669: bden pa gnyis pa ni chos can /
NK063(gu)001:4670: kun rdzob kyi bden pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4671: snang lugs nas cir yang ma 'gags pa'i phyir gzugs brnyan bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:4673: med pa nyid na sna tshogs snang ba zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:4674: kun rdzob sgyu mar mnyam pa zhes bya ba'i dam tshig ni zhes pa la sogs so //
NK063(gu)001:4675: man ngag kyang de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:4676: kun rdzob chu zla ltar yin pas //
NK063(gu)001:4679: gsum pa ni gong gi bden gnyis chos can /
NK063(gu)001:4681: kun rdzob tu snang ba'i tshe don dam las ma
NK063(gu)001:4682: g.yos shing don dam nges pa'i tshe kun rdzob ma
NK063(gu)001:4683: spangs pa'i phyir dper na byas pa dang mi rtag
NK063(gu)001:4684: pa bzhin no // de ltar yang rgyas pa las /
NK063(gu)001:4685: bden pa dbyer med pa zhes mnyam pa'i dam tshig ni zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:4687: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med de //
NK063(gu)001:4690: man ngag ni de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:4691: snang la rang bzhin med pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:4692: sems nyid d+harma k+aa yar gnas //
NK063(gu)001:4696: spyod yul dang bral ba yin te //
NK063(gu)001:4697: blo'i yul du bya bar ma dmigs pa'i phyir chos kyi dbyings bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:4698: rtags de yin par yang rdo rje gcod pa las /
NK063(gu)001:4699: chos nyid shes bya ma yin te //
NK063(gu)001:4700: de ni shes par nus ma yin //
NK063(gu)001:4702: de ltar yang lung ni 'di nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:4703: dbu ma'ang dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK063(gu)001:4706: snang dang mi snang la sogs pa //
NK063(gu)001:4707: gnyis su rtogs pa thams cad mtha' //
NK063(gu)001:4708: kun mkhyen rnams ni dbus la'ang min //
NK063(gu)001:4710: de ltar gtan la phab pas chos thams cad ming
NK063(gu)001:4711: du btags pa tsam las ngo bor ma grub par
NK063(gu)001:4712: rtogs pa ni chos skur sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:4713: de'i phyir skye med nyid las skye ba'i cho 'phrul du snang ba yi ge kun dang /
NK063(gu)001:4714: mtshon byed yi ge de'i rgyun ni phreng ba ltar
NK063(gu)001:4715: bar ma chad par snang ba yang chos sku nyid
NK063(gu)001:4716: las ma g.yos par gnas te /
NK063(gu)001:4717: yi ge nyid ngo bos stongs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4718: gnyis pa ni yi ge bsdus nas chos thams cad
NK063(gu)001:4719: la dbang sgyur zhing spyod pa ni longs sku ste
NK063(gu)001:4720: / gong gi chos sku mtshon byed a nyid kyis
NK063(gu)001:4721: go phye bas sna tshogs par snang ba'i yi ge
NK063(gu)001:4722: / gang zhe na / ka la sogs pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:4723: 'dir kha cig bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su grangs nges par ma grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:4724: rgya gar gyi yi ge la lnga bcu dang bod
NK063(gu)001:4725: kyi yi ge la sum cu yin pa'i phyir zhe
NK063(gu)001:4726: na / spyir de ltar yin mod kyang skabs 'dir bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su grangs nges te /
NK063(gu)001:4727: bskyed bya rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su nges
NK063(gu)001:4728: la de dag gi skyed byed sa bon yin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:4730: ji skad du rgyal ba'i yum las kyang /
NK063(gu)001:4731: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la mkhas par bya'o
NK063(gu)001:4732: zhes gsungs pa yang 'di'i shes byed du 'gyur ba'i
NK063(gu)001:4733: phyir ro // yi ge de dag kyang a'i sgra
NK063(gu)001:4734: yis ming gi yi ge thams cad bsdus shing des
NK063(gu)001:4735: chos thams cad bsdus pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:4736: gzhan yang yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rgyal ba
NK063(gu)001:4737: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su sangs rgyas pa'i phyir yi
NK063(gu)001:4738: ges bsdus pa'i chos thams cad kyang mngon par rdzogs
NK063(gu)001:4739: par sangs rgyas pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4740: des na chos thams cad la dbang bsgyur ba'i rgyal por nges te /
NK063(gu)001:4741: yi ge de sems nyid du nges pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4742: gsum pa yi ge nyid dbyibs dang kha dog sogs
NK063(gu)001:4743: su snang bas don mdzad pa sprul pa'i sku yin
NK063(gu)001:4744: pa ni sku gsung thugs gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:4745: e ma zhes che ba dang ngo mtshar zhes byed las dang ya mtshan gyi zhes rang bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:4746: de dag gsum du med bzhin snang bas 'phrul chen te yi ge'o //
NK063(gu)001:4747: de'i rnam grangs gong gi bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi
NK063(gu)001:4748: steng du khyab byed kyi yi ge gsum bsnan pas
NK063(gu)001:4750: de ltar yi ge 'dus pas ming byung la ming
NK063(gu)001:4751: 'dus pa las tshig rnams byung zhing des chos ma
NK063(gu)001:4752: lus pa'i don 'dzin cing brten pa'i gnas yin te
NK063(gu)001:4753: / 'bru bsgyur te yi ges rjod byed sna tshogs
NK063(gu)001:4754: pa'i ming du smra zhing brjod bya'i don chen po
NK063(gu)001:4755: ston par nus pa'i phyir gsungs yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4756: de ltar snang dus nyid na yi ge nyid bden pa'i dngos por med de /
NK063(gu)001:4757: yi ge'i rang bzhin sems nyid yin la /
NK063(gu)001:4758: sems la gang zag dang chos kyi bdag gnyis med de stong pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:4759: de ltar snang stong ngam yod med la sogs mtha'
NK063(gu)001:4760: thams cad dang bral te cir yang mi dmigs pa
NK063(gu)001:4761: don dam pa'i bden pa ni thugs yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4762: kyang zhes pa de ltar mtha' gang du yang ma grub cing kun rdzob tsam du /
NK063(gu)001:4763: ji skad du mdo chen po las /
NK063(gu)001:4764: a yi ge sgra 'byin pa lta bu la sogs dbyibs sna tshogs dang /
NK063(gu)001:4765: rang bzhin dang rigs kyi kha dog rnams su shar bas /
NK063(gu)001:4766: gong ltar ming dang tshig dang yi ge'i tshogs su
NK063(gu)001:4767: snang ba rnams kyis ma 'gags pa'i rol pa lha
NK063(gu)001:4768: dang dkyil 'khor la sogs cir yang 'phrul zhing gdul
NK063(gu)001:4769: bya'i ngo la ston pa sku yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4770: de ltar sangs rgyas pa de dag gi mtshon byed ni rgyal ba nyag gcig gi ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4771: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa ma lus
NK063(gu)001:4772: pa'i bdag nyid kyi ye shes sems dpa'i sku gsung
NK063(gu)001:4773: thugs kyi mtshon byed yi ge yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4774: de'i phyir ye shes sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu
NK063(gu)001:4775: rtsa gnyis bskyed pa'i sa bon yi ge bzhi bcu
NK063(gu)001:4776: rtsa gnyis te de ni khyab bya yin la /
NK063(gu)001:4777: de dag gis sku gsung thugs mtshon pa ni khyab byed kyi yi ge gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:4778: de ltar bzhi bcu rtsa lnga nyid do //
NK063(gu)001:4779: de dag yi ge'i 'go ber ka ris nas tha ma k+sha yan chad la rdzogs zhes pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:4780: de la kha cig k+sha'i 'og na thub pa'i yi
NK063(gu)001:4781: ge rnams yod pa'i phyir rdzogs par mi 'gyur zhe
NK063(gu)001:4782: na / a la gi gus ir 'gyur pa la sogs yan lag gi yi ge yin la /
NK063(gu)001:4783: de dag lus kyi yi ge a nyid la rdzogs pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4785: tshig cung zad bsgyur te 'og nas yi ger snang
NK063(gu)001:4786: ba de bden pa'i dngos por yod pa ma yin
NK063(gu)001:4787: te / gong nas yi ge'i rang bzhin sems kyi
NK063(gu)001:4788: cho 'phrul tsam yin pa'i phyir snang stong gnyis su
NK063(gu)001:4791: de ltar mtshan nyid mtha' gang du yang dmigs su
NK063(gu)001:4792: med pa de nyid rtogs shing mngon du byas pas
NK063(gu)001:4793: 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan sna tshogs pa'i rang
NK063(gu)001:4794: bzhin te / de gang zhe na sku gsung thugs
NK063(gu)001:4795: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo chen por snang
NK063(gu)001:4796: ba yang theg pa 'og ma ltar rgyu rkyen las
NK063(gu)001:4797: byung ba ma yin pa'i phyir 'bru bsgyur te ngo
NK063(gu)001:4798: bzhin te / mtshar zhes pa'o // gong du de
NK063(gu)001:4799: ltar sku gsung thugs kyi mdzad pa bsam gyis mi
NK063(gu)001:4800: khyab pas bdag gzhan gyi don grub pas ya mtshan
NK063(gu)001:4801: bzhin te / mtshar zhes pa'o // zhes bya'o // de dag med bzhin snang ba'i 'phrul chen la /
NK063(gu)001:4802: de yi ge'i sgo nas grub pas rab tu 'gug pa zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:4804: rtogs bya chos kyi dbyings la blo'i dbang po dbyings
NK063(gu)001:4805: rtogs byed so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis chos
NK063(gu)001:4806: kyi dbyings rtogs pa la bris pa zhes bya ste
NK063(gu)001:4807: / rtogs bya rtogs pa de'i phyir yi ge zhes ni dbyings rtogs pa la brjod par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:4808: khyab byed kyi yi ge gsum ni /
NK063(gu)001:4809: mtshon byed yi ge gsum las gang /
NK063(gu)001:4810: des mtshon pa dag bya'i rtog pa sgo gsum las gang /
NK063(gu)001:4811: de dag byed kyi lam thabs shes dbyer med gsum las gang /
NK063(gu)001:4812: des dag pa rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs las gang zhes bzhi sbrag tu sbyar ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:4813: de yang yi ge rnams kyi mgo ni zhes pa ber ka ris yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4814: ji skad du dpal sbyin gyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK063(gu)001:4815: 'go ni thog mar mtshon pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:4816: dang la gzugs su gang gsal ba //
NK063(gu)001:4817: de ni yi ge'i 'go yin phyir //
NK063(gu)001:4818: ber ka ris la 'go zhes bya //
NK063(gu)001:4821: yi ge sbrul lta bus thams cad kyi 'go 'dren pa'i phyir zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:4822: ber ka ris kyis 'go drangs nas yi ge thams cad 'jug pas ma nor ba'i lam zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:4823: don gyi dbang du ber ka ris kyis dag bya yid yin la /
NK063(gu)001:4824: de dag byed thabs shes rab dbyer med kyis dag
NK063(gu)001:4825: pa rgyal ba'i thugs gnyis med kyi ye shes mtshon
NK063(gu)001:4826: pa'o // tig ni zhes tshig yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4827: ming tig tu gdags pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:4829: tig ni shes rab ming du smra //
NK063(gu)001:4831: de ni dpal sbyin gyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK063(gu)001:4832: yi ge'i dgos pa kun bsdus nas //
NK063(gu)001:4833: rtseg gis sde yi don mtshon te //
NK063(gu)001:4834: shes par bya ba'i rab chen gyis //
NK063(gu)001:4835: don du rtseg gis gsal bar byed //
NK063(gu)001:4837: rgyal po drag shul can gyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK063(gu)001:4838: tig ni tsheg tu sgrub pa ste //
NK063(gu)001:4839: yi ge sdud cing ming du smra //
NK063(gu)001:4840: don gyi snying po sde ru slong //
NK063(gu)001:4841: de phyir tsheg ni tig ces bya //
NK063(gu)001:4844: sdud pa'i phyir ni rtseg ni tig /
NK063(gu)001:4845: 'thor ba bsdus nas ming du smra //
NK063(gu)001:4847: yi ge rnams bsdus nas don gsal bar ston pa'i phyir shes rab ming du smra zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:4848: don gyis dbang du rtseg gis dag bya ngag yin cing /
NK063(gu)001:4849: de dag byed shes rab kyi lam gyis dag pa
NK063(gu)001:4850: rgyal ba'i gsung du ma 'gags pas chos ston par
NK063(gu)001:4851: mtshon pa'o // shad ni zhes pa mdo chen po las /
NK063(gu)001:4852: dbyug pa ni 'phang thung lta bu'o zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:4854: ces pa des tshigs su bcad nas sh+lo kar sdeb pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:4856: gcod pa mtshon pa la ni ming shad ces bla dwags su btags so zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:4857: don gyi dbang du shad kyi dag bya lus kyi rtog pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4858: de dag byed thabs kyi lam gyis dag pa rgyal
NK063(gu)001:4859: ba'i skur ma 'gags pas don mdzad par mtshon pa'o
NK063(gu)001:4860: // 'dir bka'i don la rmongs shing log rtog gi gdon gyis barlamasa pa 'ga' zhig /
NK063(gu)001:4861: khyab byed kyi yi ge gsum po 'di rgya gar nas bsgyur ba ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4862: 'di dag rgya gar gyi yi ge la med pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:4863: bka' yongs su grags pa rgyan dam pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:4864: rgyal po gzugs can snying po dang /
NK063(gu)001:4865: dpal sbyin gyis zhus pa'i mdo rnams kyang rgya gar nas bsgyur ba ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:4866: de dag nas khyab byed gsum bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4867: rtags de gong gi lung gis grub la /
NK063(gu)001:4868: khyab pa med na 'dir yang mtshungs shing /
NK063(gu)001:4870: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi don bshad pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:4871: mngon rtogs las sdebs kyi dbang du le'u lnga pa
NK063(gu)001:4872: ltar thabs gsum las gzhi'i thabs rten gzhal yas khang
NK063(gu)001:4874: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i thabs brten pa lha bskyed
NK063(gu)001:4875: pa la cho ga gsum las 'di gsung yig 'bru'i
NK063(gu)001:4877: de yang yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po 'di
NK063(gu)001:4878: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi sa bon du btu
NK063(gu)001:4879: bar bya ste / ji skad du rgya mtsho las /
NK063(gu)001:4880: sa dang nam mkha' spyan rdo rje //
NK063(gu)001:4881: stobs chen lnga ni dang po lnga //
NK063(gu)001:4882: gnyis pa lnga po rim bzhin du //
NK063(gu)001:4883: sgeg mo phreng dang dbyangs dang gar //
NK063(gu)001:4884: ya m+aan+ta krita nyid du bshad //
NK063(gu)001:4885: lnga pa gsum ni rim pa bzhin //
NK063(gu)001:4886: snang mdzad rdo rje rin chen dang //
NK063(gu)001:4887: dpag med don grub nyid du bshad //
NK063(gu)001:4888: bzhi pa lnga po rim bzhin du //
NK063(gu)001:4889: nam mkha' spyan dang na bza' dkar //
NK063(gu)001:4890: m+aa ma k+ai dang sgron mar bshad //
NK063(gu)001:4891: lnga pa lnga ni rim bzhin du //
NK063(gu)001:4892: byams dang sgrib sel kun bzang dpal //
NK063(gu)001:4893: rta mgrin rim par 'dod pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:4894: drug pa bzhi ste rim pa bzhin //
NK063(gu)001:4895: bdug spros me tog mar me dang //
NK063(gu)001:4896: dri chab lha mo zhes su bshad //
NK063(gu)001:4897: bdun pa bzhi ni rim pa bzhin //
NK063(gu)001:4898: rtag chad mtshan ma dag pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:4899: bdag med ma ste rim pa bzhin //
NK063(gu)001:4900: mthar zad byed po rdo rje ni //
NK063(gu)001:4901: ma lus 'dus pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK063(gu)001:4902: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje las //
NK063(gu)001:4903: rnam par sprul pa'i sprul pa drug /
NK063(gu)001:4904: brgyad pa yi ge drug tu bshad //
NK063(gu)001:4905: sgrib pa kun zad ye shes ni //
NK063(gu)001:4906: 'ching ba gsod byed yin par bshad //
NK063(gu)001:4908: de yang yi ge las lha'i sa bon du btu ba'i rgyu mtshan bzhi yod de /
NK063(gu)001:4909: ming gi yi ge dang po yin pas dang /
NK063(gu)001:4912: rnam par thar ba mthun pa'i phyir sa bon btu ba rnams las /
NK063(gu)001:4913: 'dir phal cher phyi ma gnyis kyi dbang du byas pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4914: de las dang po a ni sa bon gyi yi
NK063(gu)001:4915: ge kun gyi dang por bzhag pa'i 'thad pa ni
NK063(gu)001:4917: a nyid sna tshogs par snang ba'i //
NK063(gu)001:4918: ka la sogs pa bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK063(gu)001:4919: sgra yi ming gis thams cad bsdus //
NK063(gu)001:4922: a ni stong pa ye nas stong //
NK063(gu)001:4923: stong pa nyid na stong pa med //
NK063(gu)001:4924: yi ge kun gyi rgyu'am gzhi //
NK063(gu)001:4925: yin pa'i phyir na dang por gzhag /
NK063(gu)001:4928: ces pa sarba d+harma'i sgra las drangs na chos thams cad do //
NK063(gu)001:4929: de a yis bkag pas chos thams cad skye ba med pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:4930: de ni yum kun tu bzang mo yin pa'i phyir de'i sa bon yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4931: des go phye ba las yi ge gzhan rnams snang ba'i tshul ni /
NK063(gu)001:4932: tha tha la sogs bcu las de bzhin gshegs pa yab yum bcu bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:4934: ta th+aa ga ta'i sgra las drangs na de bzhin
NK063(gu)001:4935: gshegs pa zhes bya ba yin pa'i phyir de tsam
NK063(gu)001:4936: du chos mthun par sbyar ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4937: de yang yi ge log pa las yab bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:4938: de ni kun rdzob kyi cha 'dzin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4939: yum rnams ma log pa las bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:4940: don dam gyi cha 'dzin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4941: de yang tha ni sgyu 'phrul zhes pa la sogs yab rigs lnga la sgyu 'phrul du bshad de /
NK063(gu)001:4943: sgyu ma lta bu'i phung po las //
NK063(gu)001:4944: rang rig thabs kyis rigs lngar 'phrul //
NK063(gu)001:4947: ces pa la sogs gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:4948: tha ni d+r+wa bas zhes pa rigs kyi yul lnga la dra bar bshad de /
NK063(gu)001:4949: yum gyi mkha' dang d+r+wa ba chos mthun pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4950: de ltar yang rdo rje las /
NK063(gu)001:4951: d+r+wa ba cir yang 'gyur ba ste //
NK063(gu)001:4953: gang nas bltas kyang gsal bar snang //
NK063(gu)001:4954: cir yang sdud cing shong ba bzhin //
NK063(gu)001:4955: de bzhin yum gyi mkha' dbyings kyang //
NK063(gu)001:4957: gang nas zhugs kyang gsal bar snang //
NK063(gu)001:4958: thams cad sdud cing shong ba'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:4959: yum la d+r+wa ba zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:4963: ka kha la sogs las sa'i snying po la sogs nang gi sems dpa' bzhi bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:4965: ka ru ni ka'i sgra las drangs na snying rje byang chub kyi sems zhes bya ba yin la //
NK063(gu)001:4966: de ni sa snying la sogs bzhi yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4967: de yang yi ge dang lha dang po de gtso bor byas nas sbyar ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:4968: ka ni spyan gyi zhes pa mig shes la sogs rnam shes bzhi'o //
NK063(gu)001:4970: ces pa rnam shes de dag gi rang bzhin thugs yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4971: chos rig cing gsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4972: de ltar yang rdo rje las /
NK063(gu)001:4973: rnam par shes pa kun yid yin //
NK063(gu)001:4974: yid kyi rnam shes gcod byed pa //
NK063(gu)001:4975: thugs nyid rig pa sna tshogs pas //
NK063(gu)001:4976: de phyir thugs kyi mchog ces bya //
NK063(gu)001:4978: tsa tsha la sogs bzhi las la s+ye la sogs nang gi sems ma bzhi bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:4980: tsar+ya zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na spyad par bya ba zhes bya ba yin la /
NK063(gu)001:4981: de ni gzugs la sogs pa'i yul bzhi yin te /
NK063(gu)001:4982: de dag gi rang bzhin la s+ye la sogs sems ma bzhi yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4983: tsa ni spyan gyi zhes pa gzugs la sogs pa bzhi'o //
NK063(gu)001:4985: ces pa yul la skur bshad de /
NK063(gu)001:4986: rnam shes skye ba'i rten byed pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:4988: rnam shes bzhi yis dmigs pa'i yul //
NK063(gu)001:4989: mthong bar bya ba la sogs pa //
NK063(gu)001:4990: dmigs par bya phyir sku yi mchog /
NK063(gu)001:4992: pa pha la sogs pa las byams pa la sogs phyi'i sems pa bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:4994: pa ra mi ta'i sgra las drangs na don dam byang chub kyi sems zhes bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:4995: de'i rang bzhin ni byams pa la sogs bzhi yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4996: ba ni spyan gyi zhes pa mig sogs dbang po bzhi'o //
NK063(gu)001:4998: pa dbang po la gsung du bzhag pa ni des yul dang shes pa brda sprod pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:4999: ya wa ra la bzhi las d+h+au pe ma la sogs phyi'i sems ma bzhi bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:5001: ya a yan ta zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na skye zhing 'byung ba zhes bya ba yin la /
NK063(gu)001:5002: de ni dus bzhi yin te /
NK063(gu)001:5003: de'i rang bzhin mchod pa'i lha mo bzhi yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:5004: yang sde tshan dang po'i mtha'i nga dang /
NK063(gu)001:5007: thams cad kyi mthar 'byung ba'i o las gshed po la sogs sgo ba bzhi bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:5009: yi ge yang mthar zad kyi yi ge yin cing /
NK063(gu)001:5010: sgo ba bzhi yang dkyil 'khor gyi mthar gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:5011: 'o na 'di dag la sku yang 'jigs byed ces
NK063(gu)001:5012: pa la sogs sku gsung thugs 'jigs byed du bshad
NK063(gu)001:5013: pa ni ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:5014: 'di ni gdul bya'i ming gis 'dul byed la btags pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:5015: le'u bco lnga pa na dpa' bo lha rje zhes gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:5016: 'o na gdul bya la sku gsung thugs kyi sgra ci'i phyir brjod ce na /
NK063(gu)001:5017: gong du rnam shes la thugs su 'jog pa'i 'thad
NK063(gu)001:5018: pa la sogs lung gi shes byed dang bcas pa
NK063(gu)001:5019: bshad zin to // yang na nang ltar du gsang
NK063(gu)001:5020: ba'i rnam shes rig pa yin pa'i phyir thugs la
NK063(gu)001:5021: de'i bde ba skyes pa'i tshe tha mal pa'i rnam
NK063(gu)001:5022: shes kyi rtog pa ji snyed pa rnams 'jigs pas
NK063(gu)001:5023: bshad zin to // 'jigs byed do // de bzhin
NK063(gu)001:5024: du gsang ba'i yul las de'i rnam shes skye ba'i
NK063(gu)001:5026: gsang ba'i dbang pos yul dang rnam shes brda sprod pa'i phyir gsung ste /
NK063(gu)001:5027: de dag 'jigs pa ni gong gis shes so //
NK063(gu)001:5028: sha sha sa ha bzhi las sgo ma bzhi bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:5030: bi shud+d+he'i sgra las drangs na zhi ba zhes bya la /
NK063(gu)001:5031: de ni rtag par ma yin pa la sogs te
NK063(gu)001:5032: de dag gi rang bzhin lcags kyu ma la sogs
NK063(gu)001:5033: sgo ma bzhi yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:5034: k+sha las kun tu bzang po bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:5036: k+sha k+sha ta'i sgra las drangs na gnyis su med pa'i ye shes zhes bya la /
NK063(gu)001:5037: de'i rang bzhin kun tu bzang po yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:5038: yi ge de thub pa'i yi ge'i gong du 'ong ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:5039: hri ha ya na'i tan+t+ra las /
NK063(gu)001:5040: k+sha ni kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' //
NK063(gu)001:5041: b+ha ga rgya mtsho'i klong mtha' yas //
NK063(gu)001:5042: chos nyid yangs pa'i mkha' gting nas //
NK063(gu)001:5043: 'bras bu kun tu bzang mor shar //
NK063(gu)001:5044: mkha' dang gnyis med rnam par dag /
NK063(gu)001:5045: bde chen rnam dag sku gsung thugs //
NK063(gu)001:5046: de rtogs pa las thub drug 'byung //
NK063(gu)001:5048: i +ai la sogs las thub pa drug bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:5050: kun bzang chos kyi sku skye ba med pa'i dbyings
NK063(gu)001:5051: mtshon byed a las gug 'greng zhabs kyu la sogs
NK063(gu)001:5052: pas skye ba'i cho 'phrul thub pa drug mtshon pa'i
NK063(gu)001:5053: phyir de dag de tsam du chos mthun par sbyar
NK063(gu)001:5054: ba yin no // le'u bsdu ba gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:5055: grol lam du bsdu ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:5057: dang po ni bsdu ba gong ma ltar don gsum las bsdu ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:5058: thabs dang shes rab dgyes sprin zhes par /
NK063(gu)001:5059: a ni stong dang mi stong gi /
NK063(gu)001:5060: dbu ma'ang dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK063(gu)001:5062: tshul ni thabs zhes kun rdzob snang ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:5063: shes rab ces don dam stong nyid do //
NK063(gu)001:5064: dgyes zhes pa dbyer med mngon du byas pas bdag
NK063(gu)001:5065: don du dgyes pa'i longs spyod bsam gyis mi khyab
NK063(gu)001:5067: sbyin zhes gzhan don du thugs rje sprin phung ltar
NK063(gu)001:5068: snang ba ni 'bras bu chos sku'i bdag nyid do
NK063(gu)001:5071: rab tu brtan gyur zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:5074: de ni byang ba stong pa dang chub pa snang ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:5075: de gnyis dbyer med a la sems sbyang ba'i don no //
NK063(gu)001:5077: de las ming tshogs zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:5078: de bzhin no zhes gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:5079: de ni a las sgra dbyangs kyi yi ge tshogs
NK063(gu)001:5080: su snang ba ni thabs kyi bkod pa yin zhes
NK063(gu)001:5085: de ni sgra dbyangs kyi yi ge rnams bskyed pa'i
NK063(gu)001:5086: sa bon yin pa'i phyir ye shes kyi rgyu yin
NK063(gu)001:5087: no zhes so // 'khor lo zhes par /
NK063(gu)001:5088: ka kha ga g+ha nga zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:5089: gyur to zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK063(gu)001:5090: de ni mi zad pa gsung gi 'khor lo dngos
NK063(gu)001:5091: ka kha la sogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su bkod
NK063(gu)001:5093: 'bras bu rgyal ba smin grub ces par /
NK063(gu)001:5094: phyogs bcu dus bzhir zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:5095: k+sha la rdzogs pa'i bar bzhi dang /
NK063(gu)001:5097: 'go ni ma nor lam yin te //
NK063(gu)001:5099: +amo ni thams cad zhig pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:5101: de ni grol lam ting nge 'dzin dang thabs kyi
NK063(gu)001:5102: khyad par las 'bras bu rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa
NK063(gu)001:5103: gnyis kyi skur smin pa'i sgo nas bdag don grub
NK063(gu)001:5106: e ma ho ngo mtshar ya mtshan gyi //
NK063(gu)001:5110: de ni de lta bu grub pas ngo mtshar zhing
NK063(gu)001:5111: gzhan yang yi ge'i sgo nas yang dag pa'i don
NK063(gu)001:5112: ston pa la sogs pa don byed du ma nus
NK063(gu)001:5113: pa'i phyir ro // ming tshogs zhes par /
NK063(gu)001:5114: thams cad ming tsam zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:5117: de ni chos thams cad ming du btags pa'am ming
NK063(gu)001:5118: 'dus pa'i tshig gi tshogs kyis mtshon pa yang yang
NK063(gu)001:5119: dag par na ngo bos ma grub ces mtshon pa
NK063(gu)001:5120: yi ge nyid la gnas pa'i don no //
NK063(gu)001:5122: a nyid sna tshogs par snang zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:5125: de ni de lta bu'i mtshon byed yi ge rnam grangs ni bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su nges te /
NK063(gu)001:5126: des bskyed bya rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bskyed pa'i phyir zhes pa'i don no //
NK063(gu)001:5128: dngos med yi ge'i zhes pa gnyis dang /
NK063(gu)001:5130: sems kyi rang bzhin yi ge ste //
NK063(gu)001:5134: de ni yi ge de dag kyang rgyu rkyen 'dus
NK063(gu)001:5135: nas byed pa po gzhan gyis ma byas pa nyid
NK063(gu)001:5136: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i
NK063(gu)001:5138: 'dus byas rdo rje dkyil 'khor zhes par /
NK063(gu)001:5139: dbyibs dang kha dog ces pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:5142: de ni yi ge de ni 'dus byas ltar dbyibs
NK063(gu)001:5143: dang kha dog gis rol pa cir yang ston pas
NK063(gu)001:5145: de nyid ngo bor ma grub pa dang rang bzhin dbyer med pas rdo rje ste /
NK063(gu)001:5146: de rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor yin no zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:5148: dbyings la dbyings kyis zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:5151: de lta bur rang dkyil 'khor de chos kyi dbyings
NK063(gu)001:5152: yin la de yi ges mngon du 'byin pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:5153: gsung gi dam tshig yi ge 'khor lo'i zhes so
NK063(gu)001:5154: // 'da' bar mi mdzad la sogs su //
NK063(gu)001:5157: de ni gsung gi 'khor lo des 'bras bu grub
NK063(gu)001:5158: pa las 'da' bar mi mdzad mi 'grub pa'i dbang
NK063(gu)001:5159: med de / 'grub byed kyi rgyu rkyen ma tshogs pa gang yang med pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:5160: rgyu nus pa thogs med bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:5161: des na rgyu rkyen tshogs pa'i mthu chen po las
NK063(gu)001:5162: 'bras bu 'byung ba mtshan nyid yin no zhes pa'i
NK063(gu)001:5163: don no // de la mnyes pas ho zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:5164: gnyis pa thabs lam du bsdu ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:5165: thabs dang zhes pa yab dang /
NK063(gu)001:5166: shes rab ces pa yum mo //
NK063(gu)001:5167: dgyes sprin zhes rol pa'i bde ba gzhi ma nges
NK063(gu)001:5168: pa las thabs kyi bkod pa cir yang snang ba'o
NK063(gu)001:5169: // byang chub sems zhes pa gsang ba'i theg le sgra dbyangs kyi yi ger gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:5170: tshogs zhes pa thig le de nyid dga' ba bcu
NK063(gu)001:5171: drug las ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su snang
NK063(gu)001:5172: ba'o // rgyu 'khor lo zhes pa yi ge nyid
NK063(gu)001:5173: lha bskyed pa'i rgyu 'bras su mi zad pa gsung
NK063(gu)001:5174: ba'o // gi 'khor lo'o // des 'bras bu rgyal
NK063(gu)001:5175: ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su bsgoms pas de nyid
NK063(gu)001:5176: du smin cing grub par byed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5177: de'i phyir gsang ba'i rnam shes nyid 'bras bur shar bas ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:5178: 'bras bu de'i mtshon byed ni gong gi thig le
NK063(gu)001:5179: las ming dang tshig gi tshogs su snang ba sgra
NK063(gu)001:5180: dbyangs kyi yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:5181: des ji ltar mtshon na rang bzhin lhan cig skyes
NK063(gu)001:5182: pa'i ye shes 'dus ma byas pa de nyid 'dus
NK063(gu)001:5183: byas rten can gyi dga' ba bcu drug las /
NK063(gu)001:5184: thig le bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis yi ge'i tshogs su
NK063(gu)001:5185: bkod cing de ye shes su lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK063(gu)001:5186: phyir rdo rje'o // de ltar gsang ba byang chub
NK063(gu)001:5187: sems kyi dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin lhan cig skyes
NK063(gu)001:5188: pa'i ye shes mngon du gsal ba la 'byin pa
NK063(gu)001:5189: phyir rdo rje'o // zhes bya ste / de'i don las mi 'da' bas dam tshig go //
NK063(gu)001:5190: des 'bras bu rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis grub
NK063(gu)001:5191: pa las 'da' bar mi mdzad cing mi 'grub pa'i
NK063(gu)001:5192: dbang med de / rgyu byang chub sems kyi thig
NK063(gu)001:5193: le dang de nyid rkyen thabs kyi bkod pa gnyis
NK063(gu)001:5194: tshogs pas las su rung ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:5195: de'i nus pa'am mthu ni gnas skabs su /
NK063(gu)001:5196: ji skad du bcu gcig pa las /
NK063(gu)001:5199: mthar thug tu yon tan chen po thob pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:5200: yid bzhin sprin gyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:5202: de lta bu'i thob byed ni thabs kyi lam yin zhing de la mnyes bas ho zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:5203: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u bzhi pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5205: // le'u lnga pa'i gzhung don la brgyad las /
NK063(gu)001:5206: dang po 'bras bu 'grub pa'i rgyu ni /
NK063(gu)001:5207: gzhung 'di nyid nas chos lnga dang ldan pa gcig gis 'grub par bshad de /
NK063(gu)001:5209: gzhung 'og nas ston pa zhes pa ston pa'i rang bzhin dang mnyam pa'i rdo rje slob dpon no //
NK063(gu)001:5210: mchod ces pa de sgo gsum gyis mnyes par bya
NK063(gu)001:5211: dka' ba sna tshogs kyis mnyes par byed pa la
NK063(gu)001:5212: brtson pa ste / de yis rang gi spyod lam yongs su sbyang ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:5213: le'u gsum pa ltar gtan la phab pa'i chos nyid
NK063(gu)001:5214: kyi don ji lta ba bzhin rtogs pa'i lta ba
NK063(gu)001:5215: rang gi blo la gsal ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:5216: dam tshig ces pa dang 'og gi ma nyams zhes
NK063(gu)001:5217: pa gnyis sbyar bas le'u bcu dgu pa ltar 'di'i
NK063(gu)001:5218: bsrung bya rnams rnam par dag pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5219: sngags dang zhes pa de bzhi dang /
NK063(gu)001:5220: phyag rgya zhes pa bzhis lha'i sku bskyed pa'i rim
NK063(gu)001:5221: pa rnams bsgoms shes shing de dag gi cho ga
NK063(gu)001:5222: las kyi rim pa la mkhas pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5223: yo byad ces pa sgrub pa'i dus kyi yo byad ni /
NK063(gu)001:5228: +aa li k+aa li ste de dag dang ldan pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5230: dam tshig lta ba ting nge 'dzin //
NK063(gu)001:5231: byang chub sems dang snying rje dang //
NK063(gu)001:5232: lhag pa'i yo byad lnga rdzogs bya //
NK063(gu)001:5233: zhes lam gyi yo byad lnga po de yin par sems so //
NK063(gu)001:5234: de ltar chos lnga po de rnams dang ldan pa'i
NK063(gu)001:5235: sgo nas bsgrubs na bsgrub bya'i 'og gi mchog thun
NK063(gu)001:5237: chos de dag dang mi ldan na bsgrubs pa'i don
NK063(gu)001:5238: med cing rgyud brlag par 'gyur zhes 'grub pa'i rgyu
NK063(gu)001:5239: khe nyen dang bcas te bstan pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:5240: 'og gi bsgrub bya gnyis po kho na'i rgyur gsungs la /
NK063(gu)001:5241: de las gzhan yang spyir bla na med pa'i byang
NK063(gu)001:5242: chub 'grub pa'i rgyu la kha cig ni chos bzhi
NK063(gu)001:5243: yin te / lta ba spyi sar mi gdon pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5244: sgom nyams mu cor du mi smra ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:5245: gsang sgo yal bar mi dor ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:5246: byang chub ngo dgar mi btang ba dang bzhi yin zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:5247: yang kha cig ni gnas la nges pa med pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5248: spyod pa la dam bca' med pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5249: 'tsho bas chog par gnas pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5250: mi chos kyi bya ba thog tu ma babs pa dang bzhi yin zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:5251: yang bde gshegs chen po ni chos brgyad dang ldan dgos te /
NK063(gu)001:5252: dad pas phul btab pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5253: brtson 'grus kyi gzhu bdungs pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5254: dam tshig so mtshams kyi mkhar ltar bsrung ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:5255: dben gnas grogs ltar bsten pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5257: byang chub don du gnyer ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:5258: man ngag snying ltar 'chang ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:5259: bla ma yi dam gyi lha ltar 'khur ba dang brgyad yin no gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:5260: yang rje chen po ni byang chub kyi sems gdar sha gcad pa las ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:5261: rab kyis gangs kyi seng ge ltar //
NK063(gu)001:5262: sgra las gzugs tsam bstan mi bya //
NK063(gu)001:5263: 'bring gis brag gi gla ba ltar //
NK063(gu)001:5265: tha mas lug khyu'i bong chung ltar //
NK063(gu)001:5266: grong las spags tsam bsgom par bya //
NK063(gu)001:5269: bas mtha'i dgon par rab gnas shing //
NK063(gu)001:5270: bdag gis bdag nyid sba byas te //
NK063(gu)001:5271: ri dwags shi ba'i ro bzhin du //
NK063(gu)001:5272: chags pa med par gnas par bya //
NK063(gu)001:5277: gzhon nu ma yi gdu bu bzhin //
NK063(gu)001:5278: bdag nyid gcig pur gnas par bya //
NK063(gu)001:5281: skyes bu seng ge bzhin rgyu ba //
NK063(gu)001:5282: zhes pa la sogs gsungs pa bzhin yin gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:5283: de dag bsgom pa la mos pa'i don du 'chad pa pos rgyas par yang bsnyad do //
NK063(gu)001:5284: gtan la dbab pa'i lta ba la gnyis las gdams pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:5285: rnal 'byor pa bskal pa dman zhing gsang ba'i lung
NK063(gu)001:5286: dang man ngag gis ma zin pa gang gis yod
NK063(gu)001:5287: med la sogs mtha' gang du yang dmigs su med
NK063(gu)001:5288: de / mtha' dang bral ba'i don mi shes pas so //
NK063(gu)001:5289: de ma shes te phyogs su 'dzin pa'i blo de yis chos kyi dbyings mi shes pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:5290: chos kyi dbyings de ni dmigs su med cing mtha' dang bral ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:5291: des na dngos dang zhes pa 'og gi 'jig pa dang sbyar te /
NK063(gu)001:5292: phyi nang gi grub mtha' dngos por lta ba rnams
NK063(gu)001:5293: le'u gsum pa ltar gtan tshigs kyis dmigs med du
NK063(gu)001:5295: dngos med par zhes pa yang 'og gi 'jig pa dang sbyor te /
NK063(gu)001:5296: phyi nang gi grub mtha' med pa phyogs gcig tu
NK063(gu)001:5297: lta ba yang dmigs med mtha' bral du rtogs pas
NK063(gu)001:5298: 'jigs pa'i phyir / des na mtha' gang du yang
NK063(gu)001:5299: dmigs su med pa'i don shes par gyis shig ces
NK063(gu)001:5301: gtan la dbab bya'i lta ba dngos ni /
NK063(gu)001:5302: rgyu shes pa'i skabs su rim gyis pa'i blo la
NK063(gu)001:5303: ltos te brjod bya snang ba stong pa dbyer med
NK063(gu)001:5304: bden pa gsum dang sbyar te ldog pa tha dad
NK063(gu)001:5305: du rim par gtan la dbab pa ni gzhung gcig
NK063(gu)001:5306: la'ang / dang po stong ldog don dam gyi ngos nas ji ltar gtan la dbab na /
NK063(gu)001:5307: brten pa'i gzhi dang bskyed pa'i rtsa ba med pa'i sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes ni /
NK063(gu)001:5308: mtshan gyi sgo nas pho yang ma yin de bzhin du mo yang ma yin ma ning yang min /
NK063(gu)001:5309: mtshan med sgo nga lta bu yang ma yin /
NK063(gu)001:5310: lha dang dmyal ba la sogs 'gro ba rigs drug gi brgyud gang yang min /
NK063(gu)001:5311: dkar dmar la sogs kha dog gang yang ma yin /
NK063(gu)001:5312: gru bzhi zlum po la sogs pa dbyibs gang yang ma yin /
NK063(gu)001:5313: brten par bya ba'i gnas dang byed pa'i rdzas su
NK063(gu)001:5314: ma yin pas gang gi ngo bo yang min no
NK063(gu)001:5315: // de la de bzhin nyid las ma bcos pa'i yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:5316: dbyings las skye ba med pa'i yin la /
NK063(gu)001:5317: dbyings de nyid ye shes su gsal bas spros pa dang bral bar gsal ba'i ye shes te /
NK063(gu)001:5318: de nyid thabs kyis phyag rgya las rang bzhin gyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:5319: de chos kun gyi rgyu las ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu'o //
NK063(gu)001:5320: de ltar rtogs pa'i blo de'i don gtan tshigs 'di'i
NK063(gu)001:5321: phyir na don 'di yin zhes ngo bo gang yang
NK063(gu)001:5322: ma grub pas yin pa med pa'i lta ba zhes
NK063(gu)001:5323: bya zhing / de la skye med dam chos nyid
NK063(gu)001:5324: dam don dam tsam du yang tha snyad du mi
NK063(gu)001:5325: bsgrub pa'i phyir yongs gcod bsgrub bya med pa zhes
NK063(gu)001:5326: bya zhing / bya la / gang yang yod chos
NK063(gu)001:5327: su mi 'dod pas sgro 'dogs rtag pa las grol
NK063(gu)001:5329: 'o na de stong pa kho na'i mthar thug go zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:5330: de'i mtha' bsal ba'i phyir snang rtog kun rdzob kyi ngos nas gtan la phab na /
NK063(gu)001:5331: gong gi gzhung de nyid la gang yang yin par 'chad pa pos bsnyad la /
NK063(gu)001:5332: des de bzhin nyid las lhun gyis grub pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:5333: dbyings las snang ba mu mtha' med pa'i ye shes las ma 'gags par gsal ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:5334: thabs kyi phyag rgya las ting nge 'dzin gyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:5335: chos kun gyi rgyu las mngon gsal 'bras bu'i rang bzhin te /
NK063(gu)001:5336: blo de'i don gang yang gtan tshigs kyis grub pas min pa med pa'i lta ba zhes bya la /
NK063(gu)001:5337: de la skye ba dang chos can dang kun rdzob
NK063(gu)001:5338: tsam du gang yang grub pa'i phyir rnam bcad dgag
NK063(gu)001:5339: bya med pa zhes bya zhing /
NK063(gu)001:5340: gang yang med chos su mi 'dod pas skur 'debs chad pa las grol ba'i lta ba zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:5341: 'o na de snang ba'i mthar thug cing /
NK063(gu)001:5342: gong ma stong pa'i mthar thug pas mtha' gnyis tha dad du 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:5343: mtha' de gnyis bsal ba'i phyir snang stong ngam bden
NK063(gu)001:5344: pa dbyer med kyi ngos nas gtan la phab na
NK063(gu)001:5345: / gong gi gzhung de nyid gang yang yin min gnyis su med par bsnyad la /
NK063(gu)001:5346: de ni gnyis su med pa'i de bzhin nyid dang /
NK063(gu)001:5347: gnyis su med pa'i dbyings dang /
NK063(gu)001:5348: gnyis su med par gsal ba'i ye shes te //
NK063(gu)001:5349: phyag rgya las thabs kyis lhag pa'i phyag rgya dang /
NK063(gu)001:5350: rgyu 'bras kyi chos kun gnyis med kyi ngang du gcig pas gnyis su med pa'i rgyu zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:5351: blo de'i ngo na gang yang grub ma grub dbyer med yin te /
NK063(gu)001:5352: cir yang ma grub pa'i phyir cir yang ma 'gags la /
NK063(gu)001:5353: cir yang ma 'gags pa'i phyir cir yang ma grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:5354: de gnyis gnyis su med pas yin min gnyis med kyi lta ba zhes bya zhing /
NK063(gu)001:5356: chos can dang chos nyid gnyis dang /
NK063(gu)001:5357: don dam dang kun rdzob gnyis la sogs pa tha
NK063(gu)001:5358: dad du 'dzin pa thams cad dang bral ba'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:5359: / rnam bcad du dgag bya dang yongs gcod du bsgrub bya gnyis ka dang bral te /
NK063(gu)001:5360: gang yang yod med tha dad du mi 'dod pas
NK063(gu)001:5361: rtag chad kyi sgro skur thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK063(gu)001:5363: de ltar gnyis med ces bya ba yang dgos ched
NK063(gu)001:5364: kyi dbang gis sgro btags te bstan pa tsam du
NK063(gu)001:5365: zad kyis gnyis med nyid du yang thug pa med
NK063(gu)001:5366: de / spyod yul dang bral ba'i lta ba zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:5367: yang 'di bsam par bya ste rgyu shes pa'i skabs su gtan la dbab bya lta ba'i don la /
NK063(gu)001:5369: bdag dang gzhan dang rtog pa'i rgyun //
NK063(gu)001:5370: zhes pa la sogs bden pa gnyis su dang /
NK063(gu)001:5371: le'u bzhi par a ni stong dang mi stong gi zhes pa la sogs pa bden pa bzhir dang /
NK063(gu)001:5372: 'dir gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni la sogs
NK063(gu)001:5373: pa bden pa gsum du gtan la phab pa rnams
NK063(gu)001:5376: dang po le'u gsum par ni rgyu shes pas shes byar gtan la phab pa yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:5377: lnga pa 'dir nyams su blang byar yin la /
NK063(gu)001:5378: bzhi par bden pa dbyer med pa'i yi ge'i sku
NK063(gu)001:5379: gsum du sangs rgyas pa'i phyir 'bras bur gtan la
NK063(gu)001:5381: de yang le'u bzhi pa dang lnga pa'i go rim ni /
NK063(gu)001:5382: bzhi par lam gyi rim pa'i dbang du rgyud don nyams su blang byar bshad zin to //
NK063(gu)001:5383: de ltar gtan la phab pa'i don rkyen 'jug pas nyams su len par byed pa la /
NK063(gu)001:5384: lam gyi rim pa'i dbang du stong snying gnyis yin la /
NK063(gu)001:5385: mngon rtogs las sdeb kyis rgyud don nyams su blang
NK063(gu)001:5386: bya'i dbang du ting nge 'dzin gsum las dang po
NK063(gu)001:5387: gnyis yin te / de bsgom pa'i dgos ched ni /
NK063(gu)001:5388: sems nyid phyi nang gi dngos po dkar dmar gyi rnam pa sna tshogs su snang ba rnams /
NK063(gu)001:5389: snang dus nyid na rang rang gi ngo bos stongs
NK063(gu)001:5390: pa'i dngos po cir yang grub pa med par rtogs
NK063(gu)001:5391: na tha mal gyi rtog pa'i ngo bo 'di nyid
NK063(gu)001:5392: ma spangs par ye shes su dbang sgyur ba yin
NK063(gu)001:5393: te / gong gi rtogs pa'i ngang la gnas pa'i
NK063(gu)001:5394: ting nge 'dzin la goms pas khyad par 'gyur ba
NK063(gu)001:5396: de'i phyir blo gzhag pa'i thabs ni /
NK063(gu)001:5397: sgom pa po rnal 'byor pa gang gis ji bzhin
NK063(gu)001:5398: par rtogs kyang de'i ngang la blo gnas par ma
NK063(gu)001:5399: gyur na / dper na glang po che rgun chang
NK063(gu)001:5400: gis myos pas ngam grog dang g.yang sa rnams la
NK063(gu)001:5401: bag med du mchongs shing rgyug par byed do //
NK063(gu)001:5402: de dang 'dra bar rnal 'byor pas lta ba rtogs
NK063(gu)001:5403: kyang de'i ngang la mnyam par ma bzhag na bya
NK063(gu)001:5404: ba dang bya ba ma yin pa'i yul la sems
NK063(gu)001:5406: glang po che mchongs shing brgyugs pa'i nyes pas cher
NK063(gu)001:5407: srog dang 'bral zhing chung du rkang lag 'chag pa
NK063(gu)001:5408: ltar / rnal 'byor pa'i sems rang yan du 'phros
NK063(gu)001:5409: pas cher ngan song du ltung zhing chung du yun
NK063(gu)001:5410: ring du 'khor ba las mi thar ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:5411: 'bru bsgyur te 'og nas btul nas su //
NK063(gu)001:5412: zhes pa de'i tshe glang po de bdag po thabs
NK063(gu)001:5413: la mkhas pas sna nas lcags kyus bzung ste sdong
NK063(gu)001:5414: po la brtod pas thul te mchongs rgyug mi byed
NK063(gu)001:5415: pa ltar / rnal 'byor pa yang rtogs pa'i ngang
NK063(gu)001:5416: la mnyam par gzhag pas sems la dbang thob par
NK063(gu)001:5418: dbang thob pa de nyid thams cad du rang snang ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:5419: chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba ni rang gi sems
NK063(gu)001:5420: yin la de ni yod pa dang med pa'i mtha'
NK063(gu)001:5421: thams cad kyis stongs pa'i phyir sems nyid ni don
NK063(gu)001:5422: dam pa'i bden pa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:5423: de nyid kun rdzob tu chos rnams ma lus pa kun gyi rtsa ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:5424: sems ma rtogs pa las 'khor ba byung zhing rtogs pa las ye shes su snang ba'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:5425: dpe na ga bur gcig nyid tsha grang gi nad la sman dug gnyis su 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:5426: des na gcig tu ma nges pa las sems nyid
NK063(gu)001:5427: rtogs shing le'u bzhi pa ltar yi ge'i snang byed
NK063(gu)001:5428: la goms pas ye shes su snang ba'i rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:5429: yin te / yi ge'i snang byed las 'og nas
NK063(gu)001:5430: 'byung ba'i bsgrub bya dngos grub gnyis 'grub pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:5431: dper na yid bzhin gyi rin po che las dgos
NK063(gu)001:5432: 'dod sprin phung ltar 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:5433: de'i phyir de las dkyil 'khor bsgom pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:5434: thabs las zhes rtsa ba'i thabs te /
NK063(gu)001:5435: de ni le'u bzhi pa ltar sems nyid yi ger snang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:5436: thabs byung zhes gzhi'i thabs te le'u drug pa dang
NK063(gu)001:5437: bdun pa ltar yi ge las rten gzhal yas su
NK063(gu)001:5439: zhes pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i thabs te /
NK063(gu)001:5440: de ni le'u bzhi pa ltar gsung yig 'bru dang /
NK063(gu)001:5441: drug pa ltar thugs phyag mtshan dang /
NK063(gu)001:5442: bdun pa ltar sku rdzogs pa'i sgo nas brten pa lha bskyed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5443: de dag kyang sems su gcig pas tha dad min
NK063(gu)001:5444: las blo dman pas dus gcig tu mi lcogs shing
NK063(gu)001:5445: rim par snang bas tha dad pa'i /
NK063(gu)001:5446: nang dang zhes gong ltar bskyed pa'i brten pa'i lha'o //
NK063(gu)001:5448: zhes pa rten gzhal yas so //
NK063(gu)001:5449: dkyil 'khor zhes pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi'o //
NK063(gu)001:5450: bsam yas zhes pa de'i bkod pa'i khyad par dang che ba'i yon tan no //
NK063(gu)001:5452: zhes pa rtog pa ye nas ye shes kyi dkyil
NK063(gu)001:5453: 'khor yin pa la ting nges de ltar bskyed pas
NK063(gu)001:5454: ye shes la ye shes rol pa zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:5455: de la 'khor ba dang g.yang sa'i 'jigs pa med de /
NK063(gu)001:5456: spyod yul kun ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du dag pa'i phyir bzang po yin la /
NK063(gu)001:5457: de las mi 'da' bas phyag rgya ste de'i don mthar phyin pas mchog yin no //
NK063(gu)001:5458: des rtog pa dkar ba'i phyir blang dor med pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:5459: ye shes la ye shes rol pa gong gi thabs gsum po de nyid ci las snang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:5460: sa bon dang skyed sngags dang sku rdzogs pa'i ye shes rnams sems las gzhan ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:5461: rang gi sems nyid ye shes su snang ba'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:5462: ming zhes sa bon dang tshig ces skyed sngags dang /
NK063(gu)001:5463: gzugs nas sku rdzogs pa la sogs pa rnams sems su gcig pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:5464: gcig las 'dod rgur sgyur ba ni dper na yid
NK063(gu)001:5465: bzhin gyi rin po che las dgos 'dod 'byung ba'am
NK063(gu)001:5466: / mun pa mthug po la sgron me'i snang ba 'byung ba ji bzhin du'am /
NK063(gu)001:5467: gzhan du 'gyur bas dpe gzhan yang lcags las gser 'gyur gyi rtsi yis gser du bsgyur ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:5468: dug las dug 'gyur gyi rtsi yis dug sman gyi rang bzhin du 'gyur ba'i tshul bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:5469: de la 'dris par bslab pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:5470: sngags kyi yan lag dang ldan pas phyag rgya gcig
NK063(gu)001:5471: spros kyi ting nge 'dzin gsal ba la yul gyis
NK063(gu)001:5472: mi 'phrogs pa la blor rab tu brtan pa thob
NK063(gu)001:5473: na / 'og nas 'byung ba'i dngos grub rnams ngo
NK063(gu)001:5474: bo grub med bzhin sgrub pa po'i ngo la snang
NK063(gu)001:5475: ba'i phyir ya mtshan chen po thob par 'gyur zhes
NK063(gu)001:5476: na / bya'o // de gang zhe na dang po
NK063(gu)001:5477: thun mong gi dngos grub ni gang zhig lha chen
NK063(gu)001:5478: po'i chung ma la sogs 'jig rten pa gtsor sgrub
NK063(gu)001:5480: 'di 'chad pa la spyir rgyud kyi bshad thabs du
NK063(gu)001:5481: ma yod pa las 'di ni rgyud bdag nyid kyis
NK063(gu)001:5482: bdag nyid bshad pa zhes bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:5483: 'di'i tshig re re'ang bshad rgyud kyi le'u 'ga' zhig gis ston pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:5484: 'di yang grol lam gyi dbang du dang /
NK063(gu)001:5485: thabs lam gyi dbang du bshad pa gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:5487: rgyud kyi bshad thabs dang mthun par rgyud kyis rgyud 'chad pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:5488: 'di ltar bdud rtsir 'gyur zhing zhes pa /
NK063(gu)001:5489: rgyas pa'i zhe bzhi pa bdud rtsi sman sgrub pa
NK063(gu)001:5490: nas yi ge'i sgo nas 'phro 'dus dug bdud rtsir
NK063(gu)001:5491: 'gyur ba dang / de nad pa la byin pas bsos par 'gyur zhing /
NK063(gu)001:5493: zhes pa yi ge'i 'phro 'du las 'dod bya gzhan yang ji ltar dmigs par 'byung ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:5494: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel zhing //
NK063(gu)001:5495: zhes pa dug bdud rtsir bsgrubs pa de zos pas sam /
NK063(gu)001:5496: yang na nad pa'i lus la yi ge bkod de
NK063(gu)001:5497: 'phro 'du'i sgo nas nad zhi bar bsam na zhi
NK063(gu)001:5498: bar 'gyur ro // longs spyod 'byung zhing zhes tram las rin po che'i gter du bsam pa'am /
NK063(gu)001:5499: yang na yi ge'i 'phro 'du las mchod pa'i bye
NK063(gu)001:5500: brag tu bsams na de'i 'bras bu longs spyod 'byung
NK063(gu)001:5501: ba'o // gzhan yang 'phro 'du'i sgo nas ngan song
NK063(gu)001:5502: gi sgrib pa sbyong bar bsams na de byang bar
NK063(gu)001:5503: ba'o // 'gyur ro // ci yang gzhan du 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:5504: ba zhes snang ba mi mthun pa gzhan du bsgyur
NK063(gu)001:5505: ba ni skam sa las chu 'byung ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:5507: sol ba ljon shing du bsgyur ba la sogs so //
NK063(gu)001:5508: 'grub ces pa rgyal po sa 'dzin dang /
NK063(gu)001:5511: dmag mngas mthu chen la sogs so //
NK063(gu)001:5512: nam mkha' rdo rje sra 'byung zhing //
NK063(gu)001:5513: zhes pa so brgyad pa rdo rje snying po las
NK063(gu)001:5514: thams cad grub pa'i rdzu 'phrul bsgrub pa bstan te
NK063(gu)001:5516: de'i dbyings nas byung ba ni //
NK063(gu)001:5517: zhes pa a las h+aum tam mum de las rdo rje'i brag tu bsam na der 'gyur ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:5518: 'bar nas zhes pa a las ram de las ye
NK063(gu)001:5519: shes kyi mes tha mal pa'i me yang 'tshig pa
NK063(gu)001:5520: dang / yang a las bam de las ye shes
NK063(gu)001:5521: kyi chur gyur par bsam zhing de'i rgyun 'bab pa'ang
NK063(gu)001:5522: gong gi mes me 'tshig pa de bzhin te chus
NK063(gu)001:5523: chu nyid dag par byed do //
NK063(gu)001:5524: 'jig rten khams ni zhes pa 'og gi phyogs su
NK063(gu)001:5525: a las yam de las rlung gis 'jig rten gyi
NK063(gu)001:5526: khams thams cad g.yo zhing bskyod de 'thor bar bsams
NK063(gu)001:5528: thams cad stongs shing zhes pa sa gzhi 'jig rten thams cad la /
NK063(gu)001:5529: yi ge zhe gnyis bkod de /
NK063(gu)001:5530: de'i 'phro 'du las sa gzhi 'od du zhu nas stongs shing ltung bar bsams na der 'gyur ro //
NK063(gu)001:5531: dgug dang zhes pa dbang gi las te /
NK063(gu)001:5532: de yang 'jig rten pa thams cad dgug cing dbang du bya ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:5533: so brgyad pa yul khams dang /
NK063(gu)001:5534: zhe lnga pa rgyal po'i chung ma dang /
NK063(gu)001:5535: lha chen po gzhan gyi chung ma dbang du bya ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:5536: gzhan yang re lnga pa'i pra bsgrub pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5537: re drug pa'i lha chen po bsgrub pa dang rgyal po chen po bsgrub pa rnams so //
NK063(gu)001:5538: btang zhes pa drag po'i las te bkug pa de btang ba'am /
NK063(gu)001:5539: so brgyad pa'i dgra bgegs gling khams gzhan du btang ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:5540: bdag gi gnas na klu yod pa bskrad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5541: bcing zhes pa dbang gi las te 'jig rten las 'das pa dgug cing bcing ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:5542: so dgu pa'i stod rigs lnga bsgrub pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5543: zhe gnyis pa rigs lnga'i byin dbab cing dgug pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5544: lha zhe gnyis po thams cad kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:5545: sems ma bzhi'i byin dbab cing bcing ba ste 'di rnams mchog gi yin no //
NK063(gu)001:5546: dgrol zhes pa zhi ba'i las te /
NK063(gu)001:5547: bdag gi sde pa byad du bcug pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5548: zhe drug pa gzungs ma klu'i byad du bcug pa dgrol ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:5549: gso dang zhes pa rgyas pa'i las te /
NK063(gu)001:5554: dang po ni dug dang gdon gyis zin pa la
NK063(gu)001:5555: yi ge'i 'phro 'dus nad phyir byung bar bsams shing
NK063(gu)001:5556: gso ba ni zhe drug pa klu'i nad gso ba
NK063(gu)001:5557: la sogs so // gnyis pa bar ma do'i shes
NK063(gu)001:5558: pa 'od kyis dgug cing bstims te gso ba ni
NK063(gu)001:5559: la sogs so // / zhe drug pa khro bo ro langs bsgrub pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5560: bdun cu pa zhun chen bsgrub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5561: gsum pa ni re drug pa 'gro ba rigs drug gi tshe nyams pa gso ba la sogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5562: bsad ces pa drag po'i las te /
NK063(gu)001:5563: nga drug pa khro bo gsang ba nye bar sgrub
NK063(gu)001:5564: pa'i sgo nas bar du gcod pa'i bgegs dang bstan
NK063(gu)001:5565: pa 'jig pa'i dgra bas da pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5566: 'pham dang zhes pa drag po'i las te /
NK063(gu)001:5567: gzhan gyi g.yul ni yum gyi mkha' las mtha' yas
NK063(gu)001:5568: kyi spros pas pha rol gyi rgyud la thim pas
NK063(gu)001:5569: myos te 'pham par bsams na der 'gyur ro //
NK063(gu)001:5570: rgyal zhes pa rgyas pa'i las te /
NK063(gu)001:5571: bdag gis g.yul rgyal ba yang 'phro 'dus 'grub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5573: zhes pa phyag rgya zhig spros la brtan pa thob pas 'di dag dang dngos su 'grub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5574: gnyis pa de dag thabs lam du bshad pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:5575: tshig gong 'og bsgyur te 'og nas nam mkha' zhes
NK063(gu)001:5576: pa klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo 'dab ma
NK063(gu)001:5577: sum cu rtsa gnyis dang ldan pa'i thig le bsgom
NK063(gu)001:5578: pa'o // rdo rje zhes pa de'i bde ba dang sems nyid dbyer mi phyed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5580: zhes pa de la skye 'jig med pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5581: 'bar nas zhes pa mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor
NK063(gu)001:5582: lo 'dab ma bcu drug dang ldan pa'i thig le
NK063(gu)001:5583: bsgoms pas ro drug gi bde ba me ltar du
NK063(gu)001:5585: zhes pa des tha mal pa'i rtog pa mi gnas par bsreg pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5586: chu rgyun 'bab pa'ang de bzhin te //
NK063(gu)001:5587: zhes pa snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo 'dab ma
NK063(gu)001:5588: brgyad dang ldan pa'i thig le bsgoms pas bde gsal
NK063(gu)001:5589: mi rtog pa'i ye shes rgyun chad med pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5590: 'jig rten khams ni zhes pa lus kyi srid pa lte ba nas skyed pas 'jig rten no //
NK063(gu)001:5591: de nas lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo 'dab ma drug cu rtsa bzhi'i thig le bsgoms pas /
NK063(gu)001:5593: zhes pa spyod yul lhar gsal bas lus ngag yid gsum gyi rtog pa mi gnas par byed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5594: de ltar 'khor lo bzhi'i bde ba rim par bsgoms
NK063(gu)001:5595: te rlung la dbang thob cing byang chub kyi sems
NK063(gu)001:5597: 'og sgo nyams su blang bar bya ba ni tshig
NK063(gu)001:5598: bsgyur te gong nas bdud rtsi 'gyur 'gyur zhing zhes
NK063(gu)001:5599: pa / yab yum gyi thig le de thabs kyis zin par byas pas bdud rtsi'o //
NK063(gu)001:5601: zhes pa bde ba'i yon tan no //
NK063(gu)001:5602: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel zhing //
NK063(gu)001:5603: zhes pa thig le slar ldog pa'am /
NK063(gu)001:5604: yang na gsang dbang gi dus su longs spyad pa'i yon tan no //
NK063(gu)001:5605: longs spyod 'byung zhing zhes pa gsang ba'i 'dod yon rdzogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5607: zhes pa gsang dbang bskur bas so //
NK063(gu)001:5609: ces pa nam mkha' la 'gro ba dang kha dog
NK063(gu)001:5610: gsal ba dang tshe ring ba la sogs pa'i yon
NK063(gu)001:5611: tan rnams so // yon tan gzhan yang nam mkha'
NK063(gu)001:5612: rdo rje zhes pa bud med kyi mkha' la rdo
NK063(gu)001:5613: rje bsgoms na skyes par 'gyur ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:5615: zhes pa thig le bde bar 'bar bas rtog pa sreg par byed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5616: chu rgyun 'bab pa'ang de bzhin te //
NK063(gu)001:5617: zhes pa yab yum gyi byang chub sems kyi chu
NK063(gu)001:5618: rgyun thabs kyis zin pa'i yon tan gong bzhin no
NK063(gu)001:5620: zhes thig le'i bde ba rtsa gnas kun tu khyab pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5621: thams cad stongs shing ltung bar 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:5622: zhes pa byang chub sems kyi bde bas rtog pa thams cad mi gnas par byed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5623: dgug dang zhes byang chub sems thig le rtsa gnas nas dbab pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5624: btang dang zhes rdo rje dang pad+ma'i rtse mo ru'o //
NK063(gu)001:5625: bcing dang zhes der gzung thabs kyis thig le gnyis rtse srad de rgyas gdab pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5626: dgrol zhes so sor phye ste ldog pa'i thabs kyis rang gi gnas su ldog pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5627: gso dang zhes klad pa'i thig le bsos te sngon gyi gnas phyi mo dang 'phrad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5628: bsad dang zhes des tha mal gyi rtog pa mi gnas par ro //
NK063(gu)001:5629: 'pham dang zhes rtog pa'i g.yul lo //
NK063(gu)001:5630: rgyal zhes ye shes kyi g.yul lo //
NK063(gu)001:5632: zhes pa sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba thabs lam gyi ting
NK063(gu)001:5633: nge 'dzin 'di las su rung nas bsgrub bya ma
NK063(gu)001:5634: lus pa 'grub par 'gyur ro bya ba'i tha tshig
NK063(gu)001:5635: go // mchog gi dngos grub ni /
NK063(gu)001:5636: gang zhig rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs 'das pa gtso bor bsgrub pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:5637: de ni rnal 'byor gyi mngon sum du phyogs bcu
NK063(gu)001:5638: dus bzhi'i rgyal ba ma lus pa'i bdag nyid sgyu
NK063(gu)001:5639: 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi rnam pa can du
NK063(gu)001:5640: mngon du gyur pa ni bdag don grub pa'i tshul
NK063(gu)001:5641: yin la / de nyid dngos por ma grub ste
NK063(gu)001:5642: chos kyi sku'i rang bzhin las ma g.yos par gdul
NK063(gu)001:5643: bya dag pa la gzugs sku'i gzugs brnyan du yon
NK063(gu)001:5644: tan zad mi shes pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor snang
NK063(gu)001:5645: yin la / bas / gdul bya rang gis 'dod
NK063(gu)001:5646: pa grub pa ni gzhan don mdzad pa'i tshul yin
NK063(gu)001:5647: yin la / bas / no // de la'ang mdo
NK063(gu)001:5648: rgyas su 'jog pa'i 'thad pa tshig mang nyung la
NK063(gu)001:5649: mdzad pa yang yod mod kyi /
NK063(gu)001:5650: 'dir rang don du sangs rgyas pa las rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:5651: gnyis ka'i don grub pa ni lhag par rgyas pa
NK063(gu)001:5653: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u lnga pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5655: // le'u drug pa'i lo rgyus su brjod pa'i skabs su /
NK063(gu)001:5656: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad la nyid
NK063(gu)001:5657: kyi che ba'i dkyil 'khor 'byung bar bzhed nas zhes
NK063(gu)001:5658: pa la / kha cig rgyud drug gi 'gro ba 'di dag ston pa'i 'khor yin nam ma yin /
NK063(gu)001:5659: dang po ltar na 'gro ba rnams ma dag pa ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:5661: gnyis pa ltar na gzhung dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:5662: dngos kyi 'khor ma yin pas nyes pa dang po med la /
NK063(gu)001:5663: brgyud pa'i sgo nas yin pas gzhung dang mi 'gal ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:5665: gang zhig blo che ba cig car bas shes bya
NK063(gu)001:5666: thams cad dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin du rtogs shing
NK063(gu)001:5669: ye shes zhes pa chos thams cad gsal la rtog pa med pa me long lta bu dang /
NK063(gu)001:5670: mnyam rgyu chos can mtshan ma sna tshogs rnams mnyam
NK063(gu)001:5671: pa chos nyid mtshan med du mnyam pa mnyam pa
NK063(gu)001:5672: nyid dang / rang rang gi mtshan nyid ma 'dres pa so sor rtog pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5673: rang rig la yon tan lhun gyis grub pa bya ba grub pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5674: de ltar ye shes bzhi ni shar la sogs pa phyogs bzhi yis mtshon cing /
NK063(gu)001:5675: de dag gcig pa dang tha dad pa la sogs
NK063(gu)001:5676: mtha' gang du yang ma grub par stong pa nyid
NK063(gu)001:5677: kyi mtshon byed du dbus dang lngar brtags te /
NK063(gu)001:5678: de ltar ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor de phyogs su 'dzin pa'i blos bsam pa'i yul las 'das te /
NK063(gu)001:5679: mtha' yas pa'i chos thams cad kyi khyab byed yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:5680: 'o na de lam pa'i bsgom bya ma yin pa 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:5681: blo'i yul du ma grub pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:5683: lhun grub ces pa mtha' bral rtogs pa'i blo la
NK063(gu)001:5684: ltos te chos thams cad ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor
NK063(gu)001:5685: du rang rig la lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5686: ni zhes pa de gang gi yul yin pa ste
NK063(gu)001:5687: 'di ni grub pa mtha' 'dzin gyi rdzogs pa chen
NK063(gu)001:5689: ma h+aa'i lta ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:5690: 'o na gang zhe na ngo bo don gyi rdzogs
NK063(gu)001:5691: pa chen po ste 'bru bsgyur la chos thams cad
NK063(gu)001:5692: ye shes chen po lngar rdzogs pa'i don rtogs shing
NK063(gu)001:5693: / de'i ngang la gnas pa'i phyir rnal 'byor pas
NK063(gu)001:5694: te de'i blo ngo na snang spyod kun rang byung
NK063(gu)001:5695: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:5696: de lta bu'i yul yin la chen po zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:5697: lhag pa ting dkyil las khyad par du gyur pas
NK063(gu)001:5698: so // spyod ces pas lta bas ji ltar rtogs pa bzhin du ste /
NK063(gu)001:5699: ji skad du bcu gcig pa las /
NK063(gu)001:5700: spyod pa ci la'ang thogs med spyod //
NK063(gu)001:5703: de ltar blos ma lcogs shing rim gyis pa'i bsgom bya 'di yin te /
NK063(gu)001:5704: 'di ston pa la bshad tshul nyes pa'i skyon brgyad las /
NK063(gu)001:5705: 'dir mngon par rtogs pa'i rim pa bsgrig ma shes na bdud rtsi ro nyams kyi skyon spangs nas /
NK063(gu)001:5706: bshad tshul legs pa'i yon tan las kyang phrin las
NK063(gu)001:5707: lag tu lon par bya ba'i phyir mngon rtogs las
NK063(gu)001:5709: de'i rgyu mtshan yang rgyud dang lag len 'brel ba bzhi dang ldan te /
NK063(gu)001:5714: de bla ma'i phyag bzhes dang 'brel dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:5716: yongs grags zhes bya ste rgyud gzhung spyi'i rnam gzhag gi lag len gtsor 'dzin pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5717: bka' ma zhes bya ba rang gi bla ma'i phyag bzhes dang zhal gdams gtsor 'dzin pa gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:5719: de la rgyud 'di nas gang la phan gdags pas 'dul ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:5720: gdul dka' drag pos 'dul ba gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:5722: bdud 'dul khro bo'i mngon par rtogs pa gnyis ston no //
NK063(gu)001:5723: de las rgyud 'di'i stod nas zhi ba'i mngon par rtogs pa 'byung la /
NK063(gu)001:5725: ting nge 'dzin sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5726: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5727: ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos dang /
NK063(gu)001:5728: ting nge 'dzin gyi 'jug gi rim pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5729: dang po la bdun te phyag bzhes ltar ro //
NK063(gu)001:5730: gnyis pa ni lam kun gyi sngon du 'gro ba ste de la yang gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:5731: 'di don dam sems bskyed yin te /
NK063(gu)001:5732: de le'u gnyis par gsum du bstan pa'i dang po rang bzhin gzhi'i sems bskyed do //
NK063(gu)001:5736: dang po ni lam rim las /
NK063(gu)001:5737: sgrub pa'i gtsor ni ting 'dzin pas //
NK063(gu)001:5741: mun la snang byung ji bzhin du //
NK063(gu)001:5744: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa dngos la gsum ste /
