NK063(gu)001:5745: ting nge 'dzin gsum bsgom pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5746: dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK063(gu)001:5747: las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK063(gu)001:5749: snang ba la rang rgyud du zhen pa zlog pa'i phyir de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK063(gu)001:5751: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med par //
NK063(gu)001:5752: rtog pa'i dbang sgyur ting 'dzin yin //
NK063(gu)001:5754: stong pa phyogs gcig gis mtha' la zhen pa bzlog
NK063(gu)001:5755: pa'i phyir kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin ni
NK063(gu)001:5757: rtsa ba med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK063(gu)001:5758: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK063(gu)001:5760: de gnyis tha dad du zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK063(gu)001:5762: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK063(gu)001:5763: yi ge yid bzhin rin cen sprin //
NK063(gu)001:5765: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor bsgom pa la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:5766: gzhi'i thabs rten gzhal yas khang /
NK063(gu)001:5767: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i thabs brten pa lha bsgom pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5769: dbang chen yum lnga'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK063(gu)001:5770: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5771: dang po ni rtsa ba'i thabs sems nyid yi ger
NK063(gu)001:5772: gsal ba rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi khyad par las
NK063(gu)001:5773: / 'byung ba lnga'i sa bon gyi yi ge rim par spros te /
NK063(gu)001:5774: de dag las 'od 'phros pas phyi nang gi 'byung
NK063(gu)001:5775: ba der zhen gyi rtog pa sbyangs shing ye shes
NK063(gu)001:5776: kyi 'byung ba'i bcud bsdus pa las /
NK063(gu)001:5777: nam mkha' mthing kha gru gsum dang /
NK063(gu)001:5778: rlung dkyil sngo skya ljang gu dang /
NK063(gu)001:5779: chu dkyil dkar po zlum po dang /
NK063(gu)001:5780: sa dkyil ser po gru bzhi dang /
NK063(gu)001:5781: me dkyil dmar po gru gsum rnams kun tu bzang
NK063(gu)001:5782: mo la sogs yum lnga'i mkha' dbyings rnam par dag
NK063(gu)001:5783: par gsal ba'o // gnyis pa ni rgyu ting le'u
NK063(gu)001:5784: bzhi pa'i a las le'u bdun pa'i b+h+r+aum chad de
NK063(gu)001:5785: 'phros pas rgyal ba mchod cing sems can gyi yul
NK063(gu)001:5786: dang gnas la der zhen pa'i rtog pa sbyangs te
NK063(gu)001:5787: par gsal ba'o // / bsdus pas rgyal ba'i zhing khams dang gzhal yas kyi bcud 'dus pa las /
NK063(gu)001:5788: bdun pa'i skyed sngags kyis gzhal yas bskyed la /
NK063(gu)001:5789: de gsal gdab pa ni 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi zhes
NK063(gu)001:5790: pa la sogs dkyil 'khor don rtags kyis bshad pa
NK063(gu)001:5792: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis kyis brgyan //
NK063(gu)001:5794: kha cig lha bskyed nas brgyan na de yan chad du bskyed par bshad pa med la /
NK063(gu)001:5795: ma bskye par brgyan na le'u bdun pa'i skyed sngags rnams mi dgos par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:5796: lan ni spar khab ltar lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK063(gu)001:5797: kyi cha byad can gyi sprul pa'i 'phro 'dus brgyan
NK063(gu)001:5798: par mngon no // de ltar yin kyang rgyan la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:5802: dang po ni nang gi rgyan gdan sa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis te 'og tu 'chad do //
NK063(gu)001:5803: gnyis pa ni phyi'i rgyan te /
NK063(gu)001:5805: dpag bsam shing dang rin cen 'bar //
NK063(gu)001:5806: yid bzhin nor bu'i rgyan gyis mdzes //
NK063(gu)001:5809: ye nas mnyam nyid mi g.yo'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:5810: ta la'i ljon shing rang bzhin gnas //
NK063(gu)001:5813: zhabs dang ma chags za ra tshags //
NK063(gu)001:5815: thams cad la ni dbang sgyur phyir //
NK063(gu)001:5816: 'jig rten lha chen rnams kyis bskor //
NK063(gu)001:5818: 'o na de dag gis le'u dang po ltar rang
NK063(gu)001:5819: bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor 'og min na yod pa la
NK063(gu)001:5820: brgyan nam / drug pa 'di ltar lhag pa ting dkyil rig pa la bskyed pa la brgyan nam /
NK063(gu)001:5821: dgu pa ltar lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs pa la brgyan zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:5823: de bas na rang bzhan gyis kyang 'di ltar bzhungs shing dri ba yang 'di kho na ltar la /
NK063(gu)001:5824: bsgom pa yang de bzhin no zhes pas gsum char la brgyan la brgyan pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:5825: tha ma ni gang gzhal yas yin pa la ngo bo nyid kyis mdzes par grub byas te /
NK063(gu)001:5826: dper na gser yin la ngo bo nyid kyis ser
NK063(gu)001:5827: pa'am khye'u dang bu dang bu mo 'bras legs par
NK063(gu)001:5828: grub na ngo bo nyid kyis gzugs mdzes pa grub
NK063(gu)001:5829: pa bzhin no // de ltar yang rgya mtsho las /
NK063(gu)001:5830: yon tan lnga yi bdag nyid de //
NK063(gu)001:5831: ma spangs rgyan sogs gzhal yas khang //
NK063(gu)001:5833: de las 'di ni bdag po'i rgyan gdan sar lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis so //
NK063(gu)001:5834: 'o na lha da rung ma grub bo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:5835: rang bzhin grub pa'i dbang du ni lha dang gzhal yas khang la dus snga phyi med de /
NK063(gu)001:5836: dper na dri ma gang yod na kho'i gnas kyang yod pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:5837: 'dir snga phyi ni lam pa blo chung bas dus
NK063(gu)001:5838: gcig tu mi lcogs pa'i dbang du ste phyis 'byung
NK063(gu)001:5840: der gdan ji ltar 'god pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:5841: pho brang gi dbus na 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte
NK063(gu)001:5842: ba dang bcas pa ni chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK063(gu)001:5843: ba'i gdan no // de'i steng du rigs lnga la lnga brtsegs te /
NK063(gu)001:5845: pho brang dbus kyi lte ba la //
NK063(gu)001:5846: mi 'jigs seng ge brgyad dang ldan //
NK063(gu)001:5847: shar gyi lte bar stobs glang ste //
NK063(gu)001:5848: lho ru rdzu 'phrul rta brgyud gding //
NK063(gu)001:5849: nub tu dbang byed rma bya dang //
NK063(gu)001:5850: byang du phrin las shang shang ngo //
NK063(gu)001:5851: zhes pa zhe sdang dag nas mi 'jigs pa bzhi grub pa'i phyir dbus su seng ge dang /
NK063(gu)001:5852: gti mug dag nas stobs bcu dang ldan pa'i phyir shar du glang chen dang /
NK063(gu)001:5853: nga rgyal dag nas rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir lhor rta dang /
NK063(gu)001:5854: 'dod chags dag nas dbang bcu dang ldan pa'i phyir nub tu khyung ste /
NK063(gu)001:5855: 'di la kha cig le'u dang po dang 'od rim
NK063(gu)001:5856: la sogs nas rma byar bshad pa dang 'gal lo
NK063(gu)001:5857: zhe na / ma yin te 'di gnyis mun snang
NK063(gu)001:5858: ltar phan tshun spangs pa dang tsha grang ltar lhan
NK063(gu)001:5859: cig mi gnas pa'i 'gal ba gang yang ma yin
NK063(gu)001:5860: zhe na / no // des na tha dad pa tsam la 'gal ba'i khyab pa med do //
NK063(gu)001:5861: 'o na 'di ji ltar yin na pin tar las /
NK063(gu)001:5862: gsung ni dbang bcu mthar phyin rgyal po'i tshul //
NK063(gu)001:5863: zhes pa mtha' yas kyi de kho na nyid dbang yin la /
NK063(gu)001:5864: dbang gi mtshon byed du de gnyis mtshungs te rma
NK063(gu)001:5865: byas dug dang khyung gis klu dbang du byed pa'i
NK063(gu)001:5866: phyir ro // phrag dog dag nas phrin las bzhi
NK063(gu)001:5867: 'grub pa'i phyir byang du nam mkha' lding ste shang
NK063(gu)001:5868: shang rnams ni sa'i khyad par bgrod pa'i gdan no
NK063(gu)001:5869: phyir ro // // de dag gi bar na 'bru bsgyur te /
NK063(gu)001:5870: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i phyir rin po che'i
NK063(gu)001:5871: khri chen po la de'i steng du nyon mongs pas
NK063(gu)001:5872: ma gos shing gdul bya la thugs rje chags pa'i
NK063(gu)001:5873: phyir pad+ma dang / shes rab rnam par dag pa'i phyir nyi ma dang /
NK063(gu)001:5874: thabs ma 'gags par gsal ba'i phyir zla ba rnams
NK063(gu)001:5875: ni yon tan gyi che ba spyom pa'i gdan no
NK063(gu)001:5876: // sems dpa' yab yum gyi gdan ni gsum brtsegs te /
NK063(gu)001:5878: nyi zla chu skyes gsum brtsegs sems //
NK063(gu)001:5880: rtsibs mchan bzhi dang gru chad bzhi la'o //
NK063(gu)001:5881: kun bzang yab yum la bzhi brtsegs te /
NK063(gu)001:5883: bya byed kun bzang yab yum la //
NK063(gu)001:5884: nyi zla pad+ma rin cen rgyas //
NK063(gu)001:5885: zhes pas glo 'bur shar nub tu'o //
NK063(gu)001:5886: sgo ba la rdo rje brag gi steng du nyi ma dang thub pa la pad+ma rkyang pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:5887: nyi rkyang khro la pad rkyang thub //
NK063(gu)001:5888: ces pas sgo bzhi dang lho byang gi glo 'bur dang khyams kyi zur rnams la'o //
NK063(gu)001:5889: gnyis pa brten pa lha bskyed pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:5890: d+r+wa chung ltar bdag sras gzhan sras su bskyed pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5891: d+r+wa ba 'bring po ltar cho ga gsum gyis bskyed pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5892: d+r+wa ba chen po ltar rdzogs tshul du bskyed pa las /
NK063(gu)001:5893: 'dir 'bring po lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis pa 'di cho ga gsum gyis bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:5895: cho ga gsum gyis lha so so'i sku bskyed pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5897: dkyil 'khor gyi tshad dam che ba bstan pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:5898: dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5901: le'u bzhi pa ltar a nas k+sha'i bar yi ge
NK063(gu)001:5902: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rnams gdan sa rnams su bsgoms
NK063(gu)001:5903: te gsal ba dang 'phros pas sems can gyi ngag
NK063(gu)001:5904: gi sgrib pa sbyangs shing rgyal ba la gsung mnyes
NK063(gu)001:5905: pa'i p+au dza phul nas de'i yon tan nam bcud
NK063(gu)001:5906: bsdus de yig 'bru de dag 'od phung du gyur
NK063(gu)001:5907: pa las / gnyis pa thugs phyag mtshan gyi cho
NK063(gu)001:5908: ga ni badz+ra tsakra la sogs thugs mtshan gyi skyed
NK063(gu)001:5909: sngags kyis rdo rje 'khor lo la sogs phyag mtshan
NK063(gu)001:5910: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:5911: de las gong ltar 'phros pas sems can gyi yid
NK063(gu)001:5912: sgrib sbyangs shing rgyal ba la thugs mnyes pa'i p+au
NK063(gu)001:5913: dza phul nas thugs kyi yon tan nam bcud bsdus
NK063(gu)001:5914: te / phyag mtshan la thim pas de dag 'od phung du gyur pa las /
NK063(gu)001:5915: le'u bdun pa'i skyed sngags rnams kyis rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi sku gsal bar bskyed do //
NK063(gu)001:5916: gnyis pa gsal gdab pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:5917: gong du bkod pa'i gdan rnams la bzhi bcu rtsa
NK063(gu)001:5918: gnyis kyi sku rgyan cha lugs dang bcas pa yongs
NK063(gu)001:5920: dang po bzhugs tshul bzhugs gnas dang bcas pa gsal gdab ste /
NK063(gu)001:5921: sems dpa' tshul zhes pa gzhung gi cha la gnas pa 'chad pa po'i gnyen gyis bshad de /
NK063(gu)001:5922: dang po rigs lnga yab yum dang kun bzang yab yum rnams rdzogs pa'i skyil krung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:5923: sems dpa' yab yum ni 'bab tshul lam phyed skyil
NK063(gu)001:5924: krung ste yab rnams g.yon bskums g.yas brkyangs la yum
NK063(gu)001:5926: sgo ba dor thabs la thub pa rnams drang por bzhengs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5928: 'khor lo zhes pa rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang lnga
NK063(gu)001:5929: la rgyal mchog rigs lnga po dang de dag gi
NK063(gu)001:5931: dang zhes pa ma smos gzhan ston pa'i sgra ste
NK063(gu)001:5932: thugs kyi sems dpa' rnams gang du dgod ce na
NK063(gu)001:5934: spyan snga'i glo 'bur mdzes pa la //
NK063(gu)001:5935: lag na rdo rje sngo skya'i mdog /
NK063(gu)001:5936: rang rtags rdo rje rtse gsum pa //
NK063(gu)001:5937: gtso bo nyid dang mthun pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5938: zhes pas glo 'bur la dgod zer ba ni ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:5940: lhag pa'i ye shes glo 'bur zhes gsungs pas //
NK063(gu)001:5941: de ltar na lhag pa ma yin par 'gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:5944: sems dpa' gtso bo'i g.yas phyogs shar lho'i rtsibs mchan
NK063(gu)001:5945: la sa'i snying po btsun mo dang bcas pa bzhugs
NK063(gu)001:5948: rtsibs mchan la thugs kyi sems dpa' bzhi ste zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:5949: gtso bo zhal shar du gzigs pa'i g.yas shar lho'i rtsibs mchan nas brtsams te /
NK063(gu)001:5950: der mthong ba mig gi rnam par shes pa sa'i snying po'o //
NK063(gu)001:5951: 'o na thos zhes pa shar lho'i rting la lho
NK063(gu)001:5952: nub 'ong bas der mthong ba'i rjes su thos pa
NK063(gu)001:5953: phyag na rdo rje mi 'ong bar /
NK063(gu)001:5954: sa snying gi rjes su der nam snying 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:5956: gral ni lugs su mthun pa kho na ste rim pa ni yi ge'i dbang du smos pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:5957: zhes sa snying gi rjes su lho nub tu nam snying 'god par bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:5958: snom pa la sogs go rim bzhi dang dang gru
NK063(gu)001:5959: chad la gsung gi sems dpa' yab yum ste gzhung
NK063(gu)001:5960: brtag go // bar khyams la ni thub pa drug ste de'i dgod rim ni /
NK063(gu)001:5961: shar lho lha la lho phyogs mi //
NK063(gu)001:5962: lho nub nub byang yi dwags byol //
NK063(gu)001:5963: byang dang byang shar lha min dmyal //
NK063(gu)001:5965: dang zhes pa gzhan yang khyams la dkyil 'khor gyi
NK063(gu)001:5966: mdun shar dang rgyab nub tu rim pa bzhin byed
NK063(gu)001:5967: pa po kun tu bzang po dang bya ba mo
NK063(gu)001:5968: kun tu bzang mo dag ni gnas par bstan no
NK063(gu)001:5969: // 'di la kha cig dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo log pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:5970: kun po yab yum khyams la bzhugs pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:5971: rgyud 'chad pa'i tshe gtso bo khyams la bzhugs pa'i phyir log zer ram /
NK063(gu)001:5972: dkyil 'khor du 'god pa'i tshe gtso bo khyams la bzhugs pa log zer /
NK063(gu)001:5973: dang po ltar na rtags ma grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:5974: ston pa pho brang lte ba la bzhugs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:5975: der bzhugs par ma grub ce na /
NK063(gu)001:5976: ji skad du rgya mtsho las /
NK063(gu)001:5977: pho brang dbus kyi lte ba la //
NK063(gu)001:5978: bdag po kun bzang 'khor lo bskor //
NK063(gu)001:5980: gnyis pa ltar na kun bzang yab yum khyams la
NK063(gu)001:5981: bzhugs kyang gtso bo log pa ma yin na ci
NK063(gu)001:5982: 'gal te / de'i tshe gtso bo mi bskyod pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:5983: de yin par ma grub ce na /
NK063(gu)001:5985: ji skad du le lag las /
NK063(gu)001:5986: rdo rje sems dpa' dkyil nyid de //
NK063(gu)001:5987: rigs bzhi lha dang lha mo 'khor //
NK063(gu)001:5989: des na de dag ma brtags pa'i sgro skur yin gyi /
NK063(gu)001:5990: zhal gdams su kun po yab yum khyams la bzhugs pa'i dgos pa gsum yod de /
NK063(gu)001:5991: dgos pa dang po ni thub pa drug gi 'byung khungs yin te /
NK063(gu)001:5992: ji skad du rdo rje las /
NK063(gu)001:5993: bde chen rnam dag sku gsung thugs //
NK063(gu)001:5994: de rtogs pa las thub drug 'byung //
NK063(gu)001:5996: gnyis pa ni dper na lha khang gi phugs 'gel
NK063(gu)001:5997: ba'i ph+y+wa mkhan de phyir bskyed de bzo'i khyad par
NK063(gu)001:5998: rnams legs mi legs lta ba ltar /
NK063(gu)001:5999: 'dir sras kyi tshogs bkod pa la rim par mdzes
NK063(gu)001:6000: mi mdzes gzigs pa'i tshul du khyams la bzhugs so
NK063(gu)001:6001: // tha ma ni sbyang bya 'jig rten pa'i gleng gzhi dang mthun te /
NK063(gu)001:6002: 'jig rten na bu tsha la khang pa bzang po
NK063(gu)001:6003: byin nas pha ma khang pa ngan par sdod pa
NK063(gu)001:6005: de dag ltar na shugs las gtso bos 'khor byas par mngon pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:6006: yang kha cig rtog pa'i tshe yul dang yul can gnyis su 'dus la /
NK063(gu)001:6007: de dag pa dbyings dang ye shes yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:6008: de ni kun po yab yum yin pa'i phyir khyams la bzhugs zer ba ni ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:6009: de ltar yin pas khyams la shar nub tu bzhugs pa'i rgyu mtshan ci yang med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:6010: yang na khyams la bzhugs pa'i kun bzang yab yum 'di gtso bo yin par ma grub pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:6012: kun tu bzang po'i bye brag lnga las /
NK063(gu)001:6013: rang bzhin kun tu bzang po ni shes bya'i khyab byed sems kyi gnas lugs yin pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:6014: ston pa kun tu bzang po ni de mngon du
NK063(gu)001:6015: byas pa'i ye shes te le'u dang po dang gnyis
NK063(gu)001:6016: par bstan pa ltar rgyud kyi byed pa po yin
NK063(gu)001:6017: la / sangs rgyas kun tu bzang por grags pa ni stong rtsa gnyis kyi ya gyal yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:6018: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po ni sems dpa'i ya gyal yin te /
NK063(gu)001:6019: de dang 'di ni longs sku kun tu bzang po zhes bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:6020: de gnyis dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor gyi lha yin pa'i phyir snyam du sems so //
NK063(gu)001:6021: gnyis pa thugs phyag mtshan ni /
NK063(gu)001:6023: thub pa dang yum rnams ma gtogs pa zhal gsum phyag drug tu bshad de /
NK063(gu)001:6024: de'i dbang du phyag mtshan yang /
NK063(gu)001:6027: dril bu pad+ma rin po che //
NK063(gu)001:6030: mi bskyod pa'i g.yas dang po rdo rje dang g.yon
NK063(gu)001:6031: dang po dril bu ste de gnyis rgya bcings shing
NK063(gu)001:6033: gzhan gang gnas su rdo rje shes //
NK063(gu)001:6035: rigs bzhi la g.yas rang rtags 'khor lo dang rin
NK063(gu)001:6036: po che dang pad+ma dang ral gri rnams 'dzin pa
NK063(gu)001:6037: dang / g.yon pa kun mthun par dril bu ste gong bzhin thugs kar rgya bcings pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6038: g.yas kyi bar pa bzhi ni rim pa bzhin rdo rje 'khor lo rat+na pad+ma'o //
NK063(gu)001:6039: de bzhin g.yon gyi bar ma bzhi yang rim pa bzhin pad+ma 'khor lo rat+na rdo rje'o //
NK063(gu)001:6040: g.yas mtha' ma bzhi yang rim bzhin rat+na rdo rje 'khor lo pad+ma'o //
NK063(gu)001:6041: de bzhin g.yon mtha' ma bzhi yang rim pa bzhin 'khor lo rin chen pad+ma ral gri'o //
NK063(gu)001:6042: de dag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i dbang du rdo
NK063(gu)001:6043: rje la sogs rang rtags thugs kar 'dzin cing dril
NK063(gu)001:6046: ut+pala klu shing zhes pas sngon la thugs kyi sems dpa' dang po'i phyag mtshan nas mi smos par /
NK063(gu)001:6047: gsung gi sems dpa' mtha' ma'i phyag mtshan nas smos pa'i rgyu mtshan gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:6048: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis don mdzad pa'i sngon du byams snying rje 'gro la /
NK063(gu)001:6049: de shes rab las skyes pa'i phyir sngon du 'jam dpal gyi phyag mtshan nas smos pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:6051: rin cen myu gur ral gri 'bar //
NK063(gu)001:6052: pad+ma dkar po rdo rje che //
NK063(gu)001:6053: ut+pala klu shing po ti snye //
NK063(gu)001:6054: gzugs mdzes rin cen phreng ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:6055: pi wang gar bsgyur pog me dang //
NK063(gu)001:6056: byug pa la sogs rim shes bya //
NK063(gu)001:6058: sems dpa' 'di dag kyang zhal gsum phyag drug pa'i dbang du 'di ltar /
NK063(gu)001:6059: sa'i snying po g.yas gsum rim bzhin rin cen myu gu rdo rje ral gri dang /
NK063(gu)001:6060: g.yon dang po kun mthun par dril bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:6061: 'og ma gnyis pad dkar rdo rje'o //
NK063(gu)001:6062: nam snying g.yas gsum ral gri rat+na rin myug dang /
NK063(gu)001:6063: g.yon gnyis pad dkar rdo rje'o //
NK063(gu)001:6064: spyan ras g.yas gsum pad dkar de dmar rin myug dang /
NK063(gu)001:6065: g.yon gnyis ral gri pad dkar ro //
NK063(gu)001:6066: phyag rdor g.yas gsum rdo rje klu shing ral gri /
NK063(gu)001:6067: g.yon gnyis pad dkar rin snye'o //
NK063(gu)001:6068: byams pa g.yas gsum klu shing rdo rje po ti dang /
NK063(gu)001:6069: g.yon gnyis rin snye ut+pala lo //
NK063(gu)001:6070: sgrib sel g.yas gsum po ti rat+na klu shing dang /
NK063(gu)001:6071: g.yon gnyis rin snye ut+pala lo //
NK063(gu)001:6072: kun bzang g.yas gsum rin snye pad dmar klu shing dang /
NK063(gu)001:6073: g.yon gnyis po ti ut+pala lo //
NK063(gu)001:6074: 'jam dpal g.yas gsum ut+pala ral gri klu shing dang /
NK063(gu)001:6075: g.yon gnyis po ti rin snye'o //
NK063(gu)001:6076: 'di dag kyang zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i dbang du g.yas g.yon dang po'i phyag mtshan gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:6077: 'o na 'dir ut+pala klu shing zhes sems dpa'i phyag
NK063(gu)001:6078: mtshan gnyis las mi smos pa'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe
NK063(gu)001:6079: na / sems dpa'i phyag mtshan gzhan rnams rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan du 'dus te /
NK063(gu)001:6080: rin cen snye dang rin myug kyang rat+na'i bye brag
NK063(gu)001:6081: yin la gnyis po ma 'dus pas smos pa yin
NK063(gu)001:6082: no // 'on kyang la sogs pa zhes pa sogs
NK063(gu)001:6083: khongs su gzhan du sbas pa bsdus pa yin te
NK063(gu)001:6084: no // / de yang spyir gzhung gzhan du dang /
NK063(gu)001:6086: skabs gzhan du sbas pa las /
NK063(gu)001:6087: 'di le'u gzhan brgyad par sbas pas der ston no //
NK063(gu)001:6088: sgo ba'i phyag mtshan kyang zhal gsum phyag drug pa'i dbang du /
NK063(gu)001:6090: gri mgo rdo rje tho rgya gram //
NK063(gu)001:6091: lcags kyu zhags pa s+pho ta hoh /
NK063(gu)001:6093: phyag gnyis pa'i dbang du gong ltar ro //
NK063(gu)001:6094: kun tu bzang po yang zhal gsum phyag drug pa'i dbang du /
NK063(gu)001:6097: ye shes rtse lnga chos khams dril //
NK063(gu)001:6098: thugs kar bstan pa nyid du bshad //
NK063(gu)001:6100: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i dbang du mnyam gzhag rdo rjes mtshan pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6101: thub pa ni zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa kho na ste /
NK063(gu)001:6103: thub chen nges par phyag gnyis shes //
NK063(gu)001:6104: zhes gsungs shing phyag mtshan yang /
NK063(gu)001:6106: gseg par pi wang go mtshon sdeb //
NK063(gu)001:6107: sgrom gtod po ti chos 'chad tshul //
NK063(gu)001:6108: med dpung bum par shes par bya //
NK063(gu)001:6110: yum rnams ni zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa 'ba' zhig ste /
NK063(gu)001:6112: g.yas pa thabs kyis yab la 'khyud //
NK063(gu)001:6115: gsum pa sku mdog tshul dang bcas pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:6116: sku mdog la rang bzhin gyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:6118: rigs ma nges pa'i dang gsum du bzhed do //
NK063(gu)001:6120: le'u dang por bstan la phyi ma gnyis gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:6121: tshul ni dgu ste gzhung brtag cing /
NK063(gu)001:6122: bye brag tu ldem zhes pa ni thub pa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:6123: de la 'khril ba med pas lha thams cad la
NK063(gu)001:6124: tshul brgyad brgyad khyab byed du yod pa yin no
NK063(gu)001:6125: // dkyil 'khor gyi tshad dam che ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:6126: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la mtha' dbus dang phyi
NK063(gu)001:6127: nang dang rgya khyon la sogs dang bral bas mnyam
NK063(gu)001:6128: pa nyid du gnas pa'i don de rig pa la
NK063(gu)001:6130: gnyis su med par gnas pa'i don shes bya'i khyab byed yin la /
NK063(gu)001:6131: de cig car bas blo la gsal ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:6132: de ltar rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor de blo dman
NK063(gu)001:6133: pa'am rim gyis pa'i spyod yul min pas bsam yas
NK063(gu)001:6134: so // de rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pa'i phyir lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6135: 'di ni lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor 'di'i tshad du 'chad kyang /
NK063(gu)001:6136: de ma yin par sems te /
NK063(gu)001:6137: rang dkyil shes bya la grub pa'i don 'di blo
NK063(gu)001:6138: chen po cig car ba'i bsgom bya yin pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:6139: ro // 'o na lhag pa ting dkyil gyi tshad gang yin zhe na de ni /
NK063(gu)001:6140: le'u dgu pa las ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:6141: yang na rgyang grags dpag tshad dam //
NK063(gu)001:6142: nam mkha' dbyings ni bsam yas par //
NK063(gu)001:6145: rig pas dpags pa'i tshad du'o //
NK063(gu)001:6146: zhes pa de yin par sems so //
NK063(gu)001:6147: de nas le'u bdun pa ltar dbang bskur zhing byin
NK063(gu)001:6148: gyis brlabs nas de yan chad kyis dkyil 'khor bsgom
NK063(gu)001:6149: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi yan lag rdzogs pa yin
NK063(gu)001:6150: te / de'i mtshan nyid ni ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK063(gu)001:6151: khyad par gang zhig cho ga yan lag gis mtshan
NK063(gu)001:6152: bcas lha'i skur gsal ba zhig yin no //
NK063(gu)001:6153: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa sku'i dkyil 'khor
NK063(gu)001:6154: ni mtshan nyid dang phrin las gnyis gzhung brtags la
NK063(gu)001:6155: / 'grub tshul la byang chub sems dpa'i lam nas ji ltar grub ce na /
NK063(gu)001:6156: sgrib pa sbyong zhing 'bras bu thob tshul la ngag don lnga ste /
NK063(gu)001:6157: sgrib pa de rten gang la brten te sbyang ba'i yul dang /
NK063(gu)001:6158: de des sbyong tshul gyi dpe dang /
NK063(gu)001:6159: sbyong ba po gang zag gang gis ngos zin pa'i tshul dang /
NK063(gu)001:6160: gang sbyang bya sgrib pa'i ngo bo dang /
NK063(gu)001:6161: ji ltar sbyangs pas dag pa'i yon tan no //
NK063(gu)001:6163: rgyu'i theg pa'i lugs kyis rang don chos sku thob nas gzhan don gzugs sku gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:6165: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni rnam par snang mdzad lta bu ste /
NK063(gu)001:6166: de ni nges pa lnga dang ldan pa'i tshul yin te /
NK063(gu)001:6168: sku de nyid mtshan dper nges pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:6170: mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs //
NK063(gu)001:6173: mtshan ni sum cu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK063(gu)001:6174: dpe byad brgyad cu'i bdag nyid 'di //
NK063(gu)001:6176: gnas nges pa ni gong du /
NK063(gu)001:6177: 'og min bla med gnas mchog ni //
NK063(gu)001:6178: zhes pa dbang phyug chen po'i 'og min te /
NK063(gu)001:6180: 'og min gnas ni nyams dga' bar //
NK063(gu)001:6181: yang dag sangs rgyas zhes gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:6182: 'khor nges pa ni yang 'og na byang chub sems dpa' 'khor dang 'phags pa'i tshogs rnams te /
NK063(gu)001:6183: kun byed le'u bcu pa las /
NK063(gu)001:6184: longs spyod rdzogs pa sku yi 'khor bstan pa //
NK063(gu)001:6185: mos spyod bzhi yi sa las 'das pa ste //
NK063(gu)001:6186: dang po rab tu dga' ba'i sa mnan nas //
NK063(gu)001:6187: bcu pa chos kyi sprin gyi par zhes gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:6188: de dag la chos ston pa'i tshul yang lha mi'i
NK063(gu)001:6189: ston pa gsung dbyangs yan lag dang bcas pa'i sgo
NK063(gu)001:6190: nas chos ston pa de bzhin 'bru bsgyur te 'dir
NK063(gu)001:6191: longs sku ni tshig tu mi smra ste /
NK063(gu)001:6192: 'o na gang gis ston zhe na longs sku'i gsung
NK063(gu)001:6193: de ni gzhan las mchog tu gyur pa yin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6194: phyir sku'i brda yis go bar ston pa yin te
NK063(gu)001:6196: de bzhin gshegs pa la la ni spyan phye bas so //
NK063(gu)001:6197: la la ni btsums pas so //
NK063(gu)001:6198: la la ni phyag brkyangs pas so //
NK063(gu)001:6199: la la ni bskums pas so //
NK063(gu)001:6200: la la ni btsun mo dang bcas pas so //
NK063(gu)001:6201: la la ni btsun mo med pas so zhes gsungs pa'i bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:6202: chos nges pa ni theg pa chen po rnams kho na ste /
NK063(gu)001:6204: theg chen nye bar longs spyod phyir //
NK063(gu)001:6205: thub pa'i longs spyod rdzogs skur 'dod //
NK063(gu)001:6207: dus nges pa ni 'khor gyis go ba'i tshul la 'jal bar ston par bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:6208: de ba'i ngos nas chos ston pa'i dus kyi rtog pa dang bral la /
NK063(gu)001:6209: gdul bya'i ngos nas ji srid 'khor ba ma stongs kyi bar du ste /
NK063(gu)001:6211: yid bzhin nor bu lta bur rnam mi rtog /
NK063(gu)001:6212: 'gro grol bar du 'jig rten 'byor slad rtag /
NK063(gu)001:6214: yang kha cig na re 'dir gleng gzhi gcig byung
NK063(gu)001:6215: bas rgyud 'byung ba khyad par can gyi yin na
NK063(gu)001:6217: bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i yin na gsum pa'i stod dang zlos la /
NK063(gu)001:6218: gdul bya dgos ched kyi yin na bco lnga pa dang zlos par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:6219: de dag dang mi zlos te /
NK063(gu)001:6220: 'di gleng gzhi rang ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:6221: 'o na phun sum tshogs pa tshang ba 'di ci yin zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:6222: 'di ni byang chub sems dpa' rnams sa bcu'i spang
NK063(gu)001:6223: bya dang sgrib pa sbyong tshul smos pa yin gyi
NK063(gu)001:6224: / ston 'khor gnas la sogs pa tshang ba thams
NK063(gu)001:6225: cad la gleng gzhi yin pa'i khyab pa med do
NK063(gu)001:6226: / // gal te yod na ha cang thal te /
NK063(gu)001:6227: le'u dgu pa dang bcu gcig pa'i tshogs sgrub pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6228: tshe phun sum tshogs pa lnga la sogs kyang der
NK063(gu)001:6231: rang gi byad lta bar 'dod pa la me long bstan pas bzhin gyi gzugs brnyan snang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:6232: snang ba des tshig bsgyur te byad bzhin dngos kyi
NK063(gu)001:6233: dri ma la sogs mdog ngan thams cad shugs la
NK063(gu)001:6234: sel lo // des na sgrib pa sbyong ba'i tshul
NK063(gu)001:6235: ni me long la bltas pas rang gi byad bzhin
NK063(gu)001:6236: gyi skyon mthong ba bzhin du ston pa'i sku mthong
NK063(gu)001:6237: ba tsam gyis rang gi sgrib pa ngos zin pa
NK063(gu)001:6238: sel lo // yin no // gsum pa de ngos zin pa'i tshul ni /
NK063(gu)001:6239: 'khor gyis zhes pa gong gi 'khor nges pa sa dang po pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams te /
NK063(gu)001:6240: ji skad du lang kar gshegs pa las /
NK063(gu)001:6241: sa dang po'i byang chub sems dpa' de la longs
NK063(gu)001:6242: spyod rdzogs pa skus ting nge 'dzin gyis byin gyis
NK063(gu)001:6243: brlabs nas / theg pa chen po rab tu snang
NK063(gu)001:6244: ba ces bya ba sa dang po na rang gis
NK063(gu)001:6245: mthong ba'i chos nyid ting nge 'dzin gyis snyoms par
NK063(gu)001:6247: de ni byin brlabs gnyis las dang po ting nge 'dzin gyi byin brlabs yin no //
NK063(gu)001:6248: ting nge 'dzin la zhugs ma thag tu phyogs bcu'i
NK063(gu)001:6249: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yis zhal bstan nas phyag
NK063(gu)001:6250: gis dbang bskur bas sa dang po pa de gzhan
NK063(gu)001:6251: gyis don byed nus pa'i snying rje'i snying po dang
NK063(gu)001:6252: rdzu 'phrul dang ldan par gyur to //
NK063(gu)001:6253: zhes pas de ni byin brlabs gnyis las gnyis pa
NK063(gu)001:6254: zhal nas phyag gis dbang bskur ba'i byin brlabs so
NK063(gu)001:6255: // de ltar byin brlabs gnyis kyis zhal mthong zhing
NK063(gu)001:6256: sgrib pa ngos zin pa ni bzhin gyi skyon lta
NK063(gu)001:6257: bar 'dod pas me long la blta ba de bzhin
NK063(gu)001:6258: du sa dang po pa des longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6259: sku la ltos pas sku de la bltas na rang
NK063(gu)001:6260: gi rgyud la sgrib pa dpag tu med pa yod
NK063(gu)001:6261: par shes pa ste gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:6262: de pa ni ye shes sgyu ma'i sku skye 'jig med cing /
NK063(gu)001:6263: sems dpa'i lus smon lam las grub pa skye 'jig can du 'dug pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:6264: de pa gcig dang du ma dang bral ba yin la /
NK063(gu)001:6265: sems dpa' ni rgyud gcig gis bsdus pa yin pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:6266: de pa kha sbyor la gnas kyang mi dag la
NK063(gu)001:6267: sems dpa' rnams thabs kyis ma zin na 'khrul par
NK063(gu)001:6268: 'gyur ba dang / de pa ni mnyam par bzhag ma bzhag gnyis dang bral la /
NK063(gu)001:6269: sems dpa' ni mnyam par 'jog dgos pa'i phyir sgrib par ngos zin no //
NK063(gu)001:6270: bzhi pa sgrib pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK063(gu)001:6271: sa dang po'i byang chub sems dpa' des zag bcas mthong spang gi sgrib pa sbyangs zin mod kyang /
NK063(gu)001:6272: sgom spang la sogs lam gong ma'i sgrib byed du
NK063(gu)001:6273: gyur pa gting dpag tu med pa rnams ma smras
NK063(gu)001:6274: kyang go ba me long la bltas pa bzhin du
NK063(gu)001:6275: de pa'i sku la bltas pas sgrib pa ji ltar
NK063(gu)001:6276: snang ba ni / 'di ltar za ma tog bkod pa las /
NK063(gu)001:6277: sa dang po na chos dang gang zag la mtshan
NK063(gu)001:6278: ma can du mngon par zhen cing 'khor ba dang
NK063(gu)001:6279: ngan song gi nyon mongs pa la 'jigs pa dang
NK063(gu)001:6280: / gnyis pa na ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par
NK063(gu)001:6281: bzhag pa'i ro la sred cing chos rnam par dag
NK063(gu)001:6283: gsum par 'khor ba la shin tu skyo zhing mya ngan las 'das pa la sred pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:6284: bzhi par 'du byed kyi rgyu ba mngon du gyur
NK063(gu)001:6285: pa la rmongs shing mtshan ma sbom po la mngon
NK063(gu)001:6287: lnga par 'khor ba la shin tu skyo zhing mya
NK063(gu)001:6288: ngan las 'das pa la mngon par gzhol ba'i dang
NK063(gu)001:6289: / drug par mtshan ma phra mo mngon du gyur
NK063(gu)001:6290: zhing mtshan ma med pa yid la byed pa'i dang
NK063(gu)001:6291: / / bdun par mtshan med la ched du rtsol
NK063(gu)001:6292: zhing mtshan mar 'dzin pa la dbang ma thob pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6293: / / dang / brgyad par gang chos ston pa
NK063(gu)001:6294: dang tshig dang yi ge tshad med pa la mkhas
NK063(gu)001:6295: par ma gyur zhing spobs pa la dbang mthob pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6296: / / dang / dang / dgu par mngon par
NK063(gu)001:6297: shes pa chen po la dbang sgyur ba ma thob
NK063(gu)001:6298: cig don dang las gsang ba phra mo la mkhas
NK063(gu)001:6300: bcu par spyod yul shin tu cha phra ba thams
NK063(gu)001:6301: cad la shes bya'i sgrib pas rmongs shing nyon mongs
NK063(gu)001:6302: shin tu cha phra ba'i bag la nyal gyis rmongs
NK063(gu)001:6304: mtha' ma des sbyangs pas dag pa'i yon tan ni /
NK063(gu)001:6305: rang rang gi sa gong ma la sgrib byed ngos
NK063(gu)001:6306: zin pa de nas longs sku'i byin rlabs re res
NK063(gu)001:6307: sa gnyis pa nas bcu pa'i bar du rtogs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6308: ye shes re re shar bas yon tan rnams rim
NK063(gu)001:6309: gyis thob cing sbyang bya rnams rim gyis 'byang ba'o
NK063(gu)001:6310: // yon tan ni gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:6311: sa dang po'i byang chub sems dpa' la yon tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:6312: 'di ltar sangs rgyas brgya'i zhal mthong //
NK063(gu)001:6315: sngon dang phyi ma'i bskal pa brgyar ye shes la 'jug /
NK063(gu)001:6317: ting nge 'dzin brgya la mnyam par 'jog /
NK063(gu)001:6318: 'jig rten gyi khams brgya g.yo zhing snang bar byed /
NK063(gu)001:6319: sems can brgya smin par byed /
NK063(gu)001:6324: sa gnyis pa la de dag stong phrag bcu gnyis pas lhag pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:6325: de ltar zhig khams grangs med 'bum phrag bcu'i rdul
NK063(gu)001:6326: phran gyi grangs dang mnyam par 'gyur ba ni bcu
NK063(gu)001:6327: pa'i bar ro // de'i 'bras bu ni bla med
NK063(gu)001:6328: ces pa 'dod rgyal du smra ba ste kun tu
NK063(gu)001:6329: pa'i bar ro // 'od do // byang ba ni
NK063(gu)001:6330: gong gi spang bya rnams yin la chub pa ni
NK063(gu)001:6331: gong gi sa'i yon tan rnams so //
NK063(gu)001:6332: de thob pas yang dag ni 'og gi sku gsum thob pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6334: gnyis pa des thob pa'i 'bras bu rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK063(gu)001:6335: nam mkha' ltar rten sku gsum dang //
NK063(gu)001:6336: zla ba ltar brten pa ye shes bzhi dang /
NK063(gu)001:6337: de'i gzugs brnyan ltar mdzad pa phrin las dang bcas pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6338: dang po ni chos sku zhes pa dag pa gnyis
NK063(gu)001:6339: su zhi zhing bral ba dang smin pa'i yon tan
NK063(gu)001:6340: thams cad kyi rten byed pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:6341: rgya mtsho ltar zab pas blos dpag tu med cing tshig gis brjod du med pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6342: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni gong ltar nges pa
NK063(gu)001:6343: lnga dang ldan zhing yon tan zad med 'byung ba
NK063(gu)001:6344: rin cen gyi gter ltar zag med kyi bde bas
NK063(gu)001:6346: sprul pa'i sku ni gdal bya dang mthun par sna tshogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:6347: nor bu'i dgos 'dod ltar byed pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'dod pa rnams grub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6348: gnyis pa brten pa ye shes ni //
NK063(gu)001:6349: rtog med du gzugs sku gnyis kyi yon tan du gsal ba ni me long lta bu ste /
NK063(gu)001:6351: me long ye shes rtog pa med //
NK063(gu)001:6352: shes bya kun la ma rmongs pa //
NK063(gu)001:6354: ji srid zhi ba'i mtha' la mi gnas shing chos
NK063(gu)001:6355: dbyings rtogs pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes te
NK063(gu)001:6356: / mi gnas zhi bar bzhugs pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:6357: mnyam nyid ye shes yin par 'dod //
NK063(gu)001:6359: chos thams cad kyi rang rang gi mtshan nyid ji
NK063(gu)001:6360: snyed pa dag thugs su chud pa ni so sor
NK063(gu)001:6362: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes ni //
NK063(gu)001:6363: shes bya kun la rtag mi thogs //
NK063(gu)001:6365: gdul bya'i don ji ltar 'dod pa rnams grub pa ni bya ba grub pa'i ye shes te /
NK063(gu)001:6366: dpag med bsam yas sprul pa yis //
NK063(gu)001:6367: sems can don kun grub par mdzad //
NK063(gu)001:6369: gsum pa mdzad pa phrin las ni /
NK063(gu)001:6373: dang po ni rtog pa dang rtsol ba med pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:6375: rnam par rtog med lhun grub par //
NK063(gu)001:6376: 'dod pa thams cad yongs skong byed //
NK063(gu)001:6378: gnyis pa ni gang la gang gis 'dul ba ltar snang ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:6379: 'gro la phan pa sna tshogs dag /
NK063(gu)001:6380: mnyam du mdzad pa'i sku de ni //
NK063(gu)001:6382: mtha' ma ni ji srid 'khor ba ma stongs kyi bar du 'gro don sgrub pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:6386: sngags kyi lam gyis 'bras bu 'grub tshul ni /
NK063(gu)001:6387: tshig bsgyur te 'og nas thabs zhes pa lam mtshan
NK063(gu)001:6388: nyid gsum gyis ji ltar nyams su len pa'i thabs
NK063(gu)001:6389: dang / shes rab ces pa yang dag rtogs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6390: shes rab kyis 'ching ba la spyad kyang mi gos
NK063(gu)001:6392: sa'i mchog ces pa de gong gi kun tu 'od las khyad par du gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:6393: gong nas de la mtshan bzang po so gnyis dag
NK063(gu)001:6394: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu ni thun mong dang
NK063(gu)001:6395: thun min gsal ba thams cad rdzogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6396: de'i tshe 'di ltar snang ba'i spyod yul kun ye
NK063(gu)001:6397: shes kyi dkyil 'khor du dag pas ma d+ha la
NK063(gu)001:6398: zhes bya'o // des ma 'gags pa bsod nams dang
NK063(gu)001:6399: de ltar ma dmigs pa ye shes te tshogs chen
NK063(gu)001:6400: po gnyis kyang yongs su rdzogs shing gnyis su med
NK063(gu)001:6401: par ye shes la ye shes rol par spyod pa
NK063(gu)001:6402: de la sogs pa che ba'i yon tan mtha' yas
NK063(gu)001:6403: mchog dang ldan pa ni 'khor lo tshogs chen te
NK063(gu)001:6404: zhes bya'o // / de ltar thob tshul sangs rgyas kyis sa gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:6405: de lta thob pa 'bras bu'i ngo bo ni sku lnga ste /
NK063(gu)001:6406: skye shi la sogs pa 'ching ba mtha' dag gi
NK063(gu)001:6407: bsgribs g.yogs dang bral ba ni skye ba med pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6408: don mngon du byas pa chos sku'o //
NK063(gu)001:6409: de la 'pho 'gyur med pas g.yung drung yin la /
NK063(gu)001:6410: sku zhes pa de 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan ma lus pa'i rten byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:6411: 'dir kha cig g.yung drung bzhes pas bon yin no zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:6412: phag mo mngon 'byung gi rgyud kyang bon du 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:6414: g.yung drung 'khyil ba'i phyag rgya las //
NK063(gu)001:6417: khyab pa med na 'dir yang mtshungs la /
NK063(gu)001:6422: zla gam lta bur nye bar brgyan pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6423: zhegs gsungs pa yang de ltar 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:6424: dkyus lhag ma rnams gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:6425: yang rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin dkyil 'khor gyi skabs 'dir /
NK063(gu)001:6426: sku yi phyag rgya che mchog ni //
NK063(gu)001:6427: zhes sku lnga bshad pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:6428: chos sku dpag med brjod du med //
NK063(gu)001:6429: ces sku gsum bshad pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:6430: skye shi med pa g.yung drung sku //
NK063(gu)001:6431: zhes sku lnga bshad pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:6432: de ltar sku lnga lan gnyis dang sku gsum rnams zlos so zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:6433: dang po ni rang rig la sku lngar grub tshul yin la /
NK063(gu)001:6434: gnyis pa sku gsum ni byang chub sems dpa'i lam nas 'bras bu grub tshul yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:6435: mtha' ma ni 'di'i lam gyis mos pa can drang
NK063(gu)001:6436: ba'i phyir rgyu'i theg pa dang sgo bstun nas lam
NK063(gu)001:6437: sbyangs pas 'bras bu grub tshul du gsungs pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:6438: mi zlos so // 'o na rgyu'i theg pa bas
NK063(gu)001:6439: grub pa'i 'bras bu chos sku dpag med ces pa
NK063(gu)001:6441: 'di'i 'bras bu skye shi med pa g.yung drung sku
NK063(gu)001:6442: la sogs pa'i sku gsum la khyad par yod dam
NK063(gu)001:6443: med / med na 'bras bu zlos par 'gyur la /
NK063(gu)001:6444: yod na gang yin zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:6446: rgyu 'bras khyad par lhun gyis grub //
NK063(gu)001:6447: ces pas khyad par yod pa'i phyir zlos pa'i skyon med do //
NK063(gu)001:6448: 'o na khyad par gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:6449: sku gsum la ngo bo dang /
NK063(gu)001:6451: byin gyis brlabs kyi khyad par dang gsum gsum yod de /
NK063(gu)001:6452: dang po ni 'og ma'i chos sku don dam spros
NK063(gu)001:6453: bral mngon du byas pa'i phyir ngo bo stong pa
NK063(gu)001:6454: phyogs gcig pa'am skye med sgra ji bzhin pa yin
NK063(gu)001:6455: la / cig shos kyi chos sku ni rnam kun
NK063(gu)001:6456: mchog ldan gyi stong pa mngon du byas pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:6457: sku dang ye shes ma spangs te skye med sgra
NK063(gu)001:6458: ji bzhin pa ma yin pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6459: gnyis pa ni 'og ma'i chos sku de skye med
NK063(gu)001:6460: sgra ji bzhin pa yin pa'i phyir mtshan nyid stong
NK063(gu)001:6461: pa phyogs gcig tu gzung du yod la /
NK063(gu)001:6462: 'di'i chos sku skye med sgra ji bzhin pa min
NK063(gu)001:6463: pa'i phyir mtshan nyid stong pa phyogs gcig tu gzung
NK063(gu)001:6464: du med pa'o // mtha' ma ni 'og ma'i chos
NK063(gu)001:6465: sku'i byin rlabs gzugs sku gnyis su mi snang ste
NK063(gu)001:6466: stong pa phyogs gcig pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:6467: 'di'i chos sku las ma g.yos bzhin de'i byin rlabs
NK063(gu)001:6468: gzugs sku gnyis su snang ste stong pa phyogs gcig
NK063(gu)001:6470: gzugs sku gnyis la'ang gong bzhin khyad par gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:6471: dang po ngo bo ni 'og ma'i gzugs sku ni
NK063(gu)001:6472: tshogs bsags shing smon lam las grub pa yin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6473: phyir ngo bo 'dus byas yin la /
NK063(gu)001:6474: cig shos kyi gzugs sku ni rang rig sgyu ma
NK063(gu)001:6475: ltar snang bas rgyu rkyen la rags ma lus pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6476: phyir ngo bo 'dus ma byas pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:6478: rgyun rkyen rag lus med pa yi //
NK063(gu)001:6479: sgyu ma rdo rje btsan po mchog /
NK063(gu)001:6482: 'og ma'i gzugs sku rgyu rkyen las skyes pa'i phyir mtshan nyid skye 'jig can yin la /
NK063(gu)001:6483: cig shos kyi gzugs sku rkyen la rag ma las pa'i phyir skye 'jig dang bral ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:6484: gsum pa yon tan gyi khyad par la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:6488: longs spyad bya zhing gi dang /
NK063(gu)001:6489: spyod tshul gyi khyad par ro //
NK063(gu)001:6490: dang po ni khog gzhung las /
NK063(gu)001:6491: gang gis chos kyi longs spyod ni //
NK063(gu)001:6492: ji ltar 'dod bzhin nyer spyod pa //
NK063(gu)001:6493: sku 'di longs spyod rdzogs par spyad //
NK063(gu)001:6495: 'og ma'i lugs kyi longs sku ni rnam par dkar
NK063(gu)001:6496: ba'i chos kyi phung po la spyod cing 'khor ba'i
NK063(gu)001:6497: chos la longs spyod mi nus la /
NK063(gu)001:6498: cig shos kyi lugs kyi longs sku ni 'khor 'das gnyis ka la spyod pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:6500: dngos po gnyis kyi longs spyod la //
NK063(gu)001:6501: bstar la mi 'dzin dbang phyug che //
NK063(gu)001:6503: gnyis pa spyod tshul gyi khyad par ni /
NK063(gu)001:6504: 'og ma pa'i longs skus rnam par dkar ba'i chos nyid zab mo yul du byas nas spyod la /
NK063(gu)001:6505: cig shos kyi lugs kyis ni thams cad rig pa
NK063(gu)001:6506: yin pa'i phyir yul med de bdag nyid chen par
NK063(gu)001:6507: spyod pas khyad par yod do //
NK063(gu)001:6508: sprul sku'i yon tan la gsum /
NK063(gu)001:6511: don byed pa 'bras bu'i khyad par ro //
NK063(gu)001:6512: dang po ni 'og ma'i sprul skus nyon mongs pa
NK063(gu)001:6513: spong ba dang sbyong ba kho na la mos pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6515: nyon mongs pa bsgyur ba la sogs pa la mos pa rnams mi 'dul la /
NK063(gu)001:6516: cig shos kyi lugs kyis ni nyon mongs pa spong
NK063(gu)001:6517: sbyong la mos pa dang de la mi mos te
NK063(gu)001:6518: bsgyur ba la sogs pa la mos pa thams cad
NK063(gu)001:6519: 'dul bas sam / yang na 'og ma'i sprul sku'i gdul byar rigs drug gyur la /
NK063(gu)001:6520: cig shos kyi sprul pa'i gdul byar 'og ma'i sprul skur gyur pas 'phags zhes kyang zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:6521: gnyis pa ni 'og ma pa'i sprul skus spong sbyong gi thabs phyogs gcig gis 'dul la /
NK063(gu)001:6522: cig shos kyi lugs kyis sprul skus de'i steng du
NK063(gu)001:6523: bsgyur ba dang dbang du byed pa la sogs thabs
NK063(gu)001:6524: dam pas 'dul bas khyad par 'phags so //
NK063(gu)001:6525: mtha' ma ni 'og ma pa'i sprul skus don byas pas kun tu 'od kyi sa thob la /
NK063(gu)001:6526: 'di'i sprul skus don byas pas yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa thob pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:6529: khyod kyi bcu gcig kun tu 'od //
NK063(gu)001:6530: thabs chen theg pa'i bsti gnas sa //
NK063(gu)001:6533: pad+ma can du gyur pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:6535: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro zhes gsungs te /
NK063(gu)001:6536: 'di rnams ni rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gnyis kyi
NK063(gu)001:6537: rang rang gi 'dod lugs kyi khyad par yin gyi
NK063(gu)001:6538: / 'bras bu'i rang ldog la gong gi khyad par de dag med par sems so //
NK063(gu)001:6539: gal te khyad par de dag yod na gang yang
NK063(gu)001:6540: rung ba gcig 'bras bu ma yin par 'gyur te
NK063(gu)001:6541: / 'bras bu yin pa'i 'gal zla yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:6542: de ltar yin par ma grub ce na /
NK063(gu)001:6544: ngo bo 'dus byas yin min dang /
NK063(gu)001:6545: mtshan nyid skye 'jig yod med dang /
NK063(gu)001:6546: byin rlabs gzugs sku gnyis su 'char mi 'char la sogs pa rnams dngos 'gal yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:6547: des na khyad par de dag theg pa gnyis kyi
NK063(gu)001:6548: 'dod lugs kyi khyad par yin par shes par bya'o
NK063(gu)001:6549: // le'u bsdus pa la gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:6550: lo rgyus su brjod pa ni sdud pa po mtshams sbyar ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:6551: bsdus pa dngos la gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:6552: gzhi rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK063(gu)001:6553: lam lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK063(gu)001:6554: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa sku'i dkyil 'khor bsdus pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6557: de nas de pa thams cad kyi rang bzhin zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:6558: ye shes phyogs bzhi zhes gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:6560: ye nas gnas pa'i chos nyid shes bya'i khyab byed de dmigs par bya ba'i yul yin zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:6562: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK063(gu)001:6564: tshul ni dmigs bya chos nyid de rtogs rung gi blo ste /
NK063(gu)001:6565: de ni grub pa mtha' 'dzin gyi ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:6566: ngo bo don gyi rdzogs pa chen po rtogs pa zhig gis dmigs par byed do //
NK063(gu)001:6567: mi dmigs zhes pa la sogs par /
NK063(gu)001:6570: de ni gong gi blo des yul de la yod
NK063(gu)001:6571: med la sogs mtha' gang du yang mi dmigs par
NK063(gu)001:6572: rtogs pa ni gting dpag tu med pas zab cing
NK063(gu)001:6573: / blos bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i phyir rgya che
NK063(gu)001:6574: ba ste de ni shes bya'i gnas lugs yin no
NK063(gu)001:6575: / zhes so // don gnyis pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:6576: ye shes rang rig la sogs su /
NK063(gu)001:6577: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:6578: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK063(gu)001:6579: ces pa'i bar du sho lo ka brgyad do //
NK063(gu)001:6580: de ni de mngon du byed pa'i ye shes ni
NK063(gu)001:6581: rang rig pa'i rtsal las lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK063(gu)001:6582: gyi dkyil 'khor rten gzhal yas dang brten pa lha
NK063(gu)001:6583: la sogs pa'i bkod pa sna tshogs su snang zhing
NK063(gu)001:6584: de'i che ba'i yon tan tshig tu brjod kyis mi
NK063(gu)001:6585: lang ba yin no zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:6587: mnyam dang zhes pa la sogs par /
NK063(gu)001:6588: sku yi phyag rgya che mchog ni //
NK063(gu)001:6590: de ni de ltar chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid
NK063(gu)001:6591: du rtogs pa mya ngan las 'das pa dang tha
NK063(gu)001:6592: dad du bzung bas mi mnyam par rtogs pa 'khor
NK063(gu)001:6593: ba'i chos kun la rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor gyis
NK063(gu)001:6594: khyab pa ste / de yang khyab bya dngos po
NK063(gu)001:6595: gnyis la bden pa'i rang bzhin med pa'i phyir khyab
NK063(gu)001:6596: byed dang dkyil 'khor gyis khyab pa'i tshul ni gyang
NK063(gu)001:6597: dang ri mo ltar rten dang brten pa ma yin
NK063(gu)001:6598: khyab pa ste / te / gser dang ser po
NK063(gu)001:6599: ltar ngo bo nyid kyis khyab pa'i don la chos
NK063(gu)001:6600: kyi dbyings zhes bya'o zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:6601: ye nas kun gsal zhes pa la sogs pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:6602: de ltar ye nas gnas pa'i chos nyid de mngon
NK063(gu)001:6603: du byas pa'i tshe chos kun gyi rang bzhin sku
NK063(gu)001:6604: lngar gsal bas rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6605: dkyil 'khor du gdul bya'i ngo la rnam par spros
NK063(gu)001:6606: pa ste / de la don gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:6607: de bzhin dbyings las zhes pa la sogs pa rkang
NK063(gu)001:6608: pa bcu gcig gis rang rig 'bras bur lhun gyis
NK063(gu)001:6609: grub pas la sku lnga'i ldog pa so sor spros
NK063(gu)001:6610: pa dang / 'og min bla med ces pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:6611: bla med byang chub yang dag thob //
NK063(gu)001:6612: ces pa'i bar bcu gnyis kyis rgyu'i theg pa'i gzhung dang /
NK063(gu)001:6613: mtshan dang dpe byad ces pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:6614: bsam yas mchog ces pa'i bar lngas 'bras bu'i theg
NK063(gu)001:6615: pa'i gzhung gis sku lngas don mdzad pa'i phyir theg
NK063(gu)001:6616: pa'i gzhung so sor spros pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:6617: chos sku dpag med brjod du med //
NK063(gu)001:6618: ces rkang pa gsum gyi rgyu'i theg pa 'bras bu dang /
NK063(gu)001:6619: skye shi med ces pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:6620: sku lnga kun kyang rdzogs zhes pa'i bar bdun gyis theg pa 'di'i 'bras bu ste /
NK063(gu)001:6621: theg pa'i gzhung de dag gis bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bu so sor spros pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6622: de ltar spros pa'i dpe yang //
NK063(gu)001:6623: dper na me long chu zla bzhin //
NK063(gu)001:6625: rim pa bzhin zhes pa'i bar drug ste /
NK063(gu)001:6626: de dag kyang gdul bya'i snang ba la spros pa
NK063(gu)001:6627: yin gyis de pa'i snang ba nas spros pa gang
NK063(gu)001:6629: de la mnyes pa'i don la ho zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:6630: bsdu ba'i skabs 'dir 'di ltar brtag par bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:6631: rgyud 'di'i le'u dang po dang gsum pa dang bzhi
NK063(gu)001:6632: pa dang drug pa rnams su le'u'i bsdu ba re
NK063(gu)001:6633: byung la gzhan rnams su mi 'byung ba ji ltar
NK063(gu)001:6634: yin zhe na / lan du kha cig na re
NK063(gu)001:6635: spyir rgyud kyi rang bzhin gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum
NK063(gu)001:6637: le'u dang por gleng gzhi bsdus pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:6638: gleng gzhi chos nyid du bsdu ba ces bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:6639: gsum pa dang bzhi par lam bsdus pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:6642: zhes brtag gzhi gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab pa ni shes rab grol ba'i lam yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:6643: bzhi par thabs dang shes rab ces lam gnyis dngos
NK063(gu)001:6644: su gsungs pa'i phyir lam gyi ngo bo bsdus pa
NK063(gu)001:6646: sku yi phyag rgya che mchog ni //
NK063(gu)001:6647: zhes pa la sogs pa 'di'i 'bras bu sku lnga
NK063(gu)001:6648: dang rgyu'i theg pa'i 'bras bu sku gsum gsungs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6649: phyir 'bras bu bsdu bar 'thad zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:6650: 'o na gzhan rnams su mi 'byung ba ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:6651: de dag tu brjod bya gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum gtso bor gsungs pa'i phyir byung la /
NK063(gu)001:6652: gzhan rnams su phal cher lam gyi cha rkyen rnams gsungs pa'i phyir mi 'byung ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:6653: rgyu mtshan med pa la rtog ldan blo 'jug mi srid do zhes grag go //
NK063(gu)001:6654: lan 'di rnams ni 'thad par ma mthong ste /
NK063(gu)001:6655: 'di ltar brjod bya gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum gtso
NK063(gu)001:6656: bor ston cing de'i bye brag lam gyi ngo bo
NK063(gu)001:6657: ston pa le'u gzhan na'ang yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:6658: le'u gsum pa'i lta ba de lam gyi cha rkyen
NK063(gu)001:6659: yin pas bsdu bar 'thad pa'i rgyu mtshan du dang
NK063(gu)001:6660: / le'u gzhan rnams su lam gyi cha rkyen ston
NK063(gu)001:6661: pas bsdu ba mi 'ong ba yin zhes lam gyi
NK063(gu)001:6662: cha rkyen de bsdu ba dang mi bsdu ba gnyis
NK063(gu)001:6663: ka'i 'thad par 'gal ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:6664: gzhan yang rgyu mtshan med pa la rtog ldan blo
NK063(gu)001:6665: 'jug mi srid zer ba ni rigs pa ma yin
NK063(gu)001:6666: te rgyud kyi gnas lugs 'di rtog ldan gyis blos
NK063(gu)001:6667: brtags nas byas pa ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:6668: 'o na 'di ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:6669: rgyud kyi dngos po'i gnas lugs yin te /
NK063(gu)001:6670: le'u bzhi par bsdu ba 'ong zhing gzhan rnams su
NK063(gu)001:6671: mi 'ong ba gnyis ka la shes byed mi dgos
NK063(gu)001:6672: so // gal te dgos na gsungs pa lo rgyus
NK063(gu)001:6673: su brjod pa yang dang po gnyis pa gsum pa
NK063(gu)001:6674: la sogs 'ga' zhig tu mi 'ong zhing 'ga' zhig
NK063(gu)001:6675: tu 'ong ba la rgyu mtshan ci yang med do
NK063(gu)001:6676: so // // des na khyod kyi mig de dpral
NK063(gu)001:6677: ba kho na la yod kyi gzhan na med pa
NK063(gu)001:6678: ci zhes pa dang kun nas mtshungs so //
NK063(gu)001:6679: de'i phyir 'di lta bu la rtog pa ni blo'i skyon yin te mu thug pa med do //
NK063(gu)001:6680: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u drug pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6682: // le'u bdun pa ni stod nas zhi ba lhag pa
NK063(gu)001:6683: ting dkyil bskyed pa'i sngags te mngon rtogs le'u drug
NK063(gu)001:6685: de yang sngags 'di dag la 'di nyid kyi drug
NK063(gu)001:6686: pa ltar phyi grol lam bskyed rim gyi dbang du
NK063(gu)001:6687: dang / thal rgyud ltar nang thabs lam bde ba'i
NK063(gu)001:6688: dbang du bshad pa gnyis gnyis su shes par bya'o
NK063(gu)001:6689: dang / // de las rten gzhal yas khang gi
NK063(gu)001:6690: sngags ni b+h+r+aum zhes pa rgyu sa bon yin la
NK063(gu)001:6691: bi shwa bi shud+d+he zhes pa skyed sngags te /
NK063(gu)001:6692: 'di yang chos dang po'i dbang du dkyil 'khor bsdus
NK063(gu)001:6693: pa 'bring po rgyas pa rnams gang bskyed kyang rung
NK063(gu)001:6694: ste / de nyid gdan dang bcas pa bskyed cing gsal gdab pa la le'u drug pa ltar ro //
NK063(gu)001:6695: chos gnyis pa'i dbang du thal rgyud las /
NK063(gu)001:6696: b+h+r+aum dbyibs b+ha gar sna tshogs 'dus //
NK063(gu)001:6697: las dang ngo bos dag pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:6698: sangs rgyas rin cen za ma ci //
NK063(gu)001:6699: byin brlabs skyob phyir sngags su brjod //
NK063(gu)001:6701: brten pa lha bskyed pa la yang dang po rigs
NK063(gu)001:6702: lnga bskyed pa ni h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika la sogs pas
NK063(gu)001:6703: rdo rje 'dzin pa la sogs bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:6704: de yang chos dang po ltar na dkyil 'khor bsdus
NK063(gu)001:6705: 'bring rgyas gsum la drug par bstan pa ltar bskyed
NK063(gu)001:6706: tshul gsum po gang gis bskyed kyang rung ste /
NK063(gu)001:6707: spyir sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la mtshungs pa thun mong gi chos gang dang ldan /
NK063(gu)001:6708: tha dad pa khyad par gyi chos ji lta bu zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:6709: dang po ni 'di'i drug pa las /
NK063(gu)001:6710: mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs //
NK063(gu)001:6712: thun mong dang thun min gsang ba'i mtshan dang dpe
NK063(gu)001:6713: byad rnams kyis brgyan cing tshul dgu rnams khyab byed
NK063(gu)001:6714: du yod pa'i phyir thun mong gi chos so //
NK063(gu)001:6715: gnyis pa ni lha tshogs rnams tshan tshan du bsdu na rigs lnga dang /
NK063(gu)001:6720: bye brag tu phye na bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su tha dad pas khyad par gyi chos so //
NK063(gu)001:6721: bye brag tu dang po rigs lnga yab yum la thun mong gi chos gdan khri bzhi brtsegs dang /
NK063(gu)001:6722: bzhugs tshul rdzogs pa'i skyil krung dang /
NK063(gu)001:6723: rgyas bsdus gang yin yang zhal phyag dang /
NK063(gu)001:6725: phyag gnyis pa'i dbang du yab kyi g.yon dang yum gyi phyag mtshan dril bu dang /
NK063(gu)001:6728: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi lha lnga dang /
NK063(gu)001:6729: chig rdzogs kyi dbang du dbu rgyan dang /
NK063(gu)001:6730: 'od kyi rgyab yol la sogs 'dra bar bsgoms pas thun mong ngo //
NK063(gu)001:6731: yang seng ge la sogs sems can gyi khri dang /
NK063(gu)001:6732: dbus dang shar la sogs bzhugs gnas dang /
NK063(gu)001:6733: tha tha la sogs skyed pa'i sa bon dang /
NK063(gu)001:6734: rdo rje la sogs thugs phyag mtshan dang /
NK063(gu)001:6735: badz+ra d+h+rika la sogs skyed sngags dang /
NK063(gu)001:6736: mthing kha la sogs sku mdog dang /
NK063(gu)001:6737: rang rtags g.yas kyi phyag mtshan dang /
NK063(gu)001:6738: thugs ka'i ye shes sems dpa' dang /
NK063(gu)001:6739: phyed skyil gyi dbang du dbu rgyan gyi rigs bdag dang /
NK063(gu)001:6740: mi bskyod pa la sogs mtshan dang /
NK063(gu)001:6741: rdo rje'i rigs la sogs pa rigs rnams ni tha dad pa'i phyir khyad par gyi chos yin te /
NK063(gu)001:6742: chos de rnams dang ldan par skyed do //
NK063(gu)001:6743: de nyid chos gnyis pa'i dbang du na dang po yab lnga ni /
NK063(gu)001:6745: tsit+ta khams lnga'i shi ra la //
NK063(gu)001:6746: rdo rje rgyal ba rin chen chos //
NK063(gu)001:6747: shes rab rig ldan bcud kyi gzungs //
NK063(gu)001:6748: nges par 'dzin pa gsang ba'i sngags //
NK063(gu)001:6750: mum d+h+aa tu shwa r+ai la sogs yum lnga yang /
NK063(gu)001:6752: de nyid dwangs ma'i ye shes lnga //
NK063(gu)001:6753: ma rig gnyis sogs bzhi po dang //
NK063(gu)001:6754: mi phyed phrag dog rdo rje'i sngags //
NK063(gu)001:6755: dbyings su skyob phyir dga' mar brjod //
NK063(gu)001:6757: sems dpa' yab yum la chos dang po'i dbang du na /
NK063(gu)001:6758: spyi'i chos gdan gsum brtsegs dang /
NK063(gu)001:6759: bzhugs tshul phyed skyil lam 'bab tshul te /
NK063(gu)001:6760: yab rnams mthun cing yum rnams mthun la /
NK063(gu)001:6761: g.yon gyi phyag rgya'am phyag mtshan dang /
NK063(gu)001:6762: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i lha dang /
NK063(gu)001:6763: rgyan chas rnams thun mong ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:6765: ka dang tsa la sogs sa bon dang /
NK063(gu)001:6766: rin myug la sogs thugs mtshan dang /
NK063(gu)001:6767: k+shi hi r+aa dza la sogs skyed sngags dang /
NK063(gu)001:6768: shar lho'i rtsibs mchan la sogs bzhugs gnas dang /
NK063(gu)001:6769: dkar po la sogs sku mdog dang //
NK063(gu)001:6771: rigs bdag gi dbu rgyan dang /
NK063(gu)001:6772: thugs ka'i ye shes sems dpa' dang /
NK063(gu)001:6773: rigs dang mtshan rnams tha dad pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:6774: chos de dag dang ldan par skyed do //
NK063(gu)001:6775: de las nang gi sems dpa' ni /
NK063(gu)001:6776: k+shi hi r+aa dza ya la sogs gong ltar ba skyed cing /
NK063(gu)001:6777: nang gi sems ma ni h+aum la s+ye sa ma ya s+t+wam zhes pa la sogs kyis bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:6778: sems ma de dag chos gnyis pa'i dbang du na /
NK063(gu)001:6780: las kyi bde bas sgeg pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:6781: chags pa'i dam tshig dus yin no //
NK063(gu)001:6782: slar yang lan gyis 'brel ba ni //
NK063(gu)001:6783: gnyis ka dgyes pa'i mchog tu bshad //
NK063(gu)001:6784: ha dang si yi bde sgra dag /
NK063(gu)001:6785: bdag gis chags pa thob pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6786: shin tu bskyod pa'i bde ba nyid //
NK063(gu)001:6787: kun nas bskyod pa'i rlung zhes bya //
NK063(gu)001:6789: phyi'i sems dpa' ni mi d+ha ra ni la sogs pas gong ltar bskyed cing /
NK063(gu)001:6790: phyi'i sems ma ni dzahd+h+au pe pra be sha la sogs pas bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:6791: de ni chos gnyis pa'i dbang du na /
NK063(gu)001:6794: de nyid phye ba las byung ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:6795: me tog bsdus pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK063(gu)001:6796: bdag po'i zhal du thim par bshad //
NK063(gu)001:6797: shin tu bsdams pa'i rim las byung //
NK063(gu)001:6798: gsal ba'i ye shes bde ba che //
NK063(gu)001:6799: kun gsal brjod dang bde ba'i sgra //
NK063(gu)001:6800: gnyis med thugs su shes par bya //
NK063(gu)001:6802: sgo ba yab yum ni h+aum ya m+aan+ta krita phata /
NK063(gu)001:6803: zhes pa la sogs pa yab rnams dang /
NK063(gu)001:6804: badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri la sogs kyis yum rnams te /
NK063(gu)001:6805: de dag la gdan rdo rje brag gi steng du nyi dkyil dang /
NK063(gu)001:6808: ltag lpags sbrul chun la sogs rgyan chas dang /
NK063(gu)001:6809: me ri rnams spyi'i chos la /
NK063(gu)001:6810: sa bon thugs phyag mtshan skyed sngags sku mdog phyag
NK063(gu)001:6811: mtshan dbu rgyan ye shes sems dpa' rigs mtshan bzhugs
NK063(gu)001:6812: gnas rnams khyad par gyi chos te de dag dang
NK063(gu)001:6814: rgyal mchog kun bzang yab yum ni h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra tsit+ta +amo zhes pas yab dang /
NK063(gu)001:6815: a a a badz+r+aa b+ha dra sa man+ta a zhes pas yum bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:6816: de yang gdan khri bzhi brtsegs dang /
NK063(gu)001:6817: bzhugs tshul skyil krung du dang /
NK063(gu)001:6820: mtshan dang rigs ni rigs kyi bdag por dang /
NK063(gu)001:6821: yan lag gi lha dang rgyan chas rnams mthun pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6822: phyir spyi'i chos la bzhugs gnas dang sa bon dang
NK063(gu)001:6823: yab dang yum gyi khyad par dang phyag mtshan rnams
NK063(gu)001:6824: tha dad pa'i phyir khyad par bas te de dag
NK063(gu)001:6826: de ni nang du na de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:6827: rnam shes gsum 'das rdo rje ni //
NK063(gu)001:6828: ye shes lnga rdzogs thugs nyid de //
NK063(gu)001:6829: dbyings gsum rnam dag 'dus ma byas //
NK063(gu)001:6830: kun tu'ang de bzhin gnas byed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6832: thub pa ni +amo mu ni h+aum trum s+w+aa h+aa
NK063(gu)001:6833: zhes pa la sogs pas spyi'i chos gdan pad+ma dang
NK063(gu)001:6834: bzhugs tshul ldem par dang zhal phyag dang cha lugs
NK063(gu)001:6835: rab tu byung ba rnams mthun la /
NK063(gu)001:6836: khyad par bzhugs gnas sa bon skyed sngags sku mdog
NK063(gu)001:6837: phyag mtshan rnams tha dad de de dag dang ldan
NK063(gu)001:6838: par skyed do // de nyid nang du na de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:6839: sa bon zung gsum bde de ba //
NK063(gu)001:6840: nges skyes rang rig gyur pa yis //
NK063(gu)001:6843: de ltar thabs kyi bshad pa 'di rnams 'grel pas
NK063(gu)001:6844: thal rgyud ltar bkral ba rnams gong ma rnams kyi
NK063(gu)001:6846: de dag de ltar bskyed pa'i thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' bsgom ste /
NK063(gu)001:6847: ji skad du 'grel pa bdud rtsi thig pa las /
NK063(gu)001:6848: ye shes sems dpa' snying gi d+h+au t+ai'i nang du bsgom la zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:6849: lha rnams rang rang gi thugs kar nyi zla chu
NK063(gu)001:6850: skyes kyi steng du rang rang ci 'dra ba'i ye
NK063(gu)001:6851: shes sems dpa' sku de dag nyid kyi tshon gang
NK063(gu)001:6852: ba'o // de'i thugs kar rang rang gi phyag mtshan
NK063(gu)001:6853: gyi lte ba la zla dkyil dbus su so so'i
NK063(gu)001:6854: sa bon la rang rang gi skyed sngags kyis bskor
NK063(gu)001:6855: ba ste 'od 'phro ba ni phra mo shes rab
NK063(gu)001:6858: rin chen smug po'i gnas gcig tu //
NK063(gu)001:6859: tshon gang sems dpa' 'od ldan pa //
NK063(gu)001:6860: thugs kyi sa bonabazlasa pas bskor //
NK063(gu)001:6861: kun gyi bdag phyir dkyil du bsam //
NK063(gu)001:6863: yan lag gi lha gzhan bsgom pa 'og tu 'chad /
NK063(gu)001:6864: de nas le'u drug pa ltar gdan la rdzogs dang zhes bzhugs tshul dang /
NK063(gu)001:6866: rdo rje 'khor lo zhes pa la sogs phyag mtshan dang /
NK063(gu)001:6867: mthing kha la sogs sku mdog dang /
NK063(gu)001:6868: mnyen lcugs la sogs tshul rnams gsal btab ste /
NK063(gu)001:6869: tshad dam che ba yan chad bstan nas /
NK063(gu)001:6870: dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:6872: de nas zhes pa la sogs lo rgyus su brjod pa yang mngon rtogs dang sbyar te /
NK063(gu)001:6873: gtso bo'i thugs ka'i ye shes sems dpa'i thugs ka'i h+aum las /
NK063(gu)001:6874: h+aum gcig gyen du phyung ste spyi gtsug tu gnas pa las 'od 'phros pas /
NK063(gu)001:6875: phyogs bcu rgyal ba'i thugs dam bskul mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs te /
NK063(gu)001:6876: de dag gi rang bzhin byed pa po rdo rje
NK063(gu)001:6877: dang bya ba mo rdo rje'am rigs lnga yab yum
NK063(gu)001:6878: 'ba' zhig gi cha bzung gnyis su med par sbyor
NK063(gu)001:6879: ba'i byang chub sems kyi rgyun ting nge'i dkyil 'khor
NK063(gu)001:6880: rnams la thim par mdzad do //
NK063(gu)001:6881: des lha rnams kyi dbu'i gnas su rin po che'i
NK063(gu)001:6882: khang bur rigs lnga yab yum gyi sa bon gyi
NK063(gu)001:6884: de las 'od 'phros don gnyis byas ye shes lnga'i bcud bsdus slar thim pa las /
NK063(gu)001:6886: +amo ma h+aa shu nya ta zhes pa la sogs
NK063(gu)001:6887: don de nas phyogs bcu dus bzhii'i de pa thams
NK063(gu)001:6888: cad kyi 'bru bsgyur te 'og nas ye shes lnga'i
NK063(gu)001:6889: rang bzhin nga'am gong nas bdag nyid chen po yin
NK063(gu)001:6890: pa'i rtags su dbu'i gnas lngar rigs lnga yab yum
NK063(gu)001:6891: gyis brgyan pa'o // de la lugs gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:6892: chig rdzogs dang phyed nyil las /
NK063(gu)001:6893: dang po ni mi bskyod pas gtso byas pa sha stag go //
NK063(gu)001:6894: gnyis pa ni mi bskyod pa dang byed po yab yum la chig rdzogs ltar la /
NK063(gu)001:6895: rigs bzhi'i gtso bo rang rang gi rigs bdag tu go 'gyur ba'i shul du mi bskyod pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6896: 'khor rnams la yang lnga char bsgom pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:6897: re rer bsgom pa gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:6898: gang du bsgom yang rigs kyi bdag pos dbang byas pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:6899: shar gyi sgo ba dang thub pa ma gtogs pa /
NK063(gu)001:6900: shar dang shar lho'i lha rnams mi bskyod pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:6902: nub dang nub byang mtha' yas /
NK063(gu)001:6903: byang dang byang shar don yod grub pas dbu brgyan pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6905: mi bskyod byed po yum dang bcas //
NK063(gu)001:6906: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i phyag rgyar ldan //
NK063(gu)001:6907: byams pa sa snying de bzhin te //
NK063(gu)001:6908: gzhan dag rang gi phyag rgya'o //
NK063(gu)001:6910: shar gyi sgo ba la rnam snang gis brgyan te /
NK063(gu)001:6912: gshin rje'i gshed la rtag par bshad //
NK063(gu)001:6914: thub pa la mi bskyod pas dbu brgyan pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:6917: zla dang bral bas dpa' bo che //
NK063(gu)001:6919: de yang zla dang bral bas zhes pas gong ma
NK063(gu)001:6920: rnams yum dang bcas par shugs la mngon pa yin
NK063(gu)001:6922: thub drug rang byung sprul sku'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:6923: byin brlab dbang bskur ma gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:6925: me long lta bu las kyang /
NK063(gu)001:6926: thub drug lus kyi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK063(gu)001:6927: byin brlab dbang bskur ma gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:6928: zhes bshad pa'i phyir thub pa la byin brlab dbang bskur mi dgos par 'dod pa yang yod do //
NK063(gu)001:6930: gong ltar byang sems las spyi bor zla steng du +amo dang /
NK063(gu)001:6932: thugs kar nyi steng du h+aum dang /
NK063(gu)001:6933: lte bar rin cen zur brgyad steng du s+w+aa dang /
NK063(gu)001:6934: gsang gnas gru gsum me 'dra ba'i steng du h+aa
NK063(gu)001:6935: rnams las 'od 'phros te don gnyis byas sku gsung
NK063(gu)001:6936: thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i gzi byin bsdus pa
NK063(gu)001:6937: las / sarba ta th+aa ga ta la sogs kyis
NK063(gu)001:6938: gnas gsum gyi yi ge las sku gsung thugs kyi
NK063(gu)001:6939: rdo rje dkar dmar mthing gsum 'khor lo dang pad+ma
NK063(gu)001:6940: dang rdo rje bsnams par skyed do //
NK063(gu)001:6942: gnas gsum khyab 'jug yi ge las //
NK063(gu)001:6944: khams gsum byin brlab gzi byin bsdus //
NK063(gu)001:6945: rang bzhin rdo rje gsum gnas pa //
NK063(gu)001:6946: rgyu gnyis tshul gyis rang snang pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6948: yang lte ba dang gsang gnas kyi yi ge gnyis
NK063(gu)001:6949: las a nu ra ga dang p+au tsas yon tan
NK063(gu)001:6950: dang phrin las kyi lha ser po dang ljang khu
NK063(gu)001:6951: rin cen dang rgya gram bsnams par skyed do //
NK063(gu)001:6952: de ltar yang de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:6953: lte ba rnam gnyis zla ba las //
NK063(gu)001:6954: sngo ljang yi ge s+w+aa h+aa nyid //
NK063(gu)001:6955: rjes mthun 'od dang yon tan las //
NK063(gu)001:6956: yan lag rdzogs pa'i gzi byin ldan //
NK063(gu)001:6958: de gnyis la kha cig rat+na dang dkar dmar 'dzin pa yod mod kyi /
NK063(gu)001:6959: 'dir 'go 'gyur dang mtha' 'gyur gyis rim pa ltar
NK063(gu)001:6960: yon tan dang phrin las su bzhed gsum ste gong
NK063(gu)001:6961: ma dang gcig par sems so //
NK063(gu)001:6962: gsum pa las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:6963: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drang ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:6965: mchod bshags bya zhing smon lam gdab pa'i rim pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6969: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de pa ma lus pa'i bdag nyid rang bzhin mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor te /
NK063(gu)001:6971: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK063(gu)001:6973: de'i ngo bo ji lta bu na /
NK063(gu)001:6974: thugs rnam dag mtha' gang du yang mi dmigs pa chos kyi dbyings su gcig pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:6976: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor las //
NK063(gu)001:6978: de ltar ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor chos sku'i ngang las mi g.yo bar bzhugs bzhin du /
NK063(gu)001:6979: +amo e h+ye hi la sogs pas gzugs sku'i rnam par bzhengs te /
NK063(gu)001:6980: de yang gnyis las longs skur nges shing de la yang zhi khro gnyis las zhi bar nges te /
NK063(gu)001:6981: rnam pa ni lhag pa ting dkyil bskyed pa 'dra bar bzhengs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:6982: lag len du stong pa shin tu yod med la sogs dbyangs tshig dang sa ma dza yis so //
NK063(gu)001:6984: de'i phyir rgyal ba gzhan du ma lus mi lus lus pa med par byon pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:6986: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK063(gu)001:6988: gang du na lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor kyi gnas su ste /
NK063(gu)001:6989: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor du //
NK063(gu)001:6990: zhes pas 'dir dzahh+aum bam hohzhesa phyag rgya bzhis me ri 'dab 'byor tsam du'o //
NK063(gu)001:6991: lag len du thugs rje lcags kyu la sogs dang e h+ye hi'o //
NK063(gu)001:6992: rig pa'i me tog dor ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:6993: +aahh+aum la sogs pas dam tshig dang ye shes kyi
NK063(gu)001:6994: dkyil 'khor gnyis sngags phyir rgyud pa ltar rje 'bangs
NK063(gu)001:6995: la sogs bzang ngan dang tha dad du 'dzin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:6996: rtog pa dor nas dbyer med du rig par byed
NK063(gu)001:6997: pa'o // dngos grub bskul pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:6998: ye shes rgyal po zhes pa la sogs dang //
NK063(gu)001:6999: +amo badz+ra sa ma ya la sogs pas ye shes sems dpa'i dngos grub stsol bar ro //
NK063(gu)001:7000: 'di la rgya skad dang bod skad gnyis zlos so zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:7001: dang po nges pa'i don du bskul pa yin zhing
NK063(gu)001:7002: gnyis pa ni de nyid gnad nas phab ste bskul
NK063(gu)001:7005: lag len du rin cen seng ge'i khri la zhes
NK063(gu)001:7006: pa la sogs pa la 'dir dzahh+aum bam hohs dam
NK063(gu)001:7007: tshig pa dang ye shes pa gnyis chu la chu
NK063(gu)001:7008: dang mar la mar ltar dbyer med du bsre ba
NK063(gu)001:7009: yin no // rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa gsung gi skabs su /
NK063(gu)001:7010: gsung gcig dkyil 'khor yan lag ni //
NK063(gu)001:7011: zhes pa ni sprul pa'i sku'i gsung gcig gcig la'ang dkyil 'khor zhes pa ni mthar dkyil gsung gi'o //
NK063(gu)001:7012: de'i byin rlabs rgyud drug gi gnas su /
NK063(gu)001:7017: ka la ping ka lta bu dang /
NK063(gu)001:7019: sgra brnyan lta bu dang zhes rnam grangs drug po re re la yang yan lag gces pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:7024: mi mthun pa med pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:7027: gang gis mi tshugs pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:7030: shin tu bsangs pa ste zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:7031: de ltar gsungs dbyangs yan lag sum brgya drug cur 'gyur pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7033: dper na de bzhin sbrid bsangs bzhin //
NK063(gu)001:7034: zhes pas sprul sku'i gsung lan gnyis byung bas zlos shing lhag la /
NK063(gu)001:7035: longs sku'i gsung ma byung bas chad par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:7036: dang po mi zlos te kha cig gong ma tshig
NK063(gu)001:7037: byings chung zhing 'og ma che bas so zer ro
NK063(gu)001:7038: // yang kha cig gong ma tshig tu gsungs shing
NK063(gu)001:7039: 'og ma dbyangs su bsnyad pa yin no zhes so
NK063(gu)001:7040: // // kha cig gzhung gis gong ma don la 'og ma dpe ru gsal zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:7041: rje nyid ni gong ma tshig res don re mtshon la /
NK063(gu)001:7042: 'og ma tshig gcig gis don du ma mtshon pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:7043: de las sprid pa bsangs pa bzhin gsung ste de'i gtam rgyud 'chad pa pos bsnyad do //
NK063(gu)001:7044: 'o na longs sku'i gsung ma byung ba 'di ni ci zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:7045: de ni le'u drug pa las /
NK063(gu)001:7046: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra ste //
NK063(gu)001:7047: sku yis chos rnams 'jal bar ston //
NK063(gu)001:7048: zhes smos zin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:7049: 'dir yang sa bon med par ma grub ste yi ge med dang zhes pa de yin no //
NK063(gu)001:7050: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u bdun pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7052: // le'u brgyad par mngon rtogs las sdeb kyi dbang du mchod pa las kyi rim pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7053: de la bco lnga ste bgrang /
NK063(gu)001:7054: de la dang po mnyes pa phyag dang dam bca' ba ni lag len ltar la /
NK063(gu)001:7055: gsum pa thugs grol ba'i sgo mtshon pa phyag rgya ni /
NK063(gu)001:7056: spyir mu dra'i sgra las drangs na phyag rgya zhes bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:7057: 'da' bar dka' ba dang brda sprod pa dang mdzes par byed pas phyag rgya'o //
NK063(gu)001:7058: de yang dang po ni rgyal po'i bka' rtags ltar
NK063(gu)001:7059: lta ba'am rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya ni rang rig
NK063(gu)001:7060: gis mngon gsum du chos thams cad thabs shes gnyis
NK063(gu)001:7061: med las gang yang mi 'da' ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:7062: gnyis pa ni tshong byed mkhan gyi lag pa ltar
NK063(gu)001:7063: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya ni rdo
NK063(gu)001:7065: 'khor los de pa la sogs rigs so sor brda spros pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:7066: tha ma ni sgeg mo dpung rgyan gyis mdzes pa
NK063(gu)001:7067: cher bskyed pa ltar spros pa snang 'byed kyi phyag
NK063(gu)001:7068: rgya nyi khri bzhi stong la sogs su gsal ba
NK063(gu)001:7069: ni chos nyid kyi ngang du mdzes pa'i phyir ro
NK063(gu)001:7070: // de las rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya ni sgyu
NK063(gu)001:7071: 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes pa la spyir brjod bya snang
NK063(gu)001:7073: dbyer med pa gsum gyi rjod byed du sgyu ma
NK063(gu)001:7074: 'phrul pa d+r+wa ba gsum du gsungs pa yin no
NK063(gu)001:7075: // de yang rdo rje las ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:7076: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba yis //
NK063(gu)001:7077: sgyu 'phrul bzhes ni bzhir bshad do //
NK063(gu)001:7080: sgyu ma ni rtog tshogs su btags pa rnams yin la /
NK063(gu)001:7081: 'phrul pa ni de nyid lhar gsal ba yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:7082: d+r+wa ba ni de gnyis dbyer med du 'brel ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:7083: ji skad du bla ma las /
NK063(gu)001:7085: mang la 'brel ba d+r+wa ba'i don //
NK063(gu)001:7087: gnyis pa nang ltar na sgyu ma ni 'khor lo bzhi'i rtsa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:7088: 'phrul pa ni de la gnas pa'i theg le yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:7089: bsgom pa'i thabs kyis rtsa thig 'brel ba ni d+r+wa ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:7090: ji skad du rgya mtsho las /
NK063(gu)001:7091: gnas gzhi'i gar thabs sgyu ma la //
NK063(gu)001:7092: nam mkha' ye shes cir yang gsal //
NK063(gu)001:7093: cir snang rig pas bdag nyid 'brel //
NK063(gu)001:7094: d+r+wa ba'i don du nga yis bshad //
NK063(gu)001:7096: gsum pa gsang ba ltar na sgyu ma ni mkha' pad+ma dang /
NK063(gu)001:7097: 'phrul pa ni thabs kyi rdo rje dang /
NK063(gu)001:7098: d+r+wa ba ni yab yum bde bas 'brel ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:7099: ji skad du de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:7100: shes rab thabs rol sgyu ma las //
NK063(gu)001:7101: rang bzhin sgyu 'phrul chen por bshad //
NK063(gu)001:7102: thabs dang thabs byung 'brel ba nyid //
NK063(gu)001:7103: thams cad kun gyi gzhir gnas pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7105: bzhi pa de kho na nyid kyi dbang du gzhi
NK063(gu)001:7106: byang chub kyi sems stong pa'i rtog pa ni sgyu
NK063(gu)001:7107: ma ste / snang yang ma grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:7108: snang ba'i rtog pa ni 'phrul pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:7109: med bzhin du snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:7110: de gnyis dbyer med pa'i rtog pa ni d+r+wa ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:7111: tha dad du ma grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:7112: de yang ji skad du bla ma las /
NK063(gu)001:7113: stong zhing dben pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK063(gu)001:7114: rigs dang kha dog dbyibs med las //
NK063(gu)001:7115: cir yang med las cir yang snang //
NK063(gu)001:7119: sems nyid sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste //
NK063(gu)001:7121: des na rgyud dbu zhabs kyi rjod byed sgyu 'phrul
NK063(gu)001:7122: d+r+wa ba zhes gsungs pa thams cad 'di ltar shes
NK063(gu)001:7123: par bya'o // de ltar bzhi las skabs 'dir tha
NK063(gu)001:7124: ma ste snang stong dbyer med kyi don las gang
NK063(gu)001:7125: yang mi 'da' ba ni rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya
NK063(gu)001:7127: de nyid cig car bas rang rig gis mngon du
NK063(gu)001:7128: chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs par rtogs pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:7129: ro // ji ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad byang
NK063(gu)001:7130: ba stong pa chub pa snang ba ste de gnyis
NK063(gu)001:7131: tha dad las mchog tu gyur pa dbyer med pa
NK063(gu)001:7132: dag gi don las mi 'da' bas phyag rgya'o //
NK063(gu)001:7133: de ltar rtogs dka' bas gsang ba yin la de
NK063(gu)001:7134: kho na nyid ma nor bar rtogs pas nges shing
NK063(gu)001:7135: mi bslu ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:7136: de la don gyi bcud 'dus pas snying po yin
NK063(gu)001:7137: pa rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya yin pas rgyal po'i
NK063(gu)001:7138: bka' rtags ltar 'da' bar dka' ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:7139: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya'i rgyu ni /
NK063(gu)001:7140: sngar nas skye mched kyi rtog pa lhar gsal ba'i
NK063(gu)001:7141: lus kyi yan lag dbu de pa'i dang phyag g.yas
NK063(gu)001:7142: pa rdo rje dang g.yon rin po che dang zhabs
NK063(gu)001:7143: g.yas las dang g.yon pad+ma'i rigs rnams su gsal bar
NK063(gu)001:7144: bya'o // de'i phyag g.yas pa dang mi bskyod ces rdo rje'i rigs dang chos mthun pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:7145: gnyis car btsan pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:7146: de ltar gsal ba'i g.yas kyi sor mo'i rtse lnga
NK063(gu)001:7147: la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor stan tsa na ka tsam
NK063(gu)001:7148: gyi steng du yab kyi yi ge 'bru lnga ste
NK063(gu)001:7149: de yang gung mo la h+aum mdzub mo la +amo
NK063(gu)001:7150: mthe bong la s+w+aa srin lag la +aam mthe chung
NK063(gu)001:7152: phyag g.yon pa dang rin chen rigs chos mthun pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:7153: der longs spyod rnams gsog cing len pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:7154: de'i sor mo lnga la zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gong
NK063(gu)001:7155: ma lta bu'i steng du yum gyi yi ge 'bru
NK063(gu)001:7156: lnga ste de yang gung mo la m+aum mdzub mo
NK063(gu)001:7157: la l+aam mtheb chen la m+aam srin lag la pyam
NK063(gu)001:7158: mathe'u chung la t+aam rnams dgod do //
NK063(gu)001:7159: de ltar yig 'bru lnga tshan gnyis zung du rtse
NK063(gu)001:7160: sprad pa las yab yum sbyar bas lhag pa ting
NK063(gu)001:7161: nge 'dzin rigs lnga'i phyag rgya 'byung ba'i phyir rgyu
NK063(gu)001:7162: yin no // rigs lnga spyi'i dam tshig gam gsang dbang sbyin pa'i phyag rgya ni /
NK063(gu)001:7163: gong gi sor mo rnams la yig 'bru bkod pa'i
NK063(gu)001:7164: g.yas kyi mdzum mo'i +amo dang g.yon gyi gung mo'i
NK063(gu)001:7166: yig 'bru lhag ma brgyad po phan tshul bsnol te
NK063(gu)001:7167: thabs shes rab 'brel ba'i phyir rtse sprad pa ni
NK063(gu)001:7168: rgyal ba kun gyi bde ba chen po 'byin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:7170: ji skad du thal rgyud las /
NK063(gu)001:7171: dbyings dang ye shes bdag po'i don //
NK063(gu)001:7172: +amo dang m+aum du rang bzhin gnas //
NK063(gu)001:7173: rwa dang 'dab ma'i thig le rnams //
NK063(gu)001:7174: rang gi gnas kyis bsnol mar gyur //
NK063(gu)001:7175: rab tu'ang 'dres par gyur ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:7176: rgyal ba'i ye shes bde chen po //
NK063(gu)001:7177: myong phyir thob pa zhes su bshad //
NK063(gu)001:7178: ces pa'i phyir yig 'bru rnams phan tshun bsnol bar bshad do //
NK063(gu)001:7179: des ni rigs lnga la sogs rgyal ba kun rigs
NK063(gu)001:7180: kyi yum dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i phyir gsang ba'i
NK063(gu)001:7181: dngos grub bam rigs lnga'i bde ba chen po gsang
NK063(gu)001:7182: dbang gis 'byin zhing brda sprod pa'i phyir phyag rgya'o
NK063(gu)001:7183: // rigs lnga yab yum gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK063(gu)001:7184: phyag rgya bzhi las bdun du 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:7185: de yang rtsa ba'i phyag rgya bzhi ni /
NK063(gu)001:7186: sku phyag rgya chen po dang /
NK063(gu)001:7190: dang po ni lha gang yin pa'i sku mdog zhal
NK063(gu)001:7191: phyag rgyan cha lugs su gsal ba de yin no
NK063(gu)001:7193: g.yas pa'i yig 'bru bzhi bzhi sbas nas gung mo
NK063(gu)001:7194: la sogs re re thugs kar bkan thabs su bca'
NK063(gu)001:7195: ba ni bca' ba dam rgya yin la /
NK063(gu)001:7196: kun mo la sogs g.yon du yum bsam pa ni bsam pa dam rgya'o //
NK063(gu)001:7198: gong gi bca' ba dam rgya'i rtser h+aum bsgreng la
NK063(gu)001:7199: sogs yig 'bru yongs su gyur pa las rdo rje
NK063(gu)001:7200: la sogs phyag mtshan 'od 'bar ba bsam pa ni
NK063(gu)001:7201: bsam pa chos rgya yin la /
NK063(gu)001:7202: yab yum gyi thugs kar phyag rgya dkrol nas badz+ra
NK063(gu)001:7203: d+h+r+aika la sogs pa brjod pa ni brjod pa chos
NK063(gu)001:7204: rgya'o // tha ma la'ang gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:7205: gong gi bsam pa chos kyi rtse mor h+aum la
NK063(gu)001:7206: sogs pa'i sa bon gyi yi ge rnams sgra dang
NK063(gu)001:7207: bcas pa bsam pa ni bsam pa las rgya yin
NK063(gu)001:7208: no // g.yon gyi zla ba'i so mo rnams brtul
NK063(gu)001:7209: zhing yig 'bru rnams sbas te dril bu gsil ba'i
NK063(gu)001:7210: tshul du bya zhing yum dang 'khril ba'i tshul gyis
NK063(gu)001:7211: zhabs g.yon pa chos pad+ma'i rigs su brlabs pa la
NK063(gu)001:7212: brten thabs su bca' ba ni bca' ba las rgya'o
NK063(gu)001:7213: no // // yum rnams de'i shugs la shes shing 'khor gyi phyag mtshan rnams sla bar zad do //
NK063(gu)001:7214: rnam par snang mdzad kyi skabs su /
NK063(gu)001:7217: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i lha gsum du bsdus nas bsgom pa la /
NK063(gu)001:7218: dang por mi bskyod pa dang kun bzang lta bur
NK063(gu)001:7219: bskyed pa ni 'bru bsgyur te rtsa ba'i lha yab
NK063(gu)001:7220: yum gnyis so // ldan zhes pa de la yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu ste /
NK063(gu)001:7221: yab la yab nyid ma gtogs pa nyi shu rtsa gsum dang /
