NK063(gu)001:7222: yum la'ang nyid ma gtogs pa bcu bdun bsgom pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7223: dang po ni spyi bor rnam snang /
NK063(gu)001:7228: mig gi rtsa'i nang du sa snying /
NK063(gu)001:7232: mig gi rtsa'i phyi rol du byams pa /
NK063(gu)001:7238: rkang pa g.yon la rta mgrin /
NK063(gu)001:7243: pus mo la byol song gi /
NK063(gu)001:7245: rkang mthil du dmyal ba'i thub pa rnams so //
NK063(gu)001:7246: gnyis pa yum rnams bsgom pa ni yab kyis shes
NK063(gu)001:7247: te de ltar bzhi bcu po de thabs kyi lha'o
NK063(gu)001:7248: // de nyid yan lag spros zhes pa de dag
NK063(gu)001:7249: gis thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' bzhi bcu bsgom
NK063(gu)001:7250: pa ni d+r+wa ba shes rab kyi lha'o //
NK063(gu)001:7254: yang de dag la spyi por sku'i lha dang mgrin
NK063(gu)001:7255: par gsung gi lha dang thugs kar thugs kyi lha
NK063(gu)001:7256: rnams re re yang bzhi bcu bzhi bcu ste bsam
NK063(gu)001:7257: mi khyab kyi lha brgya nyi shu dang /
NK063(gu)001:7258: gong gi thabs shes gnyis la bzhi bcu bzhi bcu
NK063(gu)001:7259: ste brgyad cu dang nyis brgya po ni grangs kyi
NK063(gu)001:7260: gzhi yin no // gong nas bdag ste zhes pas
NK063(gu)001:7261: de dag la bdag po'i lha dbu rgyan lnga lnga
NK063(gu)001:7262: bsnan pas lnga tshan nyis brgya la stong yod do
NK063(gu)001:7263: gzhi yin no // // de rnams yod pa gang du bsgom na /
NK063(gu)001:7264: de ltar ldan pa'i gtso mchog gis //
NK063(gu)001:7265: zhes pas gtso bo mi bskyod pa yab yum ste de la stong /
NK063(gu)001:7266: rgyal ba zhes pa rigs bzhi yab yum ste de la stong /
NK063(gu)001:7267: rgyal mchog ces pa kun bzang yab yum ste de la stong /
NK063(gu)001:7268: bcu gnyis zhes pa sems dpa' yab yum bcu drug
NK063(gu)001:7269: dang sgo ba yab yum brgyad de de ltar ya
NK063(gu)001:7270: nyi shu rtsa bzhi la zung bcu gnyis yod pas
NK063(gu)001:7272: drug gi zhes pa thub pa drug ste /
NK063(gu)001:7273: de yang yab la yab dgod pa dang yum la yum dgod pa la /
NK063(gu)001:7274: thub pa la yum med pas gang du dgod ce na /
NK063(gu)001:7275: kha cig lus kyi g.yas la yab dang g.yon la yum dgod zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:7276: kha cig gtso bo lnga'i yum dang kun bzang gi yum dang drug g.yar la brtsi zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:7277: kha cig rtags kyi yum gdan pad+ma yin pas de la dgod zer ba yang yod de /
NK063(gu)001:7278: de dag gang du byas kyang stong phrag drug ste /
NK063(gu)001:7279: de dag la spyir stong phrag nyi shu rtsa bzhi ste nyi khri bzhi stong yod do //
NK063(gu)001:7280: de la thub pa la yab la yab bkod pa
NK063(gu)001:7281: mi bgrang ba'i dod gang mi bgrang zhe na thub
NK063(gu)001:7282: pa nyid do // 'o na yum la yum bkod
NK063(gu)001:7283: pa'i dod yum med pas rtsa ba'i lha thub pa
NK063(gu)001:7284: pa nyid do // nyid dang / pad+ma thabs lha zhe gcig dgod dgos pas thabs lha gcig dang /
NK063(gu)001:7285: de'i thugs ka'i shes lha dang gnyis /
NK063(gu)001:7286: gnas gsum gyi bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i lha gsum ste lnga /
NK063(gu)001:7287: de dag la dbu rgyan lnga lnga ste sum cu lhag go zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:7288: yum mi bgrang ba'i dod kun mo mi bgrang bas de dag lhag pa ma yin no //
NK063(gu)001:7289: de dag ni dbu rgyan kho na'o grangs te /
NK063(gu)001:7291: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK063(gu)001:7293: de dag ma lus pa byung ba btab na yab
NK063(gu)001:7294: yum gnyis gnyis la dbu rgyan ma gtogs pa thabs
NK063(gu)001:7295: shes bsam mi khyab kyi lha nyis brgya nyis brgya
NK063(gu)001:7296: tshan pa nyi shu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK063(gu)001:7297: de la dbu rgyan lnga lnga ste yongs su rdzogs
NK063(gu)001:7298: par nyi khri bzhi stong brgyad brgyar gsal ba'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:7300: de ltar bsgom pa 'di ni zag bcas kyi skabs
NK063(gu)001:7301: su lam mthar chags pa dngos kyi yul min te
NK063(gu)001:7303: thod rgal ba'i dngos kyi yul yin te /
NK063(gu)001:7304: spyod yul kun tu ma d+ha la //
NK063(gu)001:7305: zhes pa ltar tshogs sgrub mi dgos par rgya chen
NK063(gu)001:7306: la sbyor ba yang yod pa yin no zhes gsung
NK063(gu)001:7307: ngo // 'o na de ltar bsgom pa'i tshe dbu'i
NK063(gu)001:7308: gnas su dbu rgyan gyi lha rnam snang sku'i lha
NK063(gu)001:7309: lha'i thub pa rnams lha du ma gnas gcig tu
NK063(gu)001:7310: bsgom par mi 'thad do zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:7311: klad pa dung khang gi nang du sku'i lha /
NK063(gu)001:7312: de'i steng gi gtsug tu dbu rgyan /
NK063(gu)001:7315: de bzhin du mgrin pa'i nang du gsung gi lha /
NK063(gu)001:7316: de'i phyi rol du mtha' yas /
NK063(gu)001:7317: de'i 'og tu yi dwags kyi thub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7318: thugs kar yang snying ga'i nang du ye shes sems dpa' /
NK063(gu)001:7319: de'i phyi brang gi nang du thugs kyi lha /
NK063(gu)001:7320: phyi rol gyi thugs kar rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK063(gu)001:7322: de'i 'og tu thub pa'o gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:7323: 'di dag ni dang po can ma yin zhing sems
NK063(gu)001:7324: kyi byed pa yin pa'i phyir me long dang gzugs
NK063(gu)001:7325: brnyan ltar gcig gi go gcig gis mi 'gag par
NK063(gu)001:7328: de zhes pa gong gi nyi khri chig stong la
NK063(gu)001:7329: sogs snang ba thams cad phyag rgyar gsal ba ste
NK063(gu)001:7330: de la bsam mi khyab bsam yas lhun grub kyi
NK063(gu)001:7332: des don bya ba'i yul phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis
NK063(gu)001:7333: bsdus pa'i zhing bsam yas pa'i gnas su 'dul byed
NK063(gu)001:7334: dkyil 'khor gyis gdul bya 'gro ba'i don rnams rang
NK063(gu)001:7335: gi blo dang 'tshams par 'dul thabs so sor ston
NK063(gu)001:7336: par byed do // 'o na dkyil 'khor ma yin
NK063(gu)001:7337: pa gzhan gyis don mdzad pa med dam zhe na
NK063(gu)001:7338: par byed do // / ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:7339: gsung gi mdzad pa theg pa'i sgo nas don mdzad
NK063(gu)001:7340: tshul yang mtho ba theg chen dang dman pa theg
NK063(gu)001:7342: de dag las phyin ci log tu lta ba mu
NK063(gu)001:7343: stegs la sogs pa rnams la yang de dag rang
NK063(gu)001:7344: rang gi bsam pa dang mthun par 'dul thabs mtha'
NK063(gu)001:7346: gzhan yang zhi bas 'dul ba la tshangs pa dang
NK063(gu)001:7347: khro bos 'dul ba la srin po lta bur bstan
NK063(gu)001:7348: pa'i tshogs chen gyis 'dul ba'i gdul bya thams cad
NK063(gu)001:7349: la'ang 'dul byed so sor de dag dang mthun par
NK063(gu)001:7350: byas te dus kun tu don mdzad par snang ba
NK063(gu)001:7352: 'dir kha cig zhi khro'i tshogs chen thams cad la zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:7353: 'di gdul bya yin pa zer ba ni 'thad pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:7354: de gdul byar byas pa'i 'dul byed su yin te mi rnyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:7355: 'o na de ltar don mdzad pa kho na'i ched
NK063(gu)001:7356: du rtsol zhing phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor las g.yos par
NK063(gu)001:7358: lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir de las ma g.yos shing
NK063(gu)001:7359: rtsol rtog dang bral bas don mdzad pa yin te
NK063(gu)001:7360: / dper na gar mkhan nyid dang 'dra ba ste
NK063(gu)001:7361: de'i lus las ma bkod zer yang ma g.yos par
NK063(gu)001:7362: yan lag gi 'khyog dang rnam 'gyur sna tshogs kyis
NK063(gu)001:7363: ltad mo ba'i yid tshim par ston pa bzhin no
NK063(gu)001:7364: / // phyag rgya'i rnam grangs bsdus pa ni 'bru
NK063(gu)001:7365: bsgyur te phyag rgya de dag kyang mdor bsdus na
NK063(gu)001:7366: rtag pa'i lha dang lus la bkod pa'i lha thams
NK063(gu)001:7367: cad ni 'di kho na'o zhes pa'am gcig tu nges
NK063(gu)001:7368: pa yin no zhes phyogs gcig tu brjod du med
NK063(gu)001:7369: / // pa yin te / bsam yas lhun grub
NK063(gu)001:7370: kyi dkyil 'khor gcig la'ang slob pa'i rim pa dang
NK063(gu)001:7371: blo gsum la ltos te tshul tha dad du slob
NK063(gu)001:7372: / // pa yin te / pa'i phyir te / gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:7373: slob pa'i rim pa dang po bar pa tha ma gsum dang /
NK063(gu)001:7374: blo tha ma 'bring rab gsum la rim pa ltar
NK063(gu)001:7375: nges pa can dang don mi 'gyur la gnas skabs
NK063(gu)001:7376: 'gyur ba dang nges med du slob pa'i phyir ro
NK063(gu)001:7377: // de yang gnyis dang zhes pas thabs dang shes rab kyi lha bzhi bcu tshan pa gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:7378: gsum du zhes pas bsam mi khyab kyi lha bzhi bcu tshan gsum mo //
NK063(gu)001:7379: rnam par 'phro zhes pas dbu rgyan ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor stong du'o //
NK063(gu)001:7380: yang na gnyis dang zhes pa rkang pa gnyis la las dang pad+ma'i rigs so //
NK063(gu)001:7381: gsum du zhes pa lag pa gnyis mgo dang gsum
NK063(gu)001:7382: la rin cen rdo rje de pa'i rigs tshom bu
NK063(gu)001:7384: rnam par 'phro zhes pa yan lag gi lha nyi khri bzhi stong la sogs so //
NK063(gu)001:7385: dkyus lhag ma rnams gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:7387: de skad dag mchog nyid kyis bshad //
NK063(gu)001:7388: ces pa la ston pa ngas bshad ces pa 'di mi 'thad de /
NK063(gu)001:7389: rang gi tshig rang la lung du mi 'gyur ba'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:7390: de tshod du rgyal ba'i yum las /
NK063(gu)001:7391: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa zhes pa yang bka' ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:7394: sdud pa po'i tshig yin pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:7395: de 'dir yang mtshungs pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:7396: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u brgyad pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7398: // le'u dgu pa man chad kyi gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa na /
NK063(gu)001:7399: dgyes pa chen po zhes pa la spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:7400: thun mong gi dga' ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:7403: de dag gi 'dod pa na nye bar spyod pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:7405: mthong lam pa rnams kyi phyir zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:7406: 'dir de dag las khyad par du gyur pa thams
NK063(gu)001:7407: cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis zag med kyi bde
NK063(gu)001:7408: ba la mnga' brnyes pas na'o //
NK063(gu)001:7410: spyir gang zag gcig lam 'dir zhugs nas mthar thug
NK063(gu)001:7411: gi 'bras bu'i bar lam gyi rim pa ma nor
NK063(gu)001:7413: de yang brtags pa gnyis zhig nas dang por g.yo ba'i sems /
NK063(gu)001:7414: des gzhi byas nas 'di'i don khong du chud par
NK063(gu)001:7415: smon pa'i sgo nas lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil
NK063(gu)001:7417: sngon du rdo rje slob dpon gyis bsnyen pa bya ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:7418: shin tu phra ba sbyangs pa yi //
NK063(gu)001:7419: zhes pas phra mo'i ting nge 'dzin la blo sbyong ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:7424: dang po ni mad+ha la bya /
NK063(gu)001:7425: de la gom ye dang dri'i thig le bya zhing tshom bu bkod nas /
NK063(gu)001:7426: las kyi rim pa gzhung bsrung ba la sngon 'gro bdun gyi rjes su //
NK063(gu)001:7427: dngos gzhi ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis khyad par las gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bskyed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7429: rigs kyi bdag po la dang /
NK063(gu)001:7430: rdo rje rigs la sogs pa rigs lnga pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7431: de re re la yang bsnyen pa bya ba'i thabs dang /
NK063(gu)001:7432: bsnyen pa rdzogs pa'i tshad do //
NK063(gu)001:7437: dang po ni rgyu'i ye ge las k+sha dang a byung ste /
NK063(gu)001:7438: ak+sha dz+ny+aa na la sogs pa'i bzlas pa rdzogs pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:7439: ting nge 'dzin gsum nas bzlas pa yan chad du las gzhung bsrang ba gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:7440: thugs phra mo ni k+sha dang a 'od du zhu
NK063(gu)001:7441: ba las rdo rje dang dril bur gyur pa las
NK063(gu)001:7442: badz+ra g+han+de dz+ny+aa na la sogs pa'i bzlas pa rdzogs
NK063(gu)001:7443: pa dang las gzhung bsrang ba snga ma dang mthun
NK063(gu)001:7444: no // sku phra mo yang rdo rje 'od dang zhu ba las sku bzang dang /
NK063(gu)001:7445: dril bu zhu ba las kun tu bzang mor gyur pa las /
NK063(gu)001:7446: h+aum badz+ra tsit+ta dang a badz+r+aa b+ha dra la sogs
NK063(gu)001:7447: bdun pa ltar bzlas la grangs rdzogs pa dang las
NK063(gu)001:7448: gzhung bsrang ba snga ma ltar ro //
NK063(gu)001:7449: de nas mchod pa dang bstod pa rnams bya /
NK063(gu)001:7450: yi ge brgya pas bshags la /
NK063(gu)001:7451: re zhig nam mkhar gshegs par bya /
NK063(gu)001:7452: rigs bye brag pa yang des shes par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:7453: gnyis pa bsnyen pa rdzogs pa'i tshad ni /
NK063(gu)001:7457: mjug gi rim pa ni lhag ma btang /
NK063(gu)001:7462: de ltar shin tu phra ba'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom
NK063(gu)001:7463: zhing bsnyen pa ste bzlas pa rdzogs pa las mi
NK063(gu)001:7464: 'da' ba'i phyir dam tshig mchog ces bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:7465: dkyil 'khor gyi las kyi rim pa ni rdo rje las rim las /
NK063(gu)001:7466: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshad thig dang //
NK063(gu)001:7467: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:7468: rab gnas sbyin sreg 'jug pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:7469: yon tan rnam bcu rgyas zhes bya //
NK063(gu)001:7473: mchog gi dkyil 'khor dang gsum ka la de ltar bcu bcu shes par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:7474: de la dang po zhi dkyil 'khor gyi dbang dus
NK063(gu)001:7475: gzhi mnyam pa ni yang na zhes pa dgar ba
NK063(gu)001:7476: ste / dgar gzhi ni rgyud kyi rim pa'i dbang du /
NK063(gu)001:7477: sor ni bzhi yi tshad du bya //
NK063(gu)001:7479: dkyil 'khor mdzub gang tshad du bya //
NK063(gu)001:7480: zhes pa la sogs gsang dbang gi dkyil 'khor las dgar ba yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:7481: 'grel ba'i dbang du na spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:7482: rgyud kyi rim pa spangs te man ngag gi rim pa la 'jug par bya'o zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:7483: dgar gzhi rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dkyil
NK063(gu)001:7484: 'khor las yang na ting 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom
NK063(gu)001:7485: la / ting 'dzin dkyil 'khor las yang na lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:7490: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bri bar bya //
NK063(gu)001:7492: sa gzhi rab mnyam la zhes pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:7494: gzhi dang rang mtshan bslang dbang dang //
NK063(gu)001:7495: sbyang byin bsrung dang gzung ba ni //
NK063(gu)001:7496: dang po'i nying la nyid du bshad //
NK063(gu)001:7498: dang po gzhi dang zhes pa ni lhag pa gzugs
NK063(gu)001:7499: brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gang du bya ba gnas kyi
NK063(gu)001:7503: mtshams kyi dgra brtag pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:7506: zur brgyad la sogs rtse mang dang //
NK063(gu)001:7507: chu bo bzhin du ma bo zhing //
NK063(gu)001:7508: mnyam zhing 'o kha chu ltar dwangs //
NK063(gu)001:7509: nyi ma shin tu gnas pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:7510: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid shes par bya //
NK063(gu)001:7511: zhes pas mtshan nyid bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7513: dkyil 'khor dbang dgra mtshams brtag bya //
NK063(gu)001:7515: shar lho mtshams na gshin rje gdug pa'i mdung rtse lta bu dang /
NK063(gu)001:7516: lho nub na srin mo dus pa'i mchi rjes lta bu dang /
NK063(gu)001:7517: nub byang na ma mo rngams pa'i spar bshad lta bu dang /
NK063(gu)001:7518: byang shar na 'byung po rkus po'i 'jol sa lta bu rnams med pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7520: phyogs kyi ri brtag pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:7521: gnas nyid kyi ri brtag pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7522: dang po ni de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:7523: shar lho gzhol zhing 'jam pa la //
NK063(gu)001:7524: mtho dang 'dud pa nub byang yin //
NK063(gu)001:7527: lhun stug ri bo nags tshal ldan //
NK063(gu)001:7528: rab tu mnyam zhing snum bag can //
NK063(gu)001:7529: chu bo dbang gi phyogs yin te //
NK063(gu)001:7530: cung zad kyis ni rlung nyung zhing //
NK063(gu)001:7531: me tog shing dang bya skad brtag /
NK063(gu)001:7532: lo rgyus shis pa'ang mchog tu bshad //
NK063(gu)001:7534: gnyis pas rang gi mtshan nyid la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:7535: ngan pa brtags la spang ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:7536: bzang po brtags la dkyil 'khor bya ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:7538: mtshan nyid sbyong ba phyogs gsum ste //
NK063(gu)001:7541: thang kha sog le lta bu dang //
NK063(gu)001:7542: dma' dang bo ba'i mtshan nyid dang //
NK063(gu)001:7543: tsha sgo zug rdo rus sbal dang //
NK063(gu)001:7546: gram pa thal shing sol du ma dang //
NK063(gu)001:7547: gyo mo rus pa gseg la sogs //
NK063(gu)001:7550: nya gro ta dang pa la sha /
NK063(gu)001:7551: u dum 'bar ba a shwad tha //
NK063(gu)001:7552: a rdzu nu la sogs pa'i tshul //
NK063(gu)001:7553: 'dod pa ma yin sbyang spo bya //
NK063(gu)001:7555: gnyis pa sa bzang po ni /
NK063(gu)001:7556: bkra shis r+ts+wa dang me tog shing //
NK063(gu)001:7557: gnag dang kha dog ldan pa la //
NK063(gu)001:7558: rtsigs ma rgyus pa rab nyung zhing //
NK063(gu)001:7559: lhag par gyur pa mchog tu bshad //
NK063(gu)001:7561: gsum pa sa bslang ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:7563: mngon dang mi mngon bdag po la //
NK063(gu)001:7564: rtsod pa nye bar zhi bya'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:7565: ser sna spang ba'i sems kyis ni //
NK063(gu)001:7566: rin bcal bden pas bsgo la bslang //
NK063(gu)001:7568: mngon pa la bslang ba ni rgyal po gdug pa
NK063(gu)001:7569: can la sogs pa sa'i bdag por gyur pa la
NK063(gu)001:7571: gnyis pa mi mngon pa la bslang ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:7572: sa bdag zhing skyong la dang /
NK063(gu)001:7573: sa'i lha mo la bslang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:7575: nam mkhar bzhugs te sa rnams spang //
NK063(gu)001:7576: tshim bya bsgo ba drag byas la //
NK063(gu)001:7577: mthun pa'i rdzas kyis mchod byas bslang //
NK063(gu)001:7580: mchod pa bdud rtsi glu gar gyis //
NK063(gu)001:7581: rgyas mchod gsol ba gdab par bya //
NK063(gu)001:7583: lag len ltar cho gas bskul zhing sngags brjod pas
NK063(gu)001:7584: lha mo las 'od 'phros te sa nyid ye shes
NK063(gu)001:7585: rin po che'i sa gzhir bsam mo //
NK063(gu)001:7586: bzhi pa dbang du bya ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:7587: dngos grub dbang du bya ba'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:7588: zangs sogs phur pa zla gam la //
NK063(gu)001:7589: h+aum las gyur pa'i dbang mchog khro //
NK063(gu)001:7590: r+aa ga'i mdog 'dra zla gam la //
NK063(gu)001:7592: sdang mig phyag bzhi nges bsams te //
NK063(gu)001:7593: sku gsung byin dbab dbus su sbyar //
NK063(gu)001:7594: 'od kyis thams cad bsdu byas la //
NK063(gu)001:7595: bdag gir gyur pa'i sa dag ni //
NK063(gu)001:7596: las rnams kun la shis par 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:7597: sa gzhi dbang du bsgrub mchog go //
NK063(gu)001:7601: sbyang ba las me sngags phyag rgya //
NK063(gu)001:7611: zangs dang bkra shis rin cen nas //
NK063(gu)001:7612: 'bru sbyar byas pa sa gting du /
NK063(gu)001:7613: kham sa'i par bur blugs la gzhug /
NK063(gu)001:7615: gnyis pa go ma ye bya ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:7616: sum cu rab snyam bskam par bya //
NK063(gu)001:7618: gnyis pa sa'i mtshan nyid shin tu ngan na zhi ba'i sbyin sreg bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:7620: gzhan du bgrod dam zhi ba yi //
NK063(gu)001:7621: me yis rab tu dag par 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:7623: sa bzang ngan 'bring po tsam yin na lag pa
NK063(gu)001:7624: g.yas la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor steng du 'bru lnga
NK063(gu)001:7625: bkod pa ha na'i sngags brjod des la lan gsum
NK063(gu)001:7626: du btab pas dag par bsam mo //
NK063(gu)001:7627: gsum pa ni thal mo khong stong sbyar la shu nya ta'i sngags kyis stong pa nyid du sbyangs /
NK063(gu)001:7628: tha ma ni gnyis las mtshan med gong ltar la /
NK063(gu)001:7629: mtshan bcas ni sa la ni dbang chen gyi dkyil
NK063(gu)001:7630: 'khor bskyed la dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus pa gang
NK063(gu)001:7633: rgyas dang 'bring po la sogs pa'i //
NK063(gu)001:7634: sna tshogs rgyan ldan gzhal yas khang //
NK063(gu)001:7635: ji ltar gyur pa bzhin du bsgom //
NK063(gu)001:7637: drug pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:7638: gzhi dkyil 'khor bskyed de ye shes la spyan drangs
NK063(gu)001:7639: nas mchod pa phul te tshig gis bskul bas de
NK063(gu)001:7640: pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs
NK063(gu)001:7641: bsdus te rang nyid la thim pas zhe sdang rdo
NK063(gu)001:7642: rjer bskyed la sa gzhi rdo rje'i rang bzhin du
NK063(gu)001:7643: brlab bo // bdun pa bsrung ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:7644: nam mkhar khyab pa'i rtsibs brgyad la //
NK063(gu)001:7645: khro bo'i thugs las nges phyung dgod //
NK063(gu)001:7647: khro bo bcu'am mtshon cha 'chol ba la sogs bsrung ba'i 'khor los mtshams bcad de /
NK063(gu)001:7648: gang yang bar chad skabs med na //
NK063(gu)001:7649: bsrung ba'i mchog tu de gsungs so //
NK063(gu)001:7651: brgyad pa gzung ba ni gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:7652: dang po de pa la gzung bar tshig gis bskul nas /
NK063(gu)001:7653: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gyis lha rnams rol pa'i
NK063(gu)001:7654: gzi barjiida kyis dkyil 'khor du gsal bar bya ba
NK063(gu)001:7655: ni / nges brjod rol pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK063(gu)001:7656: thams cad dkyil 'khor rang bzhin te //
NK063(gu)001:7657: gsal byas yongs su gzung ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:7659: thig btab ste lha gnas su byang sems kyi thig
NK063(gu)001:7660: le lha grangs dang mnyam pa bya ste tshom bu
NK063(gu)001:7661: bkod la / sbyor mtshams nas gzhal yas khang dang
NK063(gu)001:7662: lha bskyed nas ye shes pa spyan drangs bstims te
NK063(gu)001:7663: mchod cing bstod pa yan chad byas la /
NK063(gu)001:7664: cho ga'i tshig gis gsol ba btab nas sa nyid lha dang gzhal yas su bsgom pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7665: de dag la ci'i phyir sa gzhi mnyam pa ni zhes bya zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:7667: thams cad rang sems mnyam sbyor bas //
NK063(gu)001:7668: sa gzhi can yang de bzhin bsgrub //
NK063(gu)001:7669: 'dir ltar gang zhig gsal gyur pa //
NK063(gu)001:7670: sa gzhi rab tu mnyam zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:7671: zhes tha dad kyi rtog pa dag nas thams cad mnyam par mtshon pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:7672: don gnyis pa tshad kyi skabs su rgyas 'bring bsdus
NK063(gu)001:7673: pa gsum la tshad gnyis gnyis su byung ba ni
NK063(gu)001:7675: tshad ni rkyen gyis ma nges te //
NK063(gu)001:7676: zhes pas slob dpon phyag bzo mi bzo dang /
NK063(gu)001:7678: slob bu mos mi mos dang /
NK063(gu)001:7679: 'byor ba che chung gis 'dam kha yin te /
NK063(gu)001:7681: mos dang 'byor pas rnam phye ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:7684: gnyis ni bzo yi yang phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:7686: mchog gi dkyil 'khor la gnyis su byung ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:7687: slob dpon dgongs pa zab mi zab dang /
NK063(gu)001:7688: slob bu las tshabs che chung gi dbang ngo //
NK063(gu)001:7689: don gsum pa thig le la bdun te /
NK063(gu)001:7694: rab gnas dang ji ltar gdab pa dngos dang /
NK063(gu)001:7696: dang po ni phur bu zhes pa 'gying phur te cha rkyen bsdus pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7697: gnyis pa rgyu ni srad bu zhes pa ste ye
NK063(gu)001:7698: shes kyi skud pa'i rgyu pad+ma'i rgyus pa la bya
NK063(gu)001:7699: zhing / dam tshig gi rgyu ni ras bal lam srin bal la bya bar gsungs so //
NK063(gu)001:7700: gsum pa grangs ni ye shes kyi nyi shu rtsa
NK063(gu)001:7701: lnga'am lnga sgrol la dam tshig gi dagu'am gsum ste
NK063(gu)001:7703: pad+ma'i rgyus las kha dog bsgyur //
NK063(gu)001:7704: bcu drug phyag rgyas legs bkal la //
NK063(gu)001:7705: snal ma gcig kyang lnga lngar ldan //
NK063(gu)001:7706: ye shes rang bzhin shes par bya //
NK063(gu)001:7708: dam tshig kyang de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:7709: kha dog gsum ldan snal ma dgu //
NK063(gu)001:7710: dam tshig skud pa'i rgyu dang grangs //
NK063(gu)001:7711: ras ba la sogs sku gsung thugs //
NK063(gu)001:7714: gos rgyan mdzes pa yid 'ong grogs //
NK063(gu)001:7715: zhes pas mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i yum lo bcu drug ma rgyan gyis brgyan pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:7716: bcu drug phyag rgyas legs btags la //
NK063(gu)001:7718: lnga pa rab gnas ni 'bru bsgyur te chos phun sum tshogs zhes pa yang /
NK063(gu)001:7720: gtsang ma'i snod du legs bkod de //
NK063(gu)001:7721: nyi ma zla ba'i gdan dag la //
NK063(gu)001:7722: thugs las yig 'bru grangs de bzhin //
NK063(gu)001:7723: phyogs bcu dus bzhi mdun drangs te //
NK063(gu)001:7724: mchod sbyar gsol ba gdab par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:7725: sbyor ba'i ye shes grangs mnyam dang //
NK063(gu)001:7726: rdo rje gsum nyid nges par bstim //
NK063(gu)001:7728: thig tshon gnyis kar rab gnas tshul gcig ste b+han+d+ha
NK063(gu)001:7729: la sogs snod gtsang ma gang yin yang snod phyogs
NK063(gu)001:7730: ma nor bar bkod la las gzhung bsrang /
NK063(gu)001:7731: de nas thig tshon dri yis bsangs la cho ga
NK063(gu)001:7732: gsum las rigs lnga yab yum du bskyed cing sku
NK063(gu)001:7733: gsung thugs gsum byin gyis brlabs ye shes lnga yis
NK063(gu)001:7734: dbang bskur snyan gsan dbab spyan drangs dbyer med par
NK063(gu)001:7735: bstims la / phyi nang gis mchod cing bstod pa ci rigs pa bya /
NK063(gu)001:7736: brtan pa dang sbyor ba'i byang chub sems las ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin du bsam pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7737: drug pa thig gdab pa dngos ni /
NK063(gu)001:7738: gong nas thig gdab ces pas gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:7739: dang po dam tshig gi gdab pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:7740: phyogs mtshams legs par phye nas kyang //
NK063(gu)001:7741: so so'i tshad bzhin rgyas par dbye //
NK063(gu)001:7744: dam tshig rjes su gsal bar dbye zer kyang sngon du nam mkha' la gdab pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7745: tha ma nyes pa spang ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:7746: mkhas ldan chen pos bsgrims te bya //
NK063(gu)001:7748: ma bsgrims pa'i nyes pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:7750: thig skud chad na slob dpon 'chi //
NK063(gu)001:7751: rgyun chad lam la gnod par 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:7752: phyogs 'khrul bas ni gnyis ka nyams //
NK063(gu)001:7754: thig skud dam btab pa la 'gong ba yang nyes pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:7756: hri sgra'i phyag rgyas 'dzul bar bya //
NK063(gu)001:7758: don bzhi pa tshon la drug ste /
NK063(gu)001:7764: dang po ni ye shes lnga'i don ma mthong ste
NK063(gu)001:7765: de'i don la rmongs pa rnams la ye shes lnga'i
NK063(gu)001:7766: don bstan pa'i phyir tshon rtsi kha dog lngar bya'o
NK063(gu)001:7767: // gnyis pa rgyu ni gong gi thig gi skabs na tshon phye dang zhes pa ste de ni /
NK063(gu)001:7769: nu sha ra ba byu ru zangs //
NK063(gu)001:7770: a rag ta las byas pa dbye //
NK063(gu)001:7771: zhes pas rab rin po che'o //
NK063(gu)001:7772: de bzhin 'byor bas gzhan dag bsdu //
NK063(gu)001:7776: kha dog nyi shu rtsa lnga'am //
NK063(gu)001:7777: lnga yi tshon gyis bri bar bya //
NK063(gu)001:7780: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor lnga rnams bsgom //
NK063(gu)001:7783: snod rim ma 'dres dag byas la //
NK063(gu)001:7784: h+aum sogs yig 'bru gcig kyang lnga /
NK063(gu)001:7785: kha dog rjes su mthun byas te //
NK063(gu)001:7787: lnga pa dgye lugs dang po ni /
NK063(gu)001:7788: 'dul ba'i cho ga bzhin du dgye //
NK063(gu)001:7790: tha ma nyes pa spang ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:7791: bag med gyur pa'i nyes pa yang //
NK063(gu)001:7792: thig gi rjes su shes par bya //
NK063(gu)001:7794: mchod pa phul nas gshegs na nyes pa med do //
NK063(gu)001:7795: don lnga pa bri ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:7796: lte ba rtsibs dang ldan pa yi //
NK063(gu)001:7797: zhes pa la sogs gzhung brtags nas de la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:7798: slob dpon gyis bri ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:7800: bris pa'i nyes pa spang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:7802: chas ldan dbang phyug thig bteg la //
NK063(gu)001:7803: dbang ldan phyogs nas bskor byas te //
NK063(gu)001:7806: de nas zhal dbang thob pa rnams //
NK063(gu)001:7808: tha ma ni gzhung gzhan las /
NK063(gu)001:7809: tshon thal shor na nad du 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:7810: tshon rtsi srab na dbul por 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:7812: don drug pa rnam pa dgod pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:7813: sku gsung thugs ldan gzugs kyang dgod //
NK063(gu)001:7816: yan lag rgyan rdzogs gzugs sku nyid //
NK063(gu)001:7817: nyi zla pad+ma rim bzhugs pa //
NK063(gu)001:7818: dkyil 'khor sku yi mtshan nyid yin //
NK063(gu)001:7819: tha sogs yang na h+aum m+aum ni //
NK063(gu)001:7820: dkyil 'khor gsung du shes par bya //
NK063(gu)001:7821: phyag rgya gsal bkod thugs dkyil 'khor //
NK063(gu)001:7823: don bdun pa rab gnas la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:7828: yul gang la rgyal ba ye shes sems dpa'i che
NK063(gu)001:7829: ba'i yon tan gyi byin bsdus te gzhug pa'i cho
NK063(gu)001:7830: ga yan lag rdzogs pas khyad par can du gyur
NK063(gu)001:7832: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK063(gu)001:7834: gnyis pa ni pra ti na'i sgras dus rgyun du
NK063(gu)001:7835: rang bzhin bzang por gnas pa las mi 'da' ba
NK063(gu)001:7836: ste / nye bar gyur pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK063(gu)001:7840: rab gnas lugs ni gsum yin te //
NK063(gu)001:7842: dbang po yang rab rtogs pa dang ldan pas dus skad cig tsam la rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:7843: 'bring ting nge 'dzin la goms pas de'i yan lag rdzogs pa'i tshe grub pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:7844: tha mas gzhung nas bshad pa ltar bsnyen pa la
NK063(gu)001:7845: sogs spyi dang bye brag gi cho ga rdzogs pas
NK063(gu)001:7847: de la'ang gsum yin te zhes pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:7851: de la'ang gsum yin te zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:7856: bum pa rin cen las byas pa //
NK063(gu)001:7857: lto dang mgrin par ldan pa la /
NK063(gu)001:7858: kha dog ldan pa'i ras dkris dgang //
NK063(gu)001:7860: bum rdzas kha rgyan mgul chings la sogs dang ldan
NK063(gu)001:7861: pa la bsnyen pa 'bum la sogs pa bya ba
NK063(gu)001:7862: ste / 'di lag len du yan lag gi rab
NK063(gu)001:7863: gnas zhes gong gi thig tshon la sogs dang thun
NK063(gu)001:7864: mong du bya ba dag yin no //
NK063(gu)001:7866: gnyis pa slob bur shes par bya //
NK063(gu)001:7867: dgos pa'i yo byad gnyis sogs la //
NK063(gu)001:7868: las kyi dkyil 'khor las rim sbyar //
NK063(gu)001:7870: slob bu lhar rab gnas bya ba ste 'og tu 'jug pa'i skabs bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:7871: gsum pa dkyil 'khor gyi rab gnas ni /
NK063(gu)001:7873: gnyis car la gzhung nas drug tu bstan kyang lag len du brgyad de /
NK063(gu)001:7874: sngon du bya ba'i rim pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:7875: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:7876: ye shes pa spyan drangs te bstim pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:7877: dbang po la sogs pa'i skyon bsal ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:7878: che ba'i yon tan rgyan chas kyis mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:7879: chu bdun gyis sku khrus gsol zhing ras kyis sku 'phyi ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:7880: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa dbul ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:7881: bden pa'i byin gyis rlabs kyis dmigs shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:7883: bcos bu'i ras ni sna tshogs dang //
NK063(gu)001:7884: rgyan phreng btung ba bro bas bskor //
NK063(gu)001:7887: lus ngag sems dang zhes pa la sogs pas stong pa nyid du sbyangs nas /
NK063(gu)001:7888: ting 'dzin rol mo zhes pa la sogs pas ting 'dzin dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7890: sa la sogs las phyag rgyar byas //
NK063(gu)001:7893: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK063(gu)001:7894: zhes pa la sogs pas dkyil 'khor gang yin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:7895: gzhung du snyan gsan dbab cing spyan drangs nas dbyer
NK063(gu)001:7896: med par bstims te brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba'o
NK063(gu)001:7898: +amo tsak+shu la sogs cho gas mig sman byugs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:7899: thur ma la sogs kyis spyan dbye ba la sogs
NK063(gu)001:7900: dbang po skyon bsal gyi chos bdun bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:7902: bum pas dbang bskur bas ye shes lnga dang ldan
NK063(gu)001:7903: zhing yi ge lngas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK063(gu)001:7904: las dang ldan par bya ba'i spyir mnga' gsol ba'o
NK063(gu)001:7905: // khyad par mnga' gsol ba s+w+aa'i 'phro 'du las
NK063(gu)001:7906: zhi ba la rin po che'i dbu rgyan la sogs
NK063(gu)001:7907: rgyan chas nyi shu rtsa lnga dang /
NK063(gu)001:7908: khro bo la rngams brjid la sogs sum cu rtsa bzhis so //
NK063(gu)001:7910: cho ga ltar zhi ba la chu gtsang la sogs
NK063(gu)001:7911: bdun dang khro bo la zhun chen la sogs bdun
NK063(gu)001:7912: gyi sku khrus gsol zhing ras kyis sku 'phyi bar
NK063(gu)001:7914: glu tshig bro gar rol mo yi //
NK063(gu)001:7915: zhes pa la sogs phyi nang gi dang /
NK063(gu)001:7916: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK063(gu)001:7917: zhes pa la sogs lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:7918: gsal ldan ma'am zhes pa la sogs gsang ba'i mchod pa rnams dbul lo //
NK063(gu)001:7919: tha ma ni che ge mo'i don yongs su ma
NK063(gu)001:7920: rdzogs kyi bar du brtan par bzhugs nas sems can
NK063(gu)001:7921: gyi don yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig la sogs
NK063(gu)001:7922: brtan bzhugs kyi me tog dor nas 'dod ga sol
NK063(gu)001:7924: 'di ni khyad par du le'u bcu pa'i dbang rdzas kyi rab gnas yin la /
NK063(gu)001:7925: spyir sku gsung thugs kyi rten rnams la yang 'di ltar bya ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:7926: don brgyad pa'i spyin sreg ni /
NK063(gu)001:7927: de nyid kyi rtsa ba las /
NK063(gu)001:7929: gnas rdzas thab kyi rnam pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:7930: gzungs dang gtso sems bsgrub pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:7931: phur pa lha dus las rim dang //
NK063(gu)001:7932: lhag ma bcu gcig rdzogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7934: las bzhi re re la yang don bcu gcig ste /
NK063(gu)001:7935: dang po gang du bya ba'i gnas ni de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:7936: ri bo 'dus pa 'i rtse dag dang //
NK063(gu)001:7937: chu gling 'jam pa'i sa phyogs su //
NK063(gu)001:7938: dang bar byed pa'i las rnams brtsam //
NK063(gu)001:7940: nags tshal sman ljongs me tog tshal //
NK063(gu)001:7941: lhun stug ri bo rgyas par bshad //
NK063(gu)001:7943: sum mdo chu bo 'dus pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:7944: bzhi mdo khang stong sdud ces bya //
NK063(gu)001:7946: dur khrod chen po'i sa phyogs su //
NK063(gu)001:7947: lhag par brtsams na nges par 'grub //
NK063(gu)001:7948: ces pas drag po'i gnas so //
NK063(gu)001:7949: don gnyis pa rdzas ni tshig bsgyur te /
NK063(gu)001:7951: bza' btung bro ba'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK063(gu)001:7954: gnyis pa rnam pa lngar bshad de //
NK063(gu)001:7961: dang po ni sngags pa'i chas gos lnga'o //
NK063(gu)001:7962: gnyis pa la yang gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:7964: rtse mo zhi byed yal ga rgyas //
NK063(gu)001:7965: sdong po dbang rtsa mngon spyod pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:7968: shug pa tsan+dana dkar po dang //
NK063(gu)001:7970: zhi rgyas yam shing shes par bya //
NK063(gu)001:7971: dmar la dril zhim shing rnams dang //
NK063(gu)001:7972: dug shing tsher ma can dag ni //
NK063(gu)001:7973: tshil byugs dbang drag me spar ro //
NK063(gu)001:7976: bsgrub bya'i dam rdzas gos sogs dang //
NK063(gu)001:7977: longs spyod de bzhin shes par bya //
NK063(gu)001:7978: dug dang tsha ba rnam gsum dang //
NK063(gu)001:7979: sha chen ra dang ba glang sha /
NK063(gu)001:7980: mchog tu gsod par byed pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:7981: skyur ba dbang ste ling+ga'i rdzas //
NK063(gu)001:7985: me tog dkar po'i gtor mas zhi //
NK063(gu)001:7986: ldong ros gro chan zho dang phrum //
NK063(gu)001:7987: me tog gser phye rgyas pa la'o //
NK063(gu)001:7988: zangs phye bu ram 'bras mar chan //
NK063(gu)001:7990: thams cad sdud pa'i gtor ma yin //
NK063(gu)001:7991: dug rnams lcags phye rdo phye dang //
NK063(gu)001:7992: ra khyi'i khrag dang sha chen dang //
NK063(gu)001:7993: dur sol mur ka'i chan rnams ni //
NK063(gu)001:7994: gsod par byed pa'i gtor ma yin //
NK063(gu)001:7997: mar dkar til dkar nas dkar chan //
NK063(gu)001:7998: mngar gsum tsan+dana dkar po'i shing //
NK063(gu)001:7999: thams cad ye shes bdud rtsi ste //
NK063(gu)001:8000: tha mas ye shes me skyed do //
NK063(gu)001:8001: zho dang mar rnying bu ram sbrang //
NK063(gu)001:8002: rgun 'brum star ka sha chen dang //
NK063(gu)001:8003: dri zhim gser zhing rgyas pa la'o //
NK063(gu)001:8004: dan ti li dang sha chen dang //
NK063(gu)001:8005: ske tshe tsha ba'i mar dag dang //
NK063(gu)001:8006: dmar po'i shing dang r+ts+wa dag gis //
NK063(gu)001:8007: thams cad 'gugs pa'i mchog tu gsungs //
NK063(gu)001:8008: dug dang tshil chen ske tshe'i mar //
NK063(gu)001:8009: sran chen khrag sna tshogs pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:8010: tsher ma can glang sha yis gsod //
NK063(gu)001:8012: don gsum pa thab kyi rnam pa ji ltar bya ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:8013: dbyibs dang kha dog mtshan ldan pa'i //
NK063(gu)001:8015: zhi ba la zlum po mdog dkar po 'khor lo +amo gyis mtshan pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:8016: dkyil 'khor zlum po rim pa gsum //
NK063(gu)001:8018: rgyas pa la gru bzhi ser po rin po che tram gis mtshan pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:8021: dbang la zla gam dmar po pad+ma h+r+aihs mtshan pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:8022: thab khung zla gam gdengs pa la //
NK063(gu)001:8024: drag po la gru gsum nag po khro zhal h+aum gis mtshan pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:8025: dkyil 'khor gru gsum brtsegs ma la //
NK063(gu)001:8027: gzhan yang zhal gdangs spyan bgrad pa'i //
NK063(gu)001:8028: khro zhal shin tu 'jigs par bya //
NK063(gu)001:8029: zhes gsungs pa rnams kyis phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:8030: de dag gi rgya dang dpangs ni /
NK063(gu)001:8032: khru gang dbangs dang zheng du yin //
NK063(gu)001:8033: zab dang gyen du phyed du bshad //
NK063(gu)001:8035: don bzhi pa gzungs ma ni 'di'i nyi shu pa las /
NK063(gu)001:8036: ljon pa dang ni lcug phran tshal //
NK063(gu)001:8037: sdong gcig dang ni mes reg drung //
NK063(gu)001:8038: zhes pa bzhi ni 'di skad du /
NK063(gu)001:8039: bong chung lus mdzes zla ba'i mdog /
NK063(gu)001:8040: g.yas 'khyil lus kyang de bzhin shes //
NK063(gu)001:8041: skad gsal sngags zlos yid mi skyo //
NK063(gu)001:8042: khro spangs pa de zhi la sbyar //
NK063(gu)001:8045: ban glang ser mo gru bzhi pa //
NK063(gu)001:8046: rna ba 'gram slang ring sha rgyas //
NK063(gu)001:8047: yan lag zla mang las la mkhas //
NK063(gu)001:8048: dal zhing blo gros ldan pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:8049: 'phel ba'i dus su shes par bya //
NK063(gu)001:8052: dmar mo zla gam mdzes pa'i zhal //
NK063(gu)001:8053: yal ga sgyu gnas rnam spangs pa //
NK063(gu)001:8054: thabs mkhas brtson 'grus ldan pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:8055: thams cad sdud par byed pa'i mchog /
NK063(gu)001:8058: nag mo gru gsum rtsid mgo ma //
NK063(gu)001:8059: khro gnyer can la gel bag chags //
NK063(gu)001:8060: gtum zhing barlanga tshig 'dzem bag med //
NK063(gu)001:8061: sngags zlos brtul zhugs ldan pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:8062: tha ma'i dus su 'di shes bya //
NK063(gu)001:8064: don lnga pa gtso bo'i sems ni gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:8065: don gyi sems ni chos nyid gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:8067: rang rig sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK063(gu)001:8068: thams cad rang dbang sgyur bdag phyir //
NK063(gu)001:8069: sgrub pa'i gtso bor 'di gsungs so //
NK063(gu)001:8071: gnyis pa stongs kyi sems ni /
NK063(gu)001:8073: dang bas dga' bas chags pas dang //
NK063(gu)001:8074: khros pas ka li rab tu bya //
NK063(gu)001:8076: don drug pa bsgrub bya ni /
NK063(gu)001:8077: rgyal blon gdug pa can la sogs pa bdag gzhan
NK063(gu)001:8078: la gnod pa'i bsam sbyor can ni zhi ba'i yin
NK063(gu)001:8079: te / bdag gzhan gnod pa'i sems dang ni //
NK063(gu)001:8081: tshe dang longs spyod la sogs sgo gsum gyi yon
NK063(gu)001:8082: tan dang mi ldan pa ni rgyas pa'i yin te
NK063(gu)001:8083: / tshe dang longs spyod sgo gsum gyi //
NK063(gu)001:8084: yon tan mngon par mi ldan pa //
NK063(gu)001:8086: mi mos shing mi 'dud pa ni dbang gi yin te /
NK063(gu)001:8087: mos 'dud med pa las rkyen can //
NK063(gu)001:8088: las gsum bdag gzhan don gyi phyir //
NK063(gu)001:8090: dam pa'i chos 'jig pa la sogs zhing bcu ni drag po'i bsgrub bya yin te /
NK063(gu)001:8091: zhing bcur gyur ba'i sems can ni //
NK063(gu)001:8092: dam pa'i chos 'jig ma rungs la //
NK063(gu)001:8094: de yang de dag gi gdug sems zhi ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:8095: longs spyod bsdus te bstim pas 'phel ba dang bdag
NK063(gu)001:8096: la mos shing 'dud par bya ba dang gdug pa
NK063(gu)001:8097: can tshar gcad par bya ba'i ched do //
NK063(gu)001:8098: don bdun pa phur bu ni /
NK063(gu)001:8100: dngul lam dkar po'i shing rnams la //
NK063(gu)001:8101: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zlum mo //
NK063(gu)001:8102: steng 'og logs la khro bcu bsgom //
NK063(gu)001:8104: sngags dang phyag rgyas byin brlabs nas //
NK063(gu)001:8105: mtha' skor yan lag snying la sbyar //
NK063(gu)001:8106: gser ram ser po'i shing dag la //
NK063(gu)001:8107: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zur bzhi //
NK063(gu)001:8108: lha rnams de bzhin rin chen khro //
NK063(gu)001:8109: zur bzhir gnas pas lus gnas bzhir //
NK063(gu)001:8111: zangs sam dmar po'i shing rnams la //
NK063(gu)001:8112: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zla gam //
NK063(gu)001:8113: de bzhin chags pa'i phur bu shes //
NK063(gu)001:8114: zla gam mtha' lngar dbang po sbyar //
NK063(gu)001:8115: lcags sam nag po'i shing rnams la //
NK063(gu)001:8116: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zur gsum //
NK063(gu)001:8117: de bzhin rdo rje phur brlab pa //
NK063(gu)001:8118: zur gsum lus ngag sems la sbyar //
NK063(gu)001:8122: sbyin dang sreg pa'i lha gnyis te //
NK063(gu)001:8124: dang po sbyin pa'i lha ni /
NK063(gu)001:8125: zhal du gyur pa'i me bos la //
NK063(gu)001:8128: sangs rgyas rigs kyi sprul pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:8129: thams cad las la thogs med 'jug /
NK063(gu)001:8130: sku mdog cha lugs rim bzhin shes //
NK063(gu)001:8133: gnyis pa sreg pa'i lha ni /
NK063(gu)001:8135: rgyal rnams zhi la dkar ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:8138: rin chen dga' 'phro ser skya ni //
NK063(gu)001:8142: 'dod chags rdo rje lcags sgrog dang //
NK063(gu)001:8143: mdog ni dmar smug 'od po che //
NK063(gu)001:8146: zhe sdang rdo rje gtum chen 'bar //
NK063(gu)001:8147: dud kha nag po mdog 'dra ba //
NK063(gu)001:8148: zhes pa la sogs rigs kyi lha rnams gtso bor 'gyur ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:8150: dbyar dgun ston dpyid las rim dang //
NK063(gu)001:8151: snga dro gung dgong nam phyed dus //
NK063(gu)001:8152: las rim brtsams na shis par bshad //
NK063(gu)001:8154: lo dang zhag gcig gi dbang du rim pa bzhin dgun nam snga dro zhi ba /
NK063(gu)001:8155: dbyar ram nyin gung rgyas pa /
NK063(gu)001:8157: dpyid dam nam gung drag po'o //
NK063(gu)001:8158: don bcu pa las kyi rim pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:8159: las bzhi'i mchod pa rab tu sbyin //
NK063(gu)001:8161: me thab kyi steng du sreg shing gi thab brtsigs /
NK063(gu)001:8162: yam shing lha grangs dang mnyam par dgod /
NK063(gu)001:8163: phyi nang gi mchod pa dang gong gi sreg rdzas rnams bshams /
NK063(gu)001:8164: me dar rigs dang mthun pa dgab /
NK063(gu)001:8165: de nas phyi rol du cha gsum btang /
NK063(gu)001:8166: nang du tshul phyag nas tshogs la sogs yan chad las gzhung bsrang /
NK063(gu)001:8168: de nas thab bsangs la dam tshig gi me lha bskyed /
NK063(gu)001:8169: de la rigs bdag gis dbu brgyan /
NK063(gu)001:8171: ye shes pa snyan gsan phab nas spyan drang /
NK063(gu)001:8172: kun po la sogs phyi nang gis mchod /
NK063(gu)001:8173: sreg rdzas rnams rtsa sngags la sh+aan+tim la sogs bsgyur la dgang blugs bdun nam nyer gcig tu dbul /
NK063(gu)001:8174: de nas bstod cing phrin las bcol la 'dod don la gsol ba gdab pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8175: de nas me lha'i lto bar b+h+r+aum las zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK063(gu)001:8176: der cho ga gsum las rang gi rigs kyis gtso bo byas pa'i sreg lha rnams bskyed /
NK063(gu)001:8177: de la dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK063(gu)001:8178: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor snyan gsan dbab cing spyan drang bstim zhing brtan par bzhugs la /
NK063(gu)001:8179: kun po la sogs phyi nang gis mchod /
NK063(gu)001:8180: de nas lha tshogs rnams kyi rtsa ba'i sngags la
NK063(gu)001:8181: sh+aan+tim ku ru la sogs las bzhir bsgyur la dgang
NK063(gu)001:8182: blugs bdun nam nyer gcig phul la /
NK063(gu)001:8183: bstod pa rdzogs pa'i rjes su 'dod don gsol gdab bo //
NK063(gu)001:8184: de nas ye shes pa gshegs shing dam tshig pa bsdu'o //
NK063(gu)001:8185: don tha ma lhag ma ni le'u nyi shu pa nas 'byung ba ltar bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:8186: de nas go bgo lus bsrung bya /
NK063(gu)001:8190: de dag gang la gang bya zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:8191: sa chog gi dus su zhi ba'i bya zhing /
NK063(gu)001:8192: slob bu'i rab gnas kyi dus su rmi lam ngan na drag po'i bya la /
NK063(gu)001:8193: dkyil 'khor rab gnas kyi dus su rgyas pa'i bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:8194: dngos gzhi dbang bskur ba'i dus su dbang gi sbyin sreg bya ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:8195: de ltar yang rdo rje las rim las /
NK063(gu)001:8196: sa dang rab gnas rnam gnyis dang //
NK063(gu)001:8197: bde ba sbyin pa'i dus nyid do //
NK063(gu)001:8199: don dgu pa dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:8203: kun byed dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK063(gu)001:8206: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang //
NK063(gu)001:8208: dang po ru 'jug pa ni ru nyid dbang gos
NK063(gu)001:8209: dang ldan pas dkyil 'khor gyi shar du phyin la
NK063(gu)001:8210: / lag tu me tog thogs te rig pa'i me
NK063(gu)001:8211: tog dor zhing sid+d+hi bskul bas lha dang gnyis su
NK063(gu)001:8214: dbang gos ldan pa dbang phyug ste //
NK063(gu)001:8215: gzhan dag gzhan gyis mdzes par bya //
NK063(gu)001:8217: lha rnams mngon byas rin chen ldan //
NK063(gu)001:8218: 'bru lnga rdo rje dam tshig gi //
NK063(gu)001:8219: sngags kyis sku gsung thugs yon tan //
NK063(gu)001:8220: phrin las ye shes gnyis med sbyar //
NK063(gu)001:8222: gnyis pa bzod gsol ni slob dpon gyis tshig brjod pas rdor dril 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis bskul //
NK063(gu)001:8224: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi zhal mdzum pa'i mdangs
NK063(gu)001:8225: kyis dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK063(gu)001:8226: kyi gdung 'tshob pa rdo rje slob dpon khyod kyis
NK063(gu)001:8227: bu dkyil 'khor du gzhug cing dbang gis rgyud smin
NK063(gu)001:8228: par gyis shig ces gnang ba thob par bsam ste
NK063(gu)001:8230: 'dzum bcas gnang ba thob par bsam //
NK063(gu)001:8232: de ltar chos gnyis kyis ru dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa de nas /
NK063(gu)001:8233: don gnyis pa slob ma dkyil 'khor du chos bcu drug gi sgo nas gzhug par bya ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:8234: ji skad du de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:8235: khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul dang //
NK063(gu)001:8236: bgegs bskrad lhar brlab dam tshig sbyin //
NK063(gu)001:8237: de nyid dpog dang chu nan dang //
NK063(gu)001:8238: bsgrag dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:8239: lha dbab pa dang nan tan dang //
NK063(gu)001:8240: mig dbye dkyil 'khor legs bstan dang //
NK063(gu)001:8241: tshogs mchog yon dang rnam bco brgyad //
NK063(gu)001:8243: 'dir bcu drug dang gong gi gnyis te bco brgyad do //
NK063(gu)001:8244: de las dang po khrus zhes pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:8245: shin tu bzang po'i bgo ba rnams //
NK063(gu)001:8246: dri yi chu yis dag par bya //
NK063(gu)001:8249: snyim par me tog ldan pa dag /
NK063(gu)001:8250: ras sogs dmar pos gdong g.yogs la //
NK063(gu)001:8252: dri dang zhes pa ni slob dpon gyis /
NK063(gu)001:8253: bu khyod ci la dga' zhes dri //
NK063(gu)001:8255: skal bzang bdag dgas lan blan la //
NK063(gu)001:8256: zhes de las kyi slob dpon gyis //
NK063(gu)001:8257: 'khor lo'i drung du bkri bar bya //
NK063(gu)001:8260: thal sbyar gus dang bcas pa yis //
NK063(gu)001:8261: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras bcas dang //
NK063(gu)001:8262: zhes rgyal ba la phul bas byin gyis rlob cing /
NK063(gu)001:8263: dbang phyug sangs rgyas da ltar bdag /
NK063(gu)001:8264: ces slob dpon la phul bas dbang bskur ba la /
NK063(gu)001:8265: ma 'ongs rang bzhin sems can la //
NK063(gu)001:8266: zhes sems can la phul bas 'gro don 'phel ba ste de ltar yang /
NK063(gu)001:8267: dgos pa gsum phyir lus dbul bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:8270: tshe bsrung sbyor ba'i khro tshogs kyis //
NK063(gu)001:8271: bar chad bgegs bskrad mtshams bcad la //
NK063(gu)001:8272: zhes pas slob dpon gyi thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum bu'i
NK063(gu)001:8273: smin phrag tu 'phros pas gzhal yas khang sgo gcig
NK063(gu)001:8274: pa zhig bskyed / de'i dbus su h+aum ka ra /
NK063(gu)001:8275: sgo la +aar+ya a tsa la bskyed la tshe bsrung /
NK063(gu)001:8276: bi shwa badz+rasa bgegs bskrad do //
NK063(gu)001:8278: sgrib pa phral zhing h+aum las rdo rje sems dpar bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:8279: sgrib sbyangs rnam shes cho ga yis //
NK063(gu)001:8280: h+aum las sems dpa' ma gzhan yang rung //
NK063(gu)001:8282: dam tshig sbyin zhes pa ni bdud rtsi sku gsung thugs su brlab sa la /
NK063(gu)001:8283: dpal ldan rdo rje sku 'chang ba //
NK063(gu)001:8284: la sogs pa'i cho gas sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig sbyin pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:8285: dam tshig chen po ye shes lnga //
NK063(gu)001:8286: rang bzhin 'bras bu sku gsung thugs //
NK063(gu)001:8287: gzi brjid ldan pas byin brlabs la //
NK063(gu)001:8288: dam tshig sdom pa'i mchog ces bya //
NK063(gu)001:8290: de nyid dpog ces pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:8291: lag len ltar tshig gis dpog pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8293: tsan+dana dkar dmar sbyar ba la //
NK063(gu)001:8294: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rab gnas bya //
NK063(gu)001:8296: tsan+dana gyi chu rdo rje gnod sbyin du bskyed nas lce la bzhag te /
NK063(gu)001:8297: cho ga brjod cing sngags kyis dam tshig ma bsrungs
NK063(gu)001:8298: ba'i skyon gyi g.yang sa bstan te nan tan bya
NK063(gu)001:8299: zhing / yang bdud rtsi'i chu snying gar bzhag ste
NK063(gu)001:8300: dam tshig bsrungs pa'i yon tan gyis brod bskyed de
NK063(gu)001:8301: srungs shig pa'i nan tan bya ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:8303: nges pa'i theg pa 'di gzhung bzhin du spyod gcig par bsgrag pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8304: rin chen dor zhes pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:8305: dkyil 'khor yid la mngon byas nas //
NK063(gu)001:8306: 'dod pa'am yang na gzhan yang rung //
NK063(gu)001:8307: dor te 'brel pa legs par brtag /
NK063(gu)001:8310: lcags kyu ha his dgug byas la //
NK063(gu)001:8311: nyes legs phrin las gsal byas la //
NK063(gu)001:8312: phyag rgyas bstims la brtan par bya //
NK063(gu)001:8314: me tog bu'i spyi bor bzhag la lha gang yin
NK063(gu)001:8315: pa 'og min nas spyan drangs la bstim pa ni
NK063(gu)001:8316: phyi'i lha dang / de nyid bsgom pa'i thabs yod de /
NK063(gu)001:8317: bsgom du gzhug pa ni nang gi lha dbab pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8319: me tog phog cing gong du phab pa'i lha de bu la bsgom par nan tan bya ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:8320: skal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes ni //
NK063(gu)001:8321: zhes pa la sogs gzhung brtags la /
NK063(gu)001:8322: bsgom pa'i yon tan gyi sgo nas nan tan bya ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:8324: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyor na //
NK063(gu)001:8326: gcig dang du ma yongs bral phyir //
NK063(gu)001:8330: lha yi sku nyid gsal bsgoms na //
NK063(gu)001:8332: de nyid chu zla'i tshul shes na //
NK063(gu)001:8335: de nyid ma bsgoms pa'i skyon gyi sgo nas nan tan bya ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:8336: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:8339: gang zhig phyag rgya 'di spangs na //
NK063(gu)001:8340: nyon mongs ngan song gsum du skye //
NK063(gu)001:8342: bla med 'gro ba'i rgyun chad de //
NK063(gu)001:8343: rigs chad nyid du gnas par 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:8346: yi dam lha yi mtshan nyid ni //
NK063(gu)001:8347: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK063(gu)001:8348: sku gsung rdo rje'i bdag po'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:8349: lha spangs dge spyad don med 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:8352: gser sogs mtshon byed nges blangs la //
NK063(gu)001:8353: 'od zer thur mas dbye bya ste //
NK063(gu)001:8355: sor mo yig 'brur bslabs pa'i 'od zer gyis phye
NK063(gu)001:8356: bas ling tog bsal nas ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK063(gu)001:8358: 'khor lo mngon pa'i nga rgyal bya //
NK063(gu)001:8360: dkyil 'khor legs bstan zhes pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:8361: chos rnams thams cad gnyis med pa'i //
NK063(gu)001:8362: dbyings su thim pa'i 'od zer gsal //
NK063(gu)001:8363: gcig dang spros pa thams cad med //
NK063(gu)001:8364: dkyil 'khor spros med zlum pa'i tshul //
NK063(gu)001:8366: rin po che'i tshar non la sogs pas dkyil 'khor gyi don rtags bshad par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:8367: tshogs mchog yon dang zhes pa ni yon dbul ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:8368: dbang dang dngos grub 'dod pas ni //
NK063(gu)001:8369: 'di la shin tu nan tan bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:8372: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK063(gu)001:8373: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK063(gu)001:8374: rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NK063(gu)001:8375: zhes pa la sogs pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:8376: rnam bco brgyad ces pa slob dpon 'jug pa'i chos
NK063(gu)001:8377: gnyis dang bu 'jug pa'i bcu drug ste bsdoms pas
NK063(gu)001:8378: dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa la tho bco brgyad do
NK063(gu)001:8379: // don tha ma bzhugs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK063(gu)001:8380: bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK063(gu)001:8381: zhes pa la sogs gzhung brtag ste /
NK063(gu)001:8382: de yang rdo rje las rim las /
NK063(gu)001:8383: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK063(gu)001:8384: dkyil 'khor mngon du zhugs pa yis //
NK063(gu)001:8385: bsod nams rtag pa gang yin pa //
NK063(gu)001:8386: phyis kyang de bzhin lung bstan phyir //
NK063(gu)001:8388: sbyor ba ye shes kyi yon tan dang /
NK063(gu)001:8389: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bar legs zhugs pas //
NK063(gu)001:8390: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi //
NK063(gu)001:8391: dkyil 'khor kun tu zhugs pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:8392: zhes pa rdo rje gsum gyis brlabs pa'i yon tan no //
NK063(gu)001:8393: gnyis pa khro bo lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK063(gu)001:8394: khro bo dkyil 'khor de bzhin te //
NK063(gu)001:8395: zhes pa'ang zhi ba ltar don bcu las /
NK063(gu)001:8397: snod skrad sa mnan byin gyis brlab //
NK063(gu)001:8398: ces pa phal cher zhi ba dang mthun no //
NK063(gu)001:8400: lus gang lus do gsum gyi tshad //
NK063(gu)001:8401: stegs bu khru gang lus gang dang //
NK063(gu)001:8402: lus gsum bcu drug khru ldan dang //
NK063(gu)001:8403: nyi shu'am nyi shu lngar ldan pa //
NK063(gu)001:8404: dpag tshad rgyang grags rim bzhin du //
NK063(gu)001:8405: 'jigs byed lha grangs rim pa bzhin //
NK063(gu)001:8408: ba su ta'am rgyus chen la //
NK063(gu)001:8409: dam tshig ye shes sku gsum lnga //
NK063(gu)001:8412: kha dog nyi shu rtsa lnga'am //
NK063(gu)001:8413: lnga yi tshon gyis bri bar bya //
NK063(gu)001:8414: dur khrod tshon byin ldan pa yis //
NK063(gu)001:8418: gru bzhi sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan //
NK063(gu)001:8419: yang na tshad med rtsibs steng lnga //
NK063(gu)001:8420: 'khor lo bar khyams sgo ldan pa'i //
NK063(gu)001:8421: pho brang lnga pa bri bar bya //
NK063(gu)001:8424: phyag rgya gzungs dang snying po rnams //
NK063(gu)001:8427: lhag pa gzugs brnyan rab gnas dang //
NK063(gu)001:8429: don brgyad zhi ba ltar la /
NK063(gu)001:8430: khyad par du che ba'i yon tan rgyan chas ni dur khrod kyi chas dang /
NK063(gu)001:8431: chu bdun ni zhun chen gyi khu ba la sogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8432: sbyin sreg ni zhi ba ltar don bcu gcig khro bor bsgyur ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:8433: 'jug pa ni gnyis su zhi ba ltar ro //
NK063(gu)001:8435: 'jigs byed stangs dpyal gnyis sa ma lnga //
NK063(gu)001:8436: byas te dad ldan rab zhugs na //
NK063(gu)001:8440: bsam yas dag la'ang de bzhin bya //
NK063(gu)001:8441: zhes pas gong ltar bcu ste bgrang /
NK063(gu)001:8442: de las sa gzhi mnyam pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:8443: chos thams cad mnyam par rtogs pa'am ji bzhin pa la blo 'jog pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8445: rig pas dpags pa'i tshad du'o //
NK063(gu)001:8447: yang na rgyang grags dpag tshad dam //
NK063(gu)001:8448: nam mkha'i dbyings ni bsam yas par //
NK063(gu)001:8451: slob dpon mthar nye'i lam gnas pas //
NK063(gu)001:8452: rgyang grags dpag tshad la sogs pa //
NK063(gu)001:8453: rdo rje'i thig tshad dor tsam gyis //
NK063(gu)001:8454: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gsal ldan pa //
NK063(gu)001:8455: dkyil 'khor sna tshogs mchog tu gsungs //
NK063(gu)001:8458: rdo rje thig sna dor tsam gyis //
NK063(gu)001:8459: zhes pas bsgom par blo btang ba tsam gyis so //
NK063(gu)001:8461: bsgom pa'i tshe rig pa la kha dog nyer lnga'am lngar gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:8463: gzhal yas khang bsgom pa nyid do //
NK063(gu)001:8465: brten pa lha'i sku gsung thugs su skyed pas bkod pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8466: rab gnas ni ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs nas bstims te mchod pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8467: phyi'i rang bzhin dang thugs rje'i dang nang gi longs
NK063(gu)001:8468: spyod dang spros bcas spros med dang gsang ba'i khams
NK063(gu)001:8469: bzhi dang gsum gyi sbyin sreg rnams so //
NK063(gu)001:8472: yon tan ni 'og min du sems dpa' zhugs pa dang mnyam pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:8475: de las 'dir de bzhin bya zhes pa ni rnam
NK063(gu)001:8476: grangs bcur gong ma la snyog pa yin gyis don
NK063(gu)001:8477: rnams tha dad par sems te /
NK063(gu)001:8478: gong ma gnyis lhag pa gzugs brnyan yin la /
NK063(gu)001:8479: 'di ni ting nge 'dzin gyi yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:8480: de dag gis phan nus kyi dbang gi dkyil 'khor bstan te /
NK063(gu)001:8481: gsang dbang gi dkyil 'khor ni phal cher gzhung brtags la /
NK063(gu)001:8483: sor ni bzhi yi tshad du bya //
NK063(gu)001:8485: dkyil 'khor mdzub gang tshad du bya //
NK063(gu)001:8486: zhes pa ni thabs kyi rdo rje'o //
NK063(gu)001:8487: 'dir kha cig mtshon byed rtags kyi dkyil 'khor zhes
NK063(gu)001:8488: pa gser dngul la sogs la bzo bo mkhas pas
NK063(gu)001:8489: byas pa la 'dod zer ba ni gsang sngags kyi
NK063(gu)001:8492: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dam pa de //
NK063(gu)001:8493: zhes bde ba dang ldan pa mkha' gsang gi dkyil
NK063(gu)001:8494: 'khor gyis de ye shes su ngos 'dzin pa yin
NK063(gu)001:8496: ye shes lnga yi ro ldan pas //
NK063(gu)001:8497: dkyil 'khor zhes su brjod pa ste //
NK063(gu)001:8499: gser dngul la sogs bem pos bde ba'i ye shes mtshon mi nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:8500: de ltar bri bar gzhung brtag /
NK063(gu)001:8501: de ltar dkyil 'khor la brten nas dbang bskur ba le'u bcu pa ltar yin no //
NK063(gu)001:8502: de ltar dbang thob nas tshogs bsgrub pa'i phyir tshogs
NK063(gu)001:8503: kyi sgrub pa po ni mjug gcod kyi chos bco
NK063(gu)001:8504: lnga tshang ba ste gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:8505: cho ga lnga ni zhes pa de lam spyi'i dbang du le'u lnga pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:8506: ston pa mchod brtson zhes pa la sogs 'grub pa'i rgyu lnga po de yin la /
NK063(gu)001:8507: lam bye brag gi dbang stong snying gnyis rgya gcig phra rags gnyis spros pa dang lnga'o //
NK063(gu)001:8508: lam de dag gi tshe 'phro 'du'i dbang du a
NK063(gu)001:8509: las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor ma las nyi ma'i dkyil
NK063(gu)001:8510: 'khor de'i steng du gsung yig 'bru de las thugs
NK063(gu)001:8511: phyag mtshan de las sku rdzogs pa ste de dag
NK063(gu)001:8513: sgrub pa'i yo byad lnga ni lam spyi'i dbang du
NK063(gu)001:8514: bsrung bya'i dam tshig bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin rtogs
NK063(gu)001:8515: pa'i shes rab don dam kun rdzob kyi byang sems
NK063(gu)001:8516: gnyis snying rje dang lnga ste /
NK063(gu)001:8518: dam tshig ting 'dzin shes rab dang //
NK063(gu)001:8519: byang chub sems dang snying rje lnga'o //
NK063(gu)001:8521: khyad par gyi lam gyi dbang du dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga dang /
NK063(gu)001:8523: 'dir tshogs kyi sgrub pa pos longs spyod pa'i dbang du //
NK063(gu)001:8525: gos rgyan bza' btung klu dang tshig /
NK063(gu)001:8528: +aa li k+aa li zhes pa la sogs pa nyid rdzogs par ldan pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:8529: sngags kyi zhes pa ni man+t+ra'i sgra las drangs na yid skyob pa'i phyir lha yin te /
NK063(gu)001:8531: ma na yid ces bya ba ste //
NK063(gu)001:8532: tra ni skyob pa nyid du bshad //
NK063(gu)001:8533: ces pas de yang rtsa ba'i lha'o //
NK063(gu)001:8534: yan lag ces pa ni le'u brgyad pa ltar thabs kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:8536: bsam mi khyab kyi lha rnams so //
NK063(gu)001:8537: lnga rdzogs zhes pa ni dbu rgyan ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor lnga'o //
NK063(gu)001:8538: de dag gi 'phro 'du'i dbang du thugs ka'i ye shes sems dpa' /
NK063(gu)001:8539: de'i thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du thugs phyag mtshan /
NK063(gu)001:8540: de'i lte ba la rgyu'i sa bon la sngags kyis bskor ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:8541: de ltar bco lnga tshang ba'i sgrub pa po ston
NK063(gu)001:8542: pa 'khor la sogs pa rnams dam tshig ma nyams
NK063(gu)001:8543: shing rkyen 'jug pa ting nge 'dzin la rab tu
NK063(gu)001:8545: lam du gyur pa'i 'bras bu tshe dbang 'grub pa'i
NK063(gu)001:8546: dus zhig dang khams dang brtson pa rab yin na
NK063(gu)001:8547: sum cu phrag drug la sogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8549: de la gnyis las blo chung na rnam smin 'grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:8550: ji skad du rdo rje las /
NK063(gu)001:8551: bro glu gar dang ting 'dzin thabs //
NK063(gu)001:8552: bar chad med pas bsgrub par bya //
NK063(gu)001:8553: gal te 'dod pa ma rdzogs par //
NK063(gu)001:8554: sgyu ma'i lus de ma brtan na //
NK063(gu)001:8555: yid kyi rdo rje gsum gnas pas //
NK063(gu)001:8556: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin te //
NK063(gu)001:8557: phyin chad 'jigs bral khyung bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:8559: blo chen tshe dbang la sbyor nus pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:8560: dbang sgyur zhes pa lus la dbang thob pa skye 'jig med pa rdo rje'i lus so //
NK063(gu)001:8561: de la'ang rigs kyi bye brag bzhi las bcud len
NK063(gu)001:8562: rtsi dang bde ba thabs dang sgron ma rlung la
NK063(gu)001:8563: sogs btags pa ba gsum las dam pa lam mchog
NK063(gu)001:8564: yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang mtshan nyid pa 'grub
NK063(gu)001:8565: pa'o // des brgyud nas mthar thug tu sku lnga 'grub pa'i dus ni /
NK063(gu)001:8566: tshe dbang grub pa de'i tshe rang don du mthar
NK063(gu)001:8567: thug gi 'bras bu la sbyor ba'i dus nges pa
NK063(gu)001:8568: ni lo brgya phrag bcu drug ste /
NK063(gu)001:8569: stong drug brgya tshun chad kyis sbyor ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:8571: lo ni bcu dang drug pa yi //
NK063(gu)001:8572: brgya brgya dag na bsnur zhing gnas //
NK063(gu)001:8573: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas sar //
NK063(gu)001:8575: de yang lam gyi rim pa ma dor bar mthar
NK063(gu)001:8576: chags su rgya chen lhun grub nas brgyud nas sku
NK063(gu)001:8577: lnga la sbyor ba yang yod cing /
NK063(gu)001:8578: thod rgal ba yin na rgya dor cig car mthar
NK063(gu)001:8579: 'gro ba zhes rgya chen dor te lhun grub nas
NK063(gu)001:8580: brgyud nas sku lnga la sbyor ba yang yod la
NK063(gu)001:8582: yun ring chos kyi bde spyad nas //
NK063(gu)001:8584: mthong ba'i chos la mya ngan 'da' //
NK063(gu)001:8585: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas sar //
NK063(gu)001:8586: zhes gong ma gnyis car dor nas mthar thug la
NK063(gu)001:8587: sbyor ba yang yod pas de dag gang yin yang
NK063(gu)001:8588: rung ste / sbyar bya sku lnga ni le'u drug par bstan pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:8589: ye nas rang rig la lhun gyis grub pa'i don
NK063(gu)001:8590: lam 'dis mngon du byas pa'i mthar thug gi 'bras
NK063(gu)001:8591: bu'i che ba'i yon tan ma lus pa rdzogs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:8593: de ltar bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bu dngos de rang snang du grub tshul ni /
NK063(gu)001:8594: lhun grub nas brgyud pa'i dbang du ye shes thig
NK063(gu)001:8595: le ni lhun grub kyi mnyam gzhag zhig dgongs pa
NK063(gu)001:8596: spros pa dang bral ba de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:8597: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes thig le ste spros bral
NK063(gu)001:8598: de nyid dang tha dad med pas snang ba yin
NK063(gu)001:8599: zhes so // 'o na lhun grub de mthar lam pa ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:8600: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa dang tha dad med pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:8602: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa snang ba la lam pa min pas khyab cing /
NK063(gu)001:8603: 'dod na lhun grub de mthar lam pa yin par gsal lo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:8604: thig le nyid ces pa ni mthar lam gyi mnyam
NK063(gu)001:8605: gzhag dang sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa gnyis spros bral
NK063(gu)001:8606: du 'dra ba'i phyir 'dra ba rgyu mtshan du byas
NK063(gu)001:8607: nas snang zhes brjod pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:8609: don dang 'dra bar myong ba la //
NK063(gu)001:8610: don myong zhes ni 'dogs pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:8614: bag la nyal dang sgrib pa rnams //
NK063(gu)001:8615: bcom ldan 'das par gyur pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:8616: zhes khyab par yod na ci 'gal te khyab pa med do //
NK063(gu)001:8617: des na sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa de blo'i yul du ma gyur pas bsam gyi mi khyab pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8618: sgrib pa dang bral ba'i ye shes de shes bya'i
NK063(gu)001:8619: dkyil 'khor ma lus pa'i khyab byed yin pas mtha'
NK063(gu)001:8621: 'o na de sangs rgyas nyag gcig gi dgongs pa yin nam zhe na ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:8622: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhir mngon par rdzogs par sangs
NK063(gu)001:8623: rgyas pa ma lus pa'i dgongs pa gcig tu mthar
NK063(gu)001:8624: phyin pa ste rgyal ba la rgyud tha dad ma
NK063(gu)001:8626: 'o na sku dang rigs dang zhi khro la sogs
NK063(gu)001:8627: tha dad du bshad pa dang 'gal lo zhe na
NK063(gu)001:8628: / de dag ni gdul bya la snang tshul yin
NK063(gu)001:8629: gyi de ba'i snang ba nas tha dad med de
NK063(gu)001:8630: / / ji skad du bzhi pa las /
NK063(gu)001:8631: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dgongs pa gcig tu
NK063(gu)001:8632: gyur nas mnyam pa chen po'i tshul rdo rje'i dbyings
NK063(gu)001:8633: su chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ting
NK063(gu)001:8634: nge 'dzin las ma g.yos par zhes pa la sogs
NK063(gu)001:8635: du ma gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:8636: de'i che ba'i yon tan ni brjod par mi nus kyang cung zad rigs bsdus na lngar gsal te /
NK063(gu)001:8638: zhing khams rnam par dag pa bsam gyis mi khyab cing mtha' yas pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:8639: 'dir rgya khyon 'di tsam zhes pa'i tshad dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang dang /
NK063(gu)001:8640: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i gdan la sogs gdan khri dang /
NK063(gu)001:8641: mtshan dang dpe byad la sogs rgyan dang /
NK063(gu)001:8642: gzugs kyi lha mo la sogs 'dod pa'i yon tan
NK063(gu)001:8643: gyi rol mo'i sprin sna tshogs pa ni longs spyod
NK063(gu)001:8644: do // de ltar rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin
NK063(gu)001:8645: pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi che ba'i yon tan ma lus
NK063(gu)001:8646: shing mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo bsam yas
NK063(gu)001:8648: thob pa'i tshul ni skad cig ma dang po la
NK063(gu)001:8649: rang mtshan mthong nas gnyis pa la de rig pa
NK063(gu)001:8650: la gsal bas thob pa la ma rag pa ni
NK063(gu)001:8651: nye bar bsnyen pa ste de mthar rdzogs shing thob
NK063(gu)001:8652: pa dang bdag don grub pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:8653: des gzhan don mdzad pa por snang ba ni rgya
NK063(gu)001:8654: che zhes pas spyir mdzad pa bsam gyi mi khyab
NK063(gu)001:8655: pa'o // bye brag tu gsung lnga lhun gyis grub
NK063(gu)001:8656: pa las gdul bya rang gi blo dang mtshams par
NK063(gu)001:8657: theg pa sna tshogs kyi don 'byung ba ni gdul
NK063(gu)001:8658: bya dang mthun par snang ba yin te lhun gyis
NK063(gu)001:8659: grub pa'i ye shes de gdul bya rang rang gi
NK063(gu)001:8660: snang ba dang mthun par shar ba'i rgyu mtshan gsum
NK063(gu)001:8662: rang byung gi ye shes dang /
NK063(gu)001:8664: lhun gyi grub pa'i ye shes gsum tshul gcig tu gyur pas /
NK063(gu)001:8667: sgra mi snyan na dpag bsam gyi shing las dgos
NK063(gu)001:8668: 'dod 'byung ba dang lha'am klu'i yul na dbang gi
NK063(gu)001:8669: rgyal po la sogs yid bzhin gyi rin po che
NK063(gu)001:8670: dang gzhan yang lha'i bum pa bzang po dang rnam
NK063(gu)001:8671: thos kyi bu'i ne'u le'i rkyal pa la sogs la
NK063(gu)001:8673: rta dang glang chen la sogs dgos 'dod rnams rin
NK063(gu)001:8674: po che de dag la rdzas su grub nas yod
NK063(gu)001:8675: pa la longs spyod pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:8677: rin po che de dag dgos 'dod kyi rang bzhin du grub cing 'bru bsgyur te /
NK063(gu)001:8678: de sems can rang rang gi sngon gyi bsod nams las grub pa ltar snang ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:8679: ji ltar dmigs shing gsol ba btab pa ltar 'dod pa rnams grub par bstan pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:8680: de dang 'dra bar chos nyid mngon du byas pa
NK063(gu)001:8681: las bdag don grub pa dang gzhan don mdzad pa
NK063(gu)001:8682: por snang bas ngo mtshar zhing rang gi ngo bo
NK063(gu)001:8683: chos kyi sku cir yang ma grub cing gzugs sku
NK063(gu)001:8684: gnyis su ma 'gags pas cho 'phrul yin la yon
NK063(gu)001:8685: tan nyer lnga la sogs khyad par 'phags pas rmad
NK063(gu)001:8686: du byung ba sangs rgyas kyi thugs su chud pa'i
NK063(gu)001:8687: chos de rang gi sems las gzhan na yod pa
NK063(gu)001:8688: cig btsal nas 'ongs pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:8690: lam gyi thabs su thabs kyis lam la brtan pa
NK063(gu)001:8691: thob cing grol ba'i lam shes rab kyis chos nyid
NK063(gu)001:8692: mngon du byas pa de lta bu'i ngang du 'bras
NK063(gu)001:8694: de ltar grub pa'i 'bras bu rang gi ngo bo
NK063(gu)001:8695: ni thob byed rgyu rkyen gzhan las byung ba ma
NK063(gu)001:8696: yin pa'i phyir / shes byed yang dag pa'i don
NK063(gu)001:8697: rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis shes bya chos kyi dbyings
NK063(gu)001:8698: chos nyid dang gzhan nyid de rtogs nas /
NK063(gu)001:8699: ji ltar snang ba thams cad thabs kyi sgo nas phyag rgyar gyur pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:8700: lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes la ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes rol pa zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:8701: 'o na de bden pa'i rang bzhin yin nam zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:8703: ye shes la ye shes rol pa nyid kyang yang
NK063(gu)001:8704: dag par nam grub ste gsog ltar snying po med
NK063(gu)001:8705: do // de las gzhan yang rgyal ba sprul pa'i
NK063(gu)001:8706: sku 'jig rten du sngon du byung nas 'khor ba
NK063(gu)001:8707: sdug bsngal las skyob pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:8708: longs sku'i brda'i sgo nas dang /
NK063(gu)001:8709: chos sku'i byin gyis brlabs kyi sgo nas chos ston
NK063(gu)001:8710: pa'ang gong ma de bzhin te yang dag par nam
NK063(gu)001:8711: grub ste ngo bos stongs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8712: 'o na don byed mi nus par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:8713: don bya ba'i yul la don byed nus pa'i rgyu
NK063(gu)001:8714: mtshan ni chos sku las ma g.yos bzhin gzugs sku
NK063(gu)001:8715: gnyis kyi sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi
NK063(gu)001:8716: 'khor lor snang ba'i phyir de'i gzi byin gyis don
NK063(gu)001:8717: mdzad pa'o // de ltar gdul bya la snang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:8718: du de pa la mdzad par ma grub pas sgyu
NK063(gu)001:8720: de gnyis dbyer med pa'i phyir rdo rje yin zhing
NK063(gu)001:8721: gnyen po dang bral bas btsan po ste de gzhan
NK063(gu)001:8722: las khyad par du 'phags pas mchog yin no //
NK063(gu)001:8723: 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid gcig dang du ma la sogs
NK063(gu)001:8724: pa'i mtha' dang bral zhing rang byung du bstan pa
NK063(gu)001:8725: ni rgyal ba rnams ni khyab byed chos skus khyab
NK063(gu)001:8726: pa cig las ma g.yos par gzugs sku tha dad
NK063(gu)001:8727: kyi mdzad pa sna tshogs su snang ba'i phyir gcig
NK063(gu)001:8728: dang bral la / khyab bya gzugs sku tha dad
NK063(gu)001:8729: kyi rang bzhin chos sku las ma g.yos pas rgyud
NK063(gu)001:8730: tha dad med pa'i phyir du ma dang bral ba
NK063(gu)001:8731: dang bral la / ste / kun byed las /
NK063(gu)001:8732: chos skus khyab pa gcig pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:8733: che ba'i chen por rang bzhin gnas //
NK063(gu)001:8735: de la sogs pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK063(gu)001:8736: phyir dbus zhes pa gcig dang tha dad la sogs
NK063(gu)001:8737: gnyis ka yin pa'am gnyis ka ma yin pa'i phung
NK063(gu)001:8738: po gsum pa'ang med pa ste de ltar chos nyid
NK063(gu)001:8739: de ji ltar gnas pa bzhin mngon du byas pa
NK063(gu)001:8740: nyid las gzhan du 'bras bu zhig sangs rgyas nyid
NK063(gu)001:8741: kyis kyang yul du mi gzigs te /
NK063(gu)001:8742: des na de rgyu rkyen dang bral bas rang byung yin la /
NK063(gu)001:8743: ye nas yin pa'i don mngon du byas pas ye
NK063(gu)001:8744: shes te de nyid thugs rje chen pos zhi ba'i
NK063(gu)001:8745: dang shes rab chen pos 'khor ba'i mtha' gnyis la
NK063(gu)001:8746: gnas pa med par bzhugs pa la de pa'i snang
NK063(gu)001:8747: ba zhes bya'o // ye shes des gdul bya gzigs tshul ni /
NK063(gu)001:8748: log par rtog ces pa ye nas sems nyid 'bras
NK063(gu)001:8749: bu'i rang bzhin yin yang gzhan du 'dzin pa ni
NK063(gu)001:8751: brtags zhes pa de'i rgyun gyis las dang nyon mongs
NK063(gu)001:8752: pa la sogs tha dad du 'dzin pa'i blo ni
NK063(gu)001:8754: gang de las log ste chos thams cad rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:8755: gyis rnam par dag pa thugs su chud pa ni
NK063(gu)001:8756: ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes yin cing /
NK063(gu)001:8758: 'gro drug gi rtog pa la yod pa'i dus snga
NK063(gu)001:8759: phyi dang gnas mtho dman la sogs ma lus par
NK063(gu)001:8760: snang ba rnams mtshan nyid ma 'dres par mkhyen pa
NK063(gu)001:8761: ni ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes so //
NK063(gu)001:8763: ye shes des gdul bya sems can la rgyun du gzigs pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:8764: sems can gyi rang bzhin chos kyi dbyings las mi gzhan te tha dad med pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:8765: de ni mtshan nyid don gyi thugs rje ste bskye
NK063(gu)001:8766: bya skye byed las khyad par du byas pa'i chen
NK063(gu)001:8767: pos ngo bo ris med du 'brel ba de rgyu
NK063(gu)001:8768: mtshan du byas nas gzigs pas na thugs rje rgyun
NK063(gu)001:8769: chad pa mi mnga' ba ni theg pa mchog 'di'i
NK063(gu)001:8770: lugs kyi thugs rje yin no //
NK063(gu)001:8771: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u dgu pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8773: // le'u bcu par dbang bskur ba ston te /
NK063(gu)001:8774: de yang sngon byung gi dang /
NK063(gu)001:8776: dang po ni le'u gnyis pa dang bco lnga pa ltar ro //
NK063(gu)001:8777: gnyis pa la yang zhi khro gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:8778: 'di dngos su zhi ba'i yin la /
NK063(gu)001:8779: khro bo'i dbang yang shugs la shes par byed de /
NK063(gu)001:8780: ji skad du le'u dgu pa las /
NK063(gu)001:8781: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de bzhin te //
NK063(gu)001:8783: de yang rdo rje las rim las /
NK063(gu)001:8784: rgyu rkyen ngo bo 'bras bu dang //
NK063(gu)001:8785: las rim skyon yon brgyad ces bya //
NK063(gu)001:8787: dang po rgyu la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:8790: dang po ni dbang gi don mtshungs ldan tsam du rang la gnas pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:8792: dbang mchog rang la yod par ni //
NK063(gu)001:8793: dus gsum rgyal ba'i lung las gsungs //
NK063(gu)001:8795: de mi gnas nas bskur yang mi thob pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:8796: dper na rdo dang shing la sogs pa la bskur
NK063(gu)001:8797: yang de dag gis thob pa med pa bzhin no
NK063(gu)001:8799: dbang rnams rang la mi gnas na //
NK063(gu)001:8800: bskur bas thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK063(gu)001:8803: gro sran 'bras bu dbang bskur yang //
NK063(gu)001:8804: de la 'bras bu snang ba med //
NK063(gu)001:8808: rang la gnas pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:8810: mtshungs ldan gnas pa yin gyi mngon gyur gyi nus pa mi gnas pas bskur dgos pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:8812: gdod nas ldan phyir mtshungs pa ste //
NK063(gu)001:8813: gzhan phyir thog mar bskur ba yin //
NK063(gu)001:8815: rgyu gnyis pa ni man ngag las shes pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:8816: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:8817: rgyu'i rkyen ni de ma thag pa de yin no //
NK063(gu)001:8818: bdag po'i rkyen ni ston pa'i bdag nyid nas dbang
NK063(gu)001:8819: gi rim pa bar ma chad pa'i rdo rje slob
NK063(gu)001:8820: dpon no // dmigs pa'i rkyen ni thob bya'i ngo bo lnga ste /
NK063(gu)001:8822: ngo bo nus phan gsang ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:8823: shes rab ye shes bde chen po //
NK063(gu)001:8825: de ma thag rkyen ni thabs kyi yan lag snga
NK063(gu)001:8826: mas go phye nas phyi mar dbang rim par gnang
NK063(gu)001:8827: ba'o // gsum pa ngo bo'am dbang tsam du mtshon pa'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK063(gu)001:8828: rang yul la bde blag tu spyod pa'i nus pa gang zhig /
NK063(gu)001:8829: rdo rje slob dpon las byung ba'i thabs kyi yan
NK063(gu)001:8830: lag gis mtshungs ldan smin par byed pa cig yin
NK063(gu)001:8831: no // bzhi pa 'bras bu ni gnas skabs kyi
NK063(gu)001:8832: bde ba dang mthar thug gi bde ba chen po
NK063(gu)001:8833: no // thob pa ste / ji skad du lam rim las /
NK063(gu)001:8834: nyi zla za ba'i dbang byin nas //
NK063(gu)001:8835: rol pa'i ka ra brtan pa yis //
NK063(gu)001:8836: ye shes brtan rdzogs dbang thob nas //
NK063(gu)001:8837: de bzhin de bzhin gshegs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8838: zhes pa 'og gi yon tan gyi skabs su'ang 'chad do //
NK063(gu)001:8839: lnga pa bskur ba'i las ni chos yin te 'og tu 'byung /
NK063(gu)001:8840: drug pa gang la gang bskur ba'i rim pa ni dgu par bstan zin la /
NK063(gu)001:8841: de nyid thal ba las kyang ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:8842: gang du dang dad brtson 'grus pas //
NK063(gu)001:8843: brtul zhugs gsum dang ldan pa la //
NK063(gu)001:8844: sa bon 'jog dang nus bskyed nas //
NK063(gu)001:8845: bde ba'i dbang ni rim bzhin sbyin //
NK063(gu)001:8848: tha ma'i 'du shes kun bzlog nas //
NK063(gu)001:8849: rang rang lhar byas gsal ba la //
NK063(gu)001:8850: nus pa'i tshad dang mnyam sbyar nas //
NK063(gu)001:8851: nyan pa'i dbang dang sgom pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:8852: 'chad dang phrin las byed pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:8853: rdo rje rgyal po slob dpon dbang //
NK063(gu)001:8854: rang bzhin ngo bos gnas pa la //
NK063(gu)001:8855: ji ltar chu la chu bzhag ltar //
NK063(gu)001:8856: thabs dang ting 'dzin dbang bskur bas //
NK063(gu)001:8857: mi nus nus pa thob pa'i tshad //
NK063(gu)001:8858: mi nus pa la bskur ba yin //
NK063(gu)001:8859: tshad ldan rnams la rim pa bskur //
NK063(gu)001:8861: bdun pa ma bskur ba'i skyon dang /
NK063(gu)001:8862: brgyad pa bskur ba'i yon tan gnyis 'og tu 'chad do //
NK063(gu)001:8863: de ltar chos de dag rdo rje las rim gyi gzhung gis bstan pa'i dbang yin la /
NK063(gu)001:8864: 'dir gsung sgros kyi dbang du gang bskur bya phyi
NK063(gu)001:8865: nang gsang ba'i dbang gsum po 'di dag re re
NK063(gu)001:8866: la yang / gzhi gang la bskur ba'i mtshungs ldan dang /
NK063(gu)001:8867: gang gis bskur ba dbang rdzas dang /
NK063(gu)001:8868: ji ltar bskur ba'i las kyi rim pa dang gsum gsum du shes par bya gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:8869: de la dang po phan pa'i dbang ni /
NK063(gu)001:8870: dbu rgyan cod pan zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:8874: khams bcud bde ba'i lam gnyis dang //
NK063(gu)001:8875: dbu ma bcud 'dus mtshan ldan pa //
NK063(gu)001:8876: d+r+wa ba'i rtsa dang dbang po dang //
NK063(gu)001:8877: phung sogs ye shes bde 'khor lo //
NK063(gu)001:8878: h+aum gis bde ba'i ye shes bcas //
NK063(gu)001:8879: tshogs brgyad rang bzhin ye shes lnga //
NK063(gu)001:8880: sngags rdzas dgongs pa gang bslang ba //
NK063(gu)001:8881: kun nas ldang zhing skyob pa yis //
NK063(gu)001:8882: sdug bsngal las grol rigs su nges //
NK063(gu)001:8884: dbu rgyan gyi rnam shes tshogs brgyad do //
NK063(gu)001:8885: cod pan gyi rtsa ro rkyang gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:8886: phreng ba'i kun d+har ma la mdud pa so gnyis yod pa de'o //
NK063(gu)001:8887: go cha'i lus rtsa'i d+r+wa bas khebs pa de'o //
NK063(gu)001:8888: rgyal mtshan gyi pho mo'i dbang po'o //
NK063(gu)001:8889: phyag rgya'i phung po lnga la sogs pa'i rtog tshogs so //
NK063(gu)001:8890: gdugs kyi klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo'o //
NK063(gu)001:8891: bum pa'i rtsa thig les gang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:8892: bza' btung gi snang ba 'dod yon du ma 'gags pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8893: snying po lnga'i khams lnga'i bcud do //
NK063(gu)001:8894: gnyis pa dbang rdzas ni phyag rgya tsaka lir bris
NK063(gu)001:8895: pa la bya zhing gzhan rnams dngos su bsham pa
NK063(gu)001:8896: yin no // gsum pa bskur ba'i thabs la lnga ste /
NK063(gu)001:8897: dbang rdzas rab gnas bya ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:8898: gang du bskur zhing bstim pa'i gnas dang /
NK063(gu)001:8899: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dgongs pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:8902: dang po rab gnas ni le'u dgu par bstan la /
NK063(gu)001:8903: de gang la gang gis bya ba'i rim pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:8905: rin chen rab gnas las byung ba'i //
NK063(gu)001:8906: rin chen mdzes pa'i dbu rgyan bcings //
NK063(gu)001:8908: dbu rgyan la rin chen 'byung ldan gyis so //
NK063(gu)001:8909: rab gnas chos 'byung ye shes dngos /
NK063(gu)001:8910: kha dog gnyis ldan dbang bskur bya //
NK063(gu)001:8911: zhes pas cod pan la mtha' yas kyis so //
NK063(gu)001:8912: rin chen rab gnas phreng ba bcings //
NK063(gu)001:8913: zhes pas phreng ba la rin 'byung gis so //
NK063(gu)001:8914: las mchog rab gnas rdo rje'o //
NK063(gu)001:8915: zhes pas go cha la don yod grub pas so //
NK063(gu)001:8916: rdo rje rab gnas las 'byung ba //
NK063(gu)001:8917: zhes pas rgyal mtshan la rdo rje sems dpas so //
NK063(gu)001:8918: mchog tshogs phyag rgya gang yin pa //
NK063(gu)001:8919: rang gi rab gnas cung zad mchod //
NK063(gu)001:8920: ces pas tsaka li rnams la rang rang gis so //
NK063(gu)001:8921: mi bskyod rab gnas rin chen gdugs //
NK063(gu)001:8922: zhes pas gdugs la mi bskyod pas so //
NK063(gu)001:8923: rigs lnga 'dus pa'i bum chu sbyin //
NK063(gu)001:8924: zhes pas bum pa la rigs lnga spyi yis so //
NK063(gu)001:8925: sangs rgyas rab gnas lha mo'i tshogs //
NK063(gu)001:8926: zhes pas bza' btung la rnam snang gis so //
NK063(gu)001:8927: snying po 'bras zhes pas snying po yig 'bru lnga
NK063(gu)001:8928: la sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga yis
NK063(gu)001:8929: rab gnas bya'o // gnyis pa gnas ni /
NK063(gu)001:8931: gnas ni spyi dang khyad par te //
NK063(gu)001:8934: spyi dbang lus la bskur ba ste //
NK063(gu)001:8937: khyad par snying po dbu rgyan bum //
NK063(gu)001:8938: gdugs dang cod pan phreng ba mgo //
NK063(gu)001:8939: go cha lus te rgyal mtshan lag /
NK063(gu)001:8940: bza' gtung ngag gi lam la'o //
NK063(gu)001:8941: phyag rgya spyi bo snying gar te //
NK063(gu)001:8942: zhes pas gnas de dag tu bskur zhing mtshungs ldan gang yin la bstim pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:8944: gzhag pa'i gnas dang bstim pa'i gnas //
NK063(gu)001:8945: de bzhin khong du chud par bya //
NK063(gu)001:8948: bu lhar gsal ba la dbu rgyan bskon te sngags
NK063(gu)001:8949: dang phyag rgyas rat+na'i khang bu lnga'i nang du gdan
NK063(gu)001:8950: khri'i lnga'i steng du rigs lnga yab yum gyi sa
NK063(gu)001:8951: bon bcu dgod / de nas rdo rje slob dpon
NK063(gu)001:8952: gyi phyag gi sor mo bcu la'ang gong gi yi
NK063(gu)001:8953: ge rnams gsal bas phyag rgya bcas te yab yum
NK063(gu)001:8954: sbyor ba'i byang chub sems kyi rgyun gyis spyi bo
NK063(gu)001:8955: la sogs gnas lngar thim pas /
NK063(gu)001:8956: yi ge rnams las don ye shes lnga'i dbang la rtags su rigs lngas dbu brgyan par bsam /
NK063(gu)001:8957: cod pan gyis yon tan thams cad rdzogs shing khams
NK063(gu)001:8958: gsum gyi gdug pa can thams cad 'dul bar dang
