NK063(gu)001:8959: / phreng bas 'bras bu'i chos thams cad rdzogs par dang /
NK063(gu)001:8960: go chas phas kyi rgol bas mi tshugs par dang /
NK063(gu)001:8961: rgyal mtshan gyis bdud dang mu stegs la sogs log par lta ba zil gyis mnon par dang /
NK063(gu)001:8962: phyag rgya yis rtog pa dag nas lha'i skur dang /
NK063(gu)001:8963: gdugs kyis nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba las skyob par dang /
NK063(gu)001:8964: bum pa'i chus rgyud kyi nyon sgrib dag nas ye shes lnga'i dbang thob par dang /
NK063(gu)001:8965: bza' btung gis 'dod yon lnga ma 'gags par longs spyod par dang /
NK063(gu)001:8966: snying po lngas sangs rgyas kyi sku gsung thugs yon
NK063(gu)001:8967: tan phrin las lnga'i byin rlabs bsdus te rigs lnga'i
NK063(gu)001:8968: skur bsam pa la sogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:8969: bzhi pa bskur ba'i tshig ni bcu char rdo rje
NK063(gu)001:8970: las rim gyi gzhung ltar lag len du shes par
NK063(gu)001:8971: bya'o // tha ma bsgrags pa ni bden pa'i rjes
NK063(gu)001:8972: su bskur bya gang yin gyi gyur shog brjod pa'o
NK063(gu)001:8973: bya'o // // de dag gis 'di phyi gnyis su
NK063(gu)001:8974: phan pa'i sa bon tsam 'jog pa'i phyir na phan
NK063(gu)001:8979: de bskur ba'i dus ni smon pa'i sems bskyed nas
NK063(gu)001:8980: dgu pa ltar chos bcu drug gi sgo nas dkyil
NK063(gu)001:8981: 'khor du zhugs pa'i dus su bskur ba yin no
NK063(gu)001:8982: // nus pa'i dbang la yang gong ltar don gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:8987: bu'i rna ba gnyis kyi 'doms rtsa na sgra nyan
NK063(gu)001:8988: par nus pa'i thig le shin tu dwangs par gnas
NK063(gu)001:8989: pa ni nyan pa'i yin no //
NK063(gu)001:8990: snying gi thig le de ltar gnas pa ni sgom pa'i yin no //
NK063(gu)001:8991: lag pa ni phrin las kyi'o //
NK063(gu)001:8993: yan lag lnga'i thig le dwangs par gnas pa ni rdo rje rgyal po'i yin no //
NK063(gu)001:8994: gnyis pa ni nyan pa'i glegs bam bsgom pa'i phreng
NK063(gu)001:8995: ba phrin las kyi rdo rje rgya gram 'chad pa'i
NK063(gu)001:8996: 'khor lo rdo rje rgyal po'i rdo rje dril bu'o
NK063(gu)001:8997: // de yang rdo rje las rim las /
NK063(gu)001:8998: glegs bam phreng ba rgya gram ljang //
NK063(gu)001:8999: 'khor lo rdo rje dril bu sbyin //
NK063(gu)001:9001: gsum pa bskur thabs kyi las rim la lnga las /
NK063(gu)001:9002: dbang rdzas rab gnas ni po ti la rin 'byung gis dang /
NK063(gu)001:9003: phreng ba la yi dam gang yin gyis dang /
NK063(gu)001:9004: rgya gram la don yod grub pas dang /
NK063(gu)001:9005: 'khor lo la mtha' yas kyis dang /
NK063(gu)001:9006: rdo rje dril bu la rigs lnga spyi yis bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:9008: 'byung ldan don yod snang mtha' yas //
NK063(gu)001:9009: yi dam rigs lnga'i rab gnas ldan //
NK063(gu)001:9011: gnas ni lag tu bskur zhing mtshungs ldan la bstim pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:9012: gnas ni rna ba snying yan lag /
NK063(gu)001:9013: lce dang yan lag rnam lnga'o //
NK063(gu)001:9015: slob dpon gyi dgongs pa ni lnga char 'dis shes par bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:9016: nyan byed ces pa rna ba ste de la sogs
NK063(gu)001:9017: pa mtshungs ldan rnams kyi rten dbang po rnams so
NK063(gu)001:9018: // de la man ngag bzhin rgyu gnyis pa rdzas
NK063(gu)001:9019: kyi thig le las gzhal yas kyi sa bon no
NK063(gu)001:9020: // // de las bskyed sngags kyis dbus 'khor lo
NK063(gu)001:9021: rtsibs bzhi khyams spangs pa'i gru chad sgo dang bcas
NK063(gu)001:9022: pa'i gzhal yas su gdan rnams tshang bar bkod pa
NK063(gu)001:9023: // // der / brten pa mtshungs ldan gsal ba'i
NK063(gu)001:9024: thig le dwangs par gnas pa dbang gi ngo bo
NK063(gu)001:9025: // // der / de nyid / tram gi zhes
NK063(gu)001:9026: pa de la sogs pa rigs kyi sa bon rnams
NK063(gu)001:9027: zung lnga la bcur bsam pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9028: de las thugs mtshan rnams so //
NK063(gu)001:9029: de las sku phyag rgya rnams sku mdog phyag mtshan rgyan cha lugs dang bcas pa bskyed pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:9031: gtso bo rin chen 'byung ldan yab yum ni dkyil 'khor yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9032: de la sogs pa'i rigs so so'i gtso bo yab
NK063(gu)001:9033: yum rnams rang rang gi rigs chung gi 'khor dang
NK063(gu)001:9034: bcas pa la gsal bar bskyed do //
NK063(gu)001:9035: de nas gong gi tshogs zhes pa ni mang po'i sgras yan lag lha dang bcas pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9036: de ltar dam tshig sems dpa' de'i mchog 'og min
NK063(gu)001:9037: nas ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor snyan gsan dbab cing
NK063(gu)001:9040: thim zhes pa ni dbyer med par ro //
NK063(gu)001:9041: gong na spro zhes pa ni kun tu bzang po
NK063(gu)001:9042: la sogs pa phyi nang gi mchod pa ci rigs
NK063(gu)001:9044: bskur ba'i tshig ni lnga char so sor gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:9045: bsgrag pa yang rang rang gi smon lam brjod pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9046: 'di dag gis rang gzhan gyi don dngos su nus pa'i phyir na nus dbang zhes bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:9048: nus bskyed nas zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9049: de bskur ba'i dus ni phan dbang thob nas bdag
NK063(gu)001:9050: don gyi brtson 'grus dang ldan pa la nyan pa
NK063(gu)001:9051: dang bsgom pa'i dbang bskur la /
NK063(gu)001:9052: gzhan don gyi brtson 'grus dang ldan pa la 'chad pa dang phrin las kyi dbang bskur zhing /
NK063(gu)001:9053: gnyis ka'i brtson 'grus can la bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang bskur ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:9054: gsum pa zab mo'i dbang gsum la'ang gong ltar gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:9055: dang po mtshungs ldan ni bu'i lus la thig le
NK063(gu)001:9056: mi rtog pa'i ye shes don dam pa'i ngo bor
NK063(gu)001:9057: ye nas gnas pa ni gsang dbang gi yin la
NK063(gu)001:9058: / bu la don dam 'od gsal gyi ye shes
NK063(gu)001:9059: ye nas gnas pa ni ye shes rang gnas kyi
NK063(gu)001:9060: / yin zhing / dbyer med kyi ye shes rang
NK063(gu)001:9061: chas su gnas pa ni bde ba chen po'i dbang
NK063(gu)001:9062: / yin zhing / gi yin no // gnyis pa
NK063(gu)001:9063: dbang rdzas ni rdo rje slob dpon yab yum gyi
NK063(gu)001:9064: nyi zla gnyis 'dres ni gsang ba'i dbang rdzas yin
NK063(gu)001:9065: / yin zhing / gi yin no // la /
NK063(gu)001:9066: bu nyid kyi yum zla ba 'dzag pa ni ye
NK063(gu)001:9067: shes rang gnas kyi yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9069: rdzas ni skabs kyi phyag rgya mo //
NK063(gu)001:9070: zla ba ldan pa gtad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9072: bu nyid kyi yum nyi ma 'dzag pa ni bde ba chen po yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9073: khyad par cung zad nyi ldan ma //
NK063(gu)001:9075: gsum pa bskur ba'i thabs ni dkyus gcig la zur gsum du bshad de /
NK063(gu)001:9076: dang po gsang dbang gi dbang du na shes rab
NK063(gu)001:9077: ces pa mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i yum rdo rje
NK063(gu)001:9078: gzungs ma ste / lo nyi shu ma khrus byas
NK063(gu)001:9079: zas bsrung gos barje rgyan gyis brgyan pa la sogs
NK063(gu)001:9080: 'dod pa'i bstan bcos dang ldan pas bde ba rgyas
NK063(gu)001:9081: par bya ste dbang bskur zhing dam phog nas rigs
NK063(gu)001:9082: kyi yum gyi bskyed cing byin gyis brlabs pa de'o
NK063(gu)001:9083: gzungs ma ste / // thabs zhes pa rdo rje
NK063(gu)001:9084: slob dpon nyid dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo yab tu
NK063(gu)001:9085: gzungs ma ste / // bskyed pa'o // de ltar gsal bas phyag rgya bzhi yis rol pa las /
NK063(gu)001:9086: lhan skyes kyi bde ba'i rang bzhin yab kyi zla
NK063(gu)001:9087: ba yig 'bru h+aum gi tshogs su gsal ba'i byang
NK063(gu)001:9088: chub sems kyi chu rgyun de dbab pa'i thabs kyis
NK063(gu)001:9089: phab ste yab kyi rdo rje'i lam nas phyung ste
NK063(gu)001:9090: yum gyi mkha' pad+mara bzung ba ni 'khyil ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:9091: de ltar rdor pad kyi rtse gnyis nas ba dang
NK063(gu)001:9092: be'u 'am bung ba dang me tog ltar bskur ba
NK063(gu)001:9093: ste / bzhag pa'i gnas ni bu'i lce la bzhag nas snying gi dbus su bstim pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9095: gnas ni bzhag dang bstim gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:9097: yang na bya dang bye'u ltar te ldog pa'i thabs kyis rtsa gnas su rim par ldog /
NK063(gu)001:9098: mgrin pa longs spyod nas ljags steng du drang zhing de nas bu'i lce thog tu bzhag pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9100: ji skad du bla ma las /
NK063(gu)001:9101: sems kyi dkyil nas drangs pa'i chu //
NK063(gu)001:9102: khyod kyi lce la bzhag pa 'di //
NK063(gu)001:9103: snying gi dkyil du gzung bar byos //
NK063(gu)001:9105: dkyil 'khor bsgyur zhes pa ni yab yum gyi thig le h+aum gi tshogs su gsal ba nyid /
NK063(gu)001:9106: rdo rje sems dpa' yungs 'bru tsam pa mang por gyur te snying la thim pas /
NK063(gu)001:9107: bu'i snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo'i rtsa bzhi la
NK063(gu)001:9108: rigs drug tu skye ba'i sa bon drug po bsregs
NK063(gu)001:9109: nas don dam mi rtog pa'i ye shes su bsgyur
NK063(gu)001:9110: ba'o // de la ci'i phyir gsang dbang zhes bya zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:9111: gnyis med kyi ye shes ngos zin dka' ba'i don
NK063(gu)001:9112: de rdzas kyi khyad par du byas nas thob pa'i
NK063(gu)001:9113: phyir ro // de bskur ba'i dus ni nus dbang
NK063(gu)001:9114: rnams rdzogs par thob nas rdzogs pa rdzogs rim la
NK063(gu)001:9115: slob pa'i dus su bskur ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:9116: gnyis pa ye shes rang gnas kyi dbang du na
NK063(gu)001:9117: shes rab ces sring mo ste lo bcu drug ma
NK063(gu)001:9119: thabs zhes pa slob bu nyid do //
NK063(gu)001:9120: de ltar yab yum gnyis kyis lha'i sku phyag rgyar
NK063(gu)001:9121: gsal bas rol ba las byung ba'i bde ba'i rang
NK063(gu)001:9122: bzhin sgra dbyangs kyi yig 'bru'i tshogs su gsal ba
NK063(gu)001:9125: rang snang sku yi 'khor lo las //
NK063(gu)001:9126: rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK063(gu)001:9128: de yang dbab pa'i thabs kyis rdo rje'i lam du
NK063(gu)001:9129: phab nas yum gyi pad+mara gzung ba'i thabs kyis bzung
NK063(gu)001:9130: ste 'khyil ba de'i tshe bskur ba'i gnas rig pa'i
NK063(gu)001:9131: pho brang du nyams su myong ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:9133: gnas ni rig pa'i pho brang du //
NK063(gu)001:9135: de ltar rdor pad kyi rtse nas phan tshun bsnol
NK063(gu)001:9136: mar dgod de spyi gtsug bde chen nas bcu drug
NK063(gu)001:9137: tu bab de bzhir zags te /
NK063(gu)001:9139: sde tshan brgyad dang phyed pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:9140: khyab 'jug gsum yang de bzhin te //
NK063(gu)001:9143: yang bzhir zags te snying gar gcig tu 'dril /
NK063(gu)001:9144: de rdo rje'i lam nas bcu drug tu bab /
NK063(gu)001:9145: de'i phyed brgyad dang de'i phyed bzhir gyur te rdo
NK063(gu)001:9146: rje'i rtser gcig tu 'dril ba ltar yum la'ang de
NK063(gu)001:9147: bzhin no // de ltar yab yum gnyis car la
NK063(gu)001:9148: bde ba bcu drug bcu drug bkod pa de phan
NK063(gu)001:9149: tshun gcig la gcig bstim zhing bu'i sems nyid bden
NK063(gu)001:9150: pa dbyer med pa'i dkyil 'khor don dam 'od gsal
NK063(gu)001:9151: gyi ye shes su bsgyur ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:9153: rim par bkod pa rang snang bas //
NK063(gu)001:9155: de la ci'i phyir ye shes rang gnas zhes bya na /
NK063(gu)001:9156: nyams su myong ba'i ye shes de rang gi rgyud la gsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9157: de bskur ba'i dus ni gsang dbang thob pa'i rjes su'o //
NK063(gu)001:9158: gsum pa bde ba chen po'i dbang du ni /
NK063(gu)001:9159: shes rab ces pa yum lo bcu gnyis ma nyi zla dang ldan pa chas su bcug pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9160: thabs kyi zhes pa bu nyid do //
NK063(gu)001:9161: de gnyis ka sku phyag rgyar gsal bas rol pa
NK063(gu)001:9162: las byung ba'i byang sems 'dres pa'i bde ba nyid
NK063(gu)001:9163: gong ltar yig 'bru'i tshogs su gsal ba'i tshe /
NK063(gu)001:9164: de nyid yab yum gnyis kyi rtsa ba'i dga' ba bzhi ni /
NK063(gu)001:9166: bla mas lhan skyes ye shes ston //
NK063(gu)001:9167: shes rab ye shes dbang bskur bas //
NK063(gu)001:9168: dga' ba mchog dga' dag 'bral dang //
NK063(gu)001:9169: lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba yis //
NK063(gu)001:9171: re re la'ang bzhi bzhi'i phyir bcu drug bcu drug
NK063(gu)001:9172: tu bkod pa ni mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa
NK063(gu)001:9173: gnyis so // yab kyi dga' ba re re yang
NK063(gu)001:9174: sems lnga lnga dang ldan pa ni dpe byad bzang
NK063(gu)001:9176: de ltar lhan skyes kyi bde ba bar ma chad
NK063(gu)001:9177: pa'i rgyun dang bcas pa rdo rje'i lam nas phab
NK063(gu)001:9178: ste rtog med ma'i mkha' pad+mara thabs kyis bzung bas
NK063(gu)001:9179: 'khyil ba'o // de'i tshe tha ma rdzogs pa'i sems
NK063(gu)001:9180: yin te thig le rdo rje'i rtse nas ldog pa'i
NK063(gu)001:9181: thabs kyis ldog ste lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo
NK063(gu)001:9182: la sogs rim par klad pa bde chen la thug
NK063(gu)001:9183: gi bar bstim pas sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran
NK063(gu)001:9184: pa ni lhan skyes ye shes su mngon du byas
NK063(gu)001:9185: 'khyil ba'o // pa yin zhing / de lta bu'i
NK063(gu)001:9186: rdzu 'phrul gyi bya ba shes pas nyon mongs pas
NK063(gu)001:9187: ma gos pa'i phyir pad+ma spyan gyis yin la /
NK063(gu)001:9188: des rtog tshogs thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi
NK063(gu)001:9189: dkyil 'khor du gnas bsgyur te mi zad pa rgyan
NK063(gu)001:9190: gyi 'khor lor gsal ba ni 'khor lo tshogs chen
NK063(gu)001:9193: yid kyi dri ma dag byas nas //
NK063(gu)001:9194: sa ni phyed dang gsum rdzogs pas //
NK063(gu)001:9196: chos kyi sku la sbyor bar byed //
NK063(gu)001:9198: de la ci'i phyir bde ba chen po zhes bya
NK063(gu)001:9199: na gnyis par gsal ba'i ye shes de rgyud la
NK063(gu)001:9201: de bskur ba'i dus ni gong ma gnyis rdzogs nas sa'i rlung thur du rgyu ba'i dus su'o //
NK063(gu)001:9202: yang zab mo'i dbang 'di rnams la gzhung 'ga' zhig nas /
NK063(gu)001:9203: snod dang dkyil 'khor bskur ba'i dus //
NK063(gu)001:9204: ngo bo rdzas dang thabs rgyu rkyen //
NK063(gu)001:9205: gnas dang dgos ched bcu yis bshad //
NK063(gu)001:9206: ces pa ltar yang rung ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:9207: de ltar phyi nang gsang ba gsum la bco brgyad
NK063(gu)001:9208: du phye ba ni zhi ba'i dbang du yin la
NK063(gu)001:9210: ji skad du khro bo rdo rje las rim las /
NK063(gu)001:9211: rnam grangs rjes su 'jug pa yang //
NK063(gu)001:9212: lha dbang phyag mtshan rgyan chas dang //
NK063(gu)001:9213: sgrub rdzas gsang ba rnam gsum mo //
NK063(gu)001:9214: zhes pas rnam grangs lngar gsal ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:9215: de yang de gnyis car la dkyil 'khor gyis phye
NK063(gu)001:9216: na lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la brten
NK063(gu)001:9217: pa ni phyi dang nang gi dbang yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:9218: mkha'i dkyil 'khor la brten pa ni gsang dbang yin la /
NK063(gu)001:9219: lus kyi dkyil 'khor la brten pa ni shes rab ye shes kyi yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9220: sems kyi dkyil 'khor du thob pa ni bde ba chen po'i dbang yin no //
NK063(gu)001:9221: de dag lam gyi rim pa'i dbang du zag bcas
NK063(gu)001:9222: kyi lam du de'i lam pa la slob dpon drod
NK063(gu)001:9223: thob pas zhi khro lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil
NK063(gu)001:9224: 'khor du rigs ngan mo zhes pa ltar dngos kyi
NK063(gu)001:9226: bar chad med pa'i lam du de'i lam pa la
NK063(gu)001:9227: slob dpon rig 'dzin gyis lhag ma tshogs kyi dkyil
NK063(gu)001:9228: 'khor zhi khro gnyis su lha mo zhes ting nge
NK063(gu)001:9229: 'dzin 'od kyi yum la brten nas dang /
NK063(gu)001:9230: zag med kyi lam du de'i lam pa la slob
NK063(gu)001:9231: dpon sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin gyis 'bras bu mthar
NK063(gu)001:9232: phyin gyi dkyil 'khor zhi khro gnyis su ye shes
NK063(gu)001:9233: kyi yum la brten nas dbang bskur ba rnams ni
NK063(gu)001:9234: rgyud tshod kyis phye ba dag yin no //
NK063(gu)001:9235: 'di dag la kha cig lam dang por nus pa
NK063(gu)001:9236: tsam 'jog cing gnyis par nus pa cher 'jog la
NK063(gu)001:9237: / gsum par ni nus pa dngos su 'jog pa
NK063(gu)001:9238: yin zer ba ni rnam gzhag la 'khrul pa yin
NK063(gu)001:9239: / te / nus pa 'jog tshul gsum po 'di
NK063(gu)001:9240: bye brag phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi khyad par
NK063(gu)001:9241: / te / yin te / ji skad du thal ba las /
NK063(gu)001:9242: gang du dad dang brtson 'grus dang //
NK063(gu)001:9243: brtul zhugs gsum dang ldan pa la //
NK063(gu)001:9244: sa bon tsam 'jog nus bskyed nas //
NK063(gu)001:9245: bde ba'i dbang ni rim bzhin sbyin //
NK063(gu)001:9246: zhes phan dbang gis nus pa tsam 'jog cing nus
NK063(gu)001:9247: dbang gis cher 'jog pa zab mo'i dbang gis dngos
NK063(gu)001:9249: de ltar phyi nang gsang ba gsum ni gong gi lam gsum char du bskur dgos te /
NK063(gu)001:9250: khyab byed yin pa'i phyir ro snyam du sems so //
NK063(gu)001:9251: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u bcu pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9253: // le'u bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa sdeb nas tshogs sgrub ston te /
NK063(gu)001:9254: de ltar rgyud kyi bshad thabs yang rdo rje ltar
NK063(gu)001:9255: rked pa nas bzung ste bshad par zhes bya ste
NK063(gu)001:9256: / 'di'i lam gyi brjod bya ma lus pa 'dir
NK063(gu)001:9257: mtshan nyid gsum du dril nas 'chad par byed do
NK063(gu)001:9259: skal ldan gsal ba'i khyad par gyis //
NK063(gu)001:9260: rim gyis yang na cig car du //
NK063(gu)001:9262: lam pa'i blo che chung gi khyad par gyis rim gyis pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:9263: cig car ba gnyis gnyis su shes par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:9264: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni /
NK063(gu)001:9265: kha cig sangs rgyas kyi sar bgrod pa'i dus myur bul dang /
NK063(gu)001:9266: kha cig sems lnga rgyud la skye ba'i rim pa myur bul la 'dod kyang /
NK063(gu)001:9267: 'dir rje sgro phug pa'i rjes su 'brangs te bden
NK063(gu)001:9268: pa gsum ka 'brel mi 'brel gyi khyad par du
NK063(gu)001:9269: byas par bzhed de don 'og tu 'chad pas shes
NK063(gu)001:9270: so // de ltar rim cig car gnyis ka yang
NK063(gu)001:9271: mtshan nyid gsum gyis don mthar phyin par byed de
NK063(gu)001:9272: so // / ji skad du lta phreng las /
NK063(gu)001:9273: lam gnyis ka yang mtshan nyid gsum gyis don mthar phyin par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:9275: mtshan nyid gsum gang zhe na dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:9276: le'u bsgyur te bcu gnyis pa nas so //
NK063(gu)001:9277: de'i yang tshig bsgyur te 'og gi rgyu zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:9278: dang gong gi shes pa gnyis sbyar nas mtshan nyid
NK063(gu)001:9279: ces pa gsum char la sbyar bas /
NK063(gu)001:9280: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid de ni dang por thos bsam gyis lta ba 'tshol ba cig yin no //
NK063(gu)001:9281: yang rkyen zhes pa dang 'jug pa gnyis sbyar bas
NK063(gu)001:9282: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid de ni lam gyi rnal
NK063(gu)001:9283: 'byor rnams ci rigs par bsgom pa cig yin no
NK063(gu)001:9284: // yang smin byed ni gong gi lta sgom gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:9285: de gnyis 'byor pas phyir mi ldog pa'i gzungs la
NK063(gu)001:9286: zhugs pa ni 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid
NK063(gu)001:9287: de / de ni gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi'o //
NK063(gu)001:9288: mdor na lam mtshan nyid gsum gyi tshul du mthar
NK063(gu)001:9289: phyin pa de nus pa mthu can du gyur pa
NK063(gu)001:9290: gang zhe na / rig 'dzin zhes pa dper na
NK063(gu)001:9291: rgyal po'i bu yin pa la rgyal rigs zer ba
NK063(gu)001:9292: gang zhe na / bzhin / dang po de las
NK063(gu)001:9293: byung zhing bar du de la gnas pas tha ma
NK063(gu)001:9294: de'i rgyud mi stongs pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:9295: lhun gyis grub pas chos sku dang /
NK063(gu)001:9296: rgya chen gyis longs sku'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:9297: rnam smin tshe dbang gis sprul sku'i rig 'dzin pa nyid de /
NK063(gu)001:9298: de ltar 'di'i bcu dgu pa las /
NK063(gu)001:9299: rgyal ba'i rigs mchog 'dzin pa de //
NK063(gu)001:9301: mthar thug pa'i ni rgyal ba sku gsum nyid zhing
NK063(gu)001:9302: thams cad du yongs su grags par 'gyur zhes pa'o
NK063(gu)001:9304: dang po rgyu shes pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:9306: cig car ba'i lta ba gtan la 'bebs tshul lo //
NK063(gu)001:9307: dang po ni lam rim las /
NK063(gu)001:9308: gzhi de gtan tshigs grub pa'i don //
NK063(gu)001:9310: de yang gzhi ni gang gzhal bya chos can dang /
NK063(gu)001:9311: gtan tshigs ni gang gis 'jal byed gtan tshigs dang /
NK063(gu)001:9312: grub pa'i don ni gang du gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha'o //
NK063(gu)001:9313: dang po gzhal bya ni le'u 'di'i gzhung nas mi
NK063(gu)001:9314: ston kyang 'og gi gtan tshigs 'di dag la gzhal
NK063(gu)001:9315: bya dgos pas cung zad ngag don du sbyar na
NK063(gu)001:9316: / skabs dang dgos ched kyis rigs gsum du 'gyur ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9317: de yang rgol ba dang phyi rgol gnyis rtsod pa'i
NK063(gu)001:9318: tshe bum pa lta bu'i mthun snang du grub pa
NK063(gu)001:9320: de der bzhag pas de tshad mas grub pa'i dgos pa yod de /
NK063(gu)001:9321: ji skad du gzhung gzhan las /
NK063(gu)001:9322: rgol ba gnyis ka'i shes pa la //
NK063(gu)001:9323: ji tsam snang ba'i cha yod pa //
NK063(gu)001:9324: de tsam de la brten nas ni //
NK063(gu)001:9325: de tshe rjes su dpag pa 'byung //
NK063(gu)001:9327: yang slob dpon gyis bu la gdams ngag 'bogs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:9328: tshe bu'i tshogs brgyad yul dang bcas pa de chos
NK063(gu)001:9329: can yin te / de der bzhag pas bstan bya
NK063(gu)001:9330: gdams ngag de bu'i rgyud thog tu khel ba'i dgos
NK063(gu)001:9331: can yin te / pa yod do // yang slob
NK063(gu)001:9332: dpon gyis bu la gzhung 'chad pa'i tshe 'khor 'das
NK063(gu)001:9333: thams cad chos can yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9334: de der bzhag pas de dag gi chos nyid gtan
NK063(gu)001:9335: la phebs pas shes bya la mi shes pa'i 'ching
NK063(gu)001:9336: ba las grol ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK063(gu)001:9337: de ltar gsum las 'dir phyi ma len pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9338: ji skad du rnam bkod las /
NK063(gu)001:9339: brtags pa'i spyod yul gnyis la gzhal //
NK063(gu)001:9341: 'o na gzhal du mi btub par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:9342: tshad mas ma grub pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:9344: 'di'i lugs kyi tshad ma ni kun khyab gsum la byed pa'i phyir 'ga' zhig ni lung dang /
NK063(gu)001:9345: 'ga' zhig ni nyams su myong ba'i man ngag dang /
NK063(gu)001:9346: 'ga' zhig ni rig pas grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9347: de yang 'khor 'das kyi rang mtshan gzhal bya ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9348: de gnyis kyi zhen snang gzhal bya yin zhes le'u
NK063(gu)001:9349: gsum par bstan par ltar 'dir yang 'chad pa pos
NK063(gu)001:9351: gnyis pa gang gis 'jal byed gtan tshigs ni /
NK063(gu)001:9352: dgag sgrub gnyis su byed pa'i las can te /
NK063(gu)001:9353: ji skad du lam rim las /
NK063(gu)001:9354: de phyir gtan tshigs las la brjod //
NK063(gu)001:9356: de yang gzhung gcig la'ang blo che chung gi dbang gis rim gyis gtan la 'bebs pa'i tshul dang /
NK063(gu)001:9357: cig car gtan la 'bebs tshul gnyis su sbyar te /
NK063(gu)001:9360: rgyu gcig pa dang zhes pa la 'grel pa'i dgongs pa ltar na /
NK063(gu)001:9361: gong gi gzhal bya 'khor 'das gnyis chos can /
NK063(gu)001:9363: gnyis char sems las byung ba'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:9364: dper na sgra rtag 'dzin gyi sgro 'dogs dang mi
NK063(gu)001:9365: rtag par nges pa'i tshad ma gnyis dmigs yul sgra
NK063(gu)001:9367: rtags de ni tshad mas grub pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9368: sems rtogs pa las 'das pa byung zhing ma rtogs
NK063(gu)001:9369: pa las 'khor ba byung ba de gnyis char sems
NK063(gu)001:9371: ji skad du spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:9372: de gnyis ni bsal bas tha dad kyang ngo bo gcig ste /
NK063(gu)001:9375: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas
NK063(gu)001:9376: pa'i ngo bo nyid du gcig pa'i mtshan nyid yin
NK063(gu)001:9377: pas / zhes pa la sogs pa du ma gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9378: rtags de la brten pa'i blos 'khor 'das gnyis rgyu
NK063(gu)001:9379: sems su gcig par rtogs shing sems kyi rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:9380: stong par rtogs pa yang shes bya stong pa'i ldog
NK063(gu)001:9381: pa don dam skye med du rtogs pa yin no
NK063(gu)001:9382: // yig 'bru'i tshul zhes pa ni sngar gyi stong nyid chos can /
NK063(gu)001:9383: de mtshon byed sems nyid yi ger ma 'gags pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9384: rim gyis pa la ltos nas dbyings ye ges mtshon nas rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:9385: mdzub mo dang ri bong can bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:9386: dbyings yi ges mtshon nas rtogs par yang /
NK063(gu)001:9388: dbyings la dbyings kyis bris pas na //
NK063(gu)001:9389: yi ge zhes ni de phyir brjod //
NK063(gu)001:9391: de ltar du gang yi ges mtshon nas don rtogs
NK063(gu)001:9392: pa de yig 'bru'i tshul gyis rtogs pa yin par
NK063(gu)001:9394: ji skad du bcu gsum pa las /
NK063(gu)001:9395: yi ge sgra btags ming tshogs las //
NK063(gu)001:9396: brten pa'i tshig gis rab mtshon te //
NK063(gu)001:9397: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK063(gu)001:9399: rtags de la brten pa'i blos yig 'bru'i tshul gyis
NK063(gu)001:9400: rtogs pa yang shes bya snang ldog kun rdzob 'gag
NK063(gu)001:9401: med du rtogs pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:9402: byin gyis brlabs dang zhes pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:9403: de ltar snang stong gnyis po chos can /
NK063(gu)001:9404: de gnyis dngos su rtogs pa'i byin rlabs las dbyer
NK063(gu)001:9405: med kyi rtogs pa shugs las byung ba yin te
NK063(gu)001:9406: / dper na ras dkar po dmar por gtong ba'i nus pa brtsod la yod pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:9407: de ltar yang rngam glog las /
NK063(gu)001:9408: skye med dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK063(gu)001:9409: chos kun snang bar shes pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:9410: de lta bu yi rang bzhin te //
NK063(gu)001:9412: rtags de la brten pa'i blos byin gyis brlabs kyis
NK063(gu)001:9413: rtogs pa yang snang stong dbyer med kyi ldog pa
NK063(gu)001:9414: bden pa dbyer med spyi'i mtshan nyid tsam du rtogs
NK063(gu)001:9415: pa yin no // mngon sum pa zhes pa ni
NK063(gu)001:9416: rtags kyi rjes su dpag pa'i bsgrub bya rtogs pa
NK063(gu)001:9418: de dang mi 'gal bar dbyer med rang mtshan du rtogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:9419: de nyid las ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:9420: gzhan la ma brten mi 'gal bar //
NK063(gu)001:9421: mngon sum rig pas thag chod na //
NK063(gu)001:9422: rnal 'byor sa la slebs pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:9424: de yang mngon sum bzhi las rnal 'byor gyi mngon
NK063(gu)001:9425: sum ni zag bcas kyi skabs su rgyud la ma
NK063(gu)001:9426: skyes shing / dbang po'i mngon su ni blo 'di la ltos te 'khrul pa'i yul can yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9427: ji skad du ting 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK063(gu)001:9428: ji ltar mig dang rna ba sna dang lce yang tshad ma min //
NK063(gu)001:9429: de bzhin lus dang yid kyang tshad min te //
NK063(gu)001:9430: ji srid dbang po de dag tshad yin na //
NK063(gu)001:9431: 'phags pa'i lam gyis de la ci zhig bya //
NK063(gu)001:9434: dbyibs dang kha dog dbang po'i spyod yul min //
NK063(gu)001:9436: yid kyi mngon sum la sgrub byed kyi tshad ma med pas /
NK063(gu)001:9437: 'dir rang rig gi mngon sum ste shes bya'i gnas
NK063(gu)001:9438: lugs ji ltar yin pa'i don la sgrib g.yogs dang
NK063(gu)001:9439: bral bar rtogs pa cig yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9441: mngon sum mthong ba'i mig med mngon sum mthong ba'i mig /
NK063(gu)001:9442: de phyir thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan zhes de la bya //
NK063(gu)001:9444: de ltar rtogs pa bzhi po 'di dag snga ma'i bsgrub bya phyi ma'i gzhal bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:9445: ra zam pa la sbrengs pa ltar rim par skye ba'i phyir rim gyis pa'i rtogs tshul yin no //
NK063(gu)001:9446: de las bskyed du byar med pas rab tu rtogs pa zhes bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:9447: de'i rnam grangs ni gong gi rgyu gcig pa la
NK063(gu)001:9448: sogs rnam pa bzhi yis gtan la phab pas gzhal
NK063(gu)001:9449: bya dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK063(gu)001:9450: ye nas mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i don
NK063(gu)001:9451: mngon du byas pa'i chos thams cad la dbang sgyur
NK063(gu)001:9452: ba'i phyir rgyal po yin la de khyad par du
NK063(gu)001:9454: gnyis pa dag pa'i gtan tshigs la yang gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:9455: dang po ni snod ces pa 'byung ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:9457: rigs kyi yum lngar dag pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9458: de ltar rtogs shing bsgoms na de ltar snang du rung ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9459: yang bcud ces pa phung po lnga yang rigs kyi yab lnga dang /
NK063(gu)001:9460: rgyud ces pa rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad kyang
NK063(gu)001:9461: ye shes lngar dag pa'i gtan tshigs kyis bsgrub pa
NK063(gu)001:9462: gong dang 'dra'o // de dag gi mthun dpe ni
NK063(gu)001:9463: zad par gyi skye mched goms pa lta bu ste
NK063(gu)001:9464: gong dang 'dra'o // / rtags de ltar rtogs shing
NK063(gu)001:9465: goms pa ltar snang bar ma grub bo zhe na
NK063(gu)001:9466: gong dang 'dra'o // / / ji ltar brtags pa de ltar snang ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9467: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin gcig tu ma nges
NK063(gu)001:9468: pa'i phyir dper na bum pa gcig nyid bden don
NK063(gu)001:9469: bcu bdun du dus gcig la snang ba bzhin no
NK063(gu)001:9470: // de ltar a ti'i gzhung las /
NK063(gu)001:9471: rang bzhin gcig tu ma nges pas //
NK063(gu)001:9472: ji ltar brtags pa de ltar snang //
NK063(gu)001:9474: de dag gi bye brag gzugs phung rnam snang du
NK063(gu)001:9475: ma nges te rin 'byung yin no zhes ma nges
NK063(gu)001:9476: pa'i ltar snang du 'gyur ba ni le'u dang por
NK063(gu)001:9477: spangs zin no // tha ma mnyam pa'i gtan tshigs la yang thun mong gi dang /
NK063(gu)001:9478: lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:9479: dang po ni chos thams cad don dam skye med du dang /
NK063(gu)001:9480: kun rdzob sgyu mar mnyam pa gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:9482: don dam nyid snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu lhun gyis grub pas lhag cing /
NK063(gu)001:9483: kun rdzob snang ba nyid rang bzhin med pas lhag pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9484: 'o na bden pa dbyer med dang spyod yul dang bral ba gnyis la gang gis lhag ce na /
NK063(gu)001:9485: de gnyis la lhag lugs mi dgos te /
NK063(gu)001:9486: 'dir lhag pa ni rgyu'i theg pa las khyad par 'phags pa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:9487: de gnyis rgyu'i theg pa la med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9488: de ltar thun mong ma yin pa'i mnyam pa gnyis
NK063(gu)001:9489: kyis gzhal bas chos thams cad bden pa dbyer med
NK063(gu)001:9490: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor du gtan la phab
NK063(gu)001:9491: pa ni / bden pa tha dad du 'dzin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:9492: spyod yul dag pa la kun tu bzang po rang
NK063(gu)001:9493: pa ni / bzhin te / de ni ngo bo
NK063(gu)001:9494: nyid kyis dag par gnas pa'i phyir zhing zhes bya'o
NK063(gu)001:9495: pa ni / bzhin te / // de ltar mnyam
NK063(gu)001:9496: pa'i don rtogs na sgo gsum gyis ji ltar byed
NK063(gu)001:9497: cing spyod pa thams cad ma 'gag par bsod nams
NK063(gu)001:9498: dang de dag tu ma dmigs pa ye shes kyi
NK063(gu)001:9499: tshogs chen po gnyis su gyur nas rang bzhin 'bras
NK063(gu)001:9500: bu mthar phyin pa la sbyor ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:9501: de ltar na gtan tshigs 'di dag gi skabs su
NK063(gu)001:9502: 'di lta bu cig dpyad pa'i yul du mthong ste
NK063(gu)001:9503: / gzhal bya zhen snang cig la gtan tshigs kyi
NK063(gu)001:9504: sgo dag mnyam rtogs pa gsum po des dus gcig
NK063(gu)001:9506: dang po ltar na shes rgyud gcig la rtog pa gsum dus gcig tu skye bar 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:9507: 'jal byed blo rdzas gsum gyis dus gcig tu 'jal ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9509: khyab pa tshad mas grub la /
NK063(gu)001:9512: rnam 'grel rtog gnyis cig car 'jug pa med //
NK063(gu)001:9514: 'gro la shes rgyud gnyis med ldan //
NK063(gu)001:9516: gnyis pa ltar na gtan tshigs gsum po zlos par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:9517: gzhal bya gcig la gtan tshigs gsum gyis re mos
NK063(gu)001:9518: su 'jal ba'i phyir ro zhes zer ba dag srid
NK063(gu)001:9519: na'ang / lan du 'di ltar 'thad par sems te /
NK063(gu)001:9520: de dag dus gcig tu'ang re mos su 'jal na de ltar bden mod kyi /
NK063(gu)001:9521: 'dir ni gnyis gang yang ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9522: bsgrub bya bsgrub 'dod la rags las pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:9523: de'i don yongs gcod du bsgrub bya lta ba'i rang
NK063(gu)001:9524: mtshan rtogs par 'dod pas rtogs pa'i gtan tshigs kyis
NK063(gu)001:9525: 'jal la / rnam bcad du dgag bya log ltog
NK063(gu)001:9526: dag par 'dod pas dag pa'i gtan tshigs kyis 'jal
NK063(gu)001:9527: 'jal la / zhing / dgag sgrub gnyis dang bral
NK063(gu)001:9528: bar 'dod pas mnyam pa'i gtan tshigs kyis 'jal ba
NK063(gu)001:9530: sngon chad mkhas pa rnams kyis 'di la brtags shing dpyad par ma mthong ngo //
NK063(gu)001:9531: yang kha cig 'dir gtan tshigs kyis gzhal bya gtan
NK063(gu)001:9532: la 'bebs pa 'di le'u gsum pa dang zlos so
NK063(gu)001:9534: gsum pa shes bya la gnas tshul du gtan la 'bebs pa yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:9535: 'dir lam pas rtogs tshul du gtan la 'bebs pa'i phyir snyam mo //
NK063(gu)001:9536: da ni gnyis pa cig car bas rgyu shes pa ltar gtan la 'bebs tshul la'ang gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:9538: dang po rtogs pa bzhi ni rgyu gcig pa dang zhes pas 'khor ba'i rgyu ma rig pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:9539: 'das pa'i rgyu ye shes gnyis don dam spros bral
NK063(gu)001:9540: du gcig cing kun rdzob sgyu ma yang gcig la
NK063(gu)001:9541: bden pa dbyer med du yang gcig par rtogs pas
NK063(gu)001:9542: te / ji skad du rngam glog las /
NK063(gu)001:9543: rgyu ni bden gnyis gcig pa ru //
NK063(gu)001:9544: gcig pas gcig pa'i mtshan nyid dang //
NK063(gu)001:9546: yig 'bru'i tshul zhes pa yi ge gsum gyis mtshon nas bden pa dbyer med du rtogs pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:9547: as mtshon nas sku dbyer med don dam du dang /
NK063(gu)001:9548: de la na ro ma 'gags pa o yis mtshon nas gsung 'gag med kun rdzob tu dang /
NK063(gu)001:9549: de la klad kor bzhag pa +amo gyis mtshon nas thugs skye 'gag dbyer med du rtogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9550: byin gyis brlabs dang zhes pa ras dkar po dmar
NK063(gu)001:9551: por gtong ba'i mthu btsod la yod pa ltar rtogs
NK063(gu)001:9552: pa gong ma'i mthu ngo shes pa las kyang yin
NK063(gu)001:9553: gyi / 'dir yi ge 'bru gsum gyis phung po
NK063(gu)001:9554: khams dang skye mched la sogs snang ba thams cad
NK063(gu)001:9555: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis rlob pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:9557: sku gsung thugs kyi yi ge ru //
NK063(gu)001:9558: chos kun rang bzhin gcig pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:9560: mngon sum pa ni gong gi rim gyis pa dang 'dra'o //
NK063(gu)001:9561: 'o na rim cig car gnyis khyad med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:9562: mngon sum pa ni rtogs pa rang gi ngo bo
NK063(gu)001:9563: yin pa'i phyir 'di la ltos nas 'dod pa yin
NK063(gu)001:9564: la / rtogs tshul la ltos te khyad par med pa'i rgyu mtshan ma grub bo //
NK063(gu)001:9565: gal te mngon sum par rtogs pa'i skabs 'dir dbyer
NK063(gu)001:9566: med rang mtshan de rtogs pa yin nam ma yin
NK063(gu)001:9567: / phyi ma ltar na mngon sum pa'i rtogs pa ma yin par 'gyur la /
NK063(gu)001:9568: dang po ltar na gtan tshigs byas na grub mtha' med la /
NK063(gu)001:9569: grub mtha' byas na gtan tshigs med do zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:9571: zhor sel zho bsgrub zhes bya ba /
NK063(gu)001:9572: dper na dngos po'i steng du byas pa'i rtags kyis
NK063(gu)001:9573: sgra mi rtag par bsgrub pa'i zhor la rtag pa
NK063(gu)001:9574: sel ba ltar / dbyer med rang mtshan rtogs pas
NK063(gu)001:9575: ma rtogs pa dang tha dad la sogs 'gal zla
NK063(gu)001:9577: de bsal bas rtogs pa rang gi ngo bo zhor la grub pa'i phyir na gtan tshigs yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:9578: zhor sel zhor bsgrub de lta bu dang bral bar phyir na grub mtha' yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9579: dper na nyan rang dgra lha 'bar la bu gcig
NK063(gu)001:9580: btsas ma thag des dgra gnyen gnyis la phan gnod
NK063(gu)001:9581: ma byas kyang de gnyis la dga' mi dga' gnyis
NK063(gu)001:9583: gnyis pa dag pa ni snod 'byung ba dang bcud
NK063(gu)001:9584: phung po dang shes pa'i rgyud tshogs brgyad rnams kun
NK063(gu)001:9585: rdzob tu rigs kyi yab dang yum dang ye shes
NK063(gu)001:9586: su dag cing / don dam du de dag chos
NK063(gu)001:9587: kyi dbyings su dag par rtogs shing de la gnas
NK063(gu)001:9588: su dag cing / pa'o // gsum pa mnyam pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:9589: thun mong gi mnyam pa gnyis dang lhag pa'i mnyam
NK063(gu)001:9590: pa gnyis la sogs pa'i tha snyad kyis stongs te
NK063(gu)001:9591: / shes bya thams cad rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor du gcig pas /
NK063(gu)001:9592: chos thams cad ye nas mnyam pa nyid yin don
NK063(gu)001:9593: la de rtogs kyi blos dgag sgrub tu 'dzin pa
NK063(gu)001:9594: yongs su dag pa'i phyir kun tu bzang po yin
NK063(gu)001:9596: mi len mi 'dor mnyam pa'i rgyal por gnas //
NK063(gu)001:9598: de'i zhing ni mnyam pa nyid yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9599: ji skad du spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:9600: ngo bo nyid kyi zhing khams zhes bya ba kho na'o //
NK063(gu)001:9603: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba yi //
NK063(gu)001:9605: blo de la ltos te gong ltar gzhal bya dang
NK063(gu)001:9606: gtan tshigs dang grub mtha' gsum du 'dzin pa dang
NK063(gu)001:9608: ji skad du lam rim le'u tha ma las /
NK063(gu)001:9609: chos dang chos can kun bral ba //
NK063(gu)001:9610: rang spyi dbyer med dus gcig tu //
NK063(gu)001:9611: mi phyed rdo rje thugs mchog go //
NK063(gu)001:9613: spyi don gsum pa gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha' ni /
NK063(gu)001:9614: bsgrub bya la 'khrul pa dang bral ba zhig yin pa de ni tshig bsgyur te 'og gi /
NK063(gu)001:9615: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas zhes pa de yin no //
NK063(gu)001:9616: 'khrul pa ni de rang gi sems las gzhan du 'dzin pa zhig yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9617: des na yang gong na 'khrul pa las yod pa'i shar la sogs pa phyogs bcu dang /
NK063(gu)001:9618: 'das ma 'ongs la sogs pa dus bzhi gang nas btsal kyang /
NK063(gu)001:9620: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnyed par mi 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:9621: ji skad du spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:9622: sangs rgyas ni gdul bya'i dbang gis btags su zin
NK063(gu)001:9623: kyang ngo bo nyid kyis bstan par dka' ba'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:9625: 'o na gang du btsal zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:9626: rang gi sems nyid ye nas rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK063(gu)001:9627: yin la de ltar shes pa ni bdag zhal bdag
NK063(gu)001:9630: ma lus bdag nyid zhal mthong ba //
NK063(gu)001:9631: dbang bsgyur mchog nyid dam pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:9634: rang bzhin gnas phyir gnas nas 'ong ba med //
NK063(gu)001:9635: zhen pa log nas bdag zhal bdag gis mthong //
NK063(gu)001:9637: des na sangs rgyas zhes ni rang gi sems las gzhan du ma 'tshol cig ces gdams pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:9638: gong gi gtan tshigs de dag gis sems las gzhan
NK063(gu)001:9639: du 'dzin pa bkag nas rang gi sems sangs rgyas
NK063(gu)001:9640: su rtogs pa ni bsgrub bya grub pa'i mtha' yin
NK063(gu)001:9641: no // gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid la yang rim gyis pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:9643: dang po la yang gnyis te gang gis gang du
NK063(gu)001:9644: gang la brten te nam gyi tshe sgrub pa bzhi
NK063(gu)001:9646: gang ji ltar grub pa sgrub pa'i thabs phun sum tshogs pa gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:9647: dang po sgrub pa po ni tshig bsgyung te 'og
NK063(gu)001:9648: nas rnal 'byor zhes pa ston pa phun sum tshogs
NK063(gu)001:9649: pa rdo rje rgyal po dang /
NK063(gu)001:9650: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa rgyas thebs nas rdul phyags
NK063(gu)001:9651: skyes bu yan chad pho mo du ma 'tshogs pa'o
NK063(gu)001:9652: // de dag gi mtshan nyid 'jug spyod kyi chos
NK063(gu)001:9653: bco lnga tshang ba ste le'u dgu pa bshad pa
NK063(gu)001:9654: ltar gong nas lha'i yan lag lnga po mnyams shing
NK063(gu)001:9655: // / sgrub pa'i yo byad lnga dang ldan nas
NK063(gu)001:9656: lam gyi rim pa'i cho ga lnga rdzogs pas bsgrub
NK063(gu)001:9657: bya grub par shes pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:9658: yang 'og nas bsgom bya tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyis /
NK063(gu)001:9659: nges par 'bras bu grub ste legs pa ni gnas
NK063(gu)001:9660: skabs la dgongs pa ste mthar thug gi 'bras bu
NK063(gu)001:9661: 'grub pa'o // gnas dang yo byad phun sum tshogs pa gnyis la /
NK063(gu)001:9662: dang po gang du bsgrub pa'i gnas ni 'tsho ba yo byad kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:9664: srog gi dang bar chad gsum med pa ste mtshan nyid ni le'u dgu par bshad zin to //
NK063(gu)001:9665: dang zhes pa gzhan sdud pa ste gnas der slob dpon gyi bsag bya sgrub rdzas rnams dang /
NK063(gu)001:9666: 'khor gyi bsag bya bza' ba dang btung ba'i yo byad la sogs longs spyod dang /
NK063(gu)001:9667: thun mong du bsag bya rkyen zlog rnams so //
NK063(gu)001:9668: ci bde zhes pa de dag 'byongs pas bde bar longs spyod du yod pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9669: de dang gong gi yan lag bco lnga po ma
NK063(gu)001:9670: nyams shing rtogs goms kyi blo dang ni rab tu
NK063(gu)001:9672: dang po dam mnos zhes pa ni kha cig zhag
NK063(gu)001:9673: grangs dam mnos pa la 'dod pa ni ma yin
NK063(gu)001:9674: te / dam mnos pa des mi 'grub pa dang de mi dgos pa yang srid pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9675: 'o na gang zhe na zhi khro'i tshom bu gang
NK063(gu)001:9676: sgrub dang por dam nos pa bzhin du mthar phyin
NK063(gu)001:9677: par bya ba'o // de ltar sgrub pa'i tshe spang
NK063(gu)001:9678: bya le lo dang sgyid snyoms rnams spangs te med
NK063(gu)001:9679: pa yis dngos grub kyi gegs the tshom yin la
NK063(gu)001:9680: de dang bral ba ste med par bsgrub bya bsgrubs
NK063(gu)001:9681: par bya ba'o // par byas na / 'bras bu
NK063(gu)001:9682: mthar phyin pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:9685: yon tan lhun gyis grub pas rdo rje la sku
NK063(gu)001:9686: gsung thugs kyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab cing
NK063(gu)001:9687: bsgrub bya gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas mchog
NK063(gu)001:9689: de rang rig la mngon du gyur pas thob ces brjod pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9690: dus phun sum tshogs pa ni tshig gong 'og bsgyur nas spyir tshogs sgrub kyi dus bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:9694: zag med la sbyor ba'i zhag gi dus so //
NK063(gu)001:9695: de dag rgyud 'di nyid kyi le'u dgu pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:9696: rgyud gzhan las kyang smos pa bzhin du bshad de /
NK063(gu)001:9697: dang po ni gza' skar tshes grangs bzang po la 'jug pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:9699: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad la brtsam //
NK063(gu)001:9701: shin tu skar ma rgyal rnams la //
NK063(gu)001:9703: gnyis pa yang de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:9706: gsum pa ni skya rengs shar ba'i dus so //
NK063(gu)001:9707: tha ma ni 'di'i dgu pa las /
NK063(gu)001:9708: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK063(gu)001:9709: bcu gnyis bcu gzhi bcu drug gis //
NK063(gu)001:9710: dbang sgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK063(gu)001:9712: yang 'dir kha cig rgyud log pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9714: rgyud las smos pa bzhin du bshad //
NK063(gu)001:9715: ces pa ni 'di rgyud ma yin par shugs la mtshon par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:9716: de ltar bshad kyang 'di rgyud ma yin par mi 'gyur na ci 'gal te khyab pa med do //
NK063(gu)001:9717: gal te khyab pa yod na /
NK063(gu)001:9718: spyir rgyud 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba yang de ltar 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:9720: rgyud chen sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las //
NK063(gu)001:9722: kho na re de ni bstod pa glu blangs kyi
NK063(gu)001:9723: le'u de sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khri drug stong pa
NK063(gu)001:9724: de nyid du kha 'phangs pas de ltar mi 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:9725: zhe na / mtshungs te 'dir yang zag med rig
NK063(gu)001:9726: 'dzin la sbyor pa'i dus 'di nyid kyi le'u dgu
NK063(gu)001:9728: gzhan yang 'jug pa dang dkyil 'khor bri ba'i dus
NK063(gu)001:9729: bam brgyad dang rdo rjee bkod pa la sogs su
NK063(gu)001:9730: kha 'phangs kyang 'di rgyud ma yin par mi 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:9732: gsar ma'i dgyes pa rdo rje yang rgyud ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:9734: ji ltar de nyid bsdus pa yi //
NK063(gu)001:9735: dkyil 'khor cho ga de bzhin bya //
NK063(gu)001:9736: zhes de nyid bsdus par kha 'phangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9737: gzhan yang mdo sngags thun mong du grags pa'i sor
NK063(gu)001:9738: sor 'brang ma yang bka' ma yin par 'gyur te
NK063(gu)001:9739: / ji skad du de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:9740: cho ga las ni 'byung ba bzhin //
NK063(gu)001:9741: zhes sgrub thabs su kha 'phangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9743: rgyud las smos pa bzhin du bshad //
NK063(gu)001:9744: ces pas rang gi don ni spyir dka' stsal ston pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:9746: mtshams sbyor sdud pa po'i tshig gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:9748: gang gis bsgrub pa'i thabs la zhi khro gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:9749: zhi ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi mdor bstan pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:9750: rigs kyi bye brag bzhir sbyar te /
NK063(gu)001:9751: rtogs bya lta ba'i don dang sbyar ba /
NK063(gu)001:9752: sgrub pa lam gyi rim pa dang sbyar ba /
NK063(gu)001:9753: rjes 'jug gi tshogs sgrub pa zhig gis dus dang sbyar ba /
NK063(gu)001:9754: dngos gzhi sbyor ba'i thabs kyi yan lag dang sbyar ba dang bzhi'o //
NK063(gu)001:9755: de yang bsnyen pa dang ni zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:9756: dang po ltar na rtogs bya byang chub kyi sems
NK063(gu)001:9757: de bzhin nyid de gzhan la rag ma las par
NK063(gu)001:9759: gnyis pa ltar na rgyu shes par lta ba gtan
NK063(gu)001:9760: la phab nas de ting dang kun ting gis de'i
NK063(gu)001:9762: gsum pa ltar na phun sum tshogs pa lngas gzhi bzung ste sngon 'gro shom byed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9763: bzhi pa ltar na mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i yum
NK063(gu)001:9764: phyi nang gi chos gsum gyis bsten par bya ste
NK063(gu)001:9765: khrus dang rgyan gyis brgyan nas lhar gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:9766: nye bsnyen dang zhes pa dang po ltar na rang
NK063(gu)001:9767: gi byang sems de yang bde bar gshegs pa'i snying
NK063(gu)001:9768: por grub nas yod pa de'o //
NK063(gu)001:9769: gnyis pa ltar na bdag lhar shes pa phyag rgya gcig spros so //
NK063(gu)001:9770: gsum pa ltar na ji tsam grub pa'i phyed tshul gyis snod du rung bar byed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9771: bzhi pa ltar na yum byin gyis brlab cing gdan gcig la 'dug pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9772: sgrub pa dang ni zhes pa dang po ltar na
NK063(gu)001:9773: grub pa'i don de gsang ba'i lung dang man ngag
NK063(gu)001:9774: gis mtshon cing gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9775: gnyis pa ltar na tshogs sgrub yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9776: yo byad lnga dang ldan pas dngos grub don du gnyer ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:9777: gsum pa ltar na tha ma'i zhag gcig ma gtogs pa ji tsam sgrub pa'i phyed phan chad do //
NK063(gu)001:9778: bzhi pa ltar na yab yum gnyis lha'i sku gsung
NK063(gu)001:9779: thugs dang mnyam par sbyor bas phyag rgya bzhis rol
NK063(gu)001:9780: pa ste dbab bzung gi dgongs pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:9781: sgrub chen po zhes pa dang po ltar na gtan
NK063(gu)001:9782: la phab pas lta ba nges te mthar phyin pa'o
NK063(gu)001:9783: // gnyis pa ltar na tshogs sgrub rgyun gyi tha
NK063(gu)001:9784: ma ste zag med kyi rigs 'dzin thob la ma
NK063(gu)001:9785: // rag pa'o // gsum pa ltar na nub tha
NK063(gu)001:9786: ma'i dgongs pa cho ga'i sgo nas bkod pa rdzas
NK063(gu)001:9788: bzhi pa ltar na byang sems yum gyi mkha' nas
NK063(gu)001:9789: rdo rje lce yis len pa sde ldog dgram gyi
NK063(gu)001:9791: bsnyen sgrub bzhi rgyas pa la gzhi'i sngon du bya ba'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:9792: bya ba las kyi bsnyen pa gnyis kyi 'bru gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:9793: 'dir bsgom bya tshom bu zhes bya ba rigs gang
NK063(gu)001:9794: dang gang gis gtso bo byas pa la de dang
NK063(gu)001:9795: de'i 'khor gyis bskor ba 'di dkyil 'khor dang ngo
NK063(gu)001:9796: bo tha dad pa cig yin nam /
NK063(gu)001:9797: yang na ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad pa cig yin nam /
NK063(gu)001:9798: gal te ming gi rnam grangs pa cig yin zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:9799: 'di gnyis lha'i ngo bo mthun zhing grangs mnyam yang
NK063(gu)001:9800: tshom dkyil gnyis la chos tha dad pa yod pas
NK063(gu)001:9802: kha cig na re rnam grangs byung rdzogs su brjod
NK063(gu)001:9803: pa'i ngos nas dkyil 'khor yin la pho brang gtso
NK063(gu)001:9804: bo'i ngos nas tshom bu yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9805: gtso bo gcig yod pas tshom bu gcig pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:9806: gsum yod pas gsum pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:9807: lnga yod pas lnga par 'gyur ba'i phyir zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:9809: yang kha cig ni rnal 'byor pa pho mo re
NK063(gu)001:9810: re dang lha yab yum re re brang sprod du
NK063(gu)001:9811: bsgom pa tshom bu yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:9812: rnal 'byor pa gcig gis lha kun bsgom pa'am brang
NK063(gu)001:9813: sprod du bsgom par ma nges par dkyil 'khor yin
NK063(gu)001:9814: no // yang na bdag don gtso che ba tshom
NK063(gu)001:9815: bu dang gzhan don gtso che ba dkyil 'khor yin
NK063(gu)001:9816: no // zhes gsung ngo // kha cig ni lha
NK063(gu)001:9817: yab yum 'brel par nges pa tshom bu dang der
NK063(gu)001:9818: ma nges pa dkyil 'khor yin zhes gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:9819: bud+d+ha k+airti ni zhi ba la yab yum zung du
NK063(gu)001:9820: nges shing gtso 'khor rigs nges pas gong ma dag
NK063(gu)001:9822: khro bo la de dag gis khyad par mi byed de /
NK063(gu)001:9823: gnas yul dbang mo rnams tshom dkyil gnyis ka la zhugs pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:9824: ji skad du bco lnga pa las /
NK063(gu)001:9825: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po zhes pa nas
NK063(gu)001:9826: chu lha mo rnams 'khril lo zhes dbang mo'i yab
NK063(gu)001:9827: rigs lngar bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9829: dkyil 'khor gyi sgra tsam gcig tshom bu la yang 'jug ste /
NK063(gu)001:9830: tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor zhes zer ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9831: 'on kyang gtso bo rigs chung dang bcas pa rang gi rigs su nges pa tshom bu yin la /
NK063(gu)001:9832: gtso bo rigs chung yang spyi'i rigs su nges shing
NK063(gu)001:9833: sgo bzhir sgo srung dang bcas pa ni dkyil 'khor
NK063(gu)001:9835: rnal 'byor pas lha spyi'am bye brag tu bsgom pa ni gzhung brtags la /
NK063(gu)001:9836: 'di tshom bu gcig pa bsgom pa yin nam /
NK063(gu)001:9837: dkyil 'khor bsdus pa bsgom pa yin /
NK063(gu)001:9838: dang po ltar na tshom bu'i gtso bo rigs nges pa can yin pa la /
NK063(gu)001:9839: 'di'i 'grel par gtso bo rigs drug po gang yang rung ba ste ma nges so //
NK063(gu)001:9840: 'di ni tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dang gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor kun la sbyar ro //
NK063(gu)001:9842: gnyis pa ltar na gzhung gis rnal 'byor pa dang
NK063(gu)001:9843: lha brang sprod du bsgom par gsal zhing gzhan yang
NK063(gu)001:9844: le'u gnyis sdeb nas tshogs sgrub pa'i bsgom bya tshom
NK063(gu)001:9845: bu yin pa'i phyir dkyil 'khor yin par mi 'thad
NK063(gu)001:9846: de zhe na / spyir tshom bu gcig pa dang
NK063(gu)001:9847: dkyil 'khor bsdus pa gnyis lha grangs mnyam ste rigs
NK063(gu)001:9848: gang yang rung ba'i gtso bo yab yum la de'i
NK063(gu)001:9849: rigs chung yab yum brgyad de bco brgyad do //
NK063(gu)001:9850: skabs 'dir 'grel pa'i ngag 'di tshom dkyil gnyis kyi
NK063(gu)001:9851: khyad par phye nas 'di dkyil 'khor bsdus par bzhed
NK063(gu)001:9852: de / gtso bo ma nges par gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9853: 'o na skyon phyi ma gang gis spong zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:9854: mi shes pas brjod pa'i skyon de spang mi dgos te /
NK063(gu)001:9855: lha dang rnal 'byor pa brang sprod du bsgom pa dkyil 'khor ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9856: tshogs sgrub la dkyil 'khor bsgom pa khegs par rgyud
NK063(gu)001:9857: 'grel gang nas kyang bshad pa med pa'i phyir ro
NK063(gu)001:9858: // 'o na dkyil 'khor rgyas bsdus kyi khyad par gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:9859: spyir rgyas pa'i khongs nas 'bring po'i lha tshogs 'byung
NK063(gu)001:9860: zhing der bsdus pa'i lha rnams 'byung dgos pa la
NK063(gu)001:9861: / 'dir de ltar ma byung bas rgyas bsdus su mi 'thad do zhes rtog na /
NK063(gu)001:9862: rgyas bsdus la bye brag gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:9866: dang po ni gcig khongs su gcig 'byung ba gong ltar yin no //
NK063(gu)001:9867: 'di ni rigs rgyas bsdus te gtso bo rigs lnga
NK063(gu)001:9868: la rigs spyi'i sems dpa' yab yum brgyad kyis bskor
NK063(gu)001:9869: ba ni rigs rgyas pa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:9870: gtso bo rigs lnga la 'khor sems dpa' yab yum
NK063(gu)001:9871: gnyis gnyis las ma smos pa ni 'bring po yin
NK063(gu)001:9872: zhing / gtso bo rigs lnga gang rung gcig la
NK063(gu)001:9873: rang gi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad kyis bskor ba
NK063(gu)001:9874: ni rigs gcig gi cha las med pas bsdus pa
NK063(gu)001:9875: zhing / yin no // tshom bu gsum la sgrub pa ni gzhung brtags la /
NK063(gu)001:9876: 'dir kha cig tshom bu gcig pa gsum pa lnga pa gsum la khyad par yod dam med /
NK063(gu)001:9877: phyi ma ltar na khyad par yod par gzhung gis gsal te /
NK063(gu)001:9879: gnyis med 'gyur nas phyag rgya che //
NK063(gu)001:9880: gcig pa'i 'bras bu rgya chen po //
NK063(gu)001:9882: zhes gsum pa'i 'bras bu lhun grub dang /
NK063(gu)001:9883: dngos grub mchog gi snying po 'grub //
NK063(gu)001:9884: ces lnga pa'i 'bras bu sku lngar bshad pa'i phyir ro zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:9885: de la 'bras bu la khyad par gsungs kyang rgyu
NK063(gu)001:9886: tshom bu la khyad par med na ci 'ga' byas
NK063(gu)001:9887: pas / kho na re 'bras bu chos can //
NK063(gu)001:9888: rgyu'i rjes su 'gro ldog mi byed par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:9889: rgyu khyad par med pa la 'bras bu khyad par can dmigs pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:9890: rtags de'i zur dang po khas blangs la gnyis pa gzhung nas gsungs pas grub cing /
NK063(gu)001:9891: rgyu la khyad par med cing 'bras bu khyad par
NK063(gu)001:9892: can du dmigs pa de la 'bras bu rgyu'i rjes
NK063(gu)001:9893: su 'gro ldog mi byed par 'gyur bas khyab bo
NK063(gu)001:9894: // 'dod na rgyu khegs pas 'bras bu khegs par bsal lo zhes zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:9895: yang tshom bu gsum pa khyad par yod na /
NK063(gu)001:9896: rdo rje'i rigs su thams cad dkyil //
NK063(gu)001:9897: zhes gcig pa'i gtso bo dang /
NK063(gu)001:9898: thugs nyid de zhes gsum pa'i gtso bo dang /
NK063(gu)001:9899: dkyil 'khor lnga dang zhes lnga pa'i gtso bo dang
NK063(gu)001:9900: gsum rdo rje sems dpar ngo bo mi gcig par
NK063(gu)001:9901: 'gyur te / khyad par yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9903: khyad par yod pa la ngo bo gcig ma yin pas khyab la /
NK063(gu)001:9904: 'dod na tshom bu gsum gyi gtso bo rdo rje sems dpar gcig pas gsal lo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:9905: de'i lan ni bsgom bya tshom dkyil la ltos te
NK063(gu)001:9906: lha mang nyung gi khyad par cung zad yod kyang
NK063(gu)001:9907: lha'i ngo bo gcig pa'i phyir khyad par med pas
NK063(gu)001:9909: 'o na 'bras bu'i khyad par gsum bshad pa de
NK063(gu)001:9910: dag rgyu'i rjes su 'gro ldog byas pa ma yin
NK063(gu)001:9911: par 'gyur te / rgyu tshom bu gsum ngo bo gcig pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:9913: bsgom bya gcig nyid la'ang sgom pa po rten gyi gang zag gi rgyud tshod dang /
NK063(gu)001:9914: lam slob pa'i rim pa la ltos te grangs mang nyung dang /
NK063(gu)001:9915: rnam pa gsal mi gsal dang /
NK063(gu)001:9916: tshom bu'am dkyil 'khor rgyas bsdus la sogs pa ni bsgom bya'i khyad par ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9917: sgom pa po'i khyad pa yin pa'i phyir skyon phyi ma'ang med par sems te /
NK063(gu)001:9918: ji skad du rdo rje las kyang /
NK063(gu)001:9919: mos pa'i tshul dang sbyar ba yin //
NK063(gu)001:9920: tshom bu gcig pa'i lha rnams dang //
NK063(gu)001:9921: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:9922: des na sgom pa po la khyad par yod pas
NK063(gu)001:9923: tshom bu la khyad par byung la de byung bas
NK063(gu)001:9924: 'bras bu la'ang khyad par byung ba sems so //
NK063(gu)001:9925: yang bzhi ba tshogs sgrub kyi skabs 'dir lnga dang
NK063(gu)001:9926: lnga yi zhes pa la sogs pa tshom bu lan
NK063(gu)001:9928: rdo rje'i rigs su thams cad dkyil //
NK063(gu)001:9929: zhes par lan cig gsungs pa gnyis zlos so zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:9930: 'di skabs dang dgos ched gnyis kyi phyir mi zlos te /
NK063(gu)001:9931: de yang skabs ni dang po bsnyen pa'i skabs yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:9932: gnyis pa sgrub pa'i skabs yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:9933: dgos ched kyang dang po tshom bu'i rnam grangs bde
NK063(gu)001:9934: blag tu rtogs pas de sgom shes pa'i dgos pa
NK063(gu)001:9935: yod cing / gnyis pa bsgoms pas 'bras bu'i rim
NK063(gu)001:9936: pa gsum thob tshul dang bcas pa'i sgo nas ma
NK063(gu)001:9937: 'ongs pa'i gdul bya rnams brod pas 'jug pa'i dgos
NK063(gu)001:9939: sgrub pa chen po'i yo byad spyir lnga las /
NK063(gu)001:9940: gzhi la spyad thabs ni gzhung brtags la /
NK063(gu)001:9941: bye brag +aa li k+aa li la spyad pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:9942: spyir mtshon byed +aa li k+aa lis thabs shes rab
NK063(gu)001:9943: dang yab yum la sogs du ma mtshon pa las
NK063(gu)001:9944: / skabs 'dir sbyor sgrol gnyis mtshon pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:9946: 'dis ni rang bzhin sbyor sgrol dang //
NK063(gu)001:9947: ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyor sgrol dang //
NK063(gu)001:9948: dbang po yul dus sbyor sgrol dang //
NK063(gu)001:9949: thabs chen po yi sbyor sgrol dang //
NK063(gu)001:9950: mngon du phyung ba'i sbyor sgrol lo //
NK063(gu)001:9952: dang po ni ye nas gnas pa'i mtshan nyid kyi
NK063(gu)001:9953: don la de rtogs kyi blos sbyor ba ni sbyor
NK063(gu)001:9954: ba yin la / des ma rig pa rnam par dag pa yi sgrol ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:9956: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba yis //
NK063(gu)001:9959: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK063(gu)001:9961: gnyis pa ni bskyed rim gyi tshe bsgom bya yin
NK063(gu)001:9962: la de mngon du byung ba'i cha rkyen du 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:9963: ba yin no // de yang thabs zhags las /
NK063(gu)001:9964: rnam shes h+aum gis bsdus rdubs te //
NK063(gu)001:9965: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK063(gu)001:9966: gtso bo dang ni gtso mo dang //
NK063(gu)001:9967: sems dpa' dang ni sems ma rnams //
NK063(gu)001:9968: sbyor ba'i lhums su phata kyis 'phang //
NK063(gu)001:9970: gsum pa ni snang ba thams cad sku dang ye
NK063(gu)001:9971: shes su gsal bas rtog tshogs su btags pa las
NK063(gu)001:9972: grol ba ste / bcu gsum pa las /
NK063(gu)001:9973: dbang po yul dus rig pa rnams //
NK063(gu)001:9974: byang chub sems ni rdo rje'i tshogs //
NK063(gu)001:9976: bzhi pa ni sngon byung du rgyal ba rnams kyis drag po'i phrin las kyi don mdzad pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:9978: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kas //
NK063(gu)001:9979: pho bsgral dur khrod brgyad du byas //
NK063(gu)001:9980: mo rnams sbyar te slas su byas //
NK063(gu)001:9981: de ni thabs kyi mdzad spyod do //
NK063(gu)001:9982: zhes pas te le'u bco lnga par ston no //
NK063(gu)001:9983: tha ma ni 'dir tshogs sgrub kyi dus su dngos kyi spyad bya yin te /
NK063(gu)001:9984: de rten gyi gang zag ji lta bu zhig gis spyad ce na /
NK063(gu)001:9985: kha cig na re ting nge 'dzin gyis 'gugs shing
NK063(gu)001:9986: sgrol bar nus la ji srid ma mos na zlog
NK063(gu)001:9987: par yang nus te nus pa gnyis dang ldan pa
NK063(gu)001:9989: 'dir ni gong du bshad pa'i sgrub pa po'i mtshan nyid /
NK063(gu)001:9990: ma nyams blo ni rab ldan pas //
NK063(gu)001:9991: zhes pa rgyu shes pa mtshan nyid rtogs pa'i blo dang ldan zhing /
NK063(gu)001:9992: rkyen 'jug spyod kyi yan lag bco lnga ma nyams
NK063(gu)001:9993: shing snang byed kyi ting nge 'dzin la goms pa
NK063(gu)001:9994: dang rlung sems la dbang thob pa zhig yin te
NK063(gu)001:9998: des ji ltar spyad par bya ba ni gzhung ltar gsum mo //
NK063(gu)001:9999: dang po +aa li sbyor ba la yang gsum las gang la sbyar ba'i yul ni /
NK063(gu)001:10000: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK063(gu)001:10001: zhes pa sgrub pa po dgongs pa stobs che na
NK063(gu)001:10002: dang po gnyis dngos yin la phyi ma mi'i bu
NK063(gu)001:10003: mo ste de chung na gsum ka mi'i bu mo'o
NK063(gu)001:10004: // de dag gi khyad par rim pa ltar mtshan
NK063(gu)001:10005: gyi sgo nas dung can ma mnyam ma zhar ma
NK063(gu)001:10006: // zhes bya / thig le'i sgo nas zla ba
NK063(gu)001:10007: dang ldan pa nyi ma dang ldan pa gnyis ka
NK063(gu)001:10009: bde ba'i sgo nas gnyis ka bde ba dang gzhan bde ba dang rang bde ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:10010: lo grangs kyi sgo nas bcu gnyis ma dang bcu drug ma dang nyer lnga ma'o //
NK063(gu)001:10011: de dag kyang sgeg pa'i gzhung las rigs can brgyad du bshad de /
NK063(gu)001:10013: pad can dung can ri mo can //
NK063(gu)001:10014: ba lang can dang lcug phran dang //
NK063(gu)001:10015: sdong gcig mes reg phyal ba brgyad //
NK063(gu)001:10017: de dag gi mtshan nyid kyang de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:10018: mnyen drang rked ring stod smad phyed //
NK063(gu)001:10019: yan lag phra 'jam tshigs rmig zlum //
NK063(gu)001:10020: dpral ba'i dgyes che smin dkyus ring //
NK063(gu)001:10021: mig phra dkyil nas ut+pala mdog /
NK063(gu)001:10022: mchu zheng gnyis ka 'bring du bshad //
NK063(gu)001:10023: lus la chu rlung ga bur dri //
NK063(gu)001:10024: gsang thub shes rab spyod pa dkyil //
NK063(gu)001:10025: dad ldan 'grogs shing dad pa che //
NK063(gu)001:10026: gsang ba'i gnas su spyad par bya //
NK063(gu)001:10028: de dag sgrub pa po thabs sam dgongs pa stobs
NK063(gu)001:10029: chung na mtshan la bde ba rag las pa'i phyiir
NK063(gu)001:10030: rigs dbye ste bzang po la rol pa'am yang na
NK063(gu)001:10031: thabs dang dgongs pa stobs chen mi dbye bar rol
NK063(gu)001:10032: pa'o // ji ltar spyad pa'i thabs ni bsnyen pa
NK063(gu)001:10033: dang ni zhes pa la sogs sbyor ba dus kyi
NK063(gu)001:10034: yan lag bzhi dang ldan pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:10035: gong gi mdor bstan pa'i skabs su bye brag bzhi'i tha ma 'dir ngos gzung ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:10036: de yang sgeg pa'i gzhung las /
NK063(gu)001:10037: dbang bskur dam dpog chos gsum bshad //
NK063(gu)001:10038: lus la rigs lnga'i rdul tshon dgye //
NK063(gu)001:10039: thabs la mkhas pas skabs kyis sbyar //
NK063(gu)001:10041: de ltar yum gyi mkha' pad+ma brgyad du brlabs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:10042: dkyil 'khor du nyams su myong ba'i bde ba de
NK063(gu)001:10043: rgyal ba'i thugs gnyis su med pa'i ye shes mtshon
NK063(gu)001:10044: byed yin la / de'i rten kun rdzob byang chub
NK063(gu)001:10045: sems kyi dkyil 'khor las skyes pa'i brten pa bde
NK063(gu)001:10046: bas lus kyi srid pa kun tu khyab pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:10047: byed yin la / spros pa'o // des rtog pa
NK063(gu)001:10048: thams cad sku dang ye shes su sangs rgyas pa
NK063(gu)001:10049: ni sprin tshogs lta bu mang la 'brel ba ma
NK063(gu)001:10050: lus pa rnams la bde bas dgyes pa'i ro yab
NK063(gu)001:10051: yum gnyis ka la dus mnyam du bstar bas tha
NK063(gu)001:10052: mal gyi 'dod chags ye shes su dag pas mchog
NK063(gu)001:10053: byed yin la / spros pa'o // yin la /
NK063(gu)001:10054: de la 'dzin pa dang bral bas sbyin pas te
NK063(gu)001:10055: yab yum gnyis phan tshun gcig gis bde ba gcig
NK063(gu)001:10056: la dgod cing gnyis su med pa bstim pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10057: de'i yon tan sbyor ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi las byung
NK063(gu)001:10058: ba'i nyi zla ni yab yum gyi rtsa sa ya
NK063(gu)001:10059: phrag bcu gsum gyi bcud 'dus pa'i snying po'o //
NK063(gu)001:10060: de ltar byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor de yab
NK063(gu)001:10061: kyi thabs kyi rdo rje'i lce yis so sor phye
NK063(gu)001:10062: nas yum gyi mkha' nas blangs te ldog pa'i thabs
NK063(gu)001:10063: kyis ldog cing dgram par byas nas /
NK063(gu)001:10064: spyi gtsug bde chen du sngon gyi gnas phyi mo
NK063(gu)001:10065: dang 'phrad pa'i tshe thun mong gi yon tan ni
NK063(gu)001:10066: mkha' la 'gro zhing kha dog gsal ba dang 'od
NK063(gu)001:10067: 'bar zhing tshe ring ba dang mngon shes dang ldan
NK063(gu)001:10068: zhing rdzu 'phrul grub pa la sogs du ma grub
NK063(gu)001:10069: la / thun mong ma yin pa'i yon tan yid
NK063(gu)001:10070: bzhin gyi nor bu bzhin dgos 'dod rnams sprin las
NK063(gu)001:10071: char gyi rgyun ltar 'byung bas che ba'i yon tan
NK063(gu)001:10072: du ma'i bdag nyid chen por 'gyur ba ni sku
NK063(gu)001:10073: la / lnga nyid do // gzhan yang sgeg pa'i gzhung las ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:10074: dngos grub yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK063(gu)001:10075: slob bu smin zhing las rnams 'grub //
NK063(gu)001:10076: skye gnas kun grol rigs su nges //
NK063(gu)001:10077: thabs kyi theg pa 'di bshad do //
NK063(gu)001:10079: gnyis pa k+aa li sgrol ba la spyad pa yang gong ltar gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:10080: gang bsgral bya'i yul ni thugs rjes bzung ba'i zhing bsgral ba'i zhing du gyur pa la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:10081: mchog ces pa bkra shis dag pa'i zhing dang /
NK063(gu)001:10082: mchog phran zhes pa thugs rjes gzung ba'i zhing ngo //
NK063(gu)001:10083: de yang dang po ni byang chub sems dpa' skye
NK063(gu)001:10084: ba bdun pa gzhan phan gyi blos lus sbyin par
NK063(gu)001:10085: gtong ba la thugs rjes bskul ba lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:10086: gnyis pa ni sgeg pa'i gzhung las /
NK063(gu)001:10087: dkon cog slob dpon sku dgra gnyis //
NK063(gu)001:10088: dam nyams log dang 'khus pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:10090: dam dgra ngan pa'i ngang tshul can //
NK063(gu)001:10091: ngon song gsum dang bcu po 'di //
NK063(gu)001:10092: rnal 'byor kun gyis dang du blangs //
NK063(gu)001:10093: zhes pas zhing bcu po rnams so //
NK063(gu)001:10094: ji ltar bsgral ba'i thabs ni /
NK063(gu)001:10095: dkyil 'khor gyi byang phyogs su e'i dkyil 'khor du nyi zla'i gdan bkod pa'i steng du /
NK063(gu)001:10096: gang gis na sgrol ba'i thabs la mkhas pas 'khor ba ru zlog pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:10097: ji ltar na gan rkyal du bsgyel la gzhag go //
NK063(gu)001:10098: de yang thabs la mkhas pa de ging ta ki
NK063(gu)001:10099: r+aa tsar bskyed pa'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas lag
NK063(gu)001:10100: gi 'du byed sor mo lnga la zla dkyil steng
NK063(gu)001:10101: du dpa' bo 'bru lnga bsgom zhing /
NK063(gu)001:10102: ka ra ri m+aum las 'jam dpal rnon por bskyed
NK063(gu)001:10103: de gzung 'dzin gyi rgya dral ba'i phyir khog dbugs
NK063(gu)001:10104: dral te rnam par shes pa'i rten tsit+ta la gong
NK063(gu)001:10105: gi dpa' bo 'bru lngas reg pa'i tshe 'khor ba'i
NK063(gu)001:10106: sa bon drug po bsregs te h+aum drug tu gyur
NK063(gu)001:10107: pas sgrib pa rnam par dag cing thugs ye shes
NK063(gu)001:10108: su gcig pa'i rtags su h+aum dkar po gcig tu
NK063(gu)001:10109: gyur te mdzub mo'i rtse la blangs te /
NK063(gu)001:10110: dkyil 'khor gyi nub phyogs na rdo rje rgyal po yab yum dgongs pa la bzhugs par phul bas /
NK063(gu)001:10111: rdo rje rgyal pos shangs phug nas rdubs te yab
NK063(gu)001:10112: yum sbyor bas klad pa'i rgyas su phyug sgal tshigs
NK063(gu)001:10113: kyi rta brgyud rdo rje'i lam nas phyug ste yum
NK063(gu)001:10114: gyi mkha' dbyings su thim nas cho ga gsum gyis
NK063(gu)001:10115: rigs nges pa'i sras sku phyag rgyar bskyed pa ni
NK063(gu)001:10116: / byang sems gsung yig 'bru h+aum du gnas pa
NK063(gu)001:10117: las badz+ra zhes pas thugs phyag mtshan rdo rje'i 'od
NK063(gu)001:10119: de las badz+ra sa t+wa zhes pas rdo rje sems
NK063(gu)001:10120: dpa'i skur yongs su rdzogs pa mtshon gang bar gyur
NK063(gu)001:10121: te / rtog pa dag pa'i rtags su 'od zer
NK063(gu)001:10122: rnam pa lngar 'phro bas gzi brjid dang ldan pa'o
NK063(gu)001:10123: te / // de'i gtsug tu ngan song las rnam
NK063(gu)001:10124: par rgyal ba'i rtags su bud+d+ha bee ro tsa na
NK063(gu)001:10125: +amo zhes pas rnam snang gis dbu brgyan par bsgom
NK063(gu)001:10126: te / // / de nas a yam zhes pas
NK063(gu)001:10127: de'i 'og tu zla dkyil de'i 'og tu zla dkyil
NK063(gu)001:10128: de'i 'og tu yam las rlung gis zla dkyil skur
NK063(gu)001:10129: bcas bteg ste e yam dza s+pha ra nas 'og
NK063(gu)001:10130: min na rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum sbyor ba'i
NK063(gu)001:10132: byang sems kyis dbang bskur nas rigs nges pa'i sras su bskyed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10133: de yang sgeg pa'i gzhung las /
NK063(gu)001:10134: ting 'dzin sngags dang phyag rgya rnams //
NK063(gu)001:10135: shin tu goms pas dbang bskur te //
NK063(gu)001:10136: byang chub zhing du dgod par bya //
NK063(gu)001:10137: ting 'dzin sngags rgyas bag chags sbyang //
NK063(gu)001:10139: ye shes tshogs kyang rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:10140: phung po byin brlab mchod par bsngo //
NK063(gu)001:10143: de'i yon tan nam dgos pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:10144: 'bru bsgyur te bsgral bya zhing bcu po rnams las
NK063(gu)001:10145: ngan pa spyad pa'i 'bras bu ngan song du 'gro
NK063(gu)001:10146: ba las thar te gnas spar bas rigs nges pa'i
NK063(gu)001:10147: sras rgyal ba'i go 'phang thob pa'i thabs yin pas
NK063(gu)001:10150: de ltar bsgral ba'i dgos ched kyang /
NK063(gu)001:10151: byang chub spyod 'phel sems can bde //
NK063(gu)001:10152: lha mnyes bdag nyid dam skong zhing //
NK063(gu)001:10153: las ngan bar chad sdug yun thung //
NK063(gu)001:10154: rang gis bsags med ngan song las //
NK063(gu)001:10155: bde lam 'di las gzhan med do //
NK063(gu)001:10157: gsum pa de gnyis la spyad par bsgrub pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:10159: de la rtsod pa'i skyon spangs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10160: dang po ni tshig bsgyur te 'og nas sbyor sgrol zhes pas de chos can /
NK063(gu)001:10161: spyad par bya ba'i dam tshig tan gan la sogs
NK063(gu)001:10162: kun la spyad par byas kyang gos par mi 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:10163: te / rtogs shing goms pa'i blo la ltos te
NK063(gu)001:10164: don la rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med pa'i
NK063(gu)001:10165: te / phyir ro // de ma grub bo zhe na rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med de /
NK063(gu)001:10166: yang 'og nas chos thams cad ye nas skye ba
NK063(gu)001:10167: med pa de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings su gcig cing
NK063(gu)001:10168: / 'dir de mngon du gyur pas spyad pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:10169: dper na sgyu mar snang ba'i skyes bus mig yor
NK063(gu)001:10170: du snang ba'i gang zag la sbyar zhing bsgral ba'i
NK063(gu)001:10171: tshul bzhin no zhes rtags kyis bsgrub bo //
NK063(gu)001:10173: sbyor sgrol gnyis po chos can /
NK063(gu)001:10174: spyad bya ma yin pa la spyod par thal /
NK063(gu)001:10175: 'khor bar 'ching zhing ngan 'gror ltung byed yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:10176: dper na mtshams med lnga la spyod pa bzhin zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:10177: ci sbyor sgrol de thams cad kyis thams cad kyi tshe spyad bya ma yin par thal /
NK063(gu)001:10178: 'khor ba'i ltung byed yin pa'i phyir zhes sam /
NK063(gu)001:10179: 'ga' zhig gis 'ga' zhig gi tshe spyad bya ma yin par thal /
NK063(gu)001:10181: dang po ltar na mdo sde nas 'byung ba ltar
NK063(gu)001:10182: byang chub sems dpa' gzhan don gyi tshe na rngon
NK063(gu)001:10183: pa dang smad 'tshong du sprul nas don byed pa'ang
NK063(gu)001:10184: spyad bya ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:10185: gsod sbyor de thams cad kyis spyad bya ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:10186: de ltar yang sgeg pa'i gzhung las /
NK063(gu)001:10188: byang chub sems dpa' 'dul dbang gis //
NK063(gu)001:10189: rngon dang smad 'tshong ston pa'ang ltung //
NK063(gu)001:10191: gal te byang chub sems dpas gzhan don du de
NK063(gu)001:10192: dag spyad kyang ltung bar mi 'gyur na ci 'gal
NK063(gu)001:10193: zhe na / thams cad kyis thams cad kyi spyad bya ma yin pa nyams so //
NK063(gu)001:10194: gnyis pa ltar na khyab pa med de /
NK063(gu)001:10195: blo dman zhing thabs kyis ma zin pa'i yul min
NK063(gu)001:10196: yang de las ldog ste lta ba rtogs shing thabs
NK063(gu)001:10197: kyis zin pas tshogs sgrub kyi dus su de dag
NK063(gu)001:10198: la spyad kyang 'ching bar mi 'gyur na ci 'gal
NK063(gu)001:10199: te / ji skad du de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:10200: kheng grags spyod pas de min phyir //
NK063(gu)001:10201: thabs chen lam la gnas pa yi //
NK063(gu)001:10202: skyes bu kun gyis spyad par gsungs //
NK063(gu)001:10204: bsgrub bya dngos grub la gnyis su gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:10205: yang de ltar bsgrub pa la gang zag mos pa
NK063(gu)001:10206: tha dad pa'i phyir khro bo'i sgo nas tshogs sgrub
NK063(gu)001:10207: pa ni khro bo zhes badz+ra he ru ka dang
NK063(gu)001:10208: khro mo zhes badz+ra kro ti'o //
NK063(gu)001:10209: tshogs chen ni rigs bzhi yab yum dang /
NK063(gu)001:10210: pho nya ni gnas kyi ma mo la /
NK063(gu)001:10211: phyag brnyan ni yul gyi phra men te /
NK063(gu)001:10212: bka' nyan ni sgo ma'i tshogs so //
NK063(gu)001:10213: ci bgyid ni dbang phyug ma'o //
NK063(gu)001:10214: mngon rtogs nas tshom bu gcig pa la de ltar lnga bcu rtsa brgyad bsgom par bshad cing /
NK063(gu)001:10216: dang por lnga bcu brgyad goms nas //
NK063(gu)001:10218: spar khab nas gong ma rnams mthun la /
NK063(gu)001:10219: la sogs zhes pa ni rigs 'dra gzhan khro bo
NK063(gu)001:10220: khro mo nyi shu bsdus pas bdun cu rtsa brgyad
NK063(gu)001:10222: bdun cu rtsa brgyad de bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:10224: tshogs rnams zhes pa tshom bu gsum la pho brang
NK063(gu)001:10225: gi shar nub tu de pa dang pad+ma'i rigs la
NK063(gu)001:10226: nyi shu ste dgu bcu rtsa brgyad do //
NK063(gu)001:10227: lnga pa la de'i steng du lho byang gnyis su
NK063(gu)001:10228: rin po che dang las kyi rigs la nyi shu
NK063(gu)001:10229: ste brgya dang bco brgyad do //
NK063(gu)001:10230: kyis zhes pa byed pa po'i sgra ste gong gi
NK063(gu)001:10231: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor de dag gis 'bru bsgyur te
NK063(gu)001:10232: bsgrub bya las bzhi'i dngos grub rnams ma lus shing
NK063(gu)001:10234: don gnyis pa cig car ba ni gzhung bsgyur te
NK063(gu)001:10235: bcu gnyis pa'i gsham nas cho ga zhes pa lam
NK063(gu)001:10236: gyi rim pa ste stong snying gnyis phyag rgya gcig
NK063(gu)001:10237: pa la phra rags gnyis spros pa dang lnga'o //
NK063(gu)001:10238: 'di la snga rabs pa rnams 'di ltar bzhed do //
NK063(gu)001:10239: lhag ces pa mthar chags pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:10241: rim gyis pas stong snying gnyis mthar ma phyin par
NK063(gu)001:10242: phyag rgya gcig pa bsgoms pas thun mong gi skyon
NK063(gu)001:10243: bying pa rgod pa brjed pa gsum dang /
NK063(gu)001:10244: khyad par gyi skyon ni lam rim nas /
NK063(gu)001:10245: gang tshad dmigs pa tshad dang tshul //
NK063(gu)001:10246: grangs dang cha lugs mdog dbyibs dang /
NK063(gu)001:10247: kha dog 'ba' zhig rim par nub //
NK063(gu)001:10248: ces pa rnams byung nas stong snying la bskyar nas bsgom pa lta bu yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:10249: ma tshang ba ni phyag rgya gcig pa'i blo che
NK063(gu)001:10250: shos nas thod rgal du song ba la spros pa
NK063(gu)001:10251: chad kyang don lhag pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:10252: dper na byang chub sems dpa'i lam du bsam gtan bzhi dang /
NK063(gu)001:10253: snyoms 'jug bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin rtsal sbyong byed pa dang 'dra gsungs nas mdzod kyi gzhung 'dren no //
NK063(gu)001:10254: yang bla ma ni 'grel chen nas rim gyis pa
NK063(gu)001:10255: rgan po tshig gtso bor mi byed ces gsungs pa
NK063(gu)001:10256: ltar cho ga'i go ba brjod tshig la brjod de
NK063(gu)001:10257: / de blo che ba la de'i lhag chad kyis
NK063(gu)001:10258: mi gnod par 'dod pa bde gsung pa ni ma
NK063(gu)001:10260: ji skad du dgu pa las /
NK063(gu)001:10261: cho ga lnga ni rdzogs byas shing //
NK063(gu)001:10264: cho ga rdzogs par shes pa yis //
NK063(gu)001:10266: cho ga'i go ba lam gyi rim pa yin par gsungs ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:10267: 'dir ni rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid cig car ba 'dod de /
NK063(gu)001:10268: de yang cho ga ces pa gong ma ltar la /
NK063(gu)001:10269: lhag ces pa ni ma dgos pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:10270: ji skad du spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:10271: lhag pa ni don lhag pa ste thod rgal ba'i
NK063(gu)001:10272: ting nge 'dzin lta bu thams cad la mi dmigs
NK063(gu)001:10275: des na gong gi rim gyis pa la dgos pa'i
NK063(gu)001:10276: lam gyi rim pa dang bsnyen sgrub kyi dbye ba
NK063(gu)001:10278: 'dir cig car ba la skyon ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:10280: ma tshang ba ni chad pa ste sems med pa'i
NK063(gu)001:10281: ting nge 'dzin lta bu rang gi ngo bo nyid
NK063(gu)001:10282: kyang ma dmigs na gzhan lta ci smos /
NK063(gu)001:10284: de'i don gtan tshigs kyis bsgrub ste 'bru bsgyur la /
NK063(gu)001:10285: lam cig car ba chos can /
NK063(gu)001:10286: lam gyi lhag chad kyi nyes pa med de /
NK063(gu)001:10287: chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa'i ngang
NK063(gu)001:10288: la gnas pas lam gyi rim pa la grogs mtshan
NK063(gu)001:10289: mar 'dzin pa thams cad rnam par dag pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:10290: / dper na nam mkha' la rdul gyis mi gos pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:10292: lhun gyis rtogs nas lhun gyis bsgom //
NK063(gu)001:10293: rim bral de nyid gsal gyur 'brel //
NK063(gu)001:10296: ma bcos ji bzhin ngang bzhag dang //
NK063(gu)001:10300: thig le chen po nyag gcig la //
NK063(gu)001:10301: sgom pa rnam gsum dus gcig rdzogs //
NK063(gu)001:10302: zhes pa dag gis shes pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:10303: gsum pa 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid la'ang rim cig car gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:10304: dang po la'ang yo byad lnga la spyad pa'i 'bras
NK063(gu)001:10305: bu ni sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes pa la bzhi
NK063(gu)001:10306: las 'di nang gi ste gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:10307: tshe dbang gi cha lugs ni sngon tshogs sgrub kyi
NK063(gu)001:10308: lus gang yin pa'i mi dang lha dang de'i bye
NK063(gu)001:10309: brag tshangs pa la sogs pa'i skye ba rnam par
NK063(gu)001:10311: de'i lus de rdo rje'i lus su khyer bas tshe
NK063(gu)001:10312: gcig gi 'bras bu yin pa'i phyir snyam du sems
NK063(gu)001:10313: so // 'o na tshe dbang de chos can //
NK063(gu)001:10314: lha mi dang khyad par med par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:10315: skye ba rnam dag 'dzin par mtshungs pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:10316: skye ba rnam dag 'dzin pa tsam du 'dra mod kyang /
NK063(gu)001:10317: dgongs pa dang yon tan gyi khyad par du byas
NK063(gu)001:10318: pa yin na ci 'gal te khyab pa med do
NK063(gu)001:10319: // des khyad par du byas par ma grub ce na /
NK063(gu)001:10320: dgongs pas khyad par du byas pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:10321: lus la rang dbang thob pas tshe la dbang ba yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:10322: yon tan ni zag med kyi sa la gnas par gyur ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:10323: 'o na tshe dbang de chos can /
NK063(gu)001:10324: byang chub sems dpa' sa dang po pa dang khyad par med par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:10325: sa khyad par can la gnas par mtshungs pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:10327: tshe dbang gis rgyu'i sa dang po la bgrod mi dgos shing /
NK063(gu)001:10328: rgyu'i theg pa'i sa dang po pas tshe dbang la da gzod bgrod dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:10329: de gnyis ma grub bo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:10330: tshe dbang gis rgyu'i sa dang po la bgrod mi dgos te /
NK063(gu)001:10331: rim gyis pa'i dbang du sngar bgrod zin cing /
NK063(gu)001:10332: cig car ba'i dbang du de la gtan nas ltos mi dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:10333: rgyu'i sa dang po pas tshe dbang la gzod bgrod dgos pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:10334: ji skad du tha ma las /
NK063(gu)001:10335: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK063(gu)001:10336: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK063(gu)001:10338: de bzhin du sgom lam dang mthar lam kyang gong ma dang mtshungs so //
NK063(gu)001:10339: mthar thug pa'i 'bras bu la sbyor tshul ni /
NK063(gu)001:10340: de ltar lam gyi dus na rgyu'i theg pa'i pha
NK063(gu)001:10341: rol tu phyin pa bcu po kun 'di'i lta ba
NK063(gu)001:10342: la dus gcig tu rdzogs pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:10344: gnyis med mthar phyin pa ni gang la yang mi 'dzin pas sbyin pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:10345: gang la yang ma chags pas tshul khrims dang /
NK063(gu)001:10346: gnyis med kyi lta ba ni zab mo'i don yin la de la mi skrag pas bzod pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:10347: de'i ngang las mi g.yo bas gsam gtan dang /
NK063(gu)001:10348: de las dus thams cad mi yengs pas brtson 'grus dang /
NK063(gu)001:10349: yang dag pa'i don phyin ci ma log pa gsal bas shes rab dang /
NK063(gu)001:10350: de mngon du gyur pas smon lam dang /
NK063(gu)001:10351: 'bras bu gzhan nas mi 'tshol bas thabs dang /
NK063(gu)001:10352: des lta ngan zil gyis gnon pas stobs dang /
NK063(gu)001:10353: ye nas yin pa'i don mngon du gsal bas ye shes kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10354: de'i phyir tshig bsgyur te 'og nas rgyu'i theg pa'i
NK063(gu)001:10355: sa'i khyad par bcu yang 'dir mnyam pa nyid du
NK063(gu)001:10356: rtogs pa'i ye shes gcig la lhun gyis grub pa
NK063(gu)001:10357: yin te / 'di ltar mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings mthong bas dang po rab tu dga' ba /
NK063(gu)001:10358: des mthar lta dag pas gnyis pa dri ma med pa /
NK063(gu)001:10359: sems nyid rang gsal bas 'gro don mi 'gog par byed pas gsum pa 'od byed pa /
NK063(gu)001:10360: rang rig nyid thams cad du snang bas bzhi pa 'od 'phro ba /
NK063(gu)001:10361: don gnyis dus gcig tu byed pas lnga pa sbyang dka' ba /
NK063(gu)001:10362: mtshan nyid yul dang bral bar gsal bas drug pa mngon du gyur ba /
NK063(gu)001:10363: mtha'i lta ba spong bas bdun pa ring du song ba /
NK063(gu)001:10364: g.yeng ba'i yul med pas brgyad pa mi g.yo ba /
NK063(gu)001:10365: yon tan lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes mnga' bas dgu pa legs pa'i blo gros /
NK063(gu)001:10366: yon tan de dag gi 'byung gnas su 'gyur pas bcu pa chos kyi sprin no //
NK063(gu)001:10367: dang zhes pa 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi sa gsum yang grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:10368: yang gong nas sa bcu'i bsgrub bya'i mchog kun tu
NK063(gu)001:10369: 'od yin la de 'dir gnyis med rtogs pa'i ngang
NK063(gu)001:10370: du rdzogs / rdzogs pa'i lta ba des nyon mongs
NK063(gu)001:10371: la sogs dngos po gnyis la ma 'gags par spyad
NK063(gu)001:10372: kyang shes rab kyis de dag tu mi dmigs par
NK063(gu)001:10373: rtogs pas chos sku mngon du byas pa ni dper
NK063(gu)001:10374: na pad+ma 'dam nas skyes kyang des mi gos pa
NK063(gu)001:10375: ltar kun tu 'od kyi mchog pad+ma can gyi sa'o
NK063(gu)001:10376: du rdzogs / // gi zhes pa pad+ma can gyi yang mchog tu gyur pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:10378: de ltar chos sku mngon du gyur nas gzugs sku
NK063(gu)001:10379: gnyis kyis don mdzad pa'i thabs dang theg pa bsam
NK063(gu)001:10380: gyis mi khyab pa la sogs sku gsung thugs mi
NK063(gu)001:10381: zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo la mnga' brnyes pa
NK063(gu)001:10382: ni 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10383: de ltar yang dag pa'i don mngon du byas pa'i
NK063(gu)001:10384: shes rab kyis sku lnga mthar phyin pa'i tshe yang
