NK063(gu)001:10385: 'og nas byang chub sems dpa'i lam du rgyu pha
NK063(gu)001:10386: rol tu phyin pa bcu dang 'bras bu sa bcu'i
NK063(gu)001:10387: khyad par ram / yang na rgyu'i theg pa'i sa
NK063(gu)001:10388: dang 'bras bu rdo rje theg pa'i sa'i khyad par
NK063(gu)001:10389: khyad par ram / ram / yang na rgyu sa bcu dang /
NK063(gu)001:10390: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi sa gsum gyi khyad par
NK063(gu)001:10391: de dag 'dir lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes gcig
NK063(gu)001:10392: la yongs su rdzogs pa yin no zhes pa'i don
NK063(gu)001:10393: no // gnyis pa cig car ba ni bsgrub bya'i tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor kun dang /
NK063(gu)001:10394: lam du gyur pa'i 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi char
NK063(gu)001:10395: rig pa gcig la gsal ba'i blos rab tu sbyor
NK063(gu)001:10396: bas na rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dkyil
NK063(gu)001:10397: 'khor gyi che ba'i yon tan thams cad 'grub par
NK063(gu)001:10398: 'gyur ba'o // le'u'i mtshan gyi skabs su tshogs kyi zhes pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:10399: zhub can mang po 'tshogs pa la dmag tshogs zer ba ltar /
NK063(gu)001:10400: 'dir yang rnal 'byor pa du ma 'tshogs nas dang /
NK063(gu)001:10401: yo byad du ma la brten nas dang /
NK063(gu)001:10402: bsgrub bya lha du ma bskyed nas bsgrub pa'i phyir tshogs zhes bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:10403: dang po ni rdo rje las /
NK063(gu)001:10404: skye bo mdza' ba kun 'tshogs pa //
NK063(gu)001:10406: zhes pas skal ldan mi'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:10408: 'byor ba longs spyod tshang ba ni //
NK063(gu)001:10409: bde ba'i longs spyod tshogs su bshad //
NK063(gu)001:10410: ces pas 'byor ldan yo byad kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:10412: lha dang dam can kun 'dus pa //
NK063(gu)001:10413: 'dus pa chen po'i tshogs su gsungs //
NK063(gu)001:10414: zhes pas dgyes ldan lha'i 'tshogs te /
NK063(gu)001:10415: de dag la ma 'gags par spyad pas bsod nams dang /
NK063(gu)001:10416: de dag tu ma dmigs par shes pas spyad kyang
NK063(gu)001:10417: ma gos pa ni ye shes su gyur pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:10418: te / thams cad spyod la mi 'dzin pas //
NK063(gu)001:10419: tshogs gnyis rgyun du rdzogs byed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10421: dkyil 'khor gyi zhes pa ni bsgrub bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:10423: rdo rje sems dpa' dkyil nyid de //
NK063(gu)001:10424: rigs bzhi lha dang lha mo 'khor //
NK063(gu)001:10426: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10428: // le'u bcu gsum pa mtshon par byed pa'i sgo nas
NK063(gu)001:10429: gol sgrib gdar sha chod par bya ba'i phyir lta
NK063(gu)001:10430: ba brgal brtag gis bshad pa zhes bya ba yin
NK063(gu)001:10432: 'dod pa phyogs lhung gi lta ba rnams sun dbyung ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:10433: 'di'i dbyer med kyi lta ba'i don bsgrub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10435: rang rang gi lta ba rnams kyi thun mong gi tshul brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:10437: dang po ni rang rang gi rtogs bya'i yul la
NK063(gu)001:10438: rtogs byed kyi blo ma 'khrul par 'dod pa ste
NK063(gu)001:10440: grub pa'i mthar phyin 'khrul pa med //
NK063(gu)001:10442: gnyis pa la yang de lta bu'i grub mthas blo ma bsgyur ba dang bsgyur ba gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:10443: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni rang gi ston pa
NK063(gu)001:10444: dang bstan pa'i rjes su blo ma 'brangs pa dang
NK063(gu)001:10446: de las dang po ni ma rtogs pa dang zhes
NK063(gu)001:10447: pa 'jig rten phal pa ste ma rig pa dang
NK063(gu)001:10448: mtshungs par ldan pa'i lta ba phyogs gcig pa zhig
NK063(gu)001:10449: yin no // ma rig pa la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:10450: yang dag pa'i don la rmongs pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:10451: las rgyu 'bras la rmongs pa'i ma rig pa'am /
NK063(gu)001:10452: yang na lhan cig skyes pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:10453: kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10454: de las 'di ni rgyu 'bras la rmongs pa dang mtshungs par ldan pa'i lta ba tsam mo //
NK063(gu)001:10455: de la yang 'jig rten phyal pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:10457: dang po la yang ngo bo nges tshig dbye ba
NK063(gu)001:10458: gsum las ngo bo ni tshe snga phyi dang las
NK063(gu)001:10460: nges tshig ni lta ba 'di ltar yin min gyi dmigs ma rnyed pa'i phyir de skad ces bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:10464: de ltar yang rgyas pa las /
NK063(gu)001:10465: nges med 'di zhes bstan du med //
NK063(gu)001:10469: rgyang 'phen pa la yang gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:10470: ngo bo ni phyal ba dang 'dra ba'i steng du
NK063(gu)001:10471: tshe gcig gi phan bde bag tsam bsgrub pa'i blo
NK063(gu)001:10472: can no // nges tshig ni phyi ma phan chad
NK063(gu)001:10473: kyi bde ba rgyang du bor nas 'di'i phan bde
NK063(gu)001:10474: kho na la dmigs pa ste 'jig rten brang breng
NK063(gu)001:10475: gi ngor sad pa zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:10482: dang po ni theg pa chen po'i grub mtha' 'dzin pas 'dod bya ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:10483: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying pos ma khyab cing gzhi bzang ngan can du 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:10485: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa
NK063(gu)001:10486: las kyang 'byung ste yun ring du brgyangs pa tsam
NK063(gu)001:10487: la bya'o zhes gang gsungs pa de yin te /
NK063(gu)001:10488: thun mong gi theg pa ltar na tshig kyang mi
NK063(gu)001:10489: zin cing don yang mi go bas dbang po rtul
NK063(gu)001:10490: por gyur pa'o // de yang ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:10491: chos kyi dbyings kyis kun la khyab gyur kyang //
NK063(gu)001:10492: rang rig rtogs pa'i skal dang mi ldan na //
NK063(gu)001:10493: ji ltar dmus long mdun du mdog bstan ltar //
NK063(gu)001:10494: de ni skal med rigs chad sa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:10496: 'du shes can la yang bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:10501: de yang mdo chen po las /
NK063(gu)001:10502: 'du shes can bzhi chags pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:10503: gang la g.yeng dang ya nga can //
NK063(gu)001:10504: mos pa can bzhi grags pa bzhi //
NK063(gu)001:10505: sa bon 'dzin pa'i zhing du snang //
NK063(gu)001:10507: gnyis pa grub mthas blo bsgyur ba la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:10509: nang pa'i grub mtha' 'dzin pa gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:10510: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni kha cig lta ba bdag yod med dang /
NK063(gu)001:10511: spyod pa sems can la 'tshe ba mi spong zhing spong ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:10512: skyabs yul dkon cog gsum la mi byed cing byed
NK063(gu)001:10513: pa dang gsum gyis khyad par du byas zhes zer
NK063(gu)001:10514: ba ni ma nges pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:10515: rim pa ltar lta ba mu stegs rgyang 'phen pa yang bdag mi 'dod pa'i nang par 'gyur la /
NK063(gu)001:10516: rang sde nyan rang yang chos bdag 'dod pas phyi rol par 'gyur ro //
NK063(gu)001:10517: spyod pa gcer bu yang sems can la 'tshe ba spong bas nang par 'gyur zhing /
NK063(gu)001:10518: skyabs yul 'jig rten phyal ba la sogs pa yang
NK063(gu)001:10519: dkon cog gsum la mi 'dzin pas phyi rol par
NK063(gu)001:10521: yang kha cig ni lta ba rtag chad kyi mthar zhen cing /
NK063(gu)001:10522: spyod pa brtul zhugs phyin ci log tu spyod la /
NK063(gu)001:10523: skyabs yul dbang phyug la sogs pa la 'dzin pas
NK063(gu)001:10524: 'bras bu 'jig rten par smin pa ni phyi rol
NK063(gu)001:10525: pa yin la / lta ba rtag chad kyi mtha' las grol zhing /
NK063(gu)001:10526: spyod pa brtul zhugs dag par spyod la /
NK063(gu)001:10527: skyabs yul dkon cog gsum la 'dzin pas 'bras bu
NK063(gu)001:10528: 'das par smin pa ni nang pa yin zer ba
NK063(gu)001:10529: yang cung zad gnod pa dang bcas pa yin no
NK063(gu)001:10531: 'di grub mtha' 'dzin lugs kyi khyad par yin te /
NK063(gu)001:10532: khyab 'jug gam dbang phyug la sogs pa la ston
NK063(gu)001:10533: par 'dzin cing de'i bstan pa'i rjes su blo 'brangs
NK063(gu)001:10534: te de'i grub mtha' 'dzin pa ni phyi rol pa
NK063(gu)001:10535: yin la / yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK063(gu)001:10536: la ston par 'dzin cing des gsungs pa'i bstan pa'i
NK063(gu)001:10537: rjes su blo 'brangs nas de'i grub mtha' 'dzin pa
NK063(gu)001:10539: de ltar gnyis las dang po log par rtog zhes pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:10541: log par rtog 'di ya mtshan can //
NK063(gu)001:10542: brgya phrag gsum dang drug cu gnyis //
NK063(gu)001:10544: lta log sum brgya drug cu rtsa gnyis ni /
NK063(gu)001:10545: gang zag gi bdag nyer len gyi phung po lnga
NK063(gu)001:10546: po re re la'ang ngo bo'i sgo nas gzugs bdag
NK063(gu)001:10547: yin la / rgyan gyi sgo nas gzugs bdag dang ldan /
NK063(gu)001:10548: byed pa'i sgo nas gzugs bdag gi yin /
NK063(gu)001:10549: brten pa'i sgo nas gzugs la gnas zhes pa la sogs bzhi bzhi ste nyi shu'o //
NK063(gu)001:10550: de dag sngon gyi mtha' dang /
NK063(gu)001:10552: da ltar du rtog pa ste de ltar dus gsum
NK063(gu)001:10553: log pa'i ri bo nyi shu phrag gsum po de
NK063(gu)001:10554: ston pa mi 'pham skra'i lwa ba can la sogs
NK063(gu)001:10555: pa drug gis khas blangs pas sum brgya drug cu
NK063(gu)001:10556: dang rtsa ba rtag chad gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:10557: gnyis pa nang pa la'ang theg pa che chung gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:10558: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni /
NK063(gu)001:10559: chos lnga dag dang zhes pa /
NK063(gu)001:10560: blos btags pa sna tshogs su snang ba'i mtshan ma dang /
NK063(gu)001:10561: de dag la btags pa'i ming dang /
NK063(gu)001:10562: de dag la rtogs pa'i rnam rtog dang /
NK063(gu)001:10563: de dag gis stongs pa'i de bzhin nyid dang /
NK063(gu)001:10564: de rtogs pa'i ye shes so //
NK063(gu)001:10566: kun brtags gzhan dbang yongs grub gsum ste 'di sems tsam pa'i skabs su 'chad do //
NK063(gu)001:10567: rnam par shes pa brgyad nyid dang zhes pa /
NK063(gu)001:10572: bdag med gnyis rtogs zhes pa /
NK063(gu)001:10573: phyi rol pas btags pa'i gang zag gi bdag dang /
NK063(gu)001:10574: nyan rang gis btags pa'i chos bdag go //
NK063(gu)001:10575: de ltar chos de rnams khas len pa'i nang du ni /
NK063(gu)001:10576: theg pa chen po'i mtha' dag 'dus zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:10577: yang slob dpon a ro'i gzhung ltar /
NK063(gu)001:10578: theg pa'i rang bzhin shes rab snying rje kho na ste //
NK063(gu)001:10579: 'di dag che chung dbang gis theg pa'i khyad par bstan //
NK063(gu)001:10581: gang shes rab chung ste bdag med phyogs re las ma rtogs shing /
NK063(gu)001:10582: snying rje chung ste sems can gyi don gtso bor mi spyod pa ni theg chung yin la /
NK063(gu)001:10583: gang shes rab che ste bdag med gnyis rdzogs par rtogs shing /
NK063(gu)001:10584: snying rje che ste gzhan don gtso bor spyod pa ni theg chen no //
NK063(gu)001:10585: de las theg chung ni phyogs rtogs zhes pa shes
NK063(gu)001:10586: bya'i bye brag las ma rtogs shing mtshan mar 'dzin
NK063(gu)001:10588: dang po nyan thos la'ang gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:10589: spyi don du snang ba thams cad shes pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:10590: de yang shes pa nyid don du snang ba ma yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:10591: lkog na mo zhes bya ba phra mo don dam
NK063(gu)001:10592: gyi dmigs rkyen las skyes pa ni don gyi rnam
NK063(gu)001:10593: pa gtod byed kyi rgyur 'dod cing /
NK063(gu)001:10594: don gyi rnam pa can gyi shes pa 'bras bur
NK063(gu)001:10595: 'dod pa ni rnam bcas mdo sde pa yin la
NK063(gu)001:10596: / phyi don du snang ba thams cad gsum du nges pa las don spyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:10597: dngos med gsal snang gnyis yul dngos por med cing /
NK063(gu)001:10598: don rang mtshan ni yul dngos por bden par 'dod do //
NK063(gu)001:10599: yang de dag 'dzin pa'i shes pa yang gsum du nges pa las /
NK063(gu)001:10601: rtog med 'khrul pa gnyis blo 'khrul pa yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:10602: 'dzin pa mngon sum ni blo ma 'khrul par 'dod do //
NK063(gu)001:10603: des na yul can blo ma 'khrul pa des yul
NK063(gu)001:10604: dngos po 'dzin pa yang khab dang khab len ltar
NK063(gu)001:10605: 'brel med dus mnyam thug 'phrad du 'dzin par 'dod
NK063(gu)001:10606: pa ni rnam med bye brag pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:10608: gang zag gi bdag med rtogs la /
NK063(gu)001:10609: chos bdag bye brag pas 'dod pa'i gzung yul rdul
NK063(gu)001:10610: phran cha med don dam gyi dngos po yang rang
NK063(gu)001:10611: bzhin med de / phyogs kyi cha dang bcas pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:10612: gal te de ma grub na rags pa mi snang
NK063(gu)001:10613: bar 'gyur ba las dmigs pa'i phyir zhes rdul phran
NK063(gu)001:10615: 'dzin shes skad cig bden dngos su 'dod pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:10616: gzung don rtog pa spong phyir dang //
NK063(gu)001:10617: 'dzin pa'ang mi spong phyir dang ni //
NK063(gu)001:10618: rten gyi bse ru lta bu'i lam //
NK063(gu)001:10620: gnyis pa theg pa chen po la'ang rgyu mtshan nyid kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:10622: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni le'u gsum par bstan zin to //
NK063(gu)001:10623: de las mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ni yang dag nyid ma rtogs zhes pa /
NK063(gu)001:10624: yang dag pa'i don phyogs 'ga' tsam las ma rtogs pa byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:10625: de la yang sems tsam dang /
NK063(gu)001:10627: dang po ni 'di ltar gang zag gi bdag tu
NK063(gu)001:10628: sgro btags pa lta bu'i mtshan nyid yongs su chad
NK063(gu)001:10629: pa'i dang / rig shes kyi blo la ltos te
NK063(gu)001:10630: shes pa las tha dad pa'i don du snang ba
NK063(gu)001:10631: gzugs la sogs pa lta bu rnam grangs pa'i kun
NK063(gu)001:10632: pa'i dang / brtags gnyis / gzhan rkyen rnam par
NK063(gu)001:10633: rtog pa las byung ba lta bu ma dag pa
NK063(gu)001:10634: pa'i dang / brtags gnyis / dang / sa bcu'i rjes thob lta bu dag pa'i gzhan dbang gnyis /
NK063(gu)001:10635: bdag gnyis kyis stongs pa'i 'gyur ba med pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:10636: mtshan nyid de rtogs byed kyi lam dang mya ngan
NK063(gu)001:10637: las 'das pa'i chos gnyis ni phyin ci ma log
NK063(gu)001:10638: pa'i yongs su grub pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:10639: de ltar kun brtags dang gzhan dbang gnyis kun rdzob la /
NK063(gu)001:10640: yongs grub ni don dam yin zhes smra'o //
NK063(gu)001:10641: de yang kun rdzob la gzung yul gsum la bden rdzun dang /
NK063(gu)001:10642: de 'dzin shes pa gsum la 'khrul ma 'khrul bye brag pa dang 'dra la /
NK063(gu)001:10643: gzugs la sogs yul gyi rnam pa rnams rang rig
NK063(gu)001:10644: tu bden par 'dod pa ni rnam bden pa yin
NK063(gu)001:10645: la / de rdzun par 'dod pa ni rnam rdzun pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10646: gnyis pa dbu ma pa ni chos thams cad bden pa gnyis su 'dus par smra ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:10648: sangs rgyas rnams kyis chos bstan pa //
NK063(gu)001:10649: bden pa gnyis la yang dag brten //
NK063(gu)001:10652: 'jig rten kun rdzob bden pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:10653: dam pa'i don gyi bden pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10655: de yang don dam la dbu ma pa gnyis mthun te /
NK063(gu)001:10657: ji ltar snod kyi dbye bas mkha' la dbye ba med de ltar //
NK063(gu)001:10658: dngos byas dbye ba 'ga' yang de nyid la yang de yi phyir //
NK063(gu)001:10659: shes bya thams cad mnyam pa nyid du yang dag gzigs gyur pa //
NK063(gu)001:10660: mkhyen bzang khyod kyis skad cig gcig gis shes bya thugs su chud //
NK063(gu)001:10661: ces pa ltar khyad par gyi dbye ba cung zad tsam yang med par 'dod do //
NK063(gu)001:10664: snang du 'dra yang don byed dag /
NK063(gu)001:10665: nus pa'i phyir dang mi nus phyir //
NK063(gu)001:10666: yang dag yang dag ma yin pa //
NK063(gu)001:10667: kun rdzob kyi ni dbye ba byas //
NK063(gu)001:10669: snang la don byed nus pa yang dag pa'i kun rdzob la /
NK063(gu)001:10670: de dang des stongs pa log pa'i kun rdzob tu 'dod pa rang rgyud pa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:10671: yang yul bden pa la dbang shes ma 'khrul pa
NK063(gu)001:10672: dung dkar 'dzin lta bu ni yang dag pa'i kun
NK063(gu)001:10673: rdzob la / yul rdzun zhing blo 'khrul pa dung
NK063(gu)001:10674: ser 'dzin lta bu ni log pa'i kun rdzob tu
NK063(gu)001:10676: de ltar gzhi kun rdzob la yul bden rdzun dang /
NK063(gu)001:10678: rang rgyud dngos po'i stobs kyis zhugs pa'i tshad ma yod med gsum gyis phye la /
NK063(gu)001:10679: lam slob lam rjes thob la 'khrul ma 'khrul gyi phye zhing /
NK063(gu)001:10680: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi sa na rang snang gi
NK063(gu)001:10681: ye shes yod med gnyis kyis rang thal gnyis su
NK063(gu)001:10683: gnyis pa 'bras bu rdo rje'i theg pa la yang phyi nang gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:10684: 'di gnyis kyi khyad par phyogs gcig gis phyed par dka' yang /
NK063(gu)001:10686: dang po rtogs bya lta ba rang mtshan rtogs ma rtogs kyi khyad par ni /
NK063(gu)001:10687: phyi pas bden pas tha dad du btags pas rang
NK063(gu)001:10688: mtshan dbyer med ma rtogs pa'i phyir rang mtshan khas
NK063(gu)001:10689: mi len te / si ti ka ra las /
NK063(gu)001:10690: don dam dang ni kun rdzob la /
NK063(gu)001:10691: bslab pa'i rim pas bslang bar bya //
NK063(gu)001:10693: cig shos kyis dbyer med mtha' bral du rtogs pa ni rang mtshan yin phyir khas len pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:10695: gcig dang du ma bral ba yi //
NK063(gu)001:10696: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK063(gu)001:10697: sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs te //
NK063(gu)001:10698: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK063(gu)001:10700: gnyis pa lam thabs dang shes rab la dngos su brten mi brten gyi khyad par ni /
NK063(gu)001:10702: mu stegs rtsod pa spang ba'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:10703: bde gshegs yum ni phyag rgyar sbas //
NK063(gu)001:10705: yum dngos su mi brten la /
NK063(gu)001:10706: cig shos ni drug pa las /
NK063(gu)001:10707: btsun mo'i tshogs dang ldan par gnas //
NK063(gu)001:10710: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK063(gu)001:10711: zhes pa la sogs zab cing rgya che bar gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:10712: gsum pa bsgrub pa'i rdzas lnga la spyod nus mi nus kyi khyad par ni /
NK063(gu)001:10713: phyi pas dag cing gtsang ba la gtso bor spyod de /
NK063(gu)001:10714: ji skad du si ti ka ra las /
NK063(gu)001:10715: me tog dkar po dri zhim pa //
NK063(gu)001:10718: cig shos bdud rtsi lnga la spyod de /
NK063(gu)001:10720: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen //
NK063(gu)001:10721: dag pa'i snod bcud mi dor ro //
NK063(gu)001:10722: zhes pa la sogs du ma gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:10723: bzhi pa thob bya zab mo'i dbang yod med kyi khyad par ni /
NK063(gu)001:10724: phyi pas zab mo'i dbang bskur thob mi nus te /
NK063(gu)001:10726: sarba byid kyis ji ltar dbang bskur ba //
NK063(gu)001:10727: bum pa la sogs ji snyed ma thob par //
NK063(gu)001:10728: rdzas bcu rnams kyis dbang bcu ci dgar bskur //
NK063(gu)001:10730: cig shos zab mo'i dbang gtsor 'dzin pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:10732: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya las //
NK063(gu)001:10733: bde ba'i 'du tshogs gsal ba'i rgyun //
NK063(gu)001:10734: zhes pa la sogs gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:10735: tha ma de dag gis thob pa'i 'bras bu dus myur bul gyi khyad par ni /
NK063(gu)001:10736: phyi pa mi tshe bdun la sogs pa dus la ltos te /
NK063(gu)001:10738: ye shes tshe stobs na tshod dang //
NK063(gu)001:10739: kun tu 'gro ba nyid rnams thob //
NK063(gu)001:10741: cig shos mi tshe dang lo dang bskal pa la sogs la mi ltos te /
NK063(gu)001:10743: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug dang //
NK063(gu)001:10744: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK063(gu)001:10745: dbang sgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK063(gu)001:10748: 'dul ba ces pa bya ba'i rgyud de /
NK063(gu)001:10750: don dam dag pa mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i byin
NK063(gu)001:10751: rlabs kun rdzob rigs gsum gyi lhar snang ba yang
NK063(gu)001:10752: ye shes dang dam tshig rje dang khol ltar blta
NK063(gu)001:10753: zhing / de ltar bden gnyis de nyid dang gzhan du brjod du med par 'dod de /
NK063(gu)001:10755: kun rdzob rigs gsum dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK063(gu)001:10756: rang bzhin du na brtag bya ste //
NK063(gu)001:10757: don dam dag pa'i chos nyid du //
NK063(gu)001:10759: u pa ya ni spyod pa kri ya ltar spyod la lta ba yo ga ltar lta ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:10760: don dam mthun zhing kun rdzob rigs bzhi'i dkyil 'khor
NK063(gu)001:10761: yang ye shes dang dam tshig dpon dang g.yog ltar
NK063(gu)001:10762: 'dod do // dgongs pa zhes pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud de /
NK063(gu)001:10763: spros bral rnam par snang mdzad chen po'i ye shes ni don dam la /
NK063(gu)001:10764: ye shes de'i byin rlabs las kun rdzob snang ba
NK063(gu)001:10765: thams cad rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor du shar ba yang
NK063(gu)001:10766: / rgyud gzhan tha dad cing ye shes dang dam tshig gnyis grogs ltar mnyam par 'dod do //
NK063(gu)001:10767: der gsang sngags phyi rgyud mtha' dag gi rgyud kyi
NK063(gu)001:10768: dgongs pa bsdus te bstan pa'i phyir de skad ces
NK063(gu)001:10769: bya'o // gnyis pa gsang sngags nang pa la yang gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:10770: ji skad du mdo chen po las /
NK063(gu)001:10771: dbang sgyur thabs kyi theg pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:10772: 'di yang yul gyis gsum nyid de //
NK063(gu)001:10773: bskyed dang rdzogs dang yongs su rdzogs //
NK063(gu)001:10774: zhes pas bskyed pa ma h+aa dang /
NK063(gu)001:10776: rdzogs pa chen po a ti'i theg pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10777: de gsum gyi lta ba'i khyad par ni slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i gzhung las /
NK063(gu)001:10778: cho 'phrul rtsal dang rang snang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:10780: ma h+aa'i lugs kyis chos thams cad sems nyid snang stong dbyer med pa'i rnam 'phrul te /
NK063(gu)001:10781: de sems can gyi rgyud la ngos bzung na yid kyi rnam shes so //
NK063(gu)001:10782: de 'khor ba'i byed po yin la /
NK063(gu)001:10783: de rtogs pa gnyis med kyi ye shes ni 'das pa'i byed po ste /
NK063(gu)001:10784: ji skad du 'di'i gnyis pa las /
NK063(gu)001:10785: de nas bcom ldan 'das byed pa po rdo rje
NK063(gu)001:10786: yid kun tu bzang po zhes pas de ni de
NK063(gu)001:10787: pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid chen po'o //
NK063(gu)001:10788: a nu ltar na chos thams cad sems nyid dbyings
NK063(gu)001:10789: dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i rtsal gyis 'khor
NK063(gu)001:10791: de sems can gyi rgyud la ngos bzung na kun gzhi rnam shes yin la /
NK063(gu)001:10792: de rtogs pa'i tshe sras bde ba chen po ste /
NK063(gu)001:10793: ji skad du mdo chen po las /
NK063(gu)001:10794: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba kun gzhi ste //
NK063(gu)001:10795: kun gzhi gnas gyur ye shes lngar snang ba //
NK063(gu)001:10796: ye shes lnga yang gcig tu 'dus rigs bya //
NK063(gu)001:10797: chos rnams rtsa ba kun gzhi'i don rtogs na //
NK063(gu)001:10798: ye nas sangs rgyas sa nyid ma btsal yang //
NK063(gu)001:10799: gdal khyab sa nyid ye nas thob par gsungs //
NK063(gu)001:10801: a ti ni chos thams cad sems nyid ye nas
NK063(gu)001:10802: skye 'gag dbyer med pa'i rang byung ye shes su
NK063(gu)001:10804: de sems can gyi rgyud la ngos bzung na tshogs brgyad yul dang bcas pa thams cad do //
NK063(gu)001:10805: de nyid rnam par grol bas sangs rgyas kyi dgongs
NK063(gu)001:10806: pa sems nyid la lhag chad med par ye nas
NK063(gu)001:10807: bzhugs pa ste / ji skad du mdo bcu las /
NK063(gu)001:10808: rang byung rgyu rkyen med par byung ba yin //
NK063(gu)001:10809: ye shes 'gag pa med par gsal ba yin //
NK063(gu)001:10811: de dag kyang dper na gnod sbyin la sogs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:10812: cho 'phrul ni 'od dang rmi lam gyi mtshan ma
NK063(gu)001:10813: lta bu la / rtsal ni des nad dang gnod pa 'byung ba lta bu yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:10814: rang snang ni kho rang gi ngo bo mthong ba lta bu'o gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:10815: gzhan yang sgra don gyi khyad par yang yin te /
NK063(gu)001:10817: cho ga yan lag gis lha bskyed pa'i phyir bskyed pa ma h+aa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:10818: de la mi brten par chu la nya ldang ltar rdzogs pa ni rdzogs pa a nu yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:10819: bskyed du med pa'i phyir de lta bu'i rtsol ba
NK063(gu)001:10820: las grol ba ni rdzogs pa chen po a ti'o
NK063(gu)001:10821: // de yang gsang ba dang zhes pa ni rnal 'byor chen po'i tshul ma h+aa ste /
NK063(gu)001:10822: phyi rgyud man chad thun mong gi sgor gyur pa'i yul ma yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:10823: thabs mkhas pa'i rnal 'byor chen po rnams kyis lta ba dang spyod par bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:10824: 'bru bsgyur te yang gsang ba'i zhes pa ni a
NK063(gu)001:10825: nu ste dbyings ye shes gnyis med kyi sras bde
NK063(gu)001:10826: ba chen po ni zab cing rtogs dka' bas gsang
NK063(gu)001:10827: ba bas kyang ches gsang bar bstan pa'i phyir ro
NK063(gu)001:10828: // yang gong nas rang bzhin zhes pa ni a
NK063(gu)001:10829: ti ste skye 'gag gnyis su med pa rang byung
NK063(gu)001:10830: gi ye shes la chos thams cad rdzogs pas lam
NK063(gu)001:10831: gyis bsgrub cing gnyen pos bcos su med de /
NK063(gu)001:10832: ye nas mya ngan las 'das pa ni shes bya'i gnas lugs yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:10833: yang 'og nas don rnams ni zhes pa gsang ba'i theg pa gsum gyi lta ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:10834: 'dod pa phyogs lhung gi lta ba rnams bkag pa bsgrub bya'i don zhes pa'i don no //
NK063(gu)001:10835: 'dir kha cig 'di ma h+aa'i theg pa yin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:10836: phyir gong ma gnyis kyi lta ba gtan la 'bebs
NK063(gu)001:10838: 'og mas gong ma'i don mi mthong ba'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:10839: lta phreng ltar rnal 'byor chen po'i tshul la yang
NK063(gu)001:10840: gsum du phye ba'i 'di ma h+aa'i a ti yin
NK063(gu)001:10841: pa'i phyir 'di ltar gtan la 'bebs par 'thad do
NK063(gu)001:10842: // bstan pa de dag gis mtshon byed ni yi ge sgra btags zhes pa /
NK063(gu)001:10843: yi ge a'i sgra las btags pa'i phyir sgra'i yi ge sum cu rtsa bzhi dang /
NK063(gu)001:10844: a'i sgra gdangs las snang ba dbyangs kyi yi ge bcu gnyis dang /
NK063(gu)001:10845: gnyis ka las byung ba ma ning gi yi ge bzhi'o //
NK063(gu)001:10846: ming tshogs las zhes pa de dag 'dus pa ming gi tshogs so //
NK063(gu)001:10847: brten pa'i tshig gis zhes pa ming gi tshogs la brten pa tshig gi tshogs so //
NK063(gu)001:10848: rab mtshon te zhes pa de dag las byung ba
NK063(gu)001:10849: bstan pa'i tshogs rgya mtsho lta bu mtshon byed kyi
NK063(gu)001:10850: theg pa ni lam gyi rgyud kho na yin no
NK063(gu)001:10851: // rgyud de yang brjod bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud kyi khong na gab pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:10852: rjod byed yi ge'i rgyud du sbas pa'i don rnams 'byin par byed pa po gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:10853: dang po ni ston pa'i bdag nyid dang 'chad pa'i
NK063(gu)001:10854: skyes bu'i thugs la gnas pa de mtshon byed kyi
NK063(gu)001:10855: rgyud du bka' stsal pas 'byin cing /
NK063(gu)001:10856: gnyis pa ni mtshon byed kyi rgyud de rdo rje
NK063(gu)001:10857: slob dpon gyi thugs la phyin ci ma log par
NK063(gu)001:10858: gnas pa de rgyud bshad thabs kyis 'byin pa yin
NK063(gu)001:10859: no // gnyis pa myong bar byed pa'i thabs la gdams ngag gis gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:10860: phyi shes rab grol ba'i lam gyi dbang du dang /
NK063(gu)001:10861: nang thabs lam steng sgo'i dbang du dang /
NK063(gu)001:10862: gsang ba zab mo 'og sgo'i dbang du bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10863: dang po la'ang lnga'i dang po ni /
NK063(gu)001:10864: dkyil 'khor zhes pa don dam chos nyid kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:10865: kun rdzob ye shes kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:10866: bden pa dbyer med kyi dkyil 'khor gsum mo //
NK063(gu)001:10867: ldan pa'i zhes pas gang la na sems can dang sangs rgyas thams cad la'o //
NK063(gu)001:10868: ji ltar na rten dang brten pa lta bu ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:10869: rang bzhin ngo bo nyid kyis ldan pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10870: dkyil 'khor gyi zhes pa ni de rtogs par byed pa'i thabs tshang ma bka' gzhung gis so //
NK063(gu)001:10871: dkyil 'khor la ni zhes pa des rtogs pa lta ba'i ngo bo bsgom bya'i gzhir gnas pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10872: dkyil 'khor bsgom zhes pa de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin mi rtog par ro //
NK063(gu)001:10874: don dam chos nyid kyi dkyil 'khor ma rtogs pas
NK063(gu)001:10875: 'khor ba la ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor las snying
NK063(gu)001:10876: rje sgyu ma ltar byung ba yin no zhes pa'i
NK063(gu)001:10877: don no // gsum pa bden pa dbyer med pas thugs kyi'o //
NK063(gu)001:10878: de yang cho ga phra mo gsum las phyag rgya
NK063(gu)001:10879: gcig pa gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor lhag pa'i lha dang
NK063(gu)001:10880: bcas pa gsal ba'i phyir dkyil 'khor gyi sgra yang
NK063(gu)001:10882: de bden pa tha dad las khyad par du gyur pas dkyil 'khor mchog ces so //
NK063(gu)001:10883: bzhi pa ni de ltar dbyer med kyi lta ba
NK063(gu)001:10884: zab mo'i don de tha dad du zhen pa'i blos
NK063(gu)001:10885: rtogs dka' bas gsang ba yin la /
NK063(gu)001:10886: de nyid mtha'i spros pa dang bral bas thig le yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:10887: phyag rgya gcig pas dkyil 'khor la goms na spros
NK063(gu)001:10888: pa 'byung ba'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir 'byung khungs kyi
NK063(gu)001:10889: dbyings yin no // tshig bsgyur te 'og nas chen
NK063(gu)001:10890: po ni 'byung ba rags pa ste de dag rigs
NK063(gu)001:10892: de bzhin te zhes pa yang gong nas 'byung ba
NK063(gu)001:10893: cha phra ba ni shes rab rigs kyi yum lnga'o
NK063(gu)001:10894: // yang 'og nas mig gi dbang po la sogs
NK063(gu)001:10895: pa dbang po dang gzugs la sogs pa yul bzhi
NK063(gu)001:10896: dang 'das pa la sogs pa dus bzhi dang rig
NK063(gu)001:10897: pa ni mig sogs rnam shes bzhi'o //
NK063(gu)001:10898: rnams zhes pa sdud pa'i sgras reg sogs lus kyi
NK063(gu)001:10899: chos bzhi dang rtag sogs phyin ci log bzhi dang
NK063(gu)001:10900: rgyud drug gi bag chags kyang bsdu'o //
NK063(gu)001:10901: de rnams gang du dag ce na gong nas /
NK063(gu)001:10902: byang chub sems zhes pas dbang po bzhi phyi'i sems dpa' la dus bzhi phyi'i sems ma dang /
NK063(gu)001:10903: rnam shes bzhi nang gi sems dpa' la yul bzhi
NK063(gu)001:10904: nang gi sems ma dang ni zhes pa lus kyi
NK063(gu)001:10905: chos bzhi ni sgo ba yin la phyin ci log
NK063(gu)001:10907: rgyud drug gi rtog pa ni thub pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:10908: rdo rje zhes pa rtog pa dang lha de dag dbyer med pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10909: tshogs zhes pa mang po'i sgras gong gi lha dang rtog pa rnams so //
NK063(gu)001:10910: de dag kyang yid kyi rnam shes dang chos 'dus
NK063(gu)001:10911: byas 'dus ma byas su 'dus la de ni kun
NK063(gu)001:10912: tu bzang po yab yum ste /
NK063(gu)001:10913: de ltar rtog pa'i rang bzhin lhar dag pa ni
NK063(gu)001:10914: spros bcas kyi dkyil 'khor yin la de rang gi
NK063(gu)001:10915: sems kyi rnam 'phrul yin pa'i phyir bdag nyid chen
NK063(gu)001:10916: po ste / lhag pa'i zhes pa de dag yan
NK063(gu)001:10917: lag lhag pa'i lha dagu'am bcu gcig dang bcas pa
NK063(gu)001:10918: ste gang zhe na thugs kyi zhes pa ye shes
NK063(gu)001:10919: po ste / sems dapa'o // ye shes lnga zhes pa dbu rgyan no //
NK063(gu)001:10920: de ltar sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum yang bsgom
NK063(gu)001:10921: zhing yon tan phrin las kyi lha dang bcas par
NK063(gu)001:10922: gsal ba'o // lnga pa ni snying po zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:10923: rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pas sam yang na tshogs
NK063(gu)001:10924: bsgrubs pas dag med thob pa ni 'bras bu yin
NK063(gu)001:10925: gsal ba'o // pa'i phyir ro // thig le zhes
NK063(gu)001:10926: pa spros pa dang bral ba ste thob bya rig
NK063(gu)001:10927: 'dzin gyi dgongs pa'am yang na thob byed kyi rgyur
NK063(gu)001:10928: yang rung ste tshogs sgrub pa'i cha rkyen yo byad
NK063(gu)001:10929: lnga las +aa li k+aa li gtsor blangs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10930: mnyam sbyor bas zhes pa tshogs bsgrub pa'i lam gyi
NK063(gu)001:10931: cha rkyen dang ldan pas thob bya rig 'dzin la
NK063(gu)001:10932: sbyor ba'i phyir sbyor lam zhes kyang bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:10933: bde ba'i ye shes zhes tshogs bsgrubs pas rtags thon pa'i dngos grub zug rngu dang bral ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:10934: de yang dper na rol mo yis ltad mo ba'i
NK063(gu)001:10935: yid tshim pa ltar bde ba'i dngos grub kyis sgrub
NK063(gu)001:10937: ye shes dgyes la zhes pa lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK063(gu)001:10938: ye shes la nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba med pas
NK063(gu)001:10939: sam yang na dgyes ldan lha'i tshogs ye shes kyi
NK063(gu)001:10941: mchod pa 'bul zhes pa ni dngos grub 'dod pa'i
NK063(gu)001:10942: 'dzin pa dang bral pas yo byed lnga yis mchod
NK063(gu)001:10943: pa'o // gnyis pa thabs lam steng sgo dbang du bshad pa la yang bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:10944: dang po ni tshig rkang pa bzhis ston te /
NK063(gu)001:10945: 'di snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo bsgom pa yin
NK063(gu)001:10946: la de la kun tu bzang po thig le bsgom
NK063(gu)001:10947: pa'i man ngag tu bzhag pa'i 'thad pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:10949: kun tu bzang po rgyud la ldan pa la dgongs pa'o zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:10950: de yang dkyil 'khor zhes pa rang dkyil 'khor te dbus kyi rtsa dkyil yin la /
NK063(gu)001:10951: yan lag gi rtsa 'khor yin pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10952: ldan pa'i zhes pa de snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo la'o //
NK063(gu)001:10953: ji ltar ldan na thabs dang shes rab kyi rang
NK063(gu)001:10954: bzhin snying dkar dmar nyi zla ga'u'i dbus na gleng
NK063(gu)001:10955: gzhi bstan pa ltara'agro ba thams cad la 'byung ba
NK063(gu)001:10956: dwangs ma lnga 'dus kyi rang bzhin yum lnga dang
NK063(gu)001:10957: sku lnga ye shes lngar bde la mi rtog par
NK063(gu)001:10958: gzugs can rnams la dngos dang gzugs med rnams la
NK063(gu)001:10960: dkyil 'khor gyis zhes pa bsgom pa'i gdams ngag gis
NK063(gu)001:10961: de'i gnas lugs ji lta ba bzhin shes par byed
NK063(gu)001:10962: pa'o // dkyil 'khor la ni zhes pa snying ga
NK063(gu)001:10963: chos kyi 'khor lo de ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor
NK063(gu)001:10964: bsgom pa'i gzhir gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:10965: dkyil 'khor bsgom zhes pa rnam bkod ltar bsgom pa'i thabs bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:10966: mkha' 'gro ma dang bcas pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:10969: 'khor lo bzhi bskul te bsgom pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:10970: yang na 'di ltar dkyil 'khor zhes pa ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)001:10971: dkyil 'khor las byung ba zhes pa de bsgoms pa'i stobs las byung ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:10972: gang byung na thugs kyi dkyil 'khor zhes pa thig
NK063(gu)001:10973: le 'od du 'bar bas rtsa bzhi'i sku gsung thugs
NK063(gu)001:10975: des 'khor ba'i sa bon drug dang shes pa bzhi'i
NK063(gu)001:10976: bag chags sbyangs nas ye shes kyi snying po la
NK063(gu)001:10977: 'dus te cir yang mi dmigs pa nyid ye shes
NK063(gu)001:10978: lngar gsal ba'o // dkyil 'khor mchog ces pa ni
NK063(gu)001:10979: de'i gong na 'bras bu gzhan med pa'i phyir ro
NK063(gu)001:10980: lngar gsal ba'o // // gnyis pa rkang pa brgyad kyis ston pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:10981: 'dir lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo bsgom pa yin
NK063(gu)001:10982: la de la kun tu bzang mo'i thig le bsgom
NK063(gu)001:10983: pa'i man ngag tu bzhag pa'i 'thad pa yang lte
NK063(gu)001:10984: ba la a gnas shing a de ni /
NK063(gu)001:10986: a ni skye med de bzhin nyid //
NK063(gu)001:10987: ces pas de kun tu bzang mo'i sa bon dang rang bzhin yin par gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:10988: de yang gsang ba'i thig le zhes pa lte ba
NK063(gu)001:10989: sprul pa'i 'khor lo na kun gzhi kun mo'i thig
NK063(gu)001:10990: le dbyings phyug lnga'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa de
NK063(gu)001:10992: dkyil 'khor dbyings zhes pa yum lnga'i dkyil 'khor de
NK063(gu)001:10993: thabs kyi rgyu'am bde ba thams cad kyi 'byung gnas
NK063(gu)001:10995: 'byung ba dngos ni 'byung ba lnga cha phra ba shes rab kyi cha rigs kyi yum yin la /
NK063(gu)001:10996: chen po ni rig pa rnams rigs kyi yab lnga yin pa'ang de bzhin te /
NK063(gu)001:10997: dbang po yul dus rig pa rnams //
NK063(gu)001:10998: byang chub sems ni rdo rje'i tshogs //
NK063(gu)001:10999: zhes pa lte ba'i a las byung ba gsal byed
NK063(gu)001:11000: kyi yi ge ba dang ya la sogs pa las
NK063(gu)001:11001: phyi'i sems dpa' yab yum dang /
NK063(gu)001:11002: ka dang tsa la sogs pa las nang gi sems dpa' yab yum dang /
NK063(gu)001:11003: mthar gnas kyi yi ge sha la sogs pa las
NK063(gu)001:11004: sgo ba yab yum la sogs pa rnams bde ba'i
NK063(gu)001:11005: rang bzhin las lhar gsal ba'i phyir skye mched rdo
NK063(gu)001:11006: rjer gnas pa'o // kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor
NK063(gu)001:11007: zhes pa rtog tshogs bde ba'i lhar dag pa ste
NK063(gu)001:11008: rjer gnas pa'o // / la zhes pa de bsgom bya'i gzhir gnas pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11009: de las gzhan ma dmigs pa'i phyir bdag nyid chen
NK063(gu)001:11010: po dngos po thams cad rang byung gi ye shes
NK063(gu)001:11011: su gsal ba'o // lhag pa'i zhes pa gong gi
NK063(gu)001:11012: snying ga'i thig le la ye shes lnga ye nas
NK063(gu)001:11013: gnas pa las 'dir khyad par du bsgom pas so
NK063(gu)001:11014: su gsal ba'o // // thugs kyi ye shes ni
NK063(gu)001:11015: snying ga'i thig le mi rtog pa de yin no
NK063(gu)001:11016: su gsal ba'o // // // lnga ni dwangs ma lnga ye shes lngar gnas pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11017: lta zhing zhes pa de 'od du 'bar nas rtsa
NK063(gu)001:11018: kun d+har mar thur du zhugs te lte ba'i thig
NK063(gu)001:11019: le la 'od phog pas ye shes lnga'i bde ba
NK063(gu)001:11020: mthong ba med pa'i tshul du myong bas na lha
NK063(gu)001:11021: zhes bya'o // yang na thugs rang bzhin gyi ye
NK063(gu)001:11022: shes lnga kun mo la sogs dbyings phyug ma lnga'i
NK063(gu)001:11023: zhes bya'o // thig le las / snying ga chos
NK063(gu)001:11024: kyi 'khor lo'i ye shes kyis bltas pa ni bsgom
NK063(gu)001:11025: pa yin zhing de gsal ba'i dus na kun mo'i
NK063(gu)001:11026: thig le las me byung bas /
NK063(gu)001:11027: snying ga'i dwangs ma lnga'i 'od thur du drangs te kun mo'i thig le la thim pas /
NK063(gu)001:11028: de'i tshe dwangs ma'i dbugs dang yid kyi rgyu ba
NK063(gu)001:11029: yang chad de shin tu bde ba'i rang bzhin du
NK063(gu)001:11030: gyur pa ni kun mo'i thig le rnyed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11031: gsum pa ni rkang pa gsum gyis ston te /
NK063(gu)001:11032: 'di mgrin pa longs spyod kyi thig le bsgom pa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11033: de la ci'i phyir sbyor ba dag pa zhes bya na /
NK063(gu)001:11034: lte ba'i thig le las gyen du 'phros te mgrin
NK063(gu)001:11035: pa'i thig le dang sbyor ba ro drug gi bde
NK063(gu)001:11036: ba nyams su myong ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11037: de yang snying po zhes pa gong gi lte ba
NK063(gu)001:11038: kun mo'i thig le'i bde ba la rgyu 'bras thams
NK063(gu)001:11040: thig le zhes pa ni mgrin pa longs spyod kyi
NK063(gu)001:11041: thig le ni 'dab ma bcu drug gi dbus na
NK063(gu)001:11043: mnyam sbyor zhes pa sprul pa'i bde ba'i 'od yungs
NK063(gu)001:11044: 'bru tsam kun d+har ma'i nang nas gyen du zhugs
NK063(gu)001:11045: nas longs spyod kyi thig le la phog ste /
NK063(gu)001:11046: dpe chab rom zhu ba bzhin bab pas mgrin pa
NK063(gu)001:11047: dang lte ba'i bde ba dus gcig tu myong ba'i
NK063(gu)001:11048: phyir thig le gnyis ngo bos mnyam par sbyor ba'o
NK063(gu)001:11049: // bde ba'i ye shes zhes pa de la rtog
NK063(gu)001:11050: pa'i zug rngu med pas bde ba yin zhing mgrin
NK063(gu)001:11051: pa'i yi ge bcu drug 'od du zhu nas 'dab
NK063(gu)001:11052: ma bcu drug ye shes su gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:11053: rol mo yis zhes pa ye shes kyi bde bas
NK063(gu)001:11054: mgrin pa'i rtog tshogs tshim pas rol mo lta bu'o
NK063(gu)001:11055: // de yang ye shes ni mgrin pa'i bde ba la /
NK063(gu)001:11056: dgyes la ni des tshim pa la rtog pa'i gdung ba med pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11057: mchod par 'bul zhes pa rgyud la myong bas gnas
NK063(gu)001:11058: su stobs shing de la'ang 'dzin pa dang bral ba'o
NK063(gu)001:11059: // bzhi pa ni rkang pa lngas ston te /
NK063(gu)001:11060: 'dir klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo bsgom pa
NK063(gu)001:11061: yin la de la khyab gdal chen por bzhag pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11062: 'thad pa ni / spyi gtsug bde chen gyi thig
NK063(gu)001:11063: le zhu ba'i tshe lus kyi srid pa ma lus
NK063(gu)001:11064: pa la bde ba khyab byed du skye ba'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:11065: 'thad pa ni / ro // de ni gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11066: zag pa med pa'i bsod nams zhes pa 'bru bsgyur
NK063(gu)001:11067: te gong gi lte mgrin mnyam sbyor gyi bde ba
NK063(gu)001:11068: rim par skyes nas ro drug gi bde bar ma
NK063(gu)001:11070: de'i dus su longs spyod kyang mi 'dzin pas bag
NK063(gu)001:11071: chags su mi 'gyur ba'i phyir dag pa med pa'o
NK063(gu)001:11072: // kyis zhes pa byed pa'i sgras gong gi ye
NK063(gu)001:11073: shes de 'od zer drug tu byas nas rtsa kun
NK063(gu)001:11074: d+har ma nas gyen du song bas klad pa bde
NK063(gu)001:11075: chen gyi 'khor lo 'dab ma so gnyis kyi dbus
NK063(gu)001:11076: na byang chub sems kyi thig le la 'od phog
NK063(gu)001:11077: // pa'o // ye shes ni des bde ba gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:11078: sgyu ma ni de snang la rang bzhin med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11079: rang snang ba ni rang gi bde ba rang la snang ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:11080: rol mo'i zhes pa bde ba'i ye shes kyis bsgom pa po'i yid tshim par byed pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:11081: gzhi ma nges pa las thabs kyi grangs sna tshogs su snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11082: de yang bsgom bya spyi bo'i dbus kyi byang sems ham gi rnam pa dkyil yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11083: 'dab ma so gnyis kyi bde ba'i rang bzhin 'khor yin no //
NK063(gu)001:11084: de ji ltar bsgom na ham las tshangs bug nas
NK063(gu)001:11085: 'od 'phros te rgyal ba'i zhing khams mtha' yas par
NK063(gu)001:11086: khyab pas / rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs /
NK063(gu)001:11087: de dag kyang rigs lnga yab yum 'ba' zhig gi
NK063(gu)001:11088: cha bzung sbyor ba'i chu rgyun rang gi tshangs bug
NK063(gu)001:11089: la sogs pa'i gnas su thim pas 'khor lo rnams
NK063(gu)001:11090: ye shes su gnas bsgyur bas /
NK063(gu)001:11091: rtog pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su gsal ba'i phyir mchog ces bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:11092: de phal gyi yul ma yin pas gsang ba yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11093: thig le ni bde ba chen po'i ngo bor gnas pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11094: de yang steng sgo'i bde ba de nyid kyi 'byung gnas thig le nyid yin pas dbyings zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:11095: de ltar steng sgo la dbang thob pa de ni
NK063(gu)001:11096: sems la dbang sgyur ba'i phyir las dang ngo bo
NK063(gu)001:11097: nyid kyis sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes dang 'dra
NK063(gu)001:11098: bar nyams su myong ba yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11099: de mthar phyin pas 'bras bu mngon du gyur pa dngos gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11100: phyogs bcu dus bzhi zhes pa la sogs dang 'brel lo //
NK063(gu)001:11101: gsum pa gsang ba 'og sgo'i dbang du bshad pa la gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:11102: dang po ni rkang pa bzhis ston te /
NK063(gu)001:11103: de yang dkyil 'khor zhes pa gsang ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)001:11104: de nyid bde ba'i ro dang bcas pa sgom pa
NK063(gu)001:11105: po yab yum gnyis la rang bzhin gyis ldan pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11106: phyir ro // dkyil 'khor gyis zhes pa de nyid
NK063(gu)001:11107: gsang ba'i lung man ngag gis gtan la 'bebs pa'o
NK063(gu)001:11108: phyir ro // // dkyil 'khor zhes pa yab yum lhar bskyed pa lhag pa ting dkyil lo //
NK063(gu)001:11109: la ni zhes pa de skye mched dang gsang gnas brlab pa'i gzhi yin pas so //
NK063(gu)001:11110: de gang zhe na dkyil 'khor bsgom zhes yan lag
NK063(gu)001:11111: gi lha yab la yab dang yum la yum rnams
NK063(gu)001:11112: bskyed pa ni skye mched brlab pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11113: de gnyis kyi mkha' pad+ma brgyad dang thabs rdo rje
NK063(gu)001:11114: rtse lnga par bsgom pa ni mkha' gsang byin gyis
NK063(gu)001:11115: brlabs pa'o // dkyil 'khor dkyil 'khor zhes pa yab yum gnyis lhar gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:11116: las byung ba zhes pa gnyis su med par rol pa las bde ba byung ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:11117: de ji ltar byung na yab kyi byang sems dbab
NK063(gu)001:11118: pa'i thabs kyis phab ste rdo rje'i dbu'i dkyil du
NK063(gu)001:11119: snang ba'i dus na gzung thabs kyis de nyid gnyis
NK063(gu)001:11120: med kyi ye shes su gsal la mi rtog pa
NK063(gu)001:11121: ni thugs kyi dkyil 'khor yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11122: thabs de shes rab kyis ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du sbyor bas mchog ces bya ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:11123: gnyis pa ni rkang pa brgyad kyis ston pa las
NK063(gu)001:11124: gsang ba'i thig le zhes pa de las byung ba'i
NK063(gu)001:11125: bde ba nyid thabs kyis zin pa dang ma zin
NK063(gu)001:11126: pas 'khor 'das gnyis su byed pas khe nyen che
NK063(gu)001:11127: ba'i phyir ro // dkyil 'khor ni byang chub sems kyi'o //
NK063(gu)001:11128: de thabs kyis zin pa ni rtog tshogs lhar gsal ba'i gnas yin pa'i phyir dbyings so //
NK063(gu)001:11129: lhar gsal ba dngos gang zhe na 'byung ba shes
NK063(gu)001:11130: rab rigs kyi yum la sogs rkang pa bzhis 'byung
NK063(gu)001:11131: ba cha phra ba yum dang rags par snang ba
NK063(gu)001:11132: yab dang dbang po dang rnam shes la sogs sems
NK063(gu)001:11133: dpa' dang sgo ba la sogs pa skad cig gis
NK063(gu)001:11134: gsal ba'i nus pa dang ldan pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11135: kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor la zhes pa des spyod yul bde ba'i rang bzhin du dag pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11136: de la bdag nyid chen po zhes bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:11137: yab yum gyi thig le rdor pad kyi nor bu
NK063(gu)001:11138: dang ze 'brur 'thon pa'i tshe rang bzhin lhan cig
NK063(gu)001:11139: skyes pa'i ye shes mngon du gsal ba las gzhan
NK063(gu)001:11141: de thabs kyis bsgom pas khyad par du 'gyur ba'i phyir lhag pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11142: 'bru bsgyur te bde ba nyid mi rtog pa'i ye
NK063(gu)001:11143: shes lngar gsal ba ni rgyal ba ma lus pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11145: des na bde bar snang ba'i dus na rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:11146: med par rtogs pa'i lta bas dngos grub kyi zhing
NK063(gu)001:11147: ma lus pa la dbang byed pa'i phyir shes rab
NK063(gu)001:11148: nyid thabs su sbyor ba zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:11149: gsum pa rkang pa brgyad kyis ston pa las /
NK063(gu)001:11150: snying po ni thig le ste yab yum gyi rtsa
NK063(gu)001:11151: sa ya phrag bcu gsum gyi bcud 'dus pa yin
NK063(gu)001:11152: pa'i phyir ro // de gang las byung na 'bru
NK063(gu)001:11153: bsgyur te yab yum sbyor bas thig le dus mnyam
NK063(gu)001:11155: de la rtog pa'i gdung ba med pa'i bde ba
NK063(gu)001:11156: yin la de lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes mtha'
NK063(gu)001:11158: de rgyud la myong ba'i tshe steng sgo rlung la
NK063(gu)001:11159: goms pas gar thabs chen po bcu drug la sogs
NK063(gu)001:11160: pa thabs kyis slar ldog pa ni dper na rol
NK063(gu)001:11161: mo lta bu yis rtsa gnas tshim zhing /
NK063(gu)001:11162: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes de ni zug rngu dang bral ba'i phyir dgyes pa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11163: de sngon gyi gnas phyi mo mngon du byas pa ni mchod pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:11164: der 'dzin pa dang bral bas zag med kyi dbyings su gnas stobs pa la 'bul ba zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:11165: zag pa med pa'i zhes pa thabs kyis zin pas 'khor bar mi 'ching bas so //
NK063(gu)001:11166: bsod nams zhes pa yang dag pa'i 'dod chags spyad pa'i yon tan no //
NK063(gu)001:11167: kyis zhes pa de thob byed kyi sgra'o //
NK063(gu)001:11168: ji ltar thob na dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11169: ye shes ni dpe sgyu ma ltar rang gi sems
NK063(gu)001:11170: nyid ye shes su snang ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:11171: rol mo'i zhes pa de dag gi bde bas sgom pa po yid tshim zhing /
NK063(gu)001:11172: dkyil 'khor zhes pa des sems nyid sku dang ye shes su gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:11173: mtha' yas zhes pa dkyil 'khor de yang gcig tu ma nges pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:11174: dkyil 'khor ma lus pa'i bdag nyid kyi phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11175: mchog ces pa de la sogs pa che ba'i yon tan grangs las 'das pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11176: de yang gsang ba zhes pa nyams su myong ba'i ro yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11177: thig le ni myong byed nyi zla ste de nyid
NK063(gu)001:11178: las lhan skyes kyi ye shes 'byung bas dbyings yin
NK063(gu)001:11179: pa'i phyir thabs shes gnyis su med par sbyor ba
NK063(gu)001:11180: zhes bya'o // de ltar thabs kyis sems nyid ye
NK063(gu)001:11181: shes su gsal zhing de chos kyi dbyings su sbyor
NK063(gu)001:11182: ba de ni phyogs bcu dus bzhis sangs rgyas kun
NK063(gu)001:11183: gyi bdag nyid kun tu bzang po yab yum dngos
NK063(gu)001:11184: zhes bya'o // yin te / rang rig la dbang
NK063(gu)001:11185: sgyur bas mthar thug gi 'bras bu mngon du byas
NK063(gu)001:11186: pa'i phyir phyogs bcu dus bzhi zhes pa la sogs
NK063(gu)001:11187: zhes bya'o // yin te / dang 'brel lo //
NK063(gu)001:11188: de ltar gzhung 'di dag thugs thig dang gsang thig
NK063(gu)001:11189: gi dgongs pas rten gang zag 'dod chags can gyi
NK063(gu)001:11190: lam gyi cha rkyen tshang bar bstan pa yin no
NK063(gu)001:11191: zhes bya'o // yin te / dang 'brel lo //
NK063(gu)001:11192: // gsum pa mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu ni
NK063(gu)001:11193: zhes bya'o // yin te / dang 'brel lo //
NK063(gu)001:11194: // / lam de dag gis tshogs sgrub pa man
NK063(gu)001:11195: chad du bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu thob tshul yin te
NK063(gu)001:11196: zhes bya'o // yin te / dang 'brel lo //
NK063(gu)001:11197: // / / de yang lam du gyur ba'i 'bras
NK063(gu)001:11198: bu tshe dbang ni zag pa ces spyir zag pa
NK063(gu)001:11199: tsam gyi go ba ni tha mal gyi 'dzin shes
NK063(gu)001:11200: bag chags dang bcas pa zhig yin te /
NK063(gu)001:11201: ji skad du spar khab las /
NK063(gu)001:11202: de dag 'jig rten pa la yod na 'dzin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11203: phyir zag par 'gyur la zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro
NK063(gu)001:11204: // de la phye na lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa gsum yin no //
NK063(gu)001:11205: 'dir tshe dbang la de dag dang bral ba'i phyir med pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11206: de yang bsod nams kyi tshogs khyad par can yo
NK063(gu)001:11207: byad lnga la spyad pas grub pa'i sku yin zhing
NK063(gu)001:11208: / kyis zhes pa de'i dgongs pa ston pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:11210: ye shes zhes pa sngar ma mthong ba'i chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid mngon du mthong ba de'o //
NK063(gu)001:11211: de dpe sgyu ma ltar snang la rang bzhin med par sems nyid rang snang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:11212: de yang rol mo ltar zag pa med pa'i bde ba des yid tshim pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11214: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor mngon du gyur ba'i dgongs pa tshad las 'das pas mtha' yas so //
NK063(gu)001:11215: de zag bcas kyi ting nge 'dzin las khyad par du gyur pas mchog yin no //
NK063(gu)001:11216: de lta bu'i tshe dbang gi dgongs pa de zab cing gting dpag dka' bas gsang ba yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11217: spros pa dang bral bas thig le ste /
NK063(gu)001:11218: de nyid yon tan thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas dbyings so //
NK063(gu)001:11219: de ltar chos nyid rang mtshan mthong ba de ni
NK063(gu)001:11220: 'dra ba dang 'brel ba gnyis ka rgyu mtshan du
NK063(gu)001:11221: byas nas sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:11222: gnyis pa rgya chen ni gzhung bsgyur te 'og nas
NK063(gu)001:11223: dkyil 'khor zhes pa sbyar sa rgya chen la sbyar
NK063(gu)001:11224: ba'i tshe 'di'i dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid la gnas
NK063(gu)001:11225: pa ni rang dkyil 'khor yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11226: dkyil 'khor nyid ces pa de'i cha lugs longs sku
NK063(gu)001:11227: dang 'dra ba'i phyir na de rgyu mtshan du byas
NK063(gu)001:11229: gsum pa lhun grub kyi ngo bo ni rdzogs zhes
NK063(gu)001:11230: pa rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK063(gu)001:11232: de mthar lam la mnyam gzhag gi tshe lhun gyis grub ste tha dad med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11233: rjes thob kyi tshe sku de la rgyan du mtshan
NK063(gu)001:11234: dpe du mas spras shing dkyil 'khor bdun gyis bsdus
NK063(gu)001:11235: pa'i chos ma lus pa yongs su rdzogs pas 'gro
NK063(gu)001:11236: ba'i don thogs pa med pas gang 'dul du snang
NK063(gu)001:11237: ba'o // de ltar 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan
NK063(gu)001:11238: ma lus pa rdzogs pa'i rang dkyil 'khor mthar phyin
NK063(gu)001:11240: mthar lam gyi dgongs pa mnyam par sbyor bas rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin zhes bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:11241: rang bzhin dbyer med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11242: gnyis pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu la sbyor tshul ni /
NK063(gu)001:11243: ye shes ni sku lnga'i dgongs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11244: rdzogs pa ni de 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan ma lus pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK063(gu)001:11245: de ltar rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dkyil
NK063(gu)001:11246: 'khor de mthar lam gyi dgongs pas sbyang bya'i yul
NK063(gu)001:11248: ji ltar sbyor ba'i tshul ni thos bsam sgom pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11249: zhes pa mthar lam shes rab gsum gyis rgyal ba
NK063(gu)001:11250: dang dgongs pa mnyam par sbyor ba'i tshul gyis thams
NK063(gu)001:11251: cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes mthar phyin pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11252: dgongs pa'i ngo bo dang bral bas rang byung zhes bya la /
NK063(gu)001:11253: de la rgyal ba kun gyi dgongs pa ngam zhing ngo mtshar ba lhun gyis grub pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:11254: rgyal ba la rgyud tha dad med cing rgyu rkyen las byung ba ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11255: des na lam 'di ni phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs
NK063(gu)001:11256: rgyas thams cad kyi bgrod pa gcig pa yin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11257: phyir thugs dam 'di las 'da' bar mi mdzad pas
NK063(gu)001:11258: na dam tshig mchog ces bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:11259: de ltar 'bras bu la sbyor tshul 'di ni lam
NK063(gu)001:11260: rim gyis pa'i bgrod tshul de las kyang mthar chags
NK063(gu)001:11261: pa'i dbang du bshad pa yin gyi /
NK063(gu)001:11262: cig car ba thod rgal ba'i dbang du na le'u
NK063(gu)001:11263: bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa bshad pa ltar
NK063(gu)001:11265: gnyis pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK063(gu)001:11266: gzhung 'og nas phyogs bcu dus bzhi zhes pas phyogs
NK063(gu)001:11267: dus kyi rgyal ba ma lus pa'i bdag nyid du
NK063(gu)001:11268: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:11269: de dag gi sku dang gsung dang yon tan dang phrin las dang thugs rnams bsdus pa lnga /
NK063(gu)001:11271: rgyas par mtha' yas pa la sogs che ba'i yon
NK063(gu)001:11272: tan ji snyed pa rnams ma lus pa'i bdag nyid
NK063(gu)001:11273: du gyur pa sku lnga lhun grub kyi zhal rang
NK063(gu)001:11275: rang rig la dbang thob pas cir yang 'dod rgur
NK063(gu)001:11276: sgyur ba ni bdag don du dgyes pa'i longs spyod
NK063(gu)001:11277: dang / gzhan don du mdzad pa'i phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pa la mnga' brnyes pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11278: de las bsgrub bya gzhan med pas mchog ces bya zhing /
NK063(gu)001:11279: de nyid thun mong gi lam gyi 'bras bu las khyad par du gyur pas ngam pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:11280: des don mdzad tshul ni yang 'og nas /
NK063(gu)001:11281: rtag par rgyun gyi thugs rje la sogs te de
NK063(gu)001:11282: yang dkyil ni spros pa dang bral ba las 'khor
NK063(gu)001:11283: ni don mdzad par ma 'gags pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:11284: dper na nyi ma nam mkhar shar bas 'od zer
NK063(gu)001:11285: 'jig rten du 'byung ba ltar rtsol rtog med par
NK063(gu)001:11287: des phyogs bcu'i zhing ma lus par dus rtag tu
NK063(gu)001:11288: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dkyil 'khor des gdul bya
NK063(gu)001:11289: 'dul zhing 'gro ba rnams sdug bsngal las skyob pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11290: mgon dang gnyen gcig pur gyur pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11291: de ltar snang dus nyid na ma grub pas sgyu
NK063(gu)001:11292: ma lta bu'i dkyil 'khor gyis 'gro ba rnams yang
NK063(gu)001:11293: dag pa'i sa la sgrol ba yang lhun gyis grub
NK063(gu)001:11294: pa yis don bya ba'i yul dang byed pa po
NK063(gu)001:11295: gnyis med par mthar phyin pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi bdag
NK063(gu)001:11297: yang snod dang ldan pa'i spyod yul gyi skabs su /
NK063(gu)001:11298: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du //
NK063(gu)001:11299: shin tu sbyangs la rab gnas shing //
NK063(gu)001:11300: zhes pas rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po de chos can /
NK063(gu)001:11302: bskal par sbyangs pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11303: rtags ma grub na rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon
NK063(gu)001:11304: po ma yin pa 'gyur zhing khyab pa med na
NK063(gu)001:11306: 'dod na de'i yul yin par bsal lo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11307: 'di la khyab pa ma grub kyis lan 'debs so //
NK063(gu)001:11308: 'o na gzhung de dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11310: sbyangs rno'i yul yin pas rang rno'i yul yin pa mi khegs pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:11311: de gnyis dngos 'gal ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11312: man ngag gi che ba ni 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin /
NK063(gu)001:11313: zhes pa de nyid la kha cig gsang sngags pa
NK063(gu)001:11314: 'bras bu lam du byed pa de smin pa zhig
NK063(gu)001:11315: gam / ma smin pa zhig lam du byed /
NK063(gu)001:11316: dang po ltar na thug med du 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:11317: smin pa lam du byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11319: khyab pa tshad ma ste na ning gi 'bras bu
NK063(gu)001:11320: da gzod kyi sa bon du 'gyur ba bzhin no
NK063(gu)001:11322: gnyis pa ltar na 'bras bu lam du byed pa ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:11323: ma smin pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11324: kha cig ngo bo smin zhing mtshon tshul ma smin
NK063(gu)001:11325: pa lam du byed ces zer ba ni ma yin
NK063(gu)001:11326: te / 'o na 'bras bu gcig gi ngo bo
NK063(gu)001:11327: dang mtshon tshul gnyis 'grel pa med par 'gyur te
NK063(gu)001:11328: te / / smin ma smin 'gal ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11329: rtags de tshad ma yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11330: 'gag pa la 'brel med kyis khyab ste mun snang bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:11331: 'o na ji ltar zhe na rnam par dbye ste ye nas yin pa'i 'bras bu dang /
NK063(gu)001:11332: de lam gyis mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:11333: 'di dang po yin pas 'bras bu lam du byed pa ma yin par 'gyur ba'i skyon med la /
NK063(gu)001:11334: de mngon du byas pa ma yin pa la thug med du 'gyur ba'i skyon med do //
NK063(gu)001:11335: 'o na theg pa thams cad chos can /
NK063(gu)001:11336: 'bras bu lam du byed pa 'ba' zhig tu thal /
NK063(gu)001:11337: de yin tsam khyab byed du yod pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11339: yin kyang thams cad kyis de ltar gtan la 'bebs shing rtogs pa med do //
NK063(gu)001:11340: yang na gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu gnyis las 'di dang po ste /
NK063(gu)001:11341: 'og ma'i 'bras bu 'di'i lam yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11342: de ltar yang dbyig gi sgron ma las /
NK063(gu)001:11343: khyod kyi bcu gcig kun tu 'od //
NK063(gu)001:11344: thabs chen theg pa'i bsti gnas sa //
NK063(gu)001:11347: de ltar che ba de dag dang ldan pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:11348: rgyud 'di ni dus bzhi'i rgyal ba thams cad kyi
NK063(gu)001:11349: bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam yin no //
NK063(gu)001:11350: gzhung don tha ma'i skabs su thos bsam sgom la
NK063(gu)001:11351: zhes pa thos pa ni ming la dmigs pa ste
NK063(gu)001:11352: gzhon nu me tog 'thu ba ltar sgra dang tshig
NK063(gu)001:11353: la brten nas shes bya rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11354: bsam pa ni ming don gnyis ka la dmigs pa
NK063(gu)001:11355: ste rgya sol la rlung gis btab pa ltar tshig
NK063(gu)001:11356: gi rjes su rtog pa dang dpyod pa'i sgo nas
NK063(gu)001:11358: sgom pa ni don kho na nyid la dmigs pa
NK063(gu)001:11359: ste bum pa'i nang gi mar me ltar gong ma
NK063(gu)001:11360: gnyis kyis nges pa'i steng du gnas pa cig yin
NK063(gu)001:11361: no // de ltar shes rab gsum la blo rab tu sbyangs pa'i zhes pa la sogs gzhung brtag /
NK063(gu)001:11362: yang 'dir le'u gong 'og gi zlos skyon 'di lta bu zhig bsam pa'i yul du mthong ste /
NK063(gu)001:11363: dang po le'u lnga par yo byad ldan zhes grol lam rim gyis pa'i tshogs sgrub cig bstan /
NK063(gu)001:11364: dgu par yang cho ga lnga ni zhes pa la sogs tshogs sgrub cig bstan /
NK063(gu)001:11365: bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis par yang yan lag ma nyams zhes pa la sogs su bstan /
NK063(gu)001:11366: bcu gsum pa 'dir yang byung bas de dag zlos so zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11367: dgos ched so so'i dbang gis mi zlos te /
NK063(gu)001:11368: lnga par ni rgyu tshang bas phyag rgya gcig spros
NK063(gu)001:11369: las su rung bas yi ge sgyu 'phrul bsgrubs pas
NK063(gu)001:11370: dngos grub gnyis kyi thob tshul yin te /
NK063(gu)001:11371: ji skad du de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:11372: sngags dang phyag rgya rab brtan na //
NK063(gu)001:11373: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:11375: dgu par zab mo'i dbang thob nas tshogs bsgrub pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11376: gnas skabs su tshe dbang dang mthar thug tu sku
NK063(gu)001:11377: lnga la sbyor ba'i dus gtso bor bstan pa yin
NK063(gu)001:11379: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK063(gu)001:11380: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK063(gu)001:11381: dbang sgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK063(gu)001:11384: de tshe bcu drug tshun chad kyis //
NK063(gu)001:11385: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:11387: bcu gcig par gzhi phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang
NK063(gu)001:11388: thabs bsnyen sgrub bzhi rgyas par bstan pas sgrub pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11389: yan lag tshang zhing gtso bor mngon du phyung ba'i
NK063(gu)001:11390: tan gan la spyad pas gnas skabs dang mthar thug
NK063(gu)001:11391: gi 'bras bu la sbyor tshul yin te /
NK063(gu)001:11393: ngo mtshar ngan 'gro thar pa'i thabs //
NK063(gu)001:11396: yid bzhin sprin gyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:11398: bcu gsum pa 'dir ni dgag bya gzhan gyis brtags
NK063(gu)001:11399: pa'i ma rtogs log rtogs bsal nas thun mong gi
NK063(gu)001:11400: lam nas bkod pa'i mtha' 'di'i lam mngon du byed
NK063(gu)001:11401: tshul gtso bo bstan pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:11402: ji skad du yi ge sgra btags ming tshogs la //
NK063(gu)001:11403: brten pa'i tshig gis rab mtshon te //
NK063(gu)001:11404: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK063(gu)001:11406: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yis //
NK063(gu)001:11407: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:11409: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u bcu gsum pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11411: // le'u bcu bzhi pa'i mngon par rtogs pa'i dbang du
NK063(gu)001:11412: mchod pa las kyi rim pa la bco lnga las
NK063(gu)001:11413: tha ma rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dkyil
NK063(gu)001:11415: de yang sgro skur dang bral ba'i dkyil 'khor la de dang mthun par nyid kyis bstod pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:11416: 'dir kha cig chos sku'i sku gsung thugs gsum ldog pa gcig tu 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:11417: sku yang thig le zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11418: gsung yang thig le zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11419: thugs zhes pa yang stong pa nyid kyi ye shes te /
NK063(gu)001:11420: de gsum skye med spros bral du gcig pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11422: dper na bum pa gcig gi steng du dbyibs dang kha dog byas pa dang mi rtag pa /
NK063(gu)001:11423: shes bya dang gzhal bya la sogs ldog pa'i chos su ma brten pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:11424: skye med spros bral gyis go phye nas 'bras bu
NK063(gu)001:11425: che ba'i yon tan thams cad kyi rten byed pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11426: ldog pa nas sku yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:11427: des de nyid du go zhing brda' sprod pas na gsung yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11428: de nyid rnam pa cir yang mi rtog pa'i ldog pa nas thugs yin no //
NK063(gu)001:11430: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK063(gu)001:11431: zhes pa la sogs spyir bstod pa'i skabs su /
NK063(gu)001:11433: gangs chen po mtsho lnga yang de dag lnga'i ngo bo kho na'o phyir zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:11434: de la kha cig gangs chen po mtsho lngas bsdus pa'i chos thams cad sku gsung thugs yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:11436: de der ma 'dus pa med do zhes bya ba yin zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:11437: 'o na gangs chen po mtsho lnga rang gang yin zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11438: de ni barnga yis bshad pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:11439: bdag tu zhen pa'i nyon mongs pa lnga ni ye
NK063(gu)001:11440: shes kyis bzhu dka' ba'i phyir gangs zhes bya la
NK063(gu)001:11441: / de'i dbang gis 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor gnas pa
NK063(gu)001:11442: ni gnyen pos bskam par bya ba'i phyir mtsho zhes
NK063(gu)001:11443: / bya'o // 'o na sangs rgyas la bstod par mi 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:11444: sems can la bstod par 'dug pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11446: dper na stod mnga' ris skor gsum na mi'i sde
NK063(gu)001:11447: tshan dang bye brag mang po yod kyang mnga' bdag
NK063(gu)001:11448: rtse lde'i mnga' 'og tu ma 'dus pa med cing
NK063(gu)001:11449: sku drin gyis khyab la 'bangs yin no zhes smos
NK063(gu)001:11450: pas rtse lde'i che bar 'gyur ba ltar /
NK063(gu)001:11451: rang bzhin la ltos te 'khor ba'i nyon mongs pa
NK063(gu)001:11452: lngar snang ba yang ngo bo nyid kyis stongs pas
NK063(gu)001:11453: chos skur lhun gyis grub cing 'khor 'das ngo bo
NK063(gu)001:11454: tha dad du ma grub pa'i phyir sangs rgyas la
NK063(gu)001:11456: kha cig gangs ma yin gang zhes yin te /
NK063(gu)001:11457: gangs chen mtsho ni rnam snang yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11458: rnam snang la sogs pa rigs lnga yin zer ba yang 'thad pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:11459: 'di sku lnga la bstod pa yin la rigs lnga ni de'i bye brag yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11460: yang kha cig 'grel pa'i ngag de ni 'byung ba
NK063(gu)001:11461: lnga'am nyon mongs pa lnga yang rigs lnga'i ngo bo
NK063(gu)001:11462: yin pas de skad ces bya'o zer ba la yang
NK063(gu)001:11463: rgyu mtshan yod par ma mthong ngo //
NK063(gu)001:11464: 'o na gang zhe na de dag ni 'grel pa'i dgongs pa ma mthun pa yin gyi /
NK063(gu)001:11465: gzhung gi thad sor 'bru sbyar na thams cad ma lus zhes pa ni rgyal ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:11466: sku gsung thugs zhes pa der 'dus pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11467: 'o na yon tan phrin las ma lus 'dus sam zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11468: der ma zad der 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan ma lus pa yang 'dus pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:11469: ji skad du bcu gcig pa las /
NK063(gu)001:11470: yang na sku gsung thugs nyid de //
NK063(gu)001:11471: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK063(gu)001:11473: des na sku gsung thugs kyis bsdus pa'i rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:11474: ni sku lnga'i bdag nyid chen po yin pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:11475: / khyab byed sku gsung thugs kyis khyab bya rgyal
NK063(gu)001:11476: ba kun la de dang de'i bdag nyid du khyab
NK063(gu)001:11477: / pa'o // de ltar sku gsung thugs kyis bsdus
NK063(gu)001:11478: pa'i chos thams cad ni thig le ste spros pa
NK063(gu)001:11480: che zhes pa ni de'i ngo bo nyid dam mngon par byang chub pa'i sku yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11481: de nas mchod bshags bya zhing smon lam gdab pa lag len ltar la /
NK063(gu)001:11482: ting nge 'dzin mjug gi rim pa ni khro bo'i skabs su thun mong du 'chad do //
NK063(gu)001:11483: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u bcu bzhi pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11485: // le'u bco lnga pa ni spyir rgyud 'di la gleng
NK063(gu)001:11486: gzhi gsum yod pa las 'di gdul bya dgos ched
NK063(gu)001:11488: de yang de nas zhes pa la sogs la gzhung
NK063(gu)001:11489: don bzhi las gang gis 'dul byed kyi gnyen po
NK063(gu)001:11490: de pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid chen po sangs
NK063(gu)001:11491: rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid du gyur pa
NK063(gu)001:11492: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11493: des 'dul ba'i gdul bya la mos pa tha dad
NK063(gu)001:11494: pa yod pa'i phyir rgyud 'di nas mngon par rtogs
NK063(gu)001:11495: pa zhi khro gnyis ston pa las /
NK063(gu)001:11496: le'u bcu bzhi pa yan chad du phal cher zhi ba'i don rnams bstan nas /
NK063(gu)001:11497: bco lnga pa 'di nas khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du mngon par 'du mdzad de zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:11498: spyir khro bo la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:11501: phyag rgya chen po'i khro bo'o //
NK063(gu)001:11502: dang po ni chos nyid mi dmigs pa rtogs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11503: shes rab kyis dngos por 'dzin pa'i rtog pa 'joms
NK063(gu)001:11505: rang rig ye shes rgyal po yis //
NK063(gu)001:11506: phyogs bcu'i khams rnams dbang bsdus nas //
NK063(gu)001:11507: kun kyang mi dmigs dbyings su thim //
NK063(gu)001:11509: gnyis pa ni ji bzhin pa mngon du byas pas 'ching ba thams cad dang bral ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:11511: yang dag khro bo chen po ni //
NK063(gu)001:11512: mtshan ma 'joms phyir khro bo'i mchog /
NK063(gu)001:11514: tha ma ni dregs pa chen po 'dul ba'i don
NK063(gu)001:11515: du sku mdog zhal phyag rgyan cha lugs dang bcas
NK063(gu)001:11517: de nas bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen po rngams pa'i skyi bung zhes byed pa /
NK063(gu)001:11518: 'bar ba chen po khrag 'thung sku smug nag cir yang 'gyur ba /
NK063(gu)001:11519: dbu dang phyag zhabs stong khams kyi rdul snyed mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:11520: zhes pa la sogs pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:11521: 'o na dngos po'i gnas lugs la zhi khro gnyis po gcig pa zhig gam tha dad pa yin /
NK063(gu)001:11522: dang po ltar na gnyis su bshad pa dang 'gal la /
NK063(gu)001:11523: gnyis pa ltar na kun khyab gsum gyis gnod byed yod de 'di ltar /
NK063(gu)001:11524: rig pa ni zhi khro gnyis po chos can /
NK063(gu)001:11525: rang bzhin chos skur gcig pa ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:11526: rgyud gzhan tha dad pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:11528: tha dad pa la gcig ma yin pas khyab la lhas byin dang mchog sbyin bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:11529: 'dod na gong nas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo
NK063(gu)001:11530: bo nyid kyis zhes ngo bo gcig tu bshad pas
NK063(gu)001:11531: bsal lo // gzhan yang zhi ba las khro bor bsgyur du mi btub par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:11535: khro bo'i rang bzhin shin tu gdug cing 'jigs pa ma yin zhing //
NK063(gu)001:11536: zhi ba'i mdzad pas kun gyi yid la 'thad par gnas 'gyur yod ma yin //
NK063(gu)001:11537: de gnyis gnyis su med pa'i ngang du gnas //
NK063(gu)001:11541: sgyur ba'i 'khor lo de bzhin te //
NK063(gu)001:11543: yang dag gi rtsa ba las kyang /
NK063(gu)001:11544: dngos grub dam shis blang ba'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:11545: snga ma las kyi gnas bsgyur te //
NK063(gu)001:11546: zhes pa la sogs dang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11547: 'dir kha cig zhi khro re mos pa 'gog pa ni 'thad pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:11548: gang zag gcig gis gnyis car bsgom par nges shing rtog gnyis cig car 'jug pa med la /
NK063(gu)001:11549: bsgyur ba ni re mos pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11550: 'o na ji ltar zhe na lam pas bskyed cing bsgom bya zhi khro gnyis po chos can /
NK063(gu)001:11551: dngos po'i gnas lugs la dbyer med pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:11552: gzhi sems nyid la tha dad du ma grub cing /
NK063(gu)001:11553: lam ting nge 'dzin gyis bsgyur tu btub la /
NK063(gu)001:11554: 'bras bu la de gnyis rgyud so sor ma grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:11555: rang bzhin chos skur gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11556: kha cig rang bzhin gnas lugs kyi zhi khro gnyis su 'dod pa ni btags pa ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:11557: des na rtags khyab gnyis ka gong gi lung dang man ngag gis grub bo //
NK063(gu)001:11558: 'o na spyir zhi khro gnyis su bshad cing khyad
NK063(gu)001:11559: par du 'dir khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du mngon par
NK063(gu)001:11560: 'du mdzad pa de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11561: dri ba de'i lan la rang spyi dang khyad par gyi rgyu mtshan gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:11562: dang po ni gdul bya dgos ched kyi dbang gis zhi khro gnyis su snang ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:11563: de yang gdul bya'i rgyud tha dad la ltos nas mos pa tha dad pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:11564: rgyud gcig la ltos nas snga phyi res 'ga' bar dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11566: gdug pa can ru dra 'khor bcas 'dul pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:11567: le'u bco lnga pa 'dir khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du
NK063(gu)001:11569: de yang gong ltar gsum las 'dir phyag rgya chen
NK063(gu)001:11570: po'i khro bo ste de rjes 'jug gis nyams su
NK063(gu)001:11571: blang bya yin pa'i phyir mngon par rtogs pa dang
NK063(gu)001:11573: de ni bla ma gong ma dag gi gsung gis
NK063(gu)001:11574: sngon byung du dpal chen po'i mdzad pa dang mthun
NK063(gu)001:11575: par rjes 'jug tu bdag sras kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK063(gu)001:11576: le'u bco lnga pa 'di ltar nyams su blang ste
NK063(gu)001:11577: / sngon byung dang tshul mthun pa rjes 'jug tu
NK063(gu)001:11578: gang zag yid ches par byed pa'i phyir zhes gsungs
NK063(gu)001:11580: sngar zhi ba'i skabs su bshad pa ltar gsang sngags
NK063(gu)001:11581: kyi bshad tshul la nyes legs kyi skyon yon 'dor
NK063(gu)001:11582: len du shes par bya zhing rgyud 'grel pa bzhi
NK063(gu)001:11584: 'dir khro bo'i mngon par rtogs pa la don bzhis nyams su blang ste /
NK063(gu)001:11585: ting nge 'dzin sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11586: sngon gyi gleng gzhis khro bor bsgom pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK063(gu)001:11587: ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos dang /
NK063(gu)001:11588: ting nge 'dzin mjug gi rim pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11589: dang po ni zhi ba dang thun mong ba yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11590: gnyis pa la yang gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:11592: 'dul byed dpal chen po'i gleng gazhi'o //
NK063(gu)001:11593: dang po ni gzhung don gnyis pa gang gdul bya'i yul te /
NK063(gu)001:11595: spyir sems can thams cad gol ba'i rgyu ni ma rig pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11597: ma rig pa tsam du mtshon pa'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK063(gu)001:11599: dang po ni de ma yin la der zhen pa' rtog pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:11600: ji skad du 'di'i gsum pa las /
NK063(gu)001:11601: srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs bdag tu rtog las 'phros //
NK063(gu)001:11604: bdag tu rmongs pa'i rtog pa lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11605: brtags pa la mngon par zhen pa kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11606: yang dag pa'i lam ni 'bras bu rdo rje'i theg pa 'di yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11607: de ston par byed pa'i rdo rje slob dpon dang
NK063(gu)001:11608: bral ba ni ma mjal ba dag gis sems can
NK063(gu)001:11610: bye brag tu ru dra gol ba'i rgyu ni 'di'i
NK063(gu)001:11611: khungs ji lta bar ston pa mdo chen po'i byung
NK063(gu)001:11613: de yang de'i le'u nyi shu pa las /
NK063(gu)001:11614: ji skad du dran pa bskal pa dpag tu med pa 'das pa'i sngon du byung ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:11615: sangs rgyas mi bskyod pa zhes bya ba bskal pa kun dga' zhes bya ba la /
NK063(gu)001:11616: zhing khams mngon par dga' ba zhes bya bar byung
NK063(gu)001:11617: ba'i bstan pa la rab tu byung ba'i dge slong
NK063(gu)001:11618: thub dka' gzhon nu zhes bya ba /
NK063(gu)001:11619: gang ji lta ba bzhin theg pa chen po'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba /
NK063(gu)001:11620: thams cad nas thams cad du ma bcos ma bslad
NK063(gu)001:11621: pa'i rnal 'byor du gnas pa skyes bu dam par
NK063(gu)001:11622: chud pa zhig byung ba des /
NK063(gu)001:11623: sems can thams cad rgyal ba'i sras su mthong zhing
NK063(gu)001:11624: de yongs su bskul ba la brtson pa 'ba' zhig
NK063(gu)001:11625: byed do // de'i tshe de'i dus na 'khor ba
NK063(gu)001:11626: thog ma dang tha ma med par skye ba thog
NK063(gu)001:11627: ma dang tha ma med pa'i las dang skye ba
NK063(gu)001:11628: dpag tu med pa ni brjod kyis mi rdzogs te
NK063(gu)001:11629: byed do // / las skabs shig gi skye ba cha gcig la bzung na 'di lta ste /
NK063(gu)001:11630: nye 'khor du khyim bdag ke'u ka ya zhes bya
NK063(gu)001:11631: ba zhig la bu thar pa nag po zhes bya
NK063(gu)001:11632: ba yod de / bu de la g.yog dan 'phag ces bya ba yod de /
NK063(gu)001:11633: de'i tshe mi gang dag dge slong thub dka' gzhon
NK063(gu)001:11634: nu la rnal 'byor gyi lam bslabs te kun kyang
NK063(gu)001:11635: rnal 'byor la gnas shing spyod par gyur to //
NK063(gu)001:11636: de'i tshe thar pa nag po 'di ltar rtog ste /
NK063(gu)001:11637: dge slong thub dka' gzhon nu 'dis thams cad ji lta ba bzhin spyod pa thos nas /
NK063(gu)001:11638: thams cad ji dga' bar spyod bzhin du lam yod
NK063(gu)001:11639: pa'i chos dag 'byung ngam zhes rtog la gang dag
NK063(gu)001:11641: thams cad kyis de ltar 'byung bar smras so //
NK063(gu)001:11642: de nas g.yog dang bcas te dge slong gang na
NK063(gu)001:11643: ba der zhugs te gan du phyi te 'dun pa
NK063(gu)001:11646: thams cad ji lta bar spyod bzhin du lam ston pa'i thabs la mkhas par thos na /
NK063(gu)001:11647: de de lta nyid du nges sam zhes gsol ba las /
NK063(gu)001:11650: de de lta nyid du 'byung ba dag yod par rung ngo zhes smras pas /
NK063(gu)001:11651: thar pa g.yog dang bcas pa dga' mgu yi rangs
NK063(gu)001:11652: te bdag g.yog dang bcas pa 'di khyod kyis bka'
NK063(gu)001:11654: bdag kyang thams cad mi 'gog pa'i lam bslabs te
NK063(gu)001:11655: rnal 'byor du gnas par 'tshal bas dam pa nyid
NK063(gu)001:11656: du nges par bzung du gsol zhes 'dun pa las
NK063(gu)001:11657: / dge slong des smras pa yin no legs so de ltar bya'o zhes legs so byin nas /
NK063(gu)001:11658: thar pa nag po rab tu byung nas dam par bzung /
NK063(gu)001:11659: dan 'bag ni dus 'dzin du bzung nas thar ba'i g.yog tu byas so //
NK063(gu)001:11660: de nas thar pa dge slong gis gsol pa /
NK063(gu)001:11661: dge slong chen po thams cad ji lta ba'i lam dam pa de gang lags /
NK063(gu)001:11663: ji bzhin nyid de ma bcos na //
NK063(gu)001:11664: dngos po bzhi la gnas spyad kyang //
NK063(gu)001:11665: nam mkha' la ni sprin bzhin te //
NK063(gu)001:11667: de skad smras pas thar pa g.yog dang bcas pa
NK063(gu)001:11668: yi rangs te e ma ho thabs la mkhas so
NK063(gu)001:11672: bdag thams cad du de la gnas so zhes gsol
NK063(gu)001:11673: pa ni gab pa'i gsang ba ma rtogs par sgra
NK063(gu)001:11674: ji lta ba de bzhin spyad pa las /
NK063(gu)001:11675: thar pa dge slong ni blo gros kyis nges pa
NK063(gu)001:11676: ma rnyed de sgra 'ba' zhig la phyogs pas so
NK063(gu)001:11677: // de las gzhan yang sbas pa'i gsang ba tan
NK063(gu)001:11678: gan la sogs la mngon par 'chel nas dngos po
NK063(gu)001:11679: bzhi kho nar spyad de zhen nas lus dam pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11680: cha byad du bcug nas sems ngan 'gro'i lam du
NK063(gu)001:11681: // zhugs so // dan 'bag ni gzhi'i don gyi
NK063(gu)001:11682: nges pa rnyed nas blo gros dam par 'brel te
NK063(gu)001:11683: don 'ba' zhig la phyogs pas ji bzhin pa kho
NK063(gu)001:11684: nar spyad de zhen nas yongs su rnal 'byor pas
NK063(gu)001:11685: // zhugs so // / lus ma rabs su gnas
NK063(gu)001:11686: kyang sems dam par nges pa'i lam du zhugs so
NK063(gu)001:11687: // zhugs so // / // de nas thar pa g.yog dang lta ba ma mthun te smras pa /
NK063(gu)001:11688: bdag cag dpon gcig la sgra gcig tu byung ba
NK063(gu)001:11689: 'di la so sor ma mthun pa 'di ji lta
NK063(gu)001:11690: ba zhig / dan 'bag gis smras pa /
NK063(gu)001:11691: bdag gis ni da ltar nges par 'jog pa 'di kho na las gzhan ma thos so //
NK063(gu)001:11692: smras pa bdag gis kyang nges pa rnyed de spyod
NK063(gu)001:11693: pa 'di kho na las gzhan ma thos so zhes
NK063(gu)001:11694: smras pas / rtsod pa chen por gyur te lta
NK063(gu)001:11695: ba ma mthun pas g.yog dang so sor bskal te
NK063(gu)001:11696: ma mthong ma 'phrad par dam bcas nas khams ring
NK063(gu)001:11698: de nas thar ba dge slong de mngon pa'i nga rgyal log pa'i ri bo skyes te /
NK063(gu)001:11699: dpon la so so'i nges pa rnyed pa gsol ba las /
NK063(gu)001:11700: dge slong thub dka' gzhon nu ni ma bcos ma bslad pa'i rnal mar spyod pas /
NK063(gu)001:11701: kha gsag med de rang bzhin gsong por smra bas
NK063(gu)001:11702: dan 'bag ltar nges so zhes bsgo bas thar pa
NK063(gu)001:11704: dpon du byas pa 'dra na gnyis ka ltar ro
NK063(gu)001:11705: zhes kyang ma bsnyad par nges par bdag bkar bcag
NK063(gu)001:11706: pa dang sun dbyung ba 'di byas pas /
NK063(gu)001:11707: dpon 'di yang khams 'dir ma chags par byas la
NK063(gu)001:11708: 'di dag bdag gis khams su bya'o zhes dam bcas
NK063(gu)001:11709: nas che ba'i nga rgyal skyes te dpon yang khams
NK063(gu)001:11710: ring por bshugs te spangs so //
NK063(gu)001:11711: de nas gzhan yang thar pas de pa'i gsung gi
NK063(gu)001:11712: sgo grangs mang zhing rgya che bar gyur bas thams
NK063(gu)001:11713: cad du ston pa la dpag par dka' ba'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:11714: yongs su ma chud de gzhal ba gnyis kyis gzhal
NK063(gu)001:11715: bar ma byas par thar pa rang gi nges pa
NK063(gu)001:11716: tshad ma la gzhan phyogs su drangs /
NK063(gu)001:11717: thams cad kyang log par bsgyur /
NK063(gu)001:11718: nyid kyang log pa'i rgya mtshor zhugs te /
NK063(gu)001:11719: log pa'i dka' thub drag po dang brtul zhugs chen
NK063(gu)001:11720: po la spyod pa ni rgyu dge sdig dang 'bras
NK063(gu)001:11721: bu bde sdug gi don la rmongs pas dang du
NK063(gu)001:11722: blang bya dang dor bya rnams mi shes pa ni
NK063(gu)001:11724: dur gyi mi ro dag blangs te kha zas su byin cing /
NK063(gu)001:11725: pags pa dag bshus te g.yang gzhir gyon nas longs spyod pa /
NK063(gu)001:11731: za byed dur phag la sogs pa gson ma mang
NK063(gu)001:11732: po bsten cing thams cad srog gcod cing sha khrag
NK063(gu)001:11733: la longs spyod par byed do //
NK063(gu)001:11734: smad 'tshong ma'i tshogs mang po bsdus te chags pa
NK063(gu)001:11735: chen po spyod pas dngos po bzhi las mi 'da'
NK063(gu)001:11736: zhing de'i rang bzhin gyis chos nyid de kho na
NK063(gu)001:11737: nyid las yongs su 'das par gyur to //
NK063(gu)001:11738: gnyis pa gol ba'i 'bras bu la yang rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu ni dmyal ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:11740: dang po ni de lta bu'i srid pa'i sa bon
NK063(gu)001:11741: rtsub mos ngan 'gro'i gnas su 'phangs nas sdug bsngal
NK063(gu)001:11743: de nas skye ba 'phos par gyur nas ce spyang
NK063(gu)001:11744: nag po la sogs pa dud 'gro'i skye ba rigs
NK063(gu)001:11746: de nas mtshams med pa rab tu tsha ba'i dmyal
NK063(gu)001:11747: ba zhes pa la sogs te dmyal ba'i skye ba
NK063(gu)001:11748: dagu'o // gnyis pa ni de nas rnam par smin
NK063(gu)001:11749: pa de zad pa dang yi dwags ltogs pa dang
NK063(gu)001:11750: skom pa'i sdug bsngal gyis nyen pa dang zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:11751: srul po'i bu ltog 'dod can la sogs pa skye
NK063(gu)001:11753: gnyis pa rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu skye ba nyi
NK063(gu)001:11754: shu rtsa lnga'i mtha' mar srin po'i lus blangs pa
NK063(gu)001:11755: ste / de la gnyis las skye ba blangs pa dngos ni /
