NK063(gu)001:11756: de ni las kyi sgrib pa zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:11757: yi dwags srin po zhes pa'i don ni /
NK063(gu)001:11758: de nyid las ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:11759: yul lang+ka pu ri zhes bya bar smad 'tshong ma
NK063(gu)001:11760: zhig gi mngal du chags te skye bar smin to
NK063(gu)001:11761: // de der skye ba blangs te zla ba dgu na ma shi bar gyur pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11762: mi gang de dag gi dwa bu lkog bu 'di
NK063(gu)001:11763: gso bar byar yul gang rme bar 'gyur bas ma'i
NK063(gu)001:11764: mchan du gzhag par rigs so zhes glengs nas /
NK063(gu)001:11765: dug shing nal bya zhes bya ba'i rtsa na dur phag gti mug gam tshang bcas pa'i bar na /
NK063(gu)001:11766: dug sprul zhe sdang gi 'khra sa byed pa /
NK063(gu)001:11767: rtse la 'dod chags bya'i tshang bcas pa'i rtsar /
NK063(gu)001:11768: kun gyi ma'i ro khang brtsigs te ro khyogs la
NK063(gu)001:11769: blangs nas der ba cug ste bu yang ma'i ro
NK063(gu)001:11771: dwa bu des ma'i ro la 'jus nas nu ma
NK063(gu)001:11772: la 'jibs pas chu ser du drangs te zhag bdun
NK063(gu)001:11774: de nas khrag tu 'jibs pas zhag bdun gyi 'tsho bas 'tsho bar byas so //
NK063(gu)001:11775: de nas nu ma gnyis zos pas zhag bcu'i 'tsho bas 'atsho'o //
NK063(gu)001:11776: de nas ma'i nang khrol zad par zos pas 'tsho ba'i bya bar gyur to //
NK063(gu)001:11777: de nas sha zad par zos pas zla ba bdun gyi 'tsho ba'i bya ba byas so //
NK063(gu)001:11778: de nas gzhon nu de brtas par gyur nas dur
NK063(gu)001:11779: khrod kyi ro rnams kyis 'tsho ba'i bya ba byas
NK063(gu)001:11780: so // de nas shin tu brtas par gyur pa
NK063(gu)001:11781: dang ro rnams zas su za zhing ro gos dang
NK063(gu)001:11782: pags pa rnams gyon te dur khrod kyi ma mo
NK063(gu)001:11783: dang sha za dang yi dwags dang mi ma lags
NK063(gu)001:11784: pa'i tshogs mang po yang mi ro rnams kyi sha
NK063(gu)001:11785: rjen par zos pas rang bzhin gyi mthus dbang du
NK063(gu)001:11786: so // 'dus te / dur khrod kyi gdug pa
NK063(gu)001:11787: can kun gyi bdag por gyur te gzhan gyi gzi
NK063(gu)001:11788: byin 'phrog pa'i mi gang dag gson por za zhing
NK063(gu)001:11789: mdangs 'phrog pa shin tu 'jigs pa'i gzugs can ma
NK063(gu)001:11791: ma'i sha rjen par zos pas na ma zan ma
NK063(gu)001:11792: tang ka zhes ming gang dag gis yongs su grags
NK063(gu)001:11793: so // gnyis pa de'i lus dang mthu'i mtshan nyid
NK063(gu)001:11794: ni rab tu gdug pa gtum po la sogs pa
NK063(gu)001:11795: ste mgo sna tshogs pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:11796: rdo rje phur pa'i rgyud las /
NK063(gu)001:11797: ma rungs srin po'i mgo bo bcu //
NK063(gu)001:11802: rta dang rnga mong sbrul dang ni //
NK063(gu)001:11803: phag dang spyang ki la sogs bcu'o //
NK063(gu)001:11805: de la sogs pa myos shing nyams par byed pa'i mthu ni /
NK063(gu)001:11807: mi dug gis phog pas 'chi bar nges pa drag
NK063(gu)001:11808: po'i sngags gzer bzlas par byas pas thams cad dbang
NK063(gu)001:11810: lus chen po la mdog thal kha sngo skyar 'dug pa khrag dang zhag gi thig les brgyan pa /
NK063(gu)001:11811: thod pa'i phreng ba se ral du thogs pa /
NK063(gu)001:11812: dmar po khrag gis brkus pa'i pags pa bgos pa /
NK063(gu)001:11813: thod skyogs khrag gi bkang ba rtag par 'thung ba /
NK063(gu)001:11814: sku ral pa kham nag 'bar zhing snyigs pa /
NK063(gu)001:11815: 'bru mar thod rus zas su za ba /
NK063(gu)001:11816: ba dang kro ta an dza nas lus brgyan pa /
NK063(gu)001:11817: bya'i gshog pa lus la byung bas nam mkha' la bya bzhin bya ba byed pa /
NK063(gu)001:11818: gcer bu thogs pa med pas chu la nya bzhin bya ba byed pa /
NK063(gu)001:11819: gang gis mthong ba'i mig rtsa rig rig dngangs shing brgyal bar byed pa /
NK063(gu)001:11820: lus phag gi spu can rtsub la yan lag sbrul du byung ba /
NK063(gu)001:11822: sen mo kang ka'i mchu sder du byung bas gang zin pa'i lus myags par byed pa /
NK063(gu)001:11823: sngon goms pa'i mthus lus can thams cad gsad par dmigs pa /
NK063(gu)001:11824: gang mo'i dbang po sdud par dmigs pa /
NK063(gu)001:11825: lus can mtha' dag hag dngangs te zil gyis mnan nas 'dar yed yed 'jog pa /
NK063(gu)001:11826: 'jig rten gyi ma mo dang 'byung po dang gnod
NK063(gu)001:11827: sbyin mthu can gyis phyag byas te gtso bor mthong
NK063(gu)001:11828: ba / gdug pa can mtha' dag mag pa dang
NK063(gu)001:11829: pho nya dang g.yog dang yang g.yog dang bran dang
NK063(gu)001:11830: yang bran du 'khol zhing kun la dbang bsgyur ba'i
NK063(gu)001:11831: dbang phyug chen por gyur to zhes pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11832: des nga rgyal gyi tshig sgrogs te /
NK063(gu)001:11835: e ma ho thams cad kyi dbang phyug chen po
NK063(gu)001:11836: ni bdag med na bdag las gzhan pa'i dbang phyug
NK063(gu)001:11837: dang phru ma yod na de yang bdag gir 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:11838: na bdag ni 'gran gyi zla med che btsan gcig
NK063(gu)001:11839: pur byung ngo // zhes sgrogs shing stong pa rgyun
NK063(gu)001:11840: chad la sogs log lta dgu la btsud cing thams
NK063(gu)001:11842: de nas srid pa gsum dbang du bsdus te klu'i
NK063(gu)001:11843: rigs dang zhes pa la sogs ni nyer gnyis pa
NK063(gu)001:11844: ltar srin po dang lha'i tshogs dang lha min g.yo
NK063(gu)001:11845: 'gul thams cad dbang du bsdus te de ltar log
NK063(gu)001:11846: pa'i lam du gyur pas byang chub kyi myu gu
NK063(gu)001:11847: chad de mun sros pa ltar gyur te zhes pa'o
NK063(gu)001:11848: // gnyis pa 'dul byed dpal chen po'i gleng gzhi
NK063(gu)001:11849: ni gzhung don gsum pa ji ltar 'dul thabs kyi
NK063(gu)001:11850: // phrin las te / de yang de sngon bsten
NK063(gu)001:11851: pa'i stobs kyis zhes pa la sogs mdor bstan pa
NK063(gu)001:11853: 'dir kha cig gsang sngags kyi theg pa 'di nye lam ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:11854: thar pa'i skye ba gcig gcig la yang bskal pa
NK063(gu)001:11855: dpag tu med cing mtha' ma btul ba'i bar de
NK063(gu)001:11856: srid du / dan 'bag ni rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11857: skyes bu zhes mthar lam la gnas pa'i phyir te
NK063(gu)001:11859: thar pa nag po gang yin pa ru trar smin par gyur pa de'i tshe /
NK063(gu)001:11860: gang thub dka' gzhon nu snying po byang chub gang
NK063(gu)001:11861: na der rdo rje sems dpa'i de bzhin nyid du
NK063(gu)001:11862: gyur to // dan 'bag gang yin pa de'i tshe
NK063(gu)001:11863: de'i dus na rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i skyes bu dam
NK063(gu)001:11864: pa rdo rje 'dzin pa zhes bya ba nyid du
NK063(gu)001:11865: gyur to zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11867: 'khrul pa'i blo 'di la mngon par zhen pa dag la bskal pa tshad las 'das par snang yang /
NK063(gu)001:11868: mthar lam gyi mnyam gzhag gi dgongs pa la ltos te thun gcig las med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11869: de ltar 'dul thabs kyi phrin las rgyas pa la ngag don gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:11870: gdul bya sngon du bya ba'i sbyor ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:11872: las kyi mjug gsang sngags kyi sgor zhugs nas 'bras bu dbang thob pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11873: dang po ni mdo chen po le'u nyer gsum pa ltar bdud btul ba'i cho 'phrul bskul ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:11874: nyer bzhi pa ltar 'dul bar bka' bgros bcad pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11875: nyer lnga pa ltar gang gis 'dul ba'i bka' bgros pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11876: nyer drug pa ltar las kyi bskos gdab pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:11877: de dag rgyud 'di'i mngon par rtogs pa'i dbang du
NK063(gu)001:11878: don gsum pa ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos
NK063(gu)001:11879: yin te / de la gzhung don bcu gnyis la
NK063(gu)001:11880: dang po ni de bzhin gshegs pa che ba'i rdo
NK063(gu)001:11881: rje bkod pa'i zhes pa la sogs rnams kyis khro
NK063(gu)001:11882: bo'i ting nge 'dzin ston pa'i phyir mngon rtogs ltar
NK063(gu)001:11885: ting nge 'dzin gsum bsgom pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11886: dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK063(gu)001:11887: las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin to //
NK063(gu)001:11889: ting nge 'dzin gsum po spyi'i rnam par gzhag pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11890: ting nge 'dzin gsum so so'i rang bzhin bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11892: rnam grangs gsum du nges pa'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK063(gu)001:11893: de dag gi go rim nges pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11894: ngo bo ji ltar bsgom pa'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK063(gu)001:11895: des mi mthun pa'i phyogs spang bya gang spong ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:11897: dang po ni shes bya'i chos thams cad bden pa
NK063(gu)001:11898: gsum du nges shing der gtan la phab nas de
NK063(gu)001:11899: nyams su len pa la ting nge 'dzin gsum du
NK063(gu)001:11901: gnyis pa ni de bzhin nyid dang por bsgom par nges te /
NK063(gu)001:11902: ting nge 'dzin phyi ma dag gi sgo 'byed cing bskyed pa'i rgyu'am gzhi yin pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:11903: ji skad du rim drug las /
NK063(gu)001:11904: don dam kun gyi rgyu yin phyir //
NK063(gu)001:11905: lhag pa'i rgyu de thog mar bsgom //
NK063(gu)001:11907: kun snang bar du bsgoms par nges te /
NK063(gu)001:11908: mtshams sbyor gyi ting nge 'dzin yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:11910: mtshams sbyor snying rje g.yo min pas //
NK063(gu)001:11911: de bzhin nyid kyi rjes su bstan //
NK063(gu)001:11913: rgyu ting ni phyi la bsgom par nges te /
NK063(gu)001:11914: ting nge 'dzin gsum du nges shing cig shos gnyis
NK063(gu)001:11915: dang po dang bar du bsgom par gsungs pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:11916: dang / gzhan yang rten gzhal yas khang dang brten pa lha bskyed pa'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11917: 'o na rgyu ting nge 'bras bu'i ting nge 'dzin du 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:11918: gong ma gnyis las skyes pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11920: don gzhan ting nge 'dzin snga ma las skyes pa'i
NK063(gu)001:11921: 'bras bu yin kyang don gzhan ting nge 'dzin phyi
NK063(gu)001:11922: ma bskyed pa'i rgyu yin te da ltar gyi sa
NK063(gu)001:11923: bon bzhin no // gsum pa ngo bo'am mtshan nyid gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:11926: de la rtsod pa spang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:11927: dang po ni kha cig de ting gi mtshan nyid stong pa nyid yin zer ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:11928: gzhan yang mi g.yo ba dang rtog med dang mi
NK063(gu)001:11929: dmigs pa la sogs pa rnams yin zer ba ni
NK063(gu)001:11931: dngos gzhi rdzogs rim la khyab ches pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11932: gnyis pa rang lugs ni rgyu shes par gtan la
NK063(gu)001:11933: phab pa'i don spros pa dang bral ba gang zhig
NK063(gu)001:11934: dran pa'i rdzas su gnas pa zhig yin te /
NK063(gu)001:11936: de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin gyis //
NK063(gu)001:11937: bla med 'bras bu thob pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:11938: spros dang bral ba'i mtshan nyid 'dzin //
NK063(gu)001:11940: gsum pa ni spros bral des dngos gzhi rdzogs rim la ma khyab bam khyab /
NK063(gu)001:11941: dang po ltar na rdzogs rim bsgoms pa la dgos pa med par thal te /
NK063(gu)001:11942: spros pa ma khegs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:11944: spros pa ma khegs na rdzogs rim don med du 'gyur bas khyab ste /
NK063(gu)001:11947: gnyis pa ltar na de gnyis kyi rnam dbye mi dgos par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:11948: khyab pas skyon dang po med la /
NK063(gu)001:11949: khyab med kyang de gnyis rnam dbye med par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:11950: dag pa'i snang ba bskyed rdzogs bsgom pa'i sngon du
NK063(gu)001:11951: ma dag pa'i blo 'jig rten rags pa'i rtog pa
NK063(gu)001:11952: 'joms pa'i phyir spros bral du bsgom pa ni de
NK063(gu)001:11953: ting yin la / dag pa bskyed rim gyi mtshan
NK063(gu)001:11954: ma'i nyes pa cung zad yod pa 'joms pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:11955: spros bral du bsgom pa ni mtshan med rdzogs rim
NK063(gu)001:11957: kun ting gi ngo bo ni de bzhin nyid ma
NK063(gu)001:11958: rtogs pa rgyu mtshan du byas nas sems can la
NK063(gu)001:11959: snying rje ma 'gags pa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:11960: rgyu ting gi ngo bo ni sems dbyer med kyi rnam pa yi ger gsal ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:11962: ting nge 'dzin dang pos sna tshogs zhen bcas kyi rtog pa spong zhing /
NK063(gu)001:11963: gnyis pas stong pa phyogs gcig la zhen pa spong la /
NK063(gu)001:11964: mtha' mas bden pa res 'jog gi rtog pa spong ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:11965: mtha' ma 'bras bu ni de gsum la goms pa
NK063(gu)001:11966: mthar phyin pa na sku gsum mngon du gyur pa'o
NK063(gu)001:11967: // de la kha cig 'og gi bskyed rdzogs rnams bsgom mi dgos par thal te /
NK063(gu)001:11968: sku gsum las lhag pa'i thob bya med cing de
NK063(gu)001:11969: ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis thob pa'i phyir zhe na
NK063(gu)001:11970: / spyir rgyus 'bras bu thob pa thams cad dngos
NK063(gu)001:11971: su thob pa dang brgyud pa'i sgo nas thob pa
NK063(gu)001:11972: / gnyis yin la / 'di phyi ma yin pa'i phyir khyab pa med pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:11973: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gsum so so'i rang bzhin ni lag len ltar brjod /
NK063(gu)001:11974: tshig gi sgo nas de dag gi rnam pa bsgom pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:11975: don gnyis pa dkyil 'khor bsgom pa la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:11979: dbang chen yum lnga'i dkyil 'khor ni rgyu ting las 'byung ba lnga'i sa bon gyi 'phro 'du yis /
NK063(gu)001:11985: kro ti'i shwa ri lnga'i mkha' dbyings su bsgom zhing de gsal gdab par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:11986: gnyis pa ni rgyu las gzhal yas kyi sa bon
NK063(gu)001:11987: 'phro 'du'i sgo nas khro dkyil mngon rtogs ltar bskyed
NK063(gu)001:11988: de le'u bcu bdun pa ltar gsal gdab pa yin
NK063(gu)001:11989: no // don gnyis pa brten pa lha bskyed pa la yang gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:11990: bdag sngon gyi sangs rgyas yin pa'i phyir bdag gi sras su de ba bya ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:11991: rigs mi nub cing lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i phyir de pa'i sras su bdag bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:11993: dgongs gzhi gang la dgongs pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11994: theg pa'i sgo gang dang bstun pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11995: rgyud kyi khungs gang nas btus pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11996: sbyang bya'am dpe 'jig rten gyi bslab gzhi gang dang mthun pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:11997: de rang gang zag gi nyams su blang na ji ltar blang ba'o /
NK063(gu)001:11999: gtso bo yab yum bskyed de mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs la rol pa bya ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:12000: byang chub sems las sprul pa spro ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:12001: sras kyi lha tshogs bskyed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12002: dang po ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:12003: zhugs te zhes pa'i bar gyis yab bskyed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12004: de yang rgyu ting dbus kyi gdan thog tu phab
NK063(gu)001:12005: ste 'phro 'du'i sbyor ba las sngags dang bskyed tshig
NK063(gu)001:12006: gis bskul zhing gsal gdab pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:12008: de bzhin nyid kyi zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:12009: sprin las zhes pa'i bar yum bskyed pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:12010: yab kyi thugs ka'i sa bon las g.yon phyogs su chad de sngags kyis bskyed la gsal gdab pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12011: gnyis pa byang sems las sprul pa spro ba ni
NK063(gu)001:12012: gzhung don gsum pa ste h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:12013: nas / brjod pas zhes pa sbyor mtshams nas byang
NK063(gu)001:12014: sems las khro bo'i sprul pa phyogs bcur spros pa'o
NK063(gu)001:12015: nas / // gzhung don bzhi pa ni 'jig rten drug gi zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:12016: 'thon par gyur pas zhes pa'i bar ni sprul pa
NK063(gu)001:12017: de dag gi grangs dang che chung gi tshad do
NK063(gu)001:12019: de dag gis 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad g.yos pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:12020: de ltar sa g.yo ba la le'u bzhi pa ltar
NK063(gu)001:12021: bzhi las 'di de pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis so
NK063(gu)001:12022: // de yang phyi ltar gzhung rang lugs la /
NK063(gu)001:12023: nang du lam pa'i sems nyams dang sbyor ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:12024: gzhung don drug pa ni des 'jig rten drug gi
NK063(gu)001:12025: phyogs bcu'i gdug pa can thams cad brgyal ba la
NK063(gu)001:12026: sogs pa ni bsgral zhing btul bas tshar bcad par
NK063(gu)001:12027: gyur to // gsum pa sras kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:12028: gtso bo rigs lnga yab yum dang /
NK063(gu)001:12029: ngo mtshar tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12030: dang po rigs lnga yab yum bskyed pa la gzhung
NK063(gu)001:12031: don bdun pa nas bcu gcig pa'i bar lnga las
NK063(gu)001:12032: / dang po ni de nas bcom ldan zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:12033: bzhugs so zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK063(gu)001:12034: gnyis pa ni de nas grags pa chen po zhes pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:12035: rngam mo zhes pa'i bar ni rdo rje srin po la dmag gsar ba'i tshul te /
NK063(gu)001:12036: ji skad du nyer bdun pa las /
NK063(gu)001:12037: dbang phyug chen po rnams shin tu dngas shing 'khrugs te rngams nas rong rong por gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:12038: mya ngan gyi dug lo 'tshubs pa bzhin bdud kyi phru mar 'dus te bdud kyi ru mtshon phyar /
NK063(gu)001:12040: bdud kyi sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba bkram te /
NK063(gu)001:12041: bswo dang cha'i sgra bsgrags te sbags pa las zhes pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:12043: ngag don gnyis pa bdud btul ba dngos yin te /
NK063(gu)001:12045: de nas bcom ldan 'das dbu dgu zhes pa he ru ka dbu klong rngams pa'i rtags so //
NK063(gu)001:12046: ji skad du bla ma las /
NK063(gu)001:12047: dbu gsum dang por byung ba ni //
NK063(gu)001:12048: g.yas dkar g.yo dmar dbus mthing nag /
NK063(gu)001:12049: rnam par thar pa'i dbu gsum la /
NK063(gu)001:12050: khams gsum mya ngan 'das pa'i zhal //
NK063(gu)001:12051: dbu gsum bar pa rngams pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:12052: g.yas sngo g.yon ljang dbus mthing zhal //
NK063(gu)001:12053: thabs dang shes rab sems kyi dbu //
NK063(gu)001:12054: srid gsum dbyings su thongs pa'i zhal //
NK063(gu)001:12055: dbu gsum tha ma rngams pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:12056: g.yas mthing g.yon mthing dbus mthing zhal /
NK063(gu)001:12057: khams gsum re ba skong ba yi //
NK063(gu)001:12058: lung dang man ngag sems kyi dbu //
NK063(gu)001:12059: 'gyur ba med pa'i mthing nag zhal //
NK063(gu)001:12061: phyag bco brgyad ces pa ni sgrol byed kyi ging bco brgyad kyi phyir te phyag mtshan yang /
NK063(gu)001:12063: bco brgyad phyag na bsnams pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:12064: rdo rje glo ni zhing chung g.yas //
NK063(gu)001:12065: b+han+d+ha zhing dbyug snying phyung g.yon //
NK063(gu)001:12066: rgyu zhags nyi ma khyung chen g.yas //
NK063(gu)001:12067: zhing chen zla ba 'ug pa g.yon //
NK063(gu)001:12068: me dang rgya mtsho 'ug pa g.yas //
NK063(gu)001:12069: rlung dang rin chen ri rab g.yon //
NK063(gu)001:12070: yon tan bco brgyad dbyings su rdzogs //
NK063(gu)001:12072: yang na g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis rdo rje mdung dmar la /
NK063(gu)001:12073: g.yas kyi 'og ma brgyad ma mo brgyad dang /
NK063(gu)001:12074: g.yon gyi 'og ma brgyad phra men brgyad pa snams pa yang yin no //
NK063(gu)001:12075: zhabs brgyad du gnas nas zhes pa ni tshad med
NK063(gu)001:12076: bzhi dang phrin las bzhis don mdzad pa'i phyir te
NK063(gu)001:12078: zhabs brgyad lha chen bardzisa pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:12079: bsam gtan bla na med pa yis //
NK063(gu)001:12080: nga rgyal can rnams tshar gcad do //
NK063(gu)001:12082: h+aum h+aum h+aum la sogs gsum gsum ni 'dul byed kyi dbang du sku gsung thugs la /
NK063(gu)001:12083: gdul bya'i dbang du sgo gsum mam dug gsum du zhen pa kun bsgral zhing btul ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:12084: sha khrag rus pa'i tshogs rnams lte ba chos kyi dbyings su sbyangs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12085: bzhi pa ni de nas h+aum h+aum zhes pa dang
NK063(gu)001:12086: srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo zhes pa nas
NK063(gu)001:12087: / 'khor zhing gi rdul snyed kyang bsdus so zhes pa'i bar te /
NK063(gu)001:12088: 'di dag phyi srin mo'i tshul dang /
NK063(gu)001:12090: gsang ba mkha' 'gro'i tshul las 'di mtha' ma'o //
NK063(gu)001:12091: lnga pa ni de nas bcom ldan 'das zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:12092: la sogs te de ltar gtso bo ru dra la
NK063(gu)001:12094: mdzad pa mthar dbyung ba'i phyir mo rnams la sbyar ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:12095: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po rdo rje'i sku la zhes pa la sogs ni /
NK063(gu)001:12097: rigs la lnga lnga 'khril zhes pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:12098: gtso bo la phyogs kyi dbang mo bzhi dang sgom bzhi ste brgyad dang /
NK063(gu)001:12099: rigs bzhi la phyogs kyi lhag ma lnga lnga'o //
NK063(gu)001:12100: 'o na de dag dang re mos rol lam /
NK063(gu)001:12102: mdun rgyab zur gnyis dbu gsum dang /
NK063(gu)001:12103: mdun la sogs gtso mo bdun gyis 'khril zhes pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:12104: dus gcig tu rol zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:12106: de pa'i snang ba nas sbyor ba'i rtog pa med la /
NK063(gu)001:12107: ma mo'i snang ba nas de pa re re dang sbyor bar snang ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:12109: ma mo re re yang de pa re re dang sbyar bar mthong ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:12111: don gnyis pa ngo mtshar tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed
NK063(gu)001:12112: pa ni gzhung don bcu gnyis pa'i mtha' ma ste
NK063(gu)001:12114: dang po ni de nas dgyes te zhes pa la sogs te /
NK063(gu)001:12115: rgyu de ltar rol pa'i byang sems las rkyen ha zhes pa brgyad brjod pas /
NK063(gu)001:12117: dkar mo'i zhes pa ni ke'u r+ai ma ste /
NK063(gu)001:12118: de ni dpal chen po'i thugs yang dag pa las snang ba'i phyir dkar mo zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:12120: mi'i dbang du de dag re re'ang nyer brgyad kyi phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:12121: de rnams thugs ye shes su gcig pa'i phyir rigs gcig gcig tu bsdus nas 'god pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:12122: de ltar 'og mar rnams kyang shes par bya zhing gsum car gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:12123: 'dir sras kyi dkyil 'khor gnas yul sgo ma 'di
NK063(gu)001:12124: rnams dbang mo dang rol pa las bskyed pa dang
NK063(gu)001:12125: / sgrub thabs nas rigs kyi yum dang rol pa
NK063(gu)001:12126: las bskyed par 'dod pa gnyis 'gal lo zhe na
NK063(gu)001:12128: 'dir dregs pa can bsgral zhing de'i 'khor mo rnams
NK063(gu)001:12129: dbang du bsdus te sbyor ba ni thabs chen po'i
NK063(gu)001:12130: tan gan gyi che ba dbyung ba'i dgos pa yod
NK063(gu)001:12131: pa'i phyir dbang mo dang rol la //
NK063(gu)001:12132: don gyis 'dir yang ye shes kyi yum dang rol pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:12134: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nas /
NK063(gu)001:12136: yang btsun mo khrag 'thung chen mo'i mtshan nyid rnams
NK063(gu)001:12137: so so'i sku la 'khril pa'i tshul gyis bzhugs so
NK063(gu)001:12139: yang 'dir ma dbang mo nyer brgyad la bu mo
NK063(gu)001:12140: nyi shu las ma byung ba ni nyung bar 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:12141: ro zhe na / ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:12142: tshogs dang bcas pa mi'i dbang du na re re yang nyer brgyad nyer brgyad de /
NK063(gu)001:12143: brgya phrag lnga dang bcu phrag drug yod la /
NK063(gu)001:12144: dkyil 'khor du 'god pa'i tshe de dag thugs ye
NK063(gu)001:12145: shes su gcig pa'i phyir rigs re rer bsdus nas
NK063(gu)001:12147: gzhung don bzhi'i tha ma de ltar btul ba'i 'bras bu ni /
NK063(gu)001:12148: ngag don tha ma 'bras bu dbang thob pa ste de la bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:12150: de nas zhes pa nas dus gcig tu btul lo zhes pa'i don ni //
NK063(gu)001:12151: sngon du gtso bo dang 'khor gyis 'gyod pa'i sgo nas rgyud sbyangs te /
NK063(gu)001:12152: de nas dkyil 'khor du bcug cing zhugs pa'i sgo nas /
NK063(gu)001:12153: 'bras bu dbang bskur ba dngos ni /
NK063(gu)001:12155: am zhes pa'i bar ni dam rdzas rlon sbyor gyis
NK063(gu)001:12156: zab mo'i dbang bskur ba ste sngon byung gi dbang
NK063(gu)001:12157: yin no // gnyis pa gzhung brtag go //
NK063(gu)001:12158: gsum pa'i ma dang sring mo bu rnams so //
NK063(gu)001:12159: dkyil 'khor chen por bzhes su gsol //
NK063(gu)001:12160: zhes phul nas dkyil 'khor gyi mu ran la bkod cing lhag ma sbyin par gsungs pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:12162: dbus su mchis skal mi ldan gyis //
NK063(gu)001:12164: phud la 'tshal skal mi ldan gyis //
NK063(gu)001:12165: lhag ma'i zhal chab sbron la gsol //
NK063(gu)001:12167: de dag gis kyang dam bcas pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:12169: ming tsam 'dzin par byed pa yang //
NK063(gu)001:12170: gtsug gi nor bu 'bar ba ltar //
NK063(gu)001:12171: zhes pa la sogs ni rnal 'byor pa la de dag gis mthong ltas gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:12172: rab la lha'am klu'i dbang po'i gtsug gi nor bu
NK063(gu)001:12173: la gang gis kyang 'tshe bar mi nus shing ji
NK063(gu)001:12174: srid 'tshe ba byas na de nyid brlag par 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:12175: ba ltar / rnal 'byor pa lta sgom gdengs su
NK063(gu)001:12176: gyur pa'i phrin las de dag gis rang bzhin gyi
NK063(gu)001:12178: 'bring la rje dpon dbang po che'i gzi brjid bran gyis mi bzod pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:12179: rnal 'byor pa lha'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i gzi brjid mi bzod de /
NK063(gu)001:12180: pho nya dang mngag gzhug gi las thams cad byed do //
NK063(gu)001:12181: tha ma ni rje dpon yang bran nam spyan 'dren
NK063(gu)001:12182: ngo che ba'i bsnyen bkur la 'byon zhing bskul ba
NK063(gu)001:12183: ltar / rnal 'byor pa yang lta sgom sngags la
NK063(gu)001:12184: sogs pa'i mthu dang mi ldan yang dam tshig bsrung
NK063(gu)001:12185: zhing mthun pa'i dam rdzas tshang ba'i sgo nas cho
NK063(gu)001:12186: ga dag par bskul nas las la 'jug pa yin
NK063(gu)001:12187: ltar / te / de dag gis sngon rgyal ba'i spyan sngar dam bcas pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:12188: de dag thams cad dang mi ldan par las la
NK063(gu)001:12189: bskul na slar rnal 'byor pa de nyid la bka'
NK063(gu)001:12190: chad kyi gnas su 'gyur ro zhes gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)001:12192: le don gnyis pa 'khor gyi mkha' 'gro dam la
NK063(gu)001:12193: btags te dbang rdzas lag tu rdo rje 'byin nas
NK063(gu)001:12194: rang rang gi khyo la grags pa'i ming gis dbang
NK063(gu)001:12195: bskur te / dbang rtags su lcags kyi rdo rje
NK063(gu)001:12196: rtse gsum pa res dbu brgyan cing dkyil 'khor gyi
NK063(gu)001:12198: da ni 'di ltar bsam par bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:12199: le'u bco lnga pa'i gzhung 'dir gsungs pa'i ru tra zhes bya ba 'di rang rgyud pa zhig gam /
NK063(gu)001:12200: 'on te sprul pa ba zhig yin /
NK063(gu)001:12201: dang po ltar na lung dang rig pa gnyis kyis gnod de /
NK063(gu)001:12204: dbu dgu brgya phyag stong brgyad brgya sku 'bar ba
NK063(gu)001:12205: chen pa'i dkyil 'kho na bzhugs par mthong ngo zhes
NK063(gu)001:12206: snang byed thob pas bshad pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:12207: gzhan yang 'di'i lung ji lta bar ston pa /
NK063(gu)001:12208: mdo chen po'i nyer gcig pa las /
NK063(gu)001:12209: gsang ba mchog gi bdag yin pas //
NK063(gu)001:12212: 'gro ba'i tshul du mngon byung ba //
NK063(gu)001:12213: zhes 'gro ba dang tshul mthun par sprul par bshad pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:12215: bdag ni rdo rje mngon du dbang bskur bas //
NK063(gu)001:12216: sangs rgyas kun gyis de nyid bdag dbang bskur //
NK063(gu)001:12217: bcom ldan thams cad mchog ni bdag lags te //
NK063(gu)001:12218: zhes pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bdag nyid du bshad pa dang 'gal zhing /
NK063(gu)001:12219: gzhan yang mdo mya ngan las 'das pa las /
NK063(gu)001:12220: de'i tshe bdud sdig to can ni gzhan du ma
NK063(gu)001:12221: rtog cig ces pa de yang sprul par bshad pa
NK063(gu)001:12222: dang mtshungs so // rig pa ni mtshams med lnga
NK063(gu)001:12223: spyo pa la sogs sgrib pa gang che ba des
NK063(gu)001:12224: rgyal ba'i sku mthong zhing gsung thos par 'gyur te
NK063(gu)001:12225: dang mtshungs so // / gsang sngags kyi dam tshig
NK063(gu)001:12226: nyams pa las byung ba'i ru tra des rgyud ma
NK063(gu)001:12227: sbyangs par rgyal ba'i sku mthong zhing gsung thos pa'i
NK063(gu)001:12228: dang mtshungs so // / phyir ro // rtags gzhung gis grub la /
NK063(gu)001:12229: khyab pa med na dam tshig nyams pa dang mtshams
NK063(gu)001:12230: med lnga spyad pa gnyis rgyu mtshan mtshungs pa la
NK063(gu)001:12231: / gcig gis rgyal ba'i sku mthong zhing gsung thos la /
NK063(gu)001:12232: kha cig gis de mthong zhing thos par mi 'gyur ba la rgyu mtshan ci yang med do //
NK063(gu)001:12233: thal 'gyur 'dod par yang mi nus so //
NK063(gu)001:12234: yang gnyis pa ltar na lung rig gnyis kyis gnod de /
NK063(gu)001:12237: bdag tu rmongs pa'i rtog pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:12238: btags pa la mngon par zhen pa dang zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:12239: la sogs rgyu mtshan gsum gyis rgyu byas par gsungs
NK063(gu)001:12240: pa dang / gzhan yang mdo chen po'i nyi shu
NK063(gu)001:12241: pa'i mtshan las ma dag pa'i skye rgyud bstan pa
NK063(gu)001:12244: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ltar //
NK063(gu)001:12245: da lta dus 'di nyid du byung //
NK063(gu)001:12246: zhes sngar sprul pa byung ba ltar da lta rang rgyud pa byung bar mngon pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:12248: stong pa rgyun chad du gyur te mthar zad pa sha stag go //
NK063(gu)001:12250: 'di nyid nas nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhis 'debs par
NK063(gu)001:12251: byed pa la sogs ni sprul pa pa'i mdzad pa
NK063(gu)001:12254: 'og gi phyogs kyi 'jig rten thal bas khebs pa
NK063(gu)001:12255: zhes bya bar 'tshang rgya bar lung bstan pa thob
NK063(gu)001:12257: da lta'i bskal pa 'di'i yun du dge bsnyen legs
NK063(gu)001:12258: ldan nag po zhes bya bar gyur nas rnal 'byor
NK063(gu)001:12259: ba'i chos srung bar byed la /
NK063(gu)001:12260: bskal pa phyi ma la thal ba'i dbang po dbyangs
NK063(gu)001:12261: zhes bya bar 'tshang rgya bar lung bstan pa dang
NK063(gu)001:12262: 'gal zhing / gzhan yang mdo sde nas bshad pa'i
NK063(gu)001:12263: rigs ngan gyi bu mtshon cha'i 'khor lo can la
NK063(gu)001:12264: sogs pa sdig pa'i 'bras bu ngan song gi sdug
NK063(gu)001:12265: bsngal myong ba thams cad kyang sprul par 'gyur la
NK063(gu)001:12266: 'gal zhing / / de 'dod na rang rgyud pa mi rnyed do //
NK063(gu)001:12267: rig pa'i gnod byed kyang yod de /
NK063(gu)001:12268: mtshams med pa lnga la sogs pa spyad pa'i 'bras
NK063(gu)001:12269: bu ngan song gi sems can thams cad kyang sprul
NK063(gu)001:12271: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig nyasama pa las byung ba'i ru tra 'di sprul pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:12272: rtags khas blangs shing khyab pa med na /
NK063(gu)001:12273: dam tshig nyams pa dang mtshams med spyad pa gnyis
NK063(gu)001:12274: 'bras bu sdug bsngal du smin par mtshungs pa la
NK063(gu)001:12275: / gcig sprul pa yin zhing gcig de ma yin
NK063(gu)001:12276: pa'i rgyu mtshan ci yang med la 'dod par yang
NK063(gu)001:12278: de'i lan la snga rabs pa kha cig gzhung gis
NK063(gu)001:12279: gnyis car gsal ba'i phyir phyogs gnyis ka khas blangs
NK063(gu)001:12280: nas skyon brjod rnams gcig gis gcig spong par byed
NK063(gu)001:12281: zer ba ni 'thad pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:12282: spyir dang sprul gnyis su yod kyis kyang gzhung 'di
NK063(gu)001:12283: nas bshad pa'i ru tra zhes bya ba shes rgyud
NK063(gu)001:12284: gcig gis bsdus pa 'di gnyis car yin par 'gal
NK063(gu)001:12285: ba'i phyir ro // yang kha cig rang rgyud pa
NK063(gu)001:12286: yin na 'jigs byed chen po rigs lnga las gcig
NK063(gu)001:12287: tu bsdus te dregs pa can bsgral pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:12288: yang gcig las lngar snang ste mo rnams la sbyar
NK063(gu)001:12289: te sras kyi tshogs bskyed pas sprul pa yin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:12290: phyir rang rgyud par 'gal zer ba ni 'thad pa
NK063(gu)001:12291: ma yin te / sangs rgyas sprul pa yin pas
NK063(gu)001:12292: ru tra rang rgyud pa ma yin par mi 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:12293: ma yin te / ba'i phyir ro // yang de
NK063(gu)001:12294: la kha cig sangs rgyas la ru trar bshad pa
NK063(gu)001:12295: mi 'thad ces rtsod pa'i lan mnyam sbyor gyi lung
NK063(gu)001:12296: drangs nas lan 'debs pa ni dris lan gnyis ka
NK063(gu)001:12298: gdul bya rang rgyud pa yin pas 'dul byed der mi 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:12299: 'o na ji ltar zhe na 'di slob dpon rngo mdos sprul par bsgrubs te /
NK063(gu)001:12300: de la gong gi gnod byed rnams lung gi dgongs pa gzhan yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:12301: rig pas gnod par mi 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:12302: 'di ltar le'u nyi shu pa'i mtshan yang sprul pas
NK063(gu)001:12303: gdul bya'i ngo la ma dag pa'i skye ba blangs
NK063(gu)001:12304: pa ltar bstan pa yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:12305: nyer bzhi pa nas 'das pa'i dus su sprul pa
NK063(gu)001:12306: byung ba ltar phyis sprul pa 'byung ba ma bkag
NK063(gu)001:12307: la / nyer gcig pa'i log lta dgu yang mu
NK063(gu)001:12308: stegs la sogs pa de dag la zhen pa rnams
NK063(gu)001:12309: la de dag tu bstan nas bkri zhing drang ba
NK063(gu)001:12311: so gcig pa'i ma 'ongs pa'i dus su 'tshang rgya bar lung bstan pa yang /
NK063(gu)001:12312: sprul pa nyid bskal pa 'di'i yun du srung ma
NK063(gu)001:12313: mdzad pa ni bstan pa'i che ba dbyung ba yin
NK063(gu)001:12314: la lung yang gdul bya'i ngo la bstan pa yin
NK063(gu)001:12315: te / ji skad du de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:12316: bcom ldan thams cad mchog ni bdag lags te //
NK063(gu)001:12317: zhes sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bdag nyid du bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:12318: rig pas gsang sngags kyi dam tshig nyams pa las
NK063(gu)001:12319: byung ba'i ru tra 'di sprul pa yin na thun
NK063(gu)001:12320: mong gi mtshams med pa lnga la sogs pa sdig
NK063(gu)001:12321: pa'i 'bras bu ngan song du ltung ba thams cad
NK063(gu)001:12322: sprul par 'gyur ba ni bden mod kyi /
NK063(gu)001:12323: 'dir dam tshig nyams par ma grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:12324: de'i tshul du bstan pa tsam yin pa'i phyir 'go mi mtshungs so //
NK063(gu)001:12325: zhes sprul pa bar bzhed par rang nyid kyang de'i rjes su 'brangs pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:12326: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u bco lnga pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12329: brten pa lha bskyed pa la gnyis yod pa'i rigs
NK063(gu)001:12330: mi nub cing lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:12331: de pa'i sras su bdag bya ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:12332: de la yang gong ltar lnga ste /
NK063(gu)001:12337: de rang nyams su blang na ji ltar blang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:12340: chos kun byang chub sems su gcig par thim pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:12341: cho ga gsum gyis gtso bo yab yum bskyed de mkha' gsang brlabs la rol pa bya ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:12342: yum gyi mkhar lha bskyed cing gdon pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:12343: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i yon tan dang /
NK063(gu)001:12345: dkyil 'khor gyi tshad dam che ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:12346: dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12348: bdag rgyu'i he ru ka srin po phrug gu'i cha
NK063(gu)001:12349: byad lta bu tshon gang ba gcig gtso bo'i thugs
NK063(gu)001:12351: shar gyi sgo nas thal mo sbyar long bu sprad
NK063(gu)001:12352: tsog tsog pur 'dug ste bskul tshig brjod pas sgrib
NK063(gu)001:12353: pa sbyongs la rigs nges pa'i sras su bskyed cig
NK063(gu)001:12356: lha sum cu po sku gsung thugs kyi gnas sam
NK063(gu)001:12357: sbyor mtshams nas 'bru gsum 'od dang bcas pa 'phros
NK063(gu)001:12358: pas / gong gi rgyu'i he ru ka'i sgrib pa
NK063(gu)001:12359: sbyangs pas bdag gi sems gser ram dngul zhun ma
NK063(gu)001:12360: ltar dkar lteng lteng gnas pa las /
NK063(gu)001:12361: 'bru gsum 'phros pas sku gsung thugs mi zad pa
NK063(gu)001:12362: rgyan gyi 'khor lor gyur nas byang sems de h+aum
NK063(gu)001:12363: mthing nag gcig tu gsal ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:12364: a yam zhes pas de'i 'og tu yam las rlung gis zla ba h+aum dang bcas pa bteg ste /
NK063(gu)001:12365: g.yas phyogs nas lha rnams la spyi'am bye brag tu
NK063(gu)001:12366: lan gsum bskor ba byas nas gtso bo'i thugs kar
NK063(gu)001:12367: thim pas / yab yum gyi rgyud bskul te rol pa'i bde bas 'od du zhu /
NK063(gu)001:12368: des 'khor thams cad kyang zhu zhing dbus su 'dus
NK063(gu)001:12369: te 'od phung du gnas pa las tshig gis bskul
NK063(gu)001:12372: de nas 'od phung de gsung yig 'bru'i cho ga h+aum mthing nag gcig tu gyur /
NK063(gu)001:12373: de las 'od 'phros shing 'dus pas thugs phyag mtshan rdo rje mthing nag nas 'bras tsam du'o //
NK063(gu)001:12374: de las 'od kyi 'phro 'dus sku phra mo tshon gang bar ro //
NK063(gu)001:12375: de'i 'phro 'du las yab yum rags pa gong ltar
NK063(gu)001:12376: bskyed cing gsal btab nas mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs
NK063(gu)001:12377: te rol pa'o // bzhi pa ni de ltar rol
NK063(gu)001:12378: pa'i byang sems las gzhal yas khang yum gyi mkha'
NK063(gu)001:12379: te rol pa'o // la bskyed / yang 'phros pas gdan bsam /
NK063(gu)001:12380: yang 'phros pas mkha'i dkyil 'khor der lha sum cu tshang bar bskyed de /
NK063(gu)001:12381: de dag gdon pa la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)001:12382: bskyed pa rnams phyi rol tu gdon pa dngos dang /
NK063(gu)001:12383: zhor la dbang mo rig pa las bskyed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12385: gtso bo rigs lnga yab yum dang /
NK063(gu)001:12388: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta la sogs pa la mngon rtogs sbyar ba'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:12390: bsgyur ba'i sgra las 'dir ma h+aa na chen po la sogs pa ni tha ma'o //
NK063(gu)001:12391: sh+r+ai he ru ka zhes pa la 'jug pa'i sgra
NK063(gu)001:12392: mang du yod mod kyang nges par dkon cog 'grel
NK063(gu)001:12393: nas sh+r+ai ni dpal zhes so //
NK063(gu)001:12394: he ni he he kri ra tha zhes pa ni spyod pa zhes pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12395: ru ni ru ti rak+ta ni khrag gi sgra'o //
NK063(gu)001:12396: ka ni bdag po'i rkyen gyis de la rol pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:12397: mdor na spyod pas dpal khrag 'thung zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:12398: yang na ka ni ka p+aa la ste thod pa
NK063(gu)001:12399: khrag gis bkang ba la rol pa'i he ru zhes
NK063(gu)001:12400: bya'o // de ltar sngags kyis bskyed cing gdon pa
NK063(gu)001:12401: la 'dir kha cig dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo rnam
NK063(gu)001:12402: bya'o // snang yin la / khro bo ni bud+d+ha he ru ka yin te /
NK063(gu)001:12403: ji skad du rngam glog las /
NK063(gu)001:12404: dbus kyi pho brang snying po las //
NK063(gu)001:12405: rnam par snang mdzad phyag rgya che //
NK063(gu)001:12406: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir zhes zer ba ltar ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:12407: rgyu mtshan ni 'di dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo la
NK063(gu)001:12408: mtshan du btags pa rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul
NK063(gu)001:12409: d+r+wa ba zhes bya ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:12410: rdo rje sems dpa' gtso bo yin par ma grub ce na /
NK063(gu)001:12413: rdo rje sems dpa' dkyil nyid de //
NK063(gu)001:12414: rigs bzhi lha dang lha mo 'khor //
NK063(gu)001:12416: yang kha cig zhi ba rnams thugs kyis 'dul ba'i phyir thugs rdo rje'i rigs gtso bo'i byung la /
NK063(gu)001:12417: khro bo rnams sku yis 'dul ba'i phyir sku bud+d+ha
NK063(gu)001:12418: he ru ka gtso bor byung ba yin zer yang
NK063(gu)001:12419: / bla ma gong ma'i bzhed kyis zhi ba gang
NK063(gu)001:12420: yin pa khro bor gnas gyur pa'i phyir 'og nas
NK063(gu)001:12421: badz+ra he ru len cing gtso bor mdzad do //
NK063(gu)001:12422: le'u bcu bdun pa'i gdan dang sku mdog la sogs kyang des shes par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:12423: lung gi shes byed kyang yod de /
NK063(gu)001:12424: rgya che 'grel pa las ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:12425: rgyud 'khrugs pa tshig sbas pa'i dbang du'o zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:12426: de ltar badz+ra he ru ka yab yum gyi sngags
NK063(gu)001:12427: kyis de mkha'i gzhal yas kyi dbus nas phyung nas
NK063(gu)001:12428: phyi rol gyi bdag nyid gtso bo yab yum dang
NK063(gu)001:12430: de ltar rigs bzhi po ni gsang ba nas phyung
NK063(gu)001:12431: ste phyi rol gyi gnas ga na bar dgod par
NK063(gu)001:12432: bya'o // gnyis pa 'khor gdon pa la gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:12434: badz+ra koo ri ha zhes pa la sogs gnas kyi
NK063(gu)001:12435: ma mo brgyad mkha'i nang nas phyung ba rnams phyi
NK063(gu)001:12436: rol gyi der 'god pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:12437: gnyis pa ni badz+ra seng ha mu kh+aa he la
NK063(gu)001:12438: sogs yul gyi phra men ma rnams kyang de ltar
NK063(gu)001:12439: la / gsum pa badz+ra ar+ya te dza la sogs
NK063(gu)001:12440: sgo ma rnams kyang de ltar bskyed cing gdon pa'o
NK063(gu)001:12441: la / // de yang 'di rnams la mda' dang
NK063(gu)001:12442: glan na lag len ltar lha re re 'don zhing
NK063(gu)001:12444: skyo yang khyed ni rigs lnga la sogs tshan tshan du gdon zhing spro bsdu byas te 'god do //
NK063(gu)001:12445: dbang mo rnams la kha cig /
NK063(gu)001:12446: ji skad du rgya mtsho las /
NK063(gu)001:12447: b+h+yo ni las byed ma mo ste //
NK063(gu)001:12448: las kyi mkha' 'gro thig ler chags //
NK063(gu)001:12449: zhes pas mkha' nas 'don par yang mngon zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:12451: byi mo yin pa'i phyir mkha' las mi 'don te b+h+yo las chu bur ltar bskyed par 'dod do //
NK063(gu)001:12453: le'u dgu pa nas sa la sogs dang zhes pa ltar la /
NK063(gu)001:12454: drug pa ni le'u bcu bdun pa nas smug nag sngo nag la sogs sku mdog dang /
NK063(gu)001:12455: stong gi 'jig rten la sogs phyag mtshan dang /
NK063(gu)001:12456: ko rlon gos ni la sogs rgyan chas dang /
NK063(gu)001:12457: dbu gsum phyag drug la sogs zhal phyag dang /
NK063(gu)001:12461: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad 'bar ba'i
NK063(gu)001:12462: dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal bar gyur to zhes pa'i
NK063(gu)001:12463: don no // mtha' ma ni sngags le'u bdun pa
NK063(gu)001:12464: ltar la mngon rtogs khro bor bsgyur ba yin no
NK063(gu)001:12465: don no // // da ni mngon par rtogs pa'i
NK063(gu)001:12466: dbang du ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos la
NK063(gu)001:12467: gsum du byas pa'i mtha' ma /
NK063(gu)001:12468: le'u 'di'i gzhung don gyi dbang du don gnyis pa las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK063(gu)001:12472: mchod bshags bya zhing smon lam gdab pa'i rim pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12473: dang po la gzhung don zung gsum ya drug las /
NK063(gu)001:12474: dang po ni b+hi sha mi tra'i gzhung las /
NK063(gu)001:12475: mnyes dka' ma yin bkur gnas phyir //
NK063(gu)001:12476: 'jig rten dbang po'i chos lugs kyis //
NK063(gu)001:12478: dper na 'jig rten gyi dbang po ni rgyal po
NK063(gu)001:12479: lta bu spyan 'dren pa la snyan gsan dbab pa
NK063(gu)001:12480: la sogs tshul dang mthun par bya dgos te /
NK063(gu)001:12481: de ltar ma byas na ko long du 'gyur ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:12482: 'dir ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor ni de ltar mnyes
NK063(gu)001:12483: par dka' ba ste ko long can lta bu ma
NK063(gu)001:12484: yin yang / dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor gyis sri
NK063(gu)001:12485: zhu gus pa'i sgo nas tshul mthun zhing ye shes
NK063(gu)001:12486: kyi dkyil 'khor bkur gnas su bya ba'i phyir snyan
NK063(gu)001:12487: gsan phab nas spyan drang ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:12488: de ni ru lu zhes pas spyir sku las chos sku /
NK063(gu)001:12489: bye brag dkyil 'khor gyi lha las rigs lnga yab yum dang /
NK063(gu)001:12490: ru lu zhes pas longs sku'am gnas yul sgo ma dang /
NK063(gu)001:12491: ru lu h+aum zhes pas sprul sku'am dbang mo ste /
NK063(gu)001:12492: de dag la snyan gsan phab pas chos sku'i ngang
NK063(gu)001:12493: las ma g.yos bzhin du gzugs skur bzhengs pa yang
NK063(gu)001:12495: de las kyang khro bor nges te /
NK063(gu)001:12496: sku mdog phyag mtshan rgyan cha lugs rnams ting nge
NK063(gu)001:12497: 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ci 'dra ba'i rnam par bzhengs
NK063(gu)001:12498: pa'o // gnyis pa ni lag len du le'u dgu pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:12499: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK063(gu)001:12501: 'dir e h+ye hi la sogs pas dam tshig gi
NK063(gu)001:12502: gnas me ri 'dab 'byor gyi sar spyan drang ngo
NK063(gu)001:12503: // gsum pa ni +amo badz+ra sa ma ya ho
NK063(gu)001:12504: zhes pas ye shes pa dang dam tshig pa gnyis
NK063(gu)001:12505: bzang ngan dang tha dad du 'dzin pa'i rtog pa
NK063(gu)001:12506: // dor zhing / bzhi pa ni +amo khro la
NK063(gu)001:12507: zhes pa la sogs tshig dang +amo badz+ra kro ta
NK063(gu)001:12508: sa ma ya s+t+wam gyis sku gsung thugs kyi dam
NK063(gu)001:12511: phata kyis ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gyi thugs ka nas phata nag po grangs med pa 'phros pas /
NK063(gu)001:12512: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor gyi thugs kar thim pas snod dag cing dngos grub bskul ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:12513: lnga pa ni drin gang yod na 'das ma thag
NK063(gu)001:12514: gi phata kyi 'od zer gyis snod sbyangs pa'i drin
NK063(gu)001:12515: no // de'i lan du a li u li la sogs kyis 'dod pa'i yon tan gyis mchod ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:12516: drug pa ni h+aum gis rigs lnga yab yum dang /
NK063(gu)001:12517: ha yis gnas kyi ma mo dang /
NK063(gu)001:12518: he yis yul gyi phra men dang /
NK063(gu)001:12519: phata kyis ye shes kyi sgo ma dang /
NK063(gu)001:12520: shugs la gnas pa b+h+yo yis dbang mo rnams chu la chu ltar dbyer med du bstim zhing /
NK063(gu)001:12521: ram zhes pa de dag gi sku la me ri 'bar bar bsam mo //
NK063(gu)001:12522: de dag gi steng du lag len ltar brtan par bzhugs shing /
NK063(gu)001:12523: gdug pa can zhal du za ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:12524: sngon gyi dam tshig bstan pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:12525: zil gyis mnan pa rnams kyang bya ba yin no //
NK063(gu)001:12526: de'i yon tan ni zhes brjod pas zhes pa 'di
NK063(gu)001:12527: dag gzhung gong 'og bsgyur te 'jig rten drug gi
NK063(gu)001:12528: phyogs bcu thams cad du dkyil 'kho gyi tshogs kyis
NK063(gu)001:12529: gang ba'i sku la me ri 'bar /
NK063(gu)001:12531: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u bcu drug pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12533: // le'u bcu bdun pa'i mngon rtogs gong du blangs zin
NK063(gu)001:12534: te rten gzhal yas dang brten pa lha gsal gdab
NK063(gu)001:12536: 'bru cung zad 'chad dgos pa rnams ni 'di ltar gdan gyi skabs su khyu mchog ces pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:12538: gdan mchog gdul dka' mi 'jigs khyu mchog dang //
NK063(gu)001:12541: mi 'jigs bzhi ldan khyu mchog ste //
NK063(gu)001:12542: zhes pas seng ge la bshad do //
NK063(gu)001:12544: khyu mchog glang po che'i gnas su bca' zhes pas glang po cher bshad do //
NK063(gu)001:12545: bla ma'i gsung gis de gnyis rol pa las byung bar bshad do //
NK063(gu)001:12546: de ltar gdan 'di rnams mngon rtogs nas ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:12547: lha chen po rnams kyi bzhon pa phrogs pa'o zhes pas /
NK063(gu)001:12548: rgyal byed dpa' rtags kyi stan du gsol lo //
NK063(gu)001:12549: brten pa lha'i gtso bo la bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:12550: dang po dang gnyis pa gzhung brtag /
NK063(gu)001:12551: gsum pa ni ko rlon gos ni zhes pa rtog pa lha rgyud las /
NK063(gu)001:12552: glang chen 'dul stobs theg pa'i rgyan //
NK063(gu)001:12553: stag ni dpa' rtul za byed rgyan //
NK063(gu)001:12554: g.yang gzhi tshul khrims gos kyi rgyan //
NK063(gu)001:12555: zhes pas gos gsum gyon pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12556: sna tshogs zhes pas byug pa'i rgyan gsum bsdu ste /
NK063(gu)001:12558: rak+ta thugs rje chags pa'i rgyan //
NK063(gu)001:12559: thal ba 'dul byed phrin las rgyan //
NK063(gu)001:12560: gzi chen don dam bcud kyi rgyan //
NK063(gu)001:12562: rngams pa'i zhal nas h+aum ha he phata la sogs
NK063(gu)001:12563: gshe zhing myur ba bzhad mo'i sgra chen po sgrogs
NK063(gu)001:12564: pas bdud dang mu stegs la sogs log par lta
NK063(gu)001:12565: ba thams cad 'jigs par byed pa ni gsung gi
NK063(gu)001:12568: sprul pa dpal brjid gnyen lcug rgyan //
NK063(gu)001:12570: de yis dbu la dkris shing snyan cha dang /
NK063(gu)001:12573: phyag zhabs kyi gdub bu dang /
NK063(gu)001:12576: dang zhes pa gzhan sdud pa'i sgra kro ta an dza nas kyang brgyan no //
NK063(gu)001:12577: thod phreng zhes pa dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas mtshon pa'i phyir thod skam gyi dbu rgyan dang /
NK063(gu)001:12578: thod tshal lam ra ri'i dpung rgyan dang /
NK063(gu)001:12579: thod rlon gyi do shal lo //
NK063(gu)001:12580: nyi zla'i chas zhes pa gsal ba'i rgyan gnyis te
NK063(gu)001:12581: snyan gong na nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor stong 'byed pa'o
NK063(gu)001:12582: // bzhi pa ni spyir thabs zhags nas phyag mtshan gyi rnam grangs bcu gcig tu bshad de /
NK063(gu)001:12584: mtshon pa rang rtags kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:12585: thabs dang shes rab kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:12586: dbyings dang ye shes kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:12587: rgyal byed dpa' rtags kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:12588: rbod gtong phra men gyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:12589: yid bzhin re skong gi dang /
NK063(gu)001:12590: thugs chud chos nyid kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:12593: phrin las skul byed kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:12594: thugs ye shes rang snang gi phyag mtshan las /
NK063(gu)001:12595: gzhung 'dir bstan pa ni 'ga' zhig gang yin zhing 'ga' zhig gang yin te /
NK063(gu)001:12596: gtso bor mtha' ma len no //
NK063(gu)001:12598: stong gi 'jig rten khor yug bcas //
NK063(gu)001:12599: zhes pa ni badz+ra he ru ka'i g.yon mtha' ma na'o //
NK063(gu)001:12600: rdo rje zhes pa de'i g.yas dang po na rtse dgu pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:12601: rigs lnga char gyi g.yas bar ma na rtse lnga pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12602: dung chen gang pa zhes pa ni yab lnga'i g.yon bar pa dang yum lnga'i g.yon na'o //
NK063(gu)001:12603: ral gri zhes karma'i g.yon mtha' la /
NK063(gu)001:12604: dgra s+t+wa ni rat+na'i g.yon mtha' ste /
NK063(gu)001:12606: la sogs zhes pa sogs khongs su mang po sdud de /
NK063(gu)001:12607: bud+d+ha'i g.yon mtha' tri shul dang /
NK063(gu)001:12608: gzhan yang lnga char gyi g.yas dang po 'khor lo la sogs rang rtags dang /
NK063(gu)001:12609: g.yas mtha' ma rnams ti ra dang //
NK063(gu)001:12610: g.yon dang po rnams dril bu dang //
NK063(gu)001:12611: yum rnams kyis g.yas yab la 'khyud pas kha t+w+aam 'dzin pa rnams bsdus pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:12612: de ltar phyag mtshan 'di rnams rtsa rgyud 'di dang /
NK063(gu)001:12613: bshad rgyud rgyas pa dang rdo rje me long dang
NK063(gu)001:12614: bla ma la sogs rnams cung zad mi mthun pa
NK063(gu)001:12615: yod kyang / spyir bde bar gshegs pa'i sku mdog
NK063(gu)001:12616: phyag mtshan rgyan cha lugs la sogs gcig kho nar
NK063(gu)001:12617: ma nges par shes par bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:12618: rgyal ba'i thugs rje dang mdzad pa la phyogs ris
NK063(gu)001:12619: med cing gdul bya la mos pa tha dad yod
NK063(gu)001:12620: pa'i phyir ro // 'o na gang zag gis nyams su blang du mi btub par 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:12621: gcig tu ma nges pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:12623: rgyud gzhung re re'i dbang du nges pa can du gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:12624: gang zag gis de ltar nyasama su len pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:12625: de ltar ye shes rang snang gi mtshon byed du lag cha sna tshogs bsnams shing /
NK063(gu)001:12626: btsun mo 'jigs pa'i tshogs kro ti shwa ri lnga
NK063(gu)001:12627: dang 'khril bas lhan cig skyes pa'i skur bzhugs pa
NK063(gu)001:12628: ni dbyings dang ye shes kyi mtshon byed do //
NK063(gu)001:12630: gnas dang zhes pa ni dur khrod kyi gnas brgyad do //
NK063(gu)001:12631: de la phyi nang gsang ba gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:12642: nang gi ni lha'i ded dpon ma tang ka ru tra bsgral ba'i yan lag bzhi /
NK063(gu)001:12644: snying khog pa dang bcas pa /
NK063(gu)001:12646: mtshan ma dang brgyad phyogs mtshams brgyad du bzhag pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12647: gsang ba ni 'gro ba rnams kyi rang rang gi rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad de //
NK063(gu)001:12648: yul gyi zhes pa gong gi dur khrod brgyad kyi yod pa ste 'di ltar ma ga d+ha dang /
NK063(gu)001:12655: li yul rnams ni phyi'i yin la /
NK063(gu)001:12656: nang gi ni dur khrod dang mtshungs la /
NK063(gu)001:12657: gsang ba ni chos 'dus byas 'dus ma byas la sogs brgyad do //
NK063(gu)001:12658: de ltar yang ba ma brgyad bzhi pa nas /
NK063(gu)001:12659: de yi lus snying ma ga ta //
NK063(gu)001:12660: dur khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal //
NK063(gu)001:12661: ma mo chen mo ke'u ri ha //
NK063(gu)001:12662: zhes pa la sogs pas shes so //
NK063(gu)001:12663: phyag rgya dang zhes pa ni rten gong gi gnas
NK063(gu)001:12664: yul de dag na brten pa lha'i sku phyag rgya
NK063(gu)001:12665: chen po ni ke'u ri dang sing ha la sogs
NK063(gu)001:12667: de dag gi mtshan dang phyag mtshan dang sku mdog rnams 'jig rten 'das mdo ltar /
NK063(gu)001:12668: ke'u ri ban dman byis dbyug sngo //
NK063(gu)001:12669: la sogs pa rnams kyis shes par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:12670: yang na phyag rgya zhes pa ni phyag mtshan 'dzin tshul te /
NK063(gu)001:12672: byis dbyug mda' gzhu rgyal mtshan dang //
NK063(gu)001:12673: byis snying rdo rje za tog tshul //
NK063(gu)001:12676: dang po gnas ma'i phyag rgya ni //
NK063(gu)001:12677: s+t+wa re'i dbyug pa g.yas pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12679: thabs kyi mda' drag g.yas pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12680: shes rab gzhu thogs g.yon pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12681: chu srin rgyal mtshan g.yas pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12683: rdo rje rtse lnga sdigs mdzub mgo bcad g.yon //
NK063(gu)001:12690: b+han+d+ha bcad pa g.yas pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12691: ti ra mchog lus g.yon pa na'o //
NK063(gu)001:12694: yul gyi phra men phyag rgya ni //
NK063(gu)001:12695: phyag gnyis bsnol nas shin tu 'gying //
NK063(gu)001:12696: ti ra chen po sprug cing gsol //
NK063(gu)001:12697: phyag gnyis gyad kyi dor thabs kyis //
NK063(gu)001:12698: ti ra bsgyur nas 'bru tshugs lta //
NK063(gu)001:12699: phyag gnyis ti ra'i nang khrol 'bru //
NK063(gu)001:12700: phyag gnyis rol pa chen po yis //
NK063(gu)001:12701: ti ra phyed mar bcad nas gsol //
NK063(gu)001:12702: zangs gri dmar po g.yas pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12703: rgyu zhags drangs nas g.yon du 'god //
NK063(gu)001:12704: tir chung stod smad g.yas g.yon na //
NK063(gu)001:12705: rngams pa'i tshul gyis phrag la khur //
NK063(gu)001:12706: zangs gri dmar po g.yas pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12708: rdo rje lcags kyu g.yas pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12709: tir chung spyir bcom g.yon pa na'o //
NK063(gu)001:12711: 'o na gnas ma dang yul ma'i khyad par gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:12712: kha cig bsil ba tshal la sogs pa gong ltar
NK063(gu)001:12713: lha chen po'i yan lag las grub pa la ni
NK063(gu)001:12714: dur khrod kyi gnas zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:12715: de na mchod rten dang shing dang me dang chu
NK063(gu)001:12716: dang sprin dang zhing skyong la sogs yon tan re
NK063(gu)001:12717: re yang brgyad tshan brgyad dang ldan par gnas pa
NK063(gu)001:12718: la gnas kyi ma mo zhes bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:12720: ma ga d+ha la sogs pa yul brgyad na gnas
NK063(gu)001:12721: pa'i ma mo la yul gyi phra men zhes bya
NK063(gu)001:12722: ste sing ha la sogs so zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:12723: de la bla ma'i gsung gis yul brgyad na dur
NK063(gu)001:12724: khrod brgyad yod pa'i phyir ma mo dang phra men
NK063(gu)001:12725: ma gnas gcig tu gyur pa'i skyon yod pas 'thad
NK063(gu)001:12726: pa ma yin zhes dper brjod kyang mdzad do //
NK063(gu)001:12727: 'o na ji ltar zhe na kun gzhi la sogs
NK063(gu)001:12728: rang rang gi rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad gnas
NK063(gu)001:12729: gyur pa'i ma mo la gnas kyi ma mo zhes
NK063(gu)001:12730: bya ste koo r+ai la sogs pa yin la /
NK063(gu)001:12731: de dag gi yul chos 'dus byas 'dus ma byas
NK063(gu)001:12732: la sogs pa yul brgyad gnas su gyur pa la
NK063(gu)001:12733: yul gyi phra men zhes bya ste sing ha la
NK063(gu)001:12735: 'di ni phyi yul dang sbyar na snga ma ltar bde ste /
NK063(gu)001:12736: bam brgyad kyi lung gis shes so //
NK063(gu)001:12737: nang don du sbyar na bla ma'i gsung sgros ltar bde ste /
NK063(gu)001:12739: mdzod ldan chen mo la sogs pa //
NK063(gu)001:12740: zhes rnam shes la sogs gnas gyur par bshad pa'i phyir snyam du sems so //
NK063(gu)001:12741: sgo bzhi zhes pa ni khyams nang ma'i sgo'o //
NK063(gu)001:12742: phyag rgya zhes pa ni de na gnas pa'i lha
NK063(gu)001:12743: mo ste rta gdong sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa
NK063(gu)001:12744: la sogs pa'o // yang na phyag mtshan 'dzin tshul te /
NK063(gu)001:12746: rdo rje lcags kyu g.yas pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12748: lcags kyi dril zhags g.yas pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12749: b+han+d+ha rlon pa g.yon pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12750: lcags sgog me 'bar g.yas pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12751: b+han+d+ha rlon pa g.yon pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12752: dril bu thal byed g.yas pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12753: b+han d+ha rlon pa g.yon pa na //
NK063(gu)001:12755: lha tshogs de rnams kyis bdag po'i rgyan du rab tu mdzes par gnas shing /
NK063(gu)001:12756: gzhan yang dpal gyi pho brang slas par byed pa
NK063(gu)001:12757: dang yum ni ma yin la thabs kyis sbyor bas
NK063(gu)001:12758: byi mo'i tshogs kyi yang gtso bor gyur pa ste
NK063(gu)001:12759: / bcu phrag gnyis dang brgyad de nyer brgyad kyis yongs su mdzes par bskor ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:12760: 'khor de rnams rang rang gi gdan ni gnas yul
NK063(gu)001:12761: sgo ma rnams kyi gdan 'jig rten 'das mdo ltar
NK063(gu)001:12762: shar nas brtsams te rim pa ltar dri za dang
NK063(gu)001:12763: gshin rje dang nyi ma dang zla ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:12764: shar lho nas rim bzhin me lha bden bral rlung lha dbang ldan no //
NK063(gu)001:12765: de bzhin phra men kyang khyams shar nas rim bzhin dri za grul bum yi dwags gnod sbyin dang /
NK063(gu)001:12767: sgo ma'i yang shar phag chen /
NK063(gu)001:12770: byang gnod sbyin gsus chen no //
NK063(gu)001:12771: yang na mngon rtogs nas khro mo nyi shu la nyi dkyil te steng du zhing rlon pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:12772: dbang mo rnams zhing skam po dang chas bshad do //
NK063(gu)001:12773: lag cha dang zhes pa dbang mo'i phyag mtshan te /
NK063(gu)001:12775: srin mo smug nag rdo rje thod rlon 'dzin //
NK063(gu)001:12776: zhes pa la sogs te shes par zad do //
NK063(gu)001:12777: las ci bgyi zhes ni chas te khyams phyi ma la gnas pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12778: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u bcu bdun pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12780: // le'u bco brgyad pa ni zhi khro gnyis char thun mong pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:12781: mngon par rtogs pa'i dbang du las kyi rim pa'i
NK063(gu)001:12782: ting nge 'dzin las p+au dza las kyi rim pa'o
NK063(gu)001:12783: // de la bco lnga las sgrol sbyor ni rgyas par le'u bcu gcig pa ltar la /
NK063(gu)001:12784: 'dir ni de la zhes pa gang la mchod pa'i yul dkyil 'khor gnyis so //
NK063(gu)001:12785: mchod ces pa ni gang rgyal ba mnyes par byed pa cig yin te /
NK063(gu)001:12786: de mdor bsdu na gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:12787: yon chab bdug spos la sogs thun mong phyi'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:12788: 'dod pa'i yon tan la sogs khyad par nang gi dang /
NK063(gu)001:12789: tan gan la sogs gsang ba rmad du byung ba'i mchod pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12790: sbyin zhes pa gong ma dag gis gtso bor dkyil
NK063(gu)001:12791: 'khor gyi lha tshogs mchod cing zhor la 'khor gyi
NK063(gu)001:12793: dam pa zhes pa nang dang gsang ba'i mchod pa ni kun gyi yul ma yin pas so /
NK063(gu)001:12794: de las kyang gsang ba gtso bor ston pa ste
NK063(gu)001:12795: thog mar zhes pa tan gan gnyis kyi sngon du
NK063(gu)001:12796: 'gro ba'o // de gang zhe na 'bru bsgyur te
NK063(gu)001:12797: 'og nas rtogs goms zhes pa ste de yang rtogs
NK063(gu)001:12798: pa ni rgyu shes pa'i lta ba yin la /
NK063(gu)001:12799: goms pa ni rkyen 'jug pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK063(gu)001:12800: de gnyis dang ldan pas gang bsgral na gong nas
NK063(gu)001:12801: bdag nyid ces pa bdag gi ma rig pa dang
NK063(gu)001:12802: log rtog go // de ltar gong gi rtogs goms
NK063(gu)001:12803: gnyis kyi blos ma rig pa rnam par dag pa
NK063(gu)001:12804: ni rang don du rtogs pas bdag bsgral ba yin
NK063(gu)001:12805: log rtog go // la / rtogs pas bdag bsgral
NK063(gu)001:12806: ba de nas gzhan don du thugs rjes gzhan bsgral
NK063(gu)001:12808: gnyis zhes pa bsgral bya gzung yul dang sgrol ba'i blo 'dzin pa'i sems te /
NK063(gu)001:12809: med ces pa gzung 'dzin gnyis chos nyid de bzhin nyid du rtogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12810: blo de yis ni gang bsgral na blo ngan zhes
NK063(gu)001:12811: pa mi shes pa'i 'ching bas rgyud bcings pa thams
NK063(gu)001:12812: cad do // de'i 'bras bu 'jig rten zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:12813: sems can las ngan pa la spyod pa'i zhing bcu
NK063(gu)001:12814: ste le'u bcu gcig par bstan no //
NK063(gu)001:12815: gang gis phyir na snying re rje zhes pa 'bras
NK063(gu)001:12816: bu sdug bsngal nyams su myong ba de rgyun gcad
NK063(gu)001:12817: pa'i phyir ro // ji ltar na gnyis su med
NK063(gu)001:12818: par zhes pas chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings
NK063(gu)001:12819: pa'i phyir ro // sam / yang na yab yum
NK063(gu)001:12820: thabs shes rab gnyis med kyi mkha' dbyings su bsgral
NK063(gu)001:12821: pa'i phyir ro // sam / bar bya'o // 'di
NK063(gu)001:12822: ltar sgrol ba la le lag ltar rnam grangs lnga
NK063(gu)001:12823: po re re yang sgeg pa'i gzhung las /
NK063(gu)001:12824: byed pa'i tshig lngar shes par bya //
NK063(gu)001:12826: byed tshig lnga lnga dang sbyar bar bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:12827: dang po rang bzhin gyi sgrol ba la yang /
NK063(gu)001:12828: gang bsgral na ma rig pas phyin ci log tu 'dzin pa'i blo'o //
NK063(gu)001:12829: gang gis na chos nyid ji bzhin pa rtogs pa des so //
NK063(gu)001:12830: ji ltar na shes rab gsum dang ma bral bas so //
NK063(gu)001:12831: de'i dgos pa ni chos nyid mngon du byas pas mthar thug gi bde ba thob pa'i ched do //
NK063(gu)001:12832: dpe ni nyi mas mun pa bsal ba lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:12833: gnyis pa dbang po yul dus kyi la yang /
NK063(gu)001:12835: spyod yul 'di dag la rang rgyud du zhen pa'i rtog pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12836: gang gis na bskyed rim la goms shing 'jug pa'i gang zag gis so //
NK063(gu)001:12838: rtog pa lhar sprad de der shes pa'i lam brlabs nas so //
NK063(gu)001:12839: dgos pa ni lhar gsal bas rtog tshogs rnam par
NK063(gu)001:12840: dag cing de nyid de bzhin du dag pas don
NK063(gu)001:12841: dam mngon du gyur pa'i ched do //
NK063(gu)001:12842: dpe rgyal bu rgyal sar bton pa lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:12843: gsum pa ting nge 'dzin gyi la yang /
NK063(gu)001:12845: log pa'i rnam rtog mtha' dag go //
NK063(gu)001:12847: mtshan bcas mtshan med gang yin yang rtse gcig tu gnas pa'i sems kyis so //
NK063(gu)001:12848: ji ltar na rig pa bsrang du 'dzud pa'i gnad shes pa'i thabs kyis so //
NK063(gu)001:12849: dgos pa ni sems la dbang thob pas lam rtags mngon du gyur pa'i ched do //
NK063(gu)001:12850: dpe ni mkha' la bya dang chu la nya yis dbang thob pa lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:12851: bzhi pa thabs chen po'i la yang /
NK063(gu)001:12854: gang gis na dpal chen po'i sku gsung thugs kyis so //
NK063(gu)001:12856: yul dang mthun par gtso bo bsgral zhing 'khor dam la btags nas so //
NK063(gu)001:12858: drag po'i phrin las mthar phyin pa'i ched do //
NK063(gu)001:12859: dpe ni dpa' bos dgra thul ba lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:12860: mtha' ma mngon du byung ba la yang /
NK063(gu)001:12864: rtogs goms kyi blo dang ldan pas gsad gso'i grub pa brnyes pas so //
NK063(gu)001:12866: le'u bcu gcig pa'i thabs ltar ro //
NK063(gu)001:12868: de'i sdug bsngal yun thung byang chub kyi sems 'phel
NK063(gu)001:12869: gsang sngags kyi spyod pa mthar phyin pa la sogs
NK063(gu)001:12870: pa'i ched do // dpe ni bshan pa'i lag pa ltar ro //
NK063(gu)001:12871: sbyor ba ni gzhung brtags te de lnga la yang gong bzhin lnga lnga ste /
NK063(gu)001:12872: dang po rang bzhin gyi sbyor ba ni gang la na ye nas gnas pa chos nyid la'o //
NK063(gu)001:12873: gang gis na de rtogs par nus pa'i blo dbang po rnon po des so //
NK063(gu)001:12874: ji ltar na shes 'jug gi lam gyi mtshan nyid kyis so //
NK063(gu)001:12875: dgos pa ni 'khrul pas bcings pa las grol nas zag med kyi bde ba thob pa yis so //
NK063(gu)001:12876: dpe ni sngar 'dris kyi mi phyis shes pa lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:12877: gnyis pa dbang po yul dus kyi la yang /
NK063(gu)001:12879: rtog tshogs ji snyed pa rnams la'o //
NK063(gu)001:12880: gang gis na de sku dang ye shes su rtogs pa'am bsgoms pa'i blo yis so //
NK063(gu)001:12881: ji ltar cho ga yan lag gi sa mtshan bcas lha'i rnal 'byor du gsal bas so //
NK063(gu)001:12882: dgos pa ni tha mal gyi rtog pa dag nas
NK063(gu)001:12883: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor la blo 'byongs pa yis
NK063(gu)001:12884: so // dpe ni gser 'gyur gyi rtsi lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:12885: gsum pa ting nge 'dzin gyi la yang /
NK063(gu)001:12887: lha mo zhes 'od kyi yum la'o //
NK063(gu)001:12888: gang gis na ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa thob pas so //
NK063(gu)001:12889: ji ltar na rang lus thabs dang ldan pas lus sems bde bas rgyas par ro //
NK063(gu)001:12890: dgos pa ni kha sbyor la ltos mi dgos par snang spyod bde ba'i rang gzugs su 'char ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:12891: dpe ni rmi lam gyi 'gro ba bzang mo lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:12892: bzhi pa thabs chen po'i la yang /
NK063(gu)001:12893: gang la na ru dra'i chung ma kro ti shwa ri la'o //
NK063(gu)001:12894: gang gis na phyag rgya chen po'i khro bor snang ba'i dpal chen pos so //
NK063(gu)001:12895: ji ltar na mi rtog pa'i tshad pa'i gdungs pa bsal nas ye shes kyi sprul pa zhags pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12896: dgos pa ni rgyal ba'i mdzad pa lhun gyis grub pa yis so //
NK063(gu)001:12897: dpe ni tsan+dana dang sbrul lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:12898: mtha' ma mngon du byung ba'i la yang /
NK063(gu)001:12899: gang la na rigs ngan mo zhes pa zag bcas kyi yum la'o //
NK063(gu)001:12900: gang gis na 'dod chags can gyi gang zag steng sgo las su rung bas so //
NK063(gu)001:12901: ji ltar na sbyor ba'i dus kyi bsnyen sgrub bzhis
NK063(gu)001:12902: dbab bzung ldog dgram la bslabs pas lhan skyes mngon
NK063(gu)001:12903: du byed pa'o // dgos pa ni 'dod chags lam
NK063(gu)001:12904: du slongs pas tha mal gyis bcings pa las grol
NK063(gu)001:12905: du byed pa'o // ba yis so // dpe ni rma bya dug gis 'tsho ba lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:12906: de ltar le'u 'dir bstan pa'i sbyor sgrol 'di dag
NK063(gu)001:12907: dngos su mngon du byung ba yin zhing de'i cha
NK063(gu)001:12908: rkyen du dgos pa'i phyir rang bzhin dang ting nge
NK063(gu)001:12910: 'di spyad par mi 'thad pa'i skyon le'u bcu gcig par spangs zin to //
NK063(gu)001:12911: 'o na le'u bcu gcig pa dang zlos so zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:12912: kha cig gong ma mngon du phyung ba yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:12913: 'di ting nge 'dzin gyi yin pas mi zlos zer ro //
NK063(gu)001:12914: yang kha cig gong ma spyod pa yin la 'di mchod pa yin pas mi zlos zer te /
NK063(gu)001:12915: de gnyis ka ma nges par sems te /
NK063(gu)001:12916: gong ma yang mchod par 'gyur zhing 'dir yang mngon du phyung bar bzhed pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:12918: gong ma tshogs sgrub kyi dus su nyams su blang byar gsungs pas lam gyi ngo bo yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:12919: 'di mchod pa'i skabs yin pas lam gyi cha rkyen du 'thad par sems so //
NK063(gu)001:12920: gti mug dam rdzas kyi mchod pa ni mnyam pa'i
NK063(gu)001:12921: zhes pa rdzas lnga la gtsang rme tha dad du
NK063(gu)001:12923: grub rdzas zhes pa dam rdzas lnga la grub pa bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:12924: chos nyid rang bzhin gyis dang /
NK063(gu)001:12927: byin gyis brlabs kyis grub pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12929: dngos po ma lus sems nyid phyir //
NK063(gu)001:12930: mtshan nyid bral ba chos kyi dbyings //
NK063(gu)001:12934: rang bzhin med pa'i ye shes lnga //
NK063(gu)001:12935: byed pa med par snang ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:12938: shes rab ting 'dzin thabs dag gis //
NK063(gu)001:12942: 'di lta'i lam la gang gnas pa //
NK063(gu)001:12943: phyogs dus kun nas byin gyis rlobs //
NK063(gu)001:12946: de nas mngon rtogs kyi dbang du mchod bshags bya
NK063(gu)001:12947: zhing smon lam gdab pa yang 'dir don gyis shes
NK063(gu)001:12948: par byas nas las kyi rim pa de dag gi
NK063(gu)001:12950: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u bco brgyad pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:12952: // le'u bcu dgu pa 'di yang zhi khro gnyis kar thun mong ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:12953: lam 'di nyams su len pa'i bsrung bya dam tshig go //
NK063(gu)001:12954: de la gzhung don bdun las /
NK063(gu)001:12955: dang po che ba mdor bstan pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:12956: tshig bsgyur te 'og nas lhag pa tshul khrims kyi
NK063(gu)001:12957: bslab pas 'dul ba'i gdul bya dag gi nyon mongs
NK063(gu)001:12958: pa'i dbang gis nyan thos kyi theg pa la gnyen
NK063(gu)001:12959: po tshul khrims bsrung ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:12960: yang 'bru bsgyur te byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa
NK063(gu)001:12961: la sdom pa dang de la sogs pa gdul bya
NK063(gu)001:12962: ji snyed pa la bsrung bya mtha' yas pa rnams
NK063(gu)001:12963: / gong nas bla na med pa theg pa'i mchog
NK063(gu)001:12964: rdo rje'i theg pa 'di'i dam tshig gi nang du
NK063(gu)001:12965: yang 'og nas theg pa 'og ma'i bsrung bya de
NK063(gu)001:12966: dag ma lus pa kun 'dus shing ma gos pas
NK063(gu)001:12967: rnam par dag pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:12968: yang gong nas rigs kyi spyi dam tshig 'dir bsrung bya rnams phun sum tshogs pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:12969: dper na sor mo lnga'i tshogs pa grub na bye
NK063(gu)001:12970: brag mthe bong grub pa bzhin no zhes bkod pa
NK063(gu)001:12971: la / kha cig de ltar ma grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:12972: 'di'i spyad par bya ba'i dam tshig tan gan la
NK063(gu)001:12973: sogs pa ni nyon mongs pa mi spong ba yin
NK063(gu)001:12974: la / de 'og ma'i bsrung bya dang 'gal ba yin pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:12975: theg pa 'di la ltos nas 'gal bar ma grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:12977: 'dod chags la sogs nyon mongs pa dang mtshams med
NK063(gu)001:12978: la sogs las ngan pa rnams kun la spyod kyang
NK063(gu)001:12979: / 'bru 'og ma blang ste mi sogs zhes pa ni mi gos pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:12980: de'i rgyu mtshan ni gong nas bla na med pa
NK063(gu)001:12981: rdo rje'i theg par blo rab tu nges pas don
NK063(gu)001:12983: las nyon la spyad par byas kyang don la de
NK063(gu)001:12984: nyid ma grub par rtogs pa'i phyir dper na sgyu
NK063(gu)001:12985: ma bzhin no // des na yang 'og nas tshul
NK063(gu)001:12986: khrims zhes pa 'dis chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:12987: rnam par dag pa rtogs pa ni yang dag pa'i
NK063(gu)001:12989: 'di ltar las dang nyon mongs pa la spyad kyang ma gos pas sdom pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:12990: des don phra ba yang mi 'dor bas sems can don byed kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:12991: sgo gsum phyag rgya chen po las mi yengs pas dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims so //
NK063(gu)001:12992: sdom pa zhes pa des sogs bsrung bya mtha' dag 'dir 'dus pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:12994: bsrung bya de dag tu ma 'gags pa bsod nams dang /
NK063(gu)001:12995: der ma grub pa ye shes kyi tshogs su 'gyur
NK063(gu)001:12996: ba ste de'i phyir dam tshig gi che ba yin
NK063(gu)001:12997: no // de rgyas pa la bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:12999: yod ces pa mu stegs kyi rtag dngos dang /
NK063(gu)001:13000: nyan rang gi chos bdag dang /
NK063(gu)001:13001: sems tsam pa'i rang rig bden dngos la sogs yod pa'i mtha' dang /
NK063(gu)001:13002: med ces pa mu stegs kyi chad mtha' dang /
NK063(gu)001:13003: dbu ma rgyun chad kyi stong nyid la sogs med pa'i mtha' dang /
NK063(gu)001:13004: dbu ma zhes pa de gnyis ka dang bral ba'i dbu ma'ang mi dmigs shing ma grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:13005: ltos sa yod med kyi mtha' gnyis ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:13006: dper na chu phar ka med na tshur ka yang med pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:13007: de ltar chos thams cad mtha' bral du rtogs pa'i don ta na'i dam tshig la spyad kyang /
NK063(gu)001:13008: tshig bsgyur te gnyis kyi 'og nas don la gcad
NK063(gu)001:13009: bya srog dang gcod byed skyes bu gnyis chos can
NK063(gu)001:13010: / gong gi tshig gi 'bru bsgyur la /
NK063(gu)001:13011: tha snyad du srog tu btags kyang don la gcad du med pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:13014: srog dang skyes bur 'dzin pa ni log rtog 'khrul ngo tsam yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:13015: mthun dpe ni gong nas sgyu mar snang ba'i sems
NK063(gu)001:13016: can gyi srog mig yor lta bu'i skyes bus bcad
NK063(gu)001:13018: yang de dag gdams ngag gi dbang du bshad na
NK063(gu)001:13019: 'dir chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pas
NK063(gu)001:13020: srog gcad bya dang gcod byed gnyis su 'dzin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:13021: 'khrul pa dang / de dag pas rang dbang med pa'i skye ba khegs /
NK063(gu)001:13022: de khegs pas 'chi ba dang bral ba ni srog
NK063(gu)001:13023: gcod pa'i dam tshig yang dag pa yin par sems
NK063(gu)001:13024: so // gnyis pa bden pa gnyis ka zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:13025: ma byin par blang bya len byed gnyis don dam
NK063(gu)001:13026: gyi ngos nas blo'i yul tsam du yang ma grub
NK063(gu)001:13027: so // pa'i phyir dang / kun rdzob kyi ngos
NK063(gu)001:13028: nas blang bya len byed gnyis ka ngo bo nyid
NK063(gu)001:13029: kyis stongs pa'i phyir dbyer med pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:13030: tshig bsgyur te gnyis kyi 'og nas //
NK063(gu)001:13031: de ltar rtogs na ci blangs kyang don la blangs pa med de /
NK063(gu)001:13033: bdag po gzhan dang de'i rdzas ma byin par blangs pa gnyis med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:13036: bdag po gzhan dang de'i rdzas ma byin par blangs pa gnyis med de /
NK063(gu)001:13037: chos thams cad de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings su gcig par rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:13038: mthun dpe ni gong nas 'phrul dag'i longs spyod rang
NK063(gu)001:13039: las sprul zhing rang gis longs spyod pa'i tshul bzhin
NK063(gu)001:13040: te tha dad pa min no //
NK063(gu)001:13041: gsum pa ni chos rnams zhes pa rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin pa thams cad /
NK063(gu)001:13042: 'og nas de dag la 'dod zhen gyis ming dang
NK063(gu)001:13043: tshig tha dad du brtags shing spyad pas thams cad
NK063(gu)001:13045: bden pa'i rang bzhin logs su ma grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:13046: mthun dpe gong nas sgyu ma lta bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:13047: dang zhes pa mi bden pa'i dpe gzhan yang rmi lam la sogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13049: bden pas stong pa ngo bo nyid kyi brdzun nyid
NK063(gu)001:13050: la ni yod las med smra la sogs log pa'i
NK063(gu)001:13052: bardzusa zhes tha snyad du btags pa tsam las yang dag par na yod pa ma yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13053: tha ma ni ma chags pa la zhes pa yang
NK063(gu)001:13054: dag gi don la chags mkhan dang chags yul gnyis
NK063(gu)001:13055: med pas so // chags pa dang zhes pa de
NK063(gu)001:13056: ma rtogs te 'khrul ngo na gnyis su snang pas
NK063(gu)001:13057: med pas so // so // de ltar chags pa'i
NK063(gu)001:13058: dus nyid na ma grub par rtogs pas chags pa'i
NK063(gu)001:13059: yul dang yul can gnyis med pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13060: de ltar rtogs pa ni spyad kyang ma zhen pas tshangs par spyod pa'i mchog yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:13061: thabs kyis zin pas spyad kyang tha mal gyi 'dod chags la dbang sgyur ba'i phyir rgyal po ste /
NK063(gu)001:13062: de ltar dbyer med kyi don la shin tu chags
NK063(gu)001:13063: pas yang dag pa'i don dang 'du 'bral med pa'i
NK063(gu)001:13065: rnam grangs mdor bstan pa la gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:13067: gnyis pa la mi spang ba ni gti mug chags
NK063(gu)001:13068: dang zhes pa la sogs nyon mongs pa lnga las
NK063(gu)001:13069: / mi spang ngo zhes pas 'di la bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:13070: nyon mongs pa mi spong ba de gsang ba yin nam bsgrag pa yin pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13071: drang don yin nam nges don yin pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13072: mi spong ba'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK063(gu)001:13073: ma spangs pa'i dgos ched do //
NK063(gu)001:13074: dang po ni snod min la gsang zhig snod ldan la bsgrag bya yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13075: gnyis pa ni blo chung la drang don yin zhes pa ni 'thad par mi sems te /
NK063(gu)001:13076: theg pa 'di blo chung gi yul ma yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:13077: nyon mongs mi spong ba 'di drang don du bstan du yang mi btub pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:13078: 'di blo chen po la nges don yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13079: gsum pa ni rtags kyis bsgrub pa ste gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:13080: nyon mongs pa lngar snang ba de chos can /
NK063(gu)001:13082: spang bya'i rdzas ma grub pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:13083: rang bzhin chen po yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:13084: lam 'di thabs la mkhas pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)001:13085: dper na smig rgyu la shwa rags kyi rtsol ba mi dgos pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13086: skyes bu pha nor la bu spyod pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13087: bya 'dab gshog can nam mkha' la 'phur ba bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:13088: rtags de dag ma grub bo zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:13089: dang po'i tshul bsgrub pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:13090: dper na thag khra la sbrul du 'khrul pa'i tshe sbrul med de thag pa yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:13091: der ma grub ste spu nyag ma re yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:13092: de yang ma grub ste rdul phran no //
NK063(gu)001:13093: der yang ma grub ste rang bzhin med pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:13094: sems can gyi shes rgyud nyon mongs lngar 'khrul pa'i
NK063(gu)001:13095: tshe nyon mongs pa de gzhan du ma grub ste
NK063(gu)001:13096: rang rang gi sems yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13097: sems la brtags shing dpyad na dbu ma pas yang
NK063(gu)001:13098: bden pa'i gcig dang du ma dang bral bar rtogs
NK063(gu)001:13099: na / 'dir chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin mtha'
NK063(gu)001:13100: gang du yang ma grub par rtogs pas spangs bya'i
NK063(gu)001:13101: rdzas grub par lta smos kyang ci dgos te /
NK063(gu)001:13104: chos thams cad rang rang gi ngo bo nyid kyis stongs pa'i phyir nam mkha' bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:13105: de ltar spang bya'i rdzas ma grub bzhin spong ba
NK063(gu)001:13106: ni smig rgyu la shwa rags kyi rtsol ba byed
NK063(gu)001:13107: pa dang 'dra ste shes rab 'chal ba'i rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:13108: no // gnyis pa'i tshul bsgrub pa yang chen po
NK063(gu)001:13109: zhes bya ba ni yang dag pa'i dug lnga yin
NK063(gu)001:13111: rgyal ba'i thugs nyid la chos tha dad ris su mi 'byed pa'i gti mug dang /
NK063(gu)001:13112: chos nyid kyi don dang 'du 'bral med pa'i 'dod chags dang /
NK063(gu)001:13113: ma rig pa'am log rtog sgrol ba'i zhe sdang dang /
NK063(gu)001:13114: yang dag pa'i don las mi nyams pa'i nga rgyal dang /
NK063(gu)001:13115: lta ba ngan pa 'gegs shi nga sel ba'i phrag dog rnams dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:13116: yang na rtags kyis bsgrub ste /
NK063(gu)001:13117: nyon mongs pa lngar snang ba chos can /
NK063(gu)001:13118: chen po ye shes lnga yin te /
NK063(gu)001:13119: nyon mongs pa las rdzas gzhan du ye shes lnga
NK063(gu)001:13120: ma grub pa'i phyir byas pa dang mi rtag pa
NK063(gu)001:13121: bzhin no zhes pa'i rtags kyis bsgrub pa yang yin
NK063(gu)001:13122: no // de ni dper na pha mdzangs pa zhig
NK063(gu)001:13123: gis bsags pa'i nor la bu dge slong lta bus
NK063(gu)001:13124: spyad kyang ma byin len gyi nyes pa med pa
NK063(gu)001:13125: no // dang 'dra'o // gsum pa'i tshul bsgrub pa
NK063(gu)001:13126: ni dper na gur gum dang pad+ma 'dam nas skyes
NK063(gu)001:13127: kyang de mi gos pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:13128: 'di'i lam las thabs lam gyi dbang du rlung sems
NK063(gu)001:13129: la dbang thob pas kha sbyor gyi bde ba lhan
NK063(gu)001:13130: skyes kyi ye shes su 'gyur zhing /
NK063(gu)001:13131: grol lam gyi dbang du nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin
NK063(gu)001:13132: chos nyid du gtan la phab pas ma grub par
NK063(gu)001:13134: de ltar thabs gnyis dang ldan pa ni dper na
NK063(gu)001:13135: bya 'dab gshog can nam mkha' la 'phur yang ltung
NK063(gu)001:13136: ba'i 'jigs pa med pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:13137: de ltar nyon mongs pa mi spong zhing lam du
NK063(gu)001:13138: byed pa la kha cig dngos la lam du byed
NK063(gu)001:13139: pa zhes bya ba zhe sdang mnar sems spun dgu
NK063(gu)001:13140: lta bur skyes pa'i ldog pa lam du byed zer
NK063(gu)001:13141: ba ni 'thad pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:13142: de ltar na pha bas da kyi bu dwa'u yang grol bar 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:13143: yang kha cig khyab bya yin na lam du byed
NK063(gu)001:13144: pa zhes bya ba zhe sdang la sogs nyon mongs
NK063(gu)001:13145: par ma 'gags pa ni snang ba yin la /
NK063(gu)001:13146: de la rang bzhin med pa khyab byed du yod pas de lam du 'gyur zer ba yang /
NK063(gu)001:13147: nyon mongs pa lam du byed par mi 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:13148: de'i chos nyid lam du byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:13149: yang kha cig de'i gshis kha la lam du byed
NK063(gu)001:13150: pa zhes bya ste gang zhe sdang la sogs skyes
NK063(gu)001:13151: pa ni kun rdzob rig pa sgyu ma dang /
NK063(gu)001:13152: de la rang bzhin med pa ni don dam rig
NK063(gu)001:13153: pa spros bral gnyis zung du zhugs te dbyer med
NK063(gu)001:13154: pa de lam du byed zer ba yang nyon mongs
NK063(gu)001:13155: lam du byed pa ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:13156: de shes bya'i gnas lugs tsam yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:13157: 'o na ji ltar zhe na ru mda' seng ge'i
NK063(gu)001:13158: bzhed kyis nyon mongs pa chos nyid yin lugs dang
NK063(gu)001:13159: / de lam du 'gro lugs gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:13160: dang po ni nyon mongs pa rang dang spyi'i mtshan
NK063(gu)001:13161: nyid ma nor ba dang rang mtshan sgyu ma dang
NK063(gu)001:13162: spyi mtshan spros bral du rtogs pa de yin te
NK063(gu)001:13163: / ji skad du rgyas pa las /
NK063(gu)001:13164: nyon mongs rang dang spyir bstan pa //
NK063(gu)001:13165: mtshan nyid ma nor don rtogs na //
NK063(gu)001:13167: gnyis pa ni rgyu shes pa'i skabs su gtan tshigs
NK063(gu)001:13168: kyis nyon mongs pa chos nyid du gtan la phab
NK063(gu)001:13169: nas / rkyen 'jug pa tshogs sgrubs kyi dus su thabs dang ldan pas tan gan la spyad pas /
NK063(gu)001:13170: gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu mngon du byed pa zhig yin te /
NK063(gu)001:13172: rnam par byang bas lam du 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:13173: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub kyang //
NK063(gu)001:13174: gang na med de de nyid yin //
NK063(gu)001:13176: yang na chos nyid yin lugs ni gong gi mi
NK063(gu)001:13177: spong ba'i gtan tshigs kyi skabs su rtags kyis bsgrubs
NK063(gu)001:13178: pa ltar yin par yang sems so //
NK063(gu)001:13179: tha ma ma spangs pa'i dgos pa la yang gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:13180: dngos po la mngon par zhen pa ldog pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13181: chos nyid bden pa'i don la rtogs pa'i blo myur ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13182: bka' zab mo la gus pa'i stobs skye ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:13183: dang po ni khyim bdag cig gis me bsten nyes
NK063(gu)001:13184: te nor phyugs khang pa la sogs pa tshig pas
NK063(gu)001:13185: / me'i dngos po la tsha zhing bsreg pa kho nar zhen pa'i tshe /
NK063(gu)001:13186: rkyen zhig gis 'brog dgon par phyin pa na drang srong me lha dang /
NK063(gu)001:13187: gzhan yang me'i yi dwags ma zhes bya ba dang /
