NK063(gu)001:13188: byol song me byi dkar po dang /
NK063(gu)001:13189: ri dwags me'i gtsang sbra can la sogs pa me
NK063(gu)001:13190: la gnas shing zas skom dang longs spyod kyang me
NK063(gu)001:13192: 'o na 'ga' zhig gi gnas dang longs spyod kyang
NK063(gu)001:13193: byed pa'i phyir tsha zhing bsreg pa kho na'o snyam
NK063(gu)001:13194: du zhen pa las log pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:13195: theg pa 'og ma bas nyon mongs pa la 'khor
NK063(gu)001:13196: ba'i chos kho nar bzung ste 'ga' zhig gis spong
NK063(gu)001:13197: zhing 'gegs la / 'ga' zhig gis sbyong zhing /
NK063(gu)001:13199: 'dir nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin sems nyid yin pa'i
NK063(gu)001:13200: phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes par shes nas lam du
NK063(gu)001:13201: byas pas 'bras bu mngon du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:13202: nyon mongs pa'i dngos po la 'khor ba'i chos kho nar zhen pa las ldog pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13203: dpe gzhan yang btsan dug de rma bya'i srog skyed
NK063(gu)001:13204: byed yin kyang mi'i 'gag byed yin pa'i phyir gcig
NK063(gu)001:13206: de yang dug de res bskyed cing res 'gag pa min te /
NK063(gu)001:13207: rma bya la ltos te rtag tu skyed cing /
NK063(gu)001:13208: mi la ltos te rtag tu 'gog byed yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13209: 'on kyang rma bya'i skyed byed de gzhan gyi 'gog
NK063(gu)001:13210: byed kho nar yang ma nges te 'bras la sogs
NK063(gu)001:13211: pa ni gnyis car gyi skyed byed yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13212: yang 'gag pa brdzun la skyed pa bden pa yang ma yin te /
NK063(gu)001:13213: mi la ltos nas 'gag pa bden la skyed pa brdzun zhing /
NK063(gu)001:13214: rma bya la ltos te 'gag pa brdzun zhing skyed pa bden pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13215: de dang 'dra bar dngos po thams cad la rang
NK063(gu)001:13216: rang gi mngon pa zhen pa rnams ma grub pa
NK063(gu)001:13218: yi dwags dud 'gro mi rnams dang //
NK063(gu)001:13219: lha rnams da ltar rigs rnams su //
NK063(gu)001:13220: dngos gcig yin ni tha dad phyir //
NK063(gu)001:13221: don ma grub par 'dod pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:13222: zhes pa bzhin nyon mongs pa spong sbyong la sogs kho nar ma grub pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13223: gnyis pa ni 'khrul snang nyon mongs la ma spyad
NK063(gu)001:13224: na bden don chos nyid rtogs pa'i dus med la
NK063(gu)001:13225: / de la dpyad pas de rtogs pa'i blo myur ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:13226: de gnyis la rdzas tha dad med pa'i phyir dper
NK063(gu)001:13227: na brdzun snang sbrul la ma dpyad na bden don
NK063(gu)001:13228: thag par rtogs dus med la /
NK063(gu)001:13229: de la dpyad pas der rtogs pa myur ba bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:13230: tha ma ni gdul bya skal pa can dag nyon
NK063(gu)001:13231: mongs pa ma spangs par 'bras bu thob par gsungs
NK063(gu)001:13232: pa'i bka' dang theg pa 'di gzhan las khyad par
NK063(gu)001:13233: 'phags shing zab mo'i don yin snyam du gus pa'i
NK063(gu)001:13235: gnyis pa mi dor ba'i dam tshig ni dkar rtsi
NK063(gu)001:13236: dmar rtsi zhes pa la sogs te dam rdzas lnga
NK063(gu)001:13238: mi dor zhes pas dor bya ma yin zhing dang du blang bya yin pas /
NK063(gu)001:13241: grub pa bzhi dang nad lnga bsal //
NK063(gu)001:13242: thun mong dgongs pa lnga don gnyer //
NK063(gu)001:13243: gtsang rme'i rtog pa gzhom phyir blang //
NK063(gu)001:13245: grub pa bzhi ni le'u bco brgyad par bstan la /
NK063(gu)001:13246: nad lnga ji ltar sel na dri chen gyis dug nad dang /
NK063(gu)001:13249: sha chen gyis mdze nad dang /
NK063(gu)001:13250: byang sems gyis tsha ba'i nad rnams sel lo //
NK063(gu)001:13251: thun mong gi dgos pa ni rang bzhin gyi nus pa lnga yod de /
NK063(gu)001:13252: dri chen dang du blangs pas tshe ring ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13254: sha chen gyis mthu che la /
NK063(gu)001:13256: byang sems kyis mi brjed pa'i gzungs thob pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13257: mchog gi dgos pa yang rigs dang ye shes dang sku la sogs lnga lnga 'grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:13259: dri chen gyis rigs las de pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:13260: ye shes las stong pa nyid kyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:13261: sku las chos kyi sku grub bo //
NK063(gu)001:13262: de bzhin dri chus las kyi rigs dang /
NK063(gu)001:13263: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK063(gu)001:13264: sha chen gyis rat+na'i rigs dang mnyam nyid ye shes rdo rje'i sku'o //
NK063(gu)001:13265: rak+tasa pad+ma'i rigs dang so sor rtog pa'i ye shes mngon byang ngo //
NK063(gu)001:13266: byang sems kyis rdo rje'i rigs dang me long ye shes longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku 'grub bo //
NK063(gu)001:13267: de ltar mchog thun gnyis 'grub byed kyi rdzas yin pa'i phyir dang du blang bya yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13268: tha ma ni gong ltar rtsa ba lnga las bla ma rgyun du bkur ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13269: yang dag pa'i lam du zhugs pa la byams par bya ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13270: gsang ba'i don rnams phyir mi smra bar byed pa dang gsum ni bsrung ba'i dam tshig yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:13271: bla na med pa byang chub kyi sems mi spang ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13272: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad pa gnyis ni sgrub pa'i dam tshig ste /
NK063(gu)001:13273: de ltar lnga po de rtsa ba yin te /
NK063(gu)001:13274: ji srid nyams na rigs chad de 'bras bu med pa nyid du 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:13275: de ltar yang rdo rje las /
NK063(gu)001:13276: lam dang sgrub pa'i rtsa ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:13277: dngos grub kun gyi rtsa ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:13278: 'di dag nyams na kun nyams pas //
NK063(gu)001:13279: rtsa ba zhes su bshad pa yin //
NK063(gu)001:13281: yang mi spang ba ni nyon mongs pa lnga dang /
NK063(gu)001:13282: mi dor ba bdud rtsi lnga ste lnga tshan gnyis te bcu ni yan lag gi yin te /
NK063(gu)001:13283: mi spang ba nyams na nyan thos su gol zhing /
NK063(gu)001:13284: mi dor ba nyams na phyi par gol la /
NK063(gu)001:13285: lta spyod ma 'brel bas nang par mi tshud pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13286: de yang spyir dam tsig gces pa'i mtshon bya sgra
NK063(gu)001:13287: bshad na samskri ta'i skad las sa ma ya zhes
NK063(gu)001:13288: pa'i sgra la sam b+ha ra'i rkyen byin pas sdom
NK063(gu)001:13289: pa la 'jug pa la sogs mang du yod kyang
NK063(gu)001:13290: / 'da' daka'o zhes pa sgra rang gi ngo bo
NK063(gu)001:13291: ni dam tshig gam tha tshig yal gam zhes bya'o
NK063(gu)001:13294: nges tshig skyon yon skabs kyis bsgyur //
NK063(gu)001:13296: thub pa yon tan gyi dbang du na dam zhes
NK063(gu)001:13297: pa ni sgo gsum sdom par gnas pas gnas ngan
NK063(gu)001:13298: par mi gtong ba'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:13299: ji skad du rgyas pa las /
NK063(gu)001:13300: mi gtong phyir na dam zhes bya //
NK063(gu)001:13301: gzung du gyur pas dam zhes bya //
NK063(gu)001:13303: tshig ces pa de nyid bden pa'i tshig yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:13304: des mtshon pa ni ma nor ba'i lam yin pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:13306: rdo rje ma nor lam ston pa //
NK063(gu)001:13307: de la yang ni tshig ces bya //
NK063(gu)001:13309: gnyis pa ma thub pa'i skyon gyi dbang du na
NK063(gu)001:13310: dam zhes pa ni bsrung bya las 'da' bar dka'
NK063(gu)001:13311: ba'i phyir dang / tshig ces pa ni ji srid
NK063(gu)001:13312: 'das na mi khom pa'i gnas su 'tshig pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:13313: ba'i phyir dang / te / de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:13314: yang na de bzhin bka' bcag na //
NK063(gu)001:13318: gzhi chos thams cad ye nas mnyam pa nyid yin
NK063(gu)001:13319: pa'i don la de ltar rtogs pa'i blo dang ldan
NK063(gu)001:13321: le'u bcu gcig pa ltar rgyu shes pa mnyam pa'i gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab nas /
NK063(gu)001:13322: mnyam par gnas pa dang de ltar rtogs pa'i blo
NK063(gu)001:13323: gcig tu sbyor ba yis de'i don las mi 'da'
NK063(gu)001:13324: ba'i phyir mnyam pa'i dam tshig ste /
NK063(gu)001:13325: de'i ngang la gnas na 'bras bu mnyam rdzogs chen
NK063(gu)001:13326: po ni kun tu bzang po dbye ba med pa'i
NK063(gu)001:13328: de'i 'ga' zla mnyam pa las 'das te tha dad
NK063(gu)001:13329: du rtog na sangs rgyas thob pa ma yin no
NK063(gu)001:13330: zhes skyon dang bcas te bstan no //
NK063(gu)001:13332: lnga pa ni dam tshig ces pa'i sgra don bshad zin to //
NK063(gu)001:13333: de la sogs pa'i bsrung bya ji snyed pa rnams ni rang gis sems yin te /
NK063(gu)001:13335: dam tshig dam tshig ces bya ba //
NK063(gu)001:13336: gud na yod pa ma yin te //
NK063(gu)001:13337: rang gi lta ba dam tshig yin //
NK063(gu)001:13339: rdo rjee zhes pa ni sems la rdo rjer 'jog
NK063(gu)001:13340: pa'i mtshan lnga las 'dir rang bzhin gnyis su med
NK063(gu)001:13341: pa'i phyir te / sems dang bsrung bya tha dad
NK063(gu)001:13342: med pa'o de bsrung bya gzhan las khyad par 'phags
NK063(gu)001:13344: de ltar gnyis med kyi don las dus gsum gyi
NK063(gu)001:13345: sangs rgyas thams cad yang mi 'da' ba'i phyir rgyal
NK063(gu)001:13346: ba kun gyi thugs dam mam bdag nyid yin no
NK063(gu)001:13347: // drug pa ni lam rim gyis pa'i dbang du
NK063(gu)001:13348: bsrung mtshams kyi dmigs phyed par bya ba'i dam tshig
NK063(gu)001:13349: rnam grangs kyi bshad pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:13350: de yang gnyis las dang po ni /
NK063(gu)001:13351: rnam grangs su bgrang bya'i gzhi gong du bstan pa'i
NK063(gu)001:13352: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga la ni brgya drug cu
NK063(gu)001:13354: gcig la'ang zhes pa lnga po re re la'o //
NK063(gu)001:13355: gnyis dang zhes pa shes rab lta bas rtogs pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13356: thabs spyod pas grub pa gnyis gnyis te bcu phrag gcig dang por gzhag go //
NK063(gu)001:13357: gsum zhes pas zung lnga po re re la yang
NK063(gu)001:13358: sgo gsum gyi bsrung bya bcu phrag gsum gsum ste
NK063(gu)001:13359: brgya lnga bcu'o // de'i steng du gong gi rtsa ba gnyis te brgya drug cur dabye'o //
NK063(gu)001:13360: de dag phra rgyas kyi dbang du brtsis na /
NK063(gu)001:13361: dang po bla med mi spang ba'i bcu phrag gsum
NK063(gu)001:13362: ni yi dam lha la zhi ba'i lhag pa'i lha
NK063(gu)001:13364: khroo bo la yang de bzhin te nyi shu thun
NK063(gu)001:13365: mong dang thun min gyi tshad med pa bzhi bzhi
NK063(gu)001:13366: brgyad kyi steng du don dam kun rdzob kyi byang
NK063(gu)001:13367: sems gnyis dang bcu ste de ltar sum cu'o //
NK063(gu)001:13368: gnyis pa bla ma bkur ba la yang sgo gsum gyi bcu bcu ste /
NK063(gu)001:13369: dang po lus kyi bcu ni /
NK063(gu)001:13370: phra rgyas las ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:13371: lus kyi bsrung ba brdeg la sogs //
NK063(gu)001:13372: 'thing slad tsam du'ang bya ba min //
NK063(gu)001:13373: 'dod yon lnga yis mchod pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:13374: gsang ba'i snod du dug mi spyod //
NK063(gu)001:13375: 'gro ba drang ba'i phyogs spang dang //
NK063(gu)001:13376: gdan dang gdan sa mi rlom shing //
NK063(gu)001:13378: rgyan 'dogs gzi ldir de bzhin te //
NK063(gu)001:13379: ma rabs spyod pa kun spangs pa //
NK063(gu)001:13380: spyod lam zon chags bsti gnas bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:13384: rdzun dang phra ma tshig rtsub dang //
NK063(gu)001:13385: 'khyal pa nam yang mi bya ste //
NK063(gu)001:13386: be phogs ma yin rdabs skad dor //
NK063(gu)001:13387: lkog tu tshul brjod nyams par 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:13388: yon tan brjod cing snyan par smra //
NK063(gu)001:13389: ca co la sogs ma yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13392: dam pa ston pa'i bla ma la //
NK063(gu)001:13393: chags dang gti mug nga rgyal dang //
NK063(gu)001:13394: phrag dog dug lnga'i sems mi bya //
NK063(gu)001:13395: ngan du mi sems lci ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13396: pha ma yi dam lhar bsam dang //
NK063(gu)001:13397: rtag tu gdung ba rgyun mi gcad //
NK063(gu)001:13399: gsum pa sngags dang phyag rgya la yang bcu phrag gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:13401: zhi khro'i phyag rgya bdun gnyis dang //
NK063(gu)001:13402: phyogs bcing rten dang khang gi sngags //
NK063(gu)001:13403: rtsa ba bskyed dang las bzhi'i sngags //
NK063(gu)001:13404: dbang bskur byin bsdu gsang sngags dang //
NK063(gu)001:13405: spyan drang bstim brtan phyag 'tshal mchod //
NK063(gu)001:13407: bzhi pa yang dag pa'i lam du zhugs pa la byams par bya ba la yang sum cu ste /
NK063(gu)001:13409: bsnun dang ma byin blang mi bya //
NK063(gu)001:13410: zla zer ma yin gzungs mi spyad //
NK063(gu)001:13411: lta spyod mtho ba'i gong mi gcad //
NK063(gu)001:13412: dbang dang dam tshig de bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:13413: kun tu'ang bag zon 'khrig can dang //
NK063(gu)001:13414: bkur sti mchod byed dga' bar spyod //
NK063(gu)001:13417: rdzun sogs rnam bzhi spang ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:13418: bya ba mi smra tshul mi brjod //
NK063(gu)001:13419: snyan dang zhe sa gsong por smra //
NK063(gu)001:13420: bden smra sri zhu'i sgra byed pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13423: sems kyis sngon bzhin dug lnga dor //
NK063(gu)001:13424: rngan dang skyo sems dor ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:13425: mig 'drar blta zhing gdung bar bya //
NK063(gu)001:13426: gnod sems spang ba rnam bcu'o //
NK063(gu)001:13428: tha ma gsang ba gzhan la mi bstan pa yang bcu phrag gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:13429: spyi dang bar gsang bzhi bzhi dang //
NK063(gu)001:13430: 'os dang gnyer gtad rnam pa bcu //
NK063(gu)001:13431: sems kyis bstan par mi bsam zhing //
NK063(gu)001:13432: ngag gis brjod par yongs mi bya //
NK063(gu)001:13433: lus brdas bstan min sum cu'o //
NK063(gu)001:13435: gnyis pa yan lag gi rnam grangs ni /
NK063(gu)001:13436: yan lag zhes pa mi spong zhing mi dor ba'i
NK063(gu)001:13437: lam 'dis 'bras bu grub pa'i grogs byed pa'am gong
NK063(gu)001:13438: gi rtsa ba'i cha rkyen du 'gyur ba'i phyir ro
NK063(gu)001:13439: // dam tshig ces pa bshad zin /
NK063(gu)001:13440: lnga gnyis la zhes pa mi spang ba lnga dang /
NK063(gu)001:13441: mi dor ba lnga ste bcu'o //
NK063(gu)001:13442: gcig la'ang zhes pa de dag re re la'ang bcu
NK063(gu)001:13443: phrag gnyis su zhes pas bdag don du bcu dang
NK063(gu)001:13444: / gzhan don du bcu ste nyi shur dabye'o //
NK063(gu)001:13446: gti mug gi nyi shu ni /
NK063(gu)001:13447: ji skad du phra rgyas las /
NK063(gu)001:13448: thabs kyi mdzad pas mi 'byed cing //
NK063(gu)001:13449: shes rab gnyis med mi 'byed pa'i //
NK063(gu)001:13450: gti mug bcu gnyis 'da' mi byed //
NK063(gu)001:13452: zhe sdang gi nyi shu ni /
NK063(gu)001:13453: zhing bcu thabs kyis mdzad pas 'joms //
NK063(gu)001:13454: shes rab rang bzhin med pas sgrol //
NK063(gu)001:13456: nga rgyal gyi nyi shu ni /
NK063(gu)001:13457: zhing bcu thabs kyis zil gnon dang //
NK063(gu)001:13458: shes rab rang bzhin med pas gnod //
NK063(gu)001:13461: zhing bcu thugs rjes mi gtong ba //
NK063(gu)001:13462: rigs lnga yum la thabs kyis rol //
NK063(gu)001:13463: ting 'dzin thabs dbang rang bzhin sbyar //
NK063(gu)001:13466: phrag dog gi nyi shu ni /
NK063(gu)001:13467: ma rtog gnyis dang log rtog gnyis //
NK063(gu)001:13468: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems //
NK063(gu)001:13469: gsang sngags phyi pa'i theg pa gsum //
NK063(gu)001:13470: gsang sgor mdzad pas mi chud dang //
NK063(gu)001:13471: shes rab dman pas mi chud pa //
NK063(gu)001:13472: phrag dog chen po'i dam tshig go //
NK063(gu)001:13474: gnyis pa mi dor ba yang /
NK063(gu)001:13476: sgrub rdzas lnga la rtsa ba brgyad //
NK063(gu)001:13477: brgyad cha re zhing dwangs snyigs lnga //
NK063(gu)001:13478: re re'ang rnam pa bcur ni 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:13479: zhing bcu'i bdud rtsi de bzhin pas //
NK063(gu)001:13480: rnam par dbye ba nyi shu 'gyur //
NK063(gu)001:13482: dam rdzas lnga la re re'ang nyi shu nyi shu ste /
NK063(gu)001:13483: de yang 'gro ba spyi'i dam rdzas rtsa ba brgyad dwangs snyigs gnyis dang bcu /
NK063(gu)001:13484: 'gro ba bye brag gi zhing bcu'i dang nyi shu'o //
NK063(gu)001:13485: de yang dang por dkar rtsi rtsa ba brgyad la mngon pa phyi'i bzhi dang /
NK063(gu)001:13492: chu ser rnams mthar phyin pa las /
NK063(gu)001:13498: gnyis pa nang gi bzhi ni /
NK063(gu)001:13501: gshegs shul rdo rje chu ba /
NK063(gu)001:13502: pho brang be ga lig go //
NK063(gu)001:13503: phyi nang gi dwangs snyigs gnyis dang bcu /
NK063(gu)001:13505: de bzhin du dmar rtsi la yang mngon pa phyi'i bzhi ni /
NK063(gu)001:13509: gshegs lam mkhal ma'i khrag go //
NK063(gu)001:13510: nang gi ni gzhon nu dang por 'dzag pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:13511: gzungs ma mtshan ldan gyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:13512: slob dpon gyi nas g.yon pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:13513: rgyud lnga bsgral ba'i khrag go //
NK063(gu)001:13514: dwangs snyigs dang zhing bcur shes par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:13515: dri chen gyi phyi'i bzhi ni /
NK063(gu)001:13525: sha chen gyi phyi'i ni rkang lag bzhi'i nywa sha'o //
NK063(gu)001:13531: dri chu phyi'i ni ba dmar ser dang /
NK063(gu)001:13535: nang gi ni drang srong sgom chen dang /
NK063(gu)001:13539: de dag la dwangs snyigs gnyis gnyis dang bcu /
NK063(gu)001:13540: zhing bcu'i dang nyi shu nyi shu'o //
NK063(gu)001:13541: gzhung don tha ma'i skabs su /
NK063(gu)001:13542: nyams na bskang pas rdzogs pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:13544: ji srid bsrung bya las 'das na bskang zhing bshags pa'i thabs yod do //
NK063(gu)001:13545: de med na nyams pa bden dngos su 'gyur te /
NK063(gu)001:13546: nyams par bden la bskang ba'i thabs med pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:13547: des na 'dis bsrung bya ni gser dngul zhom pa ltar nyams kyang slar gso ba'i thabs yod de /
NK063(gu)001:13548: ji skad du rdo rje las /
NK063(gu)001:13549: gal te rtsa ba'i dam nyams na //
NK063(gu)001:13550: bla ma grogs po brgya dag la //
NK063(gu)001:13551: bzlas pa bye ba bdun 'bum bya //
NK063(gu)001:13552: sbyin sreg 'bum phrag bcu gcig go //
NK063(gu)001:13553: de nas slar yang bslang ba'am //
NK063(gu)001:13554: bla mas gnang nas gnas par bya //
NK063(gu)001:13555: zhes pa rtsa ba'i bskang thabs dang /
NK063(gu)001:13557: yan lag dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK063(gu)001:13558: zla ba bdun du smra gcad bya //
NK063(gu)001:13559: sbyin sreg stong rtsa brgyad du bya //
NK063(gu)001:13560: bzlas pa bye ba 'bum phrag dang //
NK063(gu)001:13561: gtor ma khri khrag gcig tu bya //
NK063(gu)001:13562: de nas slar yang bslang ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:13563: dag dang tshangs par bsgrag par bya //
NK063(gu)001:13565: yang na mdo chen po las /
NK063(gu)001:13566: rtsa ba nyams dang yan lag nyams //
NK063(gu)001:13567: de bzhin zhor nyams zlas nyams lnga //
NK063(gu)001:13568: zhes nyams pa'i rnam grangs lnga la bskang thabs kyang de bzhin te /
NK063(gu)001:13570: gang de bskang bar bya ba'i thabs //
NK063(gu)001:13571: rnam pa lngar ni shes par bya //
NK063(gu)001:13572: las dang rdzas dang 'dun pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:13573: ting nge 'dzin dang de nyid do //
NK063(gu)001:13574: zhes pa ltar bskang ba yang yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13575: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u bcu dgu pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13577: // le'u nyi shu pa ni thun mong gi chos phrin las te /
NK063(gu)001:13578: 'di yang gong gi mngon rtogs zhi khro gnyis char
NK063(gu)001:13579: gyi dbang du ting nge 'dzin mjug gi rim pa'o
NK063(gu)001:13584: las kyi mkha' 'gro bskyang zhing gtor ma sbyin par bsngo ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13585: dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing go ba go lugs srung bya ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13586: yi ge brgya pas kha bskang zhing dge ba bsngo ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13587: rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin la gnas par bya ba las /
NK063(gu)001:13588: dang po ni 'dzab la dbye ba'am yang na dkyil
NK063(gu)001:13589: 'khor gsal btab la 'dzab drang zhing de'i 'phro 'du
NK063(gu)001:13590: byas te 'dzab bstod le'u nyer gcig par ston no
NK063(gu)001:13591: // gnyis pa tshogs la bzhi las /
NK063(gu)001:13592: drang zhing bsangs la brlabs nas mgron spyan drangs te /
NK063(gu)001:13593: mchod pa la zhi ba'i dbang du lha mo bcu gnyis kyis spyir dang /
NK063(gu)001:13595: 'dir khro bo'i dbang du yang spyi dang /
NK063(gu)001:13598: dang pos mchod cing bar pas bshags nas /
NK063(gu)001:13599: tha ma bstab cing phrin las bya ba la lugs gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:13600: gdul bya rgyas par byed pa la don bcu gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:13601: 'dod yon gyi lha mo h+aum gis bsdus te ling+ga bya ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13602: drag po'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13603: lha las la gzud pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13604: drag po'i dkyil 'khor las la bskul ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13607: sras mchog bton la phur bus gdab pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13609: mtshon cha'i char dbab pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13610: khrag 'thung gi dkyil 'khor spyan drang ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13612: dug gsum gyi mchod pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13613: rtsa ba'i sngags kyis bstab pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13614: de ltar lag len gyi don bcu gsum po 'dir
NK063(gu)001:13615: rdzas kyi sgo nas phrin las bya ba bzhi char
NK063(gu)001:13616: la gzhung don lnga lngar sdud do //
NK063(gu)001:13617: de la dang po drag po'i phrin las la gzhung
NK063(gu)001:13618: don lnga'i dang po dang lag len gyi chos bcu
NK063(gu)001:13619: gsum gyi dang po gnyis ling+ga bya ba yin te
NK063(gu)001:13621: gzhung bsgyur te 'og nas bdud rtsi lnga'am zhes pa
NK063(gu)001:13622: gang la bya ba gzas pa po'i zag rdzas so
NK063(gu)001:13623: // zas lnga la zhes pa ni nya sha til
NK063(gu)001:13624: sbrang bu ram 'bras rnams la ling+ga byas te pho
NK063(gu)001:13625: mo gang yin gyi mtshan ma dang /
NK063(gu)001:13626: gro shog la snying gar ming dpral bar rus barla la bla dwags dang bcas pa byas la /
NK063(gu)001:13627: rabs chad sogs kyi thod pa mtshan ngan du mgo bo lho nub mtshams su bstan la gzhag go //
NK063(gu)001:13628: gzhung gi gnyis par lag len gyi gnyis pa drag po'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK063(gu)001:13629: gsum pa lha las la gzud pa /
NK063(gu)001:13630: bzhi pa drag po'i dkyil 'khor las la bskul ba gsum sdud de /
NK063(gu)001:13631: de yang gong nas e'i zhes pa e ram gyis
NK063(gu)001:13632: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten mthing nag gru gsum 'byams
NK063(gu)001:13634: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog ces pas nang bcud kyi
NK063(gu)001:13635: skye 'gro thams cad drag po'i sprul pa phyag na
NK063(gu)001:13636: 'jigs pa'i mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs pa ste dz+wa
NK063(gu)001:13637: la ram zhes pas de dag gi sku las me
NK063(gu)001:13638: ri 'phro bar bskyed de las la gzud cing bskul
NK063(gu)001:13639: ba'o // gzhung gi gsum par lag len gyi lnga pa bden pa bdar ba /
NK063(gu)001:13640: drug pa pho nyas dgug pa /
NK063(gu)001:13641: bdun pa sras mchog gis gdab pa /
NK063(gu)001:13642: brgyad pa mtshon gyis gtub pa /
NK063(gu)001:13643: dgu pa mtshon cha'i char dbab pa /
NK063(gu)001:13644: bcu pa khrag 'thung gi dkyil 'khor spyan drang ba /
NK063(gu)001:13645: bcu gcig pa bstab pa rnams sdud de /
NK063(gu)001:13646: dang po bden pa bdar la /
NK063(gu)001:13647: sprul pa spros shing pho nya btang la btul nas
NK063(gu)001:13648: zhes pa sprul pa rnams kyis mtshang can btson du
NK063(gu)001:13649: zin pa ltar gzas pa po gnas nas bkug ste
NK063(gu)001:13650: lha dang phral nas skyabs med par 'dar phril phril
NK063(gu)001:13651: gnas pa la / pra be shas ling+ga dbye zhing
NK063(gu)001:13652: a be shas bstims la phyag rgya bzhis basngama bcing
NK063(gu)001:13654: de la lcags sam drag po'i shing la byas pa'i
NK063(gu)001:13655: rdo rje phur pa sras mchog badz+ra k+ai la yar
NK063(gu)001:13656: bskyed de / sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs nas gnas rkyang sgrags bdun du gdab bo //
NK063(gu)001:13657: de nas rdul phra rab tsam du gris gtubs par byas nas /
NK063(gu)001:13658: dgu pa mtshon cha'i char dbab /
NK063(gu)001:13659: bcu pa khrag 'thung gi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs la /
NK063(gu)001:13660: bcu gcig pa tshogs de rnams la bstabs te dbul ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:13661: de nas bcu gnyis pa dug gsum gyi mchod pa bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:13662: gzhu don bzhi pa ni lag len gyi tha ma rtsa ba'i sngags kyis bstab pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:13663: 'bar ba gtum chen rngams pa ni drag po khrag 'thung gi lha tshogs la /
NK063(gu)001:13664: stongs kyi sems gdul bya la khros pa'i yid bsgral
NK063(gu)001:13665: bar mos pa'i sems kyis bde bar gshegs pa la
NK063(gu)001:13666: mchod cing 'khor gyi mkha' 'gro la sbyin par bya
NK063(gu)001:13667: ste / bstod cing phrin las la bskul ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:13668: de'i yon tan ni sangs rgyas kyi bsod nams las
NK063(gu)001:13669: grub pa'i sku yang 'jig par nus na gzhan lta
NK063(gu)001:13670: ci smos so // gzhung don tha ma ni lu
NK063(gu)001:13671: gu rgyud kyi bro'i sgo nas phrin las bya ba
NK063(gu)001:13672: ci smos so // ste / de yang e b+h+r+aum
NK063(gu)001:13673: zhes pas dbus su drag po'i gzhal yas gru gsum
NK063(gu)001:13675: der drag po'i lha tshogs rnams sngags kyis bskyed pa'i dkyil 'khor du /
NK063(gu)001:13676: sgrub pa po rnams langs te mathe'u chung lu gu
NK063(gu)001:13677: rgyud du sbrel zhing bsdams nas phyag rgya bcings te
NK063(gu)001:13678: gsal bar gyur ba'i tshe na zhabs kyi bro stabs
NK063(gu)001:13679: kyis bskyod nas 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad phyogs
NK063(gu)001:13680: bcur mer mer du g.yos par bsams te /
NK063(gu)001:13681: lha rnams kyi gnas gsum nas 'od zer nag po
NK063(gu)001:13682: 'phros nas gzas pa po'i lus ngag yid gsum la
NK063(gu)001:13683: thim pas myos nas snying gas te bsgral bas rgyud
NK063(gu)001:13685: de ltar dbang dang rgyas pa dang zhi ba rnams la yang shes par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:13686: de nas lag len gyi dbang du rdo rje rgyal
NK063(gu)001:13687: pos tshogs dbang bskur nas thabs dang ldan par rol
NK063(gu)001:13688: zhing / 'khor gyi mkha' 'gro mchod phyir lhag ma gsog 'jog med par gzhag go //
NK063(gu)001:13689: gzhung gi gnyis pa lag len gyi gsum pa ni lhag ma ste /
NK063(gu)001:13690: de yang mdor bstan pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:13691: slas dang zhes pa sngon gtso bo ru dra bsgral
NK063(gu)001:13692: zhing de'i 'khor rnams dkyil 'khor gyi mu ran la
NK063(gu)001:13693: bkod de slas dang byi mor byas pa rnams so
NK063(gu)001:13694: // lhag ma zhes pa gong ltar dkyil 'khor lha
NK063(gu)001:13695: la phul ba'i lhag ma de rnal 'byor pa rol
NK063(gu)001:13696: pa'i phud yin pas lhag phud ces bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:13697: yang na tshogs la cha lngar byas te /
NK063(gu)001:13703: cha lnga'i tha ma yin pa'i phyir de skad du bya bar yang gsungs so //
NK063(gu)001:13704: de rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:13705: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kas //
NK063(gu)001:13706: zhes pa la sogs pa la lag len nor bu lugs dang chig rdzogs gnyis las /
NK063(gu)001:13707: gong ma'i phyag bzhes ltar chig rdzogs la bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:13708: lhag ma'i lha spyan drang zhing mchod pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13709: mchod bshags bya zhing smon lam gdab pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13710: 'dod gsol gdab cing bshags pa bya ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13711: gshegs su gsol zhing lhag dkyil bsdu ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:13712: dang po ni rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal gdab cing
NK063(gu)001:13713: gtor ma shod du phab la lhag phud bsres te
NK063(gu)001:13715: lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13716: snyan gsan dbab cing spyan drang ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13717: gdan dbul zhing dbang bskur te dam dpog pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13718: zil gyis mnan cing rigs lngar phye la mchod pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13719: dpal chen po'i nga rgyal gyis zhal gyi zer spros
NK063(gu)001:13720: te kha chus gdab pa rnams spyi'i las rim yin
NK063(gu)001:13721: la / bye brag tu mkha' 'gro la sogs rang
NK063(gu)001:13722: rang gi mtshan nyid brjod cing mchod pa phul nas
NK063(gu)001:13725: zhes pa la sogs te gnas lnga'am bdun la sogs gang byed ni bye brag gi las rim mo //
NK063(gu)001:13727: phud la 'tshal skal mi ldan gyis //
NK063(gu)001:13728: lhag ma zhal chab bran la gsol //
NK063(gu)001:13730: de nas mjug gi rim pa'i don bzhi pa man chad lag len du shes par bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:13731: gzhung don gsum pa ni sla bar zad do //
NK063(gu)001:13732: 'on kyang mdzod ldan chen mo zhes pa ni rgyu ming 'bras la btags pa ste /
NK063(gu)001:13733: rgyu kun gzhi'i rtog pa ni chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pa'i phyir mdzod ces bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:13734: de'i miing gis de gnas su dag pa'i lha mo koo r+ai ma la yang mdzod ldan zhes bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:13735: yang na 'jig rten gyi ming snying khrin la btags pa lta bu yang yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13737: gong gi thabs de dag gis phrin las byed pa
NK063(gu)001:13738: la shes rab dang bral na mi grub pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:13739: gzungs ma gang la brteen te bya ba ni /
NK063(gu)001:13740: dape'am brda'i sgo nas bstan pa ste shing ljon pa
NK063(gu)001:13741: ni zhes pa de ni 'dzer thug med cing mnyen
NK063(gu)001:13742: pa ltar / zhi ba'i phrin las kyi tshe yum rgyud dul ba zhig gis bya ste /
NK063(gu)001:13743: ji skad du rdo rje las /
NK063(gu)001:13744: gang bong lus mdzes mdog dkar rtsub //
NK063(gu)001:13745: ngos su lus kyang de bzhin te //
NK063(gu)001:13746: skad gsal sngags zlos mi skyo ba //
NK063(gu)001:13747: khro spangs sems rgyud zhi las bya //
NK063(gu)001:13749: lcug phran ni skye zla mang bas tshal ltar rgyas pa'i yum ni spun zla mang ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:13751: ba lang ser mo gru bzhi rgyas //
NK063(gu)001:13752: rna ba 'gram barlanga ring ba la //
NK063(gu)001:13753: sha rgyas yan lag zla mang zhing //
NK063(gu)001:13754: las kyi rim pa la mkhas pa //
NK063(gu)001:13756: sdong gcig dang ni zhes pa zla med pa ltar /
NK063(gu)001:13757: dbang gi yum spun zla med pa zhig ste /
NK063(gu)001:13759: dmar mo bzhin mdog zla gam la //
NK063(gu)001:13760: rang nyid gcig pur gnas pa ste //
NK063(gu)001:13761: thabs mkhas brtson 'grus che ba ni //
NK063(gu)001:13762: dbang du bsdu ba'i yum du shis //
NK063(gu)001:13764: mes reg ces pa ni shing 'gal dum ltar drag
NK063(gu)001:13765: po'i yum ni sdug bsngal gyi mes reg pa yugs
NK063(gu)001:13767: nag mo gru gsum rtsid mgo ma //
NK063(gu)001:13768: khro gnyer can la gel bag chags //
NK063(gu)001:13769: gtum barlanga 'dzem bag med pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:13770: sngags zlos brtul zhugs ldan pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13772: gtso bo'i sems ni don dang /
NK063(gu)001:13774: dang po ni chos nyid ji bzhin pa rtogs pa'i ngang nas bya ba ste /
NK063(gu)001:13775: phrin las bzhi char la khyab byed du dgos pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13776: gnyis pa ni dang bas zhes pa zhi ba'i tshe gdug sems kyis ma gos pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13777: dga' bas zhes pa ni rgyas pa'i tshe rtogs pa
NK063(gu)001:13778: dang ye shes tshe dang bsod nams la sogs 'phel
NK063(gu)001:13780: chags pa dang zhes pa dbang gi tshe thams cad
NK063(gu)001:13781: mngar 'dus par 'dod pas gdul bya la chags pa'o
NK063(gu)001:13782: // khros pas zhes pa drag po'i tshe gdug pa can gcod par 'dod pa'i sems so //
NK063(gu)001:13783: sems de dag dang ldan pas k+aa li ni phrin las te rab tu 'bad pas bya'o //
NK063(gu)001:13784: rgyud don rnam nges las le'u nyi shu pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13787: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa khro bo'i sku
NK063(gu)001:13788: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga la bstod pa
NK063(gu)001:13790: dbang chen dkyil 'khor la bstod pa ni yang na 'di ltar /
NK063(gu)001:13791: rdo rje brag chen sra ba po //
NK063(gu)001:13792: zhes pa phyag rgya chen po'i khro bo thams cad
NK063(gu)001:13793: kyi gzhal yas khang gi gzhi rdo rjee brag gis
NK063(gu)001:13794: gtams pa'o // chu bo sdud chen po ni rak+ta'i rgya mtsho zhal du sdud cing gsol ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:13795: me ste kun 'bar che ni me ri smug nag gi klong na bzhugs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13796: 'thor rlung che ni zhal dang shangs nas drag po 'thor byed kyi rlung byung ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:13797: yang na de dag don gyi dbang du gzhi chos
NK063(gu)001:13798: nyid mtha' gang du yang mi 'gyur ba ni rdo
NK063(gu)001:13800: chos can ji snyed pa rnams chos nyid ji bzhin par sdud pa ni chu yin la /
NK063(gu)001:13801: shes rab chen pos ma rig pa'i bud shing sreg pa ni me yin te /
NK063(gu)001:13802: des sgrib pa thams cad mi gnas par 'thor bar
NK063(gu)001:13803: byed pa ni rlung yin no snyam du'ang sems so
NK063(gu)001:13804: // rgyud don rnam nges las le'u nyer gcig pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13806: // de ltar de yan chad nas gsum pa'i smad man chad kyis rgyud don dngos bstan nas /
NK063(gu)001:13807: spyi don bzhi pa rgyud kyi dgos 'brel ni gong
NK063(gu)001:13808: ma dag gi khyab byed yin pa'i phyir shugs la
NK063(gu)001:13809: bstan zhing / 'on kyang yan lag bzhir 'dir yang stong thun ltar 'chad pa pos bsnyad do //
NK063(gu)001:13810: spyi don tha ma gdams shing gtad pa ni le'u tha mas ston te /
NK063(gu)001:13812: rang bzhin gyi rgyud ye nas sangs rgyas pa las mi 'gyur bas 'bod gcig par gdams pa ni /
NK063(gu)001:13813: rgyud dbu zhabs kyi brjod bya snang ba bzhi yin la /
NK063(gu)001:13814: de rjod byed 'dir sh+lo ka gnyis su bsdus nas bstan la /
NK063(gu)001:13815: de yang rang bzhin gyi snang ba sems kyi de
NK063(gu)001:13816: kho na nyid gcig tu bstan pa'i phyir rgyud ral
NK063(gu)001:13817: gri ltar rtsa ba nas bzung ste bshad pa zhes
NK063(gu)001:13820: kye kye zhes pa dang pos lhan cig pa dang /
NK063(gu)001:13821: gnyis pas go phye ba'i 'khor la 'bod pa'am /
NK063(gu)001:13822: yang na rang bzhin gyi rgyud gdams pa dang mtshon byed kyi rgyud gtad pa gnyis kyi phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:13824: 'khrul ngo na yod pa'i shar la sogs pa'i phyogs
NK063(gu)001:13825: bcu dang 'das ma 'ongs la sogs dus bzhis bsdus
NK063(gu)001:13826: pa 'khor ba'i rang bzhin 'di dag chos can /
NK063(gu)001:13827: yin lugs nas ye nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid yin te /
NK063(gu)001:13828: rang bzhin la ltos te 'khor ba'i chos su snang
NK063(gu)001:13829: zhing zhen pa'i tshe de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo
NK063(gu)001:13830: nyid yin pa las skad cig kyang ma bral zhing
NK063(gu)001:13831: / de der nges pa'i tshe 'khor ba'i chos rdzas gzhan du ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:13832: dper na dung ser 'dzin bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:13833: de ma grub ce na dngos po gnyis chos can /
NK063(gu)001:13835: rang bzhin dbyer med du ma grub ste gzhan dang gzhan yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:13836: dper na rta glang bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:13837: dbyer med ma yin pa la rdzas tha dad pas khyab cing /
NK063(gu)001:13838: 'dod na 'khor ba spangs kyang 'das pa mi 'grub ste /
NK063(gu)001:13839: rta spangs kyang glang po mi 'grub pa bzhin no //
NK063(gu)001:13840: gzhan yang lam dang theg pa rnams chos can /
NK063(gu)001:13842: dngos po gnyis rang bzhin tha dad yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:13843: dper na dung sol gnyis tha dad pas sol ba
NK063(gu)001:13844: la byi dor byas kyang dung gi dkar po mi
NK063(gu)001:13846: de ltar yang rgyas pa las /
NK063(gu)001:13847: so so'i rang bzhin nges she na //
NK063(gu)001:13848: yang dag lam gyis ba cos su med //
NK063(gu)001:13850: des na dngos po gnyis ldog pa gcig tu bsgrub pa yin gyis /
NK063(gu)001:13851: sgrub byed rang bzhin gyi gtan tshigs kyis bsgrub bya
NK063(gu)001:13852: dngos po gnyis kyi rang bzhin dbyer med du sgrub
NK063(gu)001:13853: pa 'di chos nyid kyi rig pa yin pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:13854: / blo des de ltar brtags na rtogs su rung la bslabs na 'grub tu rung bas /
NK063(gu)001:13855: gang gis de ltar rtogs shig sgrubs shig 'bod cig ces gdams pa yin no //
NK063(gu)001:13856: gnyis pa rgyud gtad pa dngos la ngag don gsum ste /
NK063(gu)001:13858: gang zag chos mig can la dang /
NK063(gu)001:13859: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro la gtad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13860: de dag re re la yang byed tshig bzhi bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)001:13866: de dag gsum char 'chad pa'i skyes bus gtad par mthun la /
NK063(gu)001:13867: gnyis pa yul ni gong gi gsum la'o //
NK063(gu)001:13868: gsum pa dgos ched ni sdud pa po la gtad
NK063(gu)001:13869: pas rgyal tshab rgyud kyi ston par dbyung ba'i dgos
NK063(gu)001:13870: pa yod la / gang zag chos mig can la
NK063(gu)001:13871: gtad pas gsang ba'i bstan pa 'di lha dang mi'i
NK063(gu)001:13872: 'jig rten du dar zhing rgyas par 'gyur zhing /
NK063(gu)001:13873: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro la gtad pas bstan pa
NK063(gu)001:13874: 'di yongs su mi nub pas brtan zhing bka'i byin
NK063(gu)001:13875: che ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK063(gu)001:13876: tha ma tshul la dang po sdud pa po la
NK063(gu)001:13877: gtad tshul ni gzhung bsgyur te 'og nas phyogs bcu
NK063(gu)001:13878: dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la dgongs
NK063(gu)001:13879: pa gsang ba'i snying po 'di las lhag pa'i don
NK063(gu)001:13881: 'di'i brjod bya ni yod pa sgro 'dogs dang med
NK063(gu)001:13882: pa skur 'debs la sogs pa'i mtha' thams cad zhi
NK063(gu)001:13883: ba ni bral bar ston pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK063(gu)001:13884: de'i rjod byed gsang ba'i snying po'i de kho na
NK063(gu)001:13885: nyid nges pa zhes bya ba mtshon byed kyi rgyud
NK063(gu)001:13886: 'di yang sgro skur thams cad dang bral ba yin
NK063(gu)001:13887: no // des na ston pa'i bdag nyid kyis chos
NK063(gu)001:13888: nyid de bzhin nyid nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung pa'i
NK063(gu)001:13889: rgyud 'di zungs shig ces sdud pa po la gtad
NK063(gu)001:13890: no // pa'o // gnyis pa ni gong nas de
NK063(gu)001:13891: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung gi phyag rgya
NK063(gu)001:13892: gsang chen nges pa mtshon byed kyi rgyud 'di /
NK063(gu)001:13893: ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa gang zhig rang gis
NK063(gu)001:13894: phyin ci ma log par rtogs nas gzhan la smra
NK063(gu)001:13895: bar gang byed pa de ston pa'i bdag nyid nga
NK063(gu)001:13896: dang dgongs pa mnyam pa yin te /
NK063(gu)001:13897: shes rab kyi spyan dang ldan zhing rig pa rtsal gyi dbang yang rdzogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:13898: gsum pa ni 'og nas de'i yang tshig bsgyur zhing 'bru yang bsgyur te /
NK063(gu)001:13899: de ltar rgyal ba'i thugs las skyes pa'i sras de
NK063(gu)001:13900: ni nges pa'i skyes bur lung bstan pa thob pa
NK063(gu)001:13901: yin te / de ni gang zhe na /
NK063(gu)001:13902: sa rab rig pa 'dzin pa sngags kyi sa la gnas pa yin pa'i phyir te /
NK063(gu)001:13904: sngags kyi rtogs pas mi gtong bas //
NK063(gu)001:13905: ting 'dzin nus pa'i mthu med kyang //
NK063(gu)001:13906: sa sbyong sems dpas bskyod du med //
NK063(gu)001:13907: bde gshegs nyid dang spyod yul gcig /
NK063(gu)001:13908: rig pa'i skyes bur lung bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13909: zhes pa ltar gang zag chos mig can la gtad pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13910: mkha' 'gro ma rnams la gtad tshul ni snod dang
NK063(gu)001:13911: ldan pa la 'phrad par byed cing snod min la
NK063(gu)001:13912: mi 'phrad par bya ba'i phyir bka'i srung mar gnyer
NK063(gu)001:13913: gtad pa ni 'di nas mi gsal yang /
NK063(gu)001:13914: rgyas pa'i lnga bcu pa las ji skad du /
NK063(gu)001:13915: gsang sngags kyi rgyal po 'di brtan zhing mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK063(gu)001:13916: 'jig rten gyi khams su yang yun ring du gnas par bya ba'i ched du /
NK063(gu)001:13917: 'byung po rnams kyi jo mo'i yang jo mo srin
NK063(gu)001:13918: mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang bcas pa la
NK063(gu)001:13919: sogs dang / yang de nyid las /
NK063(gu)001:13920: de yi gzungs la gtad pa ni //
NK063(gu)001:13921: yid bzhin mdzod 'byor bka' yi gnas //
NK063(gu)001:13922: nga yi thugs kyi snying po 'di //
NK063(gu)001:13923: phyogs bcu kun tu spel ba dang //
NK063(gu)001:13924: phyi nang theg pa bstan bcos dang //
NK063(gu)001:13925: stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi rnams //
NK063(gu)001:13926: spyod dang sgom dang bzlas pa dang //
NK063(gu)001:13927: sdom pa kun la mkhas pa yi //
NK063(gu)001:13928: sgom pa dran dang chos phyogs rnams //
NK063(gu)001:13929: bstan pa 'dzin par nus pa yis //
NK063(gu)001:13930: gsang ba snying po mchog tu gsungs pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13931: don tha ma rgyud rdzogs pa'i bya ba la gsum las /
NK063(gu)001:13933: zhes pa gong du bstan pa'i rgyud kyi dngos po rnams so //
NK063(gu)001:13934: de lhan cig pa dang go phye ba'i 'khor gnyis
NK063(gu)001:13935: la brjod cing bstan pas ston pa de bzhin gshegs
NK063(gu)001:13936: pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid kun tu bzang po
NK063(gu)001:13937: nyid / 'khor gyis chos thams cad dbyer med par gnas pa'i don mngon du byas shing /
NK063(gu)001:13938: rgyud kyi mdzad pa rdzogs pas dgyes nas /
NK063(gu)001:13939: 'khrul ngo na yod pa'i dus bzhi tha dad du 'dzin pa dag ste /
NK063(gu)001:13940: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su chos thams
NK063(gu)001:13941: cad ye nas 'bras bu sku gsung thugs mi zad
NK063(gu)001:13942: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor lhun gyis grub pa la
NK063(gu)001:13943: sel med pas stug po bkod pa'o //
NK063(gu)001:13944: mdzad pa de chos nyid kyi ngang du mdzes pa rgyan yin zhing /
NK063(gu)001:13945: de bzhin nyid du gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyis gnas par bzhugs so //
NK063(gu)001:13947: 'phags pa zhes pa rgyud 'di gzhan las don brgyad kyis khyad par du byas pas sam /
NK063(gu)001:13948: yang na 'bras bu thob pa'i dus dang /
NK063(gu)001:13950: thob pas 'bras bu'i ngo bo rnams gzhan las khyad
NK063(gu)001:13951: par du gyur par ston pa'i rgyud yin pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:13952: ro // rtog pa zhes pa ni kha cig 'khrul pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)001:13953: yang dag pa'i rtog pa gnyis las phyi ma'o zhes 'dod kyang /
NK063(gu)001:13954: 'di rgyud dang ming gi rnam grangs yin par sems so //
NK063(gu)001:13955: de ltar rtog pa 'di'i mtshan sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes bya la /
NK063(gu)001:13956: de'i le'u'i grangs ni stong phrag brgya pa gcig rgya gar na bzhugs pa las /
NK063(gu)001:13957: rtsa ba'i rgyud 'di ni rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ston pa'i mdo thams cad dang /
NK063(gu)001:13958: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi theg pa ston pa'i rgyud thams cad dang lung gi spyi yin te /
NK063(gu)001:13959: dbyer med kyi rgyud 'dis thams cad gtan la 'bebs pa'i phyir ro //
NK063(gu)001:13960: des na 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK063(gu)001:13961: kyi thugs kyi gsang ba las kyang ches gsang ba
NK063(gu)001:13964: de ltar thugs kyi rgyud gsang ba'i snying po de
NK063(gu)001:13965: kho na nyid nges pa zhes bya ba'i rgyud 'di'i
NK063(gu)001:13966: khungs gong ltar le'u stong phrag brgya pa bzhugs pa
NK063(gu)001:13967: las 'dir phyi nang gi theg pa thams cad ma
NK063(gu)001:13968: lus par spros te chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba
NK063(gu)001:13969: de dag gi bsgrub byar gyur pas 'bras bu'o //
NK063(gu)001:13970: de ni gang gis smad par mi nus shing gzhan
NK063(gu)001:13971: las khyad par du 'phags pas mchog yin pa'i phyir
NK063(gu)001:13973: de ltar 'bras bu'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba
NK063(gu)001:13974: 'di re zhig rdzogs so zhes pa ni bshad du
NK063(gu)001:13975: med pa'i don no zhes gsungs so //
NK063(gu)001:13976: rnam bshad 'di dag phal cher skyes chen bla ma'i gsung //
NK063(gu)001:13977: sgrub byed rig pas gnad don lung gis rab brgyan pa //
NK063(gu)001:13978: cung zad gzhan las rtogs pa yang yod rang gis sbyar //
NK063(gu)001:13979: bzod pa bla ma mkhas sogs dpang gyur rnams kyis bzhes //
NK063(gu)001:13980: 'ga' zhig ming stong bsgrigs pa tshig gi dpung bskyed dang //
NK063(gu)001:13981: yang dag theg pa'i bye brag tsam gyi don mthong la //
NK063(gu)001:13982: kun shes rlom shing chags sdang zhe 'dod kyis //
NK063(gu)001:13983: sma ba de dag phyogs re'i blo can yin //
NK063(gu)001:13984: dbang gis ma smin brgyud pa'i gdams pa med //
NK063(gu)001:13985: rnam dpyod blo bral gzhung don ma rtogs kyang //
NK063(gu)001:13986: dregs dang 'dod pa'i dbang gis 'chad 'dod la //
NK063(gu)001:13987: blo dman skal med dag gi yul 'di min //
NK063(gu)001:13988: rgya chen shes bya'i gnas la ma rmongs dang //
NK063(gu)001:13989: rab zab thabs kyis myur 'grod khyad par lam //
NK063(gu)001:13990: mthar phyin don gnyis phun tshogs bstan pa'i rgyan //
NK063(gu)001:13991: theg mchog 'dir ni kun kyang 'jug bya yin //
NK063(gu)001:13992: rdo rje'i tshig 'di dka' bas gang bshad pa //
NK063(gu)001:13993: de yi dge ba 'gro rnams la bsngo zhing //
NK063(gu)001:13994: blo ldan yul gyur rgyud don rnam nges 'di //
NK063(gu)001:13995: skal ba can la rab tu rgyas gyur cig /
NK063(gu)001:13996: rgyud don rnam par nges pa zhes bya ba dpal sman lung du mi bskyod rdo rjes sbyar ba'o //
NK063(gu)001:13999: // mdo sngags chos tshul tshang la ma nor ba //
NK063(gu)001:14000: mkhas shing grub brnyes rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i srol //
NK063(gu)001:14001: thub bstan snying po gsang sngags snga 'gyur ba'i //
